NK128(nyo)001:0: //+aa sh+tsa r+yam sha dra m+aa la n+aa ma si
NK128(nyo)001:1: n+na pa da su t+r+aa b+hi shi ny+tsa gu ru
NK128(nyo)001:2: pa ram pa ra s+ya bi mo k+sha bi ha
NK128(nyo)001:3: ra ti sma ///'dus pa mdo dbang gi bla ma
NK128(nyo)001:4: brgyud pa'i rnam thar ngo mtshar dad pa'i phreng ba
NK128(nyo)001:6: na ma s+sa rba gu ra be /
NK128(nyo)001:7: e ba d+ha rma d+ha t+wa sam skri t+aa pa
NK128(nyo)001:8: tha kya d+ha rma sh+aa ri ram ma h+aa su
NK128(nyo)001:9: kha / pra kri t+ya m+aa ru d+ha nir b+ho k+shithan+tarudapany+tsa b+ho ga ya p+ta ///
NK128(nyo)001:10: bla ma rnams la phyag 'tshal lo //
NK128(nyo)001:11: ngo bo chos dbyings 'dus ma byas pa ma bcos chos sku bde ba che /
NK128(nyo)001:12: rang bzhin ma 'gags lhun gyis grub pa lnga ldan zhi khro longs spyod rdzogs ///
NK128(nyo)001:13: ka ru na n+t+ra bi dza g+aa r+tha k+aa ra
NK128(nyo)001:14: ba t+sa ma ng+gu roo h+aa ni rma na s+ya
NK128(nyo)001:15: k+aa ya sh+aa stra kri ng+gi b+hu pra me d+ha
NK128(nyo)001:16: badz+ra t+aa tri b+ha k+ta na mya t+ya ///
NK128(nyo)001:17: thugs rje'i thabs kyis 'gro ba'i don mdzad dpal ldan
NK128(nyo)001:18: bla ma sprul pa'i skur ston mdzad khyab gdal blo
NK128(nyo)001:19: mchog rdo rjer gus pa gsum gyis phyag bagyi'o //
NK128(nyo)001:20: grangs med bskal par tshogs gnyis phul byung bas //
NK128(nyo)001:21: byang chub mngon mdzad ston mchog sh+aakya'i rgyal //
NK128(nyo)001:22: chags bral dam chos tshogs mchog dge 'dun bcas //
NK128(nyo)001:23: thar pa'i lam mkhan mchog de gus pas 'dud //
NK128(nyo)001:24: ston pa mchog des gsang chen theg pa'i lam //
NK128(nyo)001:25: ston phyir nyid las mi gzhan rgyal ba'i dbang //
NK128(nyo)001:26: khyab bdag pad+ma ka rar rnam sprul pa //
NK128(nyo)001:27: u rgyan rdo rje 'chang der snying nas 'dud //
NK128(nyo)001:28: zab don smin grol dbang bzhi'i chu bo'i rgyun //
NK128(nyo)001:29: skal bzang gdul bya'i zhing sar legs drangs te //
NK128(nyo)001:30: sku bzhi'i 'bras bu'i dga' ston mchog stsol ba //
NK128(nyo)001:31: rgya bod brgyud pa'i bla mar spyi bos btud //
NK128(nyo)001:32: rnam dag theg pa'i rim pa bcu gcig gi /
NK128(nyo)001:33: ma nor grub pa'i gzhung lugs cher zhugs te //
NK128(nyo)001:34: yongs rdzogs rgyal ba'i bstan pa tshul gcig tu //
NK128(nyo)001:35: 'chad mkhas snga 'gyur dri med tshad ma'i srol //
NK128(nyo)001:36: 'dus pa mdo dbang rgya mtsho chen po'i chos //
NK128(nyo)001:37: bshad dang sgrub pa'i lam la rab brten nas //
NK128(nyo)001:38: 'og min tshogs chen 'dus pa'i dkyil 'khor du //
NK128(nyo)001:39: grub pa'i sar bzhugs btud pa'i rnam thar bri //
NK128(nyo)001:40: de yang 'dus pa mdo'i dbang gi cho ga khrigs
NK128(nyo)001:41: su byas pa dkyil 'khor rgya mtsho'i 'jug ngogs bshad
NK128(nyo)001:42: pa la spyi don gsum gyi /
NK128(nyo)001:43: dang po yid ches shing khungs btsun par bya ba'i
NK128(nyo)001:44: phyir gang las byung ba'i brgyud pa bshad pa la
NK128(nyo)001:45: gnyis te / bla ma brgyud pa'i tshul bshad pa dang /
NK128(nyo)001:46: brgyud pa'i bla ma de rnams kyi lo rgyus rtogs brjod rnam thar bshad pa'o //
NK128(nyo)001:47: dang po bla ma brgyud pa'i tshul bshad pa ni gzhung nyid du bshad zin la /
NK128(nyo)001:48: gnyis pa rtogs brjod rnam thar bshad pa logs su
NK128(nyo)001:49: 'chad par khas blang pas de nyid 'dir bri bar
NK128(nyo)001:50: bya ba'i de la dang po ston pa byon tshul
NK128(nyo)001:51: / bar du snga 'gyur gyi bstan pa byung tshul /
NK128(nyo)001:52: mthar bstan 'dzin gyi bla ma brgyud pa'i tshul ji
NK128(nyo)001:53: ltar byon par rnam par thar par dang bcas pa'o
NK128(nyo)001:54: // de las dang po nyid mdo tsam smos na /
NK128(nyo)001:55: sgyu 'phrul rtsa ba'i rgyud gsang ba'i snying po las /
NK128(nyo)001:56: de nas de bzhin gshegs pa thams cad las /
NK128(nyo)001:57: thugs rje chen po'i byin gyis brlabs zhes bya ba'i /
NK128(nyo)001:58: rig pa'i skyes bu thub pa drug de bzhin gshegs
NK128(nyo)001:59: pa'i sku dang gsung dang thugs rdo rje las 'thon
NK128(nyo)001:61: rigs thams cad kyi bdag po drug pa kun tu
NK128(nyo)001:62: bzang po'i thugs spros bral ye shes kyi cha las
NK128(nyo)001:63: / thugs rje chen po'i byin brlabs gdul bya la
NK128(nyo)001:64: cir yang 'char ba'i rig pa'i skyes bu thub pa
NK128(nyo)001:65: drug ston pa de nyid kyi sku gsung thugs rdo
NK128(nyo)001:66: rje las ma g.yos bzhin du thon tshul bshad nas
NK128(nyo)001:67: / / chos sku'i zhing khams phyogs bcu mtha' yas mu med pa dang /
NK128(nyo)001:68: longs sku'i zhing stong mtshams sbyor yongs su 'das pa longs sku nyag gcig gi zhing khams /
NK128(nyo)001:69: stong gsum gyi stong chen po sprul sku nyag cig gi zhing khams rnams las /
NK128(nyo)001:70: sprul sku'i zhing khams stong gsum gyi stong chen po'i 'jig rten gyi khams re rer /
NK128(nyo)001:71: sprul sku bcom ldan 'das re rer snang ba'i ston pa phun sum tshogs pa re res /
NK128(nyo)001:72: 'dul ba rnam pa bzhi'i gdul bya 'dul ba ni bstan pa phun sum tshogs pa ste /
NK128(nyo)001:73: de lta bu'i tshul gyis 'gro ba lnga'i don mdzad de zhes ston par byed pa la /
NK128(nyo)001:75: 'thon nas kyang las kyi dbang gi s+n+rel bzhi dang
NK128(nyo)001:76: yan man gyi 'jig rten drug gi phyogs bcu mtha'
NK128(nyo)001:77: yas mu med pa'i stong gsum gyi stong chen po
NK128(nyo)001:78: re rer / thub pa chen po bcom ldan 'das
NK128(nyo)001:79: re res 'dul ba rnam pa bzhis 'gro ba lnga'i
NK128(nyo)001:80: re rer / don mdzad do // zhes gsung ba'i phyir /
NK128(nyo)001:81: de ltar mi rnams kyi thub pa sh+aakya seng ge'i
NK128(nyo)001:82: 'di nyid theg pa thun mong ba rnams kyi snang
NK128(nyo)001:83: ngor mdzad pa bcu gnyis kyi sgo nas sems can
NK128(nyo)001:85: snga 'gyur ba'i lugs la theg dman gyi ngor rgyal
NK128(nyo)001:86: bu don 'grub sems can 'ching ba kun ldan zhig
NK128(nyo)001:87: yin pa la / ser skya'i grong khyer gyi sgor
NK128(nyo)001:88: skye ba'i tshul bstan nas rgyal srid spangs te rab
NK128(nyo)001:89: yin pa la / tu byung / lo drug dka'
NK128(nyo)001:90: ba spyad mthar nyan thos kyi ngor dgra bcom pa'i
NK128(nyo)001:91: yin pa la / tu byung / 'bras bu /
NK128(nyo)001:92: rang rgyal gyi ngor yid bzhin bde ba mchog gi
NK128(nyo)001:93: 'bras bu bse ru'am ne tso lta bu thob la
NK128(nyo)001:94: yin pa la / tu byung / 'bras bu /
NK128(nyo)001:95: / sngags phyi rgyud rnams kyi ngor lha'i bu dam
NK128(nyo)001:96: pa tog dkar po de byang sems sa mthar phyiin
NK128(nyo)001:97: pa srid pa tha ma pa skye ba gcig gis
NK128(nyo)001:98: thogs pa can zhig mi'i rgyal bu don 'grub tu
NK128(nyo)001:100: khyim nas khyim med pa rab tu byung zhing /
NK128(nyo)001:101: chu bo ne rany+dza na'i 'gram na dka' thub mdzad
NK128(nyo)001:102: pa'i tshe sangs rgyas rnams kyi bskul bas mi g.yo
NK128(nyo)001:103: ba'i ting nge 'dzin las bzhengs te rnam smin gyi
NK128(nyo)001:105: yid kyi lus 'og min du byon te /
NK128(nyo)001:106: don dam byang sems bskyed pas sangs rgyas rnams kyis dbang bskur nas /
NK128(nyo)001:107: dpal kun rig rnam par snang mdzad du mngon par
NK128(nyo)001:108: rdzogs par sangs rgyas te sum cu rtsa gsum gyi
NK128(nyo)001:109: gnas su babs te lha yul gyi gdul bya rnams
NK128(nyo)001:111: mi'i yul gyi gdul bya'i don du slar yang dka'
NK128(nyo)001:112: thub kyi khogs par zhugs te byang chub kyi shing
NK128(nyo)001:113: drung du sangs rgyas par bzhed cing /
NK128(nyo)001:114: de'i tshul rigs pa'i shes byed du /
NK128(nyo)001:116: nyan thos rnams la dgra bcom gzugs //
NK128(nyo)001:117: rang rgyal rnams la bse ru'i tshul //
NK128(nyo)001:118: gzhan yang theg mchog rim pa bzhin //
NK128(nyo)001:119: 'og min bla med gnas mchog tu //
NK128(nyo)001:120: sku ni rnam par snang mdzad tshul //
NK128(nyo)001:122: 'on kyang mthun snang du grags pa byang chub sems dpa'i theg pa ltar bshad kyang rung ste /
NK128(nyo)001:123: gzhan yang theg mchog rim pa bzhin /
NK128(nyo)001:125: de la rang lugs su mdzad pa brgyad dang /
NK128(nyo)001:126: spyir mdzad pa bcu gnyis su bshad pa'i /
NK128(nyo)001:134: chos kyi 'khor lo bskor ba dang /
NK128(nyo)001:135: cho 'phrul chen po bstan pa dang /
NK128(nyo)001:136: mya ngan las 'das pa la sogs pa ston pa'i thub pas /
NK128(nyo)001:137: zhes gsungs mod kyang mdzad pa bcu gnyis khongs su
NK128(nyo)001:138: don gyis mdzad pa brgyad kyang 'du bas de'i phyir
NK128(nyo)001:139: phyi ma ltar mdzad pa bcu gnyis su 'chad rigs
NK128(nyo)001:140: la / de ltar mdzad pa bcu gnyis kyi tshul de nyid ji lta bu zhe na /
NK128(nyo)001:142: dga' ldan gnas nas 'pho ba dang //
NK128(nyo)001:143: lhums su zhugs dang bltams pa dang //
NK128(nyo)001:144: bzo yi gnas la mkhas pa dang //
NK128(nyo)001:145: btsun mo'i 'khor gyis rol pa dang //
NK128(nyo)001:146: nges 'byung dka' ba spyod pa dang //
NK128(nyo)001:147: byang chub snying por gshegs pa dang //
NK128(nyo)001:148: bdud sde bcom dang rdzogs par ni //
NK128(nyo)001:149: byang chub chos kyi 'khor lo dang //
NK128(nyo)001:150: mya ngan 'das par gshegs mdzad rnams //
NK128(nyo)001:151: yongs su ma dag zhing rnams su //
NK128(nyo)001:152: srid pa ji srid gnas par ston //
NK128(nyo)001:154: de yang bdag cag gi ston pa 'di gzod ma
NK128(nyo)001:155: nas shes rab snying rje phun sum tshogs pa'i mthus
NK128(nyo)001:156: bsod nams cha mthun gyi dge ba'i rtsa ba rgya
NK128(nyo)001:157: chen po du ma bsags pa zhig yin na'ang /
NK128(nyo)001:158: re zhig na las kyi rgyu ba 'ga' zhig gi
NK128(nyo)001:159: sems can dmyal ba'i gnas su lcags bsregs kyi sa
NK128(nyo)001:160: gzhir shing rta 'dren pa'i gyad du gyur pa'i tshe
NK128(nyo)001:161: / rang gi sdug bsngal nyams su myong ba'i mthun
NK128(nyo)001:162: grogs la snying rje tshad med pa skyes te rang
NK128(nyo)001:163: gzhan barje nus kyi tshig smras pa dmyal srung gshin
NK128(nyo)001:164: rje'i skyes bus mgo la lcags kyi tho lum bsnun
NK128(nyo)001:165: pas tshe'i dus byas te lhar skyes nas lo mang
NK128(nyo)001:166: por bde ba nyams su myong zhing /
NK128(nyo)001:167: shi 'phos nas mi'i nang du rdza mkhan gyi bu khye'u snang byed ces bya bar gyur pa'i tshe /
NK128(nyo)001:168: sangs rgyas sh+aakya thub pa chen po la gdugs gcig /
NK128(nyo)001:171: mgron bu lnga'i me tog rnams gtor te /
NK128(nyo)001:172: de bzhin gshegs pa khyed sku ci 'dra dang //
NK128(nyo)001:173: zhes sogs brjod cing thugs bskyed pa dang /
NK128(nyo)001:175: nga ni sngon tshe dbul por gyur pa'i tshe //
NK128(nyo)001:176: de bzhin gshegs pa sh+aakya thub chen la //
NK128(nyo)001:177: 'jam gang zhig ni dbul ba byas nas kyang //
NK128(nyo)001:178: dang po byang chub mchog tu thugs bskyed do //
NK128(nyo)001:180: de ltar bskal chen grangs med pa gsum gyi bar ram /
NK128(nyo)001:182: grangs med sum cu rtsa gsum du bshad pa'i lugs
NK128(nyo)001:183: te de dag gi bar du tshogs gnyis rgya chen
NK128(nyo)001:184: po bsags te / sa bcu'i byang chub sems dpa'
NK128(nyo)001:185: lha'i bu dam pa tog dkar du skye ba bzhes
NK128(nyo)001:186: nas dga' ldan du lha rnams la chos ston pa'i
NK128(nyo)001:187: tshe phyogs bcu'i sangs rgyas kyi byin gyis brlabs kyis
NK128(nyo)001:188: lha'i sil snyan gyi sgra las /
NK128(nyo)001:189: bsod rnams rgya chen tshogs mang dran rtogs shing //
NK128(nyo)001:190: blo gros mtha' yas shes rab 'od mdzad pa'i //
NK128(nyo)001:191: mtshungs med stobs mnga' rgyu rtsal rgya che ba //
NK128(nyo)001:192: mar me mdzad kyis lung bstan dgongs par mdzod //
NK128(nyo)001:193: ces bskul bas sngon gyi smon lam rjes su dran
NK128(nyo)001:194: te gzigs pa lngas dga' ldan nas 'pho bar dgongs
NK128(nyo)001:195: te / lha rnams kyis bzhugs par gsol ba la ma gnang bar /
NK128(nyo)001:196: chos snang ba'i sgo brgya rtsa brgyad bstan cing mgon
NK128(nyo)001:197: po ma pham pa'i spyi bor rin po che'i dbu
NK128(nyo)001:198: rgyan bcings shing rgyal tshab tu dbang bskur nas /
NK128(nyo)001:199: glang po che thal dkar mche ba drug par sprul
NK128(nyo)001:200: te dga' ldan nas 'pho ba'i mdzad pa ste dang
NK128(nyo)001:201: po'o // de'i tshe ser skya'i grong khyer du sa
NK128(nyo)001:202: ga zla tshes bco lngar yum gso sbyong la gnas
NK128(nyo)001:204: yum gyi lhums de yang rgyal sras kyi nye bar
NK128(nyo)001:205: spyad pa rin po che'i bkod pa zhes bya bar
NK128(nyo)001:207: yum gyi mngal nas kyang lha rnams la chos ston pa dang /
NK128(nyo)001:208: tshangs pas phul ba'i pad+ma'i zil mngar longs spyod cing
NK128(nyo)001:209: zla ba bcu zag med kyi bde ba nyams su
NK128(nyo)001:210: myong zhing skye rgu khrag khrig phrag sum cu rtsa
NK128(nyo)001:211: drug smin par gyur pa sogs lhums su zhugs pa'i
NK128(nyo)001:213: de nas dbo zla ba'i tshes brgyad dam bcu rgyal phur 'dzom pa'i nyin /
NK128(nyo)001:214: lum+bi ni'i tshal du shing ljon pa klag sha'i drung
NK128(nyo)001:215: du yum gyi glo g.yas pa nas bltams ma thag
NK128(nyo)001:216: / tshangs pa dang brgya byin gyis ka shi ka'i ras kyi sleb mos blangs shing /
NK128(nyo)001:217: klu'i rgyal po dga' bo dang nyer dga' bo gnyis
NK128(nyo)001:218: kyis nam mkha' nas bsil drod kyi chus sku khrus
NK128(nyo)001:219: gsol ba dang / lha'i bu brgya stong mang pos spos chu dang me tog sil ma gtor zhing /
NK128(nyo)001:220: sa la babs ma thag tu pad+ma chen po zhig
NK128(nyo)001:221: gis sa brtol te byung ba'i steng du zhabs bzhag
NK128(nyo)001:222: cing / shar lho nub byang 'og dang steng drug
NK128(nyo)001:223: tu gom pa bdun bor zhing dam bca' ba'i tshig
NK128(nyo)001:225: de'i tshe dge ba'i mtshan ma dag kyang mngon par
NK128(nyo)001:226: snang bar gyur cing don thams cad grub pas mtshan
NK128(nyo)001:227: yang gzhon nu don thams cad grub par zhes btags
NK128(nyo)001:228: pa ste sku bltams pa'i mdzad pa ste gsum pa'o
NK128(nyo)001:229: // de nas mtshan mkhan rnams kyis ltas brtag cing lung gnyis su bstan mod kyi /
NK128(nyo)001:230: gangs ri'i ngos la gnas pa'i drang srong nag pos nges par sangs rgyas kho nar lung bstan to //
NK128(nyo)001:231: de nas byang chub sems dpa' bltams nas zhag bdun
NK128(nyo)001:232: nas yum 'das kyang sru skye dgu'i bdag mo sogs
NK128(nyo)001:233: ma ma so gnyis kyis bskyed bsrings te yar skyes
NK128(nyo)001:234: pa dang / yig dpon kun gyi bshes gnyen las yi ge slob pa'i tshul bstan pa dang /
NK128(nyo)001:235: srid grub dpang du bzhag ste rtsis dang grangs kyi khyad par bstan pa /
NK128(nyo)001:236: btsun mo blangs pa'i phyir sgyu rtsal 'gran bar mdzad de 'phongs dang gyad kyi 'dzin stangs dang /
NK128(nyo)001:240: shing rta'i thabs la sogs te mdor na spos sbyor
NK128(nyo)001:241: gyi bar lha dang mi thams cad las byang chub
NK128(nyo)001:242: sems dpa' 'ba' zhig khyad par du gyur pa'i tshul
NK128(nyo)001:243: bstan pa ni bzo'i gnas la mkhas pa'i mdzad pa
NK128(nyo)001:244: ste bzhi pa'o // de nas byang chub sems dpa'
NK128(nyo)001:245: 'jig rten dang mthun par ston pa'i phyir sh+aakya'i bu
NK128(nyo)001:248: ri dwags skyes ma la sogs pa btsun mo'i 'khor
NK128(nyo)001:249: brgyad khri bzhi stong dang rol pa'i tshul bstan te
NK128(nyo)001:250: / de yang rgya cher rol par sh+aakya lag na
NK128(nyo)001:251: be con can gyi bu mo sa 'tsho ma sogs
NK128(nyo)001:252: btsun mo brgyad khrir gsungs shing mdo sde mngon par
NK128(nyo)001:253: / 'byung bar / sh+aakya dbyig pa can gyi bu mo grags 'dzin ma /
NK128(nyo)001:254: dus legs kyi bu mo sa 'tsho ma /
NK128(nyo)001:255: dril bu sgra'i bu mo ri dwags skyes gsum yin par bshad /
NK128(nyo)001:256: bya sa bskal bzang chos rjes sa 'tsho ma dang grags 'dzin ma gnyis gcig par bzhed do //
NK128(nyo)001:257: de ltar btsun mo'i 'khor de dag kyang sngon gyi
NK128(nyo)001:258: smon lam gyi mthus byang chub tu smon par mdzad
NK128(nyo)001:259: pa ni btsun mo'i 'khor gyis rol pa'i mdzad pa
NK128(nyo)001:260: ste lnga pa'o // de'i tshe byang chub sems dpa'
NK128(nyo)001:261: nyid dus mkhyen mdo'i bstan pa la dga' ba'i lha
NK128(nyo)001:262: ste lnga pa'o // klu kha cig / skyes bu
NK128(nyo)001:263: dam pa 'di nyid yun ring por khyim na gnas
NK128(nyo)001:264: te bag med par gyur nas sems can gyi don
NK128(nyo)001:265: las nyams te mngon par 'byung bar mi 'gyur grang
NK128(nyo)001:266: snyam zhing bskul bar yang byed la /
NK128(nyo)001:267: phyogs bcu'i sangs rgyas rnams kyis kyang sil snyan gyi
NK128(nyo)001:268: sgra las tshigs su bcad pa du ma dag kyang
NK128(nyo)001:270: sdug bsngal brgyas gang sems can mthong nas ni //
NK128(nyo)001:271: 'gro ba'i mgon dang skyabs dang gnas gyur cing //
NK128(nyo)001:272: phan byed mchog dang dpung gnyen gyur cig ces //
NK128(nyo)001:273: khyod kyis sngon ni smon lam de skad btab //
NK128(nyo)001:274: dge ba dpa' bo sngon gyi spyod pa dang //
NK128(nyo)001:275: 'gro phan bya zhes smon btab dran pa byos zhes sogs kyis bskul zhing /
NK128(nyo)001:276: gzhan yang grong khyer gyi shar sgor mi rgan po nyam thag pa dang /
NK128(nyo)001:277: lho sgor nad kyis nyen pa dang /
NK128(nyo)001:278: nub sgor shi ba'i ro khyogs la brteg pa mya
NK128(nyo)001:279: ngan dang bcas pa dang byang sgor lhas sprul pa'i
NK128(nyo)001:280: dge slong zhi zhing dul ba gzigs pas kyang rkyen
NK128(nyo)001:281: byas te / khyim la skyo zhing nges par 'byung ba'i dus la babs par gzigs shing /
NK128(nyo)001:282: 'on kyang phas ma gnang par rab tu byung na tshul dang mi mthun zhing /
NK128(nyo)001:283: byas pa mi gzo bar 'gyur ro snyam nas yab zas gtsang ma'i gam du byon te /
NK128(nyo)001:284: lha gcig bdag ni mngon par 'byung ba'i dus babs rigs /
NK128(nyo)001:285: gegs kyang ma mdzad mi dgyes pa yang ma mdzad cig /
NK128(nyo)001:286: rgyal po gnyen bcas yul 'khor bcas te bzod par mdzad /
NK128(nyo)001:288: rgyal pos dri lan 'ga' zhig mdzad pa'i mthar /
NK128(nyo)001:289: phan byed 'gro bar byed dang rjes su yi rang ngo //
NK128(nyo)001:290: khyod kyi bsam pa rnams ni yongs su rdzogs gyur cig /
NK128(nyo)001:292: de nas byang chub sems dpa' srod kyi cha la
NK128(nyo)001:293: grags 'dzin ma'i mngal du sras bskrun pa'i tshul bstan
NK128(nyo)001:294: nas / nam gyi gung la lha rnams kyis grogs byas te /
NK128(nyo)001:295: grong khyer ba rnams gnyid kyis myos par byas shing
NK128(nyo)001:296: khang bzang gi steng nas sangs rgyas thams cad la
NK128(nyo)001:297: phyag byas / 'dun pa las rta basngagasa ldan blangs te /
NK128(nyo)001:298: bkra shis kyi chab sgo nas mngon par byung zhing
NK128(nyo)001:299: nam mkha' la 'phags te rgyal chen bzhis btegs te
NK128(nyo)001:300: lha rnams kyis mchod pa dang bcas te gyad kyi
NK128(nyo)001:301: yul 'das te mchod rten rnam dag gi drung du
NK128(nyo)001:302: byon nas 'dun pa rta rgyan dang bcas pas phyir
NK128(nyo)001:303: log / nyid kyi dbu skra nyid kyis bcad /
NK128(nyo)001:304: lhas phul ba'i na bza' ngur smrig mnabs te rang
NK128(nyo)001:305: byung gi bsnyen par rdzogs par mdzad pa ni nges
NK128(nyo)001:306: par 'byung ba'i mdzad pa ste drug pa'o //
NK128(nyo)001:307: de nas bram ze rigs ldan dang /
NK128(nyo)001:310: be con gyi bu 'od ldan rnams kyi mgron bdag
NK128(nyo)001:311: gir mdzad cing yangs pa can du sgyu rtsal shes
NK128(nyo)001:312: kyi bu ring 'phur las ci yang med pa'i sems
NK128(nyo)001:313: dang / ma ga rdar gzugs can snying po dang thog mar mjal zhing /
NK128(nyo)001:314: rgyal po'i khab tu ring byed kyi bu lhag spyod
NK128(nyo)001:315: las srid rtse'i sems dag mngon du mdzad de rjes
NK128(nyo)001:316: 'jug gi gdul bya rnams chos kyi phyir dka' ba
NK128(nyo)001:317: spyod dgos par bstan pa dang /
NK128(nyo)001:318: de lta bu'i dka' spyad kyang phyi rol pa dag gis brtul zhugs lnga spyod pa dang /
NK128(nyo)001:319: lag pa la ldag pa sogs dang /
NK128(nyo)001:322: nyi ma la lta ba sogs dang lag pa gcig gtod pa dang /
NK128(nyo)001:323: rkang pa gcig btsugs pa la sogs te log pa'i dka' thub rnams 'gog par bya ba'i phyir /
NK128(nyo)001:324: klung ne rany+dza na'i 'gram du lo drug gi bar
NK128(nyo)001:325: du mkha' khyab kyi ting nge 'dzin la mnyam par
NK128(nyo)001:327: rgya shug 'bru gcig /'bras 'bru gcig la brten nas
NK128(nyo)001:328: dbugs rgyu ba bcad de bsam gtan gyi pha rol
NK128(nyo)001:329: tu phyin pa rdzogs pa'i tshul bstan pa ni dka'
NK128(nyo)001:330: ba ni dka' ba spyad pa'i mdzad pa ste bdun
NK128(nyo)001:331: pa'o // de nas byang chub sems dpa' ting nge
NK128(nyo)001:332: 'dzin las bzhengs te dka' thub kho nas grol bar
NK128(nyo)001:333: 'dzin pa rnams sun dbyung ba'i phyir /
NK128(nyo)001:334: kha zas rags pa gsol lo snyam du dgongs te /
NK128(nyo)001:335: bran mo grub ma shi ba'i ro gos blangs pa
NK128(nyo)001:336: lhas sprul pa'i rdzing bur brgya byin gyis phul ba'i
NK128(nyo)001:337: rdo leb kyi steng du bkrus nas /
NK128(nyo)001:338: shing sgrub byed kyi drung du phyag dar khrod pa'i chos gos drubs te /
NK128(nyo)001:339: lha'i bu 'od dri ma med pas lha'i gos ngur
NK128(nyo)001:340: smrig phul ba yang bzhes te spyod yul gyi grong
NK128(nyo)001:342: lhas sbran te steng rgyas kyi grong na dga' byed
NK128(nyo)001:343: kyi bu mo legs skyes mas ba stong gi 'o
NK128(nyo)001:344: ma lan bdun du nying khur byas pa 'bras gsar
NK128(nyo)001:345: pa dang lhan cig tu btsos pa'i nang du /
NK128(nyo)001:346: dpal be'u sogs bkra shis pa'i mtshan ma dag kyang snang bar gyur la /
NK128(nyo)001:347: mtshan mkhan gyis kyang zas de zos pa'i byang chub sems dpa' bdud rtsi thob par lung bstan to //
NK128(nyo)001:348: de nas legs skyes mas 'o thug de nyid me
NK128(nyo)001:349: tog dang spos chus gtor zhing sbrang rtsi dang ldan
NK128(nyo)001:350: par byas te gser gyi snod chen po bkang ste
NK128(nyo)001:351: byang chub sems dpa' mgron du bos pa la phul
NK128(nyo)001:352: lo // byang chub sems dpa' kyang klung 'bras du
NK128(nyo)001:353: zas kyi bya ba mdzad pas sku lus mtshan dpe
NK128(nyo)001:354: rab tu brtas par gyur te /
NK128(nyo)001:355: bdud las rgyal ba'i phyir seng ge dang /
NK128(nyo)001:358: dbang po'i 'gros kyis byang chub shing drung du gshegs pa'i lam mkhar /
NK128(nyo)001:359: r+ts+wa 'tshong bkra shis las rtsa sngo zhing 'jam pa
NK128(nyo)001:360: dag tshigs su bcad pas blangs nas byang chub kyi
NK128(nyo)001:361: shing la bskor ba lan bdun mdzad de /
NK128(nyo)001:362: r+ts+wa rnams kyi rtse mo nang dang rtsa ba phyir
NK128(nyo)001:363: bstan shar phyogs su bltas te skyil mo krung bcas
NK128(nyo)001:364: te dam bca' ba'i tshigs su bcad pas brjod de
NK128(nyo)001:365: bzhugs pa ni byang chub snying por gshegs pa'i mdzad
NK128(nyo)001:367: de nas byang chub sems dpa' rjes 'jug rnams byang
NK128(nyo)001:368: chub bsgrub pa la bar du gcod pa sna tshogs
NK128(nyo)001:369: 'byung yang de dag gis mi tshugs shing lam mthar
NK128(nyo)001:370: phyin pa byed dgos pa'i brdar smin mtshams kyi mdzod
NK128(nyo)001:372: 'od zer de dag las tshigs su bcad pa'i sgras kyang bdud bskul zhing /
NK128(nyo)001:373: bdud sdig can gyis kyang bdud dpung bsam gyis mi
NK128(nyo)001:374: khyab pa dag bshams te mtshon cha sna tshogs 'phangs
NK128(nyo)001:375: pa thams cad kyang me tog gi char du gyur
NK128(nyo)001:376: cing / bsod nams kyi tshogs la skur pa btab
NK128(nyo)001:377: pa'i tshe phyag g.yas pas sa la brdabs te sa'i
NK128(nyo)001:378: lha mo bstan mas dpang byas so //
NK128(nyo)001:379: de ltar thabs gang gis kyang bar du gcod ma
NK128(nyo)001:380: nus pa bdud kyi dpung tshogs byer zhing rnam par
NK128(nyo)001:381: 'thor bar gyur pa ste bdud sde bcom pa'i mdzad
NK128(nyo)001:382: pa dgu pa'o // de ltar byang chub sems dpa'
NK128(nyo)001:383: bdud kyi g.yul las rnam par rgyal te dgung lo
NK128(nyo)001:384: so lnga pa sa ga'i tshes bco lnga'i nam gyi
NK128(nyo)001:385: cha smad skya rengs 'char kha rnga brdung ba'i tshod
NK128(nyo)001:386: pa dgu pa'o // / mtshan mo'i thun tha ma'i
NK128(nyo)001:387: dus su bsam btan bzhi dang rig pa gsum skyes
NK128(nyo)001:388: pa dgu pa'o // / / rten 'brel bcu gnyis
NK128(nyo)001:389: dang bden pa bzhi'i tshul khong du chud nas mthar
NK128(nyo)001:390: gyi gnas pa'i snyoms 'jug dgu mngon du byas nas
NK128(nyo)001:391: pa dgu pa'o // / / / skad cig gcig
NK128(nyo)001:392: dang ldan pa'i shes rab kyis mngon par rdzogs par
NK128(nyo)001:393: pa dgu pa'o // / / / sangs rgyas so
NK128(nyo)001:394: // de'i tshe zla ba yang gzas zin zhing sgra
NK128(nyo)001:396: de nas shing ta la bdun srid du 'phags te lam gyi rgyun ni chad do //
NK128(nyo)001:397: zhes sogs kyi chos ched du brjod pa gsungs shing /
NK128(nyo)001:398: lha rnams kyis me tog gi char phab cing 'jig rten snang bar byas /
NK128(nyo)001:399: sa chen po rnam pa drug tu g.yos /
NK128(nyo)001:400: phyogs bcu'i sangs rgyas kyis chos kyi dgab pa bskur
NK128(nyo)001:401: zhing dgab pa de dag gis kyang stong gsum gyi
NK128(nyo)001:402: stong chen po'i 'jig rten gyii khams 'di rin po
NK128(nyo)001:403: che'i gdugs gcig gis khebs shing /
NK128(nyo)001:404: de dag las 'od zer byung bas phyogs bcu'i 'jig
NK128(nyo)001:405: rten mtha' dag snang bar byas nas sangs rgyas dang
NK128(nyo)001:406: byang chub sems dpa' lha dang bcas pa dag gis
NK128(nyo)001:407: mngon par basngagasa shing legs so'i sgra rgya cher brjod
NK128(nyo)001:408: par gyur pa 'di dag ni byang chub pa'i mdzad
NK128(nyo)001:410: de ltar sangs rgyas nas zhag bdun phrag dang po
NK128(nyo)001:411: skyil mo krung ma bshig pa dga' ba'i zas bkod
NK128(nyo)001:412: pa zhes bya ba'i ting nge 'dzin la snyoms par
NK128(nyo)001:413: zhugs shing lha rnams kyis mchod cing bstod do //
NK128(nyo)001:414: gnyis pa la stong gsum rgyang ring du 'chag go //
NK128(nyo)001:415: gsum pa la byang chub kyi shing la spyan mi 'dzum par gzigs so //
NK128(nyo)001:416: bzhi pa la shar nub tu rgyang mi ring bar 'acha ga go //
NK128(nyo)001:417: de'i tshe bdud sdig can gyis mya ngan las 'da'
NK128(nyo)001:418: bar gsol ba btab kyang gdul bya'i don ma grub
NK128(nyo)001:419: gyi bar du mya ngan las mi 'da' bar zhal
NK128(nyo)001:420: gyis bzhes shing / bdud kyi bu mo gsum gyi g.yo sgyu bstan pa'ang rgan mor mdzad do //
NK128(nyo)001:421: lnga pa la yul ngan chen po byung ba'i tshe klu btang bzung gi gnas na bzhugs so //
NK128(nyo)001:422: drug pa la shing nya gro rdar skyong gi drung
NK128(nyo)001:423: du bzhud de kun tu rgyu rnams la tshigs su
NK128(nyo)001:425: bdun phrag bdun pa la shing sgrol rgyu'i drung du
NK128(nyo)001:426: bzhugs pa'i tshe byang phyogs pa'i tshang pa ga gon
NK128(nyo)001:427: dang bzang po spun gyis sbrang rtsi dang /
NK128(nyo)001:429: bur shing bshus pa dag phul ba la rgyal chen
NK128(nyo)001:430: bzhis rin po che'i lhung bzed phul ba ma bzhes
NK128(nyo)001:431: pa rdo'i lhung bzed phul ba thog mar rnam thos
NK128(nyo)001:432: kyi bu dang / de nas gzhan gsum gyi yang
NK128(nyo)001:433: bzhes te bzhig gcig tu byin gyis brlabs pa der
NK128(nyo)001:434: kyi bu dang / gsol te / gzhan yang ga
NK128(nyo)001:435: gon dang bzang po gnyis kyis ba stong gi 'o
NK128(nyo)001:436: ma'i mar gyi nying khu'i spros ma bzhams te rin
NK128(nyo)001:437: po che'i gzhong par blugs te phul ba yang gsol
NK128(nyo)001:438: kyi bu dang / gsol te / nas / lha yi bkra shis don grub cing /
NK128(nyo)001:439: zhes kyi shis pa brjod pa'i tshigs bcad gsungs te sbrang rtsi 'byung ba'i rgyal por lung bstan to //
NK128(nyo)001:440: de nas de bzhin gshegs pa thugs las chung ngur bzhugs te /
NK128(nyo)001:441: zab zhi rdul bral sogs kyi tshigs su bcad pa
NK128(nyo)001:442: gsungs shing 'od bkye bas stong gsum gyi bdag po
NK128(nyo)001:443: tshangs pa chen po gtsug phud can gyis shes te
NK128(nyo)001:444: / tshangs pa 'bum phrag drug cu rtsa brgyad kyi
NK128(nyo)001:445: 'khor dang bcas te thal mo sbyar nas gsol ba
NK128(nyo)001:446: / btab pa ni / ye shes chen po mchog gi dkyil 'khor bsgrub nas ni /
NK128(nyo)001:447: phyogs bcu dag tu 'od zer rnam par 'gyed mdzad de /
NK128(nyo)001:448: ye shes zer gyis mi yi pad+ma kha 'byed pa /
NK128(nyo)001:449: smra ba'i nyi ma ji slad de ring btang snyoms bzhugs /
NK128(nyo)001:450: zhes sogs kyi bskul bas cang mi gsungs pas gnang ngo //
NK128(nyo)001:451: yang thugs las chung ba la gzhol ba dang tshangs
NK128(nyo)001:452: pas shes te brgya byin sbran nas brgya byin gyis
NK128(nyo)001:454: zla ba nya ba gza' las thar ba ltar //
NK128(nyo)001:455: khyod kyi thugs ni rnam par grol ba lags //
NK128(nyo)001:456: g.yul las rnam par rgyal ba bzhengs su gsol //
NK128(nyo)001:457: 'jig rten mun par shes rab 'od byung gsol //
NK128(nyo)001:459: yang thugs las chung ngur brgyud pa'i tshe ma ga
NK128(nyo)001:460: rdar me mi 'bar ba sogs mi dge ba'i ltas
NK128(nyo)001:461: byung bas slar yang tshangs pas bskul zhing bka' mchid
NK128(nyo)001:462: du mar glengs te zhal gyis bzhes nas /
NK128(nyo)001:463: thog ma'i gdul bya ring 'phur dang lhag spyod rjes su dgongs pas /
NK128(nyo)001:464: de gnyis shi bar mkhyen nas /
NK128(nyo)001:465: lnga sder dgongs te ma ga rda nas gsal ldan
NK128(nyo)001:466: du byon pa'i lam du 'tsho ba pa dang bka'
NK128(nyo)001:468: gang+g+aa'i nam mkha' la gshegs te wa ra n+aa sir
NK128(nyo)001:469: bsod snyoms bzhes te drang srong lhung ba ri dwags
NK128(nyo)001:470: kyi nags su byon nas lnga sde'i nang khrims zhig
NK128(nyo)001:472: de nas chos kyi 'khor lo bskor bar mngon par
NK128(nyo)001:473: phyogs pa de'i tshe sa phyogs der rin po che
NK128(nyo)001:474: sna bdun gyi khri stong byung ba'i gsum la bskor
NK128(nyo)001:475: ba mdzad cing / bzhi pa la bzhugs shing sku
NK128(nyo)001:476: las 'od byung ste 'jig rten thams cad snang bar
NK128(nyo)001:477: mdzad cing sa yang rnam pa drug tu g.yos so
NK128(nyo)001:478: ba mdzad cing / // de'i tshe lha rnams kyis
NK128(nyo)001:479: 'khor gyis khyams chen po brgyan pa la sogs te
NK128(nyo)001:480: bkod pa sna tshogs bshams shing gsol ba btab /
NK128(nyo)001:481: byang chub sems dpa' sems dpa' chen pos sems bskyed
NK128(nyo)001:482: ma thag tu chos kyi 'khor lo bskor ba zhes
NK128(nyo)001:483: bya bas / chos kyi 'khor lo lha'i 'dzam bu
NK128(nyo)001:484: chu bo'i gser las byas shing rin po che sna
NK128(nyo)001:485: tshogs kyis brgyan pa rtsibs stong yod pa /
NK128(nyo)001:486: 'od zer stong dang ldan pa me tog gi lda ldi gser gyi d+r+wa ba dang dril g.yer /
NK128(nyo)001:489: g.yung drung 'khyil ba dang bcas pa lha'i gos dang /
NK128(nyo)001:492: phreng bas brgyan cing shug pas byugs pa sangs rgyas thams cad kyis byin gyis brlabs shing bzhes te /
NK128(nyo)001:493: sngon yang bskor ba chos kyi 'khor lo bskor ba'i
NK128(nyo)001:494: phyir de bzhin gshegs pa la phul zhing thal mo
NK128(nyo)001:495: sbyar te / tshigs su bcad pa'i dbyangs kyis bsnyad de gsol ba btab bo //
NK128(nyo)001:496: de nas de bzhin gshegs pas nam gyi cha stod la cang mi gsungs shing /
NK128(nyo)001:497: gung thun la yang dag par chags pa'i gtam dang /
NK128(nyo)001:498: nam gyi cha smad la lnga ste bzang po bos
NK128(nyo)001:499: te bden pa bzhi lan gsum bzlas pa rnam pa
NK128(nyo)001:500: bcu gnyis kyi 'khor lo bskor bas dang pos koon+di
NK128(nyo)001:501: nya dang lha mang po mthong lam skyes /
NK128(nyo)001:502: gnyis pa la koon+di nya dgra bcom ste 'jig rten du dkon cog gsum byung la /
NK128(nyo)001:503: gzhan bzhir mthong lam skyes par gyur to //
NK128(nyo)001:504: de nas gsum pas ni lnga sde lhag ma bzhis kyang dgra bcom pa'i 'bras bu thob cing /
NK128(nyo)001:505: de ltar lnga sde dang lha'i 'dus pa mtha' yas
NK128(nyo)001:506: pa la bka' dang po bden pa bzhi'i chos kyi
NK128(nyo)001:508: de nas bya rgod phung po'i ri la sogs par 'khor dge slong stong nyis brgya lnga bcu /
NK128(nyo)001:511: byang chub sems dpa'i 'khor bye ba khrag khrig brgya
NK128(nyo)001:512: stong la bka' bar pa mtshan nyid med pa'i chos
NK128(nyo)001:513: kyi 'khor lo rgya cher bskor ro //
NK128(nyo)001:514: de nas ri ma la ya la sogs par 'khor
NK128(nyo)001:515: theg pa thams cad la yang dag par zhugs pa'i
NK128(nyo)001:516: byang chub sems dpa' rnams la tha ma legs par
NK128(nyo)001:517: rnam par phye ba dang ldan pa nges pa don
NK128(nyo)001:518: gyi rnam pas bstan pa'i chos kyi 'khor lo bskor
NK128(nyo)001:519: ro // de ltar chos 'khor gsum gyi dus ni
NK128(nyo)001:520: mi mthun pa 'ga' zhig snang bas 'dir ma bris
NK128(nyo)001:521: ro // la / mdor na chos kyi 'khor lo
NK128(nyo)001:522: rim pa gsum du bskor ba yang phyogs gcig nas
NK128(nyo)001:523: mtshon pa'i dbang gis bzhag pa yin la /
NK128(nyo)001:524: gzhan du rnam pa thams cad du bskor bar yang shes par bya dgos shing /
NK128(nyo)001:525: gsang ba snying po'i lugs kyi mdzad pa brgyad du
NK128(nyo)001:526: byed pa'i tshe cho 'phrul chen po bstan pa yang
NK128(nyo)001:528: 'di la yang thun mong dang thun mong ma yin pa gnyis 'byung ngo //
NK128(nyo)001:529: de bas na 'di dag ni chos kyi 'khor lo bskor ba'i mdzad pa ste bcu gcig pa'o //
NK128(nyo)001:530: de ltar ston pa sku dngos kyi mdzad pa rnams
NK128(nyo)001:531: rdzogs te dgung lo brgyad cu pa'i dus mdo myang
NK128(nyo)001:532: 'das las dpyid zla tha chung sa ga zla ba'i
NK128(nyo)001:533: tshes bco lnga'i gung thun dang /
NK128(nyo)001:534: lung phran tshegs kyi rgya 'grel du smin drug zla ba dkar po tshes brgyad dang /
NK128(nyo)001:535: g.yung ston pa dpyid zla 'bring po'i tshes bco lnga'i nyin sogs dang /
NK128(nyo)001:536: gzhan yang bzhed tshul mang du yod mod kyis 'dir
NK128(nyo)001:537: dpyid zla tha chung sa ga'i bco lnga nyid gco
NK128(nyo)001:538: bor bzung ba'i lugs su bgyis te /
NK128(nyo)001:539: dus de'i tshe grong khyer rtsa can gyad kyi yul
NK128(nyo)001:540: dang nye ba shing s+aa la zung zhig gi drung
NK128(nyo)001:541: du seng ge'i khri la glo g.yas pa phab ste
NK128(nyo)001:542: gdul bya rtag mtshan can rnams skyo bar bskul ba
NK128(nyo)001:543: dang / bdag sogs skal med kyi gdul bya rnams
NK128(nyo)001:544: la thams cad mkhyen pa'i sku mngon du mthong ba'i
NK128(nyo)001:545: skal ba med pa'i phyir yongs su mya ngan las
NK128(nyo)001:547: de'i tshe mi dgos pa'i mtshan ma du ma snang zhing /
NK128(nyo)001:548: de ma thag tu dgra bcom pa brgyad khri yang mya ngan las 'das par bshad /
NK128(nyo)001:549: de'i tshe gnas brtan 'od srungs chen po rgyal po'i
NK128(nyo)001:550: khab tu gnas pas ston pa mya ngan las 'das
NK128(nyo)001:551: par shes nas mya ngan byed cing 'khor dang bcas
NK128(nyo)001:552: pa sku gdung gi drung du song nas sku ma
NK128(nyo)001:553: nyams pa la phyag byas shig /'khor los sgyur ba'i
NK128(nyo)001:554: rgyal po la bya ba bzhin du pur sbyangs shing
NK128(nyo)001:555: sku gdung cha brgyad du dgos te lha klu mi
NK128(nyo)001:556: rnams kyi mchod pa'i rten du so sor sbyin pa
NK128(nyo)001:557: sogs mya ngan las 'das pa'i mdzad pa ste bcu
NK128(nyo)001:558: gnyis pa'o // de'i rjes su bka'i bsdu ba rim
NK128(nyo)001:559: pa gsum dang bstan pa'i gtad rabs sogs rgyas par
NK128(nyo)001:561: de ltar ston pa'i mdzad pa mdo tsam smos pa la dgos pa yod de /
NK128(nyo)001:563: 'dzam bu'i gling 'dir chu klung ji snyed cig 'bab cing //
NK128(nyo)001:564: me tog 'bras ldan sman dang nags tshal bskyed byed pa //
NK128(nyo)001:565: ma dros gnas pa'i klu dbang klu bdag brten gnas te //
NK128(nyo)001:566: de ni klu yi bdag po de yi mthu dpal yin //
NK128(nyo)001:567: rgyal ba'i nyan thos pa dag ji snyed chos ston dang //
NK128(nyo)001:568: 'chad dang rig pa dag dang ldan par brjod pa dang //
NK128(nyo)001:569: mchog 'phags bde ba byed dang de yi 'bras thob pa //
NK128(nyo)001:570: de dag kun kyang de bzhin gshegs pa'i skyes bu'i mthu //
NK128(nyo)001:571: zhes gsungs pa'i phyir na bdag cag rnams dam pa'i
NK128(nyo)001:572: chos nyan bshad bgyid pa 'di dag kyang ston pa'i
NK128(nyo)001:573: thugs rjer shes dgos pa yin la /
NK128(nyo)001:574: de ltar ston pa'i basngagasa pa brjod pa rnams btang snyoms su bzhag ste /
NK128(nyo)001:575: rang rang gi rigs mthun rnams la basngagasa par byed pa mi 'os te /
NK128(nyo)001:576: bya ba skal bzang chos kyi rgya mtsho'i mdzad pa 'khrul med las /
NK128(nyo)001:577: 'di na phal cher bstan la zhugs gyur kyang //
NK128(nyo)001:578: ston pa'i basngagasa pa rin chen phreng dod nas //
NK128(nyo)001:579: rang rang slob dpon rnams kyi basngagasa pa yi //
NK128(nyo)001:580: dbu ba'i phreng ba mgrin pa'i rgyan du byed //
NK128(nyo)001:581: ces gsungs pa don la gsal bar mthong zhing /
NK128(nyo)001:582: mdor na ston pa'i rjes su zhugs pa rnams ston
NK128(nyo)001:583: pa'i mdzad pa brjod par mi byed na bstan pa'i
NK128(nyo)001:584: bdag po mi shes pa'i skyon yod de /
NK128(nyo)001:586: thub dbang mdzad pa yon tan gtam gyi tshang tshing can //
NK128(nyo)001:587: tsan+dana ljon pa gsung zhim ngad ldan grib ma yi //
NK128(nyo)001:588: shing rtsa bsil ba srid pa'i gdung skyob mi brten na //
NK128(nyo)001:589: shes ldan khyod ni su yi bstan la zhugs pa yin //
NK128(nyo)001:590: zhes gsungs pa la nges shes rnyed cing /
NK128(nyo)001:591: rgya gar gyi mkhas mchog dpa' bos kyang /
NK128(nyo)001:592: grags pa'i mtshan mar gyur pa bzang po 'di rnams kyis /
NK128(nyo)001:593: bde bar gshegs gyur lam rnams gang yin ston par 'gyur /
NK128(nyo)001:594: yid la dad pa med pa rnam kyang dad par 'gyur /
NK128(nyo)001:595: chos dang ldan pa'i gtam gyis rab tu dga' bar 'gyur /
NK128(nyo)001:598: byang chub mchog gi rjes su rab mos shing //
NK128(nyo)001:599: lan gcig tsam yang dad pa bskyed pa ni //
NK128(nyo)001:600: bsod nams dam pa'i mchog tu 'di 'gyur ro //
NK128(nyo)001:601: zhes gsungs pas sangs rgyas kyi yon tan rjes su dran cing byang chub mchog la mos pa dang /
NK128(nyo)001:602: bsod nams kyii mchog tu 'gyur bas de'i phyir na
NK128(nyo)001:603: 'dir mdzad pa bcu gnyis kyi tshul smos pa'i rgyu
NK128(nyo)001:605: de ltar ston pa rdzogs pa'i sangs rgyas bcom ldan
NK128(nyo)001:606: 'das kyi mdzad pa bcu gnyis kyi tshul nyung ngur
NK128(nyo)001:607: brjod zin nas / ston pa gnyis pa'am ston pa'i
NK128(nyo)001:608: rgyal tshab rang cag snga 'gyur ba rnams kyi ston
NK128(nyo)001:609: mchog mtshungs pa med pa o rgyan chos kyi rgyal
NK128(nyo)001:610: po pad+ma 'byung gnas kyi sku che ba'i yon tan
NK128(nyo)001:612: de la yang thang yig las /
NK128(nyo)001:613: rnam thar stong phrag bcu dang brgya phrag dgu /
NK128(nyo)001:614: zhes rnam thar gyi grangs rags pa tsam dang /
NK128(nyo)001:615: gzhan yang bka' gter gyi lugs so sor mang ba dang /
NK128(nyo)001:616: bod 'dir yang gsar rnying mkhas grub kyi bla ma
NK128(nyo)001:617: dam pa rnams kyi mdzad pa sogs mang po rnams
NK128(nyo)001:618: gung bsgrigs par mi nus pa'i rgyu mtshan /
NK128(nyo)001:619: sangs rgyas kyi mdzad pa gdul bya'i snang tshul sna tshogs su 'char zhing ston pas mi mthun la /
NK128(nyo)001:620: de dag kyang 'gal 'dur bsam na mi rigs pas so so'i snang ngor bden pa'i phyir /
NK128(nyo)001:621: 'di yang spyi ltar rags pa tsam zhig nyung ngur bsdus te brjod par bya'o //
NK128(nyo)001:622: de la dang po spyir btang gi sa bcad tsam gyi dbang du bgyis na /
NK128(nyo)001:624: thos pas byang chub rnam thar mdor bsdu na //
NK128(nyo)001:625: rgyal sras mdzad pa bcu gcig 'di lta ste //
NK128(nyo)001:626: 'gro 'dul dgongs mdzad pad+ma'i lhums zhugs mdzad //
NK128(nyo)001:627: rang byung bltams mdzad rgyal sras rol rtsed mdzad //
NK128(nyo)001:628: rab tu byung mdzad dka' thub sna tshogs mdzad //
NK128(nyo)001:629: bdud dpung 'joms mdzad sangs rgyas byang chub mdzad //
NK128(nyo)001:630: chos 'khor bskor mdzad brtul zhugs spyod pa mdzad //
NK128(nyo)001:631: bstan pa mthar rgyas mi nub gter sbed mdzad //
NK128(nyo)001:632: ces gsungs pa dang sbyar rigs la /
NK128(nyo)001:634: dus gsum mkhyen pa'i slob dpon pad+ma 'byung //
NK128(nyo)001:635: phyi rgyud dag pas sprul sku'i bstan pa 'dzin //
NK128(nyo)001:636: nang rgyud dag pas longs sku'i bstan pa skyong //
NK128(nyo)001:637: gsang rgyud dag pas bskyed rdzogs ngang la bzhugs //
NK128(nyo)001:638: 'gran gyi do med sangs rgyas 'di yin pas //
NK128(nyo)001:639: dus gsum 'jig rten khams 'dir mtshungs med rje //
NK128(nyo)001:640: rgyal ba'i bka' las rtsod med sprul skur grags //
NK128(nyo)001:642: ston pa sku gsum gyi rnam par thar pa las gzhan du med la /
NK128(nyo)001:643: bye brag tu gu ru nyid rgyal ba'i lung gis bstan tshul ni /
NK128(nyo)001:644: mdo myang 'das dang dbus 'gyur tshal lung bstan pa'i
NK128(nyo)001:645: mdo sogs las gsungs tshul rgyas par thang yig sogs
NK128(nyo)001:646: las shes so // rtsa ba'i sa bcad dang po
NK128(nyo)001:647: 'gro 'dul dgongs mdzad ces pa'i 'bru mnan pa'i tshe
NK128(nyo)001:648: las shes so // / myang mdzad rnam thar gsol 'debs las /
NK128(nyo)001:649: 'dzam gling bye ba phrag brgya'i zhing khams su //
NK128(nyo)001:650: o rgyan pad+ma bye ba phrag brgya'i sku //
NK128(nyo)001:651: zhes sogs kyi don ltar dang /
NK128(nyo)001:652: khyad par 'dzam bu'i gling 'dir gsang sngags rdo rje theg pa'i bstan pa rgya cher spel zhing /
NK128(nyo)001:653: bye brag rang cag kha ba can pa rnams la dgongs par mdzad pa ni dang po'o //
NK128(nyo)001:654: de yang bka' ma phur pa'i phyogs kyi yig rnying 'ga' zhig dang /
NK128(nyo)001:655: gter ston pa mkhal smug po'i gter ma rnam thar rtsa 'grel sogs las mngal skyes su bshad kyang /
NK128(nyo)001:656: 'dir rdzus skyes ltar bshad na o rgyan chos kyi
NK128(nyo)001:657: rgyal po in+t+ra b+hu ti bar pa'i sras kyi skal
NK128(nyo)001:658: bar lho nub 'o ma can gyi matsho'am rda na
NK128(nyo)001:659: ko sha'i mtsho gling rgya mtsho dri med mdangs ldan
NK128(nyo)001:660: du sangs rgyas snang ba mtha' yas kyi thugs ka
NK128(nyo)001:661: nas gzigs stangs rnam pa gsum gyis gzigs pas h+r+aiyig
NK128(nyo)001:662: gi rnam par pad+ma'i lhums su zhugs pa ni mdzad
NK128(nyo)001:663: pa gnyis pa'o // de nas thang yig ltar na
NK128(nyo)001:664: 'brug lo ston zla ra ba'i skar ma rgyal la
NK128(nyo)001:665: bltams pa'i tshul bstan pa ni mdzad pa gsum pa'o
NK128(nyo)001:666: pa gnyis pa'o // // rgyal po in+t+ra b+hu tis
NK128(nyo)001:667: rgya mtshor nor bu blangs te phyir byon pa'i lam
NK128(nyo)001:668: du mjal te mtsho skyes rdo rjer mtshan gsol zhing
NK128(nyo)001:669: spyan drangs nas pho brang du bkur sti chen pos
NK128(nyo)001:670: o rgyan gyi rgyal srid la dbang bskur zhing yid
NK128(nyo)001:671: bzhin gyi nor bu la gsol btab ste /
NK128(nyo)001:672: skye rgu rnams kyi phongs pa zhi bar mdzad cing pad+ma rgyal por grags so //
NK128(nyo)001:673: rgyal po zla ba gzhon nu'i sras mo 'od 'chang
NK128(nyo)001:674: ma la sogs btsun mo'i 'khor gyis rol ba dang
NK128(nyo)001:675: / gzhan yang 'phongs sogs sgyu rtsal gyi cho 'phrul
NK128(nyo)001:676: du ma yang snang bar mdzad cing 'gro ba mang
NK128(nyo)001:677: po'i don rgya cher mdzad pa ni rol rtsed kyi
NK128(nyo)001:678: tshul te mdzad pa bzhi pa'o //
NK128(nyo)001:679: de yang rdo rje sems dpa' lha 'khor stong phrag
NK128(nyo)001:680: bdun cu rtsa gnyis kyis bskor ba mdun gyi nam
NK128(nyo)001:681: mkhar byon te tshigs su bcad pa'i sgras bskul ba
NK128(nyo)001:682: dang / pho brang gi rtse he ru ka'i gar
NK128(nyo)001:683: mdzad de kha t+wam ga shor ba ltar mdzad nas
NK128(nyo)001:684: bdud blon ma bu bkum pa'i rkyen gyis rgyal khrims
NK128(nyo)001:685: gnyan pos dur khrod bsil ba'i tshal du spyugs te
NK128(nyo)001:686: rgyal srid spangs pa'i tshul bstan /
NK128(nyo)001:687: lnga ldan gyi yul bka' skyong brag phug ces bya
NK128(nyo)001:688: bar rdo rje dbyings kyi dkyil 'khor zhal phyes te
NK128(nyo)001:689: bsgrubs pas / zhag bdun na zhi ba'i lha tshogs
NK128(nyo)001:690: kyi zhal gzigs te dngos grub bsnyen pa'i tshul bstan
NK128(nyo)001:691: bsgrubs pas / / de nas dur khrod bsil ba'i
NK128(nyo)001:692: tshal du brtul zhugs kyi spyod pa mdzad pa'i tshe
NK128(nyo)001:694: yul mi rnams kyis gsod par brtsams ma zin par
NK128(nyo)001:695: shor bas bdud po shor ba gzhon nu zhes kyang
NK128(nyo)001:696: btags so // de nas gsal ldan gyi yul gyi sh+aakya srid sgrub las rtsis bslabs pa'i tshul dang /
NK128(nyo)001:697: pad+ma can gyi yul du 'tsho byed gzhon nu'i bur sman dang /
NK128(nyo)001:698: r+aa ga la'i yul du +aa tsar+ya kun gyi bshes gnyen las sgra dang yi ge'i rigs /
NK128(nyo)001:699: bzo bo bi shwa karma las bzo dang /
NK128(nyo)001:700: phyi nang gi pan+di ta du ma las tshad ma
NK128(nyo)001:701: ste rigs pa'i gnas thams cad la sbyang ba'i tshul
NK128(nyo)001:702: bstan / brag dmar bya skyibs can du grogs sh+aakya mee tri dang /
NK128(nyo)001:703: sh+aakya bshes gnyen gnyis dang lhan gcig par byon te /
NK128(nyo)001:704: slob dpon chen po pra b+ha ha sti las rab
NK128(nyo)001:705: tu byung ba gsol pas ma gnang bar kun dga'
NK128(nyo)001:706: bo las rab tu byung bar lung gnang zhing /
NK128(nyo)001:707: rnal 'byor yo ga'i skor rnams gsan /
NK128(nyo)001:708: a su ra'i brag phug tu byon te gnas brtan
NK128(nyo)001:709: nyi ma gung pa dang ldan cig par kun dga'
NK128(nyo)001:710: bo las rab tu byung zhing /
NK128(nyo)001:711: sa lhas chos gos ngur smrig phul ba sogs thang yig tu bshad /
NK128(nyo)001:712: rnam thar gzhan du pra b+ha ha sti las rab
NK128(nyo)001:713: tu byung bar yang bshad cing gu ru sh+aakya seng
NK128(nyo)001:714: ger grags shing rab tu byung ba ste mdzad pa
NK128(nyo)001:715: lnga pa'o // mdor na kun dga' bo las 'dul
NK128(nyo)001:716: ba mdo sde mngon pa'i skor mtha' dag gsan nas
NK128(nyo)001:717: bo d+ha'i yul dur khrod sku la rdzogs su bzhugs
NK128(nyo)001:718: te nyi ma 'od zer du grags /
NK128(nyo)001:719: 'og min chos kyi dbyings kyi pho brang du byon
NK128(nyo)001:720: nas bcom ldan 'das dpal kun tu bzang po la
NK128(nyo)001:721: rdzogs pa chen po'i rgyud ma lus pa gsan /
NK128(nyo)001:722: kha che'i yul gsang lam bsnol ma'i dur khrod bde
NK128(nyo)001:723: chen brdal du byon nas blo ldan mchog sred du
NK128(nyo)001:724: grags / mkha' dbyings rnam dag gi klong du ston
NK128(nyo)001:725: pa rdo rje sems dpa' las bskyed pa ma h+aa
NK128(nyo)001:726: yo ga'i chos rnams rdzogs par gsan /
NK128(nyo)001:727: bal yul lhun 'grub brtsegs kyi dur khrod du bzhugs te seng ge sgra sgrog tu grags /
NK128(nyo)001:728: bkod pa lhun 'grub kyi pho brang du sku bzhi'i
NK128(nyo)001:729: ston pa kun tu 'chang la spyi ti yo ga'i
NK128(nyo)001:731: za hor gyi yul dur khrod lang ka brtsegs su bzhugs te pad+ma sam+b+ha grags /
NK128(nyo)001:732: dga' rab rdo rje las rdzogs chen snying thig gi rgyud sems klong gi skor rnams gsan /
NK128(nyo)001:733: o rgyan gyi yul dur khrod pad+ma brtsegs su bzhugs
NK128(nyo)001:734: shing rigs ldan bde ba bzang skyong las a nu
NK128(nyo)001:735: yo ga'i rgyud dang sgyu 'phrul sde brgyad sogs gsan
NK128(nyo)001:736: / li'i yul lo ka brtsegs pa'i dur khrod du bzhugs te /
NK128(nyo)001:737: rdo rje gro lod du grags /
NK128(nyo)001:738: bde chen gsang lam bsnol ma'i dur khrod du dge
NK128(nyo)001:739: slong ma kun dga' smon lam zhes yongs su grags
NK128(nyo)001:740: la / gzhan du gsang ba ye shes nyi zla
NK128(nyo)001:741: dngos grub las kyi dbang chen sogs du mar grags
NK128(nyo)001:743: sku lus h'u yig tu bsgyur ba zhal du mid
NK128(nyo)001:744: nas gsang bar phyung ste nang dbang bskur zhing snang
NK128(nyo)001:745: ba mtha' yas kyi sku phyi tshe'i rig 'dzin /
NK128(nyo)001:746: spyan ras gzigs kyi sku nang phyag chen rig 'dzin /
NK128(nyo)001:747: rta mgrin dbang gi sku gsang ba dregs can 'dul ba'i dbang thob /
NK128(nyo)001:748: bkod pa lhun grub tu rdo rje chos sam rdo
NK128(nyo)001:749: rje snying po rig 'dzin rgyal po kun dza ra
NK128(nyo)001:750: la yongs 'dzin dge ba'i bshes gnyen gyi dbang nas
NK128(nyo)001:751: bsdud pa'i khrom dbang bar rnams gsan te /
NK128(nyo)001:752: gser gling dben skyong gi phug par rig 'dzin sh+ri seng ha las don gyi ngo sprod gsan /
NK128(nyo)001:753: s+aa la'i yul dur khrod gsang chen rol par bzhugs /
NK128(nyo)001:754: gsang mtshan thod 'phreng rtsal du grags /
NK128(nyo)001:755: lha'i bu tshangs pa gdong bzhir sprul nas rgya nag
NK128(nyo)001:756: ri bo rtse lngar 'phags pa 'jam dpal gyi drung
NK128(nyo)001:757: du byon te / rtsis gter nas 'byin par gsol
NK128(nyo)001:758: ba btab cing gter nas phyung ste rtsis sgo brgyad
NK128(nyo)001:760: bshan pa'i grong khyer du rigs ngan gyi bu ka
NK128(nyo)001:761: ti ra sprul nas gsod gcod kyi sgo nas 'gro
NK128(nyo)001:762: don mdzad / dur khrod phung lung nag por byon
NK128(nyo)001:763: te mu stegs kha la me 'bar dang lhan cig
NK128(nyo)001:764: par sde brgyad dam la btags te bstan srung drag
NK128(nyo)001:765: sngags kyi skor mang po mdzad /
NK128(nyo)001:766: bya rgod phung po'i rir gdul zhing gzigs shing 'khrungs
NK128(nyo)001:767: yul rda na ko shar byon nas gsang sngags mkha'
NK128(nyo)001:768: 'gro'i skad kyis gsungs shing mkha' 'gro rnams dbang du
NK128(nyo)001:769: bsdus za hor gyi yul gdul byar mkhyen nas man+d+ha
NK128(nyo)001:770: ra ba la rjes su dgongs nas pho brang du
NK128(nyo)001:771: byon nas chos gsungs pa la za hor rgyal blon
NK128(nyo)001:772: gyis mtho mtshams te gson bsregs byas pa rdzu 'phrul
NK128(nyo)001:773: gyis btul zhing dad par byas te sa bka' 'dus
NK128(nyo)001:774: kyi chos 'khor bskor nas za hor gyi yul khams
NK128(nyo)001:775: chos la bkod cing rgyal po gtsug lag 'dzin gyi
NK128(nyo)001:776: skye rgyud gsungs / man d+ha ra ba las rgyar
NK128(nyo)001:777: khrid de m+aa ra ti kar byon te zla ba
NK128(nyo)001:778: gsum du tshe sgrub pas tshe dpag med mdun gyi
NK128(nyo)001:779: nam mkhar byon te yab yum gnyis kyi spyi bor
NK128(nyo)001:780: bum pa bzhag cing dbang bskur bas tshe'ii rig 'dzin
NK128(nyo)001:781: grub ste 'ja' lus rdo rje'i sku brnyes /
NK128(nyo)001:782: ko ta la'i yul g.ya' ri gangs kyi brag phug
NK128(nyo)001:783: tu rgyal po nu sha tu pa'i don mdzad cing
NK128(nyo)001:784: man d+he bzang mo rjes su bzung /
NK128(nyo)001:785: grong khyer me tog rgyas par mu stegs kyi rgyal po a shwa kar bsod snyoms mdzad pa /
NK128(nyo)001:786: rgyal pos til mar gyis zangs bkang ba'i nang du
NK128(nyo)001:787: btsos pa pad+ma'i steng na bzhugs pa'i rdzu 'phrul gyi
NK128(nyo)001:788: dad par mdzad cing rgyal por sdig sbyong gi thabs
NK128(nyo)001:789: bstan / dge slong dbang po'i sder sprul te ban+de'i yul dang sing+ga la'i yul du 'gro don mdzad /
NK128(nyo)001:790: b+hang ga la'i rgyal po nor bu 'od ldan btul te rgyal srid skyongs /
NK128(nyo)001:791: dom+b+hi he ru kar sprul te skye bdun gyi sha drang /
NK128(nyo)001:792: bir wa par sprul te chang 'tshong bi na sa'i don mdzad /
NK128(nyo)001:793: o rgyan gyi yul du man d+ha ra ba dang
NK128(nyo)001:794: lhan cig byon pas rgyal po'i chad pas gson bsregs
NK128(nyo)001:795: byas pa la / til mar gyis mtsho dbus pad
NK128(nyo)001:796: sdong rtsar yab yum snyoms 'jug gi rol pa bstan
NK128(nyo)001:797: nas rgyal blon 'khor bcas dad par gyur nas /
NK128(nyo)001:798: bka' 'dus kyi bshad sgrub sgo nas rgyal blon btsun
NK128(nyo)001:799: mo 'bangs dang bcas pa'i tshom bu lnga brgya lhag
NK128(nyo)001:801: lnga thub can gyi yul du byon te bal 'bangs
NK128(nyo)001:802: ka la sing+ng+hi rjes su bzung zhing slob dpon h'u
NK128(nyo)001:803: ka ra la bka' 'dus kyi rgyud lnga gsungs /
NK128(nyo)001:804: kha che'i yul khams chos la bkod pa sogs sems
NK128(nyo)001:805: can gyi don du bka' thub sna tshogs pa'i mdzad
NK128(nyo)001:806: pa drug pa'o // de nas zangs gling gi yul
NK128(nyo)001:807: du mu stegs kyi ston pa lnga brgya dang bgro
NK128(nyo)001:808: gleng byas pas mu stegs rnams kyi ma thub par
NK128(nyo)001:810: mkha' 'gro bdud 'dul mas bse sgrom gtad cing mu
NK128(nyo)001:811: stegs 'dul bar bsgos pas mkha' 'gro'i ngan sngags zhag
NK128(nyo)001:812: bdun gyis mu stegs kyi steng du thog phab ste
NK128(nyo)001:813: pha cher kha dag par gyur cing /
NK128(nyo)001:814: mi shi pa rnams nang pa'i bstan pa la btsud /
NK128(nyo)001:815: gzhan yang gser gling du mu stegs kyi rgyal po
NK128(nyo)001:816: nam mkha'i shugs can rdzu 'phrul gyis btul ba sogs
NK128(nyo)001:817: bdud dpung 'joms pa'i mdzad pa bdun pa'o //
NK128(nyo)001:818: gzhan yang ka ma ru pa dang /
NK128(nyo)001:829: klu'i yul sogs thams cad du 'gro don grangs med
NK128(nyo)001:830: pa mdzad cing gtsug lag khang chen po 'bum tsho
NK128(nyo)001:831: brgya dang phra mo'i bye ba dgu khri stong bcu
NK128(nyo)001:832: gsum bzhengs / de nas ri bo ta la'i rtser
NK128(nyo)001:833: dgongs pa mdzad cing rdo rje gdan du mu stegs
NK128(nyo)001:834: pa 'dul phyir bde mchog dus kyi snying por sprul
NK128(nyo)001:835: te rgyal po btul zhing bstan pa'i so nam mdzad
NK128(nyo)001:836: cing rab tu gnas pa'i me tog gtor /
NK128(nyo)001:837: gsung rab rnams bris shing bstan pa sor btsud de
NK128(nyo)001:838: thub chen sh+aakya seng ge'i mdzad pa bskyangs shing bstan
NK128(nyo)001:840: li kha ra shing 'phel gyi gtsug lag khang du
NK128(nyo)001:841: byon te mdo sngags kyi bstan gnyis rgyas par mdzad
NK128(nyo)001:842: / phyag rgya chen po'i rig 'dzin grub phyir rgya
NK128(nyo)001:843: bod kyi sa mtshams seng ge gnam mchong 'dra ba'i
NK128(nyo)001:844: ri la bzhugs te bsam gtan mdzad /
NK128(nyo)001:845: bal yul shing kun gyi gtsug lag khang du bam mo sh+aakya de wa rjes su bzung /
NK128(nyo)001:846: yang le shod kyi brag phug tu byon nas gter kha bye ba 'bum khri sbed par 'gros shing /
NK128(nyo)001:847: bar chod rnam bzhi bzlog pa'i mgur gsungs te bar
NK128(nyo)001:848: chod kyi g.yul las rgyal zhing yang phur zung 'jug
NK128(nyo)001:849: gi lam la brten nas mchog gi dngos grub phyag
NK128(nyo)001:850: rgya chen po'i rig 'dzin grub cing /
NK128(nyo)001:851: sku'i bkod pa sna tshogs kyis 'gro ba'i don mdzad de /
NK128(nyo)001:852: chos smra rin chen brtsegs dang /
NK128(nyo)001:855: pad+ma grub pa'i blo gros dang /
NK128(nyo)001:858: mgon po stobs kyi dbang phyug bir wa pa dang /
NK128(nyo)001:860: khye'u chung mkha' lding rtsal dang /
NK128(nyo)001:861: rtogs pa mchog gi dbang phyug sa ra ha dang /
NK128(nyo)001:867: pad+ma don yon zhags pa dang /
NK128(nyo)001:870: rigs ldan pad+ma dkar po dang /
NK128(nyo)001:872: pad+ma thod phreng rtsal te tshul sna tshogs su bstan
NK128(nyo)001:873: nas sems can gyi don mdzad cing bal yul tsha
NK128(nyo)001:874: ba tsha shod du byon te chu mig byang chub
NK128(nyo)001:875: ring mor bsgrub par mdzad dus sa bdag ma bzhi
NK128(nyo)001:876: dam la btags / ko sha tsan dan gling du
NK128(nyo)001:877: byon nas phu la ha rir bzhugs skabs gsang bdag
NK128(nyo)001:878: gi lung bzhin rgyal po'i khab kyi nub phyogs kyi
NK128(nyo)001:879: dur khrod kyi lho nub mtshams nas lcags sdig mgo
NK128(nyo)001:880: dgu rwa bco brgyad pa'i gzugs las phur pa'i chos
NK128(nyo)001:882: slar yang rgya gar rdo rje gdan du rgyal po
NK128(nyo)001:883: nyi ma seng ge'i bla mchod la byon pa sogs
NK128(nyo)001:884: de dag ni sangs rgyas byang chub kyi mdzad pa
NK128(nyo)001:885: brgyad pa'o // dgu pa chos kyi 'khor lo bskor
NK128(nyo)001:886: ba'i mdzad pa ni snga phyi thams cad du chos
NK128(nyo)001:887: kyi 'khor lo rgya cher bskor mod kyang /
NK128(nyo)001:888: myang mdzad rnam thar bstod par /
NK128(nyo)001:889: na lan rda tu chos kyi 'khor lo bskor /
NK128(nyo)001:891: gzhan du rgya bod thams cad dang /
NK128(nyo)001:892: khyad par rten 'brel gyi che bas bod yul du
NK128(nyo)001:893: chos 'khor bskor ba'i mdzad par bsdus kyang rung ngo
NK128(nyo)001:894: // bcu pa brtul zhugs kyi spyod pa mdzad tshul yang /
NK128(nyo)001:895: khab nas byung ste bsil tshal du brtul zhugs kyi
NK128(nyo)001:896: spyod pa mdzad nas bzung dur khrod chen po brgyad
NK128(nyo)001:897: sogs su spyod tshul du ma bstan pa dang /
NK128(nyo)001:898: nyang mdzad rnam thar bstod par /
NK128(nyo)001:899: o rgyan mkha' 'gro'i gling du spyod pa mdzad //
NK128(nyo)001:900: chu bo gyen ldog nyi zla gdong la mnan //
NK128(nyo)001:901: rdzu 'phrul stag la chibs te nam mkhar gshegs //
NK128(nyo)001:903: bod yul du lha 'dre btul tshul yang brtul zhugs
NK128(nyo)001:904: kyi spyod par 'du ba yin pas mdzad pa bcu
NK128(nyo)001:906: de lta bu'i mdzad pa dgu dang bcu pa gnyis
NK128(nyo)001:907: gong 'og thams cad du bstan par 'dod pa la
NK128(nyo)001:908: / 'di yan chod kyis rgya gar du lo gsum stong drug brgya bzhugs pa'i bar la dngos dang /
NK128(nyo)001:910: sprul pa'i tshul gyis thub pa'i bstan pa nyin mo
NK128(nyo)001:911: ltar gsal bar mdzad pas na rgyan drug mchog gnyis
NK128(nyo)001:912: / grub brgya sogs kyi rnam thar gcig tu bsdus
NK128(nyo)001:913: kyang 'di la 'gran par nus pa ma yin no
NK128(nyo)001:914: / // de nas bod du ji ltar byon pa'i tshul ni /
NK128(nyo)001:915: mnga' bdag khri srong lde'u btsun gyis thog mar bod
NK128(nyo)001:916: du mkhan po spyan 'dren pa'i pho nya sba mi
NK128(nyo)001:918: gnyags dz+ny+aa na ku m+aa ra gnyis la so sor
NK128(nyo)001:919: g.yog gsum re dang bcas par gser phye bre re
NK128(nyo)001:920: bskur zhing / bka' 'phrin bskur ba 'di lta ste /
NK128(nyo)001:921: bstan pa rin chen mchog tu gdugs khegs pa //
NK128(nyo)001:922: mtha' 'khob mun pa'i gling du skar tsam med //
NK128(nyo)001:923: sa steng gnas pa'i rab rib nyid kyis sol //
NK128(nyo)001:924: lha srin ma byed 'dre yi gzigs pas 'khums //
NK128(nyo)001:926: mkhan po dgyes bzhin byon te gsang phung mnga' bdag dang /
NK128(nyo)001:927: mjal zhing rim gyis bsam yas su phyag phebs te /
NK128(nyo)001:928: me mo glang la bsam yas gtsug lag khang gi sa ris bcad /
NK128(nyo)001:929: rgyal po nyid kyis brkos pa zhag gsum thon te rgyal pos gsol zhing mkhan pos smon lam mdzad /
NK128(nyo)001:930: de nas rtsis rmang btsugs shing brtsegs pas /
NK128(nyo)001:931: +aar+ya pa lo'i se phung la gnas pa'i klus se
NK128(nyo)001:932: phung gcod par ma bzod par lha 'dre thams cad
NK128(nyo)001:933: sbran te nyin mo brtsigs pa thams cad nub mo
NK128(nyo)001:934: bshig go // der rgyal po thugs chad de mkhan po la zhus pas /
NK128(nyo)001:935: mkhan chen dus gsum mkhyen pa des sngon gyis smon
NK128(nyo)001:936: lam btab tshul gyi lo rgyus dang bcas te g+hu
NK128(nyo)001:937: ru pad+ma spyan drongs shig par lung bstan pa ltar
NK128(nyo)001:938: / mnga' bdag gi rba mi khri bzher /
NK128(nyo)001:941: shud bu dpal seng bzhi la gser phye bre re
NK128(nyo)001:942: dang gser gyi pa tra re bskur te rgya gar
NK128(nyo)001:944: g+hu ru chen po rdo rje gdan du rgyal po
NK128(nyo)001:945: nyi ma seng ge'i mchod gnas su bzhugs pa'i yon
NK128(nyo)001:946: mchod kyi drung du bgrod de bka' 'phrin gser dang
NK128(nyo)001:947: bcas phul ba la brten nas /
NK128(nyo)001:948: sngon gyi smon lam gyi mthu dgag tu med pa'i
NK128(nyo)001:949: tshul gyis dgyes bzhin du lam du zhugs te byon
NK128(nyo)001:950: nas spyan 'dren pa rnams sngon du btang ngo der
NK128(nyo)001:951: slob dpon chen pos bal yul du zla ba gsum
NK128(nyo)001:952: bzhugs te bal po b+ha su d+ha ra rjes su
NK128(nyo)001:953: bzung / e yi gtsug lag khang /
NK128(nyo)001:956: shing kun rnams la gter sbed cing bod du byon
NK128(nyo)001:957: pas rgya bal gyi ltas log cing pan chen rnams
NK128(nyo)001:959: mkha' 'gro sde bzhis ser sna'i bshol btab pa la /
NK128(nyo)001:960: lan du mgur gsungs shing bal mo sh+aakya de war ma 'ongs lung bstan mdzad /
NK128(nyo)001:961: bal yul nyi ma khud kyi mtsho khar bod rgyal
NK128(nyo)001:962: po'i skyar shog pa nam mkha'i snying po sogs bdun
NK128(nyo)001:963: dang mjal nas sngon du bardzangasa /
NK128(nyo)001:964: o rgyan chen pos nam mkha' la byon te mang yul gung thang du byon pa dang mjal /
NK128(nyo)001:965: gser phye bre gang phul ba mang yul dang bal
NK128(nyo)001:966: yul phyogs la gtor ba la 'phangs sems skyes pa
NK128(nyo)001:967: mkhyen nas gseg ma gser du bsgyur ba gnang /
NK128(nyo)001:968: mang yul ston la khar zhang zhung dgra lha dza mun btul te rdo rje g.yu bun mar btags /
NK128(nyo)001:969: mkhar nag la khar gnam sman dkar mo btul zhing
NK128(nyo)001:970: sha med rdo rje g.yu sgron du btags 'o yug
NK128(nyo)001:971: bre mo la khar brtan ma bcu gnyis kyis thog
NK128(nyo)001:972: phab pa btul zhing bye tshang rdzogs dkar du rdo
NK128(nyo)001:973: rje legs pa 'khor bcas kyis bsus /
NK128(nyo)001:974: sham b+hu lung du sham bu btul zhing sku gnyen
NK128(nyo)001:975: thang lha dam btags 'phan yul du byang sman rnams
NK128(nyo)001:976: btul / glang sgrom du bla med don rdzogs kyi sgrub pa mdzad nas pho bdud nyer gcig btul /
NK128(nyo)001:977: khams kyis bla ba rkang gcig tu the'u rang rnams
NK128(nyo)001:978: dam la btags shing khams kyi seng ge brag tu
NK128(nyo)001:979: g.ya' spang skyes gcig drag por rigs lngar khros nas
NK128(nyo)001:980: btul / chu bo ri dang mkha' ri ma mo dang bsen mo btul /
NK128(nyo)001:981: gtsang gi bsil ma la khar sman mo dang lha sman btul /
NK128(nyo)001:982: gam pa chu mig tu dge bsnyen dang /
NK128(nyo)001:983: bye ma rab khar sde brgyad dang /
NK128(nyo)001:984: ro hor ma yams dang rong dong lung nag tu srin po dang /
NK128(nyo)001:986: g.yu 'dzin phug mor pho rgyud dang /
NK128(nyo)001:987: dung mdog brag dmar du dri za dang /
NK128(nyo)001:988: gangs te ser rgyu skar nyer brgyad dang /
NK128(nyo)001:989: star sgo gangs su gza' brgyad rnams btul /
NK128(nyo)001:990: bu ler lha 'dres tshogs 'khor bshams shing glo bor ldan ma spun dgu dang /
NK128(nyo)001:994: sku la mkha' ri gangs rnams su byon te bzhi bdag rnams btul /
NK128(nyo)001:995: slar yang rgyal po'i bskyar shog dang mjal zhing stod
NK128(nyo)001:996: lung 'gram bu tshal du 'dzom pa'i dus btab nas
NK128(nyo)001:997: kha la brag rir dgun thog tsam bzhugs shing btsan
NK128(nyo)001:998: rnams btul / zul phug tu bdud gza' dam sri btul /
NK128(nyo)001:999: g.ya' ri gangs su dpyid bzhugs shing ja rong 'gong po so sha /
NK128(nyo)001:1000: dam sri btul ba sogs mdor na dregs pa can
NK128(nyo)001:1001: de dag gis rang stobs kyi cho 'phrul ci nus
NK128(nyo)001:1002: bstan pa thams cad phyag rgya gnyen pos zil gyis
NK128(nyo)001:1003: mnan zhing dam la btags te kun kyang srung mar
NK128(nyo)001:1004: bka' bgos shing gter byang so sor gtad do //
NK128(nyo)001:1005: de nas lha sa brgyud stod lung mdor blon po
NK128(nyo)001:1006: lha bzang klu dpal phebs bsur byon pa dang mjal
NK128(nyo)001:1007: zhing gzhong pa lha chur grub chu bton /
NK128(nyo)001:1008: de nas rim bzhin brgyud de zung mkhar lo hi
NK128(nyo)001:1009: ta 'gram gyi tshal du mnga' bdag rgyal po btsun
NK128(nyo)001:1011: rnga shon klu 'bag seng shon sogs bkod pa du
NK128(nyo)001:1012: mas bsus pa'i dus yon mchod gnyis phyag la ma
NK128(nyo)001:1013: 'dums pa'i tshe / dus gsum sangs rgyas mnga' sgo 'grims //
NK128(nyo)001:1014: zhes sogs nga che nga btsan gyi mgur gsungs shing /
NK128(nyo)001:1015: phyag sor las rdzu 'phrul gyis me sbar te rgyal
NK128(nyo)001:1016: po'i na bza' bsregs pas kun gyis ma bzod par
NK128(nyo)001:1017: phyag btsal zhing / sdig sbyongs su rdo rje'i mchod
NK128(nyo)001:1018: rten lnga bzhengs shing mchod rten re la gter kha
NK128(nyo)001:1020: de nas ston zla ra ba'i tshes gcig la bsam yas su phyag phebs te /
NK128(nyo)001:1021: mkhan slob rgyal po zhal 'dzom zhing sa gzhi byin
NK128(nyo)001:1022: gyis brlab par bka' bgros shing sa gnad kyi me
NK128(nyo)001:1023: btsa' rnams bsdam dgos par gsungs te /
NK128(nyo)001:1024: gu ru nyid mal gror byon te klu gter bcug
NK128(nyo)001:1025: cing de'i kha gnon du glo bo ge dkar bzhengs
NK128(nyo)001:1026: / has po ri'i rtse mor bod kyi lha srin
NK128(nyo)001:1027: thams cad skam rlon chas dang rdzas bsdus te snang
NK128(nyo)001:1028: srid zil gnon gyi mgur bzhes shing nam mkha' la
NK128(nyo)001:1029: 'phur nas rdo rje'i 'gros mdzad pa'i grib ma gar
NK128(nyo)001:1030: byung du rtsig rmang gi ri mo byas pa la
NK128(nyo)001:1031: lha 'dre mi gsum gyis brtsigs te bsam yas mi
NK128(nyo)001:1032: 'gyur lhun gyis grub pa'i gtsug lag khang chen po
NK128(nyo)001:1033: rten dang brten par bcas pa bzhengs /
NK128(nyo)001:1034: mchims phur klu 'dul mdzad cing mal gror byon /
NK128(nyo)001:1035: mnga' bdag dang klu gnyis grogs su sbrel /
NK128(nyo)001:1036: de ltar lo lnga la gtsug lag khang legs par
NK128(nyo)001:1037: 'byongs shing lha 'dres cong 'dogs su ma bcug par
NK128(nyo)001:1038: slob dpon gyi mchims phur yang dag gi sgrub pa
NK128(nyo)001:1039: mdzad de / ru lu'i dbyangs kyis mi ma yin rnams mgo bskor te btags /
NK128(nyo)001:1040: dkor srung su la 'chol bgros pa'i tshe /
NK128(nyo)001:1041: g+hu ru'i lung bzhin b+ha ta hor yul gyi sgom
NK128(nyo)001:1042: grwa bcom pa'i nor rjes su pe kar 'brangs pa
NK128(nyo)001:1043: / pe kar gling du phyi nang gsang ba'i rten
NK128(nyo)001:1044: brtsugs shing dam la bzhag ste srung mar bskos pa
NK128(nyo)001:1045: / / rta'i lo mjug dgun zla 'bring po rgyu
NK128(nyo)001:1046: skar rgyal 'char ba la mkhan slob thun mong du
NK128(nyo)001:1047: me tog 'thor zhing khyad par mkhan chen bo d+hi
NK128(nyo)001:1048: sa t+was rab gnas lan gsum du mdzad de /
NK128(nyo)001:1049: slar yang lug lo dgun zla ra ba'i bco lnga
NK128(nyo)001:1050: zla ba gzas bsgribs pa'i nyin slob dpon chen po
NK128(nyo)001:1051: pad+mas rdo rje dbyings kyi sgrub pa zhag bdun thon
NK128(nyo)001:1052: nas mnga' bdag rgyal po la dbang bskur zhing /
NK128(nyo)001:1053: rab tu gnas pa'i me tog 'thor bar mdzad pa'i
NK128(nyo)001:1054: tshe thang yig las bshad pa ltar ngo mtshar gyi
NK128(nyo)001:1055: ltas du ma rab tu snang bar 'gyur ro //
NK128(nyo)001:1056: gzhan yang lha sa dang khra 'brug la sogs pa'ii
NK128(nyo)001:1057: gtsug lag khang rnying pa rnams la rab gnas gso
NK128(nyo)001:1058: ba dang bcas te gtsug lag khang brgya rtsa brgyad
NK128(nyo)001:1059: la slob dpon chen po pad+mas me tog 'thor zhing
NK128(nyo)001:1060: rab tu gnas pa mdzad ces grags so //
NK128(nyo)001:1061: de ltar gtsug lag khang legs par grub nas mkhan
NK128(nyo)001:1062: slob gnyis kyis rgyal po la rgya gar du 'byon
NK128(nyo)001:1063: par gsol bas mdo sngags kyi bstan pa bod du
NK128(nyo)001:1064: ma dar gyi bar du bzhugs par gsol ba btab
NK128(nyo)001:1065: pa bzhin zhal gyis bzhes te bod yul du chos
NK128(nyo)001:1066: khrims sdoms shig par gsung pa ltar chos khrims dam
NK128(nyo)001:1067: par bcas so // de rjes bod phrug shes rab
NK128(nyo)001:1068: can kha cig bsdus te mkhan slob gnyis kyis sgra
NK128(nyo)001:1069: slob par brtsams kyang ma shes par brten slob dpon
NK128(nyo)001:1070: chen pos bee ro dang ska cog lung bstan pa
NK128(nyo)001:1071: ltar bkug ste sgra bslabs shing mkhas par shes pa
NK128(nyo)001:1072: par bcas so // dang / sgra bsgyur gling du
NK128(nyo)001:1073: mkhan slob lo ts+aa gsum dang bcas par rgyal pos
NK128(nyo)001:1074: gser phye ko to ra gang gi man+dala dang bcas
NK128(nyo)001:1076: glang gi lo mjug nas stag gi lo mgo'i bar
NK128(nyo)001:1077: du slob dpon chen po pad+mas gsang sngags phyi pa
NK128(nyo)001:1078: kri yog sde gsum cog ro klu'i rgyal mtshan gyis
NK128(nyo)001:1079: bsgyur nas gsungs / gsang sngags nang pa yo ga
NK128(nyo)001:1080: rnam gsum lo chen pa bee ro tsa nas bsgyur
NK128(nyo)001:1081: bsgyur nas gsungs / te gsungs / thun mong ba
NK128(nyo)001:1082: mdo gzungs 'ga' zhig dang na rag dong sprugs cha
NK128(nyo)001:1083: lag dang bcas pa bsgyur zhing /
NK128(nyo)001:1084: mnga' bdag gi thugs dam yang dong sprugs kho nar
NK128(nyo)001:1085: mdzad pas dgung lo bcu gsum gyi sku tshe bsrings
NK128(nyo)001:1086: so // gzhan yang bka' 'dus dang rdor dbyings /
NK128(nyo)001:1088: sgyu 'phrul sde brgyad sogs kyang bsgyur ro //
NK128(nyo)001:1089: mkhan po b+ho d+hi sat+wa dang ban+de ye shes sdes
NK128(nyo)001:1090: 'dul ba lung sde bzhi dang sher phyin skor dkon
NK128(nyo)001:1093: mkhan po dang ska ba dpal brtsegs kyis bya spyod
NK128(nyo)001:1094: rnal 'byor gyi rgyud sde 'ga' zhig kyang bsgyur ro
NK128(nyo)001:1095: // slar yang mnga' bdag thugs ma tshim par sad
NK128(nyo)001:1096: mi mi bdun sogs lo ts+aa ba brgya la sgra
NK128(nyo)001:1097: bslabs shing bkur sti dang bcas te rgya gar bardzangasa
NK128(nyo)001:1098: so de rnams kyi nang nas mchog tu gyur pa
NK128(nyo)001:1099: bee ro dang rtsang legs grub gnyis rdo rje gdan
NK128(nyo)001:1100: sogs rgya gar gyi yul thams cad nyul zhing dam
NK128(nyo)001:1102: rgya gar mkhas pa sra warta nas bud+d+ha gub+ta'i bar
NK128(nyo)001:1103: gyi pan+di ta chen po nyer lnga'i zhal mjal zhing
NK128(nyo)001:1105: legs grub sngon la yongs pas lam du gum /
NK128(nyo)001:1106: bee ros slar yang man ngag sems sde'i skor rnams
NK128(nyo)001:1107: gsan cing rkang mgyogs kyang grub ste gcan 'phrang pas
NK128(nyo)001:1108: glag ma rnyed par bod du rtol te /
NK128(nyo)001:1109: mnga' bdag gis kyang dbu skra them par bkram nas spyan drangs te chibs dang gser dngul gyi man+dala /
NK128(nyo)001:1110: phyag dang bcas te gsol ba btab pa ltar rgyud
NK128(nyo)001:1111: lung man ngag gi chos kyi bdud rtsis rgyal po'i
NK128(nyo)001:1112: thugs kyi bum bzang gtams par mdzad de /
NK128(nyo)001:1113: 'on kyang rgya gar nas phra ma byung bar brten
NK128(nyo)001:1114: blon po'i ngor bee ror bardzusa pa'i sbrang ban chur
NK128(nyo)001:1115: bskur zhing / bee ro nyid bar khang gi ka
NK128(nyo)001:1116: ba'i 'chol gyis khongs su sbas te nyin bar mtshan
NK128(nyo)001:1117: nyid dang mtshan mo gsang sngags rdo rje'i theg pa
NK128(nyo)001:1118: bskur zhing / bsgyur ro // de'i tshe btsun mo
NK128(nyo)001:1119: dmar rgyan dang bdud blon rnams gros 'cham zhing bee
NK128(nyo)001:1120: ro yod par rig ste bee ro tsa na re
NK128(nyo)001:1121: zhig rgyal mo tsha ba'i rong du spyugs shing /
NK128(nyo)001:1122: tsha ba'i rong du rgyal po mdo gzher nag pos mchod gnas su bskur te /
NK128(nyo)001:1123: rgyal mo g.yu sgras lo ts+aa byas te mdo sngags kyi chos mang du gsungs so //
NK128(nyo)001:1124: de nas rgyal pos nam mkha'i snying po sogs dge
NK128(nyo)001:1125: slong mi lnga rgya gar du bardzangasa pa slob dpon
NK128(nyo)001:1126: h'u ka ra dang mjal te yang dag gi dbang
NK128(nyo)001:1127: rgyud rnams gsan te grub pa brnyes nas bod du
NK128(nyo)001:1128: byon / rje la dbang bskur zhing man ngag bshad
NK128(nyo)001:1129: pa la bon blon gyi spyug byung ste re zhig
NK128(nyo)001:1130: lho brag mkhar chur gshegs so //
NK128(nyo)001:1131: de rjes bon chos gnyis ka bsgyur ba'i tshul mdzad cing mchod rten dang bong so brtsigs /
NK128(nyo)001:1132: ska cog rma gsum rgya gar du barjangasa /
NK128(nyo)001:1133: bee ro'i lung bzhin bi ma la spyan drangs te bsnyen bkur mdzad /
NK128(nyo)001:1134: gzhan yang pan chen mang du spyan drangs te dam
NK128(nyo)001:1135: pa'i chos bsgyur zhing bon yang bsgyur bas bon chog
NK128(nyo)001:1136: la rgya gar gyi pan+di ta rnams thugs 'khangs te
NK128(nyo)001:1137: rgya gar du log par brtsams par brten /
NK128(nyo)001:1138: chos bon gnyis rtsod cing 'gran pas rgyal po chos la yid ches te bon bsnubs so //
NK128(nyo)001:1139: de nas bi ma la sogs pan chen rnams kyis chos gsungs shing /
NK128(nyo)001:1140: g.yu sgra snying pos mtshams sbyar ba la brten bee ro yang phyir byon /
NK128(nyo)001:1144: nam snying sogs lo pan brgya rtsa brgyad thams cad
NK128(nyo)001:1145: 'dus pa la mnga' bdag rgyal pos bkur sti rgya
NK128(nyo)001:1146: chen pos gsol ba btab cing mdo sngags kyi dam
NK128(nyo)001:1148: mkhan pos so sor thar pa'i sdom pa dang byang chub sems dpa'i thugs bskyed phog /
NK128(nyo)001:1149: slob dpon chen po sogs pan grub rnams kyis dbang
NK128(nyo)001:1150: rgyud man ngag bstan cing rig gnas sogs kyang bsgyur
NK128(nyo)001:1151: cing glegs bam la bris te /
NK128(nyo)001:1152: pan grub rnams kyis cho ga mi 'dra ba du
NK128(nyo)001:1153: ma'i sgo nas sku gsum thugs rten thams cad la
NK128(nyo)001:1154: rab tu gnas shing nyan bshad sgom sgrub kyis thub
NK128(nyo)001:1155: bstan gsal bar mdzad cing khyad par slob dpon chen
NK128(nyo)001:1158: rje 'bangs grogs gsum rnams la sgrub chen bka' brgyad
NK128(nyo)001:1159: kyi dbang bskur zhing rtogs grol dus gcig tu gyur
NK128(nyo)001:1160: pa ni dgu pa chos kyi 'khor bskor ba dang
NK128(nyo)001:1161: bcu pa brtul zhugs kyi mdzad pa'o //
NK128(nyo)001:1162: skabs der nam mkha'i snying po dang rgyal po 'khon byung ba la rdzu 'phrul bstan nas 'dums shing /
NK128(nyo)001:1166: lo pan rnams la gtang rag gi chos ston rgya
NK128(nyo)001:1167: cher btegs te rgya gar nas chos mi sdom par
NK128(nyo)001:1168: zhus shing pan chen rnams rang yul du byon /
NK128(nyo)001:1169: mkhan slob gnyis bod du bzhugs shing bi ma la rgya nag tu bzhud do //
NK128(nyo)001:1170: de'i tshe slob dpon chen po mchims phur dgongs pa
NK128(nyo)001:1171: la bzhugs dus mnga' bdag gi sras mo lha lcam
NK128(nyo)001:1172: pad+ma gsal tshe'i dus byas pa la skye rgyud lung
NK128(nyo)001:1173: bstan gsungs shing / dbus dang phyogs bzhi la sogs
NK128(nyo)001:1174: gter chen brgya rtsa brgyad dang gter phran bye ba
NK128(nyo)001:1175: sa ya sbas te gter ston dus rtags dang bcas
NK128(nyo)001:1176: pa lung bstan te gter ston rnams la zhal gdams
NK128(nyo)001:1177: bstan gsungs shing / gsungs / sku gsung thugs yon
NK128(nyo)001:1178: tan phrin las lnga sogs gtso bor gyur pa'i sgrubs
NK128(nyo)001:1179: gnas rnams su snga phyir zhabs kyis bcag shing lo
NK128(nyo)001:1180: zlar bzhugs te byin gyis brlabs nas ma 'ongs lung
NK128(nyo)001:1181: bstan gsungs shing / gsungs / bstan mdzad / mnga'
NK128(nyo)001:1182: bdag lnga bcu rtsa dgu 'brug lor zung mo mkhar
NK128(nyo)001:1183: du sku gshegs shing mkhan po yang byang chub gling
NK128(nyo)001:1184: bstan gsungs shing / gsungs / bstan mdzad / du
NK128(nyo)001:1185: gshegs so // de dag ni bstan pa mthar rgyas
NK128(nyo)001:1186: mi nub gter sbed kyi mdzad pa'i rim pa ste
NK128(nyo)001:1187: bstan gsungs shing / gsungs / bstan mdzad / du
NK128(nyo)001:1188: gshegs so // bcu gcig pa'o // de'i 'phros kyang
NK128(nyo)001:1190: slar yang rgyal sras mu tig btsan po'i don du bzhugs shing zhal gdams gsungs te zab chos gnang /
NK128(nyo)001:1191: khra 'brug tu bka' 'dus kyi dkyil 'khor zhal phye
NK128(nyo)001:1192: ste sgrub pa mdzad cing rje 'bangs rnams la dbang
NK128(nyo)001:1193: bskur / lha lcam man d+ha ra bas slob dpon la mtshan dpe'i sgo nas bstod cing /
NK128(nyo)001:1194: o rgyan sku tshab kyi phan yon zhus lan gsungs /
NK128(nyo)001:1195: rgyal sras lha rjer gter kha gtad cing /
NK128(nyo)001:1196: skye rgyud gsungs te skye bdun gyi phan yon bstan /
NK128(nyo)001:1197: btsan thang g.yu'i lha khang du ngang byung rgyal mo la khrid btab ste grol /
NK128(nyo)001:1198: shel brag tu skal ldan bud med gsum la zhal gdams gsungs shing /
NK128(nyo)001:1199: pe kar gyi cho 'phrul btul te dam la btags nas sgrub skor dang bcun gzir /
NK128(nyo)001:1200: gsungs shing gtsang po'i 'gram du drang srong smug 'od
NK128(nyo)001:1201: 'phro dang zhus lan mdzad de dam la bzhag cing
NK128(nyo)001:1202: bcos thabs dang ngan sngags mdzad /
NK128(nyo)001:1203: klu rnams kyang dam la btags shing mnan gtad kyi man ngag gsungs /
NK128(nyo)001:1204: bsam yas dbu rtser byon nas lha sras la brtse ba'i zhal ta gnang /
NK128(nyo)001:1205: srin yul du bzhud par dgongs te mang yul gung thang du snga 'gros bardzangasa /
NK128(nyo)001:1206: spre'u lo spre'u zla'i tshes bcur bsam yas nas chibs
NK128(nyo)001:1207: bskyod de zung mkhar rdo mchod thang du rje 'bangs
NK128(nyo)001:1208: la drang don gyi chos dang bla ma'i rnal 'byor
NK128(nyo)001:1209: gsungs / lha sar byon te zhal gdams gsungs shing gung thang la khar /
NK128(nyo)001:1214: yon bdag pho mo so sor zhal gdams dang spyir bslab bya gsungs /
NK128(nyo)001:1215: nam mkha' nas sprin dmar ser 'ja' 'od du 'khyil
NK128(nyo)001:1216: ba'i gseb nas rta rgyal ba la ha byung ba
NK128(nyo)001:1217: la chibs te slar yang rje 'bangs la brtse ba'i
NK128(nyo)001:1218: mgur gsungs / dpa' bo sde bzhis chibs sna drangs shing 'ja' 'od du khyil le bzhud do //
NK128(nyo)001:1219: de nas rje 'bangs rnams dad gus kyi sgo nas nyi zer la bltas pas bya rog dang /
NK128(nyo)001:1222: sbrang bu dang sro ma tsam gyi bar mthong zhing de nas mig gis ma mthong bar /
NK128(nyo)001:1223: las dag pa 'ga' zhig gi nyams snang du seng ga la'i gling dang srin po'i yul brgyud de /
NK128(nyo)001:1224: rnga yab dpal rir srin po'i rgyal po thod 'phreng
NK128(nyo)001:1225: rtsal gyi skur bzhugs nas srin po rnams la dam
NK128(nyo)001:1226: pa'i chos ston pa mthong bas phyi phyag mang du
NK128(nyo)001:1227: btsal te rje 'bangs rnams rang gnas su byon te
NK128(nyo)001:1228: / slob dpon gyis bstan pa'i chos la bshad sgrub dang thub bstan gus pas mchod par gyur to //
NK128(nyo)001:1229: de ltar gu ru chen po bod du bzhugs yun
NK128(nyo)001:1230: yang lugs sna tshogs su 'chad mod kyang 'dir rnam
NK128(nyo)001:1231: thar yang thang yig kho na dang mthun par btus
NK128(nyo)001:1232: shing / bzhugs yun kyang brgya dang bcu gcig tu bzhugs par 'chad la /
NK128(nyo)001:1233: de bzhin du rnam thar yang bsdus don tsam las
NK128(nyo)001:1234: rgyas par bri ma nus pas zhib par gzhan du
NK128(nyo)001:1235: blta bar bya'o // mdor na slob dpon chen po
NK128(nyo)001:1236: 'di nyid kyi rnam thar rgyas bsdus ji ltar snang
NK128(nyo)001:1237: yang de nyid mos gus kyi gsos su byas te
NK128(nyo)001:1238: gsol ba btab na byang chub la reg par 'gyur
NK128(nyo)001:1239: blta bar bya'o // ba ste / thang yig las /
NK128(nyo)001:1240: gu ru'i rnam thar rgyas bsdus gang 'thad pa //
NK128(nyo)001:1241: mthong thos mos gus tshad med bya ba gces //
NK128(nyo)001:1242: 'di la dad mos bstan pa'i mthar rgyas 'dzin //
NK128(nyo)001:1243: bla med byang chub sangs rgyas the tshom med //
NK128(nyo)001:1245: gser dngul snag tshas pad 'byung rnam thar bris //
NK128(nyo)001:1246: skyid sdug gang byung bdag gzhan 'gro don mdzad //
NK128(nyo)001:1247: ces gsungs pa ltar yin cing /
NK128(nyo)001:1249: gsol ba btab na bslu ba med par thugs rjes 'dzin nges pa yang yin te /
NK128(nyo)001:1251: gdung sems can la pad 'byung 'phags pa med //
NK128(nyo)001:1252: gsol ba 'debs la pad 'byung sgo nyal yod //
NK128(nyo)001:1254: ngan song skyes kyang nga rang slu ru yong //
NK128(nyo)001:1255: nga yi tshe la 'das drangs yod ma yin //
NK128(nyo)001:1256: dad ldan mi re'i mdun du pad 'byung re //
NK128(nyo)001:1258: thugs rje rgyun chad med do gsol ba thob //
NK128(nyo)001:1259: ces gsungs pa snying la bcangs nas blo gtad gcig
NK128(nyo)001:1260: chog tu byas te gsol ba btab na 'di phyi'i
NK128(nyo)001:1261: don chen 'grub par gdon mi za'o //
NK128(nyo)001:1262: de dag gis ston pa'i byung tshul mdo tsam bshad zin to //
NK128(nyo)001:1263: mang thos tsan dan ljon pa'i dga' tshal las /
NK128(nyo)001:1264: ngo mtshar gtam gyi dri bsung gsar pa dag /
NK128(nyo)001:1265: mos gus dri bzhon bsil bus legs bskyod pa //
NK128(nyo)001:1266: blo ldan bskal bzang yid la dga' ston ster //
NK128(nyo)001:1267: thub dbang mdzad pa'i nyin byed 'khor lo dang //
NK128(nyo)001:1268: pad 'byung rgyal ba'i rnam thar nya rgyas zla //
NK128(nyo)001:1269: shes bya'i lha lam yangs por gsal bkod pa //
NK128(nyo)001:1270: bstan 'gro'i rmongs mun sel ba'i dga' ston yin //
NK128(nyo)001:1271: thub bstan lung rtogs chos kyi ston pa la //
NK128(nyo)001:1272: dngos gcig chu zla'i gar gyi tshul ji ltar //
NK128(nyo)001:1273: shar yang gnyis med blo yi rtse gcig tu //
NK128(nyo)001:1274: dad pas yon tan brjod 'di yi rang byos //
NK128(nyo)001:1275: bar skabs kyi tshigs su bcad pa'o //
NK128(nyo)001:1276: spyi don gnyis pa bar du snga 'gyur gyi bstan pa byung tshul bshad pa ni /
NK128(nyo)001:1277: rgyas par chos 'byung rnams la blta bar bya zhing /
NK128(nyo)001:1278: 'dir mdo tsam smos na snga 'gyur rang skad la
NK128(nyo)001:1279: gzhi gdod ma'i sangs rgyas kun tu bzang po sku
NK128(nyo)001:1280: dang ye shes 'du 'bral med pa'i ngang nas /
NK128(nyo)001:1281: ston 'khor dgongs pa gnyis su med pa lhun 'grub
NK128(nyo)001:1282: 'od gsal rdzogs pa chen po'i ngang las ma g.yos
NK128(nyo)001:1283: bzhin du / rang snang longs spyod rdzogs pa'i sku
NK128(nyo)001:1284: rang shar te rigs lnga zhi khro'i dkyil 'khor gyi
NK128(nyo)001:1285: tshom bu grangs med pa sna tshogs su 'char ba
NK128(nyo)001:1286: nges pa lnga ldan gyi tshul du bzhugs pa'i rtsal
NK128(nyo)001:1287: las chu zla'i tshul gyis sprul pa mngon par snang
NK128(nyo)001:1289: rigs drug gi gnas su thub pa drug gi tshul gyis 'gro ba 'dren pa'i tshul ston cing /
NK128(nyo)001:1290: byin brlabs mchog gi sprul pa gsum dang /
NK128(nyo)001:1291: ye shes don dam pa'i sprul pa bcu gnyis sam
NK128(nyo)001:1292: ston pa bcu gnyis phun sum tshogs pa lnga ldan
NK128(nyo)001:1294: bstan pa bcu gnyis skyong bar mdzad pa ni 'di lta ste /
NK128(nyo)001:1295: dang po yul dga' ldan brtsegs kyi gnas pad+ma'i lte ba la /
NK128(nyo)001:1296: ston pa khye'u snang ba dam pa bsam gyis mi khyab pa /
NK128(nyo)001:1297: 'khor 'od snang gi sangs rgyas stong rtsa gnyis /
NK128(nyo)001:1298: bstan pa sgra thal 'gyur rtsa ba'i rgyud kyi chos /
NK128(nyo)001:1299: dus tshe lo dpag tu med pa'i dus su gsungs te /
NK128(nyo)001:1300: lha'i bu dga' byed dbang phyug dang /
NK128(nyo)001:1301: nyi ma rab tu snang byed gnyis kyis bka' bsdus so //
NK128(nyo)001:1306: bstan pa sku lnga'i rgyud kyi chos /
NK128(nyo)001:1307: dus tshe lo bye ba gcig thub pa'i tshe gsungs so //
NK128(nyo)001:1309: gnas drod gsher 'dus pa 'od kyi spungs par /
NK128(nyo)001:1310: ston pa 'jigs pa skyob pa'i yid /
NK128(nyo)001:1312: bstan pa 'khor ba dong sprugs rma bya mjing bsnol 'byung bzhi zad pa'i rgyud kyi chos /
NK128(nyo)001:1313: dus tshe lo 'bum pa'i tshe gsungs so //
NK128(nyo)001:1315: gnas chags 'byung mnga' ru snang bar /
NK128(nyo)001:1316: ston pa gzhon nu rol pa rnam par brtse ba /
NK128(nyo)001:1317: 'khor gnod sbyin dang brag srin stong phrag gcig /
NK128(nyo)001:1318: bstan pa sems sde rtsa ba'i rgyud lnga yan lag gi rgyud drug ste chos /
NK128(nyo)001:1319: dus tshe lo brgyad khri pa'i dus gsungs so //
NK128(nyo)001:1321: gnas 'tsho byed gzhon nu'i sdum rar /
