NK128(nyo)001:1322: ston pa drug pa rdo rje 'chang /
NK128(nyo)001:1324: bstan pa phar phyin drug gi chos /
NK128(nyo)001:1325: dus tshe lo bdun khri pa'i tshe gsungs so //
NK128(nyo)001:1327: gnas ri rab kyi byang phyogs dur khrod me ri 'bar ba /
NK128(nyo)001:1328: ston pa gzhon nu dpa' bo stobs ldan /
NK128(nyo)001:1329: 'khor byang sems sprin shugs can bdun dang d+aak+ki lha klu bsam yas /
NK128(nyo)001:1330: bstan pa rig pa rang shar chen po la sogs mngon sum 'od gsal rgyud kyi chos /
NK128(nyo)001:1331: dus tshe lo drug khri pa'i tshe gsungs so //
NK128(nyo)001:1333: gnas srin yul ru lu'i sgra dang ldan par /
NK128(nyo)001:1334: ston pa drang srong 'khros pa'i rgyal po /
NK128(nyo)001:1336: bstan pa dag pa 'dul ba'i rgyud bcu la sogs pa'i chos /
NK128(nyo)001:1337: dus tshe lo khri pa'i tshe gsungs so //
NK128(nyo)001:1342: bstan pa 'dul ba khri phrag dpag tu med pa'i chos /
NK128(nyo)001:1343: dus tshe lo lnga stong par gsungs so //
NK128(nyo)001:1345: gnas sog po g.yu smin can gyi yul byang chub kyi shing drung du /
NK128(nyo)001:1346: ston pa brtse bas rol pa'i blo gros /
NK128(nyo)001:1348: bstan pa ches phra rgyud bdun la sogs pa'i chos /
NK128(nyo)001:1349: dus tshe lo stong gi skabs gsungs so //
NK128(nyo)001:1351: gnas bya rgod phung por ston pa 'od srungs bgres po /
NK128(nyo)001:1352: 'khor skar ma 'od bzang la sogs pa bdun /
NK128(nyo)001:1353: bstan pa mdo sde dang kri yog a nu sogs khri phrag brgyad kyi chos /
NK128(nyo)001:1354: dus tshe lo lnga brgya par gsungs so //
NK128(nyo)001:1357: ston pa mngon rdzogs rgyal po /
NK128(nyo)001:1359: bstan pa nges pa don gyi theg pa 'ba' zhig gi chos /
NK128(nyo)001:1360: dus tshe lo sum brgya par gsungs so //
NK128(nyo)001:1362: gnas wa ra na si la sogs par /
NK128(nyo)001:1364: bstan pa sde snod gsum sogs /
NK128(nyo)001:1365: 'khor nyan thos byang sems lha klu la sogs par /
NK128(nyo)001:1366: dus tshe lo brgya par gsungs so //
NK128(nyo)001:1367: de ltar bstan pa bcu gnyis kyi bdag po ston pa bcu gnyis byon tshul /
NK128(nyo)001:1368: bcu bdun rgyud kyi nang tshan rig pa rang shar
NK128(nyo)001:1369: chen po la sogs par bshad pas rdzogs chen snying
NK128(nyo)001:1370: thig kho nar grags pa zhig 'dug mod kyang snga
NK128(nyo)001:1371: 'gyur bka' gter spyir khungs de dag dang nges par
NK128(nyo)001:1372: 'brel dgos pa zhig snang bas 'dir bris pa yin
NK128(nyo)001:1373: la / 'di dag grub mtha' spyi skad dang ma
NK128(nyo)001:1374: mthun yang rang gzhung rgyud khungs gtsang ma dang 'brel
NK128(nyo)001:1375: zhing lung gi zin pas the tshom mi bya zhing
NK128(nyo)001:1376: la / / spyi dang mi mthun pa thams cad
NK128(nyo)001:1377: 'dor dgos na theg pa mtho dman drang nges kyi
NK128(nyo)001:1378: dgongs don sna tshogs kyang mtha' gcig tu nges dgos
NK128(nyo)001:1379: pa'i skyon yod pas log par rtogs pa mi bya'o
NK128(nyo)001:1380: la / / // de ltar dgongs rgyud sprul pa
NK128(nyo)001:1381: bcu gnyis kyis 'gro ba'i don mdzad cing bstan pa'i
NK128(nyo)001:1382: la / / // khungs smos nas / brda brgyud
NK128(nyo)001:1383: dang snyan brgyud bla ma'i tshul rnams 'og tu ston
NK128(nyo)001:1384: la / / // khungs smos nas / par byed la / mdor bsdu na /
NK128(nyo)001:1385: rig 'dzin gyi slob dpon chen po pad+ma 'byung gnas kyis /
NK128(nyo)001:1386: rgyud gsum rig 'dzin bla ma'i bstan pa mtha' dag
NK128(nyo)001:1387: gi shing rta'i srol phye nas rgya bod la sogs
NK128(nyo)001:1388: par bstan pa mkha' khyab tu mdzad cing khyad par
NK128(nyo)001:1389: bod yul 'dir btsan po khri srong lde'u btsan gyi
NK128(nyo)001:1390: sku'i ring la snga 'gyur chos kyi nyi ma cher
NK128(nyo)001:1391: gdal bas mchog dman gyi 'gro ba thams cad yang
NK128(nyo)001:1392: dag pa'i sa la 'god par mdzad pa'i tshul la
NK128(nyo)001:1393: / 'phags yul gyi pan+di ta chen po jo bo
NK128(nyo)001:1394: rje dpal ldan a ti shas kyang basngagasa par mdzad
NK128(nyo)001:1395: pa'i tshul jo bo'i rnam thar gsal ba ltar dang
NK128(nyo)001:1396: / / khyad par o rgyan chen po'i dngos slob yongs grags rje 'bangs nyer lnga /
NK128(nyo)001:1399: rong zom gyi chos 'byung las yer pa'i grub thob 'od lus 'grub pa brgyad cu /
NK128(nyo)001:1400: lha lung dpal rdor la sogs pa chu bo rir
NK128(nyo)001:1401: sgom chen brgya rtsa brgyad yod pa'i lha lung dpal
NK128(nyo)001:1402: rdor rgyal po glang dar bkums pa'i rkyen gyis 'od
NK128(nyo)001:1403: lus ma grub kyang brgya dang bdun 'od lus su
NK128(nyo)001:1405: yer pa na deng sang yang grub brgya'i mchod rten
NK128(nyo)001:1406: 'dug pas grub chen de rnams kyi dwangs ma 'od
NK128(nyo)001:1407: skur yal / snyigs ma skra sen mo sogs lus
NK128(nyo)001:1408: par rdzogs chen gyi rgyud las bshad pas de dag
NK128(nyo)001:1409: gi mchod rten yin par sems /
NK128(nyo)001:1410: yig tshang gzhan las mchims phur grub chen nyer lnga /
NK128(nyo)001:1411: 'bro bza' sogs rnal 'byor ma bcu drug /
NK128(nyo)001:1412: chu bo rir dpal gyi ye shes sogs grub chen so lnga /
NK128(nyo)001:1413: myang ting 'dzin bzang po sogs ye par grub chen brgya dang bdun te /
NK128(nyo)001:1414: de rnams kyang 'od lus grub par gsungs /
NK128(nyo)001:1415: gzhan yang slob dpon chen po'i dngos slob 'khon klu dbang srung ba dang /
NK128(nyo)001:1417: a mes byang chub 'dre 'khol sogs grub thob bgrangs yas par byon pas /
NK128(nyo)001:1418: de rnams thams cad snga 'gyur rdo rje theg pa
NK128(nyo)001:1419: kho nas grol ba las gzhan du smrar med pas
NK128(nyo)001:1420: de dag gi thugs rgyud la bzhugs pa'i lung rtogs
NK128(nyo)001:1421: kyi yon tan thams cad snga 'gyur gyi bstan pa
NK128(nyo)001:1422: rin po che kho nas las gzhan du ci yod
NK128(nyo)001:1423: / de ltar gsang sngags rdo rje theg pa tsam
NK128(nyo)001:1424: du ma zad rgyu'i chos sde snod gsum gyi chos
NK128(nyo)001:1425: thams cad kyang snga 'gyur kho na la ltos dgos
NK128(nyo)001:1426: / par snang bas / phyis kyi 'gyur gsar 'ga' zhig dang /
NK128(nyo)001:1427: skad gsar bcad kyis gtan la phabs pa tsam las
NK128(nyo)001:1428: gzhan du bka' 'gyur rin po che'i 'gyur byang phal
NK128(nyo)001:1429: che bar zhus chen gyi lo ts+aa ba ban+d+he ye
NK128(nyo)001:1430: shes sdes bsgyur cing zhus te gtan la phab pa'o
NK128(nyo)001:1431: // zhes 'byung ba yang bee ro yin pas snga 'gyur kho na yin par gsal la /
NK128(nyo)001:1432: gzhan yang dam pa'i chos 'dul ba'i bstan pa smad
NK128(nyo)001:1433: 'dul du grags pa yang snga 'gyur kho na'i sdom
NK128(nyo)001:1435: khyad par 'bras bu gsang sngags rdo rje theg pa'i
NK128(nyo)001:1436: bstan pa ni glang dar gyi dus kyang ma bsnubs
NK128(nyo)001:1437: par so zur gnubs sogs kyi grub chen rnams kyis
NK128(nyo)001:1438: bshad sgrub ma nyams par gzung zhing deng sang gi
NK128(nyo)001:1439: bar du bzhugs pas na de'i phyir snga 'gyur bstan
NK128(nyo)001:1440: pa'i gzhung lugs bka' ma nyid du nges par bya
NK128(nyo)001:1441: dgos la / de ltar bu'i rig 'dzin brgyud pa'i
NK128(nyo)001:1442: rnam thar bstan pa'i zhar las bstan pa'i byung tshul
NK128(nyo)001:1444: thub bstan rgya mtsho'i snying po rdo rje theg /
NK128(nyo)001:1445: snga 'gyur bshad sgrub bstan pa rin po che'i //
NK128(nyo)001:1446: byung tshul rang gzhung gtsang ma'i lo rgyus ltar //
NK128(nyo)001:1447: gsal bar byas 'di ngo mtshar rmad du byung //
NK128(nyo)001:1448: 'jam mgon chos kyi rgyal po khri srong gis //
NK128(nyo)001:1449: sngon smon thugs bskyed snying stobs brtson pa yis //
NK128(nyo)001:1450: mkhan slob lo pan spyan drangs dam chos bsgyur //
NK128(nyo)001:1451: 'di 'dra'i bka' drin bsam pa'i yul las 'das //
NK128(nyo)001:1452: de ltar rnam dag dri med bstan pa'i srol //
NK128(nyo)001:1453: snga 'gyur gsang chen snying ma'i ring lugs 'dir //
NK128(nyo)001:1454: 'jug pa'i skal bzang bsod nams bye bas bsgrubs //
NK128(nyo)001:1455: de phyir brtson pas lam la 'bad par rigs //
NK128(nyo)001:1456: zhes bya ba yang bar skabs kyi tshigs su bcad pa'o //
NK128(nyo)001:1457: spyi don gsum pa mthar bstan 'dzin gyi bla ma
NK128(nyo)001:1458: brgyud pa'i tshul ji ltar byon pa rnam par thar
NK128(nyo)001:1459: pa dang bcas bshad pa la gnyis te /
NK128(nyo)001:1460: spyir 'dus pa'i mdo'i dbang dang rjes su 'brel ba'i theg pa'i babs tshul dang /
NK128(nyo)001:1461: bye brag yo ga gsum gyi brgyud tshul lo //
NK128(nyo)001:1462: dang po ni dbang chog gi stong thun du gsal
NK128(nyo)001:1463: bar bris zin pas 'dir phyi ma ltar bri bar
NK128(nyo)001:1464: rigs la / de la yang gnyis te /
NK128(nyo)001:1465: ston pa sku gsum nas rim par brgyud de rgya
NK128(nyo)001:1466: gar ba'i lo rgyus dang bod kyi lo rgyus gnyis
NK128(nyo)001:1467: so // dang po rgya gar ba la gsum ste /
NK128(nyo)001:1468: ma h+aa yo ga'i brgyud tshul /
NK128(nyo)001:1469: a nu yo ga'i brgyud tshul /
NK128(nyo)001:1470: a ti yo ga'i brgyud tshul lo //
NK128(nyo)001:1471: de yang 'dir a nu nyid gtso che yang /
NK128(nyo)001:1472: rgyud lung gnyis la gcig brten gyi tshul du bshad nas /
NK128(nyo)001:1473: a ti yo ga lta ba spyi 'byams kyi dbang
NK128(nyo)001:1474: bskur zhing la bzla ba'i phyir gsum ga nges par
NK128(nyo)001:1475: dgos shing / de yang rgya mtsho las /
NK128(nyo)001:1476: rgyal ba rig 'dzin gang zag gsum //
NK128(nyo)001:1477: dgongs pa rig pa rna bar brgyud //
NK128(nyo)001:1478: gang la thug gi bar du'o //
NK128(nyo)001:1480: yo ga gsum ga'i brgyud pa la dgongs brgyud dang /
NK128(nyo)001:1482: snyan brgyud gsum gyis bshad cing /
NK128(nyo)001:1483: de ltar brgyud pa gsum gyi go don ni gang
NK128(nyo)001:1484: zag brgyud pa ltar nyan bshad bya mi dgos shing
NK128(nyo)001:1485: / rig brgyud ltar brda la ltos mi dgos par
NK128(nyo)001:1486: gong ma'i dgongs pa 'og ma la byin rlabs kyis
NK128(nyo)001:1488: gang zag ltar nyan bshad bya mi dgos kyang byin
NK128(nyo)001:1489: rlabs kyis rtogs par mi nus pas dgongs pa gtad
NK128(nyo)001:1490: cing brda ston pas na rig brgyud /
NK128(nyo)001:1491: gong ma gnyis ltar rtogs ma nus pa rnams la thugs la dgongs shing mgur du bsgril /
NK128(nyo)001:1493: tshems bar nas tshangs pa'i gsung byung ste bshad pas /
NK128(nyo)001:1494: nyan byed kyis legs par nyan cing thos bsam gyis
NK128(nyo)001:1495: rtogs shing dpyad pas don nges pa ni snyan brgyud
NK128(nyo)001:1496: do // de lta bu'i tshul rnams 'chad par byed pa /
NK128(nyo)001:1497: de la dang po spyir yo ga gsum gyi dgongs brgyud sku gsum ni /
NK128(nyo)001:1499: chos sku dpag med brjod du med //
NK128(nyo)001:1500: longs spyod zad med rin chen gter //
NK128(nyo)001:1501: sprul pa bye ba bsam mi khyab //
NK128(nyo)001:1503: thog ma'i mgon po rgyal ba chos sku kun tu bzang po nyid kyis /
NK128(nyo)001:1504: sa bcu'i byang sems kho na'i gdul bya'i ngor 'chad
NK128(nyo)001:1505: pa'i skyes bu rang las mi gzhan pa'i longs spyod
NK128(nyo)001:1506: rdzogs sku rgyal ba rigs lnga byin gyis brlabs shing
NK128(nyo)001:1507: brgyud pa dang / rigs lngas rgyal sras rigs gsum
NK128(nyo)001:1508: mgon po sogs sems dpa' sems ma lhan gcig pa'i
NK128(nyo)001:1510: sprul pa'i sku la yang 'dod tshul mang na'ang 'dir
NK128(nyo)001:1511: rtsa brgyud kho na'i rjes su 'brangs te gong du
NK128(nyo)001:1513: de dag ni dgongs brgyud sku gsum mo //
NK128(nyo)001:1514: gnyis pa brda brgyud dam rig 'dzin rig pas brgyud tshul ni /
NK128(nyo)001:1515: mdo dbang lugs ma h+aa yo ga kho na'i brgyud par /
NK128(nyo)001:1516: rdor sems gsang bdag gnyis las mi dgos kyang /
NK128(nyo)001:1517: a nu'i lugs la brda brgyud rigs can dra ma
NK128(nyo)001:1518: lnga yang yod pas lo rgyus 'chad bde ba'i phyir
NK128(nyo)001:1519: 'dir ma h+aa a nu gnyis mi 'gal bar cung
NK128(nyo)001:1520: zad bshad pa'i dbang du bgyis na gnyis te /
NK128(nyo)001:1521: mi ma yin pa la brgyud pa dang /
NK128(nyo)001:1522: mi dang mi ma yin gnyis ka las brgyud tshul lo //
NK128(nyo)001:1524: thub dbang dgongs pa mya ngan las 'das pa'i tshul
NK128(nyo)001:1525: bstan nas lo nyer brgyad nas rgyal tshab rigs gsum
NK128(nyo)001:1526: mgon po las brgyud pa'i tshul te /
NK128(nyo)001:1527: 'jam dpal rdo rje rnon po mdzes pa'i skur ldan
NK128(nyo)001:1528: pas lha rnams kyi lus dang bsam pa dang mthun
NK128(nyo)001:1529: par chos bstan te lha grags ldan mchog skyong la
NK128(nyo)001:1530: gsungs / des rin cen 'od 'bar la bshad /
NK128(nyo)001:1531: des skye rgu'i bdag po tshangs pa la bshad /
NK128(nyo)001:1532: des tshangs pa kun grol la /
NK128(nyo)001:1533: des tshangs pa gtsug phud 'dzin la /
NK128(nyo)001:1534: des lha dbang brgya byin la /
NK128(nyo)001:1535: des lha'i rig 'dzin tshom bu 'bum sde la bshad
NK128(nyo)001:1536: pas lha rnams kyang byang chub sems dpa'i rig 'dzin
NK128(nyo)001:1537: cing rgyal ba'i gdung 'tshob par gyur te /
NK128(nyo)001:1538: spyan ras gzigs bdud rtsi sman gyi sku dang ldan
NK128(nyo)001:1539: pa klu dug can rnams kyi lus dang bsam pa
NK128(nyo)001:1540: dang mthun par bstan te klu rgyal mgrin pa nag
NK128(nyo)001:1541: po la gsungs / des klu mo kha 'dul ma la /
NK128(nyo)001:1542: des klu mo 'dul tshangs ma la /
NK128(nyo)001:1543: des klu yid 'ong dga' ma la /
NK128(nyo)001:1545: des klu tshom bu 'bum sde la bshad pas klu rnams kyang gong bzhin gyur to //
NK128(nyo)001:1546: phyag na rdo rje 'jigs tshul bsdigs pa'i sku gnod
NK128(nyo)001:1547: sbyin rnams kyi lus dang bsam pa dang mthun par
NK128(nyo)001:1548: bstan te gnod sbyin grags ldan mchog skyong la gsungs
NK128(nyo)001:1549: / des gnod sbyin kun tu bzang po la /
NK128(nyo)001:1550: des gnod sbyin lag na rdo rje la /
NK128(nyo)001:1551: des gnod sbyin skar mda' gdong la /
NK128(nyo)001:1552: des gnod sbyin tshom bu 'bum sde la bshad pas gnod sbyin rnams kyang gong ltar gyur to //
NK128(nyo)001:1553: gnyis pa mi dang mi ma yin gnyis ka las brgyud tshul ni /
NK128(nyo)001:1554: gsang ba'i bdag pos ri ma la ya'i rtse mor /
NK128(nyo)001:1558: srin po lang ka mgrin bcu'am blo gros thabs ldan /
NK128(nyo)001:1559: mi las skal ldan li tsa byi dri med grags pa ste d+r+wa ma lnga dang /
NK128(nyo)001:1560: gzhan yang lha klu gnod sbyin ma'i rig 'dzin du ma 'dus pa'i 'khor la gsungs shing brgyud do //
NK128(nyo)001:1561: 'di dag ni snga 'gyur bka' gter thun mong ba'i lugs yin te /
NK128(nyo)001:1563: grags ldan chos skyong gnod sbyin skar mda' gdong //
NK128(nyo)001:1564: blo gros thabs ldan klu rgyal 'jog po dang //
NK128(nyo)001:1565: dri med grags pa las can rgyal po dza //
NK128(nyo)001:1567: gsum pa gang zag snyan khung brgyud pa ni /
NK128(nyo)001:1568: mdor na gsang bdag gis 'og min du /
NK128(nyo)001:1569: ston pa sku lnga yongs rdzogs la byin brlab kyis
NK128(nyo)001:1570: thos pa de thugs la bsdus pas rgyud don dbu
NK128(nyo)001:1572: d+r+wa ma lnga la gsungs pa'i tshe srin po blo
NK128(nyo)001:1573: gros thabs ldan gyis tshig dang yi ger bsdus pas
NK128(nyo)001:1574: gzhung tshogs glegs bam du de nas grub par rig
NK128(nyo)001:1576: de ltar gsang ba'i bdag po phyag na rdo rjes
NK128(nyo)001:1577: ri ma la ya'i rtse mor gsang sngags chos kyi
NK128(nyo)001:1578: 'khor lo bskor ba'i byin rlabs las rgyal po dza
NK128(nyo)001:1579: la rmi ltas bdun byung ba yiin la /
NK128(nyo)001:1580: de ltar rmis pa'i gnas ni /
NK128(nyo)001:1581: mdo dgongs 'dus kyi le'u lnga pa las /
NK128(nyo)001:1582: mi yi gnas kyi 'jig rten khams //
NK128(nyo)001:1583: gling bzhi sa las 'dzam gling gi //
NK128(nyo)001:1584: drag shul can zhes bya ba'i ri //
NK128(nyo)001:1585: gnod sbyin 'du ba'i sa yin te //
NK128(nyo)001:1586: chos 'dzin rigs kyi bsgrub gnas su //
NK128(nyo)001:1587: zhes gsungs pas mi'i gnas 'dzam bu'i gling na yod par gsungs shing /
NK128(nyo)001:1588: de'i bye brag za hor dang nye ba'i sa na yod par gsungs te /
NK128(nyo)001:1589: mdo 'grel bde mchog rdo rjes mdzad pa las /
NK128(nyo)001:1590: za hor yul gyi nye 'khor na //
NK128(nyo)001:1591: mthu stobs zhabs bcags ma la ya //
NK128(nyo)001:1592: gnam lcags 'bar ba'i rtse dag la //
NK128(nyo)001:1594: za hor gyi bye brag lang ka'i yul na yod par bshad do //
NK128(nyo)001:1595: mdo'i le'u nyer gnyis pa las /
NK128(nyo)001:1596: lang ka'i yul gyi grong bdal /
NK128(nyo)001:1597: mtsho ko kha thang dmar gyi gling /
NK128(nyo)001:1598: byan lag ljongs kyi ri ma la ya gnam lcags
NK128(nyo)001:1599: yod pa'i rtse zhes bya ba na gsungs pa'i phyir
NK128(nyo)001:1600: / de ltar drag shul can gyi ri ma la
NK128(nyo)001:1601: ya gnam lcags yod pa'i rtse zhes bya ba'i ri
NK128(nyo)001:1602: de yang dbyibs zlum zhing dpangs mtho ba /
NK128(nyo)001:1604: mtha' skor dang chu zheng dpag tshad mang po dang ldan pa /
NK128(nyo)001:1605: rtse mor ri dwags kyi rgyal po seng ge dang /
NK128(nyo)001:1606: 'dab na gcan zan gyi rgyal po stag gnas pa /
NK128(nyo)001:1607: logs la brag seng ge dkar po khyi tshugs su byas pa 'dra ba yod pa /
NK128(nyo)001:1608: tsan dan gyi nags tshal sprin ltar 'khrigs shing bdud rtsi'i chu rgyun mang po 'bab pa /
NK128(nyo)001:1612: lo 'bras g.yur za ba'i shing gi yal ga phyogs
NK128(nyo)001:1613: bzhir gyes pa dus bzhi'i dgra las skyob pa ltar
NK128(nyo)001:1614: du yod pa / shing de'i me tog 'bras bu
NK128(nyo)001:1615: sman du gyur pa zos pas nad sna tshogs sel
NK128(nyo)001:1616: du yod pa / ba / rtsa ba na bdud rtsu'i chu mig rang brdol du yod pa /
NK128(nyo)001:1617: mdun du me tog gi snams bu yod pa /
NK128(nyo)001:1618: rtse mor bya ka lan ta ka'i tshang bcas nas
NK128(nyo)001:1619: chos thams cad thig le nyag gcig tu sgrog pa
NK128(nyo)001:1620: yod pa / ri de'i shar phyogs sam shar lhor
NK128(nyo)001:1621: tring shar a su ra'i brag phug ces bya ba
NK128(nyo)001:1622: yod pa / / phug rin po che sna bdun
NK128(nyo)001:1623: zur brgyad yod pa la nyi zla'i ri mo rang
NK128(nyo)001:1624: yod pa / / byung ba / sgo rin po che zla gam du yod pa /
NK128(nyo)001:1625: logs la ngo mtshar gyi ri mo rang byung ba /
NK128(nyo)001:1626: mkhar yang thog rim pa gsum dang ldan pa /
NK128(nyo)001:1627: skal ba dang ldan pa rnams kyis bgrod par sla zhing /
NK128(nyo)001:1628: skal med rnams kyi spyod yul du ma gyur pa ste /
NK128(nyo)001:1630: rtse na rtsal gyi rgyal po gnas //
NK128(nyo)001:1631: ngos la brag dkar khyi tshugs pa //
NK128(nyo)001:1633: rtsi sman rtsa brgyad tshang bar 'khrungs //
NK128(nyo)001:1634: 'du ba'i nad kyis yong mi tshugs //
NK128(nyo)001:1635: spyi bor ka lan ta ka ni //
NK128(nyo)001:1636: mi gnyis gcig pur gnas pa'i sgra //
NK128(nyo)001:1637: mdzod ldan de yi tshang bcas shing //
NK128(nyo)001:1638: skal ldan rnams kyis bgrod par sla //
NK128(nyo)001:1639: skal med rnams kyis yong mi thar //
NK128(nyo)001:1641: gnas de ni dus bzhi'i rgyal ba rnams kyis gsang sngags bstan pa'i gnas /
NK128(nyo)001:1642: bskal pa 'jig pa'i tshe na yang mi 'gyur ba rdo rje'i gnas su bshad pa yin te /
NK128(nyo)001:1643: mdo dgongs 'dus le'u bzhi pa las /
NK128(nyo)001:1644: drag shul can zhes bya ba'i ri //
NK128(nyo)001:1645: dgon pa chen po'i gnas de ni //
NK128(nyo)001:1646: ye shes snying po can rnams kyi //
NK128(nyo)001:1647: theg chen gsang ba 'byung ba'i gnas //
NK128(nyo)001:1648: thog ma tha ma'i dus med par //
NK128(nyo)001:1649: dam pa rnams kyi basngagasa pa yin //
NK128(nyo)001:1651: de lta bu'i gnas de na /
NK128(nyo)001:1652: za hor gyi yul a par ta mu'i rgyal po
NK128(nyo)001:1653: u ta dz+ny+aa na zhes bya ba'i sras rgyal po
NK128(nyo)001:1654: chen po gsang sngags zab mo'i rigs su gyur pa
NK128(nyo)001:1655: skal ba dang ldan cing glegs bam mngon du snang
NK128(nyo)001:1656: nus pa'i 'gugs pa'i sgra dzahzhesa bya ba'i mtshan can
NK128(nyo)001:1657: te / a su ra gsang ba'i brag phug de'i
NK128(nyo)001:1658: bar khang na gsang sngags phyi rgyud la sgrub pa
NK128(nyo)001:1660: dus cho 'phrul chen po nya'i nub mo rmi ltas
NK128(nyo)001:1661: bdun rmis pa'am yang na zhag bdun du rmis pa
NK128(nyo)001:1662: yang bshad mod / rje sgrol phug pa chen po sogs zhag gcig la rmis par bzhed de /
NK128(nyo)001:1663: mdang sum bdag la rmi lam 'di ltar rmis //
NK128(nyo)001:1664: zhes gsungs pa'i phyir gsungs shing /
NK128(nyo)001:1665: sman lung pa mi bskyod rdo rje yang de ltar bzhed pas /
NK128(nyo)001:1666: de ltar rmi ltas bdun ni /
NK128(nyo)001:1667: 'grel pa ye shes snang ba rgyan las /
NK128(nyo)001:1668: sku gsung thugs rtags thim pa dang //
NK128(nyo)001:1669: chos kyi bgro ba byas pa dang //
NK128(nyo)001:1670: rin chen glegs bam babs pa dang //
NK128(nyo)001:1671: kun gyis dam pa sngags pa dang //
NK128(nyo)001:1672: mchod pa chen po byas pa dang //
NK128(nyo)001:1673: ri chen char du babs pa dang //
NK128(nyo)001:1674: sangs rgyas sa la lung bstan pa'o //
NK128(nyo)001:1676: dgongs 'dus kyi 'grel pa lung bstan rdo rje las /
NK128(nyo)001:1677: sku gsung thugs rtags thim pa dang //
NK128(nyo)001:1678: chos kyi bgro ba mdzad pa dang //
NK128(nyo)001:1679: chos sgra chen po sgrogs pa dang //
NK128(nyo)001:1680: bdud rtsi char du babs pa dang //
NK128(nyo)001:1681: rin chen char du babs pa dang //
NK128(nyo)001:1682: pu tsa rgya chen byas pa dang //
NK128(nyo)001:1684: mdo dbang gi bskur tshig las /
NK128(nyo)001:1685: rgyal bas lung bstan skal ldan rgyal po la //
NK128(nyo)001:1686: gsang mdzod gter 'dzin sku gsung thim rtags dang //
NK128(nyo)001:1687: chos kyi bgro mdzad rin cen char 'bab dang //
NK128(nyo)001:1688: kun gyi basngagasa shes glegs bam babs pa dang //
NK128(nyo)001:1689: mchod cing sangs rgyas sa la lung bstan cing //
NK128(nyo)001:1690: zhes gsungs pa rnams khog gcig pas /
NK128(nyo)001:1691: de dag rim bzhin 'chad par byed pa la /
NK128(nyo)001:1692: rmis ltas dang po ni ri bo ma la ya'i
NK128(nyo)001:1693: rtse mo'i pho brang du gsang ba'i bdag po phyag
NK128(nyo)001:1694: na rdo rje mdun gyi nam mkha' la byon te
NK128(nyo)001:1695: / sku'i gnas nas 'od zer sngon po 'phros te
NK128(nyo)001:1696: gdul bya'i rtog sgrib sbyangs shing 'jig rten gyi khams
NK128(nyo)001:1697: thams cad bsregs nas mi snang bar byas /
NK128(nyo)001:1698: gsung bstan pa dang theg pa'i sgra 'brug stong ldir
NK128(nyo)001:1699: ba bzhin bsgrags pas gdul bya rnams kyis go bar
NK128(nyo)001:1700: mdzad / thugs ka na rdo rje 'od 'bar ba zhig byung ste rgyal po'i thugs kar thim /
NK128(nyo)001:1701: sbyi bo'i gtsug nas nyi ma 'od 'bar ba byung ste rgyal po'i spyi gtsug tu thim /
NK128(nyo)001:1702: zhabs mthil nas zla ba shar te rgyal po'i zhabs mthil du thim /
NK128(nyo)001:1703: snang srid kyi chos thams cad rgyal po'i lto ba nas 'phyo ba rmis so //
NK128(nyo)001:1705: dus gsum gyi de bzhin gshegs pa thams cad nyi
NK128(nyo)001:1706: zla pad+ma seng khrir bzhugs nas chos kyi bgro ba
NK128(nyo)001:1707: mdzad cing / gser kyi 'khor lo rtsibs stong dang
NK128(nyo)001:1708: ldan pa phyag tu bsnams nas sems can thams cad
NK128(nyo)001:1709: la chos kyi 'khor lo bskor bas srid gsum kha
NK128(nyo)001:1710: lo gyen du bsgyur ba rmis so //
NK128(nyo)001:1712: nam mkha'i khams las sprin gser gyi mdog can 'khrigs shing /
NK128(nyo)001:1713: cho 'phrul gyi 'brug skad dam pa chos kyi sgrar go sla zhing snyan par sgrog /
NK128(nyo)001:1714: drin chen sna tshogs kyi na bun 'thibs /
NK128(nyo)001:1715: bee d+aur+ya'i 'od 'byung zhing snang srid gsal ba'i glog 'gyu /
NK128(nyo)001:1716: rin po che'i char chen po 'bab pa rmis so //
NK128(nyo)001:1718: 'jig rten gyi khams rat+na 'bar ba'i sgron mes mun pa sel zhing /
NK128(nyo)001:1719: nam mkha' las sprin gyi gseb nas bdud rtsi sman
NK128(nyo)001:1720: gyi chu rgyun babs pas sa phyogs thams cad chag
NK128(nyo)001:1721: chag gdab / 'gro ba'i zug rngu dang gcong snying sbyangs /
NK128(nyo)001:1722: kun kyang rdo rje rnal 'byor zhes bya ba gsang
NK128(nyo)001:1723: sngags kyi sgra di ri ri sgrog pa rmis so
NK128(nyo)001:1725: nam mkha'i dbyings kyi nyi ma'i dkyil 'khor gyi 'od
NK128(nyo)001:1726: zer las rin po che'i sgrom bu dpal be'u'i dbyings
NK128(nyo)001:1727: phyi nang med par gsal ba'i nang na gser kyi
NK128(nyo)001:1728: gzhi la bee d+aur+ya'i zhun mas rgya rang nan du
NK128(nyo)001:1729: bris pa'i glegs bam gyi char mang po skar mda'
NK128(nyo)001:1730: lhung ba bzhin bab pa rmis so //
NK128(nyo)001:1732: glegs bam de dag la sangs rgyas byang sems rig 'dzin lha dang bcas pa grangs med pas /
NK128(nyo)001:1734: de bzhin du bskor ba dang bstod pa kha don
NK128(nyo)001:1735: byed pa la sogs pa'i yon tan brjod pa'i sgra
NK128(nyo)001:1738: nam mkha'i sprin gseb nas gzugs su ma grub pa'i lung ston pa'i sgra 'di ltar byung ste /
NK128(nyo)001:1739: las dang skal bar rab ldan zhing //
NK128(nyo)001:1740: rgyal bas 'byung bar lung bstan pa'i //
NK128(nyo)001:1741: bsod nams chen po'i d+r+wa ma khyod //
NK128(nyo)001:1742: sprul pas ji ltar lung bstan bzhin //
NK128(nyo)001:1743: da ltar dus 'dir mngon shar gyi //
NK128(nyo)001:1744: 'khor ba snying por bya ba'i phyir //
NK128(nyo)001:1745: nga yi cho 'phrul byin rlabs kyis //
NK128(nyo)001:1746: bstan pa'i snying po dam pa zhig /
NK128(nyo)001:1747: skal ldan khyod la bstan par bya //
NK128(nyo)001:1750: ma la ya zhes bya ba'i ri //
NK128(nyo)001:1751: dgon pa chen po'i gnas 'di ni //
NK128(nyo)001:1752: ye shes snying po can rnams kyi //
NK128(nyo)001:1753: gsang bar bya ba dam pa zhig /
NK128(nyo)001:1754: yod kyis de la nan tan gyis //
NK128(nyo)001:1755: de la sems kyi me long ltos //
NK128(nyo)001:1756: ji bzhin rnam par rtog ma thag /
NK128(nyo)001:1757: sangs rgyas sa dang skal bar mnyam //
NK128(nyo)001:1758: bde ba can gyi zhing khams su //
NK128(nyo)001:1759: 'od kyi rgyal po zhes bya ba //
NK128(nyo)001:1761: rdo rje gsang chen gsang ba yin //
NK128(nyo)001:1762: dam pa'i mdzod gsum glegs bam du //
NK128(nyo)001:1763: rdzogs par bris la khyod ltos la //
NK128(nyo)001:1764: lha dang mi yi rig 'dzin la //
NK128(nyo)001:1765: rim par brgyud de grags par gyis //
NK128(nyo)001:1766: zhes sogs sgrogs par rmis so //
NK128(nyo)001:1767: rmis ltas shar tshul 'di la yig rnying rnams mi 'dra tsam dang /
NK128(nyo)001:1768: bdun pa'i tshig bcad 'di yang 'dra min sna tshogs su snang yang /
NK128(nyo)001:1769: yig rnying rnams gung bsgrigs shing khyad par sman t+aika
NK128(nyo)001:1770: tu rgyal po dzahnyida kyi gsung tshigs su bcad pa'i
NK128(nyo)001:1771: don ltar mdzad 'dug pa khung che bar 'dug pas
NK128(nyo)001:1773: de nas rgyal po mnal sad pa'i tshe shin tu
NK128(nyo)001:1774: dgyes nas mnal lam gyi don 'khor rnams la tshigs
NK128(nyo)001:1775: su bcad pa'i sgo nas 'di ltar gsungs so //
NK128(nyo)001:1776: mdang sum bdag la rmi lam 'di ltar rmis //
NK128(nyo)001:1777: ri bo ma la gnam lcags yod rtse la //
NK128(nyo)001:1778: phyag na rdo rje'i pho brang gnas bzhugs te //
NK128(nyo)001:1779: sku las 'od 'phros snang srid byi dor byas //
NK128(nyo)001:1780: gsung gi sgra yis snang srid g.yo zhing 'gul //
NK128(nyo)001:1781: thugs las 'od 'phros bdag gi snying kar thim //
NK128(nyo)001:1782: nyi zla spyi bor rkang pa'i mthil du nub //
NK128(nyo)001:1783: bdag gi lto na snang srid 'phyo ba rmis //
NK128(nyo)001:1784: dang po 'di ni bag chags sbyangs ba'i ltas //
NK128(nyo)001:1785: de nas bdag dang sangs rgyas mang po rnams //
NK128(nyo)001:1786: rmad byung gsang ba'i don la bgro ba mdzad //
NK128(nyo)001:1787: nyi zla pad+ma seng ge'i khri steng nas //
NK128(nyo)001:1788: chos kyi 'khor lo 'gro la bskor ba rmis //
NK128(nyo)001:1789: gnyis pa yin te chos la dbang thob ltas //
NK128(nyo)001:1790: de nas mkha' la rin cen sprin 'khrigs te //
NK128(nyo)001:1791: snyan pa'i 'brug sgra gsal ba'i glog 'gyus nas //
NK128(nyo)001:1792: rin chen chos kyi char chen bab pa rmis //
NK128(nyo)001:1793: gsum pa yin te 'di ni dge ba'i ltas //
NK128(nyo)001:1794: 'gro la thugs rjes chos kyi char 'bebs rtags //
NK128(nyo)001:1795: de nas 'jig rten rin chen gang byas te //
NK128(nyo)001:1796: nor bu 'od 'bar 'gro ba'i mun bsal nas //
NK128(nyo)001:1797: bdud rtsi sman gyi chu rgyun bab pa yis //
NK128(nyo)001:1798: 'gro ba'i nad rnying rtag tu sbyangs byas shing //
NK128(nyo)001:1799: 'gro kun rnal 'byor zhes byar grags par byas //
NK128(nyo)001:1800: 'gro kun rdo rje'i gral du bzhag pa'i rtags //
NK128(nyo)001:1801: nyi ma dkyil 'khor 'od zer 'bar nang nas //
NK128(nyo)001:1802: dpal be'u sgrom bu'i nang nas glegs bam ni //
NK128(nyo)001:1803: gser la bee d+aur+ya'i legs bris pa //
NK128(nyo)001:1804: mngon sum snang bar rmis te lnga pa yin //
NK128(nyo)001:1805: chos kyi rgyal por dbang ni bskur ba'i rtags //
NK128(nyo)001:1806: drug pa'i rmi lam glegs bam de dag la //
NK128(nyo)001:1807: sangs rgyas byang sems rig 'dzin mang po'i tshogs //
NK128(nyo)001:1808: yon tan sgra sgrogs mchod bstod bskor byed rmis //
NK128(nyo)001:1809: rmad byung chen po ston pa'i snga ltas yin //
NK128(nyo)001:1810: tha ma nam mkha'i dbyings kyi sprin gseb nas //
NK128(nyo)001:1811: cho 'phrul rang sgras bdag lung ston pa'i tshig /
NK128(nyo)001:1812: rim gyis gsang ba dam par sgra sgrogs rmis //
NK128(nyo)001:1813: gsang ba dam pa rgya cher sgrog pa'i rtags //
NK128(nyo)001:1815: ltas 'di dag dang sbyar na bdag skal ba dang ldan par nges so //
NK128(nyo)001:1817: 'khor rnams kyis kyang de legs so //
NK128(nyo)001:1818: a ho zhes ngo mtshar du gsol te /
NK128(nyo)001:1819: de lta bu'i rmis ltas bdun po 'di rnams rgyal
NK128(nyo)001:1820: po dzahranga gi gsung 'di ga btsan par snang bas
NK128(nyo)001:1821: lo rgyus snga ma 'ga' zhig la snang la ma
NK128(nyo)001:1822: nges kyi 'khrul pa yod par sems so //
NK128(nyo)001:1823: de nas rgyal po 'khor bcas sku mkhar gyi yang thog ri ma la ya'i rtser byon pas /
NK128(nyo)001:1824: rin po che smug po las grub pa'i gsang bdag
NK128(nyo)001:1825: phyag na rdo rje'i sku zhig 'dug pa dang mjal
NK128(nyo)001:1827: phyag dang bskor ba mchod pa chen po mdzad /
NK128(nyo)001:1828: zhabs spyi bo'i gtsug tu blangs te tshigs su bcad
NK128(nyo)001:1829: pa brjod tshul la mi 'dra ba 'ga' zhig 'dug
NK128(nyo)001:1830: kyang / 'dir sman t+aika gi rjes su 'brangs na //
NK128(nyo)001:1831: bskal pa gong nas bsgrubs pa yi //
NK128(nyo)001:1832: las kyi mjal ba'i lha mchog khyod //
NK128(nyo)001:1833: bskal pa brgyar yang mi gtong ngo //
NK128(nyo)001:1834: e ma ngo mtshar mchog gi sku //
NK128(nyo)001:1835: 'dren pa'i dpal dang mchog lags grags //
NK128(nyo)001:1836: mos pa'i yid kyi lha mchog 'dzin //
NK128(nyo)001:1838: yi dam gyi lhar bzung nas zla ba bdun du bsgrub pa mdzad do //
NK128(nyo)001:1839: sgrub pa de yang sgrub thabs kyi gang gi rjes su 'brangs te bsgrubs par mi gsal yang /
NK128(nyo)001:1840: sku de nyid la mchod pa 'bul zhing gsol ba
NK128(nyo)001:1841: btabs pa yin par sman t+aika tu gsungs pa 'thad
NK128(nyo)001:1842: par sems / de ltar bsgrubs pas mnal ltas bzhin
NK128(nyo)001:1843: glegs bam rnams mngon sum du bab par gyur to
NK128(nyo)001:1844: par sems / // de nas nges don du rgyal
NK128(nyo)001:1845: pos glegs bam de rnams la brtags na rtogs pa
NK128(nyo)001:1846: par sems / // 'dug kyang / drang don gdul
NK128(nyo)001:1847: bya gzu lums can dang ras chod can dag dgag
NK128(nyo)001:1848: pa'i phyir glegs bam de rnams la brtags pas tshig
NK128(nyo)001:1849: 'bru gcig kyang brda ma mjal ba'i tshul mdzad nas
NK128(nyo)001:1850: par sems / // 'dug kyang / / 'jig rten gyi khams na mkhyen pa su che dris pas /
NK128(nyo)001:1851: za hor gyi yul na rgyal po u pa r+aa dza mkhyen rgya che'o zer te /
NK128(nyo)001:1852: rkang mgyogs pa bardzangasa te bdag la ltas mang po
NK128(nyo)001:1853: dag snang zhing glegs bam gyi char bab par gyur
NK128(nyo)001:1854: pas 'di dag gzigs su shog cig ces btang bas
NK128(nyo)001:1856: glegs bam de dag sh+aakya'i bstan pa yin na kho bos rtogs pa yang srid kyis /
NK128(nyo)001:1857: lha klu la sogs gzhan gyis bstan pa yin na
NK128(nyo)001:1858: mi rtogs pa yang srid pas 'dir spyan drongs shig
NK128(nyo)001:1859: gsungs pas / rgyal pos glegs bam rnams stag sgro
NK128(nyo)001:1860: dang gzigs sgror bcug a ka ru dang du ru
NK128(nyo)001:1861: ka sogs spos sna tshogs dang /
NK128(nyo)001:1862: gdugs dang rgyal mtshan la sogs pa mchod pa sna
NK128(nyo)001:1863: tshogs dang bcas te rgyal po u pa r+aa dza'i
NK128(nyo)001:1864: gnas su spyan drangs pa la /
NK128(nyo)001:1865: khong gis brtags pas tshig gcig kyang brda ma mjal te tshur bsrings nas 'di skad ces springs so //
NK128(nyo)001:1866: 'di dag ni bdag gi spyod yul du ma gyur gyi /
NK128(nyo)001:1867: sngar gyi tshul dang rtags de dag dang sbyar na
NK128(nyo)001:1868: rgyal po nyid kyi thugs dgongs kyis dpag 'tshal lo
NK128(nyo)001:1870: skabs 'dir a nu yo ga mdo'i dbang du byas na rgyal po nyid kyis rtogs par bzhed de /
NK128(nyo)001:1871: rgyal po rang gis mdzad pa'i spyi gcod las /
NK128(nyo)001:1873: thugs kyi sgrub pa mngon rtogs te //
NK128(nyo)001:1874: de nyid sgo nas de nyid bsgrubs //
NK128(nyo)001:1875: smon pa'i lha dang de ru mjal //
NK128(nyo)001:1877: don dam bcud kyang de nas rgyas //
NK128(nyo)001:1879: tshigs bcad dang mthun par lo rgyus kyang 'di ltar 'byung ste /
NK128(nyo)001:1880: rgyal po thugs dgongs la glegs bam 'di dag kun
NK128(nyo)001:1881: gyi thun mong ma yin pa shin tu zab pa
NK128(nyo)001:1882: gsang ba'i don zhig yin par dgongs nas /
NK128(nyo)001:1883: sangs rgyas kyi chos sngar thos pa rnams las ji
NK128(nyo)001:1884: ltar byung ba bzhin bsag sbyangs rgya cher mdzad de
NK128(nyo)001:1885: brtags pas / sgyu 'phrul dra ba rdo rje sems dpa'i zhal mthong gi le'u rtogs te /
NK128(nyo)001:1886: de ltar bsgrubs pas rdo rje sems dpa'i zhal mngon sum du mthong ste /
NK128(nyo)001:1887: rigs kyi bu dngos grub ci 'dod gsungs pa la /
NK128(nyo)001:1888: glegs bam 'di rnams kyi don rtogs pa 'tshal lo //
NK128(nyo)001:1890: rang gi phung po sbyongs dang /
NK128(nyo)001:1891: khyod kyi ston pa gsang ba'i bdag po zhes bya
NK128(nyo)001:1892: ba zhig gis don ma lus par ston par 'gyur
NK128(nyo)001:1893: ro // zhes gsungs nas mi snang bar gyur pa las yid rab tu dga' ste bsgrubs pas /
NK128(nyo)001:1894: nam zhig na sa g.yos te phyag na rdo rje'i zhal mngon sum du mthong ngo //
NK128(nyo)001:1895: de'i tshe phyag na rdo rjes rdo rje nam mkha' la spar te /
NK128(nyo)001:1896: h'u h'u zhes brjod nas brtul zhugs mdzad de 'khor
NK128(nyo)001:1897: bsdus te sgrib pa sbyangs snod du rung bar byas
NK128(nyo)001:1898: nas rgyal po dzahl tan+t+ra bco brgyad du phye ste
NK128(nyo)001:1900: ma h+aa yo ga sgyu 'phrul pa ltar na /
NK128(nyo)001:1901: u pa r+aa dzas phyir bskul rjes slar yang rgyal po rang gis brtags na rtogs par 'dug kyang /
NK128(nyo)001:1902: ma rtogs pa ltar mdzad de 'jig rten na su mkhas dris pas /
NK128(nyo)001:1903: yab r+aa dza la ga thung dang yum lwa ba'i
NK128(nyo)001:1904: skra can gyi sras rin chen mang gi sprul pa
NK128(nyo)001:1905: dge slong ku ku r+aa dza zhes bya ba tshe
NK128(nyo)001:1906: dbang rig 'dzin grub pa zhig bzhugs pa mkhas zer
NK128(nyo)001:1907: te spyan drangs pas ma byon par sngar ltar gyis
NK128(nyo)001:1908: gsungs pa ltar / glegs bam rnams bkur sti chen
NK128(nyo)001:1909: pos sngar bzhin spyan drangs pa dge slong ku ku
NK128(nyo)001:1911: sgyu 'phrul dra ba le'u stong phrag brgya pa'i rgyud
NK128(nyo)001:1912: bya ba de'i nang nas rdo rje sems dpa' thugs
NK128(nyo)001:1913: kyi sgrubs pa'i le'u'am rdo rje sems dpa' zhal mthong
NK128(nyo)001:1915: zla ba bdun du rnam dag mchod rten gyi drung du bsgrubs pas /
NK128(nyo)001:1916: ting nge 'dzin gyi ngor rdo rje sems dpa' 'byon te /
NK128(nyo)001:1917: rigs kyi bu sid+d+hi ci 'dod gsungs pas /
NK128(nyo)001:1918: bstan pa dang theg pa mtha' dag rtogs pa'i dngos grub zhu zhes zhus pas /
NK128(nyo)001:1919: phyag na rdo rje lung ston par 'gyur gyi gsungs te mi snang bar gshegs /
NK128(nyo)001:1920: yang zla ba bdun bsgrubs pas phyag na rdo rje
NK128(nyo)001:1921: mngon sum byon nas rdo rje lan gsum spar te
NK128(nyo)001:1922: / spangs len brtul zhugs spyod pa'i dbang de dag /
NK128(nyo)001:1925: rtsol ba dang bcas pa mtshan nyid kyi theg pa spangs nas /
NK128(nyo)001:1926: rtsol ba med pa gsang sngags kyi theg pa nyams
NK128(nyo)001:1927: su len pa khyod la don gyis bstan pa dang
NK128(nyo)001:1928: theg pa thams cad rdzogs par dbang bskur ro //
NK128(nyo)001:1929: tshig gi bstan pa de dag dge bsnyen li tsa
NK128(nyo)001:1930: byi dri ma med pa la zhus shig ces lung
NK128(nyo)001:1931: gnang ngo // ku ku r+aa dzas gsang bdag gi
NK128(nyo)001:1932: bka' bzhin sgyu 'phrul dra ba stong phrag brgya pa'i
NK128(nyo)001:1933: rgyud la tan+t+ra chen po sde bco brgyad du phye
NK128(nyo)001:1934: nas rgyal po dzahl gsungs shing /
NK128(nyo)001:1935: de ltar tan+t+ra bco brgyad ni sku gsung thugs yon tan phrin las re la gsum gsum dang /
NK128(nyo)001:1937: 'dren tshul mi 'dra ba cung zad re yod kyang 'dir g.yung sogs kyi dgongs pa ltar /
NK128(nyo)001:1938: sku'i rgyud gsum ni sangs rgyas mnyam sbyor /
NK128(nyo)001:1941: gsung gi rgyud gsum ni zla gsang thig le /
NK128(nyo)001:1944: thugs kyi rgyud gsum ni gsang ba 'dus pa /
NK128(nyo)001:1947: yon tan gyi rgyud gsum ni dpal mchog dang po /
NK128(nyo)001:1950: 'phrin las kyi rgyud gsum ni karma ma le /
NK128(nyo)001:1952: k+ai la ya yig 'bru bcu gnyis kyi rgyud rnams /
NK128(nyo)001:1954: spyi rgyud sgyu 'phrul dra ba'i rgyud /
NK128(nyo)001:1955: dam tshig sa ma ya 'bum sde bkod pa'i rgyud /
NK128(nyo)001:1956: rdo rje thabs kyi zhags pa'i rgyud dang bco brgyad po yin no //
NK128(nyo)001:1957: a nu'i lo rgyus dang sbyar na dge slong ku
NK128(nyo)001:1958: ku r+aa dza gsang mtshan rdo rje bde mchog rtsal
NK128(nyo)001:1959: du grags shing / mngon shes lnga dang ldan pa
NK128(nyo)001:1960: de tshom bu 'bum dang bcas te tshogs sgrubs pas
NK128(nyo)001:1961: rdo rje 'chang gi sa la gshegs par gsungs shing
NK128(nyo)001:1962: du grags shing / / lam rnam bkod las /
NK128(nyo)001:1963: de nas rdo rje gdan steng gi //
NK128(nyo)001:1964: 'dzam gling shar lho'i phyogs mtshams kyis //
NK128(nyo)001:1965: pho brang dam pa rin po che //
NK128(nyo)001:1966: bkra shis dam pa'i khang bu ru //
NK128(nyo)001:1967: ku ku r+aa dza in+t+ra b+ho d+hi dang //
NK128(nyo)001:1968: sing ha u pa r+aa dza dang //
NK128(nyo)001:1969: sras mo go ma s+aa la sogs //
NK128(nyo)001:1970: sgyu 'phrul dra ba'i dbang thob nas //
NK128(nyo)001:1971: tshogs kyi 'khor lo mngon bsgrubs te //
NK128(nyo)001:1972: rdo rje 'chang sar mngon du gshegs //
NK128(nyo)001:1973: zhes gsungs pa'i phyir ku ku r+aa dza ni slob
NK128(nyo)001:1974: dpon nyid in+t+ra b+ho d+hi de la snga phyi gsum
NK128(nyo)001:1975: du byung ba'i dang po rgyal po dzah'i mtshan gyi
NK128(nyo)001:1976: rnam grangs / o rgyan rgyal po sing ha r+aa dza /
NK128(nyo)001:1977: rgyal po u pa r+aa dza /
NK128(nyo)001:1978: sras mo go ma de wi sogs tshogs sgrubs par bstan no //
NK128(nyo)001:1979: 'di man chad ma h+aa kho na ltar bshad na /
NK128(nyo)001:1980: de ltar rgyal po dzahgasanga mtshan rdo rje nyi 'od
NK128(nyo)001:1981: rtsal lam dbang phyug 'jigs med rtsal du grags pa
NK128(nyo)001:1982: la dge slong ku ku r+aa dzas a su ra'i
NK128(nyo)001:1984: yon du rang gi rgyal srid dang 'dod pa'i yon tan lnga phul zhing /
NK128(nyo)001:1985: tshom bu khri dang bcas nas tshogs bsgrubs te rdo rje 'chang gi sa la gshegs so //
NK128(nyo)001:1986: mdo dbang kho na bzhin bshad pa'i dbang du byas nas /
NK128(nyo)001:1987: rgyal po dzahs rgyal po sha tra p+au ti la
NK128(nyo)001:1988: grong khyer skyid pa'i 'byung gnas su dbang bskur zhing
NK128(nyo)001:1989: gsungs te / 'di'i mtshan gyi rnam grangs su yang in+t+ra b+ho d+hir grags shing /
NK128(nyo)001:1990: gsang mtshan dz+ny+aa na dbang thob rtsal lam rdo rje gsal mdzes rtsal zhes grags /
NK128(nyo)001:1991: dbang yon du lha'i longs spyod bsam 'phel phul /
NK128(nyo)001:1992: tshom bu lnga stong dang bcas tshogs bsgrubs pas phyag chen rig 'dzin 'grub bo //
NK128(nyo)001:1993: des o rgyan gyi rgyal po sing ha r+aa dza
NK128(nyo)001:1994: la sin+b+hu rgya mtsho'i 'gram du dbang bskur ba'i yon
NK128(nyo)001:1995: du spos kyi glang po che phul zhing /
NK128(nyo)001:1996: gsang mtshan rdo rje drag po rtsal lam rdo rje stobs mchog rtsal du grags pa des /
NK128(nyo)001:1997: tshom bu stong dang bcas nas tshogs bsgrubs te rig 'dzin gyi sa la gshegs so //
NK128(nyo)001:1998: des o rgyan gyi rgyal po u pa r+aa dza
NK128(nyo)001:1999: la o rgyan gyi yul d+ha na ko sha'i gling
NK128(nyo)001:2000: phug tu dbang bskur ba'i yon du rin po che'i
NK128(nyo)001:2001: dbyig phul zhing / gsang mtshan rdo rje yang dag
NK128(nyo)001:2002: grub pa rtsal lam bde ba myu gu rtsal du
NK128(nyo)001:2003: dbyig phul zhing / grags shing / tshom bu lnga
NK128(nyo)001:2004: brgya dang bcas te tshogs bsgrubs pas rig 'dzin gyi
NK128(nyo)001:2006: des sras mo go ma de wi la rin chen
NK128(nyo)001:2007: g.yu sdings rtsal du dbang bskur zhing yon du gser
NK128(nyo)001:2009: gsang mtshan rdo rje zla mdzes rtsal lam bde ba bzod med rtsal du grags shing /
NK128(nyo)001:2010: tshom bum lnga brgya dang bcas te tshogs bsgrubs shing rig 'dzin gyi sa la gshegs so //
NK128(nyo)001:2012: +aa sh+ai lar dbus 'gyur tshal du dbang bskur zhing yon du gser gyi pa tra brgyad phul /
NK128(nyo)001:2013: gsang mtshan rdo rje khyung chen rtsal du grags te rig 'dzin gyi sa la gshegs so //
NK128(nyo)001:2014: des a tsar+ya dzi na mi tra la rdo rje gdan du gsungs shing gser phul gang phul /
NK128(nyo)001:2015: gsang mtshan rdo rje nges par rtsal te rig 'dzin gyi sa la gshegs so //
NK128(nyo)001:2016: des slob dpon rdo rje bzhad pa'i dri med la
NK128(nyo)001:2017: u ta pa ti'i tshal du gsungs shing rin po
NK128(nyo)001:2018: che phul / gsang mtshan rdo rje bde byed rtsal
NK128(nyo)001:2019: du grags shing rig 'dzin gyi sa la gshegs so
NK128(nyo)001:2020: che phul / // dpe slob dpon nyin byed seng
NK128(nyo)001:2021: ge'am mi 'byed seng ge la ga 'u rang gi
NK128(nyo)001:2022: shar ta pa ra'i tshal du gsungs shing rin po
NK128(nyo)001:2023: che phul / // che 'phul / gsang mtshan rdo
NK128(nyo)001:2024: rje gsang chen rtsal lam rdo rje rtsal chen rtsal
NK128(nyo)001:2025: du grags shing tshom bu gsum 'khor lnga brgya dang
NK128(nyo)001:2026: bcas te rig 'dzin gyi sa la gshegs so //
NK128(nyo)001:2027: des slob dpon bde ba gsal mdzad la grong khyer dpal yon du gsungs shing mnyes mchod 'bul /
NK128(nyo)001:2028: gsang mtshan rdo rje 'gyur med rtsal du grags shing rig 'dzin gyi sa la gshegs so //
NK128(nyo)001:2029: des slob dpon sh+aakya'i b+ho d+hi la yul ma ga rdar gsungs shing rta dang glang po che phul /
NK128(nyo)001:2030: gsang mtshan rdo rje dngos grub rtsal lam grub mchog
NK128(nyo)001:2031: rtsal du grags te rig 'dzin gyi sa la gshegs
NK128(nyo)001:2032: so // des slob dpon so kya de wa la
NK128(nyo)001:2033: bi ka m+aa la sh+ai lar gsungs shing me tog
NK128(nyo)001:2034: so // phul / gsang mtshan rdo rje dad pa
NK128(nyo)001:2035: rtsal du grags tshom bu bcu dang bcas te rig
NK128(nyo)001:2037: des slob dpon sgeg pa'i rdo rje la dbus 'gyur
NK128(nyo)001:2038: tshul du gsungs shing gser gyi rdo rje rtse lnga
NK128(nyo)001:2039: pa phul / gsang mtshan rdo rje sgeg pa rtsal lam /
NK128(nyo)001:2040: rdo rje dril bu rtsal lam /
NK128(nyo)001:2041: rdo rje drag po rtsal du grags shing rig 'dzin gyi sa la gshegs so //
NK128(nyo)001:2042: slob dpon 'di sgyu 'phrul gsang snying gi 'brel pa par khab mdzad pa po yin cing /
NK128(nyo)001:2043: slob dpon sangs rgyas gsang ba'i bla ma yin par bshad /
NK128(nyo)001:2044: mtshan gyi rnam grangs nor bu gling pa /
NK128(nyo)001:2045: dpal ldan byang chub mchog gi skal ba can /
NK128(nyo)001:2046: dpal sna tshogs pa'i gzugs can /
NK128(nyo)001:2047: sgeg pa rdo rje la sogs pa du ma dang ldan pa 'di /
NK128(nyo)001:2048: grub pa'i rnam thar chang bum ye shes sgyu ma'i
NK128(nyo)001:2049: lhar byin gyis brlabs te gzhan la bstan pa'i lo
NK128(nyo)001:2051: de yang slob dpon 'di sh+ai na man+da'i gtsug lag
NK128(nyo)001:2052: khang na tshogs kyi dbus na bzhugs pa'i tshe 'dul
NK128(nyo)001:2053: khrims shin tu dam par yod kyang dam rdzas kyi
NK128(nyo)001:2054: phyir lkog tu chang tshong ma la chang nyo zhing
NK128(nyo)001:2055: bsten pas / skabs shig tu dge 'dun rnams kyis tshor nas 'phyar ka btang du phyin pas /
NK128(nyo)001:2057: nga la chang gi nyes pas chang bum kha bshig nas ltos gsungs pas /
NK128(nyo)001:2058: chang bum chos gos kyis dril nas 'dug pa kha
NK128(nyo)001:2059: bshig nas bltas pas zhi ba sangs rgyas zhe gnyis
NK128(nyo)001:2060: kyi dkyil 'khor du bkra lam 'dug pa mthong /
NK128(nyo)001:2061: yun ring du bltas pas ye shes sgyu ma'i sku
NK128(nyo)001:2062: brtag mi bzod gsungs nas lha rnams thugs kar bsdu
NK128(nyo)001:2063: bar mdzad do // de nas gzhan du gshegs te
NK128(nyo)001:2064: chu bo gang g+aa la mi bying ba sogs rdzu
NK128(nyo)001:2065: 'phrul du ma ston cing grub mtha' rgya mtsho'i pha
NK128(nyo)001:2067: gsang rnying gi 'grel pa par bkab /
NK128(nyo)001:2070: sgrubs thabs la sogs bstan bcos du ma mdzad par grags shing /
NK128(nyo)001:2071: khro phu lugs 'jam dkar gyi lo rgyus las /
NK128(nyo)001:2072: dze ta ri dgra las rnam par rgyal bas slob
NK128(nyo)001:2073: ma 'tshol du byon pas ma ga rdar ma he
NK128(nyo)001:2074: rdzi bo rgas 'khogs 'tsho ba dang bral ba zhig
NK128(nyo)001:2075: snod ldan du gzigs nas chos sgor zhugs shig gsungs
NK128(nyo)001:2076: pas / rgas shing yi ge yang mi shes pas tshe phyi ma rjes su bzung bar zhus pas /
NK128(nyo)001:2077: slob dpon gyis 'jam dkar gyi bsgrub thabs gsungs shing
NK128(nyo)001:2078: 'jam dpal zhi khro'i dkyil 'khor du dbang bskur te
NK128(nyo)001:2079: gsang mtshan sgeg pa rdo rje zhes btags so //
NK128(nyo)001:2080: de n+aa len d+har rab tu byung ba'i mtshan mngon par byang chub pa'i skal ba can zhes btags /
NK128(nyo)001:2081: nor bu'i gling du sku 'khrungs pas nor bu gling pa zhes kyang grags /
NK128(nyo)001:2082: de nas slob dpon la phyag byas te /
NK128(nyo)001:2083: slob dpon gyis bdag rjes su bzung bas shin tu mkhas par gyur kyang /
NK128(nyo)001:2084: da bshad pa byed mi khom sgrubs pa byed zhus pas /
NK128(nyo)001:2085: slob dpon gyis khyod rang la tshe lhag lo bcu yod pa dang /
NK128(nyo)001:2086: nga la yi dam gyis lung bstan lo bcu yod pa las gnyis song brgyad yod la sbyin gyi /
NK128(nyo)001:2087: lo bco brgyad kyi bar du 'gro don gyis /
NK128(nyo)001:2088: de nas yi dam la gsol ba thob dang /
NK128(nyo)001:2089: tshe nyi zla dang mnyam pa'ang srid gsungs nas slob dpon mkha' spyod du bzhud do //
NK128(nyo)001:2090: de nas pan tri ta sgeg pa'i rdo rjes bshad sgrub spel mar mdzad cing /
NK128(nyo)001:2091: nor bu gling pa chung ba sogs rjes su bzung bar grags so //
NK128(nyo)001:2092: des chos blon de wa la dbus 'gyur gyi nags su gsungs /
NK128(nyo)001:2094: gsang mtshan rdo rje nges chen rtsal lam rdo rje
NK128(nyo)001:2095: nges byed rtsal du grags te rig 'dzin gyi sa
NK128(nyo)001:2096: la gshegs so // des mkhan po chos rgyal skyong
NK128(nyo)001:2097: la dbus 'gyur tshal du gsungs shing 'dod pa'i yon
NK128(nyo)001:2098: la gshegs so // tan phul / gsang mtshan rdo
NK128(nyo)001:2099: rje bde byed rtsal du grags shing rig 'dzin gyi
NK128(nyo)001:2101: des gnubs sangs rgyas ye shes rin po che la
NK128(nyo)001:2102: dbus 'gyur tshal du gsungs shing yon du gser srang
NK128(nyo)001:2103: lnga bcu phul nas dbang nos pa'i gsang mtshan rdo
NK128(nyo)001:2104: rje yang dbang gter du btags shing slob dpon 'di'i
NK128(nyo)001:2106: yang nye rgyud ltar na sras mo go ma de
NK128(nyo)001:2107: wi nas slob dpon sangs rgyas gsang ba rdo rje
NK128(nyo)001:2109: des slob dpon bi ma mi tra rdo rje dbang rdzogs rtsal /
NK128(nyo)001:2110: des slob dpon dz+nya na ku m+aa ra dri med zla shar rtsal /
NK128(nyo)001:2111: des slob dpon sog po rdo rje bzhad pa rtsal /
NK128(nyo)001:2112: des slob dpon sangs rgyas ye shes la gsungs zhes grags so //
NK128(nyo)001:2113: de ltar dgongs brgyud sku gsum ni yo ga gsum dang /
NK128(nyo)001:2114: brda brgyud rig rgyud ma h+aa a nu thun mong dang /
NK128(nyo)001:2115: snyan brgyud ma h+aa yo ga ltar bshad zin to
NK128(nyo)001:2116: sgyu 'phrul ba ltar na brgyud tshul mi 'dra ba
NK128(nyo)001:2117: cung zad dang / bi ma las sgyu 'phrul sde
NK128(nyo)001:2118: brgyad du phye nas rma rin chen mchog la bshad
NK128(nyo)001:2119: tshul sogs snang ba rnams sgyu 'phrul kho na'i khog
NK128(nyo)001:2120: phub so so'i skabs su 'byung ba ltar shes par
NK128(nyo)001:2121: cung zad dang / bya'o // 'dir rgya gar ba'i
NK128(nyo)001:2122: lo rgyus la gsum du yod pa'i gnyis pa a
NK128(nyo)001:2123: nu'i brgyud tshul nyid bshad pa la /
NK128(nyo)001:2124: gong ltar rgya gar ba la brgyud pa sum ldan
NK128(nyo)001:2125: du 'chad dgos pa'i dgongs brgyud dang rig brgyud gnyis
NK128(nyo)001:2126: kyi rgyas bshad gong du thun mong du bshad zin
NK128(nyo)001:2128: mkha' klong rnam dag dbyings su kun tu bzang pos
NK128(nyo)001:2129: rigs lnga'i sangs rgyas la thugs ye shes lnga'i dbang
NK128(nyo)001:2130: bskur zhing longs spyod rdzogs skur byin gyis brlabs /
NK128(nyo)001:2131: zhi ba rigs lnga khrag 'thung rigs lngar snang bar
NK128(nyo)001:2132: mdzad de rigs gsum mgon po dang khyad par gsang
NK128(nyo)001:2133: ba'i bdag po mthu stobs kyi bdag por dbang bskur
NK128(nyo)001:2134: / slar yang zhi ba rigs lngar gnas bsgyur te
NK128(nyo)001:2135: sum cu rtsa gsum rnam par rgyal ba'i khang bzang
NK128(nyo)001:2136: du lha'i bu dam pa tog dkar po rigs drug
NK128(nyo)001:2137: gi sems can smin par bya ba'i phyir sprul sku
NK128(nyo)001:2138: thub pa drug tu byin gyis brlabs so /
NK128(nyo)001:2139: de dag ni sku gsum dgongs brgyud kyi tshul lo //
NK128(nyo)001:2140: de ltar rgyal ba rigs gsum mgon po dang /
NK128(nyo)001:2141: khyad par gsang bdag gis dam pa'i rigs can dra
NK128(nyo)001:2142: ma lnga la gsungs pa'i brda brgyud dam rig 'dzin
NK128(nyo)001:2143: rig pa brgyud tshul ni gong du rgyas par bshad
NK128(nyo)001:2144: zin la / dra ma lngas gsang ba'i bdag por
NK128(nyo)001:2145: nos pa'i tshe lha grags ldan mchog skyong gis bdud
NK128(nyo)001:2147: gsang mtshan blo gros 'dus pa rtsal lam thig le chags med rtsal du btags /
NK128(nyo)001:2148: klu rgyal 'jog pos gtsug gi nor bu phul /
NK128(nyo)001:2149: gsang mtshan dbang phyug lhun 'grub rtsal du btags /
NK128(nyo)001:2150: gnod sbyin skar mda' gdong gis gnod sbyin gsang tshig phul /
NK128(nyo)001:2151: gsang mtshan blo gros dad pa rtsal lam rdo rje glog 'byin rtsal du btags /
NK128(nyo)001:2152: srin po lang ka mgrin bcus lus kyi rgyan phul /
NK128(nyo)001:2153: gsang mtshan blo gros thabs ldan rtsal du btags /
NK128(nyo)001:2154: li tsa byi dri med grags pas mi yi rin po che rnam lnga phul /
NK128(nyo)001:2155: gsang mtshan blo gros rab zhi rtsal lam dri med grags pa rtsal du btags so //
NK128(nyo)001:2157: a nu kho na ltar na li tsa byi dri
NK128(nyo)001:2158: med grags pas rgyal po dzaha su ra'i brag phug
NK128(nyo)001:2159: tu dbang bskur zhing yon du in+t+ra ni la khru
NK128(nyo)001:2160: gang pa phul / gsang mtshan rdo rje gsang mchog rtsal du btags shing /
NK128(nyo)001:2161: de'i byin brlabs kyis rgyal po dzahl ltas shar tshul
NK128(nyo)001:2162: sogs gong du rgyas par bshad zin pa ltar ro
NK128(nyo)001:2163: // de yang a nu kho na'i lugs ltar na
NK128(nyo)001:2164: rgyal po dzahranga gis glegs bam gyi don rtogs pa'i
NK128(nyo)001:2165: lugs su byas te slob dpon u pa r+aa dza
NK128(nyo)001:2167: rgyal po dza la u pa r+aa dzas grong khyer
NK128(nyo)001:2168: dpal yon can du rgyal srid rin po che sna
NK128(nyo)001:2170: gsang mtshan rdo rje yang dag rtsal du btags te rig 'dzin gyi sa la gshegs so //
NK128(nyo)001:2171: lo rgyus rnying pa dag las u pa r+aa dzas pu tri gsum la bshad de /
NK128(nyo)001:2172: pu tri gsum ni rgyal po dza'i sras te sha tra pu tri /
NK128(nyo)001:2174: n+aa ga pu tri gsum yin gsungs /
NK128(nyo)001:2175: brgyud tshul rang la u pa r+aa dza'i rjes su in+t+ra b+hu ti yod pa /
NK128(nyo)001:2176: gong du ma h+aa'i skabs su bshad pa ltar /
NK128(nyo)001:2177: sha tra pu tri'i mtshan gyi rnam grangs su in+t+ra b+hu ti yang bshad pas mi 'gal bar sems /
NK128(nyo)001:2178: de ltar sha tra pu tri'am in+t+ra b+hu ti ni
NK128(nyo)001:2179: yab rgyal po dzahs grong khyer skyid pa'i 'byung gnas
NK128(nyo)001:2180: su gsungs te yon du lha'i rin po che bsam
NK128(nyo)001:2181: 'phel phul / gsang mtshan rdo rje zla mdzes rtsal
NK128(nyo)001:2182: du btags te rig 'dzin gyi sa la gshegs skad
NK128(nyo)001:2183: 'phel phul / do // brgyud pa dngos la rgyal
NK128(nyo)001:2184: po dzah'i sras na tra pu tri ram in+t+ra b+hu
NK128(nyo)001:2185: tis klu rgyal n+aa ga pu tra la gsungs te
NK128(nyo)001:2186: 'phel phul / do // / gsang mtshan thig le
NK128(nyo)001:2187: bskyod med rtsal du grags shing rig 'dzin gyi sa
NK128(nyo)001:2189: des rgyal po ga ya pu tra la gsungs shing
NK128(nyo)001:2190: gsang mtshan rdo rje gsal 'phro rtsal te rig 'dzin
NK128(nyo)001:2192: des rgyal po sing ha pu tra la gsungs shing
NK128(nyo)001:2193: gsang mtshan rdo rje 'od zer rtsal te rig 'dzin
NK128(nyo)001:2195: des ku ku r+aa dza phyi ma la phyi'i rgya
NK128(nyo)001:2196: mtsho'i 'gram du gsungs shing dril bu g.yer kha stong
NK128(nyo)001:2197: phul te / gsang mtshan rdo rje bde mchog rtsal
NK128(nyo)001:2198: du grags shing rig 'dzin gyi sa la gshegs so
NK128(nyo)001:2199: phul te / // des ro langs bde ba'i dngos
NK128(nyo)001:2200: grub la glang po che sna'i brag phug tu gsungs
NK128(nyo)001:2201: phul te / // / rtsi sman sna tshogs phul
NK128(nyo)001:2202: zhing gsang mtshan rdo rje bde chen dngos grub rtsal
NK128(nyo)001:2203: lam bdud 'dul drag po rtsal du grags shing rig
NK128(nyo)001:2205: des slob dpon rdo rje bzhad pa la u tra
NK128(nyo)001:2206: sa ri'i tshal du gsungs shing rin po che phul
NK128(nyo)001:2207: / gsang mtshan rdo rje bde byed rtsal du grags shing rig 'dzin gyi sa la gshegs so //
NK128(nyo)001:2208: des za hor gyi rgyal po pra ha sti la
NK128(nyo)001:2209: chu bo sin d+hu'i 'gram du gsungs shing rin po
NK128(nyo)001:2211: gsang mtshan rdo rje dga' rab rtsal lam thig le
NK128(nyo)001:2212: bde byed rtsal du grags shing rig 'dzin gyi sa
NK128(nyo)001:2213: la gshegs so // slob dpon 'di ni gu ru pad+ma 'byung gnas kyi bla ma /
NK128(nyo)001:2214: bka' ma ltar na rab tu byung ba'i mkhan por
NK128(nyo)001:2215: gyur cing spyi ltar yo ga sogs gsan yul de
NK128(nyo)001:2216: yin no // slob dpon pra ha sti la slob ma sh+aakya gsum ste /
NK128(nyo)001:2217: shakya seng ge'am d+ha na rak+shi ta'am o rgyan chen
NK128(nyo)001:2218: po pad+ma 'byung gnas zhes dus gsum mkhyen pa de
NK128(nyo)001:2220: sh+aakya pra b+ha gsum la za hor rgyal po'i khab tu dbang rgyud man ngag dang bcas pa gsungs /
NK128(nyo)001:2221: rang rang gi longs spyod dang bdud rtsi bsil mchog phul /
NK128(nyo)001:2222: gsang mtshan sh+aakya seng ge la rdo rje thod 'phreng
NK128(nyo)001:2223: rtsal lam seng ge sgra sgrogs rtsal du btags te
NK128(nyo)001:2224: gsum ga rig 'dzin gyi sa la gshegs par grags
NK128(nyo)001:2225: shing / slob dpon chen po'i rnam thar mdor bsdus pa ni gong du bstan zin to //
NK128(nyo)001:2226: slob dpon pad+ma 'byung gnas sam d+ha na rak+shi tas
NK128(nyo)001:2227: o rgyan rdo rje phug tu h'u mdzad rdo rje
NK128(nyo)001:2228: la gsungs shing rdzas mchog bzang po phul /
NK128(nyo)001:2229: gsang mtshan rdo rje nyid 'od rtsal du grags te rig 'dzin gyi sa la gshegs so //
NK128(nyo)001:2230: des gu ru s+thi ra ma ti la ga'u rong
NK128(nyo)001:2231: gi brag phug tu gsungs shing rin po che gser
NK128(nyo)001:2232: phul / gsang mtshan rdo rje yang dag rdzogs pa rtsal te rig 'dzin gyi sa la gshegs so //
NK128(nyo)001:2233: des +aa tsar+ya bde ba gsal mdzad la grong khyer dpal yon can du gsungs mnyes mchod phul /
NK128(nyo)001:2234: gsang mtshan rdo rje 'gyur med rtsal lam dbang phyug rtsal te rig 'dzin gyi sa la gshegs so //
NK128(nyo)001:2235: des mdo mkhan d+ha rma b+ho d+hi'am sh+aakya b+ho d+hi
NK128(nyo)001:2236: la yul ma ga d+har gsungs shing rta dang glang
NK128(nyo)001:2237: po che phul / gsang mtshan sher rab mthar phyin rtsal te rig 'dzin gyi sa la gshegs so //
NK128(nyo)001:2238: des rgya gar mkhan po chos rgyal skyong la dpal
NK128(nyo)001:2239: sh+r+ai n+aa lan d+har gsungs shing 'dod pa'i yon tan
NK128(nyo)001:2240: lnga phul / gsang mtshan rdo rje bde byed rtsal
NK128(nyo)001:2241: du grags te rig 'dzin gyi sa la gshegs so
NK128(nyo)001:2242: lnga phul / // des bal bo b+ha su d+ha ra /
NK128(nyo)001:2243: rgya gar gtsug lag dpal dge bru sha'i mkhan po
NK128(nyo)001:2244: che btsan skyes rnams la rgyal po'i khab tu gsungs
NK128(nyo)001:2245: shing gser srang gi dkor cha phul /
NK128(nyo)001:2246: ba su d+ha ri'i gsang mtshan rdo rje thugs mchog rtsal lam rdo rje bdud 'dul rtsal /
NK128(nyo)001:2247: gtsug lag dpal dge'i gsang mtshan rdo rje gtsug tor
NK128(nyo)001:2248: rtsal bru sha'i mkhan po'i gsang mtshan rdo rje chos
NK128(nyo)001:2249: grub rtsal lam rdo rje legs thob rtsal du btags
NK128(nyo)001:2250: te gsum g.yang rig 'dzin gyi sa la gshegs so
NK128(nyo)001:2251: // des sangs rgyas ye shes la gsungs te 'di'i rnam thar 'og tu gsal lo //
NK128(nyo)001:2252: des a nu yo ga'i brgyud gsum rgya gar ba'i lo rgyus bshad zin to //
NK128(nyo)001:2253: gsum pa a ti yo ga'i brgyud gsum rgya gar gyi bla ma'i lo rgyus ni /
NK128(nyo)001:2254: chos sku'i ston pa kun tu bzang pos longs sku
NK128(nyo)001:2255: rdo rje sems dpa' la byin gyis brlabs te gsungs
NK128(nyo)001:2256: / yon du rig pa'i me tog phul lo //
NK128(nyo)001:2257: rdo rje sems dpas gsang bdag tu sprul te bka'
NK128(nyo)001:2258: bsdus shing sprul pa'i sku dga' rab rdo rje la
NK128(nyo)001:2260: yon du 'dod pa'i yon tan lnga phul /
NK128(nyo)001:2261: gsang mtshan rdo rje bde byed rtsal du grags shing
NK128(nyo)001:2262: 'di yan chod rgyal ba dgongs brgyud dang brda brgyud
NK128(nyo)001:2263: do // de ltar sprul sku dga' rab rdo rje'i
NK128(nyo)001:2264: rnam thar mdo tsam bshad pa'i dbang du bgyis na
NK128(nyo)001:2265: do // / ston pa 'das nas lo brgya rtsa
NK128(nyo)001:2266: brgyad lon pa'i dus yab rgyal po d+ha na a
NK128(nyo)001:2267: shwa ka'am chos rgyal mya ngan med ces bya bar
NK128(nyo)001:2268: grags pa de'i bu mo srid pa g.yung drung mtsho
NK128(nyo)001:2270: d+ha na ko sha'i gling phug rin chen g.yu sdings
NK128(nyo)001:2271: tshal du rab tu byung bar bzhed nas byon pa'i
NK128(nyo)001:2272: nam phyed tsam na gser bya ngang pa gshog pa
NK128(nyo)001:2273: g.yu mchu sder lcags las byas pa zhig byung nas
NK128(nyo)001:2274: / g.yung drung mtsho'i snying kar mchu lan gsum btsugs nas 'di skad do //
NK128(nyo)001:2275: srid pa g.yung drung mtsho khyod la do nub mi
NK128(nyo)001:2276: ring dkar po zhig byin gyis brlab tu 'ong gi
NK128(nyo)001:2277: de'i ngag ma bcag zer nas ngang pa de 'phur
NK128(nyo)001:2278: skad / de ni rdo rje sems dpa'i rnam sprul ye shes kyi mkha' 'gro yin gsungs so //
NK128(nyo)001:2279: de'i nub rmi lam du mi ring dkar po zhig
NK128(nyo)001:2280: gis chu bum pa gang la byin ba rlabs byas
NK128(nyo)001:2281: nas g.yung drung mtsho'i spyi bo nas blug par rmis
NK128(nyo)001:2282: shing / mi de yang rdo rje sems dpa'i sprul par grags /
NK128(nyo)001:2283: nang par sgor phyin rtsa na bya ngang pa de dpung par chags nas 'di skad de /
NK128(nyo)001:2284: srid pa g.yung drung mtsho khyod la lo dus zla
NK128(nyo)001:2285: ba'i nang du khye'u ngo mtshar can zhig 'khrungs par
NK128(nyo)001:2286: 'dug gis / de la gtsigs legs par gyis shig zer ro //
NK128(nyo)001:2287: de nas zla ba dgu ngo bcu lon pa dang /
NK128(nyo)001:2288: g.yung drung mtsho'i snying kar gser gyi rdo rje rtse
NK128(nyo)001:2289: lnga pa zhig rang 'khrungs kyis byon nas de nyid
NK128(nyo)001:2291: gser gyi rdo rje rang zhig gi nang nas khye'u
NK128(nyo)001:2292: mtshan nyid dang ldan pa rdo rje sems dpa' nam
NK128(nyo)001:2293: mkha' che zhal 'don du mdzad pa zhig 'khrungs /
NK128(nyo)001:2294: yab la de'i lo rgyus bsnyad pas yab kyi zhal nas /
NK128(nyo)001:2295: 'di ni sprul pa'i sku dngos su byon pa yin
NK128(nyo)001:2296: gsungs nas shin tu mnyes te mtshan yang sprul sku
NK128(nyo)001:2297: dga' rab rdo rje zhes gsol lo //
NK128(nyo)001:2298: de nas dga' rab rdo rjes rgyal po d+ha he
NK128(nyo)001:2299: na zhes bya ba'i bu mo rin chen gsal sgron
NK128(nyo)001:2300: grogs su khrid nas zla gam 'od 'phro seng ge
NK128(nyo)001:2301: nags steng gi tshal du slob dpon ka ra la
NK128(nyo)001:2302: rtsal chen gyi dbang zhes bya ste phar phyin mdzad
NK128(nyo)001:2304: pad+ma me tog 'ja' tshon du slob dpon chen po
NK128(nyo)001:2305: klu sgrub tsana di ka la gtan tshigs bgro gleng
NK128(nyo)001:2306: gi dbang zhes bya ste kri ya'i dbang chog nyer
NK128(nyo)001:2307: drug nos / lha bya skad snyan ljon shing tshal
NK128(nyo)001:2308: du slob dpon chen po ku ma ti la yo
NK128(nyo)001:2309: ga bkra shis drug cu rtsa bzhi'i dbang nos /
NK128(nyo)001:2310: de ltar phyi dbang brgya rtsa nos nas /
NK128(nyo)001:2311: slob dpon chen po rab tu gsal ba la /
NK128(nyo)001:2312: gdan bzhi ni zhabs drung du 'khrigs shing phyogs bzhi nas rgyan rin po che rnam lnga 'bar ba /
NK128(nyo)001:2313: mi nor rnam bzhi sa la dod pa /
NK128(nyo)001:2314: mdzes sdug gi me tog sna tshogs pa las skyes pa /
NK128(nyo)001:2315: mdzes pa'i dar bkra dpag bsam gyi shing las 'byung ba /
NK128(nyo)001:2316: 'bru sna dgu ljon shing gi yal ga las ltung ba /
NK128(nyo)001:2317: de ltar 'dod yon lnga'i longs spyod ma spangs phun sum tshogs pas mdzes par byas shing /
NK128(nyo)001:2318: slob dpon des kyang sku rgyud sangs rgyas mnyam sbyor /
NK128(nyo)001:2319: gsung rgyud zla gsang thig le /
NK128(nyo)001:2321: yon tan gyi rgyud dpal mchog dang po /
NK128(nyo)001:2322: 'phrin las kyi rgyud karma ma le /
NK128(nyo)001:2323: kri ya thams cad kyi rgyal po cha gsum /
NK128(nyo)001:2324: mtshams thams cad kyi rgyal po srung ba'i 'khor lo /
NK128(nyo)001:2325: dkyil 'khor thams cad kyi rgyal po yang dag dgu pa /
NK128(nyo)001:2326: rdzas thams cad kyi rgyal po lha mo gnas mkhar /
NK128(nyo)001:2327: ma tra ma zhal gshin rje gsal shing /
NK128(nyo)001:2328: sman thams cad kyi rgyal po bdud rtsi bum chung /
NK128(nyo)001:2329: zhi ba thams cad kyi rgyal po rin chen dra ba /
NK128(nyo)001:2330: khro bo thams cad kyi rgyal po bskyed rdzogs chen mo /
NK128(nyo)001:2331: sgom pa thams cad kyi rgyal pos ya mtshan mi g.yo ba /
NK128(nyo)001:2332: dbang thams cad kyi rgyal po nor bu'i phreng ba /
NK128(nyo)001:2335: dkyil 'khor bkod pa la sogs bstan bcos kyi bka' babs so //
NK128(nyo)001:2336: byu ru dmar po chu mig dgu sgril gyi tshal du ro langs bde ba dang /
NK128(nyo)001:2337: rin chen gsal sgron la dbang bzhi rdzogs su bskur te /
NK128(nyo)001:2338: de yang phyi yo byad zang zing rdzas kyi dbang rdzogs par bskur /
NK128(nyo)001:2339: nang rig pa ting nge 'dzin gyis dbang dang ye shes lnga'i dbang bskur /
NK128(nyo)001:2340: gsang ba byang chub sems kyi thugs kyi dbang bzhi bskur ro //
NK128(nyo)001:2341: de nas rtog tshogs lha'i dbang bskur nas shel gyi
NK128(nyo)001:2342: phyag shing rin chen lngas brgyan pa zhig dbang rtags
NK128(nyo)001:2343: su sbyin no // grogs mo la snang srid kyi
NK128(nyo)001:2344: me long 'dzam bu'i gling dus gcig tu gsal ba
NK128(nyo)001:2345: zhig kyang dbang rtags su sbyin no //
NK128(nyo)001:2346: de nas rin chen g.yu sdigs tshal du phyir byon te rgya gar gyi pha rol /
NK128(nyo)001:2347: o rgyan gyi tshu rol ma ga d+ha'i brag phug tu o rgyan rgyal po d+harma ka ya dang /
NK128(nyo)001:2348: klu'i bu mo rgya mtsho gnyis kyis o rgyan gyi
NK128(nyo)001:2349: yul nas slob ma bsdus te tshom bu stong gi
NK128(nyo)001:2351: rig 'dzin khri phrag thams cad kyang mngon par rdzogs
NK128(nyo)001:2352: par sangs rgyas pa 'ba' zhig byung ngo slob dpon
NK128(nyo)001:2353: 'di'i rnam thar gter ma'i phyogs dang snying thig gi
NK128(nyo)001:2354: lo rgyus sogs mi 'dra ba du ma yod kyang
NK128(nyo)001:2355: / 'di ni snyan brgyud zab mo khungs kyi gtad
NK128(nyo)001:2356: rgya mdo lugs nyid btsan par byas te bris so
NK128(nyo)001:2357: / // des slob dpon 'jam dpal bshes gnyen la o rgyan rin chen g.yu sdings gsungs te /
NK128(nyo)001:2358: yon du rang gi mgo dang snying phul nas gsang
NK128(nyo)001:2359: mtshan rdo rje gzhon nu rtsal te rig 'dzin gyi
NK128(nyo)001:2361: slob dpon 'di'i rnam thar bka' ma phyogs kyi yig
NK128(nyo)001:2362: rnying cher ma rnyed snying thig dang snyan brgyud rdor
NK128(nyo)001:2363: zam ltar zur tsam bkod pa ni /
NK128(nyo)001:2364: rdo rje gdan gyi nub phyogs rim pa gnyis pa zhes bya ba'i grong khyer du /
NK128(nyo)001:2365: yab bram ze legs ldan ston pa dang yum snang ba sgron ma gnyis kyi sras su 'khrungs /
NK128(nyo)001:2366: mtshan 'jam dpal bshes gnyen du gsol /
NK128(nyo)001:2367: rigs pa'i gnas lnga la mkhas par sbyangs pa zhig go //
NK128(nyo)001:2368: de la 'phags pa 'jam dpal rnon pos lung bstan pa /
NK128(nyo)001:2369: kye rigs kyi bu tshe gcig gis sangs rgyas thob
NK128(nyo)001:2370: par 'dod na dur khrod chen po bsil ba'i tshal
NK128(nyo)001:2371: du song zhig / ces thos ma thag tu slob
NK128(nyo)001:2372: dpon chen po dga' rab rdo rje dang mjal nas
NK128(nyo)001:2373: dbang khrid rdzogs par mdzad de dga' rab rdo rje
NK128(nyo)001:2376: kye ma kye hud kye ma klong //
NK128(nyo)001:2377: ston pa sgron me'i 'od nub na //
NK128(nyo)001:2378: 'jig rten mun pa gang gis sel //
NK128(nyo)001:2379: zhes sogs smre sngags phyungs pas /
NK128(nyo)001:2380: rin po che'i ga'u sen gang pa nas /
NK128(nyo)001:2381: tshig gsum gnad du brdeg pa'i 'das rjes babs nas
NK128(nyo)001:2382: slob dpon gyis snyan brgyud dang bshad brgyud du phye
NK128(nyo)001:2383: / snyan brgyud rnams mchan du btab /
NK128(nyo)001:2384: bshad brgyud kyi snod ma rnyed pas dpe rnams rdo
NK128(nyo)001:2385: rje gdan gyi byang shar du pha bong rdo rje
NK128(nyo)001:2386: rgya gram can la sbas te /
NK128(nyo)001:2387: dur khrod so sa'i gling du spyod pa la gshegs
NK128(nyo)001:2388: te sh+r+ai sing+ha rjes su bzung ste nam mkha' la
NK128(nyo)001:2390: snyan brgyud rdo rje zam pa lta na slob dpon
NK128(nyo)001:2391: 'jam dpal bshes gnyen gyis thugs dgongs la bskal pa
NK128(nyo)001:2392: grangs med par bsags sbyangs byas pas grol ba las
NK128(nyo)001:2393: / khyad par du gyur pa chos nyid kyi don skad cig mas rtogs nas /
NK128(nyo)001:2394: tshe gcig gis sangs rgya ba'i thabs 'dra yod srid pa gzhan la dris kyang thabs med pas /
NK128(nyo)001:2395: n+aa lan d+ha'i pan+di ta rnams la dri'o snyams te dris pas /
NK128(nyo)001:2396: mtshan nyid kyi pan+di ta rnams cang mi gsung /
NK128(nyo)001:2397: gsang sngags kyi pan+di ta rnams kyi zhal nas /
NK128(nyo)001:2398: chos nyid kyi don de ltar rtogs pa 'di na med de /
NK128(nyo)001:2399: 'di nas nub phyogs o rgyan gyi yul d+ha na ko sha'i gling phyi'i rgya mtsho'i 'gram /
NK128(nyo)001:2400: me tog u dum wa ra skye ba'i sa /
NK128(nyo)001:2402: dur khrod chen po gser gling he chen brdal bya bar /
NK128(nyo)001:2403: sgrub gnas gser gyi brag phug yu ba can zhes
NK128(nyo)001:2404: bya ba na slob dpon dga' rab rdo rje zhes
NK128(nyo)001:2406: de yang sems dag lha'i bu zhes bya ba snang gzugs su grub la /
NK128(nyo)001:2407: reg pa'i gzugs su ma grub pa zhig zhal gzigs /
NK128(nyo)001:2408: chos nyid kyi don skad cig gis rtogs nas tshe
NK128(nyo)001:2409: gcig gis 'tshang rgya ba'i chos khong la yod kyis
NK128(nyo)001:2411: slob dpon gyis der 'gro ba dka' sla ji ltar yod dris pas /
NK128(nyo)001:2412: dka' tshegs shin tu che zhing zla ba bcu gsum lam du 'gro dgos la /
NK128(nyo)001:2413: lam gyi 'jigs pa gnod sbyin dang mkha' 'gro ma
NK128(nyo)001:2414: rung pa dang gcan gzan gtum po sbrul gdug pa
NK128(nyo)001:2416: de ltar 'jigs pa med na nged rnams kyang 'gro bar rigs /
NK128(nyo)001:2418: slob dpon gyi thugs la lus la bar gcod byung yang /
NK128(nyo)001:2419: sems slob dpon gyi drung du rtol te byin gyis brlabs yong bas /
NK128(nyo)001:2420: de phyir the tshom med par 'agro'o snyam ste byon
NK128(nyo)001:2421: pas lus sems la bar chad med par zla ba
NK128(nyo)001:2423: der ri brag gcan gzan mang po gnas pa zhig na /
NK128(nyo)001:2424: rab tu byung ba'i cha byad can sham thabs thod du bcings pa /
NK128(nyo)001:2425: mda' lnga gzhu gcig phyag na bsnams pa zhig dang mjal te /
NK128(nyo)001:2426: 'di slob dpon yin nges gzhan gyis sa 'dir mi tshugs snyams nas /
NK128(nyo)001:2427: the tshom med par gser gyi man+dala phul /
NK128(nyo)001:2429: bskor ba lan bdun byas nas khyed kyi rtogs pa bdag la bskyed par zhu 'tshal /
NK128(nyo)001:2430: zhes zhus pas ci yang mi gsungs /
NK128(nyo)001:2431: de ltar lan gsum zhus pas kyang ci yang mi gsungs par gshegs so //
NK128(nyo)001:2432: der gdams ngag 'dra gnang du re nas phyi nas phar 'brangs te phyin pas /
NK128(nyo)001:2433: dur khrod chen po der slebs te nyin lan gsum mtshan gsum du man+dala yang phul /
NK128(nyo)001:2435: bskor ba yang byas te zla ngo re la zhu ba'i don re phul yang cang mi gsung ngo //
NK128(nyo)001:2436: de ltar zla ba ril po bcu gsum lon pa dang /
NK128(nyo)001:2437: da ni bla mas thugs la mi 'dogs par 'dug snyams thugs mug nas /
NK128(nyo)001:2438: ka ba li nas spu gri bton te rang gi ske bcad la shi'o snyam tsa na /
NK128(nyo)001:2439: slob dpon gyis 'jam dpal bshes gnyen zhes bos nas /
NK128(nyo)001:2441: khyod ci 'dod pa yin zhes gsungs /
NK128(nyo)001:2442: bdag ni chos kyi don skad cig mar rtogs par
NK128(nyo)001:2443: tshe gcig gis 'tshang rgya ba zhig zhu zhus pas
NK128(nyo)001:2444: / khyod kyi da dung ma go'am gsungs pa la
NK128(nyo)001:2445: bdag gi ni da dung ma go ma rtogs so
NK128(nyo)001:2447: slob dpon dga' rab rdo rje'i zhal nas /
NK128(nyo)001:2450: zhag bdun du 'bru gsum gyi rang sgra rgyun ma chad par byung ngo //
NK128(nyo)001:2451: 'di ni skye 'gag gnyis med ka dag gi don yin par sems /
NK128(nyo)001:2452: slar yang sur+ya d+ha ra zhes bya ba'i brda bstan
NK128(nyo)001:2453: te nyi ma'i snying po la ltos zhes par go
NK128(nyo)001:2454: nas bltas pas / nyi ma'i snying po dus gsum
NK128(nyo)001:2456: nas bltas pas / med pa / de 'dra ba
NK128(nyo)001:2457: gcig tu don rang gi mtshan nyid chos bzhi ldan
NK128(nyo)001:2458: du rtogs pa ni lhun grub kyi don /
NK128(nyo)001:2459: de ltar brda la brten nas don mchog gi dngos
NK128(nyo)001:2460: grub de nyid du thob pa'i zhar la thun mong
NK128(nyo)001:2461: gi dngos grub kyang 'grub ste slob dpon 'jam dpal
NK128(nyo)001:2462: bshes gnyen de bya 'phur ba bzhin du lho phyogs
NK128(nyo)001:2463: gyad kyi yul / b+hee ta la'i gling /
NK128(nyo)001:2464: shing dra ba gtsug dgu bkod pa'i tshal /
NK128(nyo)001:2466: dpal yon tan thams cad 'byung ba'i grong khyer du
NK128(nyo)001:2467: gshegs te sh+r+ai sing+ha rjes su bzung ste 'od phung
NK128(nyo)001:2468: chen por gyur / lo rgyus 'di dag 'dra min
NK128(nyo)001:2469: cung zad 'dug kyang drang nges kyi khyad par du
NK128(nyo)001:2470: chen por gyur / shes so // des rgyal po
NK128(nyo)001:2471: d+ha na ta lo dang shin tu bstan pa gnyis
NK128(nyo)001:2472: la yul d+ha he na'i tshal du gsungs shing /
NK128(nyo)001:2473: yon du rgyal srid rin po che sna bdun phul /
NK128(nyo)001:2474: gsang mtshan rdo rje dga' byed tshal du btags shing
NK128(nyo)001:2475: dgung lo stong chig brgyar bzhugs te rig 'dzin gyi
NK128(nyo)001:2476: sar gshegs so // des sras thu bo r+aa dza
NK128(nyo)001:2477: ha sti la yul tsan dan gyi nags su gsungs
NK128(nyo)001:2478: shing yid bzhin gyi nor bu rin po che phul
NK128(nyo)001:2479: sar gshegs so // / gsang mtshan rdo rje gsal
NK128(nyo)001:2480: ba rtsal te dgung lo brgyad brgyar bzhugs nas rig
NK128(nyo)001:2482: des sras mo wa r+aa ni dang rgyal po gser
NK128(nyo)001:2483: mkhar can gnyis la yul a nu ta'i tshal du
NK128(nyo)001:2484: gsungs shing lus kyi rgyan rnams phul /
NK128(nyo)001:2485: gsang mtshan rdo rje mdzes ma rtsal te dgung lo
NK128(nyo)001:2486: dgu brgyar bzhugs shing rig 'dzin gyi sa la gshegs
NK128(nyo)001:2487: so // des klu'i rgyal po 'jog po dang klu
NK128(nyo)001:2488: mo yak+sha kha 'dul la sin+d+hu'i 'gram du gsungs shing
NK128(nyo)001:2489: gtsugs shing gtsug gi nor bu phul /
NK128(nyo)001:2490: gsang mtshan rdo rje rdzu 'phrul rtsal te lo sum stong bzhugs shing rig 'dzin gyi sar gshegs so //
NK128(nyo)001:2491: des sras mo gnod sbyin mo byang chub dang bram
NK128(nyo)001:2492: ze mo blo gros la brda he ne'i rtsar gsungs
NK128(nyo)001:2493: shing bu dang rgyal srid phul /
NK128(nyo)001:2494: gsang mtshan rdo rje g.yung drung rtsal te dgung lo
NK128(nyo)001:2495: sum brgyar bzhugs shing rig 'dzin gyi sa la gshegs
NK128(nyo)001:2496: so // des gzung ma a ra li dang rgyal
NK128(nyo)001:2497: po glog 'od la yul d+ha na ko sha'i shar
NK128(nyo)001:2498: phug tu gsungs shing rang lus phul /
NK128(nyo)001:2499: gsang mtshan rdo rje dbyings ma rtsal te lo brgyar bzhugs shing rig 'dzin gyi sa la gshegs so //
NK128(nyo)001:2500: des slob dpon ak+sho b+h+yahl gsungs shing /
NK128(nyo)001:2501: gsang mtshan rdo rje dngos grub rtsal te rig 'dzin gyi sa la gshegs so /
NK128(nyo)001:2502: slob dpon 'di'i rnam thar zhib par ma rnyed do //
NK128(nyo)001:2503: des khyi'i mkhan po slob dpon ku ku ra dza
NK128(nyo)001:2504: rgyal po dza la d+ha he na'i 'du khang du
NK128(nyo)001:2505: gsungs shing gser gyi dril bu g.yer kha stong phul
NK128(nyo)001:2506: / gsang mtshan rdo rje drag po rtsal te lo
NK128(nyo)001:2507: drug stong bzhugs shing rig 'dzin gyi sa la gshegs
NK128(nyo)001:2508: / so // des smad 'tshong ma bud+d+ha sa ma
NK128(nyo)001:2509: ya dang bram ze mo nyi ma la d+ha he
NK128(nyo)001:2510: na'i gling phug tu gsungs shing rin chen rnam lnga
NK128(nyo)001:2511: / so // phul / gsang mtshan rdo rje yang
NK128(nyo)001:2512: dag rtsal te lo lnga brgyar bzhugs shing rig 'dzin
NK128(nyo)001:2514: des smad 'tshong ma b+hud+d+ha sa ma ti la yul
NK128(nyo)001:2515: u ti'i tshal du gsungs shing rta dang glang po
NK128(nyo)001:2516: bdun phul / gsang mtshan rdo rje nyi 'od rtsal
NK128(nyo)001:2517: te lo drug brgyar bzhugs shing rig 'dzin gyi sa
NK128(nyo)001:2518: bdun phul / la gshegs so // des o rgyan
NK128(nyo)001:2519: gyi mkhan po ma h+aa r+aa dza dang rgyal po
NK128(nyo)001:2520: thor cog can la o rgyan gyi yul rin chen
NK128(nyo)001:2521: g.yu sdings tshal du gsungs shing gser srang drug stong
NK128(nyo)001:2522: bdun phul / la gshegs so // phul / gsang
NK128(nyo)001:2523: mtshan rdo rje rdzu 'phrul rtsal te lo drug stong
NK128(nyo)001:2524: bzhugs shing rig 'dzin gyi sa la gshegs so //
NK128(nyo)001:2525: des sras mo go ma de w+ai dang bram ze
NK128(nyo)001:2526: mo gsal ba'i rgyan la yul pad+ma'i me tog tshal
NK128(nyo)001:2527: du gsungs shing rta dang glang po phul /
NK128(nyo)001:2528: gsang mtshan rdo rje dngos grub rtsal te lo brgyad
NK128(nyo)001:2529: brgyar bzhugs shing rig 'dzin gyi sa la gshegs so
NK128(nyo)001:2530: // des slob dpon +aa lo ke dang rgyal po
NK128(nyo)001:2531: su mi ta la ljon shing gi nags su gsungs
NK128(nyo)001:2532: shing gser phye phul do phul /
NK128(nyo)001:2533: gsang mtshan rdo rje g.yung drung rtsal te lo sum
NK128(nyo)001:2534: brgyar bzhugs shing rig 'dzin gyi sa la gshegs so
NK128(nyo)001:2535: // des khyi'i mkhan po phyi ma la gsungs te
NK128(nyo)001:2536: gsang mtshan rdo rje bdud 'dul rtsal te rig 'dzin
NK128(nyo)001:2538: 'di'i lo rgyus kyang ma rnyed do //
NK128(nyo)001:2539: des lha'i mkhan po ma h+aa r+aa dza dang blo
NK128(nyo)001:2540: gros mtha' yas la shing ku ti'i rtsar gsungs shing
NK128(nyo)001:2541: / lha'i bdud rtsi 'chi med dang nor bu bsam 'phel phul /
NK128(nyo)001:2542: gsang mtshan rdo rje sgeg pa rtsal te rig 'dzin gyi sa la gshegs so //
NK128(nyo)001:2543: des drang srong b+ha shi ta dang stobs chen 'bar
NK128(nyo)001:2544: ba la chu bo gang+g+aa'i bye ma'i steng du gsungs
NK128(nyo)001:2545: shing rin po che'i gser phul /
NK128(nyo)001:2546: gsang mtshan rdo rje lhun 'grub rtsal te lo bzhi
NK128(nyo)001:2547: brgyar bzhugs shing rig 'dzin gyi sa la gshegs so
NK128(nyo)001:2548: // des gzungs ma bdag nyid ma dang bram ze
NK128(nyo)001:2549: mo sman gyi blo gros la shing nal byi'i rtsar
NK128(nyo)001:2550: gsungs shing lung ras longs spyod phul /
NK128(nyo)001:2551: gsang mtshan rdo rje 'od mchog rtsal te lo brgya
NK128(nyo)001:2552: nyer lnga bzhugs shiing rig 'dzin gyi sa la gshegs
NK128(nyo)001:2553: so // des slob dpon n+aa ga rdzu na dang
NK128(nyo)001:2554: rgyal po grub pa'i snying po la yul d+ha he
NK128(nyo)001:2555: na'i nyi ma khud du gsungs shing gser srang gnyis
NK128(nyo)001:2556: so // stong phul / gsang mtshan rdo rje thogs
NK128(nyo)001:2557: med rtsal te lo stong bzhugs shing rig 'dzin gyi
NK128(nyo)001:2559: slob dpon 'di'i rnam thar mdor bsdus su brjod na /
NK128(nyo)001:2560: sangs rgyas mya ngan las 'das nas lo bzhi brgya
NK128(nyo)001:2561: na lho phyogs bee r+b+ha'i yul du bram ze phyug
NK128(nyo)001:2562: po zhig la bu med pas rmi lam du bram
NK128(nyo)001:2563: ze brgya la chos ston drangs na bu rnyed par
NK128(nyo)001:2564: lhas lung bstan pa ltar byas te gsol ba btab
NK128(nyo)001:2565: pas / khye'u zhig btsas te mtshan btags pas /
NK128(nyo)001:2566: mtshan bzang mod kyi 'on kyang zhag bdun gyi tshe las med do zer /
NK128(nyo)001:2568: bram ze brgya la chos ston drangs pas zla ba
NK128(nyo)001:2569: bdun dang dge slong brgya la chos ston drangs pas
NK128(nyo)001:2570: lo bdun thub cing de nas thabs med zer ro
NK128(nyo)001:2571: // de bzhin byas pas lo bdun du nye bar gyur nas /
NK128(nyo)001:2572: de rjes bu'i ro mthong ba pha mas ma bzod de g.yog dang bcas te 'khyam du btang ngo //
NK128(nyo)001:2573: de rim gyis song nas kha sar pani'i zhal bltas
NK128(nyo)001:2574: te dpal n+aa len da'i sgor song ste snyan ngag
NK128(nyo)001:2575: gi rigs byed dag bsgrags pa /
NK128(nyo)001:2576: de na bram ze chen po s+aa ra ha bzhugs
NK128(nyo)001:2577: pas gsan te nang du bos pa la gtam bsnyad
NK128(nyo)001:2578: pa la lo rgyus rnams bshad pas /
NK128(nyo)001:2579: blon po na re rab tu byung nus na thabs yod gsungs pas /
NK128(nyo)001:2580: rab tu byung ste tshe dpag med 'chi bdag 'joms
NK128(nyo)001:2581: pa'i dkyil 'khor du dbang bskur nas gzungs 'don du
NK128(nyo)001:2582: bcug / khyad par lo bdun lon pa'i nub mtshan
NK128(nyo)001:2583: thog thag bton pas 'chi bdag gi 'jigs pa las
NK128(nyo)001:2584: thar te pha ma'i khyim du song ste phrad pas
NK128(nyo)001:2586: slar yang bram ze chen po s+aa ra ha la
NK128(nyo)001:2587: gsang 'dus sogs kyi gzhung gdams ngag dang bcas te
NK128(nyo)001:2588: mang du zhus / n+aa len+da'i mkhan po sgra gcan
NK128(nyo)001:2589: 'dzin bzang po las bsnyen par rdzogs te mtshan yang
NK128(nyo)001:2590: dge slong dpal ldan zhes grags so //
NK128(nyo)001:2591: de'i tshe n+aa len dra'i dge 'dun gyi zhal ta
NK128(nyo)001:2592: pa babs te byas pa'i tshe yul der mu ge
NK128(nyo)001:2593: chen po byung ba la gling bar nas gser 'gyur
NK128(nyo)001:2594: gyi rtsi blangs te gser 'gyur byas shing gdugs tshod
NK128(nyo)001:2595: sbyar ro // dbyar gnas thon pa dang dge 'dun
NK128(nyo)001:2596: gyis mi rid sa shi bar mthong ste mu ge
NK128(nyo)001:2597: byung ba shes te gdugs tshod ji ltar rnyed de
NK128(nyo)001:2598: sbyar ro // sbyar dris pas / sngar gyi tshul brjod pas /
NK128(nyo)001:2599: dge 'dun la ma zhus par gser 'gyur byas pas
NK128(nyo)001:2600: dge 'dun log 'tsho la sbyar bas nyes zhes gnas
NK128(nyo)001:2601: nas phyungs te sgrub sbyangs su gtsug lag khang dang
NK128(nyo)001:2602: mchod rten bye ba gyis shig ces basgo'o //
NK128(nyo)001:2603: de nas 'jig rten dang 'jig rten las 'das pa'i dngos grub thob nas /
NK128(nyo)001:2604: de'i tshe dge slong bde byed ces bya bas rig
NK128(nyo)001:2605: pa'i rgyan ces pa'i gzhung 'bum phrag bcu gnyis pa
NK128(nyo)001:2606: zhig byas te bstan pa thams cad sun phyungs pas
NK128(nyo)001:2607: / de 'dul ba'i phyir n+aa len drar chos gsungs so //
NK128(nyo)001:2608: de'i tshe byis pa gnyis chos nyan cing sa 'og
NK128(nyo)001:2609: tu 'gro ba 'dug pa su yin dris pas klu
NK128(nyo)001:2611: slob dpon gyis gnod sbyin gyi 'dam khyer shog gsungs pas /
NK128(nyo)001:2612: klu de gnyis kyis de'i tshul klu'i rgyal po la zhus pas /
NK128(nyo)001:2613: des na slob dpon spyan drongs zer te spyan 'dren du 'ongs pas /
NK128(nyo)001:2614: don du 'gyur bar mkhyen nas klu'i yul du byon te chos gsungs so //
NK128(nyo)001:2615: de nas klus bzhugs par zhus pas /
NK128(nyo)001:2616: nga mchod rten bye ba bzhengs pa'i 'dam 'tshol ba dang /
NK128(nyo)001:2617: 'bum gdan 'dren du 'ongs kyi sdad mi khom gsungs te /
NK128(nyo)001:2620: yi ge nyung ngu gdan drangs te 'bum gyi 'phro cung zad klu rnams kyis ma bskur zhes grags /
NK128(nyo)001:2621: 'jim pa des mchod rten bye ba bzhengs pa'i grogs
NK128(nyo)001:2622: klu rnams kyis byas pas klu sgrub ces pa'i mtshan
NK128(nyo)001:2623: du grags so // gzhan du n+aa g+aa rdzu na
NK128(nyo)001:2624: ste n+aa ga ni klu ste chos dbyings su skyes
NK128(nyo)001:2625: pa rtag chad gnyis kyi mtha' la mi gnas pa
NK128(nyo)001:2626: du grags so // / gsung rab rin po che'i
NK128(nyo)001:2627: mdzod la mnga' brnyes pa bsreg cing gsal ba'i lta
NK128(nyo)001:2629: ardzu na ni srid sgrub ste chos kyi rgyal srid skyong ba dang /
NK128(nyo)001:2630: nyes pa'i dgra tshogs 'dul bas srid sgrub ste /
NK128(nyo)001:2631: de bsdus pas klu sgrub ces kyang grags so de
NK128(nyo)001:2632: nas li kha ra shing 'phel du gser 'gyur mdzad
