NK128(nyo)001:2633: de sbyin pa rgya chen po dang /
NK128(nyo)001:2634: lhag par bram ze rgan rgon gnyis la gser mang
NK128(nyo)001:2635: po gnang bas dad de rgan pos nye gnas byas
NK128(nyo)001:2636: / chos bstan pa shes nas slob dpon klu'i byang chub tu gyur to //
NK128(nyo)001:2637: de nas shar phyogs pa tra be sa dang yul ta rdar byon nas lha khang mang po bzhengs /
NK128(nyo)001:2638: dril bu lta bu'i brag gser du sgyur bar bzhed
NK128(nyo)001:2639: pa lhas bkag ste ma grub sgra mi snyan du
NK128(nyo)001:2640: byon pa'i lam grong khyer sa la ma nar byis
NK128(nyo)001:2641: pa dze ta ka lag ris las rgyal por lung
NK128(nyo)001:2642: bstan / sgra mi snyan du byon nas na bza' shing la bkal te khrus mdzad pas /
NK128(nyo)001:2643: gos de rnams kyis khyer ba la nga'i yin gsungs pas nga bdag can zer nas lta skad /
NK128(nyo)001:2644: der sgra mi snyan pa'i don mdzad de phyir byon
NK128(nyo)001:2645: pas sngar lung bstan pa'i byis pa rgyal por gyur
NK128(nyo)001:2646: pa des rin po che mang po phul /
NK128(nyo)001:2647: skyes len du chos kyi rin po che rin chen phreng ba gnang /
NK128(nyo)001:2648: slob dpon 'dis bstan pa'i bya ba dge 'dun gyi zhal ta mdzad /
NK128(nyo)001:2649: de'i rkyen gyis mchod rten dang lha khang mang po bzhengs /
NK128(nyo)001:2650: rdo rje gdan la rdo rje'i dra mig gis ra bas bskor /
NK128(nyo)001:2651: dpal ldan 'bras spungs kyi mchod rten gyi bkod pa bzhengs /
NK128(nyo)001:2652: dbu ma'i bstan bcos mang po dang /
NK128(nyo)001:2655: mdo 'grel sogs du ma mdzad tshul rnams yongs grags
NK128(nyo)001:2656: ltar la lo drug brgyar bzhugs shing mthar rgyal po
NK128(nyo)001:2657: bde spyod bzang po'i bu nus ldan la /
NK128(nyo)001:2658: mas gos srubs med zhig sbyin pa ma gyon par rgyal srid 'dzin dus dgos zer ba la /
NK128(nyo)001:2659: mas khyod kyis rgyal srid 'dzin pa mi 'ongs yab
NK128(nyo)001:2660: dang klu sgrub tshe'i bcud len stabs su byas pas
NK128(nyo)001:2661: slob dpon klu sgrub dang srog gcig smras pas /
NK128(nyo)001:2662: des dpal gyi ri la klu sgrub bzhugs pa'i sar phyin te dbu blangs pas /
NK128(nyo)001:2663: chod gsungs te ral gris bcad kyang ma chod par /
NK128(nyo)001:2664: slob dpon gyi zhal nas ngas rtsa ku sha bcad
NK128(nyo)001:2665: pas srog chags shi ba'i rnam smin yod pas ku
NK128(nyo)001:2667: mgul chod de mgul gyi rtsa ba nas /
NK128(nyo)001:2668: da ni bde ba can gyi 'jig rten du /
NK128(nyo)001:2669: phyi nas lus 'di la yang 'jug par 'gyur /
NK128(nyo)001:2671: des dbu khyer te phyin pa lam khar gnod sbyin
NK128(nyo)001:2672: mos phyogs phrogs te dpag tshad gcig sleb pa'i sar
NK128(nyo)001:2673: dor ro // dbu dang sku lus gnyis ka ma
NK128(nyo)001:2674: nyams pa lo re bzhin nyer song ba mthar sbyar
NK128(nyo)001:2675: sku des bstan 'gro'i don mdzad par gsungs so //
NK128(nyo)001:2676: rang lugs su lo stong bzhugs par bshad pas grub
NK128(nyo)001:2677: pa'i mdzad pa yin pas mtha' gcig tu 'dzin par
NK128(nyo)001:2678: mi bya'o // de ltar slob dpon klu sgrub snying
NK128(nyo)001:2679: po'am n+aa g+aa rdzu na des slob dpon de wa
NK128(nyo)001:2680: r+aa dza dang lha'i dbang po la lha'i dpag bsam
NK128(nyo)001:2683: gsang mtshan rdo rje gsang ba rtsal te rig 'dzin gyi sa la gshegs so //
NK128(nyo)001:2684: des 'jam dpal bshes gnyen phyi ma'am 'jam dpal bzang
NK128(nyo)001:2685: po dang bdud rtsi 'bebs la rda he na'i g.yu
NK128(nyo)001:2687: rta glang rin po che'i shar bu phul /
NK128(nyo)001:2688: gsang mtshan rdo rje nges pa rtsal te lo drug
NK128(nyo)001:2689: brgyar bzhugs shing rig 'dzin gyi sa la gshegs so
NK128(nyo)001:2690: // des rig 'dzin dge bsnyen legs pa dang d+harma
NK128(nyo)001:2691: b+ho d+hi la dbus 'gyur tshal du gsungs shing gser
NK128(nyo)001:2693: gsang mtshan rdo rje mchog rab rtsal te rig 'dzin gyi sa la gshegs so //
NK128(nyo)001:2694: brgyud pa dngos la dge bsnyen legs pas sangs rgyas gsang bar gsungs par bshad kyang /
NK128(nyo)001:2695: gtad rgya gsang mtshan gyi dbang du byas na /
NK128(nyo)001:2696: des gu ru d+harma r+aa dza la rin chen bde ba'i gnas su gsungs shing /
NK128(nyo)001:2697: rin po che'i bsil mchog phul /
NK128(nyo)001:2698: gsang mtshan rdo rje mi 'gyur rtsal te rig 'dzin gyi sa la gshegs par gsungs /
NK128(nyo)001:2699: brgyud tshul dngos la d+harma r+aa dza 'di chad pa 'dra'o //
NK128(nyo)001:2700: des slob dpon sangs rgyas gsang ba dang a mu
NK128(nyo)001:2701: la ku dza lar gsang ba'i khang thog tu gsungs
NK128(nyo)001:2702: shing / bdud rtsi bsil mngar gzhong pa gang phul /
NK128(nyo)001:2703: gsang mtshan rdo rje gsang rdzogs rtsal te lo sum
NK128(nyo)001:2704: brgyar bzhugs shing rig 'dzin gyi sa la gshegs so
NK128(nyo)001:2705: // slob dpon 'di gsar rnying kun la grags che bas gsar ma'i lo rgyus 'dra yang 'dug mod /
NK128(nyo)001:2706: 'dir rang lugs ltar cung zad brjod na /
NK128(nyo)001:2707: slob dpon sangs rgyas gsang ba'i 'di bde bar gshegs
NK128(nyo)001:2708: pa'i bka' rab 'byams la mkhas shing grub pa brnyes
NK128(nyo)001:2710: gsang sngags kri ya'i gzhung ltar 'phags pa 'jam dpal bsgrub pas /
NK128(nyo)001:2711: sku bzhad pa la sogs te grub pa'i rtags byung
NK128(nyo)001:2712: yang dngos grub len ma shes par the tshom du
NK128(nyo)001:2713: gyur pa'i bar der bdud kyis bar gcod byas nas
NK128(nyo)001:2714: brgyal lo // brgyal sangs te gzigs pas sku yang nag mog gis song /
NK128(nyo)001:2716: me tog kyang kha zum nas 'dug go //
NK128(nyo)001:2717: de slob dpon gyis ha cang thos pa chung ba yang bdud kyi las su rig par bya ste /
NK128(nyo)001:2718: lha bsgrub kyang dngos grub len ma shes pa bdag ltar bu'o //
NK128(nyo)001:2719: zhes gsungs nas rgya gar shar phyogs su gshegs te
NK128(nyo)001:2720: mngon par byang chub pa la sogs pa phyi rgyud
NK128(nyo)001:2721: sde gsum dang / nang bskyed rdzogs gsum la legs par sbyangs shing mkhas par gyur nas /
NK128(nyo)001:2722: rgyal po'i bla mchod mdzad de chos grwa'i pan+di ta
NK128(nyo)001:2723: chen por gyur pas 'khor mang po 'dus pa la
NK128(nyo)001:2724: skyo nas / ha cang thos pa che ba yang bdud kyi las su shes par bya ste /
NK128(nyo)001:2725: rang don med pa la 'jug pa bdag lta bu'o //
NK128(nyo)001:2726: zhes gsungs nas bod kyi yul du byon te gangs
NK128(nyo)001:2727: ti se'i bya rog gdong can du byon nas sgrub
NK128(nyo)001:2728: pa snying por mdzad pas dpal rdo rje sems dpa'i
NK128(nyo)001:2729: zhal gzigs shing mchog gi dngos grub brnyes so //
NK128(nyo)001:2730: dus de tsam na bod du mnga' bdag khri srong lde'u btsan gyis gsan te /
NK128(nyo)001:2731: slob dpon spyan 'dren par sad mi bdun gyi nang nas dbas many+dzu sh+r+ai dang /
NK128(nyo)001:2732: bran ka mu ti ka gnyis rdzangs pa slob dpon
NK128(nyo)001:2733: dang mjal te bsam yas su 'byon par zhus pas
NK128(nyo)001:2734: / slob dpon gyi zhal nas bod srin po gdong
NK128(nyo)001:2735: dmar gdul byar babs mi babs lha la dri yi
NK128(nyo)001:2736: gsungs pas dgongs pa zhig mdzad de /
NK128(nyo)001:2737: gdul byar ma gzigs nas khyod rang rnams 'dir smin
NK128(nyo)001:2738: par bya gsungs mtsho ma pham la thig sna gtad
NK128(nyo)001:2739: pa tsam gyis rdo rje dbyings kyi dkyil 'khor du
NK128(nyo)001:2740: mngon sum snang bar mdzad nas /
NK128(nyo)001:2741: lo ts+aa ba rnams la dbang bskur zhing man ngag gnang /
NK128(nyo)001:2742: gsang sngags kyi rgyud 'grel sgrub thabs mang du mdzad cing bsgyur ro //
NK128(nyo)001:2743: slar rgya gar du byon nas brgya sbyin gyi gshos
NK128(nyo)001:2744: brang khang bu brtsegs pa'i yang thog tu bzhugs te
NK128(nyo)001:2745: mi dang mi ma yin pa'i gdul bya chos kyi
NK128(nyo)001:2746: 'khor lo bskor zhing lo brgya bzhugs /
NK128(nyo)001:2747: spyir 'dzam bu'i gling du lo sum brgya bzhugs te /
NK128(nyo)001:2748: gsang ba sgyu 'phrul lam rnam bkod dang rdo rje
NK128(nyo)001:2749: las rim sogs 'grel pa dang sgrub thabs mang du
NK128(nyo)001:2750: mdzad nas mthar 'khor lnga brgya dang bcas te zag
NK128(nyo)001:2751: med rig 'dzin gyi sa la gshegs so //
NK128(nyo)001:2752: nges slob dpon sh+r+ai seng ha la d+ha he na'i
NK128(nyo)001:2753: 'du khang du gsungs shing gser gyi bum pa phul
NK128(nyo)001:2754: / gsang mtshan rdo rje bzhad pa'i gter ram rdo
NK128(nyo)001:2755: rje bzhad pa rtsal te lo lnga brgyar bzhugs shing
NK128(nyo)001:2756: rig 'dzin gyi sa la gshegs so //
NK128(nyo)001:2757: slob dpon 'di'i lo rgyus cung zad phye na /
NK128(nyo)001:2758: rgya nag po'i grong khyer sho 'khyam nag po zhes
NK128(nyo)001:2759: bya ba na khyim bdag dge ba ldan pa'i yid
NK128(nyo)001:2760: can dang / yum snang ba rab tu mkhyen ldan
NK128(nyo)001:2761: ma bya ba'i sras slob dpon chen po sh+r+ai sing+ha
NK128(nyo)001:2763: de yang 'dir ring brgyud pa'i dbang du byas na
NK128(nyo)001:2764: nye brgyud ltar na slob dpon dga' rab rdo rje
NK128(nyo)001:2765: dang mjal te / de yang tshul gnyis las /
NK128(nyo)001:2766: snyan brgyud rdor zam ltar na dus nam zhig gi
NK128(nyo)001:2767: tshe sh+r+ai sing+ha'i thugs la bskal par bsag sbyangs byas
NK128(nyo)001:2768: nas 'tshang rgya ba ma gtogs 'khor ba las zlog
NK128(nyo)001:2770: chos nyid kyi don skad cig ma gcig gis rtogs
NK128(nyo)001:2771: nas tshe gcig gis sangs rgyas pa'i thabs zhig e
NK128(nyo)001:2772: yod dgongs te / rgya gar dpal sh+r+ai na len
NK128(nyo)001:2773: dra'i gtsug lag khang du byon nas spyan g.yas kyi
NK128(nyo)001:2774: gsang sngags kyi pan+di ta rnams la gzigs /
NK128(nyo)001:2775: g.yon pas mtshan nyid kyi pan+di ta rnams la gzigs shing don de dris pas /
NK128(nyo)001:2776: mtshan nyid kyi pan+di ta rnams cang mi gsung /
NK128(nyo)001:2777: sngags kyi pan chen rnams kyi zhal nas sngon yang
NK128(nyo)001:2778: mi rabs bdun tsam gyi gong du slob dpon 'jam
NK128(nyo)001:2779: dpal bshes gnyen zhes bya ba de skad gsungs nas
NK128(nyo)001:2780: / slob dpon dga' rab rdo rje'i gan du lung bstan pa yin /
NK128(nyo)001:2781: da yang khyod 'di nas lho phyogs su phyin pa na lho gyad kyi yul be ta'i gling /
NK128(nyo)001:2782: shing dra ba gtsug dgu bkod pa'i tshal gnod sbyin
NK128(nyo)001:2783: 'brog gnas kyis dpal yon tan thams cad 'byung ba
NK128(nyo)001:2784: zhes bya ba'i grong khyer na /
NK128(nyo)001:2785: slob dpon 'jam dpal bshes gnyen zhes bya ba ste /
NK128(nyo)001:2786: slob dpon dga' rab rdo rje'i byin brlabs kyis chos
NK128(nyo)001:2787: nyid kyi don rtogs shing dngos grub brnyes nas bzhugs
NK128(nyo)001:2788: yod pas / tshe gcig gi 'tshang rgya ba'i gdams
NK128(nyo)001:2789: ngag khong la yod pas der phyin na legs zhes
NK128(nyo)001:2790: yod pas / lung bstan / 'o na der 'gro
NK128(nyo)001:2791: ba la dkar sla skyid sdug nye ring ji ltar
NK128(nyo)001:2792: yod pas / lung bstan / yod dris pas /
NK128(nyo)001:2793: lam nye na nged rnams kyang 'gro ste lam yang
NK128(nyo)001:2794: shin tu ring zhing zla ba bcu gsum tsam du
NK128(nyo)001:2795: yod pas / lung bstan / yod dris pas /
NK128(nyo)001:2796: 'gro dgos la / lam gyi 'jigs pa ni mkha'
NK128(nyo)001:2797: yod pas / lung bstan / yod dris pas /
NK128(nyo)001:2798: 'gro dgos la / 'gro dang / gnod sbyin ma
NK128(nyo)001:2799: yod pas / lung bstan / yod dris pas /
NK128(nyo)001:2800: 'gro dgos la / 'gro dang / rung ba dang
NK128(nyo)001:2802: gcan gzan ma rungs pa dang phrad de 'ong gsungs pas /
NK128(nyo)001:2803: cung zad the tshom zos te lam de bas nye ba'i thabs yod dam dris pas /
NK128(nyo)001:2804: nye lam ni ri rab ri'i khong gseng zhig la phyin na lam nye ste /
NK128(nyo)001:2805: de na yang sbrul gdug pa can dang mi ma
NK128(nyo)001:2806: yin gyi grong khyer gnas pas shin tu dka' gsungs
NK128(nyo)001:2807: / de dag la bsrung ba'i thabs med dam zhus pas /
NK128(nyo)001:2808: rtsi ma gi ta zhes bya ba lus la byug cing /
NK128(nyo)001:2809: zhun chen gyi mar me khyer nas phyin na sbrul
NK128(nyo)001:2810: dang mi ma yin gyi grong khyer gyi 'jigs pa
NK128(nyo)001:2811: srung / gzhan yang mun khung 'ba' zhig tu 'gro
NK128(nyo)001:2812: dgos pas sgron me dang mar me yang 'khyer dgos
NK128(nyo)001:2813: srung / gsungs so // der sh+r+ai seng has yo
NK128(nyo)001:2814: byad de rnams dka' bas bsgrubs te khyer nas phyin
NK128(nyo)001:2815: srung / gsungs so // pas / sa'i phug gi
NK128(nyo)001:2816: mun khang gi lam la zla ba drug 'gor yang
NK128(nyo)001:2817: gnod pa dang 'jigs pa med par be ta'i gling
NK128(nyo)001:2818: dra ba gtsug dgu'i dpal yon tan 'byung ba'i grong
NK128(nyo)001:2820: der slob dpon 'jam dpal bshes gnyen bya ba gang na bzhugs dris pas /
NK128(nyo)001:2822: slob dpon 'jam dpal bshes gnyen bya ba zhig nged
NK128(nyo)001:2823: kyi grong na yod zer te cha lugs ji ltar
NK128(nyo)001:2824: yod cha med pas ngo mi shes zer ro //
NK128(nyo)001:2825: kun la dris pas kyang de skad zer ro //
NK128(nyo)001:2826: der zla ba bdun gyi bar du phyogs thams cad du btsal bas kyang ma rnyed /
NK128(nyo)001:2827: dus nam zhig gi tshe chu mig gi kha zhig tu bzhugs pas /
NK128(nyo)001:2828: chu len ma rgan mo zhig byung ba la dris
NK128(nyo)001:2829: pas gtam mi zer bar 'gro bar rtsol pa na
NK128(nyo)001:2830: / slob dpon yang rdzu 'phrul dang ldan pa zhig
NK128(nyo)001:2831: pas chu bum pa la 'byar bcug pas mos ma
NK128(nyo)001:2832: / thegs par / mo na re tsit+ta a b+hi
NK128(nyo)001:2833: pra se sa zer bas brang kha phye nas snying
NK128(nyo)001:2834: gi nang nas dpal yang dag lha dgu'i dkyil 'khor
NK128(nyo)001:2835: / thegs par / bstan / lce brkyang bas gdong
NK128(nyo)001:2836: mer 'bar te 'bar ba'i gdong can gyi rtags kyang
NK128(nyo)001:2837: / thegs par / bstan / bstan no // de
NK128(nyo)001:2838: nas slob dpon gyis mo la 'jam dpal bshes gnyen
NK128(nyo)001:2839: ngo shes sam zhes bskyar nas dris pas /
NK128(nyo)001:2842: nga ma gtogs gzhan sus kyang mi shes zer ro //
NK128(nyo)001:2843: des nas brang kha bsdus bum pa'i chu khur te
NK128(nyo)001:2844: rang gnas su bskyal mos grogs byas te phyin pas
NK128(nyo)001:2845: btsun pa sham thabs thod du bcings pa /
NK128(nyo)001:2846: gnya' thong zung zhig phrag la bzed /
NK128(nyo)001:2847: rmon thong zung zhig mdun du bcug nas zhing rmod pa dang phrod /
NK128(nyo)001:2849: de la slob dpon sh+r+ai sing+ha yid ma ches par /
NK128(nyo)001:2850: slob dpon 'jam dpal bshes gnyen ni yang na pan+di
NK128(nyo)001:2851: ta mkhas pa'i cha byad dam yang na rnal 'byor
NK128(nyo)001:2852: ku s+aa la'i cha byad du yong thang ba la
NK128(nyo)001:2853: / 'di khyim btsun zhig tu 'dug pas ma yin nam snyam nas /
NK128(nyo)001:2854: bdag la bza' zhig slong dang byas pas /
NK128(nyo)001:2855: bza' 'di na ci yod grong khyer ya gin nga'i chung ma yod de la slong zer ro //
NK128(nyo)001:2856: des nas grong khyer du phyin nas jo mo la bza' slongs byas pas /
NK128(nyo)001:2857: nga la dpag med zer nas tshong dus nas bye'u mchil pa bdun nyos nas byung ste /
NK128(nyo)001:2858: spu rnams gtogs nang rol rnams blug nas btsos te 'bras chan dang bcas drangs pa la /
NK128(nyo)001:2860: nged dge slong yin pas sha zar mi rung zhing
NK128(nyo)001:2861: khyad par bsngosa nas bsad pa 'di'i sha bzar mi
NK128(nyo)001:2862: rung byas pas / jo mo na re /
NK128(nyo)001:2863: rjes su yi rang ngo gsungs nas /
NK128(nyo)001:2864: bye'u sha bubs bdun po lag mthil du bzhag nas
NK128(nyo)001:2865: phu btab pas nam mkha' la ci rir gyis 'phur
NK128(nyo)001:2866: song ba dang / sh+r+ai sing+ha'i thugs la 'di la
NK128(nyo)001:2867: yang rdzu 'phrul 'di ltar 'dug pas khyim btsun de
NK128(nyo)001:2868: slob dpon yin nam snyam nas da dung brtag dgos
NK128(nyo)001:2869: song ba dang / bsam te / do nub gnas g.yar byas pas 'dug gsungs nas bzhugs pas /
NK128(nyo)001:2870: der khyim btsun gyi tshul can slob dpon de byon nas /
NK128(nyo)001:2872: jo mos bza' byin kyang gsol ma song zhus pas /
NK128(nyo)001:2873: slob dpon gyi zhal nas rang stang bzang bzang gsungs so //
NK128(nyo)001:2874: de nas nang par rdo rje sems dpa' sgyu 'phrul dra ba kha ton du bton pas /
NK128(nyo)001:2875: slob dpon gyis dang por ma bzhengs par gsan /
NK128(nyo)001:2876: de nas yar bzhengs te gsan /
NK128(nyo)001:2877: rdzogs pa dang don la lta ci smos tshig la
NK128(nyo)001:2878: yang rmong gsungs slob dpon 'jam dpal bshes gnyen yin
NK128(nyo)001:2879: nam dgongs so // yang jo mos tshogs 'dus nas
NK128(nyo)001:2880: bud med kyi lag g.yon gdu bu lnga sil le
NK128(nyo)001:2881: ba zhig nyos nas byung ste /
NK128(nyo)001:2884: nged dge slong sha za mi rung zhing /
NK128(nyo)001:2885: de'i nang nas kyang ma'i sha dang bud med kyi sha 'di mi zhu byas pas /
NK128(nyo)001:2886: slob dpon des bud med kyi lag pa de phyag tu bzhag ste se gol zhig gtogs pas /
NK128(nyo)001:2887: lag pa de nam mkha' la 'od phung nge song ngo //
NK128(nyo)001:2888: de nas slob dpon 'jam dpal bshes gnyen yin pa yid ches te /
NK128(nyo)001:2891: bskor ba lan gsum byas te /
NK128(nyo)001:2892: khyed kyi rtogs pa bdag la bskyed par zhu 'tshal byas pas cang mi gsungs /
NK128(nyo)001:2893: de ltar lan gsum byas pas kyang ma gsung ngo //
NK128(nyo)001:2894: de nas sh+r+ai seng ha thugs mug nas /
NK128(nyo)001:2895: slob dpon gyi gdams ngag ma gnang bar 'dug 'gro dgos snyam yong tsa na /
NK128(nyo)001:2896: slob dpon gyi zhal nas sh+r+ai seng ha 'dir shog dang /
NK128(nyo)001:2898: drung du phyin pas slob dpon ljan ljin dang 'bags
NK128(nyo)001:2899: btsog mi gtsang ba zhig gi gseb na gzims 'dug
NK128(nyo)001:2900: pas / 'dir phyogs shig bya ba yin nam snyams
NK128(nyo)001:2901: nas phyags pas yang sngar bzhin gang nas de ltar
NK128(nyo)001:2902: lan bco brgyad kyi bar du phyags pas shin tu
NK128(nyo)001:2904: slob dpon gyi dbu sngas na shing tog mdog legs shing dri zhim pa zhig bzhag 'dug pa /
NK128(nyo)001:2905: zo bya ba yin nam snyam ste zos pas ro
NK128(nyo)001:2906: mchog brgyad dang ldan pa shin tu dri zhim pa
NK128(nyo)001:2907: zhig 'dug / zos zin pa dang de nad du
NK128(nyo)001:2908: gyur nas skyug cing 'gyel nas shi la thug ste
NK128(nyo)001:2909: zhig 'dug / bsam pa / nga ni da shi na rung snyams pa lan bdun byung ste /
NK128(nyo)001:2910: slob dpon 'di dang lor zhing rmo ba'i tshe brda
NK128(nyo)001:2911: zhig yin 'dug pa la yang ngas ma go bas
NK128(nyo)001:2912: shi na rung / bye'u'i sha drangs dus kyang brda ma go bas shi na rung /
NK128(nyo)001:2913: kha ton byas pa'i dus kyang brda ma go bas shi na rung /
NK128(nyo)001:2914: bud med kyi lag pa drangs dus kyang brda ma go bas shi na rung /
NK128(nyo)001:2915: man+dala dang phyag bskor byas gsol ba btab dus ci
NK128(nyo)001:2916: yang mi gsung ba'i brda ma go bas shi rung
NK128(nyo)001:2917: / 'gro snyams pa la shog gsungs te phyin pas
NK128(nyo)001:2918: phyag dar byas dus kyang brda ma go bas shi
NK128(nyo)001:2919: / na rung / shing tog zos pa de yang
NK128(nyo)001:2920: brdar 'dug ste ma go bas shi na rung ste
NK128(nyo)001:2921: snyams pa bdun shar ba dang skyug 'phro chad /
NK128(nyo)001:2922: 'gyel ba langs te gzigs pas slob dpon bzhengs nas 'dug ste slob dpon gyi zhal nas /
NK128(nyo)001:2923: khyod ci 'dod pa yin gsungs pas zhus pa /
NK128(nyo)001:2924: bdag ni skad cig mas rtogs pa tshe gcig gis 'tshang rgya ba'i thabs shig zhu zhus pas /
NK128(nyo)001:2925: khyod kyis da dung ma go'am gsungs pas ma go lags zhus pas /
NK128(nyo)001:2926: ngas dang po nas bstan te /
NK128(nyo)001:2927: khyod rang gi ma go bar 'dug pa /
NK128(nyo)001:2928: zhing rmo ba ni thabs shes rab kyi don bstan pa yin no //
NK128(nyo)001:2929: bye'u mchil pa'am ka lan ta ka ni skad cig
NK128(nyo)001:2930: tu smra bas de'i sha drangs pa ni tshogs drug
NK128(nyo)001:2931: chos nyid kyi brda gcig tu bstan pa yin no
NK128(nyo)001:2932: // sgyu 'phrul dra ba 'don pa'i tshe chos thams cad brjod 'das su bstan pa yiin no //
NK128(nyo)001:2933: bud med kyi lag pa drangs pa ni lag g.yon
NK128(nyo)001:2934: pa shes rab kyi rang bzhin ye shes lnga dang
NK128(nyo)001:2935: ldan par bstan pa yin no //
NK128(nyo)001:2936: man+dala phyag bskor gsol ba btab dus ci yang ma
NK128(nyo)001:2937: smras pa de chos thams cad smra bsam brjod med
NK128(nyo)001:2939: de khyod kyis ma rtogs te 'gro bsam pa'i tshe
NK128(nyo)001:2940: khyod la khams bco brgyad kyi sgribs pa sbyang ba'i
NK128(nyo)001:2941: phyir lan bco brgyad 'phyag tu bcug pa yin te
NK128(nyo)001:2942: / khyod la gzung 'dzin gyi sgrib pa zab cing
NK128(nyo)001:2943: phra ba zhig 'dug nas shing tog zar bcug pa
NK128(nyo)001:2944: / yin te / khyod shing tog de'i kha dog
NK128(nyo)001:2945: dang dri la chags pa ni phyi gzung ba'i yul
NK128(nyo)001:2947: zos pas ro mchog zhim pa la chags pa nang 'dzin pa'i sems la chags pa yin /
NK128(nyo)001:2948: khyod na ba de gzung 'dzin gnyis kyi sgrib pas na ba yin /
NK128(nyo)001:2949: de ltar na ba'i tshe shi na rung bdun dran
NK128(nyo)001:2950: pas sgrib pa dag nas gsos pa yin no gsungs
NK128(nyo)001:2951: nas / skye 'gag gnyis med kyi don du a ha ho'i zhes brda bstan pas /
NK128(nyo)001:2952: chos nyid kyi rang sgra de 'u re ba zhag bdun du byung ba'i nyams shar /
NK128(nyo)001:2953: de las sad tsam nas slob dpon yang de gar
NK128(nyo)001:2954: bzhugs nas 'dug ste don te mi brjed pa'i brdar
NK128(nyo)001:2955: / a ban rda ra zhes brda bstan nas /
NK128(nyo)001:2956: bod skad du khyod rang nam mkha'i dkyil du ltos dang bya bar go nas /
NK128(nyo)001:2958: sprin dang khu rlangs yal ba'i skabs der /
NK128(nyo)001:2959: yar nam mkha' la ma bltas mar sa la ma bltas /
NK128(nyo)001:2960: thad ka'i nam mkha'i dkyil du bltas pas /
NK128(nyo)001:2961: nam mkha' de ru rkyen ngo bo ngos bzung mtha' bral ltar /
NK128(nyo)001:2962: sems nyid dngos po'i gnas lugs kyang de bzhin du rtogs nas /
NK128(nyo)001:2963: slob dpon sh+r+ai sing+hasa mchog gi dngos grub de nyid
NK128(nyo)001:2964: du thob ste thun mong gi dngos grub zhor la
NK128(nyo)001:2965: shar / las dang las kyi rnam smin dag go //
NK128(nyo)001:2966: de nas sh+r+ai sing+ha nam mkha' la bya 'phur ba bzhin grong khyer de nas 'phur te /
NK128(nyo)001:2967: sh+r+ai na len dra'i gtsug lag khang du gshegs shing /
NK128(nyo)001:2968: mu stegs tshar gcod pa'i phyir rdo rje gdan gyi byang sgo bsrungs ba la gshegs zhes grag go //
NK128(nyo)001:2969: gsang ba snying thig gi lo rgyus su /
NK128(nyo)001:2970: slob dpon gnyis mjal tshul 'di ltar 'byung ste /
NK128(nyo)001:2971: slob dpon sh+r+ai sing ha rgya nag gi grong khyer
NK128(nyo)001:2972: sho khyam nag po nub phyogs kyi grong khyer gser
NK128(nyo)001:2973: gling zhes bya bar 'gro ba'i bar gyi thang stong
NK128(nyo)001:2974: zhig gi nam mkha' las 'phags pa spyan ras gzigs
NK128(nyo)001:2975: kyis lung bstan pa la brten nas /
NK128(nyo)001:2976: sa la khru gang gis ma reg par byon te
NK128(nyo)001:2977: zhag dgu nas dur khrod so sa gling du phyin
NK128(nyo)001:2978: slob dpon 'jam dpal bshes gnyen dang mjal te phyag
NK128(nyo)001:2980: bdag rjes su bzung bar zhu zhes pas /
NK128(nyo)001:2981: gdams pa rnams bstan cing des lung bstan te dur
NK128(nyo)001:2982: khrod de nyid kyi nam mkha' la 'od phung du
NK128(nyo)001:2983: gshegs so // der sh+r+ai seng has smre sngags bton
NK128(nyo)001:2984: nas 'das rjes sgom nyams drug pa zhes bya ba
NK128(nyo)001:2985: rin po che'i ga'u nas phyung ste babs /
NK128(nyo)001:2986: rdo rje gdan gyi pha bong nas 'jam dpal bshes
NK128(nyo)001:2987: gnyen gyis sbas pa'i man ngag rdzogs pa chen po'i
NK128(nyo)001:2988: skor rnams rgya nag po'i byang chub 'byung ba'i shing
NK128(nyo)001:2990: phyi nang gsang ba bla med kyi skor dang bzhir phye nas /
NK128(nyo)001:2991: phyi nang gsang gsum rgya nag bkra shis khri sgo'i lha khang gi ka bar sbas /
NK128(nyo)001:2992: bla na med pa'i skor bcangs pa mkha' 'gro'i lung
NK128(nyo)001:2993: bzhin de nyid du sbas te mi snang ba'i rgyas
NK128(nyo)001:2994: btab nas dur khrod chen po bsil byin du spyod
NK128(nyo)001:2995: pa la gshegs te bzhugs pa'i tshe /
NK128(nyo)001:2996: rgya gar gyi slob dpon bi ma la mi tra dang /
NK128(nyo)001:2997: dz+nya na su tra la rdo rje sems dpas lung
NK128(nyo)001:2998: bstan te sh+r+ai seng ha dang mjal zhing rjes su
NK128(nyo)001:2999: bzung ste slob dpon chen po sh+r+ai seng ha de
NK128(nyo)001:3000: nyid 'od phung chen por gshegs so //
NK128(nyo)001:3002: ngo mtshar grub thob kyi rnam par thar pa gnyis ka mi 'gal bar bzung zhig /
NK128(nyo)001:3003: de ltar slob dpon sh+r+ai seng+ha des bi ma la /
NK128(nyo)001:3004: des dge slong ma kun dga' mo la gsungs par bshad /
NK128(nyo)001:3005: 'dir dkyus su sh+r+ai seng has dge slong ma kun dga' mor gsungs pa yin te /
NK128(nyo)001:3006: de yang rda he na'i kha rag yul du gsungs shing /
NK128(nyo)001:3007: u b+hi'i mkhar dang gser srang drug phul /
NK128(nyo)001:3008: gsang mtshan rdo rje shes rab rtsal te lo nyis
NK128(nyo)001:3009: brgyar bzhugs te rig 'dzin gyi sa la gshegs so
NK128(nyo)001:3010: // des slob dpon bi ma la mi trar rnam
NK128(nyo)001:3011: dag chos kyi sprin du gsungs shing gser ka gzhu
NK128(nyo)001:3012: // tsam phul / gsang mtshan rdo rje gro bo
NK128(nyo)001:3013: lod rtsal te lo sum brgyar bzhugs shing rig 'dzin
NK128(nyo)001:3015: deng sang yang lhag med grub ste rgya nag ri bo rtse lngar bzhugs zhes kyang grags so //
NK128(nyo)001:3016: slob dpon 'di'i rnam thar zur tsam brjod na /
NK128(nyo)001:3017: rgya gar nub phyogs glang po'i sgang zhes bya ba'i
NK128(nyo)001:3018: grong khyer na khyim bdag bde ldan 'khor lo dang
NK128(nyo)001:3019: yum gsal rig ma zhes bya ba'i sras su 'khrungs
NK128(nyo)001:3020: / phyi nang gi grub pa'i mtha' thams cad la
NK128(nyo)001:3021: mkhas par sbyangs shing phul du byung ba'i pan+di ta
NK128(nyo)001:3022: chen por gyur te mtshan pan+di ta chen po bi
NK128(nyo)001:3023: ma la mi tra zhes kun tu grags par gyur
NK128(nyo)001:3024: / to // de ltar pan chen bi ma la
NK128(nyo)001:3025: de nyid pan chen lnga brgya'i gtsug rgyan du gyur
NK128(nyo)001:3026: nas rdo rje gdan na bzhugs pa'i tshe /
NK128(nyo)001:3027: nub phyogs su rgyang grags kyi sa 'dam bu'i tshal
NK128(nyo)001:3028: 'thug po me tog gis brgyan par skyo sangs la
NK128(nyo)001:3029: byon dus / rdo rje sems dpas lung bstan pa /
NK128(nyo)001:3030: kye rigs kyi bu skye ba lnga brgyar pan+di ta'i lus blangs kyang 'bras bu ma thob pas /
NK128(nyo)001:3031: tshe gcig gis grol bar 'dod na rgya nag gi /
NK128(nyo)001:3032: dur khrod bsil sbyin du song zhig ces thos ma thag tu bi ma la byon pas /
NK128(nyo)001:3033: slob dpon sh+r+ai seng ha dang mjal nas rdzogs pa
NK128(nyo)001:3034: chen po phyi nang gsang ba'i skor rnams rdzogs par
NK128(nyo)001:3035: gnang ste / rgya gar dur khrod tha chung du spyod pa la gshegs so //
NK128(nyo)001:3036: skabs der slob dpon dz+ny+aa na su tras sh+r+ai seng
NK128(nyo)001:3037: ha'i drung du phyin nas yang gsang bla na med
NK128(nyo)001:3038: pa'i skor rnams thob pa'i tshe bi ma lar mkha'
NK128(nyo)001:3039: 'gro ma dpal gyi blo gros kyis lung bstan pa
NK128(nyo)001:3040: / kye skal ldan sngar bas zab pa'i gdams pa
NK128(nyo)001:3041: bzhed na dur khrod chen po b+ha sing du song
NK128(nyo)001:3042: zhig ces thos ma thag tu phyin pas dz+nya na
NK128(nyo)001:3044: rjes su bzung bar zhu zhus pas gdams pa thams
NK128(nyo)001:3045: cad rdzogs par gnang ste 'od skur gshegs pa la
NK128(nyo)001:3046: smre sngags bton pas rin po che'i ga'u nas 'das
NK128(nyo)001:3047: rjes babs so // de nas bi ma la nyid
NK128(nyo)001:3048: rgya gar shar phyogs ka ma ru ba'i rgyal po
NK128(nyo)001:3049: seng ge bzang po'i mchod gnas su nyin par bzhugs
NK128(nyo)001:3050: rjes babs so // shing / mtshan mo dur khrod du mkha' 'gro ma la chos bstan pa las /
NK128(nyo)001:3051: sprul pa zhig rgya gar nub phyogs su b+hi d+ya'i
NK128(nyo)001:3052: grong khyer du rgyal po d+harma pha la'i mchod gnas
NK128(nyo)001:3053: mdzad cing / mtshan mo de las 'das pa'i dpag
NK128(nyo)001:3054: tshad lnga brgya 'das pa'i byang phyogs na dur khrod
NK128(nyo)001:3055: rab tu snang byed ces bya bar mkha' 'gro ma
NK128(nyo)001:3056: rnams la mchod gnas grong khyer ser skyar rgyal po
NK128(nyo)001:3057: in tra b+hu ti chung ba'i mchod gnas kyang mdzad
NK128(nyo)001:3058: mdzad cing / do // skabs der bod chos skyong ba'i rgyal po khri srong lde'u btsan gyis /
NK128(nyo)001:3059: dpal bsam yas bzhengs shing bod du sangs rgyas kyi
NK128(nyo)001:3060: bstan pa dar bar mdzad pa'i dus thang yig lta
NK128(nyo)001:3061: na bee ro'i lung bstan dang /
NK128(nyo)001:3062: gzhan du rgyal po'i mchod gnas nyang ting 'dzin bzang
NK128(nyo)001:3063: po zhes bya ba sha'i spyan gyis gling bzhi dus
NK128(nyo)001:3064: gcig tu gzigs pa des 'gros pa ltar /
NK128(nyo)001:3065: rgyal pos ska cog rma gsum la gser phye dang
NK128(nyo)001:3066: gser gyi pa tra mang po bskur te bardzangasa pa
NK128(nyo)001:3067: rgya gar grong khyer ser skya sleb ste rgyal po
NK128(nyo)001:3068: la skyes phul zhing bi ma la rdzangs bar zhus
NK128(nyo)001:3069: par pan chen lnga brgya'i dbus nas bi ma la
NK128(nyo)001:3070: bzhengs te / ga ga pa re zhes gsungs pa dang /
NK128(nyo)001:3071: thang yig tu ma nu du ru kro he zhes gsungs par bzhed /
NK128(nyo)001:3072: sgra de la lo ts+aa ba gsum por go lugs mi 'dra ba re byung ste /
NK128(nyo)001:3073: ska ba dpal brtsegs kyi go lugs la /
NK128(nyo)001:3074: gru bo dag la brten pa'i mi /
NK128(nyo)001:3075: mnyan pa'i skya bas rtsol phod na mi yi rgya mtsho'i pha rol sgrol /
NK128(nyo)001:3076: zhes dang cog ro klu'i rgyal mtshan gyis /
NK128(nyo)001:3077: gzhu mo dag la brten pa'i mda' //
NK128(nyo)001:3078: skyes bu'i mtheb mos rtsol phod na //
NK128(nyo)001:3079: mda' yis 'ben la skyol bar nus //
NK128(nyo)001:3082: rgyal po khyod kyis gtong phod na //
NK128(nyo)001:3083: lus kyi bum pa gang 'dril bar //
NK128(nyo)001:3084: sems kyi chu bo de ru 'bo //
NK128(nyo)001:3086: tshigs bcad rjes ma 'di thang yig tu /
NK128(nyo)001:3087: yon tan dag la brten pa'i mi //
NK128(nyo)001:3088: rang yul min pa'i sa phyogs su //
NK128(nyo)001:3089: lus kyi bum pa sogs sngar ltar gsungs /
NK128(nyo)001:3090: de nas bod du byon pas rgya gar gyi ltas
NK128(nyo)001:3091: mkhan rnams la nyi ma bod du nub pa dang
NK128(nyo)001:3092: / rtsi shing nags tshal thams cad bod du mgo dud pa sogs byung ngo //
NK128(nyo)001:3093: bod du byon pa'i lo rgyus gzhan thang yig tu blta la /
NK128(nyo)001:3094: 'dir rdzogs chen snying thig gi lugs su byas nas /
NK128(nyo)001:3095: de ltar bi ma la bod du byon nas mnga'
NK128(nyo)001:3096: bdag rje 'bangs kyis bsus te bsam yas su phyag
NK128(nyo)001:3097: phebs / rin po che seng ge'i khri sum brtsegs la bzhugs dus /
NK128(nyo)001:3099: thams cad kyi mthong bar nam mkhar rdo rje dbyings
NK128(nyo)001:3100: kyi dkyil 'khor bstan pa la thams cad ngo mtshar
NK128(nyo)001:3102: chos bsgyur zhing gsungs bar zhus pas rdo rje sems
NK128(nyo)001:3103: dpa' sgyu 'phrul dra ba la sogs te gsang sngags
NK128(nyo)001:3104: phyi nang mtshan nyid kyi theg pa dang bcas mang
NK128(nyo)001:3106: mtshan mo dbu rtse bar khang du gsang ba mchog gi man ngag rnams rgyal po yab sras /
NK128(nyo)001:3108: ska cog ste lnga la gsungs /
NK128(nyo)001:3109: kun mkhyen klong chen zhabs rma rin chen mchog de dus 'das par bzhed kyang /
NK128(nyo)001:3110: sgyu 'phrul gsang ba'i snying po'i khog dbub sogs spyi ltar na sgyu 'phrul sde brgyad /
NK128(nyo)001:3111: bshad rgyud sde bzhi sogs rma rin chen mchog kho nas bsgyur bar bzhed cing /
NK128(nyo)001:3112: se ston rin chen rgyal mtshan gyis mdzad pa'i gsang snying bla brgyud gsol 'debs kyi 'grel par /
NK128(nyo)001:3113: rma rin chen mchog gis bi ma la'i lo ts+aa
NK128(nyo)001:3114: mdzad de sgyu 'phrul sde brgyad bshad rgyud sde bzhi
NK128(nyo)001:3115: bcas pa nos shing bsgyur te spel /
NK128(nyo)001:3116: rgyud la bshad thabs bcu ba /
NK128(nyo)001:3117: man ngag shes rab spyan 'byed kyi 'grel pa la sogs pa yang mdzad ces gsungs pas na /
NK128(nyo)001:3118: ma h+aa yo ga'i lo ts+aa phal cher rma rin chen mchog yin par 'dod /
NK128(nyo)001:3119: de nas bi ma las bsam yas su yun ring por bzhugs nas dam chos mang du bsgyur /
NK128(nyo)001:3120: lo chen bee ro sogs rjes su bzung /
NK128(nyo)001:3121: rdzogs chen man ngag gi skor cig tu bsdus pa'i
NK128(nyo)001:3122: zab mo'i po ti bzhi mchims phu'i brag dmar dge
NK128(nyo)001:3123: gong du sbas te rgya nag ri bo rtse lngar
NK128(nyo)001:3124: gshegs shing bskal pa ma zhig gi bar du bzhugs
NK128(nyo)001:3125: la / mi lo brgya re nas sprul pa re yang 'byon zhes grags so //
NK128(nyo)001:3126: mdo dbang gtad rgya'i dkyus la /
NK128(nyo)001:3127: de ltar slob dpon bi ma las /
NK128(nyo)001:3128: lo ts+aa ba bee ro tsa na dang gtsang sngon
NK128(nyo)001:3129: legs grub la rda he na'i gtsug lag khang du
NK128(nyo)001:3130: gsungs shing / gser phye ba men gyi rwa do dang gser gyi pa tra brgya phul /
NK128(nyo)001:3131: gsang mtshan rdo rje khyung gshog rtsal te dgung lo
NK128(nyo)001:3132: brgyad cur bzhugs shing rig 'dzin gyi sa la gshegs
NK128(nyo)001:3133: so // des rgyal po g.yu sgra snying po dang
NK128(nyo)001:3134: rgyal mo gru gnyis la rgyal mo tsha ba rong
NK128(nyo)001:3135: gi brag lha mgon por gsungs shing /
NK128(nyo)001:3136: rang gi rgyal srid phul gsang mtshan rdo rje bde
NK128(nyo)001:3137: 'byams rtsal te rig 'dzin gyi sa la gshegs so
NK128(nyo)001:3138: // lo chen bee ro tsa na'i rnam thar brjod
NK128(nyo)001:3139: pa'i shugs las g.yu sgra snying po'i rnam thar yang
NK128(nyo)001:3141: des na lo ts+aa ba chen po bee ro'i rnam thar zur tsam brjod pa'i dbang du bgyis na /
NK128(nyo)001:3143: slob dpon chen po pad+mas lung bstan tshul 'di ltar gsungs te /
NK128(nyo)001:3144: gtsang gi snye mo bye mkhar bya ba yi //
NK128(nyo)001:3145: gnas gzhi zhig gi brang khang mig dgu na //
NK128(nyo)001:3146: pha ming spa gor he 'dod bya ba la //
NK128(nyo)001:3147: ma ming bran ka bza' sgron skyid kyi bu //
NK128(nyo)001:3148: gan jag thang ta zhes pa lo brgyad pa //
NK128(nyo)001:3149: zhes gsungs pa dang mthun par snyan brgyud rdor zam las kyang 'byung zhing /
NK128(nyo)001:3150: snye mo nas bkug ste bsam yas su byon nas
NK128(nyo)001:3151: sgra bslabs tshul gyi bar thang yig dang 'dra bas
NK128(nyo)001:3152: grags che ba'i phyir ma bkod la /
NK128(nyo)001:3153: 'dir 'dra 'bag ltar na dka' ba bcu drug spyad
NK128(nyo)001:3154: tshul gyi dbang du byas te cung zad bshad na
NK128(nyo)001:3155: / yum nyang chab dang gtsang chab 'dzom pa'i 'gram
NK128(nyo)001:3156: du yab spa gor gan jag rdo rje rgyal po
NK128(nyo)001:3157: / dang / yum sgron gza' sgron skyid kyi bu gan jag thang ta zhes bya bar 'khrungs shing /
NK128(nyo)001:3158: 'khrungs yul yang gtsang bsam grub rtse'i chu shar kha
NK128(nyo)001:3159: zangs kar zer ba'i grong yod pa de nyid dang
NK128(nyo)001:3160: nye ba'i thad du 'khrungs pa'i rgyu mtshan bee ro
NK128(nyo)001:3161: byis pa'i dus kyi zhabs rjes kyang rdo la gsal
NK128(nyo)001:3162: ba yod do zhes mkhas pa rnams gsungs so //
NK128(nyo)001:3163: thang yig nas gsungs pa'i spa gor he 'dod a
NK128(nyo)001:3164: khu yin pas yab 'das rjes a khus bskyangs te
NK128(nyo)001:3165: snye mo bye mkhar du yul 'phos sam yang zer
NK128(nyo)001:3166: / gang ltar yang yul der 'khrungs nas dgung lo
NK128(nyo)001:3167: brgyad lon pa'i skabs su nag mo ri'ang brag po
NK128(nyo)001:3168: che gnyis su nyi zer la zhon nas phar 'gro
NK128(nyo)001:3170: sgra bsgyur sum brgya drug cu ma bslabs par shes
NK128(nyo)001:3171: pa sogs sprul sku'i rtags ngo mtshar can ston par
NK128(nyo)001:3172: mdzad de lo brgyad par mnga' bdag khri srong lde'u
NK128(nyo)001:3173: btsan gyi spyan sngar bos te /
NK128(nyo)001:3174: lo dgu nas phyi nang gi blon po lo gsum byas /
NK128(nyo)001:3175: bcu gnyis nas rje'i gsol ka ba lo gsum byas /
NK128(nyo)001:3178: mkhan slob gnyis kyi drung du bzhugs su bcug /
NK128(nyo)001:3179: lo bdun bar du dkar gsum mngar gsum byin //
NK128(nyo)001:3180: shes rab bskyed thabs blo 'phel gzungs bsgrub bcug /
NK128(nyo)001:3181: de nas lo ts+aa sgra rnams mkhas par bslabs //
NK128(nyo)001:3182: zhes pa dgung lo brgyad nas bco lnga'i bar gyis gung 'grig pas mi 'gal /
NK128(nyo)001:3184: khrus khang gling du mkhan po gdan drangs nas //
NK128(nyo)001:3186: mkhas pa bee ro ts+aa na rab tu byung //
NK128(nyo)001:3188: sad mi bdun nang tshan mkhan po las rab tu
NK128(nyo)001:3189: byung ba'i dge slong rnam par dag pa yin no
NK128(nyo)001:3190: // der rgyal pos blon 'bangs mkhas btsun thams cad bsags te /
NK128(nyo)001:3191: rgyu 'bras kyi chos bod du rdzogs kyang rgyu 'bras
NK128(nyo)001:3192: las 'das pa'i chos shig rgya gar na yod 'dug
NK128(nyo)001:3193: pas 'tshol du gtong dgos zhes 'gros par gan jag
NK128(nyo)001:3194: thang ta dang gtsang sngon legs grub gnyis tshogs pa'i
NK128(nyo)001:3196: rjes bka' stsol zhig bdag 'gro'i zhes khas blangs so //
NK128(nyo)001:3197: de yang pha ma yul zhing gnyen 'dun thams cad spangs te matha'i yul skad rigs mi mthun pa /
NK128(nyo)001:3198: gcan 'phrang pa la sogs pa 'jigs pa shin tu
NK128(nyo)001:3199: che bas khas len par dka' bas na dka' ba
NK128(nyo)001:3201: der mnga' bdag gi bee ro dang legs grub gnyis blo dang ldan pas don 'grub par mkhyen nas /
NK128(nyo)001:3202: khye'u gnyis la gser gyi pa tra zung 'ga' ni 'go la sbas /
NK128(nyo)001:3203: snyan brgyud rdor zam du gser gyi pa tra thod
NK128(nyo)001:3204: pa'i dbyibs su byas te mgo la g.yogs pa dang
NK128(nyo)001:3205: / mthar rgya gar du sh+r+ai seng ha la phul
NK128(nyo)001:3206: tshul sogs bshad pas gser gyi pa tra mgo la
NK128(nyo)001:3207: sbas zer ba de yin par snang /
NK128(nyo)001:3208: gser gyi pa tra dang thur ma dang lu gu rgyud 'ga' ni dug po'i gseb tu sbas /
NK128(nyo)001:3209: gser phye ba man gyi rwa do dang gser thums rta mtsha' lu bya gdong la bkal /
NK128(nyo)001:3210: lus chas mi 'dra ba dang gcan gzan gyi sder
NK128(nyo)001:3211: mo sogs dgos cha thams cad rta la bkal te
NK128(nyo)001:3213: de skabs a khu pa gor he 'dod kyis mdun
NK128(nyo)001:3214: ma chen po bsags nas rgyal po spyan drangs te
NK128(nyo)001:3215: gan jag thang ta rgya gar du mi 'gro bar
NK128(nyo)001:3217: gan jag rang la rgyu mtshan du ma'i sgo nas
NK128(nyo)001:3218: bsnyad kyang ngo mtshar ba'i mgur gsungs te a khu
NK128(nyo)001:3219: kho thag chod cing yid ches nas bu rang gang
NK128(nyo)001:3221: de ltar dgung lo bco lnga stag lo dpyid zla
NK128(nyo)001:3222: ra ba'i lo gsar gyi tshes gsum la grogs po
NK128(nyo)001:3223: legs grub rta dang bcas lam bgrod dka' ba shul
NK128(nyo)001:3224: thag ring por lam mkhan kyang med par 'gro ba
NK128(nyo)001:3225: shin tu dka' bas na 'gro bar chas pa dka'
NK128(nyo)001:3227: de nas chas pa'i nub rta mgrin gling du gzims
NK128(nyo)001:3228: pa'i nub ya mtshan can gyi ltas bzhi byung ba
NK128(nyo)001:3229: grogs po legs grub la rmi lam mgur du bzlas
NK128(nyo)001:3230: pa / legs grub rigs pa dang ldan pas rmi
NK128(nyo)001:3231: lam gyi brda 'grel mgur lan gsum gsungs te myur
NK128(nyo)001:3233: de nas rgya gar du byon pa'i lam /
NK128(nyo)001:3234: dkar la'i thog tu kha ba chen po byung nas
NK128(nyo)001:3235: zhag gsum gzims pas tho reng bee ro ngo mtshar
NK128(nyo)001:3236: can gyi ltas bee ro rang gi sku tshe de'i
NK128(nyo)001:3237: rnam thar tshang bar byung ste legs grub la mgur
NK128(nyo)001:3238: du gsungs pa / yang dag don la dgongs pa'i grogs po khyod //
NK128(nyo)001:3239: bzhengs shig bzhengs shig grogs po yar bzhengs dang //
NK128(nyo)001:3240: thum zhig log pa'i rmi lam 'di ltar rmis //
NK128(nyo)001:3241: nub nas bod du nyi zla gnyis shar bas //
NK128(nyo)001:3242: zla ba nam mkha'i dkyil du nub pa rmis //
NK128(nyo)001:3243: nyi ma has po ri la gsal byas nas //
NK128(nyo)001:3244: de nas tsha ba'i rong du shar ba rmis //
NK128(nyo)001:3245: de nas nyi ma bod du gsal ba rmis //
NK128(nyo)001:3246: rting nas nyi ma 'od du gsal ba la //
NK128(nyo)001:3247: bdag gi phung po ma lus bsregs nas ni //
NK128(nyo)001:3248: nyi ma bod du gsal zhing gnas pa rmis //
NK128(nyo)001:3249: grogs po rmi lam don de ji ltar lags //
NK128(nyo)001:3251: legs grub kyi brda 'grol bshad pas /
NK128(nyo)001:3252: nub nas bod du nyi zla gnyis shar ba //
NK128(nyo)001:3253: 'o skol grogs po spun gnyis yin par nges //
NK128(nyo)001:3254: zla ba nam mkha'i dkyil du nub pa de //
NK128(nyo)001:3255: dang po legs grub lam khar 'gum pa'i rtags //
NK128(nyo)001:3256: nyi ma phyis shar has po ri gsal ba //
NK128(nyo)001:3257: rgyal po'i thugs la man ngag 'char ba'i rtags //
NK128(nyo)001:3258: de nas tsha ba rong du shar ba de //
NK128(nyo)001:3259: bee ro lan gcig tsha ba rong du spyugs //
NK128(nyo)001:3260: tsha ba'i rong du bstan pa dar ba'i rtags //
NK128(nyo)001:3261: yang gcig bod du 'od dang nyi shar ba //
NK128(nyo)001:3262: 'od zer sprul pa bod du byon pa'i rtags //
NK128(nyo)001:3263: nyi ma bee ro bod du byon nas ni //
NK128(nyo)001:3264: rtsol med bstan pa bod du dar ba'i rtags //
NK128(nyo)001:3265: nyi mas bee ro'i lus dang khur bsregs pa //
NK128(nyo)001:3266: nyon mongs bag chags thams cad bsregs byas nas //
NK128(nyo)001:3267: tshe 'dir rtsol med mngon 'tshang rgya ba'i rtags //
NK128(nyo)001:3268: rmi lam bzang bas da ni myur du gshegs //
NK128(nyo)001:3270: de nas lam kha bas 'gags te mthar yang /
NK128(nyo)001:3271: bee ros rta'i kha 'thur bzung ste mkhar bas kha ba bshags shing lam btsal /
NK128(nyo)001:3272: legs grub kyi rta'i mjug ma nas 'jus te gom
NK128(nyo)001:3273: gang 'brul na 'chi ba'i lam rgyang grags re la
NK128(nyo)001:3274: nam langs sa rub bar du 'gor ba'i lam la
NK128(nyo)001:3275: de shi de chad kyi dka' ba gsum pa'o //
NK128(nyo)001:3276: de nas lam gzur yang bal yul tsha ba'i rong
NK128(nyo)001:3277: du mi 'dug pa'i dbang med de zhag gcig bzhugs
NK128(nyo)001:3278: pas / gnod sbyin gtum po zhes bya ba mi
NK128(nyo)001:3279: sha rlon par za bas cho 'phrul sna tshogs bstan
NK128(nyo)001:3280: pa zhi ba'i bden tshig brjod kyang ma nyan te
NK128(nyo)001:3281: cho 'phrul ma zhi ba rdzu 'phrul gyis dbang du
NK128(nyo)001:3282: bsdus shing dam la btags te bar chod thar bar
NK128(nyo)001:3283: dka' ba las thar ba ni dka' ba ba zhi
NK128(nyo)001:3284: pas / pa'o // de nas bal yul nas phar
NK128(nyo)001:3285: 'gro ba'i lam du rta dang gser la jag pa
NK128(nyo)001:3286: byung gi dogs nas mtshan 'gros mdzad pa la kha
NK128(nyo)001:3287: ba byung ste rjes mi mngon pa'i thabs su rta
NK128(nyo)001:3288: slangs sa la mi 'brul ba'i phyir rta 'phongs la
NK128(nyo)001:3290: bee ro dang legs grub gnyis kyi phyag zhabs bzhir
NK128(nyo)001:3291: gcan gzan gyi sder mo gyon nas sgur 'gros kyi
NK128(nyo)001:3292: rta'i sngon mjug byas te byon nas legs grub kyis
NK128(nyo)001:3293: rta rjes bsub kyis phyin te /
NK128(nyo)001:3294: rjes sba bar dka' ba kha ba la rjes sbas
NK128(nyo)001:3295: te thar bar dka' ba jag pa las thar ba'i
NK128(nyo)001:3297: de nas rgya bal gyi mtshams brag ri smug por /
NK128(nyo)001:3298: rkang phran dang gcan gzan gdug pa can mi sha
NK128(nyo)001:3299: dngos su za ba las thar ba ni dka' ba
NK128(nyo)001:3300: drug pa'o // de nas rgya gar du sleb ste
NK128(nyo)001:3301: chu shing gi 'phrang dam pa gzur sa med par
NK128(nyo)001:3302: 'phrang srung gi bzung ste rta dang gser phrogs pa
NK128(nyo)001:3303: drug pa'o // las / bee ros za ma rtog
NK128(nyo)001:3304: gi nang du lcags kyi spu grir sprul pas 'phrang
NK128(nyo)001:3306: rdzu 'phrul can 'di zhog la zla bo 'di gsod zer ba la /
NK128(nyo)001:3307: legs grub mthi'i mon pa spyi zlum zhig tu sprul te 'phrang srung la mgur gsungs shing /
NK128(nyo)001:3308: gser phye khyor gang byin pas 'phrang srung dga' nas
NK128(nyo)001:3309: lam rgyus bstan te 'phrang srung las thar ba'i dka'
NK128(nyo)001:3310: ba bdun pa'o // de nas yang rnga mo'i gdong
NK128(nyo)001:3311: bgegs zhes bya ba'i 'phrang la phyin pas 'phrang srung
NK128(nyo)001:3313: 'o ma'i ral gri rgyab byung ba la gser gyi
NK128(nyo)001:3314: pa tra mgo la gyon zhing sked la dkris pas
NK128(nyo)001:3315: ma phed / zhi bas bkrol zhing barngana pa byin
NK128(nyo)001:3316: pas kyang ral gri brdeg tu byung ba rdzu 'phrul
NK128(nyo)001:3317: gyis thar ba ni dka' ba brgyad pa'o //
NK128(nyo)001:3318: yang chu shing gi 'phrang 'jigs shing gi bung ba'i
NK128(nyo)001:3319: sar rta mtsha' lu bya gdong bee ro dang legs
NK128(nyo)001:3320: grub la lta zhing mchi ma phyungs te shi ba
NK128(nyo)001:3321: la khong gnyis kyis kyang bshums so //
NK128(nyo)001:3322: de'i tshe rta ro'i dri ma la ce spyang dang
NK128(nyo)001:3323: gcan gzan dur bya kang ka mchu ring mang po
NK128(nyo)001:3324: byung ste rta ro yang zos /
NK128(nyo)001:3325: khong gnyis zar byung bas gser la sbas te bros so //
NK128(nyo)001:3326: de lta bu'i thar bar dka' ba las srog thar ba ni dka' ba dgu pa'o //
NK128(nyo)001:3327: de nas ma ga rdar 'jigs pa'i dpya 'phrang chen
NK128(nyo)001:3328: po gzur sa med pa la mi 'gro ba'i dbang
NK128(nyo)001:3329: med nas gser sbas te phyin pas /
NK128(nyo)001:3330: yang 'phrang srung ba dang 'phrad de gser yod zer
NK128(nyo)001:3331: brdungs shing na bza' rnams bshus pas kyang gser ma
NK128(nyo)001:3332: rnyed nas / nya srul rnams kyang bshags te gser
NK128(nyo)001:3333: btsal bas zla ba phyed du bsnyun zhing do shi
NK128(nyo)001:3334: do chad kyi dka' ba bcu pa'o //
NK128(nyo)001:3335: de nas 'phrang srung ba gser med pa kho thag chod de log pa dang /
NK128(nyo)001:3336: gser bton te dri sha'i yul du phyin gser rnams
NK128(nyo)001:3337: sbas te grong khyer du lam dang brgyags 'tshol bar
NK128(nyo)001:3338: byon pas / matha'i rtog can pa byung ngo zer nas /
NK128(nyo)001:3339: brdungs shing sbrul dang sbal pa'i dong du zhag bdun du skyur ro //
NK128(nyo)001:3340: der zhag gcig nas 'chi ba la zhag bdun du
NK128(nyo)001:3341: ma shi ba ngo mtshar nas bton te shi ba
NK128(nyo)001:3342: las thar ba'i dka' ba bcu gcig pa'o //
NK128(nyo)001:3343: yang gser bton te khur nas phyin pas rgya gar bsu ta'i gling du phyin pas /
NK128(nyo)001:3344: stag dom sbrul sogs gdug pa can gyi gling du
NK128(nyo)001:3345: do shi do chad byas pa las thar nas bi
NK128(nyo)001:3346: bi ro'i tshal du sleb ste /
NK128(nyo)001:3347: gser sbas nas rgyal po'i pho brang du bza' slong
NK128(nyo)001:3348: bar byon pas rgyal po khros te zhag drug tu
NK128(nyo)001:3349: zas ma sbyin par dong du bcug pas /
NK128(nyo)001:3350: sna zhom zhing lus rid par gyur te gcan zan /
NK128(nyo)001:3352: rgyal po'i chad pa las thar ba'i dka' ba bcu gnyis pa'o //
NK128(nyo)001:3353: de nas gser bton te ma ga d+ha'i yul du
NK128(nyo)001:3354: slebs nas mu za'i mtsho las sgrol mkhan med par
NK128(nyo)001:3355: ras dang dbyug pa las gru byas te phyin do
NK128(nyo)001:3356: shi do chad la pha gar thon pa'i dka' ba
NK128(nyo)001:3357: bcu gsum pa'o // de nas rgya gar a ba
NK128(nyo)001:3358: d+hu ti'i gling du byon pas mon pa 'jigs su
NK128(nyo)001:3359: rung ba rnams kyis dbyug pa ma chag gi bar
NK128(nyo)001:3360: du brdungs te do shi do chad las thar ba'i
NK128(nyo)001:3362: de nas rgya gar +aat+ya pha lo'i gling du phyin
NK128(nyo)001:3363: pas bse lcags kyi 'bag dang sbrul 'bag mang pos
NK128(nyo)001:3364: bsdigs shing mthong ba tsam gyis dngangs shing 'chi la
NK128(nyo)001:3365: thug pa dang / yang kri li krish+na'i yul du
NK128(nyo)001:3366: phyin pas dug sbrul mang po lus la 'khril zhing
NK128(nyo)001:3367: 'dogs te shin tu nyams thag pa'i sdug bsngal las
NK128(nyo)001:3368: thar ba ni dka' ba bco lnga pa'o //
NK128(nyo)001:3369: de nas e b+ha ke sha'i yul du byon pas /
NK128(nyo)001:3370: brda sprad par dka' ba'i bud med mang pos zas
NK128(nyo)001:3371: la dug sbyar te sbyin pas dug nad kyis zla
NK128(nyo)001:3372: ba phyed kyi bar du 'grongs la thug pa'i snyung
NK128(nyo)001:3373: gis zin pa las thar ba ni dka' ba bcu
NK128(nyo)001:3374: drug pa'o // de nas re zhig gser rnams sbas te rgya gar gyi mthil du slebs nas /
NK128(nyo)001:3378: kun dga' ra ba la sogs par sdom bu mdzad cing zla ba drug gi bar du bzhugs nas /
NK128(nyo)001:3379: man ngag gi chos su mkhas /
NK128(nyo)001:3380: chos grwa'i mkhan po su yin /
NK128(nyo)001:3381: grub pa thob pa su yod sogs dris pas /
NK128(nyo)001:3382: spyir mkhas pa la sogs mang du yod cing /
NK128(nyo)001:3383: slob dpon sh+r+ai seng ha nyid mkhas grub 'dzom par thams cad kha mthun par sgrog par thos so //
NK128(nyo)001:3384: de nas za kha b+hu ha zhes bya bar rgyal
NK128(nyo)001:3385: po ku ma sha duhkha zhes bya bar d+ha he
NK128(nyo)001:3386: na'i gtsug lag khang dris pas rgyal pos rmi lam
NK128(nyo)001:3387: tshigs bcad smras shing mi ston par smras pa dang
NK128(nyo)001:3388: / lan du bee ros kyang mgur gsungs pas dad
NK128(nyo)001:3389: de zhabs spyi bor blangs te lo rgyus zhib tu
NK128(nyo)001:3390: bshad cing lam rgyus kyang btang ngo //
NK128(nyo)001:3391: de nas d+ha he na'i rtsar sleb pa'i tshe gtam dris pas /
NK128(nyo)001:3392: smad 'tshong ma bdag nyid ma dang dge slong kun
NK128(nyo)001:3393: dga' mos thig le nyag gcig la rgyud lung man
NK128(nyo)001:3395: rtsod pas pan+di ta rnams 'dus te /
NK128(nyo)001:3396: bod du man ngag 'tshor ba'i ltas su dgongs te sus kyang man ngag bstan du med cing /
NK128(nyo)001:3397: thun mong ma yin pa'i rgyud man ngag rnams pan grub rnams kyis thugs la gab cing /
NK128(nyo)001:3398: thun mong ba'i rgyud sde chen po drug cu man ngag dang bcas pa /
NK128(nyo)001:3399: rgya gar chos kyi rgyal po dang pan+di ta rnams rgya nyis sprod kyis mnan nas sbas te /
NK128(nyo)001:3400: lkog chos su bshad na rgyal po'i chad pa yong zer ba thos pas /
NK128(nyo)001:3401: bee ro dang legs grub gnyis zhal ngo nag ting gis song ngo //
NK128(nyo)001:3402: der d+ha he na'i sgo drung du bzhugs pas /
NK128(nyo)001:3403: 'jam dpal gyi sprul pa rgan mo zhig dang 'phrad
NK128(nyo)001:3404: de d+ha he na'i 'du khang dang po dang bar
NK128(nyo)001:3407: barngana pa gter na bshad kyis zer te /
NK128(nyo)001:3408: mtsho ku ta'i 'gram du rgan mo khrid gser barngana par byin nas dris pas /
NK128(nyo)001:3409: rgan mos chu nang du bzhugs /
NK128(nyo)001:3410: tsan dan lo mas gtong bkab /
NK128(nyo)001:3411: smyug ma'i um b+hi ring po zhig khar bstad de /
NK128(nyo)001:3412: de'i nang nas tshigs su bcad pa'i tshul gyis /
NK128(nyo)001:3413: pan grub rnams kyi rmi ltas dang po log tshul
NK128(nyo)001:3414: bzlo zhing smras te d+ha he na'i 'du khang bar
NK128(nyo)001:3416: bram ze mo shel gyi blo gros bya ba zhig chu len du 'ong gis /
NK128(nyo)001:3418: ngas smras ma zer zhig zer te rgan mo mi snang bar song skad do //
NK128(nyo)001:3419: phyis de sus smras brtags kyang ma shes skad /
NK128(nyo)001:3420: der rgan mo'i ngag ltar byas te chu len ma
NK128(nyo)001:3421: la 'phrin lan gsum bskur bar brjed zer lan ma
NK128(nyo)001:3422: byung ba la / bee ros chu bum pa la sbyar bas /
NK128(nyo)001:3423: bram ze mos kyang gser gyi gri gus brang bshags
NK128(nyo)001:3424: te rdor dbyings kyi lha tshogs bstan pa la bee
NK128(nyo)001:3425: ros phyag mdzad de bram ze mo la gser gyi
NK128(nyo)001:3426: pa tra dang gser phyes barngana nas /
NK128(nyo)001:3427: brjed thor chu bum nang du rde'u bcug yig 'phrin bskur nas btang ngo //
NK128(nyo)001:3428: de bram ze mos nang du phyin nas zangs su
NK128(nyo)001:3429: chu byo bas rde'u khrol zer ba slob dpon gyis
NK128(nyo)001:3430: gsan te ci yin gsungs pas /
NK128(nyo)001:3431: bod kyi ban de gnyis kyi brjed tho yin zer yig 'phrin phul lo //
NK128(nyo)001:3432: slob dpon sh+r+ai seng has kyang de'i lan bskur zhing
NK128(nyo)001:3433: nam gung la phrad do zhes ngag lan yang bskur
NK128(nyo)001:3434: ro // de nas nam gyi gung la grub pa'i
NK128(nyo)001:3435: slob dpon chen po sh+r+ai seng ha dang mjal zhing
NK128(nyo)001:3436: phyag rten du gser srang stong phul zhing phyag dang
NK128(nyo)001:3437: skor ba byas te mnga' bdag khri srong gi lo
NK128(nyo)001:3438: rgyus rnams kyis khog phub ste /
NK128(nyo)001:3439: skye ba 'di nyid la 'tshang rgya ba rtsol med a ti yo ga'i chos zhu 'tshal /
NK128(nyo)001:3441: slob dpon sh+r+ai seng ha'i zhal nas /
NK128(nyo)001:3442: smad 'tshong ma bdag nyid ma dang dge slong ma
NK128(nyo)001:3443: kun dga' mos bka' bslad de brtsod pas pan+di ta
NK128(nyo)001:3444: rnams kyis bka' bgros te bka' bslad pa rnams me
NK128(nyo)001:3445: la bsregs bka' thams cad bsdebs te rdo rje gdan
NK128(nyo)001:3446: du sbas chos rgyal dang pan+di ta'i rgya nyis sprod
NK128(nyo)001:3447: du btab yod pas bstan par dka'/
NK128(nyo)001:3448: 'on kyang rgyal ba'i bka' mtha' 'khob bod yul du
NK128(nyo)001:3449: dar ba'i dus la bab 'dug pas ngas rmi lam
NK128(nyo)001:3450: brtag gi gsungs te mnyam par bzhag nas brtag par
NK128(nyo)001:3452: bod du rtsol med kyi bstan pas phan thog par 'dug gis gsungs nas /
NK128(nyo)001:3453: da ni bod la bskur pa'i dus la babs pas bskur ni bskur /
NK128(nyo)001:3454: bskur thabs ni legs pa zhig dgos /
NK128(nyo)001:3455: ma legs na rgyal pos tshor te 'u cag gsum ga'i srog la 'ong /
NK128(nyo)001:3456: man ngag gi chos kyang rtsad nas med par byed /
NK128(nyo)001:3457: khyod gnyis sngon la pan+di ta gzhan la yang rgyu 'bras kyi chos rdzogs par nyon cig /
NK128(nyo)001:3458: pan+di ta phyi ma rnams la yang gser re phul
NK128(nyo)001:3459: la gsang sngags 'bras bu'i chos rdzogs par nyon cig
NK128(nyo)001:3460: / de nas ma tshor ba nam gyi gung la
NK128(nyo)001:3461: rtsol med rdzogs pa chen po'i chos bshad kyis gsungs
NK128(nyo)001:3462: / / de nas khong gnyis kyis slob dpon gyi
NK128(nyo)001:3463: bka' bzhin du pan chen nyer lnga sogs la rgyu
NK128(nyo)001:3464: dang 'bras bu'i chos mang du zhus /
NK128(nyo)001:3465: sprul sku dga' rab rdo rje dang 'jam dpal bshes gnyen yang mjal te /
NK128(nyo)001:3466: gser phye dang pa tra'i me tog phul nas phyag
NK128(nyo)001:3467: btsal skor ba byas zhabs la btugs de man ngag
NK128(nyo)001:3468: zhus pas / dbang bskur byin rlabs man ngag rnams
NK128(nyo)001:3469: rdzogs par gnang zhing slar yang sh+r+ai seng ha la
NK128(nyo)001:3471: dga' rab rdo rje sogs pan chen 'di rnams grub
NK128(nyo)001:3472: pa'i sa la bzhugs shing ye shes kyi sku can
NK128(nyo)001:3473: yin pas las dang skal bar ldan na deng sang
NK128(nyo)001:3474: yang zhal mjal nges par gsungs phyir snga phyi mi
NK128(nyo)001:3475: mtshungs so snyam pa'i ngan rtog mi bya'o //
NK128(nyo)001:3476: de nas slar yang slob dpon sh+r+ai seng ha'i drung
NK128(nyo)001:3477: du byon te man ngag gi chos rnams zhus pa'i
NK128(nyo)001:3478: tshe slob dpon nyid gnod sbyin skar mda' gdong du
NK128(nyo)001:3479: sprul / bee ro tsa nas seng ge rab brtan du bardzusa /
NK128(nyo)001:3480: legs grub ngang par bardzusa te nam gung la rdo
NK128(nyo)001:3481: rje gdan nas rgya nyis sprod kyis sbas pa'i man
NK128(nyo)001:3482: ngag gi chos rnams 'don par byon nas /
NK128(nyo)001:3483: rgya bshig ste bton pas sngags phyi nang gi dam
NK128(nyo)001:3484: can chos skyong thams cad zhal mngon sum du bstan
NK128(nyo)001:3485: nas / slob dpon sh+r+ai seng ha dang bee ro
NK128(nyo)001:3486: gnyis la bskor ba dang phyag byas zhabs spyi bos
NK128(nyo)001:3487: nas / blangs te / gdams ngag gi chos kyi
NK128(nyo)001:3488: che ba brjod cing gces spras dang bka' rgya bsdoms
NK128(nyo)001:3489: dgos pa sogs zhu ba phul te mi snang bar
NK128(nyo)001:3490: nas / blangs te / song ngo // de nas bka' brgyud man ngag dang bcas pa khyer /
NK128(nyo)001:3491: rgya bshig pa rnams sngar bzhin du rgyas btab nas d+ha he na'i 'du khang du byon no //
NK128(nyo)001:3492: der pan chen rnams kyi rmi ltas bar pa log
NK128(nyo)001:3493: ste thams cad kyang 'du zhing 'tshogs nas rmi lam
NK128(nyo)001:3494: bzlo zhing pan+di ta rnams kyi nang nas su ma
NK128(nyo)001:3495: tshang dang / rdo rje gdan du sus phyin dang
NK128(nyo)001:3496: dkon gnyer sogs la man ngag rgyas btab pa'i rtsar
NK128(nyo)001:3497: su byung zhes dris pas kyang rtsad ma chod cing
NK128(nyo)001:3498: tshang dang / / slar yang pan+di ta rnams bgros
NK128(nyo)001:3499: nas rdo rje gdan gyi man ngag sus blangs kyang
NK128(nyo)001:3500: chos skyong rgyal pos chad pas gcod par bgros so
NK128(nyo)001:3501: tshang dang / / // de nas bee ro dang
NK128(nyo)001:3502: legs grub gnyis kyis nyin ltar sngar bzhin 'jam dpal
NK128(nyo)001:3503: bshes gnyen sogs pan+di ta phyi ma bdun po la
NK128(nyo)001:3505: nub bzhin sh+r+ai seng ha la rdzogs chen nyan te /
NK128(nyo)001:3506: de yang slob dpon gyi khang pa'i nang du bzhugs te rdo chen gsum gyi khar rdza ma bzhag /
NK128(nyo)001:3507: rdza ma de d+r+wa bar bcug /
NK128(nyo)001:3508: de'i nang du slob dpon gyis bzhugs /
NK128(nyo)001:3510: phub kyi steng du sla nga chus bkang ste bzhag /
NK128(nyo)001:3511: rdza ma'i bum pa nas khang pa'i phyi ru sbubs mchu ring po btsugs te bshad /
NK128(nyo)001:3512: bee ro dang legs grub gnyis kyis phyi rol nas sha ba'i dbyibs zhu ring po re gyon /
NK128(nyo)001:3514: 'khar ba re thogs nas nam gyi gung la nyan /
NK128(nyo)001:3515: legs grub kyis zla grib mtshams la dar dkar la ra dkar mo'i 'o mas bris so //
NK128(nyo)001:3516: der bee ro ni mgo bstan pa tsam gyis thugs su chud cing /
NK128(nyo)001:3518: de yang bod du bstan pa 'byung ba'i rtags su rig pa'i khu byug /
NK128(nyo)001:3519: rdzogs par bstan pa'i rtags su rtsal chen sprugs pa /
NK128(nyo)001:3520: bsam gtan ston pa'i rtags su thig le drug pa /
NK128(nyo)001:3521: theg pa kun gyi lta spyod khog tu 'dus pa'i rtags su khyung chen /
NK128(nyo)001:3522: theg pa kun las khyad 'don pa'i rtags su lta ba mi nub pa'i rgyal mtshan rnams bshad /
NK128(nyo)001:3523: mgu 'am gsungs pas rjes su yi rang ngo zhus so //
NK128(nyo)001:3524: gzhan yang yid bzhin nor bu rje btsun dam pa /
NK128(nyo)001:3533: rdo la gser zhun te chung 'bring che bzhi rmad byung rnams dang /
NK128(nyo)001:3534: sems sde'i rgyud bco brgyad gdams ngag ngo sprod dang
NK128(nyo)001:3535: bcas pa gsungs pas legs grub tshim ste sngon la
NK128(nyo)001:3536: song ba / sngon gyi rmi ltas ltar gcan 'phrang
NK128(nyo)001:3537: pas lo bzhi bcu zhe bzhi pa la bkrongs so
NK128(nyo)001:3538: song ba / // bee ros zhag gsum gyi bar du kha sbub tu gzims te bzhugs pas /
NK128(nyo)001:3539: slob dpon gyis grogs song bas skyo'am gsungs pa la ma skyo ba'i tshul dang /
NK128(nyo)001:3540: na'am gsungs pas sems sde bco brgyad na tshul gyi mgur gsungs pas bzhad cing dgyes te /
NK128(nyo)001:3541: man ngag rgya mtsho'i klong gsungs /
NK128(nyo)001:3542: yang klong sde'i skor rgyud dang man ngag dang bcas pa gsungs /
NK128(nyo)001:3543: yang rgyud sde'i skor rnams gsungs /
NK128(nyo)001:3544: yang ke'u tshang gi skor dang gab pa'i chos skor zab la rgya che ba gsungs /
NK128(nyo)001:3546: la zlo rgyal po'i skor sogs gsungs te tshim mam gsungs /
NK128(nyo)001:3547: de rnams kyi don rtsol ba mi dgos par mngon
NK128(nyo)001:3548: sum rang grol da lta nyid du mthong ba dgos
NK128(nyo)001:3549: tshul zhus te / gser phye bre gang dang gser
NK128(nyo)001:3550: gyi pa tra bdun phul phyag dang skor ba mdzad
NK128(nyo)001:3551: tshul zhus te / / dpal ldan seng ge'i 'od can khyod /
NK128(nyo)001:3552: ces sogs kyi tshigs bcad gsol bas slob dpon dgyes te /
NK128(nyo)001:3553: d+ha he na'i 'du khang dang por gsal byed rin po che 'bar ba la brten nas /
NK128(nyo)001:3554: rgyal thabs spyi blugs kyi dbang la sogs pa dbang bdun bskur /
NK128(nyo)001:3555: thug phrad gsum gyis rang grol mngon sum du ngo sprod /
NK128(nyo)001:3556: mngon sum gnyis kyis tshad la phab /
NK128(nyo)001:3557: thig le drug gis rnam rtog spros pa bcad /
NK128(nyo)001:3558: che ba lnga yis dgongs pa khyad par dpags te /
NK128(nyo)001:3559: rtsol med ye nas sangs rgyas pa'i don nyid mngon sum du gyur to //
NK128(nyo)001:3561: yan lag gi rgyud nyi shu rtsa lnga ste sum cu /
NK128(nyo)001:3563: sprul sku dga' rab rdo rje'i rgyal ba'i bka'i man ngag bco brgyad /
NK128(nyo)001:3565: ku ku r+aa dza'i nyi ma'i snying po 'od dang ldan pa /
NK128(nyo)001:3566: sh+r+ai seng ha nyid kyi rgyan phreng 'od gsum /
NK128(nyo)001:3567: bsam gtan nyams kyi sgron ma rnams gnyer du gtad /
NK128(nyo)001:3569: bskul ba rkyen gyi man ngag ni /
NK128(nyo)001:3570: shan 'byed la zla rgyud bkrol bas //
NK128(nyo)001:3571: rgyud kyi gdams pa mngon sum bstan //
NK128(nyo)001:3572: dben par rang sems rang gis mos par gyis //
NK128(nyo)001:3573: smin par gyis shig thugs kyi sras //
NK128(nyo)001:3575: de nas bee ro tsa na'i rtogs pa mngon du gyur te /
NK128(nyo)001:3576: slob dpon la drin dran pa dang rtogs pa 'bul ba'i mgur gsungs pa /
NK128(nyo)001:3577: sprul pa'i gshegs shul rdo rje gdan //
NK128(nyo)001:3578: snying po'i don rdzogs skal ldan rje //
NK128(nyo)001:3579: nges pa yin pas de mngon bstan //
NK128(nyo)001:3580: rang rgyud rang grol bka' drin che //
NK128(nyo)001:3581: zhes btang rag kyang phul zhing zhus lan mang du mdzad do //
NK128(nyo)001:3582: de nas slob dpon gyi zhal bkod kyi mgur gsungs
NK128(nyo)001:3583: pa'i don khyed kyi grogs po yang gcan 'phrang gis
NK128(nyo)001:3584: bsad pas / gser phye barngana par byin la rkang mgyogs mkhan po dang grogs po kyis /
NK128(nyo)001:3585: ku sha lcags kyi sdong por rkang mgyogs bsgrubs la song /
NK128(nyo)001:3586: des bar gcod med par bstan pa bod du rgyas par 'gyur ro gsungs te /
NK128(nyo)001:3588: des nas bee ros dga' rab rdo rje dang 'jam
NK128(nyo)001:3589: dpal bshes gnyen sogs pan chen gzhan rnams dang yang
NK128(nyo)001:3590: mjal zhing chos 'phro rnams zhus te dgongs pa gnyis
NK128(nyo)001:3592: de rnams kyi kyang bod du gshegs la 'gro don gyis shig par lung bstan no //
NK128(nyo)001:3593: 'phrang srung dpon ku ha ra btsal bas ma rnyed
NK128(nyo)001:3594: nas rkang mgyogs dpon po ku m+aa ra la gser
NK128(nyo)001:3595: gyi pa tra byin nas grogs po byas mna' mtho
NK128(nyo)001:3596: bcad pas / rkang mgyogs phas bu la yang bstan du med /
NK128(nyo)001:3597: 'di nas bod du slebs pa tsam sbyin no zer
NK128(nyo)001:3598: nas rgya gar ba glag khra zan la 'dzum pa
NK128(nyo)001:3599: tsam yod kyang / bee ro la go bo ri rtsibs gcod pa tsam sbyin te /
NK128(nyo)001:3600: ku sha lcags kyi sdong por bsgrub pas /
NK128(nyo)001:3601: yul mi rnams kyis dri ba byed pa la mgur
NK128(nyo)001:3602: gsungs pas dad de phyag btsal zhabs nas bteg go
NK128(nyo)001:3603: // der lo gcig gis rkang mgyogs grub ste yul
NK128(nyo)001:3604: ta ko ta tsan dan gyi gling du phyin te
NK128(nyo)001:3605: yul de'i rgyal po la dris lan gyi mgur mang
NK128(nyo)001:3606: du gsungs pas dreg pa btul te byams pa'i sku
NK128(nyo)001:3607: gser las byas pa zhig phul lo //
NK128(nyo)001:3608: de nas bee ro bod du chas pas pan+di ta kun gyi rmi ltas phyi ma log /
NK128(nyo)001:3609: me tog thams cad kyang bod du kha ltas /
NK128(nyo)001:3610: tsan dan la sogs pa'i dri ngad rnams kyang bod phyogs su rlung gis spyod /
NK128(nyo)001:3611: khyi thams cad kyang bod du ltas nas zug /
NK128(nyo)001:3612: rgya gar chos skyong rgyal po dang mkhas pa bdun
NK128(nyo)001:3613: sogs dpal n+aa len+da'i gtsug lag khang gi sgor 'tshogs
NK128(nyo)001:3614: te 'gro ba byed cing lan zhes bgros par /
NK128(nyo)001:3615: bod kyi ban des man ngag gi chos khyer bas lan zer /
NK128(nyo)001:3616: der rdo rje gdan du bltas pas rgya rnams bshig nas 'dug sus bshad /
NK128(nyo)001:3617: sus bskur zhes ltas brtags pas /
NK128(nyo)001:3618: brag chen po gsum gyi kha na 'dug pa /
NK128(nyo)001:3619: lus po brag tu yod pa /
NK128(nyo)001:3622: de'i dkyil na mtsho yod pa /
NK128(nyo)001:3623: lcags mchu ring po can cig bshad 'dug /
NK128(nyo)001:3624: phyi nas sha ba'i mgo can lag na 'khar ba thogs pa /
NK128(nyo)001:3625: mig ltag khung du dod pa khres chung can gnyis
NK128(nyo)001:3626: kyis nyan 'dug pas 'di ya mtshan che lha mi
NK128(nyo)001:3627: sprul pa gang yin ngo ma shes zer ro //
NK128(nyo)001:3628: slar yang thams cad bgros nas rtsol med rdzogs pa
NK128(nyo)001:3629: chen po'i chos 'di bod du shor na rgya gar
NK128(nyo)001:3630: gyi bcud dang bsod nams thams cad 'chor /
NK128(nyo)001:3631: dkar po'i chos bstan pa'i snying po lhag med du 'chor bas /
NK128(nyo)001:3632: rkang mgyogs btang la lam du gsod cig ces bgros so //
NK128(nyo)001:3633: der rkang mgyogs mkhan po ku ma r+aas thos nas
NK128(nyo)001:3634: bee ro dang grogs po yin pas blo ma bzod
NK128(nyo)001:3635: par bee ro'i gan du rgyugs te mkhas pa bdun
NK128(nyo)001:3636: gyi rmi lam zlo zhing tshigs su bcad pa zhus
NK128(nyo)001:3637: pa'i lam du bee ros mgur gsungs shing gser tshogs
NK128(nyo)001:3638: dang pa tra gsum byin te ku m+aa ra dang
NK128(nyo)001:3640: gcan 'phrang dang po rkang mgyogs ku m+aa ra'i grogs
NK128(nyo)001:3641: po ku h+aa ra dang phrad pa la gser phye
NK128(nyo)001:3642: khyor ba gang dang pa tra gcig barngana par byin
NK128(nyo)001:3643: nas rkang mgyogs pa rnams do nub 'dir byung ste
NK128(nyo)001:3645: de dus khyod kyi ban de ma mthong mgo la
NK128(nyo)001:3646: sha ba'i dbyibs zhu ring po dang rkang pa la
NK128(nyo)001:3647: zon l+h+aam phyir log tu gyon pa sprul pa'i gnod
NK128(nyo)001:3648: sbyin lta bu zhig song ba de ni da tsam
NK128(nyo)001:3649: bod yul mthil du sleb pa yod kyis shig ces
NK128(nyo)001:3650: phrang srung la mna' bgags so //
NK128(nyo)001:3651: de nas rkang mgyogs ku m+aa ras grong khyer ser skya'i sgor dgugs te zla bo rnams sbran te /
NK128(nyo)001:3652: bod kyi ban de bee ro tsa na 'di na
NK128(nyo)001:3653: phar la song ngam zer bdas la bsad kyis byas
NK128(nyo)001:3654: pas / chos rgyal dang pan+di ta kun gyis kyang phrad na gsod cig zer ro //
NK128(nyo)001:3655: der rkang mgyogs pa rnams bee ro byon pa'i bshul
NK128(nyo)001:3656: gcan 'phrang dang por sleb pa dang 'phrang srung ba
NK128(nyo)001:3657: la dris pas / sngar bslabs pa ltar byas pas kho thag chod de phyir log go //
NK128(nyo)001:3658: de nas bee ros li yul lcags ra smug por
NK128(nyo)001:3659: byon te li tsha tshul khrims sgron dang mjal te
NK128(nyo)001:3660: gnas g.yar zhing bza' btung blang ba'i tshigs bcad gsungs
NK128(nyo)001:3661: shing / bee ro yin par shes te zhus lan mang du mdzad pa'i mthar /
NK128(nyo)001:3662: rta ngang pa gser mdog phul ba la man ngag bshad pas rtogs pa shar ro //
NK128(nyo)001:3663: de nas bal yul du pan+di ta pra dz+ny+aa sid+d+hi
NK128(nyo)001:3664: bas dri ba gsum byas par lan btab pas mnyes
NK128(nyo)001:3665: nas dgun zla ba gcig tu mchod gnas su bkur
NK128(nyo)001:3666: ro // de nas bal yul du rgya gar lha
NK128(nyo)001:3667: mo re lcam 'khrugs te kha ba phab pa la
NK128(nyo)001:3668: ro // / bee ros bka' bden rdzun brtags pa'i
NK128(nyo)001:3669: mgur gsungs pas sprin gseb nas lha mo dmar mo'i
NK128(nyo)001:3670: gzugs bstan nas phyag btsal bran du byas te kha
NK128(nyo)001:3671: ba bcad de nyi ma btang ngo //
NK128(nyo)001:3672: ta ke tsan dan gling gi rgyal pos phul ba'i
NK128(nyo)001:3673: gser gyi byams sku 'phags pa shing kun la phul
NK128(nyo)001:3675: de nas bal yul nas bskyod de nyang ro ne
NK128(nyo)001:3676: seng du gdugs tshod gsol nas bsam yas su nyi
NK128(nyo)001:3677: ma dgongs phyed tsam la sleb pa ni rkang mgyogs
NK128(nyo)001:3678: kyi mathu'o // der mnga' bdag gi 'bangs 'khor rnams phyi na bsdad /
NK128(nyo)001:3679: mnga' bdag rgyal po gur gyi nang na bzhugs pa la /
NK128(nyo)001:3680: bee ros bardzusa te gur 'dabs byang phyogs nas slog nas byon te btsad po'i snyan du gsol ba /
NK128(nyo)001:3681: rje yis bka' stsal ba'i man ngag gi chos ni thob nas mchi /
NK128(nyo)001:3682: rgya gar gyi mi rnams 'phrag dog byung srid na gsan du mi rung bar zhus nas /
NK128(nyo)001:3683: bka' rtags kyi phyag rgya dang srog tshig mnos nas phyir byon te /
NK128(nyo)001:3684: mnga' bdag rgyal po mkhar dgu rim du gshegs nas bzhugs pa la /
NK128(nyo)001:3685: bee ros 'bangs tshe mi thing the zhes bya ba la yig 'phrin 'di skad ces bskur ro //
NK128(nyo)001:3686: bod kyi mnga' bdag rgyal po chen po la /
NK128(nyo)001:3687: 'jig rten 'khor ba'i chos la thugs phyugs te /
NK128(nyo)001:3688: ma nor yang dag bden pa'i chos 'dod nas /
NK128(nyo)001:3689: gser phye rdzangs nas bdag cag 'tshol du btang /
NK128(nyo)001:3690: dmyal sbyongs lam bcad mtha' ya kha bskor te /
NK128(nyo)001:3691: las 'phro dag pas mkhas zhal mang po 'khums //
NK128(nyo)001:3692: bzo dang bstan bcos gso dpyad sman la sogs //
NK128(nyo)001:3693: tshe 'dir dgos pa'i phan bya sna tshogs pa //
NK128(nyo)001:3694: dam nyams sgrol ba'i bstan srungs sna tshogs dang //
NK128(nyo)001:3695: phyir rgol zlog pa'i lung rigs mtshon cha dang //
NK128(nyo)001:3696: dbang po'i rim 'jug lam stegs rang rang la //
NK128(nyo)001:3697: rgyu 'bras theg pa ma lus thams cad dang //
NK128(nyo)001:3698: bde chen lhun rdzogs sangs rgyas kun gyi thugs //
NK128(nyo)001:3699: rmad byung bstan pa'i snying po theg pa mchog /
NK128(nyo)001:3700: rgyu 'bras gnyis med rtsol med rdzogs pa che //
NK128(nyo)001:3701: ma lus lus pa med pas bdag la mchis //
NK128(nyo)001:3702: zhal g.yar mchis nas bka' mchid gsan du gsol //
NK128(nyo)001:3703: yun du ma mjal g.yar khams snyoms lags sam //
NK128(nyo)001:3704: mnga' bdag rgyal po zhal mjal zhes 'bul //
NK128(nyo)001:3707: chos dbyings bde chen skye med ma rtogs pas //
NK128(nyo)001:3708: zhes sogs kyis yig 'phrin bskur ba'i lan du /
NK128(nyo)001:3710: 'or ba'i rdzings chen 'dra ba'i kha dpon bdag /
NK128(nyo)001:3711: phung po ma g.yos khams chen bco brgyad bde //
NK128(nyo)001:3712: phung po lnga dang khams chen bco brgyad po //
NK128(nyo)001:3713: lan cig 'jigs pa bdag gis ma bzod nas //
NK128(nyo)001:3714: phung po khams chen 'jig pa'i sman chen po //
NK128(nyo)001:3715: phyi nas rgyu 'bras kun las 'phags pa yi //
NK128(nyo)001:3716: rgyu 'bras gnyis med snying po'i don rtsol ba //
NK128(nyo)001:3717: 'phrang srungs gnod sbyin 'jigs pa'i dom dred sogs //
NK128(nyo)001:3718: 'jigs pa'i bar gcod gdug pa gang gis kyang //
NK128(nyo)001:3719: yid bzhin nor 'dra khyod kyi phung po la //
NK128(nyo)001:3720: bskyod par ma nus bdag kyang rab tu dga' //
NK128(nyo)001:3721: rgyu 'bras gnyis med rtsol med rdzogs pa che //
NK128(nyo)001:3722: yang dag ma nor bden pa'i dam chos rnams //
NK128(nyo)001:3723: bsnams te byon pas zhal mjal spyi bor bkur //
NK128(nyo)001:3725: bla med byang chub mchog tu thugs bskyed nas //
NK128(nyo)001:3726: zhes sogs kyi lan bsrings so //
NK128(nyo)001:3727: de nas zhag gsum nas mjal skabs phyag la 'gyings te /
NK128(nyo)001:3729: dus gsum rgyal ba'i dgongs pa bcud phyung nas /
NK128(nyo)001:3730: rang byung lhun rdzogs bde chen byang chub lam //
NK128(nyo)001:3731: 'jig rten 'khrul pa'i dregs pa kun mchog la //
NK128(nyo)001:3732: mos gus sems kyis phyag tshol spyi bos long //
NK128(nyo)001:3734: rgyal po yab yum 'khor dang bcas pas phyag 'tshal /
NK128(nyo)001:3737: de nas mnga' bdag gis dbu skra them par bkram
NK128(nyo)001:3738: ste de'i steng nas bee ro nang du spyan drangs
NK128(nyo)001:3739: te / rta mtshal lu me stag dang ngang pa
NK128(nyo)001:3740: gser mdongs gnyis la gser sga g.yu yis spras pa
NK128(nyo)001:3741: te / dang / gzhan yang gser dngul /
NK128(nyo)001:3744: bzang skyes la sogs drangs te zhu don tshigs su bcad de zhus pa dang /
NK128(nyo)001:3745: bee ros zhen log gi mgur gsungs shing dam tshig bsgrags pas /
NK128(nyo)001:3746: slar yang nan tan chen pos 'bul ba dang phyag
NK128(nyo)001:3747: skor zhabs la gtugs te spyan chab phyungs te zhus
NK128(nyo)001:3748: pas / 'bangs blon gzhan gyis ma tshor bar nam gung la chos ston par zhal gyi bzhengs shing /
NK128(nyo)001:3749: man ngag gi rgya mtsho lha'i rje zhes par mtshan btags so //
NK128(nyo)001:3750: de nas bee ros nyin par rje blon kun la rgyu 'bras kyi chos bsgyur /
NK128(nyo)001:3751: nub mo nam gung la rje nyid la man ngag gi chos bsgyur ro //
NK128(nyo)001:3752: bee ro 'di ni spyir slob dpon chen po pad+mas
NK128(nyo)001:3753: bsgrub chen bka' brgyad kyi dkyil 'khor du dbang bskur
NK128(nyo)001:3754: ba'i grub mtshan bee ro tsa na ye shes spyan
NK128(nyo)001:3756: stobs ldan nag mo lha skal du babs te drag
NK128(nyo)001:3757: sngags la mnga' brnyes pa rje 'bangs nyer lnga'i gras
NK128(nyo)001:3758: dang / khyad par grub chen dgu'i nang tshan yin /
NK128(nyo)001:3759: mdor na snga phyi dam pa'i chos bsgyur ba de
NK128(nyo)001:3760: dag gi 'gyur byang thang yig dang 'dra 'bag sogs
NK128(nyo)001:3761: las shes so // de yang thang yig tu /
NK128(nyo)001:3762: mdo bsgyur nang du ye shes sde zhes bris //
NK128(nyo)001:3763: sngags bsgyur nang du bee ro tsa na bris //
NK128(nyo)001:3764: zhes sogs gsungs pa dang mthun par /
NK128(nyo)001:3765: bka' 'gyur rin po cher du ban de ye shes sdes bsgyur cing zhus te gtan la phab pa'o /
NK128(nyo)001:3766: zhes gsungs pa yang bee ro nyid yin la /
NK128(nyo)001:3768: 'das dang ma 'ongs da lta thams cad du //
NK128(nyo)001:3769: bee ro tsa na 'dra ba'i lo ts+aa ba //
NK128(nyo)001:3770: sngar yang ma byon da yang 'byon re skan //
NK128(nyo)001:3771: ma 'ongs rgya gar phal skad shes tsam la //
NK128(nyo)001:3772: lo ts+aar bzhed srid bee ro'i char mi nye //
NK128(nyo)001:3773: lo ts+aar btags kyang don la pan tri ta //
NK128(nyo)001:3774: 'di yi chos drin yod do phyi rabs rnams //
NK128(nyo)001:3775: zhes gsungs pa dang mthun par /
NK128(nyo)001:3776: lo ts+aa ba rnam gsum gyi rnam par /
NK128(nyo)001:3777: dbye ba skad gnyis smra ba'i rgyan pas /
NK128(nyo)001:3778: lo ts+aa ba blo ldan shes rab kyis mdo sde rgyan la gzhi 'gyur mdzad pas /
NK128(nyo)001:3779: sbyin pa'i phar phyin gyi skabs /
NK128(nyo)001:3780: a rak+ta a rak+ta a rak+ta zhes chags pa med
NK128(nyo)001:3781: ces pa lan gsum byung ba las bsgyur ba'i go
NK128(nyo)001:3782: skabs ma rnyed / ska ba dpal brtsegs kyi snga 'gyur la gzigs pas dus gsum dang sbyar te /
NK128(nyo)001:3783: sbyin pa'i pha rol phyin pa ni /
NK128(nyo)001:3784: ma chags mi chags chags pa med //
NK128(nyo)001:3785: ces bsgyur ba gzigs pas lhag par dang /
NK128(nyo)001:3786: khyad par lo chen bee ro tsa na ni /
NK128(nyo)001:3787: de dus lo ts+aa mkhas pa mang du tshogs pa rnams khyad par 'byed pa la /
NK128(nyo)001:3788: bye brag bshad mdzod chen mo'i rgya dpe shin tu
NK128(nyo)001:3789: bsgyur dka' bas dum bur bgos te bsgyur bcug pas
NK128(nyo)001:3791: gzhan ma rnams kyis bsgyur ma thub par lus pa'i lo rgyus dang /
NK128(nyo)001:3792: mnga' bdag khri ral pa can gyis kyang /
NK128(nyo)001:3793: lo ts+aa mkhas par tshud pa dz+ny+aa na se na zhes basngagasa shing /
NK128(nyo)001:3794: snga 'gyur gyis chos phal che ba la tshig don
NK128(nyo)001:3795: gnyis kar zhu dag mdzad de gtan la phab nas
NK128(nyo)001:3796: / so so'i 'gyur byang gi rjes su zhus chen
NK128(nyo)001:3797: gyi lo ts+aa ba ban d+he ye shes sdes skad
NK128(nyo)001:3798: gsar bcad kyis gtan la phab pa'o //
NK128(nyo)001:3799: zhes bris pa rnams gzigs pas rtsa ba med pa'i dad pa 'khrungs nas /
NK128(nyo)001:3800: bee ro tsa na nam mkha'i mtha' dang mnyam //
NK128(nyo)001:3801: ska cog gnyis ni nyi zla zung 'brel yin //
NK128(nyo)001:3802: rin chen bzang po tho rangs skar chen 'dra //
NK128(nyo)001:3803: kho bo yang ni srin bu me khyer tsam //
NK128(nyo)001:3804: zhes ched du brjod pa basngagasa par mdzad cing /
NK128(nyo)001:3805: rang nyid kyi khengs skyung bar yang mdzad de /
NK128(nyo)001:3806: lo rgyus 'di kho na chag lo'i rnam thar du yang snang ngo //
NK128(nyo)001:3808: gsar rnying mkhas grub tshad ma kun gyis bee ro'i
NK128(nyo)001:3809: rnam thar la dad pa bya ba dang drin du
NK128(nyo)001:3810: bzo bar mdzad dgos par snang ngo //
NK128(nyo)001:3811: de nas rgya gar gyi pan+di ta rnams dang chos rgyal rnams gcig la gcig thugs ma ches te /
NK128(nyo)001:3812: pan+di ta rnams ni rgya ru spre rgyal pos bshig nas bod la chos bskur bar dgongs /
NK128(nyo)001:3813: chos rgyal thugs la pan+di ta rnams kyis rgya bshig nas bskur bar dgongs /
NK128(nyo)001:3814: der man ngag a ti bstan pa rgyud dang man
NK128(nyo)001:3815: ngag tu bcas pa thun mong ma yin pa bsam
NK128(nyo)001:3816: gyis mi khyab pa rnams pan+di ta rnams kyi thugs
NK128(nyo)001:3817: la bzhugs pa rgyal po la gang yang bya dbang
NK128(nyo)001:3818: med / pan+di ta dang chos rgyal thun mong du grags pa'i sems sde bco brgyad gcig tu byas /
NK128(nyo)001:3819: rgyud sde drug cu thams pa man ngag dang bcas
NK128(nyo)001:3820: pa rgyal pos rdo rje gdan rang su gter kha
NK128(nyo)001:3821: spos te sbas sam yang zer /
NK128(nyo)001:3822: bya rgod phung po'i rir sbas sam yang zer /
NK128(nyo)001:3823: a su ra'i brag phug tu sbas sam yang zer /
NK128(nyo)001:3824: gang ltar dpe rnams rgyal pos gar song cha med par btang ste /
NK128(nyo)001:3825: dper na chu srin gyi gre bar rin po che chud pa bzhin bskal pa'i mthar sbas so //
NK128(nyo)001:3826: de'i rgyu mtshan gyis phyis rgya gar du rdzogs chen
NK128(nyo)001:3827: gyi chos cher mi grags pa de la brten par
NK128(nyo)001:3828: snang zhing / rgyu mtshan 'di ma go bar rgya
NK128(nyo)001:3829: gar du ma grags pa tsam la brten nas rdzogs
NK128(nyo)001:3830: chen chos log tu smra ba mang mod kyang /
NK128(nyo)001:3831: rgya gar du grags tshad yang dag par 'dzin cing /
NK128(nyo)001:3832: ma grags pa rnams 'khrul pa yin par bzhag dgos na /
NK128(nyo)001:3833: mu stegs byed kyi chos rnams sngar nas da lta
NK128(nyo)001:3834: yan chad shin tu grags che bas tshad mar bya
NK128(nyo)001:3835: rigs la / mdo sngags spyi dang khyad par 'dul
NK128(nyo)001:3836: ba sogs deng sang ni sgra mi drag tsam du
NK128(nyo)001:3837: rigs la / song 'dra bas / des na bod
NK128(nyo)001:3838: du dar ba'i mdo sngags phal cher 'khrul par brtags
NK128(nyo)001:3840: de nas rgya gar nas bod du phra ma 'di ltar byung ste /
NK128(nyo)001:3841: bod kyi bee ro tsa nas man ngag gi chos
NK128(nyo)001:3842: rnams ni ma rnyed bod phung bar byed pa'i rgya
NK128(nyo)001:3843: gar gyi ngan sngags rnams dang /
NK128(nyo)001:3844: khro chu phra men rnams dang /
NK128(nyo)001:3845: phung chas sna tshogs khyer nas song bas bod kyi bka' khrims chen po dang sbyor cig /
NK128(nyo)001:3847: der bod kyi blon po gdug pa can rnams kyis
NK128(nyo)001:3848: don de mnga' bdag la zhus te bee ro bkrong
NK128(nyo)001:3849: par zhus pa la ma gnang zhing /
NK128(nyo)001:3850: thabs du ma nas gsol yang rjes ma gnang bar brten /
NK128(nyo)001:3851: sdig blon rnams kyis de ltar na rgyal khrims rang
NK128(nyo)001:3852: zhig la gtong bar mdun a bcad de mnga' bdag
NK128(nyo)001:3853: nyid bcud la 'bod par bgros pas /
NK128(nyo)001:3854: mnga' bdag gi zhal nas de tsam gyi gags la
NK128(nyo)001:3855: thugs na bsad pas mi 'ong spyug gis gsungs te
NK128(nyo)001:3856: / bee ro 'dra ba'i sprang po zhig bzung ste
NK128(nyo)001:3857: bee ro'i gos lham bskon nas zangs kha sbyor gyi
NK128(nyo)001:3858: sbubs su bcug ste gtsang po la bskur nas /
NK128(nyo)001:3859: bee ro la chab gsol lo zhes sgra bsgrags te
NK128(nyo)001:3860: rgyal po nyid kyis thugs ngal mdzad pa'i tshul bstan
NK128(nyo)001:3861: / gdugs kha gi ka ba'i 'chol brus pa'i nang du bee ro sbas te /
NK128(nyo)001:3863: mnga' bdag nyid der byon te gsan pas /
NK128(nyo)001:3864: nub cig btsun mos rig ste blon po rnams bsdus
NK128(nyo)001:3865: shing gros byas te slar yang rje la nan tur
NK128(nyo)001:3866: gyi gsol ba / mnga' bdag gis spyug par zhal gyis bzhes te /
NK128(nyo)001:3867: rgyal byon rnams kyis bee ro byug par brtsams pa na /
NK128(nyo)001:3868: lo chen gyis dka' ba bcu drug mgur du bzhes pa dang /
NK128(nyo)001:3869: de bzhin du do shi do chad kyi lo rgyus mgur du bzhes pa dang /
NK128(nyo)001:3870: bod la dgos pa'i yon tan gyi mgur dang /
NK128(nyo)001:3871: rje la dam brdar ba'i mgur dang /
NK128(nyo)001:3872: bee ro spyugs na bod phung bar 'gro ba'i mgur dang /
NK128(nyo)001:3873: btsun mo la 'khong ba'i mgur dang bcas rgya cher gsungs kyang ma zlog par 'byon par chas so //
NK128(nyo)001:3874: blon po sna chen pos rje la bshol btab kyang /
NK128(nyo)001:3875: blon po gdug pa can gyis ngo ma zlog par rje yang thabs med par gyur la /
NK128(nyo)001:3876: khyad par ta ra klu gong gis ngan kha blang
NK128(nyo)001:3877: ba'i glu blangs pas dbang med du rgyal mo tsha
NK128(nyo)001:3878: ba'i rong du spyug par chas te /
NK128(nyo)001:3879: bee ros kyang rje blon kun la tsha ba rong du 'byon pa'i mgur bzhes te /
NK128(nyo)001:3880: lha klu thams cad bskul bas kun kyang dngos gzugs
NK128(nyo)001:3881: bstan te bee ro la phyag skor byed cing bka'
NK128(nyo)001:3883: de nas mnga' bdag gis gshegs skyel /
NK128(nyo)001:3886: bsil sman sogs mang du bskur /
NK128(nyo)001:3887: rta mgrin gling nas sgor byon pa la /
NK128(nyo)001:3888: btsun mo dmar rgyan gyis ma bzod par rje la
NK128(nyo)001:3889: gros btab kyang bee ro tsha rong du 'gro don
NK128(nyo)001:3890: dus babs kyis ma bzhed par mgur gsungs /
NK128(nyo)001:3891: dge 'dun sde gnyis rje blon btsun mor bcas pas skyel thung mdzad dus mgur mang du bzhes /
NK128(nyo)001:3892: zhal ta dang chos mang du gsungs nas tsha ba'i rong du nam mkha' la 'phags te gshegs so //
NK128(nyo)001:3893: rje 'bangs kun gyis phyi phyag btsal te phyir log /
NK128(nyo)001:3894: bee ros kyang tsha ba rong du shar mar byon
NK128(nyo)001:3895: par ri rtser bzhugs pas yul mi rnams kyis rtog
NK128(nyo)001:3896: can pa byung ngo zer te sbal dong du zhag
NK128(nyo)001:3897: gsum bskyur ba la mgur gsungs pas /
NK128(nyo)001:3898: sbal dong nas phyungs te shig dong du skyur der
NK128(nyo)001:3899: zhag gsum nas shig dong nas bton te zhus lan
NK128(nyo)001:3900: mdzad cing dge slong pur na'i skyes rabs gsungs pas
NK128(nyo)001:3901: rgyal mo gru la sogs pa dad cing bshags pa
