NK128(nyo)001:3902: byas te bod kyi mnga' bdag la dam tshig gi
NK128(nyo)001:3903: chad pa yong bas lung bstan cing thugs la bcag
NK128(nyo)001:3905: der tsha ba rong gi rgyal blon rnams kyis bshams pa'i gdan dgu brtsegs kyi steng du bzhugs /
NK128(nyo)001:3906: dong rtse dang gser gyi pa tra gser phye dar
NK128(nyo)001:3907: zab la sogs pa mang du phul te bla mar
NK128(nyo)001:3908: bkur / rgyal po'i bu g.yu sgra snying po 'dul
NK128(nyo)001:3909: ba'i phyir thabs dang mgur mang du gsungs te nges
NK128(nyo)001:3910: par 'byung bar mdzad pas g.yu sgra la sogs pa
NK128(nyo)001:3911: yiid ches shing chos zhus nas rnyed bkur rgya cher
NK128(nyo)001:3912: bkur / phul lo // der bee ros bzo dang
NK128(nyo)001:3913: sman dpyad dad pa bskyed pa'i bstan bcos kyis sna
NK128(nyo)001:3914: bkur / phul lo // drangs / dkon brtsegs sogs 'bum sde lnga dang /
NK128(nyo)001:3915: sde snod gsum gyi chos nyin mo gsungs /
NK128(nyo)001:3916: mtshan mo srod la gsang sngags nang gi chos gsungs /
NK128(nyo)001:3917: de'i tshe rgyal bu g.yu sgra snying pos rta bzang
NK128(nyo)001:3918: po gser sga g.yu srab can dar yug la btags
NK128(nyo)001:3919: te man ngag gi chos zhus pas che ba'i mgur
NK128(nyo)001:3921: g.yu sgras slob dpon khrus la byon skabs chu'i rba
NK128(nyo)001:3922: gseb tu slob dpon bskyur zhing bcud la bor bas
NK128(nyo)001:3924: phag nyan byas pas slob dpon gyis rdo rje sems dpa' nam mkha' che zhal 'don du mdzad pa /
NK128(nyo)001:3925: g.yu sgras blo la zin dpe cha brkus te /
NK128(nyo)001:3926: nga la yod do zhes sdigs bskur bas kyang ma gnang bas /
NK128(nyo)001:3927: rgyal bu g.yu sgras gser dngul gyi dong rtse sogs yon phul zhing phyag skor mdzad /
NK128(nyo)001:3928: spyan chab phyungs te bka' ci gsung bsgrub par khas blangs shing zhus pas /
NK128(nyo)001:3929: snod sbyang ba'i ched du sbyang ba dgu dang phod
NK128(nyo)001:3930: pa bcu gsum gyi sgo nas snod brtag pa'i tshul
NK128(nyo)001:3931: mdzad pa'i mthar g.yu sgra rjes su bzung ngo //
NK128(nyo)001:3932: de yang drang don du thun mong ba'i ngor g.yu sgra de ltar rjes su bzung la /
NK128(nyo)001:3933: nges don du g.yu sgra ni bee ro'i grogs po legs grub kyi skye ba yin la /
NK128(nyo)001:3934: legs grub kyi skye ba snga ma de rgya gar
NK128(nyo)001:3935: gyi dge slong b+ha hu la bya ba yin te
NK128(nyo)001:3936: / khyim bdag dpal skyes bya ba'i mchod gnas yin la /
NK128(nyo)001:3937: khyim bdag gi bu mos dge slong la chags te 'khrig pa spyod par bskur ba /
NK128(nyo)001:3938: dge slong gi tshul khrims srog las gces par bzung
NK128(nyo)001:3939: ste rtse chung bcad de tshe 'phos pa legs grub
NK128(nyo)001:3940: yin la / de yang yul lho brag la pha gtsang the len tra'am theg chen /
NK128(nyo)001:3941: ma mkhar chen bza' gtum mo zhes bya ba'i bu legs grub /
NK128(nyo)001:3942: bee ro dang lhan du rgya gar la byon te
NK128(nyo)001:3943: dka' ba bcu drug lhan du spyad cing dam chos
NK128(nyo)001:3944: zhus te sngon la 'ongs pas lam du 'phrang srung
NK128(nyo)001:3945: gis bkum pa sngon gyi smon lam las rgyal mo
NK128(nyo)001:3946: tsha ba'i rong gi rgyal po'i bur skyes te /
NK128(nyo)001:3947: yab rgyal po mdo bzher nag po'am rin po che /
NK128(nyo)001:3948: yum rgyal mo mtsho rgyal ma gnyis kyi sras g.yu
NK128(nyo)001:3949: sgra snying po yin pas sngon gyi bag chags brtas
NK128(nyo)001:3950: te mngon shes dang ldan pas /
NK128(nyo)001:3951: bee ros rgyal rong du byon ma thag tu ngo shes te mgul la 'khyud nas bshums /
NK128(nyo)001:3952: sbal dong du skyur dus nam mkha' che zhal 'don
NK128(nyo)001:3953: mdzad pa tshar gcig thos pas blor zin pa sogs
NK128(nyo)001:3954: yin no // de nas bee ros g.yu sgra rgyal po yab yum la blangs pas ma phul ba /
NK128(nyo)001:3955: nor mang du gnang bas yab yum gyis phul ba chos sgor bcug /
NK128(nyo)001:3956: rgyal po 'khor bcas kyis bee ro'i bzhugs khang brtsigs
NK128(nyo)001:3957: pa slob dpon gyis lha 'dre bsdus te gyad po
NK128(nyo)001:3958: ches kyang mi 'khul ba'i rdo legs la mang bas
NK128(nyo)001:3959: phyi mchod rten nang lha khang du yod pa /
NK128(nyo)001:3960: rgya dpangs mtho ba nub gcig la tshar ba'i rdzu 'phrul bstan /
NK128(nyo)001:3961: nyin par rgyu'i chos dang sngags phyi pa gsungs pa rnams g.yu sgras tshar re las shes /
NK128(nyo)001:3962: srod la gsang sngags nang gi rgyud sde gsungs pa rnams kyang tshar res shes /
NK128(nyo)001:3963: nam gung la g.yu sgra sogs thun mong ma yin
NK128(nyo)001:3964: pa'i 'khor la man ngag skor rnams gsungs te sems
NK128(nyo)001:3965: sde'i rgyud man ngag bco brgyad /
NK128(nyo)001:3969: rgyal po'i skor sogs mang du gsungs /
NK128(nyo)001:3970: yang g.yu sgras rin po che dang dar zab mang
NK128(nyo)001:3971: du phul te phyag skor grangs med byas te gsol
NK128(nyo)001:3973: spyi rgyud man ngag dang bcas pa thams cad rdzogs
NK128(nyo)001:3974: pa'i mthar rgyal thabs spyi blugs la sogs pa'i dbang
NK128(nyo)001:3975: bdun bskur ba sogs mdor na sh+r+ai seng has bee
NK128(nyo)001:3976: ro nyid la ji ltar bstan pa bzhin rgya gsum
NK128(nyo)001:3977: gyi bar du rdzogs par mdzad /
NK128(nyo)001:3978: bskur ba rkyen gyi man ngag ni /
NK128(nyo)001:3979: byang sems rang byung kun dngos can //
NK128(nyo)001:3980: rgyal po mngon sum grub byas pa'i //
NK128(nyo)001:3982: shugs la skal ldan smin par gyis //
NK128(nyo)001:3984: der g.yu sgra snying po thams cad tshig dang bral ba'i rig pa mngon sum du gyur te /
NK128(nyo)001:3985: lo chen nyid dang dgongs pa mnyam par gyur te /
NK128(nyo)001:3986: rtogs pa dbul zhing sku drin dran pa'i tshig brjod pa /
NK128(nyo)001:3987: sgra bshad don mtshon de bcad kyis //
NK128(nyo)001:3988: brda sprad rang grol yongs ma spyad //
NK128(nyo)001:3989: bskal par 'thibs pa'i mun nag tshogs //
NK128(nyo)001:3990: yud la gsal mdzad sku drin che //
NK128(nyo)001:3992: de nas g.yu sgras rgyal mo khyi stag rong du lo lnga mnyam par bzhag /
NK128(nyo)001:3993: zag med bde ba chen po'i don rtogs te slob
NK128(nyo)001:3994: dpon gnyis dgongs pa gcig tu gyur te 'gro ba'i
NK128(nyo)001:3996: gzhan yang g+hu ru pad+mas bka' brgyad kyi dbang bskur
NK128(nyo)001:3997: zhing rje 'bangs nyer lnga'i gras g.yu sgra snying po
NK128(nyo)001:3999: zhes pa de yang yin par bshad /
NK128(nyo)001:4000: thang yig ltar na bee ro slar tsha rong nas
NK128(nyo)001:4001: byon dus kyang mnga' bdag rgyal po bzhugs par bshad
NK128(nyo)001:4002: / 'dra 'bag ltar na bee ro tsha rong du
NK128(nyo)001:4003: spyugs pas rgyal po thugs ma bde zhing bee ro'i
NK128(nyo)001:4004: che ba 'don phyir bi ma la spyan 'dren pa
NK128(nyo)001:4005: / bardzangasa / der bee ro spyugs nas zhag nyer
NK128(nyo)001:4006: gcig na blon po ta ra klu gong dam tshig
NK128(nyo)001:4008: mnga' bdag kyang bi ma la dang ma mjal bar zla ba gsum nas 'das par bshad pas /
NK128(nyo)001:4009: de dag kyang drang nges su bstan pa yin pas log par rtog par mi bya'o //
NK128(nyo)001:4010: 'di 'dra 'bag lta na bi ma la bod du
NK128(nyo)001:4011: byon nas khri srong gis sras gsum gyis zhabs nas
NK128(nyo)001:4012: btegs te chos gsungs pa'i tshe /
NK128(nyo)001:4013: bee ros g.yu sgra snying po btang ste /
NK128(nyo)001:4014: bi ma la mngon pa pra ka ra sde brgyad
NK128(nyo)001:4015: 'chad cing 'dug pa la nang du thal gyis skyon
NK128(nyo)001:4016: te bi ma lar cher gyis gzigs shing /
NK128(nyo)001:4017: ka kha pa ri mi tha gsung /
NK128(nyo)001:4018: bi ma la dbu dmad cing rda thim rda thim gsungs pa la /
NK128(nyo)001:4019: 'a khor rnams kyis sgra don zhus pa bi ma las gsungs par brten /
NK128(nyo)001:4020: dz+nya na ku m+aa ras g.yu sgra la bee ro'i tshul dris shing chos zhus pas /
NK128(nyo)001:4021: bi ma la dang mnyam du gsungs par bgros /
NK128(nyo)001:4022: bi ma la dang g.yu sgra gnyis chos kyi che
NK128(nyo)001:4023: bar 'don phyir phyag dang gdan la ma 'dums pa
NK128(nyo)001:4024: ltar mdzad cing / rig pa dang rdzu 'phrul 'gran
NK128(nyo)001:4025: pa ni g.yu sgra yang bee ro'i drin gyis g.yu
NK128(nyo)001:4027: rdzu 'phrul ni g.yu sgras byi'ura sprul te lcang ma'i
NK128(nyo)001:4028: khar tsen gyis 'phur ba bi ma las bye khrar
NK128(nyo)001:4029: sprul te khungs kyis byi chung la btab pas /
NK128(nyo)001:4030: bye chung gser gyi tho lum du gyur te nam
NK128(nyo)001:4031: mkhar 'phags pas bye khra sdong po'i phag tu yib
NK128(nyo)001:4032: dgos pa byung bas g.yu sgra lhag par byung ste
NK128(nyo)001:4033: phyag rtse sprod du byas gral g.yas g.yon byas /
NK128(nyo)001:4034: chos gsungs pas nam mkha' la dkar phyogs kyi lhas
NK128(nyo)001:4035: me tog gtor zhing gser gyi dra phyed dang sa
NK128(nyo)001:4037: ngo mtshar du gyur te man ngag gi chos rnams dus gcig tu gsungs pa /
NK128(nyo)001:4038: dz+ny+aa na ku ma ras rna ba sho brag tu nyan cing bsgyur /
NK128(nyo)001:4039: de yang g.yu sgras nam mkha' che la sogs pa
NK128(nyo)001:4040: sngar bee ros mnga' bdag la gsungs pa rnams bshad
NK128(nyo)001:4042: bi ma las rtse mo byung rgyal la sogs bcu gsum gsungs pas phyi 'gyur zhes grags shing /
NK128(nyo)001:4043: gnyis ka ma bu bzhin 'grigs pas thams cad yid ches te /
NK128(nyo)001:4044: bee ro'i yon tan brjod par byed cing tsha ba'i
NK128(nyo)001:4045: rong du kha bltas te ngu zhing phyag byas so
NK128(nyo)001:4046: // de'i tshe dz+ny+aa na ku ma ra slob dpon
NK128(nyo)001:4047: gnyis ka'i gdams ngag nga la yod pas nga las
NK128(nyo)001:4048: lhag pa med snyams te nga rgyal ba la /
NK128(nyo)001:4049: slob dpon gnyis kyis mkhyen te dz+ny+aa na ku m+aa
NK128(nyo)001:4050: ra la bum pa re gtad de gtsang chu bum
NK128(nyo)001:4051: pa re khur shog gsungs te bum pa de blangs
NK128(nyo)001:4052: nas slob dpon gnyis la phul ba dang /
NK128(nyo)001:4053: slob dpon gnyis kyis dz+ny+aa na ku m+aa ra'i phyag mthil du chu thigs re blug ste /
NK128(nyo)001:4055: sangs rgyas kyi bstan pa'i chos yar gtsang gi chu bo lta bu yin /
NK128(nyo)001:4056: nged gnyis kyi bum pa gang po 'di tsam re shes pa yin /
NK128(nyo)001:4057: khyod kyis lag mthil gyi chu thigs 'di tsam re shes pa yin gsungs pas /
NK128(nyo)001:4058: dz+ny+aa na ku m+aa ras slob dpon gnyis kyi bdag
NK128(nyo)001:4059: gi ngan rtog mngon par shes pas mkhyen 'dug snyam
NK128(nyo)001:4061: slar yang slob dpon gnyis kyis gsang sngags nang gi chos mdo sgyu sems sogs mang du gsungs shing /
NK128(nyo)001:4062: de'i tshe g.yu sgras dz+ny+aa na ku m+aa ra la man ngag gi chos yod tshul gsungs pa /
NK128(nyo)001:4063: 'di bas lhag pa med kyang mtha' mi nor 'dod
NK128(nyo)001:4064: du 'dug snyam ste log rtog skyes nas zhu lan
NK128(nyo)001:4065: phul bar / man ngag gi snod min par mkhyen
NK128(nyo)001:4066: nas sku mi snang bar gshegs pas 'gyod de mchi
NK128(nyo)001:4067: ma byung zhing gsol ba btab pas sngar bzhin byon
NK128(nyo)001:4068: te de tsam du bos nas ci byed gsungs par
NK128(nyo)001:4069: phul bar / / man ngag gi chos gnang bar gsol ba btab pas /
NK128(nyo)001:4070: sngar gyi rten 'brel cung zad 'phyugs pas skabs de
NK128(nyo)001:4071: ma gnang bar slar mjal bar gnang ste tsha ba
NK128(nyo)001:4073: snyan brgyud rdor zam ltar na g.yu sgra bod du
NK128(nyo)001:4074: gshegs shul bee ro thugs skyo ba'i tshul mdzad de
NK128(nyo)001:4075: tsha ba'i rong gi gting du zhag bcu gsum byon
NK128(nyo)001:4076: pa'i sa / rgyal mo stag rtse mkhar bya ba
NK128(nyo)001:4077: na spang mi pham mgon po lo dgu cu go
NK128(nyo)001:4078: lnga lon pa rjes su bzung ba'i lo rgyus dang
NK128(nyo)001:4079: pa'i sa / / thang yig ltar na bee ro
NK128(nyo)001:4080: slar bod du 'byon lam du spang rgan dang mjal
NK128(nyo)001:4082: 'dra 'bag ltar na g.yu sgra phyir byon pa'i lam du spang dang /
NK128(nyo)001:4083: rgya blo gros gzhon nu dang /
NK128(nyo)001:4084: sbas rdo rje rgyal mtshan rnams rjes su bzung tshul bshad pas /
NK128(nyo)001:4085: de rnams kyi lo rgyus rgyas pa 'dra 'bag ltar la /
NK128(nyo)001:4086: de nas bee ro dang g.yu sgra mjal zhing bod
NK128(nyo)001:4087: kyi lo rgyus rnams zhus pas bee ro mnyes te
NK128(nyo)001:4088: mgur gsungs / bod yul gyi rje 'bangs rnams kyang bee ro gdan 'dren par 'gros shing /
NK128(nyo)001:4089: bi ma las kyang spyan drongs shig gsungs /
NK128(nyo)001:4090: dus der 'dra 'bag ltar na mnga' bdag gshegs tshul gong du smros pa ltar dang /
NK128(nyo)001:4091: khri srong gi sras gsum yod pa'i mu tig btsan po spyugs /
NK128(nyo)001:4092: mu ne btsan po dug gis bkrongs /
NK128(nyo)001:4093: sad nas legs mjing yon gyi skabs yin pas mu
NK128(nyo)001:4094: ne btsan po'i gshin gyi 'das rjes dang chos 'khar
NK128(nyo)001:4097: thang bzang dpal gyi rdo rje /
NK128(nyo)001:4098: gsang ba dpal gyi snying po gsum bee ro gdan 'dren par mngags te byon par mjal zhing /
NK128(nyo)001:4099: 'byon par zhus pa dgyes te zhal gyis bzhes nas /
NK128(nyo)001:4100: khyed rang gsum nga 'bod mkhan yin par shes na gsod du 'ong bas sngon la bros shig /
NK128(nyo)001:4101: nga rting la 'ong gi gsungs te /
NK128(nyo)001:4102: bang phyin gsum po sngon la bardzangasa /
NK128(nyo)001:4103: rgyal mo tsha ba'i rong gi gdul bya rnams la
NK128(nyo)001:4104: nga bod du 'gro bas chos gang dgos nyan pa
NK128(nyo)001:4105: dang / the tshom chod cig gsungs te chos 'phro rnams rdzogs par mdzad /
NK128(nyo)001:4106: bod du chas pas rgyal mo gru la sogs pas gser g.yu dar zab gshegs skyems phul /
NK128(nyo)001:4107: phyag btsal mchi ma phyungs te bzhugs par zhu don mang du phul yang /
NK128(nyo)001:4108: zhus lan gyi mgur mang po gsungs /
NK128(nyo)001:4111: chibs rta sogs phebs rdzongs su btab /
NK128(nyo)001:4112: zhal ta gnang bar zhus pa bzhin zhal gdams dang lan gcig 'byon par zhal gyis bzhes te /
NK128(nyo)001:4113: spang sangs rgyas mgon po chos ston gyi sku tshab tu bzhag go //
NK128(nyo)001:4114: der rgyal mo tsha ba'i rong pa rnams kyis nor sna tshogs phul ba gzhan rnams phyir slog cing /
NK128(nyo)001:4117: bla g.yu 'od 'bar rnams bsnams te byon /
NK128(nyo)001:4118: khong rnams kyis la thog tu skyel thung mdzad cing phyag bskor phul /
NK128(nyo)001:4119: zhabs spyi bor blangs te byin rlabs zhus shing /
NK128(nyo)001:4120: bee ro dang g.yu sgra gnyis glog 'khyugs pa ltar bod yul phyogs su nam mkha' la gshegs shing /
NK128(nyo)001:4121: yul mi thams cad kyi phyi phyag dang smon lam
NK128(nyo)001:4122: rgya cher btab ste rang yul du log bod nas
NK128(nyo)001:4123: spyan 'dren mi gsum ni bee ro dang dus mnyam
NK128(nyo)001:4124: du ma sleb na mi 'ong bas bee ro phyi
NK128(nyo)001:4125: nas 'byon snyams ste dal 'gros kyis phyin /
NK128(nyo)001:4126: lo chen dpon slob rdzu 'phrul gyi mthus skad cig
NK128(nyo)001:4127: la bsam yas mchims phu'i yang dben du phebs te
NK128(nyo)001:4129: de'i tshe lha sras mu ne btsan po'i gshin gyi
NK128(nyo)001:4130: chos 'khor dang thug ste pan+di ta bi ma la
NK128(nyo)001:4131: dang / lo ts+aa ba gnyags dz+ny+aa na ku m+aa gnyis kyis tshogs dpon mdzad de /
NK128(nyo)001:4132: mi mang po 'tshog gi yod pa'i tshe /
NK128(nyo)001:4133: ban de khro chu'i me stag phrom phrom byed pa gnyis byung nas su yin zer te /
NK128(nyo)001:4134: dz+ny+aa na ku ma ras bltas pas /
NK128(nyo)001:4135: lo chen dpon slob yin par ngo shes te phyag btsal /
NK128(nyo)001:4136: rje blon rnams la byon par bsgrags /
NK128(nyo)001:4137: pan+di ta bi ma la dang lo ts+aa ba chen
NK128(nyo)001:4138: po bee ro tsa na gnyis kyis phyag dang zhe
NK128(nyo)001:4140: mkhas btsun rnams dang dge 'dun sde gnyis rgyal blon rnams kyis kyang phyag 'tshal zhing /
NK128(nyo)001:4141: rang rang gi rgyan gos gser g.yu rta la sogs
NK128(nyo)001:4142: pa hab thob tu phul bas zas nor gyi phung
NK128(nyo)001:4143: po bee ro'i drung du ri spungs pa ltar byung
NK128(nyo)001:4144: sngar gyi gdan 'dren mi gsum yang slebs so //
NK128(nyo)001:4145: de nas zas gos la sogs pa de rnams la khri chen po bshams te /
NK128(nyo)001:4146: gung gral du bee ro bzhugs g.yas g.yon du bi
NK128(nyo)001:4147: ma dang g.yu sgra gnyis khri chung ngu re la
NK128(nyo)001:4148: bzhugs pa'i drung du thams cad 'dus te /
NK128(nyo)001:4149: mchi ma phyungs shing phyag 'tshal ba dang /
NK128(nyo)001:4154: rol mo sna tshogs brdung zhing 'khrol ba dang /
NK128(nyo)001:4155: glu len bro gar shon la sogs byed cing thams
NK128(nyo)001:4156: cad dga' zhing tshigs su bcad pas kyang bstod par
NK128(nyo)001:4157: byed de / der bi ma la dang bee ro gnyis kyi dgongs pa mdzad /
NK128(nyo)001:4158: g.yu sgra dang dz+ny+aa na ku m+aa ra sogs kyis las byas te rje mu ne'i gshin ston mdzad /
NK128(nyo)001:4159: chos grwa btsugs te chos kyi 'khor lo rgya cher bskor /
NK128(nyo)001:4160: khyad par bee ro tsa nas chos gsung pa'i dus su nam mkha' la 'ja' tshon sna tshogs dang /
NK128(nyo)001:4161: lha tshogs mang pos lha'i me tog sna tshogs 'thor
NK128(nyo)001:4162: zhing sa g.yo ba sogs ngo mtshar mang du byung
NK128(nyo)001:4163: ba la thams cad dad pa skyes shing sngar spyugs
NK128(nyo)001:4164: pa la 'gyod bshags kyi longs spyod sna tshogs 'bul
NK128(nyo)001:4165: zhing ngus te spyugs pa la brten pa'i snyun 'dri
NK128(nyo)001:4166: zhing rgyu mtshan rmed pa la /
NK128(nyo)001:4168: 'di na 'tshogs pa'i mkhas btsun sde gnyis dang /
NK128(nyo)001:4169: zhes sogs kyi mgur mang du bzhes so //
NK128(nyo)001:4170: der chos 'khor grub nas bod du spyi sgos kyi chos dang zhal gdams mang du gsungs shing /
NK128(nyo)001:4171: 'dra 'bag ltar na bee ro dang g.yu sgra gnyis
NK128(nyo)001:4172: slar yang rgyal mo tsha ba'i rong du lan gcig
NK128(nyo)001:4173: 'byon par zhal gyis bzhes pa bzhin gshegs te /
NK128(nyo)001:4174: bod nas gshegs skyems phul zhing zhal ta mang du
NK128(nyo)001:4175: gsungs nas tsha ba'i rong du byon te rgyal blon
NK128(nyo)001:4176: rnams dang mjal zhing chos kyi bgro ba mdzad /
NK128(nyo)001:4177: slar yang mdo khams su yar byon /
NK128(nyo)001:4178: der yang pan+di ta bi ma la yang spyan drangs te /
NK128(nyo)001:4179: khams kyi rung byams chen gyi yang dben du bi
NK128(nyo)001:4180: ma las pan+di ta dang bee ros lo chen mdzad
NK128(nyo)001:4181: de yang dag la sogs pa'i rgyud sde mang du
NK128(nyo)001:4182: bsgyur / de nas brgyud pa snga phyi bar gsum gyi chos rnams kyang de skabs byung bar grags /
NK128(nyo)001:4183: slar yang bod du byon nas has po ri'i brtser dgongs pa la bzhugs shing /
NK128(nyo)001:4184: 'khor thun mong ba rnams la drang don gyi chos 'ga' zhig gsung ba dang /
NK128(nyo)001:4185: snga 'gyur gyi mjug ma tshangs pa 'ga' zhig kyang bsgyur /
NK128(nyo)001:4186: thun mong ma yin pa'i gdul bya rnams la man
NK128(nyo)001:4187: ngag rdzogs pa chen po'i chos gsungs pa sogs mdzad
NK128(nyo)001:4188: cing bzhugs / de'i tshe li yul lcang ra smug
NK128(nyo)001:4189: po nas sngar rgya gar nas tshur lam rjes su
NK128(nyo)001:4190: bzung ba'i li tsha tshul khrims sgron yang mjal bar
NK128(nyo)001:4191: byon zhing dgongs pa mnyam par gyur nas dgyes so
NK128(nyo)001:4192: cing bzhugs / // de nas bee ro nyid yun gyi dgongs pa la gshegs par dgongs pa'i tshe /
NK128(nyo)001:4193: 'khor rnams la gdams ngag zhal thems mang du bzhag cing /
NK128(nyo)001:4194: g.yu sgra dang mnga' bdag rje blon rnams kyi ngor
NK128(nyo)001:4195: 'dra 'bag chen mo dkar chag tu btab ste gnang
NK128(nyo)001:4196: nas / 'dra 'bag ltar na li tsha tshul khrims
NK128(nyo)001:4197: sgron dang lhan du glog 'khyug pa ltar li yul
NK128(nyo)001:4198: du gshegs te yun gyi dgongs pa la bzhugs nas
NK128(nyo)001:4199: nas / / mthar sprul pa rnam par snang mdzad kyi thugs kar bsdus so zhes grags la /
NK128(nyo)001:4200: snyan brgyud rdor zam ltar na bsam yas nas sgrags yang rdzong gi rtse la gshegs te /
NK128(nyo)001:4201: bdag nyid bee ro tsa na mchis pa 'di //
NK128(nyo)001:4202: sgyu ma lta bu'i phung po yis //
NK128(nyo)001:4203: sgyu ma lta bu'i chos byas nas //
NK128(nyo)001:4204: sgyu ma lta bur mngon 'tshang rgya zhes gsungs te 'od kyi phung por gshegs so //
NK128(nyo)001:4206: deng sang yang rdzong na bee ro 'od lus su gshegs pa'i phug pa yang yod do //
NK128(nyo)001:4207: mdor na rlung sems la rang dbang thob cing ye
NK128(nyo)001:4208: shes sgyu ma'i sku 'ja' lus 'pho ba chen por
NK128(nyo)001:4209: mnga' brnyes pa'i bsam gyis mi khyab pa'i rnam thar
NK128(nyo)001:4210: yin pas sprul pa du mar bkye bsdu mdzad pa'i
NK128(nyo)001:4211: tshul la mtha' gcig tu ngos bzung mi bya bar
NK128(nyo)001:4212: gus par bya ba gces so //
NK128(nyo)001:4213: de yang lo ts+aa ba chen po bee ro tsa
NK128(nyo)001:4214: na 'di nyid bka' drin 'gran zla dang bral bar
NK128(nyo)001:4215: yin pa'i phyir / 'di nyid kyi rnam par thar pa thang yig /'dra 'bag /
NK128(nyo)001:4216: snyan brgyud rdor zam sogs las btus te bris pa cung zad mang ba tsam byung yang /
NK128(nyo)001:4217: sku drin dran pa'i phyir dang dad gus kyi gsos
NK128(nyo)001:4218: btab pa'i phyir bkod pas drin lan du dam pa'i
NK128(nyo)001:4221: mang thos mchog gyur 'phags pa kun dga' bo //
NK128(nyo)001:4222: bod yul bstan 'gro'i don du legs sprul pa //
NK128(nyo)001:4223: nges pa don gyi ma h+aa pan+di ta //
NK128(nyo)001:4224: sprul pa'i lo chen bee ro lan brgyar bstod //
NK128(nyo)001:4225: 'phags yul thub bstan rgya mtsho chen po las //
NK128(nyo)001:4226: rgyu dang 'bras bu'i dam chos yid bzhin nor //
NK128(nyo)001:4227: blangs te mun gling 'gro ba'i dbul sel mkhan //
NK128(nyo)001:4228: spa gor gan jag thang ta'i yon tan dran //
NK128(nyo)001:4229: theg mchog bstan pa'i snying po rdzogs pa che //
NK128(nyo)001:4230: bsam 'phel 'dod dgu 'byung ba'i yid bzhin dbang //
NK128(nyo)001:4231: bstan 'gro'i rgyal mtshan rtse mor legs bkod nas //
NK128(nyo)001:4232: ma lus gdod ma'i gzhi la khyod kyis drangs //
NK128(nyo)001:4233: lus dang srog la gces pa brgyags bsrings te //
NK128(nyo)001:4234: bcu drug dka' ba spyad de yongs 'dzin bsten //
NK128(nyo)001:4235: mdo sngags dam chos ma lus bod bsgyur ba'i //
NK128(nyo)001:4236: bka' drin bsam na snying nas mchi ma dku //
NK128(nyo)001:4237: khyod thugs snying stobs brnag par dka' ba yis //
NK128(nyo)001:4238: lus srog ltos med btsal ba'i snga 'gyur chos //
NK128(nyo)001:4239: deng sang la la log chos yin zhes sgrogs //
NK128(nyo)001:4240: yid ches ldan yang bstan la 'jug pa nyung //
NK128(nyo)001:4241: zhugs kyang 'od la rdo rje snying po yi //
NK128(nyo)001:4242: ka dag lhun grub bshad bsgrub mi brtson par //
NK128(nyo)001:4243: grong chog bsgrub dang ngan sngags kho na yis //
NK128(nyo)001:4244: tshe 'di'i 'dun thag bsgrub mthong snying nas skyo //
NK128(nyo)001:4245: de phyiir mgon khyod rnam thar nya rgyas zla //
NK128(nyo)001:4246: bdag sems dad pa'i yid mtshor gsal mod kyang //
NK128(nyo)001:4247: bka' drin rjes su dran phyir cha shas tsam //
NK128(nyo)001:4248: blo gsal gus pa bskyed phyir yi ger spel //
NK128(nyo)001:4249: dge 'dis mgon po khyod kyi spang rtogs kun //
NK128(nyo)001:4250: bdag sogs rgyud la 'pho ba'i skal thob nas //
NK128(nyo)001:4251: snga 'gyur bstan la bshad dang sgrub pa yis //
NK128(nyo)001:4252: khyod dgongs chos kyi dbyings su rdzogs byed shog /
NK128(nyo)001:4253: ces pa yang bar skabs kyi tshigs su bcad pa'o //
NK128(nyo)001:4254: de ltar lo chen bee ro tsa na dang rgyal
NK128(nyo)001:4255: mo g.yu sgra snying po'i rnam thar thun mong du
NK128(nyo)001:4256: brjod zin la / g.yu sgra snying pos gnyags dz+ny+aa
NK128(nyo)001:4257: na ku m+aa ra ste ye shes gzhon nu la
NK128(nyo)001:4258: yul mchims phu brag dkar ram brag dge 'ur gsungs
NK128(nyo)001:4259: brjod zin la / / phra men gyis yol skyong
NK128(nyo)001:4260: chang gis bkang ba dang g.yu stong ri ba phul
NK128(nyo)001:4261: brjod zin la / / / gsang mtshan dri med
NK128(nyo)001:4262: zla shar rtsal lam rdo rje grub pa'i gter ram
NK128(nyo)001:4263: brjod zin la / / / / rdo rje bzhad pa'i gter /
NK128(nyo)001:4264: thig le gshog rgod rtsal du yang grags te rig 'dzin sa la gshegs so //
NK128(nyo)001:4265: slob dpon 'di'i rnam thar cung zad brjod na /
NK128(nyo)001:4269: ma sum bza' blo gros kyi sras su 'khrungs /
NK128(nyo)001:4270: mgrin pa na rme ba'i rdo rje rgya gram yod pa /
NK128(nyo)001:4271: sa drug non pa'i byang chub sems dpa' chen po yin te /
NK128(nyo)001:4272: mi chos kyi mtshan rgyal ba blo gros zhes par grags so //
NK128(nyo)001:4273: de yang lo rgyus la lar dz+ny+aa na ku m+aa
NK128(nyo)001:4274: ra 'phyong rgyas 'phyos pa yin par gsungs 'dug cing
NK128(nyo)001:4276: 'phyos kyi gnyag chen dz+ny+aa na ku m+aa ra /
NK128(nyo)001:4277: zhes 'byung bas na 'phyong rgyas 'phyogs sogs yar klungs kyi nang tshan yin pas mi 'gal /
NK128(nyo)001:4278: thang yig ltar na bod du mkhan chen bo d+hi sa t+wa gdan 'dren pa po yang yin la /
NK128(nyo)001:4279: mkhan chen de nyid las rab tu byung zhing bsnyen par rdzogs /
NK128(nyo)001:4280: sgra tshad mtshan nyid sngags phyi nang kun la mkhas shing /
NK128(nyo)001:4281: slob dpon chen po pad+ma dang bi ma la /
NK128(nyo)001:4283: g.yu sgra sogs mkhas grub mang po'i zhabs la gtugs /
NK128(nyo)001:4284: khyad par slob dpon chen po pad+mas sgrub pa bka'
NK128(nyo)001:4285: brgyad kyi dkyil 'khor du dbang bskur bas che mchog
NK128(nyo)001:4287: grub mtshan yar klungs shel brag las bdud rtsi'i chu
NK128(nyo)001:4288: rgyun 'don par mdzad cing rje 'bangs nyer lnga'i gras
NK128(nyo)001:4289: su gyur / khyad par phur pa'i grub pa brnyes pa'i lo rgyus 'di ltar yang snang ste /
NK128(nyo)001:4290: mnga' bdag khri srong lde'u btsan sku 'das nas btsun
NK128(nyo)001:4291: mo dmar rgyan dbang che zhing ngan spyod kyi lo
NK128(nyo)001:4293: lo pan phal cher bas matha'i dben par brten dgos byung bas na /
NK128(nyo)001:4294: gnyags kyang yar 'brog phyogs su bzhugs skabs /
NK128(nyo)001:4295: rang gi pha spun gnyags dge ston dgrar langs te
NK128(nyo)001:4296: 'di ni mu stegs kyi sngags mkhan yin no zer
NK128(nyo)001:4298: b+han d+ha nang dmar po yod pa brkus nas gri rtses 'dred cing mi rnams la ston /
NK128(nyo)001:4299: zog 'di 'dra byed do zer ya ga sgrog /
NK128(nyo)001:4300: slob dpon bkrong zhing dben pa bshigs pa'i ngan gros bshams pas /
NK128(nyo)001:4301: de dgongs te gang du bzhugs sar rin po che
NK128(nyo)001:4302: gtor zhing bzhag pas mi rnams kyi rdzu 'phrul 'di
NK128(nyo)001:4303: 'dra bas khyed mi bden byas kyang mi nyan par
NK128(nyo)001:4304: b+han d+ha 'drad cing ston pa sogs byung bas /
NK128(nyo)001:4305: yur der ma bzhugs par g.yog zhig khrid nas kong
NK128(nyo)001:4306: po mchims yul gyi gting du byon pas lung stong
NK128(nyo)001:4307: zhig na ra ma bdun 'dug pa ded 'gro gsungs
NK128(nyo)001:4308: pas / g.yog gis bdag po yod dam zer /
NK128(nyo)001:4309: slob dpon gyi lung stong gi ra la bdag po
NK128(nyo)001:4310: ga na yod gsungs te ded pa mchims bya rog
NK128(nyo)001:4311: ces bya ba'i ra yin pas /
NK128(nyo)001:4312: khos mthong ste rkun khag btsugs /
NK128(nyo)001:4313: bdun mjal sprad kyang ma nyan par dben par bshig lcags thos ded slob dpon gyis sgo bcad pas /
NK128(nyo)001:4314: sgo'i ya them la lcags tho rgyab ste /
NK128(nyo)001:4315: btsun chung gi mgo la lcags tho thob zer /
NK128(nyo)001:4316: de yang ma chags par dbus su byon pas /
NK128(nyo)001:4317: 'bro sras chung bya ba sha ba gcig ded nas byung ba dang /
NK128(nyo)001:4319: kho'i rta 'grogs sha ba shor bas kho khros te
NK128(nyo)001:4320: gsod du byung ba la bros pas thar ba tsam
NK128(nyo)001:4321: byung skad / de'i tshe bsam yas su lha sras
NK128(nyo)001:4322: mu ne'i dgongs rdzogs kyi tshogs dbur bi ma la
NK128(nyo)001:4323: byon pa dang mjal nas gser phye long mo gang
NK128(nyo)001:4325: lo ts+aa ba dpon g.yog skyid dam gsungs pa la /
NK128(nyo)001:4327: yar 'brog sgang du skyid bgyi ru //
NK128(nyo)001:4328: dge la ston gyis sa ma ster ro //
NK128(nyo)001:4329: mchims yul gting du skyid bgyi ru //
NK128(nyo)001:4330: bya rog dmyal ba'i ma ster ro //
NK128(nyo)001:4331: bod yul dbus su skyid bgyi ru //
NK128(nyo)001:4332: 'brog sras chung gis ma ster ro //
NK128(nyo)001:4334: bi ma las lo ts+aa bar brnyas na bstan pa nub kyis dgongs nas phur pa'i chos skor gnang /
NK128(nyo)001:4335: lho brag g.yar chu sna'i brag phug tu bi ma
NK128(nyo)001:4336: la dang lo pan lhan cig seng phur nyer gcig
NK128(nyo)001:4338: phur bu 'khrol ba sogs grub mtshan byung bar gnyags kyis phur pa blangs te sgril zhing /
NK128(nyo)001:4339: bya rog la'o byas pas stong khams kyi bya rog mang po 'dus byung ba la /
NK128(nyo)001:4340: mchims bya rog la'o byas pas /
NK128(nyo)001:4341: mchiims yul gyi bya rog zung zhig byung bas gnyags
NK128(nyo)001:4342: khros nas bya rog gcig la 'debs par brtsams pa
NK128(nyo)001:4344: der bi ma las slong gsungs pa la slong ma thub pas /
NK128(nyo)001:4345: bi ma las bye ma cig btab pas gsos nas
NK128(nyo)001:4346: btang ste da phyin de ltar ma byed sdig che'o
NK128(nyo)001:4347: gsungs nas / gnas lung gi cho ga de la brten te gnang /
NK128(nyo)001:4348: de nas mchims lha g.yag dkar zhig tu sprul te byung ba yang phur pa btab ste bsgral /
NK128(nyo)001:4349: mchims bya rog kyang skabs der bsgral /
NK128(nyo)001:4350: bla spyang rab 'bring tha gsum bran khol /
NK128(nyo)001:4353: snag gi gnyen mtshams yan chod la btab pas rabs chad de brtul lo //
NK128(nyo)001:4354: de nas pha spun gnyags dge ston la btab pas
NK128(nyo)001:4355: gnyags nyid snying rje skyes shing chos nyid kyi klong
NK128(nyo)001:4356: du gyur pas ye ma thebs te /
NK128(nyo)001:4357: bi ma la grogs mtshan ldan zhig rnyed na thebs te 'ong gsungs pas /
NK128(nyo)001:4358: sog po dpal ye dang 'o bran dpal gyi gzhon
NK128(nyo)001:4359: nu rnyed de dpon slob gsum gyis sgrub pa byas
NK128(nyo)001:4360: te pha spun dge ston bsgral /
NK128(nyo)001:4361: slar yang sog po dpal yes gnyags dge ston gyi
NK128(nyo)001:4362: rtsar phyin nas kho shi 'dug pa'i snying bton nas
NK128(nyo)001:4364: sdig pa ci yang mi bya zhing //
NK128(nyo)001:4365: dge ba phun sum tshogs par spyod //
NK128(nyo)001:4366: rang gi sems ni yongs su 'dul //
NK128(nyo)001:4367: sems can thams cad bde gyur cig /
NK128(nyo)001:4368: kun kyang gnod pa rnams dang bral //
NK128(nyo)001:4369: zhes gsungs shing bde chen gyi sar gnas spar /
NK128(nyo)001:4370: gnyags lha bya khrar sprul te byung ba yang bsgral /
NK128(nyo)001:4371: sngar bzhin bla spyang bran khol /
NK128(nyo)001:4374: gnyen tshun chad bsgral zhing gnas spar ro //
NK128(nyo)001:4375: de nas 'bro sras chung ne thang zhig na rta phyugs 'tsho ba la /
NK128(nyo)001:4376: rnam shes ling ga la bkug phur pa btab ste bsgral /
NK128(nyo)001:4377: 'bro lha spyang kir byung ba dang /
NK128(nyo)001:4381: gnyen mtshams kyi bar du phur pa btab ste bsgral nas rnam shes chos dbyings su spar ro //
NK128(nyo)001:4382: de ltar ngo bo chos dbyings 'od gsal rdzogs pa
NK128(nyo)001:4383: chen po las ma g.yos bzhin du mdangs rtsal lhun
NK128(nyo)001:4384: grub sgyu ma lha'i skur bzhengs te /
NK128(nyo)001:4385: 'phrin las drag pos gdul bya rnams tshar bcad de bde chen gyi sar bkod pa dang /
NK128(nyo)001:4386: lo ts+aa ba chen po'i tshul bzung ste dam pa'i chos bsgyur ba dang /
NK128(nyo)001:4387: nyan bshad kyi sgo nas slob ma bskrun pa dang /
NK128(nyo)001:4389: dz+ny+aa na ku m+aa ra rdzu 'phrul chen po ston zhes dang /
NK128(nyo)001:4390: ku m+aa ra dza rdzu 'phrul mchog dang ldan /
NK128(nyo)001:4392: rdzu 'phrul sna tshogs kyis kyang 'gro ba 'dul zhing mthar 'od phung chen por gshegs so //
NK128(nyo)001:4393: des sog po dpal gyi ye shes la yar klungs shel brag tu gsungs /
NK128(nyo)001:4394: yon du bla ma'i sku dgra lan gsum bsgral /
NK128(nyo)001:4395: thugs lam gsum bzung zhing mnyes par byas /
NK128(nyo)001:4396: gsang mtshan rdo rje bzhad pa'i gter ram khyung gshog
NK128(nyo)001:4397: rtsal du grags te rig 'dzin gyi sa la gshegs
NK128(nyo)001:4398: so // 'di'i lo rgyus zur tsam brjod na /
NK128(nyo)001:4402: ma 'bro bza' sman ne'i bu ming stag sbyin zer zhing /
NK128(nyo)001:4403: la lar stag zil zer ba yang 'dug /
NK128(nyo)001:4404: de skabs mgar ba la sog po zer bas sog
NK128(nyo)001:4405: po mtshan mgor yong ba'i rgyu mtshan de yin par
NK128(nyo)001:4406: grags / de yang gong du bshad pa ltar dz+ny+aa
NK128(nyo)001:4407: na ku m+aa ra'i sku dgra bar pa pha spun
NK128(nyo)001:4408: sgrol skabs grogs phur pa'i mtshan ldan zhig dgos pa
NK128(nyo)001:4410: sog pos shing khur cig khur ra zhing khrid pa dang phrad khyod su yin gsungs /
NK128(nyo)001:4411: ming rus rnams zhus pas phur pa'i mtshan dang ldan par mkhyen te /
NK128(nyo)001:4412: de yang mig 'bur gyen du 'khyil ba /
NK128(nyo)001:4416: ro stod zur brgyad du 'dug pa /
NK128(nyo)001:4418: ci la yang thogs pa med par gzigs nas de'i
NK128(nyo)001:4419: phyi bzhin byon pas kho mgar byed cing 'dug pa
NK128(nyo)001:4420: la / khab nag brdungs gnyis slob dpon gyii mid pas kho dad pa skyes /
NK128(nyo)001:4421: khyod kyi chos nus sam gsungs pas /
NK128(nyo)001:4423: nang par kho'i rtsar ban de zhig byung ba la
NK128(nyo)001:4424: khos kam pa'i kha tsag cig rgyab pas a tsha
NK128(nyo)001:4426: mdang gi ban de ni khab kyang mid /
NK128(nyo)001:4427: khyod ni a tsha zer ci nyes zer zhing dgod de /
NK128(nyo)001:4428: der slob dpon gyis kho'i chung ma la barngana pa byin nas chos byed par gros thob cig gsungs /
NK128(nyo)001:4429: slar yang kho rang la chos bya'am gsungs pas /
NK128(nyo)001:4430: chung ma la dri'o zer nas dris pas /
NK128(nyo)001:4432: chos mi bya ba'i thabs gar yod chos gser srang khri tshos mi khugs zer gros btab /
NK128(nyo)001:4433: der chos sgor 'jug pa la yo byad med zer
NK128(nyo)001:4434: ba yang slob dpon gyi byin pas kho mchog tu
NK128(nyo)001:4435: dad par gyur te rab tu byung /
NK128(nyo)001:4436: chos ming lha dpal ye shes su btags shing bcom
NK128(nyo)001:4437: ldan 'das rdo rje gzhon nu'i dkyil 'khor du dbang
NK128(nyo)001:4438: bskur zhing sgrub pa'i grogs byas te gdug pa can
NK128(nyo)001:4439: bsgral ba sogs snga ma ltar yin la /
NK128(nyo)001:4440: sa la non pa'i byang chub sems dpa' yin par grags /
NK128(nyo)001:4441: lo rgyus 'ga' zhig tu yul nya 'khor gyi mda'
NK128(nyo)001:4442: mar zhes par gnyags dang dam ra pha spun gyi
NK128(nyo)001:4444: chos rgyal bzhugs dus gnyags mchod gnas lo ts+aa ba yin pas rtsod ma nus /
NK128(nyo)001:4445: phyis gong du bshad pa ltar btsun mo dmar rgyan
NK128(nyo)001:4446: dus lo ts+aa ba rnams dbu 'phangs dma' ba la
NK128(nyo)001:4447: / dam ras slob dpon gnyags btson du bzung ba
NK128(nyo)001:4448: la sog po dpal yes lus srog la ma bltas
NK128(nyo)001:4449: par btson srungs pa gnyis bkum nas slob dpon gnyags
NK128(nyo)001:4450: btson nang nas bton pa'i zhal tog bsgrub par bshad
NK128(nyo)001:4451: / / gang ltar bla ma'i sku dgra lan gsum btul ba dang /
NK128(nyo)001:4452: thugs lan gsum bzung ba sogs bshad phyir lo rgyus 'di dag kyang don la gnas par shes /
NK128(nyo)001:4453: yang se lugs kyi lo rgyus mi 'dra ba zhig
NK128(nyo)001:4454: na 'khrungs yul ming rus sogs dang gnyags dge ston
NK128(nyo)001:4455: sgrol ba'i sgrub grogs dgongs pa byung ba'i bar sngar
NK128(nyo)001:4456: dang 'dra ba la sog po nyid rjes su bzung
NK128(nyo)001:4457: tshul dang pha spun bsgral tshul mi 'dra ba 'di
NK128(nyo)001:4458: ltar snang ste / mtshan rtags kyang dpral ba na
NK128(nyo)001:4459: skra kham pa tshom zhig yod pa smin mas khebs
NK128(nyo)001:4460: ltar snang ste / pa / so dung so 'khor mar yod pa /
NK128(nyo)001:4462: ya rkan gyi dkyil na so yod pa /
NK128(nyo)001:4463: lce rtses sna rtser sleb pa'i snod ldan du gzigs nas /
NK128(nyo)001:4464: kho mgar bzo byed pa'i rtsar gnyags kyis bzhugs te
NK128(nyo)001:4465: sbud pa 'bud grogs mdzad kyin mtshan nyid kyi chos
NK128(nyo)001:4466: bshad pas / kho'i rna lam du ma byung skad /
NK128(nyo)001:4467: kri yog sde gsum bshad pas skabs re nyan cing yang thob chem chem brdung gin gda' skad /
NK128(nyo)001:4468: nang rgyud sde gsum bshad pas kho sems yengs te
NK128(nyo)001:4469: khos lcags kyi lcug ma bsnyor pa thams cad slob
NK128(nyo)001:4470: dpon gyis khong par mid par khos ma mtshor tshes
NK128(nyo)001:4471: 'phro bcad pas lcug ma ma rnyed nas ban de
NK128(nyo)001:4473: slob dpon gyis hag ces bskyugs pas khab mig dang
NK128(nyo)001:4474: zhun thar sogs kho rang gis byas pa bas kyang
NK128(nyo)001:4475: legs par sngo phung ste byung bas /
NK128(nyo)001:4476: kho ya mtshan skyes te 'di lta bu'i rdzu 'phrul ci las byung zer /
NK128(nyo)001:4477: da lta bshad pa'i chos rnams nyams su blangs pa las byung gsungs pas /
NK128(nyo)001:4478: kho dad pa skyes nas mgar ba'i lag cha thams
NK128(nyo)001:4479: cad phul zhing slob mar byas pa de la man
NK128(nyo)001:4480: ngag gi chos rnams rdzogs par gnang zhing /
NK128(nyo)001:4481: khong dpon slob kyis phur pa bsgrubs pas pha spun dge ston gyis tshor /
NK128(nyo)001:4482: ban d+he dz+ny+aa na ku ma ras sog po grogs
NK128(nyo)001:4483: su khrid de mthu bsgrub kyi yod 'dug pas gsod
NK128(nyo)001:4485: yul pa rnams kyis ban d+he la brnyes mi rung zer bkag kyang ma nyan /
NK128(nyo)001:4486: phar 'gro rgyu'i nub mo dge ston gyi rmi lam
NK128(nyo)001:4487: du bud med na chung mang bos kho'i mtha' bskor
NK128(nyo)001:4488: / mi mang pos g.yog byas te lha khang zhig
NK128(nyo)001:4489: tu khrid nas mgo bo bcad de 'od lnga'i khang
NK128(nyo)001:4490: par bcug par rmis nas chung ma la rmi lam
NK128(nyo)001:4491: / bzlas pas / chung mas bshol yang ma nyan
NK128(nyo)001:4492: par rta bzang po cig zhon nas sgrub khang gi
NK128(nyo)001:4493: / bzlas pas / sgor phyin te / gtor stegs
NK128(nyo)001:4494: zhig 'dug pas de la rta btags te bzhag nang
NK128(nyo)001:4495: du phyin nas bsad do snyams ma thag gtor stegs
NK128(nyo)001:4496: kyi rtsa nas bya chen po zhig 'phur te byung
NK128(nyo)001:4497: bas kho'i rta 'grogs te lhung nas sha kham khrag
NK128(nyo)001:4498: thig rer gyur te srung mas dngos su bsgral skad
NK128(nyo)001:4499: / bzlas pas / sgor phyin te / do //
NK128(nyo)001:4500: de ltar sku dgra bsgral bas bla ma'i thugs zin
NK128(nyo)001:4501: pa la brten nas bcom ldan 'das dpal chen po
NK128(nyo)001:4502: rdo rje gzhon nu'i zhal mngon sum du bstan zhing
NK128(nyo)001:4503: / bzlas pas / sgor phyin te / do //
NK128(nyo)001:4504: dbang bskur / sa lnga'i byang chub sems dpa' gyur
NK128(nyo)001:4505: par bshad pas lo rgyus 'di rnams 'chad tshul mi
NK128(nyo)001:4506: 'dra tsam yod pa grub thob kyi rnam thar babs
NK128(nyo)001:4507: / bzlas pas / sgor phyin te / do //
NK128(nyo)001:4508: dbang bskur / su 'dug la / khog gcig pas
NK128(nyo)001:4510: khyad par slob dpon pad+mas rje 'bangs nyer lnga la
NK128(nyo)001:4511: sgrub chen bka' brgyad kyi dkyil 'khor du dbang bskur
NK128(nyo)001:4512: ba'i tshe dbang dus su rtogs pa brnyes te grub
NK128(nyo)001:4513: mtshan yang / sog po lha dpal gcan gzan gnya' nas 'dzin /
NK128(nyo)001:4514: zhes grags pa de yin la /
NK128(nyo)001:4515: mthar zag med 'od gsal gyi phung por gshegs so //
NK128(nyo)001:4516: des gnubs sangs rgyas ye shes rin po che la grwa'i sman rgang du gsungs so //
NK128(nyo)001:4517: de dag ni rgya gar ba'i brgyud lugs gsum pa
NK128(nyo)001:4518: a ti yo ga'i brgyud pa gsum ldan bshad pa'i
NK128(nyo)001:4519: skabs so // yo ga gsum gyi rgya gar ba'i brgyud tshul dngos gzhi des tshang yang /
NK128(nyo)001:4520: slob dpon dz+ny+aa na ku m+aa ra la dbang gi chu bo babs tshul bzhi /
NK128(nyo)001:4521: gtad rgya gsang mtshan gyi lo rgyus kyi yig rnying las 'di ltar 'byung ste /
NK128(nyo)001:4522: rdzogs chen a ti yo ga'i brgyud lugs bshad ma
NK128(nyo)001:4523: thag pa ltar g.yu sgra la brgyud pa ni rig
NK128(nyo)001:4524: pa rtsal dbang ste dbang gi chu bo dang po'o
NK128(nyo)001:4525: // slob dpon chen po pad+ma 'byung gnas rdo rje
NK128(nyo)001:4526: thod phreng rtsal gyis mnga' bdag khri srong lde'u btsan
NK128(nyo)001:4527: gtso bor gyur pa'i rje 'bangs nyer lnga la mchims
NK128(nyo)001:4528: phu rdza gnyis dge ba'i dben rtsar dbang bskur /
NK128(nyo)001:4529: de'i nang nas ngan lam rgyal ba mchog dbyangs kyis
NK128(nyo)001:4530: lha sa yer pa'i phug tu gnyags la dbang bskur
NK128(nyo)001:4531: zhing gzi'i blugs ma dang 'dod yon lnga phul nas
NK128(nyo)001:4532: dbang bskur / gsang mtshan rdo rje grub pa rtsal du btags shing /
NK128(nyo)001:4533: rgyal ba mchog dbyangs ni grub chen dgu'i nang tshan /
NK128(nyo)001:4534: rgyal mchog dbyangs kyi rta skad phyogs bcur khyab //
NK128(nyo)001:4535: ces gsungs pa'i rta mgrin gyi grub thob yin la /
NK128(nyo)001:4536: des dz+ny+aa na ku m+aa ra la dbang bskur ba ni dbang gi chu bo gnyis pa'o //
NK128(nyo)001:4537: yang rgya gar gyi slob dpon chen po h'u ka
NK128(nyo)001:4538: ra'i drung du bod kyi mnga' bdag khri srong lde
NK128(nyo)001:4539: btsan gyis dge slong mi lnga rdzongs te /
NK128(nyo)001:4540: dge slong gnubs nam mkha'i snying po /
NK128(nyo)001:4544: gru gu e bag sha ste lnga pos rgya gar
NK128(nyo)001:4545: gser brag bya skyibs tshal du slob dpon chen po
NK128(nyo)001:4546: h'u ka ra'i zhabs drung du byon te /
NK128(nyo)001:4547: chu len pa rgan mor 'phrin bskur yang lan ma byung bar nang du thal gyis phyin pas /
NK128(nyo)001:4548: slob dpon gyi bod kyi gdug 'dre byung ngo zhes
NK128(nyo)001:4549: h+aum h+aum gsungs shing shangs nas me stag phrom phrom
NK128(nyo)001:4550: 'phros pas dge slong mi lnga brgyal zhing /
NK128(nyo)001:4552: bod kyi rgyal pos gsang sngags kyi chos 'tshol du
NK128(nyo)001:4553: btang bas tshe 'dir rig 'dzin gyis sar grol ba
NK128(nyo)001:4554: zhu zhes gser phul nas phyag btsal nas /
NK128(nyo)001:4555: ngas bod 'dul ba'i dus la babs mi babs yi
NK128(nyo)001:4556: dam gyi lha la 'adri'o gsungs te dar cig mnyam
NK128(nyo)001:4557: par bzhag pa'i mthar dus la babs gsungs te /
NK128(nyo)001:4558: sngon du dbang ma bskur bar bshad bsgrub bya mi
NK128(nyo)001:4559: rung zhes zla gam lnga bcu rtsa brgyad kyi dkyil
NK128(nyo)001:4561: khrag 'thung lnga bcu rtsa brgyad dngos su zhal bstan nas dbang bskur zhing rgyud sgrub thabs rnams gnang /
NK128(nyo)001:4562: dge slong mi lngas dbang dus su grub pa brnyes tshul ni /
NK128(nyo)001:4564: nam mkha'i snying po shes rab phul du phyin //
NK128(nyo)001:4565: bsod nams snying rus gnyis ka mchog tu gyur //
NK128(nyo)001:4566: sa la chag gang ma reg tsam la 'gro //
NK128(nyo)001:4567: dbang phyug nyi shu rtsa brgyad bran bzhin 'khol //
NK128(nyo)001:4568: ye shes lha mo bdun dang dngos su sbyor //
NK128(nyo)001:4569: ru gyong bir yas rdzu 'phrul ya ma zung //
NK128(nyo)001:4570: gru gu e bag ye shes 'od dang 'grogs //
NK128(nyo)001:4571: rgyal ba'i blo gros dus min 'chi ba lhogs //
NK128(nyo)001:4572: rlangs dpal 'brong rwa bshibs byung se gol bzlog /
NK128(nyo)001:4573: ces gsungs pa ltar yin la /
NK128(nyo)001:4574: de'i nang nas dge slong nam mkha'i snying po rje
NK128(nyo)001:4575: 'bangs nyer lnga dang grub chen dgu'i nang na bzhugs
NK128(nyo)001:4576: shing yang dag gi grub pa brnyes /
NK128(nyo)001:4577: nam mkha'i snying po nyi ma'i zer la chibs /
NK128(nyo)001:4579: gzhan yang rgyal ba'i blo gros ro langs gser du bsgyur /
NK128(nyo)001:4580: dpal gyi seng ge lha srin bran du khol //
NK128(nyo)001:4582: khong gnyis kyang rje 'bangs nyer lnga'i gras yin no //
NK128(nyo)001:4583: de ltar dge slong mi lnga las dpal gyi seng ge sngon du bod pa lam bar du 'das /
NK128(nyo)001:4584: gzhan bzhis bod du byon zhing khyad par nam mkha'i
NK128(nyo)001:4585: snying pos mnga' bdag la dbang bskur zhing man ngag
NK128(nyo)001:4586: bstan pa sogs rgyas par thang yig tu shes la
NK128(nyo)001:4587: / 'dir khyad par nam mkha'i snying pos gnyag la
NK128(nyo)001:4588: gnyal gyi bye brag tu dbang bskur zhing rta zag
NK128(nyo)001:4589: / pa gcig phul / gsang mtshan thig le gshog
NK128(nyo)001:4590: rgod rtsal du brtags pa ni dbang gi chu bo
NK128(nyo)001:4591: / pa gcig phul / gsum pa'o // yang pan+di
NK128(nyo)001:4592: ta chen po bi ma las yul yar klungs kyi
NK128(nyo)001:4593: yang thog tu dz+ny+aa na ku m+aa ra la dbang
NK128(nyo)001:4594: bskur zhing dbang yon du gser dngul gyi bya mda'
NK128(nyo)001:4595: tshad ma res sna drangs te nor sna bdun brgya
NK128(nyo)001:4596: phul gsang mtshan dri med zla shar rtsal du btags
NK128(nyo)001:4597: te dbang gi chu bo bzhi pa'o //
NK128(nyo)001:4598: de lta bu'i dbang gi chu bo bzhi ga'i bka'
NK128(nyo)001:4599: dz+ny+aa na ku m+aa ra la babs te gsang sngags
NK128(nyo)001:4600: kyi bstan pa dang po gnyags la babs zer ba'i
NK128(nyo)001:4601: rgyu mtshan yang de yin no //
NK128(nyo)001:4602: des sog po lha dpal dang /
NK128(nyo)001:4603: des gnubs la dbang bskur zhing man ngag bstan pa'i bar snga ma ltar ro //
NK128(nyo)001:4604: gzhan yang sgrub dbang gi skabs su rgya gar gyis
NK128(nyo)001:4605: rig 'dzin brgyad sogs pan grub 'dir ma gtogs pa
NK128(nyo)001:4606: 'ga' zhig dang / bod kyi grub chen gzhan yang bskur tshig tu yod pas /
NK128(nyo)001:4607: des na 'dus pa mdo'i dbang sgrub chen po 'di
NK128(nyo)001:4608: nyid snga 'gyur ba'i gzhung lugs chen por gyur cing
NK128(nyo)001:4609: / tshogs chen gzhal yas khang gi phyi khyams su
NK128(nyo)001:4610: rgya bod rig 'dzin brgyud pa thams cad bzhugs phyir
NK128(nyo)001:4611: spyi sgrub chen po yin pas de dag kun gyi
NK128(nyo)001:4612: rnam thar brir ma lang ngo //
NK128(nyo)001:4613: gnyis pa bod kyi lo rgyus ni de ltar yo
NK128(nyo)001:4614: ga gsum gyi dbang dang man ngag gi bka' babs
NK128(nyo)001:4615: thams cad gnubs sangs rgyas ye shes rin po che
NK128(nyo)001:4617: slob dpon 'di'i rnam thar mdo tsam brjod na /
NK128(nyo)001:4618: yul dbu ru sgrags kyi sa'i cha yang rdzong dang nye ba zhig yin te /
NK128(nyo)001:4620: skyes pa'i pha yul sgrags kyi yang rdzong na //
NK128(nyo)001:4622: deng sang yang rdzong dang khad nye ba'i yul gnubs yul zhes pa de yin par sems /
NK128(nyo)001:4623: gnubs kyi rigs las yab gsal ba'i dbang phyug dang /
NK128(nyo)001:4624: yum mchims mo bkra shis 'tsho yin la /
NK128(nyo)001:4625: de yang yab mes kyi dur skyel ba'i ri sgrags
NK128(nyo)001:4626: kyi ri bo che zhes bya ba deng sang sgrags
NK128(nyo)001:4627: rgan ri bor grags pa la tsan dan gyi sdong
NK128(nyo)001:4628: po skyes pa bsam yas nas rgya nag ha shang
NK128(nyo)001:4630: shing pho byi lo zla ba dang por sprul pa'i sku zhig 'khrungs pa'i ltas su 'dug pas /
NK128(nyo)001:4631: 'khrungs dus dar dkar gyis dril la nyi grib pa
NK128(nyo)001:4632: mtshams su snyol la dkar gsum mngar gsum gyis gsos
NK128(nyo)001:4633: sprul pa'i sku de phyir zlog srid pas /
NK128(nyo)001:4636: tsha tsha la sogs kyis nya stong tshes brgyad la tshogs kyi 'khor lo bskor zhing sbyin pa thong /
NK128(nyo)001:4637: pha ma yang khrims la gnas par gyis shig ces gsungs pa ltar /
NK128(nyo)001:4638: lo zla'i dus de kho na ltar 'khrungs pa'i rdo rje khri gtsug tu btags so //
NK128(nyo)001:4639: de nas dgung lo drug lon pa dang 'o bran
NK128(nyo)001:4640: dpal gyi gzhon nu'i drung du byon te bris klog
NK128(nyo)001:4641: sbyangs / de nas lo bdun lon pa'i tshe bal
NK128(nyo)001:4642: po'i slob dpon b+ha su d+ha ra dpal bsam yas
NK128(nyo)001:4643: sbyangs / su byon te / chos 'khor rgya cher
NK128(nyo)001:4644: bskor ba'i bar spyan sngar bzhugs te gser srang gsum
NK128(nyo)001:4645: sbyangs / su byon te / phul nas / dbang lung man ngag zhus /
NK128(nyo)001:4646: dgung lo bcu gnyis pa'i tshe b+ha su d+ha ra bal yul du gshegs khar /
NK128(nyo)001:4647: shes rab rtsal dang ldan pa'i bod kyi ban chung khyod /
NK128(nyo)001:4648: ma thogs myur du bal po'i yul du shog /
NK128(nyo)001:4649: ston pa'i zhabs kyis bcags pa'i rdo rje'i gdan //
NK128(nyo)001:4650: bya rgod phung po'i ri'i lho phyogs ngos //
NK128(nyo)001:4651: gnod 'dul rdo rje tshal gyi nags kyi gseb //
NK128(nyo)001:4652: 'brub khung rgyab bsnol brag phug bya ba na //
NK128(nyo)001:4653: sgra skad nyi shu rtsa gcig mthar phyin pa'i //
NK128(nyo)001:4654: ram bu gu h+ya tsan+ta bya ba yod //
NK128(nyo)001:4655: de yi spyan sngar bu khyod btang gis gsungs //
NK128(nyo)001:4656: de nas rdo rje khri gtsug gam sangs rgyas ye
NK128(nyo)001:4657: shes kyis yul gzhis ldum ra dang bcas pa gser
NK128(nyo)001:4658: du bsgyur bas gser srang lnga bcu rtsa gcig byung
NK128(nyo)001:4659: ba bsnams te bcu gsum sa bya lo la bal
NK128(nyo)001:4660: yul du gshegs par bka' shog rgya bo cher bshad
NK128(nyo)001:4661: / gzhan 'ga' zhig tu dgung lo nyi shur rgya gar du byon pa dang /
NK128(nyo)001:4662: bcu gcig la byon pa sogs bshad tshul 'dug kyang /
NK128(nyo)001:4663: rgya gar du lan bdun byon pa'i dang po 'di bcu gsum rang 'thad do //
NK128(nyo)001:4664: byi ba'i lo yin phyir bcu gsum gyi dgung skeg thog tu yin par gsal lo //
NK128(nyo)001:4665: de yang bal yul du ba su d+ha ra dang mjal zhing rgyud 'grel man ngag mang du gsan /
NK128(nyo)001:4666: rgya gar du bgrod pa'i grogs med pa la rom
NK128(nyo)001:4667: bu gu h+yas dgongs te dur khrod kam ka'i tshal
NK128(nyo)001:4668: du byon nas gnod sbyin rdzu 'phrul can gang ba
NK128(nyo)001:4669: bzang po la bka' bsgos te grogs su btang ba'i
NK128(nyo)001:4670: lo rgyus dang / snga phyi rgya gar du lan bdun byon te /
NK128(nyo)001:4671: de yang lo rgyus rgyas pa bka' shog rgya bo che sogs su gsal ba ltar dang /
NK128(nyo)001:4672: 'dir 'dus pa mdo'i lo rgyus kyi dbang du bgyis na /
NK128(nyo)001:4673: bal yul du slob dpon ba su d+ha ra la
NK128(nyo)001:4674: mdo dbang zhus par mkhan po chos rgyal skyong la
NK128(nyo)001:4675: zhus shig par lung bstan pa bzhin rgya gar gyi
NK128(nyo)001:4677: mkhan po chos rgyal skyong la rgya gar dbus 'gyur
NK128(nyo)001:4678: tshal du zhus tshul gong du ma h+aa yo ga'i
NK128(nyo)001:4679: bla brgyud skabs bris pa ltar la /
NK128(nyo)001:4680: de ltar mkhan po chos rgyal skyong gis dbang brgyud sgrub thabs mang du gnang ngo //
NK128(nyo)001:4681: gzhan yang +aa tsa ra ya gsal ba'i rgyan la yang nos /
NK128(nyo)001:4682: dus nam zhig gi tshe mkhan po chos rgyal skyong bru sha'i yul du byon te /
NK128(nyo)001:4683: d+ha na rak+shi ta'am sh+aakya seng ge ste /
NK128(nyo)001:4686: bru sha'i mkhan po che btsan skyes kyi /
NK128(nyo)001:4687: lo ts+aa mdzad de bru sha'i khrom du mdo 'gyur mdzad pa mos pa chung ste ma 'gyur bar /
NK128(nyo)001:4688: slar yang rgya gar du byon te bru sha'i mkhan po dang /
NK128(nyo)001:4690: dz+ny+aa na ku m+aa ra dang /
NK128(nyo)001:4692: sangs rgyas ye shes rnams la gsungs shing /
NK128(nyo)001:4693: slob dpon sangs rgyas ye shes kyi bru sha'i mkhan po la yang gsan te /
NK128(nyo)001:4694: de yang bru sha'i mkhan pos d+ha na rak+shi ta'i
NK128(nyo)001:4695: bka' dang sbyar te slar yang bru shar bsgyur ba'i
NK128(nyo)001:4696: tshe bskyar te gsan pas a nu'i brgyud pa ltar
NK128(nyo)001:4697: ro // de ltar lo ts+aa ba sangs rgyas ye
NK128(nyo)001:4698: shes nyid kyis mdo mkhan d+harma bo d+hi la yang
NK128(nyo)001:4700: man ngag sems phyogs skor bod du sog po dpal
NK128(nyo)001:4701: gyi ye shes la gsan tshul a ti'i brgyud pa
NK128(nyo)001:4702: ltar dang / gzhan yang rgya gar gyi slob dpon sh+r+ai seng ha na dang /
NK128(nyo)001:4704: rgya gar d+ha na d+ha la /
NK128(nyo)001:4705: d+ha na sam skri ta dang /
NK128(nyo)001:4707: shan ting gar ba sogs mang du bstan rgya bo che ltar na /
NK128(nyo)001:4708: rgya bal gyi rgyu mtshams rdo rje rtse lnga dgra
NK128(nyo)001:4709: 'dul brag phug tu o rgyan chen po pad+mas dbang
NK128(nyo)001:4710: brgyud man ngag gnang ba'i lo rgyus dang /
NK128(nyo)001:4711: spyi ltar na bod du rje 'bangs nyer lnga dang
NK128(nyo)001:4712: grub chen dgu la sgrub chen bka' brgyad kyi dbang
NK128(nyo)001:4713: sangs rgyas ye shes nyi zla gdan du bting /
NK128(nyo)001:4715: gzhan yang nyid kyi gsung las /
NK128(nyo)001:4716: bdag 'dra sangs rgyas ye shes rin po che //
NK128(nyo)001:4717: lo bdun lon nas shes bya'i yig rtsis bslabs //
NK128(nyo)001:4718: bcu gsum lon nas rgya dang bal por 'khyams //
NK128(nyo)001:4719: bdag gis rgya gar kha che lan bdun bskor //
NK128(nyo)001:4720: bdag gis mkhas pa bcu gcig zhal yang mthong //
NK128(nyo)001:4723: rgya gar mkhas pa bi ma mi tra dang //
NK128(nyo)001:4724: o rgyan mkhan po pad+ma 'byung gnas dang //
NK128(nyo)001:4725: bal po'i mkhan po ba su d+ha ra dang //
NK128(nyo)001:4726: bod kyi mkhas pa dz+ny+aa na ku m+aa ras //
NK128(nyo)001:4727: bdag la gnang ba'i man ngag 'di rnams yin //
NK128(nyo)001:4729: sems can don la byed pa'i man ngag brgya bcu gnyis //
NK128(nyo)001:4730: mkhas pa rnam bzhi'i man ngag rgyun ma bcad //
NK128(nyo)001:4732: de nas ban chung bdag 'dra sangs rgyas ye shes kyis //
NK128(nyo)001:4733: rgya gar mkhas pa bcu gsum zhal yang mthong //
NK128(nyo)001:4734: sh+r+ai seng ha'i zhal mthong sgom bsgrub man ngag gnang //
NK128(nyo)001:4735: ka ma sh+r+ai la sogs mkhas pa bcu yi zhal mthong man ngag gnang //
NK128(nyo)001:4737: bla ma bcu gcig zhabs nas bteg /'on kyang mkhas pa bzhi la gtugs //
NK128(nyo)001:4738: slob dpon dpal gyi seng ge dang //
NK128(nyo)001:4739: rgya gar khrag 'thung nag po dang //
NK128(nyo)001:4740: 'phung byed shan ting gar ba dang //
NK128(nyo)001:4741: bal po ba su d+ha ra bzhi //
NK128(nyo)001:4742: mkhas pa bzhi yi thugs brtol nas //
NK128(nyo)001:4743: zab pa'i chos drug thugs la btags //
NK128(nyo)001:4745: tshe bdag gi lo rgyus ltar na gshed skor rnams ba su d+ha ras gnang ba yin te /
NK128(nyo)001:4747: slob dpon bal po'i rgyal po yin //
NK128(nyo)001:4748: yang le shod kyi brag phug tu //
NK128(nyo)001:4749: gnubs kyi ban chung 'dir shog gsungs //
NK128(nyo)001:4750: bam chen ro yi dbang bskur nas //
NK128(nyo)001:4751: lha ru 'jam dpal tshe bdag gtad //
NK128(nyo)001:4752: ces gsungs pa rnams kyi don ltar /
NK128(nyo)001:4753: rgya bal bod gsum gyi pan grub mang du bstan
NK128(nyo)001:4754: nas sgra tshad lung rigs sde snod rgyud sde'i phyi
NK128(nyo)001:4755: nang thams cad la mkhas pa'i lo ts+aa ba chen
NK128(nyo)001:4756: por gyur pa ni dang por thos bsam mdzad tshul
NK128(nyo)001:4758: gsang sngags kyi bstan pa bar du gnubs la babs zer ba'i rgyu mtshan yang de yin no //
NK128(nyo)001:4759: bar du grub pa brnyes tshul yang rgya gar rdo
NK128(nyo)001:4760: rje gdan du tshogs bsog zhag gsum mdzad pa'i tshe
NK128(nyo)001:4761: gsang ba'i bdag po phyag na rdo rje'i zhal mngon
NK128(nyo)001:4762: sum du gzigs pa'i tshul 'di ltar byung ste /
NK128(nyo)001:4763: nam mkha' 'ja' 'od kyis gang zhing gser gyi rdo
NK128(nyo)001:4764: rje rtse dgu pa zhig mdun gyi nam mkha' khru
NK128(nyo)001:4765: gang gis sar byung ba la lan gnyis su ma
NK128(nyo)001:4766: zin / gsum pa'i tshe phyag g.yas pa'i mtheb srin
NK128(nyo)001:4767: gyi bar du chags pa de phyag na rdo rje
NK128(nyo)001:4768: dngos kyi sku gyur te dbang bskur zhing /
NK128(nyo)001:4769: sangs rgyas ye shes rin po cher mtshan btags so //
NK128(nyo)001:4770: de'i dbang rtags su rdo rje rtse dgu pa re mi 'bral bar 'chang bar mdzad cing /
NK128(nyo)001:4771: rdo rje deng sang rong byams chen gyi lha chen thugs kar bzhugs skad do //
NK128(nyo)001:4772: de nas gsang bdag gi lung mang du bstan zhing /
NK128(nyo)001:4773: khyad par 'ol mo tshal du sgoms shig par gsungs
NK128(nyo)001:4774: pa bzhin bsgoms pas 'jam dpal ya man+ta ka'i zhal
NK128(nyo)001:4775: gzigs shing dbang dang dngos grub gnang /
NK128(nyo)001:4776: lha srin dbang du 'dus shing gsang sngags kyi bdag por dbang bskur /
NK128(nyo)001:4777: ma gshin mkha' 'gro dbang phyug rnams srung mar gtad /
NK128(nyo)001:4778: 'jam dpal gshin rje'i lung bzhin rgya gar dur khrod
NK128(nyo)001:4779: phu lung nag por byon pas sngags srungs e ka
NK128(nyo)001:4781: bram ze mo'i thod pa dngos grub kyi rjes su byin /
NK128(nyo)001:4782: skabs der dbyings la ye shes shar ba'i rtogs pa brnyes shing sa bzhi pa mngon du gyur /
NK128(nyo)001:4783: pad+ma gar gyi dbang phyug gi zhal mthong de mon
NK128(nyo)001:4784: nag kha khra'i thod pa dngos grub kyi rdzas su
NK128(nyo)001:4785: gnang / slar yang 'jam dpal gshed po'i dkyil 'khor
NK128(nyo)001:4786: rdzogs par zhal mthong dbang rgyud man ngag du ma
NK128(nyo)001:4787: gnang / gnang / mdor na yi dam gyi lha
NK128(nyo)001:4788: rnams kyi zhal mthong zhing dam can bka' srung rnams
NK128(nyo)001:4789: gnang / gnang / bran du khol / gtso bor
NK128(nyo)001:4790: yang dag pa'i gnas lugs 'od gsal chen po'i rtogs
NK128(nyo)001:4792: mngon shes dang rdzu 'phrul thogs pa med par grub /
NK128(nyo)001:4793: gzhan yang bod yul sgrags kyi yang rdzong sgrub gnas kyi mthil du mdzad /
NK128(nyo)001:4794: de bzhin du gtsang gi phung po ri bo che /
NK128(nyo)001:4795: rtsal chen nyug gi rdo rje sgrom bu g.yung gi
NK128(nyo)001:4796: rdza lhun mo sogs sgrub gnas du ma zhabs kyis
NK128(nyo)001:4797: bcags shing / sgrub gnas kyi gtso bo mdo'i lugs
NK128(nyo)001:4798: su rdo rje sgrom bu nyid yin par bshad de
NK128(nyo)001:4799: bcags shing / / bod yul gtsang gi g.yas ru'i phyogs //
NK128(nyo)001:4800: nyug gi rdo rje sgrom bu ru //
NK128(nyo)001:4801: gnubs ban sangs rgyas ye shes kyis //
NK128(nyo)001:4802: rang byung thig le nyag gcig don //
NK128(nyo)001:4803: zla ba dgu'i sems nyid grol //
NK128(nyo)001:4804: dngos po'i gnas lugs gtan la phebs //
NK128(nyo)001:4806: ngo mtshar gyi rnam thar don bsdu yang nyid kyi gsungs las /
NK128(nyo)001:4807: g.yung drung rin chen gter gnas su //
NK128(nyo)001:4808: yi dam gsal bar bsgom pa'i tshe //
NK128(nyo)001:4809: stobs po che yi rdzas mchog 'di //
NK128(nyo)001:4810: bdag gi lag pa g.yas pas zin //
NK128(nyo)001:4811: ye shes rdo rje'i dbang mchog thob //
NK128(nyo)001:4812: 'ol mo tshal du bsgoms pa'i tshe //
NK128(nyo)001:4813: mngon sum dri za'i phru gu byung //
NK128(nyo)001:4814: sangs rgyas khyod yin mtshan btags te //
NK128(nyo)001:4815: dam brdar don la dam tshig bsres //
NK128(nyo)001:4816: rdo rje ming gi dbang yang thob //
NK128(nyo)001:4817: gang bzang gnas su bsgoms pa'i tshe //
NK128(nyo)001:4818: gnod sbyin phru gu mngon sum byung //
NK128(nyo)001:4819: 'dod yon lnga yi mchod yon stobs //
NK128(nyo)001:4820: slob dpon 'khor du dam du bcas //
NK128(nyo)001:4821: che ba'i yon tan dbang yang thob //
NK128(nyo)001:4822: gling dgu'i mtshams 'gram bsgoms pa'i tshe //
NK128(nyo)001:4823: klu phrug spun gsum mngon byung nas //
NK128(nyo)001:4824: ro brgya ldan pa'i mchod pa drangs //
NK128(nyo)001:4825: yang dag slob mar dam tshig mnos //
NK128(nyo)001:4826: gdug pa sel ba'i dbang yang thob //
NK128(nyo)001:4827: dur khrod lhas su bsgoms pa'i tshe //
NK128(nyo)001:4828: yi dwags phrug gu mngon sum byung //
NK128(nyo)001:4829: zhabs la gtugs te mchi ma phyungs //
NK128(nyo)001:4830: ci bgo nyan pa'i dbang yang nos //
NK128(nyo)001:4831: mthu rtsal bsnyen pa'i dbang yang thob //
NK128(nyo)001:4833: de ltar grub 'bras kyis dam pa'i chos kyi 'phrin
NK128(nyo)001:4834: las mdzad tshul yang spyir mnga' bdag khri srong lde'u
NK128(nyo)001:4835: btsan gyis dus mkhan chen bo d+hi sa t+wa las
NK128(nyo)001:4836: rab tu byung ba'i lo ts+aa ba chen po'i gras
NK128(nyo)001:4837: su bzhugs shing / mdo sngags kyi dam pa'i chos mang du bsgyur ba dang /
NK128(nyo)001:4838: phyis nyid kyis rgya bal du lan du mar byon
NK128(nyo)001:4839: nas dbang rgyud man ngag gsan pa rnams 'ga' zhig
NK128(nyo)001:4840: zab mo'i gter du sbas bar mdzad cing /
NK128(nyo)001:4841: 'ga' zhig las can rnams la gnang tshul sogs 'og tu 'byung la /
NK128(nyo)001:4842: 'phrin las drag po mngon spyod kyi sgo nas gdul
NK128(nyo)001:4843: bya gdug pa can rnams chos kyi dbyings su bsgral
NK128(nyo)001:4844: ba'i tshul yang du mar 'byung zhing /
NK128(nyo)001:4845: de lta bu'i rkyen yang khengs log snga phyi bar gsum du byung tshul dang /
NK128(nyo)001:4847: nyon mongs bod yul dbus su langs //
NK128(nyo)001:4850: bdag 'dra sangs rgyas ye shes kyis //
NK128(nyo)001:4851: sgrub khang ya ma'i mkhar la byas //
NK128(nyo)001:4852: sgrags la nag po'i rtse ru ni //
NK128(nyo)001:4854: sgrags kyi grong khyer sum cu rtsa bdun brlag /
NK128(nyo)001:4856: bdag 'dra gnubs kyi ban chung yang //
NK128(nyo)001:4857: snying nas chos bzhin bya sems skyes //
NK128(nyo)001:4858: zhe sdang dgra bos byed ma ste //
NK128(nyo)001:4859: sangs rgyas bstan pa bsrung ba'i phyir //
NK128(nyo)001:4860: zhe sdang de ma thag tu skyes //
NK128(nyo)001:4861: dkar po'i che ba 'don bsams nas //
NK128(nyo)001:4862: ngan sngags yig sna sna tshogs bslabs //
NK128(nyo)001:4865: der nas drug cu rtsa gcig shing pho byi ba'i lo /
NK128(nyo)001:4866: bdag gi skeg la babs nas khengs log bar pa byung /
NK128(nyo)001:4867: sgrags su ma chags gnubs yul rong du bros /
NK128(nyo)001:4869: der yang ma chags snye mo bye mkhar bzung //
NK128(nyo)001:4871: khengs log byung ste sgrags yang rdzong nas gnubs yul rong du bros /
NK128(nyo)001:4872: der yang bzhugs su ma bcug par gtsang gi snye
NK128(nyo)001:4873: mo bye mkhar bzung zhing bzhugs kyang dmag gis bskor
NK128(nyo)001:4874: zhing mdun gyis ri la sogs thams cad dmag gis
NK128(nyo)001:4875: khengs te / de dag kyang bkrongs ba'i 'dun gros ngan pa kho na byed pa gsan te /
NK128(nyo)001:4876: mkhar gyi rtser byon te 'di skad gsungs so //
NK128(nyo)001:4877: khengs so gros byed thams cad tshur nyon cig /
NK128(nyo)001:4878: snang srid lha 'dre thams cad gzu dang dpang mdzod cig /
NK128(nyo)001:4879: dam can rnams la gtor tshogs rgyun ma bcad //
NK128(nyo)001:4880: bdag gi dam chos bdud rtsi lta bu 'tshol skyong phyir //
NK128(nyo)001:4881: bcu gsum lon nas 'dzam gling khyab par 'khyams //
NK128(nyo)001:4882: rgya gar bal po'i yul du lan bdun phyin //
NK128(nyo)001:4883: mkhas pa rnams la zhabs tog rgyun ma bcag /
NK128(nyo)001:4884: ngas ni las su chos byas don du lha gnyer nas //
NK128(nyo)001:4885: bdag dang gzhan gyi don du ma phye bar //
NK128(nyo)001:4886: 'gro ba'i don du byang chub sems bsgoms nas //
NK128(nyo)001:4887: bros kyang ma phan bdag gis phyir 'brangs nas //
NK128(nyo)001:4888: bdag la 'di 'dra'i khengs log byed pa 'di //
NK128(nyo)001:4889: bka' srung dam can rgya mtsho thams cad dang //
NK128(nyo)001:4890: rig 'dzin rtsal 'chang grub thob thams cad dang //
NK128(nyo)001:4891: bod khams gnod sbyin mthu chen thams cad kun //
NK128(nyo)001:4892: ma nyes ma lan bdag gi ra mda' slog /
NK128(nyo)001:4893: ces gsungs te chos gos lan gsum brdabs pas /
NK128(nyo)001:4894: dam can thams cad mngon sum du byung ste bdag
NK128(nyo)001:4895: cag gi mthu rtsal gyis ri rab kyang thal bar
NK128(nyo)001:4896: rlog nus / ri bor dpung gis 'debs nus /
NK128(nyo)001:4898: nyi zla cha lang rdeb nus /
NK128(nyo)001:4899: gnam sa bla 'og bsgyur nus kyang /
NK128(nyo)001:4900: slob dpon nyid kyis tshe rabs snga mar las 'bras rdol bar 'dug pas /
NK128(nyo)001:4901: sngon chad ni bdag gis kyang grogs ma bgyis /
NK128(nyo)001:4902: da ni 'jig rten brlag par bagyi'am ji ltar bgyi /
NK128(nyo)001:4904: chos gos kyi cha ga nas seng ldeng gi phur bu bton nas /
NK128(nyo)001:4905: dam can rnams kyi srog sngags btab cing dril zhing /
NK128(nyo)001:4906: ri pha gi m+aa ra ya phatahzhesa gsungs pas /
NK128(nyo)001:4907: ri de las me rab tu 'bar nas dmag dpung thams cad bsregs shing brlag par bya'o //
NK128(nyo)001:4908: de'i sdig sbyangs kyi dge bar bsam gtan mig gi sgron ma yang mdzad ces grags so //
NK128(nyo)001:4909: de nas sku dgra rnams rnam pa mngon spyod kyi las rtsub pa ltar snang yang /
NK128(nyo)001:4910: don snying rjes zin pa'i sbyor sgrol mthar phyin pa
NK128(nyo)001:4911: yin pas gdul bya rnams drag pos bsgral te dang
NK128(nyo)001:4912: po'i sangs rgyas zhing du spar ba la the tshom
NK128(nyo)001:4913: ma mchis pas ngo mtshar ba'i gnas so //
NK128(nyo)001:4914: de ltar sku dgra rnam thul yang lo gsum gyis bar du dbul zhing 'phongs nas /
NK128(nyo)001:4915: sgrags yang rdzong du dngos grub sgrub cing mchis pa'i tshe /
NK128(nyo)001:4916: bsam yas su chos rgyal khri srong gi lha sras
NK128(nyo)001:4917: mnga' thang che bas spyan drangs te chos gzhi btsugs
NK128(nyo)001:4918: nas byang chub gling du chos kyi 'khor lo rgya
NK128(nyo)001:4919: cher bskor ro // slob ma bskrun tshul yang nyid kyi bka' las /
NK128(nyo)001:4920: las kyi 'brel ba'i yon tan rgya mtsho dang //
NK128(nyo)001:4921: dad pa che ba'i legs pa'i sgron ma gnyis //
NK128(nyo)001:4922: grogs mchog dam pa ye shes dbang phyug dang //
NK128(nyo)001:4923: rtsal shugs gtong phod che ba'i blon rje 'phags pa gnyis //
NK128(nyo)001:4924: dam tshig dam pa snying la 'jog pa 'dra nas su //
NK128(nyo)001:4925: dam chos gzhung bzhin bka' la brten te lo bdun bshad //
NK128(nyo)001:4927: de phyir bdag gi yon tan rgya mtsho la //
NK128(nyo)001:4928: sgrub lugs mi mthun brgyad dang rtsa bdun gtad de bzhag /
NK128(nyo)001:4930: mdor na slob dpon chen po de nyid la slob ma mtha' yas kyang /
NK128(nyo)001:4931: gtso bo ni sras dam pa bzhi dang /
NK128(nyo)001:4932: mchog tu gyur pa gcig ste lnga yod pa'i rgyu mtshan /
NK128(nyo)001:4934: shes rab kyi nags tshal las /
NK128(nyo)001:4936: snod kyi mchog lnga ru blug /
NK128(nyo)001:4937: gcig gis ni rtsa ba khyer /
NK128(nyo)001:4939: gcig gis ni lo ma khyer /
NK128(nyo)001:4941: gcig gis ni me tog khyer /
NK128(nyo)001:4945: gcig gis ni thams cad khyer /
NK128(nyo)001:4948: rtsa ba rgyud la mkhas pa spa gor /
NK128(nyo)001:4949: lo ma bdud rtsi la mkhas pa sru /
NK128(nyo)001:4950: me tog brgal lan la mkhas pa dan /
NK128(nyo)001:4951: 'bras bu sems la mkhas pa so /
NK128(nyo)001:4952: de thams cad la mkhas pa yon tan rgya mtsho yin par bshad /
NK128(nyo)001:4953: de'i nang nas kyang gtso bo yon tan rgya mtsho kho na yin te /
NK128(nyo)001:4954: sems can don la byed pa'i man ngag brgya bcu gnyis //
NK128(nyo)001:4955: mkhas pa rnam bzhi'i man ngag rgyun ma bcad //
NK128(nyo)001:4956: byang chub sems don man ngag ngos 'dzin byed pa'i ma ni ka /
NK128(nyo)001:4957: bu gcig yon tan rgya mtsho sems kyi dkyil du bstim //
NK128(nyo)001:4959: gzhan yang de rnams rjes su bzung tshul yang /
NK128(nyo)001:4960: gnubs chen sangs rgyas ye shes nyid rnam pa dge
NK128(nyo)001:4961: slong yin kyang don sum ldan rdo rje 'dzin pa
NK128(nyo)001:4962: chen po'i go sar bzhugs pas /
NK128(nyo)001:4963: gzhan don du rigs brgyud bzhag pa las /
NK128(nyo)001:4964: sras gnyis 'bangs khengs log skabs bkrongs pas thugs mug ste /
NK128(nyo)001:4965: rgya dpe rnams stag sgro dang gzig sgror bcug rgya
NK128(nyo)001:4966: bong gwa pa zhig la bkal te rgya gar du
NK128(nyo)001:4967: bskyel bar chas pa'i tshe yas bon dang mjal te
NK128(nyo)001:4969: bon pos chang nye bar phyin pas so ye shes
NK128(nyo)001:4970: dbang phyug dang phrad de nga la mchod gnas gnubs
NK128(nyo)001:4971: chen yod tshul bshad pas sos kyang mjal bar byon
NK128(nyo)001:4972: / de dang dus mtshungs su spa gor blon rje 'phags /
NK128(nyo)001:4974: dan yon tan mchog rnams kyang 'dzoms te /
NK128(nyo)001:4975: khong bzhis rgya gar la mi gshegs par gsol ba ltar bzhugs te mdo sgyu sems gsum /
NK128(nyo)001:4977: bdud rtsi sogs rgya cher gsungs /
NK128(nyo)001:4978: snar gyi shug pa nag por bzhugs pa'i tshe gnubs
NK128(nyo)001:4979: yon tan rgya mtsho rjes su bzung ba sogs bshad
NK128(nyo)001:4980: / de ltar bshad bsgrub kyi sgo nas gdul bya rgya cher mdzad de /
NK128(nyo)001:4981: mthar mya ngan las 'das par phyogs te phyi rabs
NK128(nyo)001:4982: la dgongs pa'i dam chos rnams gter du sbas pa
NK128(nyo)001:4983: bzhed nas / bal po'i yul nas bzo bo bkug
NK128(nyo)001:4984: cing bse sgrom smug po'i gter snod brdung ba'i tshe
NK128(nyo)001:4985: bzhed nas / / klu'i rgyal po ma dros pas
NK128(nyo)001:4986: 'khor dpag tu med pa dang bcas byung ste phyag
NK128(nyo)001:4987: 'tshal zhing mya ngan las mi 'da' bar gsal bar
NK128(nyo)001:4989: rig pa dbang thob slob dpon sangs rgyas khyod //
NK128(nyo)001:4990: mya ngan mi 'da' sems can don la bzhugs //
NK128(nyo)001:4991: ji tsam bar du gnas pa'i tshe na yang //
NK128(nyo)001:4992: rdzu 'phrul mthu dang nor gyi dngos grub nga yis sbyin //
NK128(nyo)001:4993: zhes gsol ba btab pa la /
NK128(nyo)001:4995: dgra la bsad kyi mi lang gram pa'i rdo phung 'dra //
NK128(nyo)001:4996: gnyen la skyongs pas mi 'khyongs mtsho matha'i sbrang bu 'dra //
NK128(nyo)001:4997: bya ba byas kyi mi zin chu yi gnyer ma 'dra //
NK128(nyo)001:4998: ban chung bdag gi dpe yang de dang 'dra ba ste //
NK128(nyo)001:4999: rdzu 'phrul mthu dang nor bu'i bdag la dgos pa med //
NK128(nyo)001:5000: ji tsam bar du sdod pa'i dbang yod kyang //
NK128(nyo)001:5001: phyag na rdo rje'i dbang gi bka' mi bcog /
NK128(nyo)001:5002: rgyal ba'i bka' bzhin 'dzin pa'i bu med pas //
NK128(nyo)001:5003: sgyu ma'i phung po 'di dang 'grogs te re zhig sa yi gter du sbed //
NK128(nyo)001:5004: bstan pa gnyan la dgos pa'i dus 'byung gis //
NK128(nyo)001:5005: lan cig rung du rdzus pa cig dang phrad pa'i tshe na yang //
NK128(nyo)001:5006: nga yi bka' 'di 'dzin dang 'chang ba dang //
NK128(nyo)001:5007: bka' 'di sgrub pa'i rnal 'byor pa rnams la //
NK128(nyo)001:5008: 'jig rten klu'i nad rnams ma btang zhig /
NK128(nyo)001:5010: zab chos rnams bse sgrom du bcug ya khebs la
NK128(nyo)001:5011: bdud brkos rje brang dkar dang ma khebs la mkha'
NK128(nyo)001:5012: 'gro e ka dza ta'i rgyas btab /
NK128(nyo)001:5013: sbrul gyi chun pos bcings te klu'i rgyal po'i lto
NK128(nyo)001:5014: bar a tham zhes klu rgyal de nyid la gtad
NK128(nyo)001:5015: do // de yang lo rgyus 'ga' zhig tu gnubs
NK128(nyo)001:5016: chen dgung lo brgya dang bcu gsum bzhugs par bshad
NK128(nyo)001:5017: do // kyang / nyid kyi gsungs las /
NK128(nyo)001:5018: gnubs kyi ban chung sangs rgyas ngas //
NK128(nyo)001:5019: lo ni brgya dang sum cu lon //
NK128(nyo)001:5020: zhes gsungs pa btsan par 'dug cing /
NK128(nyo)001:5021: rgyu mtshan mnga' bdag khri srong gi dus nas dpal
NK128(nyo)001:5022: 'khor btsan gyis bar du bzhugs pa'i lo rgyus snang
NK128(nyo)001:5023: ste / dar mas bstan pa gnubs pa thugs kyis ma bzod pa drag sngags bya bar dgongs te /
NK128(nyo)001:5024: slar bal bor log ste ba su d+ha ra la
NK128(nyo)001:5025: drag sngags spu gri reg chod 'ga' zhig nos pa
NK128(nyo)001:5026: tshur byon pa'i tshe rgyal po sdig can lha lung
NK128(nyo)001:5027: dpal rdor gyis bsgral zin 'dug pas ngan sngags mdzad
NK128(nyo)001:5028: ma dgos par gter du sbas par gsungs pa'i phyir
NK128(nyo)001:5029: / de ltar gdul bya rdzogs nas re zhig gdod
NK128(nyo)001:5030: ma'i zhing du lhun grub 'od phung chen por gshegs
NK128(nyo)001:5031: / so // de ltar gnubs ban lo ts+aa ba
NK128(nyo)001:5032: chen po rin po che rdo rje yang dbang gter
NK128(nyo)001:5033: zhes grags pa de nyid la /
NK128(nyo)001:5034: slob ma gnubs kyi bu bzhi /
NK128(nyo)001:5037: 'khor brgya drug cu sogs yod pa'i 'dren tshul mi 'dra ba 'ga' zhig 'dug kyang /
NK128(nyo)001:5038: mtshan gsal ni dbang byang las /
NK128(nyo)001:5039: gnubs kyi bu bzhi dge mched bco lnga dang //
NK128(nyo)001:5040: rin can gsum dang 'khor brgya drug cu 'jig rten sogs //
NK128(nyo)001:5041: bu bzhin 'bre ston khro chung nyang sher mchog /
NK128(nyo)001:5042: nyang ston ye 'byung zur chen sh+aakya 'byung //
NK128(nyo)001:5044: dge mched bco lnga ni dge mched dang po thugs kyi sras bzhi ni /
NK128(nyo)001:5045: so sa ye dbang rdo rje dbyings phyug gter //
NK128(nyo)001:5046: sru legs sgron ma ut+pala dbang chen rtsal //
NK128(nyo)001:5047: spa gor blon rje rdo rje gnam lcags rtsal //
NK128(nyo)001:5048: dan ston yon mchog rdo rje drag po rtsal //
NK128(nyo)001:5049: gnyis pa thugs sras gnubs ban khu lung pa //
NK128(nyo)001:5050: yon tan rgya mtsho rdo rje rig 'dzin gter //
NK128(nyo)001:5051: gsum pa sru yi slob ma mchog bzhi ni //
NK128(nyo)001:5052: dbyar ston gsal byang rdo rje mtshams byed rtsal //
NK128(nyo)001:5053: rgya blon blo gros gzhon nu dbang rdzogs rtsal //
NK128(nyo)001:5054: rgya ston sh+aakya mchog rab gzi 'bar rtsal //
NK128(nyo)001:5055: zhu don bsod sh+aaka 'phrin las mthar sbyin rtsal //
NK128(nyo)001:5056: bzhi pa spa gor beg ston ye shes dang //
NK128(nyo)001:5057: lnga pa lnga ni rgya ston gzhon nu snying //
NK128(nyo)001:5058: skyo ston dar ma byang chub skye mchog rab //
NK128(nyo)001:5059: skye ston dar rgyas lho sdod snying po'o //
NK128(nyo)001:5061: gnubs ban khu lung pa yon tan rgya mtsho rdo
NK128(nyo)001:5062: rje rig 'dzin gter mtshan gcig yin pas bla'i mtshan
NK128(nyo)001:5063: gsum gcig tu grangs pas bco lnga 'byung ba ni
NK128(nyo)001:5064: dge mched bco lnga yin par bshad /
NK128(nyo)001:5065: 'di la 'dren tshul lugs gsum tsam mthong ba gsum
NK128(nyo)001:5066: ga mi gcig par snang yang so sor khungs che
NK128(nyo)001:5067: mod / 'on kyang bu bzhi dge mched bco lnga
NK128(nyo)001:5068: thams cad la bka' lung rdzogs par bzhugs pa ni
NK128(nyo)001:5069: mod / ma yin te / la la dngos slob /
NK128(nyo)001:5070: la la yang slob tsam yin par dgos shing /
NK128(nyo)001:5071: zur po ches kyang zhabs zin pa dang ma zin pa'i bshad tshul gnyis snang bas dpyad do //
NK128(nyo)001:5072: 'dren tshul 'di la yang la las gnubs ban dang khu lung pa gnyis so sor bgrangs pa dang /
NK128(nyo)001:5073: la las skye mchog rab chad cing ye shes rgya
NK128(nyo)001:5074: mtsho bsnan pa sogs 'khrul pa yod par dgos so
NK128(nyo)001:5075: // de ltar dge mched bco lnga sogs chig rgyud du thams cad 'dren dgos pa ma yin kyang /
NK128(nyo)001:5076: 'og min tshogs chen gyi dkyil 'khor du bzhugs pa'i dbang du byas la /
NK128(nyo)001:5077: gtso bor rnam thar gyi skabs su smos pa ltar slob ma'i mchog lnga ste /
NK128(nyo)001:5082: gnubs khu lung pa yon tan rgya mtsho ste lnga
NK128(nyo)001:5083: po rgyud kyi bshad pa la spa gor gtso che
NK128(nyo)001:5084: zhing / man ngag dang dbang rgyud phyogs re ba lnga ga la yod mod kyang /
NK128(nyo)001:5085: dbang bka' yon tan rgya mtsho kho na las brgyud dgos par gsungs te /
NK128(nyo)001:5087: khu lung yon tan rgya mtsho la dbang gdams ngag gi bka' babs /
NK128(nyo)001:5088: spa gor rje blon 'phags la gzhung gi bka' babs /
NK128(nyo)001:5089: so ye shes dbang phyug la lta ba'i bka' babs /
NK128(nyo)001:5090: sru legs pa'i sgron ma la dbang bzhi'i chu bo'i bka' babs par gsungs shing /
NK128(nyo)001:5091: 'di'i lugs la mar ye shes dbang phyug /
NK128(nyo)001:5092: dbyar ga la ba'i byang chub /
NK128(nyo)001:5095: zhu bsod nams sh+aakya la sogs bco lnga la sru
NK128(nyo)001:5096: legs pa'i sgron mes 'dus pa chen po'i dbang bskur
NK128(nyo)001:5097: nas smin grol la bkod par gsungs pas dge mched
NK128(nyo)001:5098: bco lnga sru'i slob ma yin par bshad cing /
NK128(nyo)001:5100: shom yag sdings kyi gnas mchog tu //
NK128(nyo)001:5101: dbang bzhi'i chu bo bka' babs pas //
NK128(nyo)001:5102: sru ni legs pa'i sgron ma yis //
NK128(nyo)001:5103: dge mched bco lnga'i slob bu smin //
NK128(nyo)001:5104: zhes gsungs pa'i tshig 'di dbang gzhung thams cad mthun par 'dug pas btsan par snang yang /
NK128(nyo)001:5105: lo rgyus spyi dang mi mthun 'dra bas dpyad par bya la /
NK128(nyo)001:5106: sru yang gdung gi mtshan yin cing /
NK128(nyo)001:5107: legs pa'i sgron mar btags pa las gzhan skye rgyal rang yin par bshad de /
NK128(nyo)001:5108: de ltar gnubs sangs rgyas ye shes rin po che nyid kyi /
NK128(nyo)001:5109: gnubs khu lung pa yon tan rgya mtsho la rong
NK128(nyo)001:5110: snar gyi yang gsang gi brag phug tu gsungs shing
NK128(nyo)001:5112: dbang gi yig sna bco brgyad gtad /
NK128(nyo)001:5113: dbang rtags su dbang bskur rgyal po'i rgyud sbyin /
NK128(nyo)001:5114: yon du stod kyi las sgo lan gsum blan nas g.yu dkar po 'od 'dzag /
NK128(nyo)001:5118: la rdzas dang rtsi sman mang du phul /
NK128(nyo)001:5119: gsang mtshan rde rje gter bzhad rtsal du btags so //
NK128(nyo)001:5120: slob dpon 'di'i rnam thar cung zad brjod na /
NK128(nyo)001:5121: de yang gdul bya'i don du slob dpon sangs rgyas ye shes dang tshe rabs du mar 'brel zhing /
NK128(nyo)001:5122: khyad par sku tshe 'di'i snga ma yab sras su
NK128(nyo)001:5123: 'brel te gdul bya drang phyir sangs rgyas ye shes
NK128(nyo)001:5124: nyid rgya gar du bshan pa ma ru rtse bya
NK128(nyo)001:5125: bar 'khrungs shing / gnubs yon tan rgya mtsho yab
NK128(nyo)001:5126: ma ru rtse dang yum rje btsun sgrol ma'i sprul
NK128(nyo)001:5127: pa gdug rtsub kyi skor mgo ma zhes bya ba
NK128(nyo)001:5128: bar 'khrungs shing / la / sras che dga' bo /
NK128(nyo)001:5130: sras mo dga' lcam gsum yod pa'i sras chung bar 'khrungs so //
NK128(nyo)001:5131: de ltar yum sras dang bcas lnga por mchod ga
NK128(nyo)001:5132: nas slob dpon ka ru na zhes pa zhig yod
NK128(nyo)001:5133: pa mchod cing dbang dang gdams ngag zhus te /
NK128(nyo)001:5134: sras che bar dga' bo mos gus dang brtson 'grus
NK128(nyo)001:5135: btang phod che bas longs spyod thams cad bla ma
NK128(nyo)001:5136: la phul te / gdams ngag nyams su blangs pas /
NK128(nyo)001:5137: grub pa thob ste tshe dbang rig 'dzin brnyes nas
NK128(nyo)001:5138: rgya gar d+ha na d+ha la zhes grags shing da
NK128(nyo)001:5140: yab bshan pa ma ru rtse gdul bya rdzogs nas
NK128(nyo)001:5141: bod yul du lo ts+aa ba sangs rgyas ye shes
NK128(nyo)001:5142: su 'khrungs yum yang bod yul du jo mo mkhar
NK128(nyo)001:5144: sras mo dga' lcam shel dkar bza' rdo rjer sku 'khrungs /
NK128(nyo)001:5145: sras dga' chung ni rgya gar du rgyal khrims dam
NK128(nyo)001:5146: zhing gang dgar bya dbang med phyi nang gi grub
NK128(nyo)001:5147: mtha' gnyis rtsod dgos pas bshad pa dang rtsod pas
NK128(nyo)001:5148: sun nas / gsang sngags 'chol bar spyad chog pa'i smon lam btab pas /
NK128(nyo)001:5149: bod yul gnubs khu lung du gnubs kyi rigs las
NK128(nyo)001:5150: grong ban zhig gi sras su 'khrungs te yon tan
NK128(nyo)001:5151: rgya mtsho zhes grags pa khu lung pa yon tan
NK128(nyo)001:5153: de'i tshe rgya gar d+ha na d+ha las rang gi
NK128(nyo)001:5154: yab yum mched rnams gar skyes mngon par mkhyen pas
NK128(nyo)001:5155: gzigs pas / yab slob dpon sangs rgyas ye shes
NK128(nyo)001:5156: su 'khrungs pa kho rang gi slob mar gyur cing
NK128(nyo)001:5157: rang don grub nas gzhan don mdzad pa dang /
NK128(nyo)001:5158: yum mtsho rgyal yang g+hu ru pad+mas rjes su bzung
NK128(nyo)001:5159: ste rang don grub nas gzhan don mdzad pa dang
NK128(nyo)001:5160: / sras mo 'ga' lcam yang gu ru pad+ma dang
NK128(nyo)001:5161: nam mkha'i snying po sogs kyis las rgyar gyur te
NK128(nyo)001:5162: lam sna zin cing dngos grub phra mo brnyes nas
NK128(nyo)001:5163: 'dug pas khong bzhi po'i don byed mi dgos par
NK128(nyo)001:5164: / gzigs / gcung po dga' chung grong ban zhig
NK128(nyo)001:5165: gi sras rang rgyud pa ltar grogs sngags kyis 'tsho
NK128(nyo)001:5166: zhing 'dug pa snying rje bar dgongs nas de'i don
NK128(nyo)001:5167: zhig bya snyam ste bod du 'byon par chas te
NK128(nyo)001:5168: / gzigs / / rkang mgyogs sgrub par dgongs nas gnod sbyin mo'i rkang mgyogs bsgrubs te /
NK128(nyo)001:5169: de'i tshe g.yog po la drung du ma nyal gsungs pa ma nyan par nyal bas /
NK128(nyo)001:5170: nam phyed tsam na sgrub g.yog skad ngan ce re byung ste gzigs pas /
NK128(nyo)001:5171: rtse chung la sdig pa nag po zhig 'thams 'dug
NK128(nyo)001:5172: nas phyag gi gu h+ya rdo rje phud nas rgyab
NK128(nyo)001:5173: pas tog zer zhing yal song ngo //
NK128(nyo)001:5174: de nas tho rangs kyi cha la sa chag pa'i skad /
NK128(nyo)001:5175: gnam grum pa'i skad lta bu'i sgra chen po zhig byung nas gzigs pas /
NK128(nyo)001:5176: bya chen po gnam gyis sa bkab pa tsam gshog
NK128(nyo)001:5177: pa g.yas las sa 'drud pa zhig byung nas khyod
NK128(nyo)001:5179: bdag ni gnod sbyin mo rtsar langs ma bya ba
NK128(nyo)001:5180: lags pas las ci bgyi bka' stsol cig zer bas
NK128(nyo)001:5181: / slob dpon gyis bod yul gnubs khu lung du skyol zhig gsungs pas /
NK128(nyo)001:5183: 'bangs mos zhabs tog pher tsam bdogs pa lags te /
NK128(nyo)001:5184: slob dpon rang gis gshog pa bcag nas da mi phor ro zhus pas /
NK128(nyo)001:5185: 'dang gi sdig pa nag po de yin par mkhyen
NK128(nyo)001:5186: nas khyod bden gsungs te g.yog po bka' skyon no
NK128(nyo)001:5187: // de nas slob dpon gyis yang bdud nag po gnam rol gyi rkang mgyogs bsgrubs pas grub ste /
NK128(nyo)001:5188: mi nag po 'jigs su rung ba zhig slob dpon gyis drung du byung ste /
NK128(nyo)001:5190: las ci 'tshal bka' rtsol cig zer ro //
NK128(nyo)001:5191: snga bzhin bod du skyol gsungs pas /
NK128(nyo)001:5192: khams thu ba bzed nas 'o na 'dir bzhugs shig zer /
NK128(nyo)001:5195: tsan ldan gyi lo ma sngon po zhig /
NK128(nyo)001:5196: smyug ma'i yal 'dabs so ma cig rnams bcas kho'i thu bar bzhugs pas /
NK128(nyo)001:5197: mtshan gang zhig la bod kyi gnubs yul rong khu lung du phebs so //
NK128(nyo)001:5198: der nam yang langs bod du yang phebs pas kho na re /
NK128(nyo)001:5199: kho bo la bod kyi lha 'dre mang pos phrag
NK128(nyo)001:5200: dog byed par gda' bas bdag 'gro bar zhu zer
NK128(nyo)001:5202: der nyi ma thal gyis shar bas shar ba dang /
NK128(nyo)001:5203: ko ba gtong pa yin pas gru kha ste /
NK128(nyo)001:5204: phyogs der shar ba gru kha zhes grags so //
NK128(nyo)001:5206: ko mkhan lang chu la sgrol gsungs pas /
NK128(nyo)001:5207: mtha' mi ka chas med par mi sgrol zer te
NK128(nyo)001:5208: sgrol ma nyan par slob dpon gyis chu la ma
NK128(nyo)001:5209: bying bar chu steng nas yer re byon pas ko
NK128(nyo)001:5211: de nas slob dpon gyi khu lung 'og gi grong
NK128(nyo)001:5212: brdal na yon tan rgya mtsho yon bdag zhig gi
NK128(nyo)001:5213: tshe sgrub byed cing yod pa'i sar thal gyis byon
NK128(nyo)001:5214: nas / yon tan rgya mtsho khyod kyi 'di ci byed pa yin gsungs pas /
NK128(nyo)001:5215: tshe sgrub byed pa lags zhus pas /
NK128(nyo)001:5217: tshe bum la sogs tshe rdzas rnams zhabs rdo brgyab nas bsgyel /
