NK128(nyo)001:5219: dkyil 'khor bsubs pas yon bdag bza' tshor bcas pa 'dus te /
NK128(nyo)001:5220: mtha' mi 'dis thub tshod 'di tsam byed pa ltas ngan yin /
NK128(nyo)001:5221: rgyob gsod zer nas brdeg par byung ba la /
NK128(nyo)001:5222: yon tan rgya mtshos sngon gyis phu bo yin par
NK128(nyo)001:5223: ngo shes te a jo zer zhing pang du 'khyud
NK128(nyo)001:5224: de / 'di nga'i phu bo yin ma brdeg byas pas brdeb rdzogs ma nus /
NK128(nyo)001:5225: de nas slob dpon gyi zhal nas /
NK128(nyo)001:5226: da dkyil 'khor bris tshe gtor bzos gsungs pa ltar byas pa la /
NK128(nyo)001:5227: slob dpon d+ha na d+ha las dgongs pa mdzad cing byin brlabs /
NK128(nyo)001:5228: nga khyed rang tsho theg gsungs nas bteg pas kyang ma theg /
NK128(nyo)001:5230: bsgyel bas kyang ma 'gyel bas tshe bya ba de ltar byed pa yin /
NK128(nyo)001:5231: zhes gsungs nas yon tan rgya mtsho la dbang bskur /
NK128(nyo)001:5232: de'i zhor la yon bdag rnams la yang dbang bskur nas /
NK128(nyo)001:5233: yon bdag khyod la mchog gi dngos grub kyi skal
NK128(nyo)001:5234: ba mi 'dug ste thun mong gi dngos grub mi
NK128(nyo)001:5235: rabs bdun tshun chad la mi nor dar bar 'ong
NK128(nyo)001:5236: gsungs pas / phyis de kho na bzhin byung skad /
NK128(nyo)001:5237: de nas slob dpon d+ha na d+ha la'i zhal nas /
NK128(nyo)001:5238: yon tan rgya mtsho khyod kyi sgrub gnas grong gis mi 'ong ngas btsal gyis gsungs nas /
NK128(nyo)001:5239: khu lung mkhar gdongs mon mo'i gtsug tum lta bu'i sa gnad bzang po btsal te /
NK128(nyo)001:5240: der dbang gdams ngag ma lus par rdzogs par gnang /
NK128(nyo)001:5241: bstan srungs gshin rje dmar nag /
NK128(nyo)001:5242: ma gshin gyi skor sogs zab la mang bar gnang
NK128(nyo)001:5243: nas smin cing grol bar mdzad de slob dpon d+ha
NK128(nyo)001:5244: na d+ha la slar yang rgya gar du gshegs so
NK128(nyo)001:5245: // khyad par gnubs chen sangs rgyas ye shes dang mjal tshul ni /
NK128(nyo)001:5246: slob dpon sangs rgyas ye shes snar gyi shug pa
NK128(nyo)001:5247: nag por bzhugs te gdul bya smin par mdzad skabs
NK128(nyo)001:5248: / yon tan rgya mtsho lo sum cu lon pa
NK128(nyo)001:5249: zhig khyi ra la byon pa ri dwags ma sod
NK128(nyo)001:5250: par nub mor 'khyams nas 'khyags shing lhogs pa la
NK128(nyo)001:5251: spos dri tshor te gnas shig yod dam snyam btsal
NK128(nyo)001:5252: bas rnyed de sangs rgyas ye shes dang mjal te
NK128(nyo)001:5254: rus gnubs yin par dgongs te chos sgor bcug /
NK128(nyo)001:5255: jo mo 'dre sgom dang gnyis la gshin rje'i dbang bskur /
NK128(nyo)001:5256: gshin rje'i man ngag lung rdzogs 'phrang dang /
NK128(nyo)001:5257: mdo sgyu sems gsum sogs chos mang du gsungs /
NK128(nyo)001:5258: sras kyi dam pa lcam sring gnyis zhes grags pa ltar na /
NK128(nyo)001:5259: thog mar gnubs chen mjal zhing phyis rda na rda la dang mjal lam snyam mo //
NK128(nyo)001:5260: de ltar khu lung pa yon tan rgya mtsho de
NK128(nyo)001:5261: nyid kyi mchog gi dngos grub chos nyid kyi don
NK128(nyo)001:5262: rtogs pa mngon du gyur nas zag med kyi mngon
NK128(nyo)001:5263: shes shar / yi dam gyi lha mang po'i zhal gzigs /
NK128(nyo)001:5264: dam can srung ma rnams bran du 'khol zhing 'phrin
NK128(nyo)001:5265: las drag po mngon spyod kyi nus pa thon nas
NK128(nyo)001:5266: bstan pa dar rgyas che bar byung zhing /
NK128(nyo)001:5267: de'i tshul yang mdo dbang gi dngos grub bskul ba las /
NK128(nyo)001:5268: khu lung yon tan rgya mtsho ni //
NK128(nyo)001:5269: thugs sras nang nas mchog tu gyur //
NK128(nyo)001:5270: sprul pa mang po'i zhal gzigs pas //
NK128(nyo)001:5271: mchog dang thun mong dngos grub brnyes //
NK128(nyo)001:5273: gzhan don du rigs rgyud sprul sku 'jog phyir glan
NK128(nyo)001:5274: gyi ma cig so ma legs bya ba khab tu
NK128(nyo)001:5275: bzhes pa / sras lcam sring gsum 'khrungs te /
NK128(nyo)001:5276: che ba gnubs ye shes rgya mtsho /
NK128(nyo)001:5277: chung ba gnubs pad+ma dbang rgyal /
NK128(nyo)001:5278: lcam ut+pala sgron dang gsum mo //
NK128(nyo)001:5279: de'i dus su yang sangs rgyas ye shes lta bu
NK128(nyo)001:5280: rje'i khengs log gi yon tan rgya mtsho bkrong ba'i
NK128(nyo)001:5281: gshed ma brgyad bskos te btang bas /
NK128(nyo)001:5282: gnubs chen khu lung pa yon tan rgya mtshos rdzu
NK128(nyo)001:5283: 'phrul bstan te spyan g.yas nas bskal pa'i me 'bar
NK128(nyo)001:5284: zhing / g.yon nas bskal pa'i chu 'brug pa rang
NK128(nyo)001:5285: 'dra brgyar sprul bas gshed mas bkrong ma nus par
NK128(nyo)001:5287: de nas lcam sring gsum gyis yum glan mo grongs nas /
NK128(nyo)001:5288: gnas dge ri zhang snang la brten nas yar byon
NK128(nyo)001:5289: te ri bo che'i rtsar glan mo'i pur khang brtsigs
NK128(nyo)001:5290: te bzhag / stag ram dpal gyi lcam khab tu
NK128(nyo)001:5291: bzhes pa la gcen stag ram go sha dang gcung
NK128(nyo)001:5292: ro zan nag po gnyis 'khrungs pa sogs lo rgyus
NK128(nyo)001:5293: 'di rnams mi 'dra ba mang du 'dug kyang /
NK128(nyo)001:5294: 'di ni mkhas grub chen po se ston rin cen
NK128(nyo)001:5295: rgyal mtshan gyis mdzad pa'i gsang snying brgyud 'debs kyi
NK128(nyo)001:5296: 'grel pa ltar bris pas 'khrul pa med par sems
NK128(nyo)001:5297: / de ltar bshad sgrub dang 'phrin las rnam pa
NK128(nyo)001:5298: bzhi bstan 'gro'i don rgya cher mdzad pa'i mthar gzugs
NK128(nyo)001:5299: sku chos kyi dbyings su bsdus te 'og min tshogs
NK128(nyo)001:5300: chen gyi dkyil 'khor du gshegs so //
NK128(nyo)001:5301: de ltar gnubs khu lung pa yon tan rgya mtshos /
NK128(nyo)001:5302: rigs sras gnubs ye shes rgya mtsho khu lung du
NK128(nyo)001:5303: dbang dang bshad bka' man ngag dang bcas pa gsungs
NK128(nyo)001:5306: tha ma zang zing gis gnyes par mdzad cing gsang mtshan rdo rje dbang grub rtsal du btags so //
NK128(nyo)001:5307: slob dpon 'di'i rnam thar cung zad brjod na /
NK128(nyo)001:5308: yab yum ni gong du smos pa ltar gnubs yon tan rgya mtsho dang glan lcam gnyis yin la /
NK128(nyo)001:5309: sku sras che ba mtshan ye shes rgya mtshor grags
NK128(nyo)001:5310: shing yab las mdo sgyu sems phyogs ma gshin drag
NK128(nyo)001:5311: sngags kyi skor sogs bum pa gang byor gsan cing
NK128(nyo)001:5312: / rtogs pa khyad par can brnyes /
NK128(nyo)001:5313: 'jam dpal tshe bdag sogs la yig sna 'ga' zhig kyang mdzad /
NK128(nyo)001:5314: sgyu 'phrul ba ltar na nyang shes rab mchog gis 'khor gsum yongs dag lan gsum mdzad de /
NK128(nyo)001:5315: ye shes rgya mtsho'i zhabs la gtugs te smin grol gnang nas grub pa brnyes par bshad /
NK128(nyo)001:5316: drag sngags kyi nus pa yang /
NK128(nyo)001:5317: bon po dang 'gras pa la bsgrub mthu mdzad pas
NK128(nyo)001:5318: bon po rnams kha phung du btang ste sangs rgyas
NK128(nyo)001:5319: kyi bstan pa dar bar mdzad /
NK128(nyo)001:5320: mdor na gdul bya rnams la phrin las rnam bzhi'i
NK128(nyo)001:5321: don rgya cher mdzad de rig 'dzin gyi sa la
NK128(nyo)001:5322: gshegs so // gzhan yang dge mched bco lnga las
NK128(nyo)001:5323: slob bu 'phel tshul sogs rgya cher 'dug mod kyang
NK128(nyo)001:5324: gshegs so // / ha cang yi ge mang skyon
NK128(nyo)001:5325: du 'dug pas 'dir brgyud tshul dngos bshad pa la
NK128(nyo)001:5326: gshegs so // / / gnubs ye shes rgya mtshos byang chub rnam gsum la gsungs te /
NK128(nyo)001:5328: rgya ston blo gros byang chub /
NK128(nyo)001:5329: mar pa yon tan byang chub /
NK128(nyo)001:5330: sna nam tshul khrims byang chub dang gsum yin te /
NK128(nyo)001:5331: khong gsum la ye shes rgya mtshos khu lung du dbang bskur zhing /
NK128(nyo)001:5332: yon du rgya ston gyi g.yu /
NK128(nyo)001:5334: sna nam gyis khrab rnams phul zhing /
NK128(nyo)001:5335: gsang mtshan rgya ston la rdo rje las grub rtsal /
NK128(nyo)001:5336: mar pa la rdo rje lhun grub rtsal /
NK128(nyo)001:5337: sna nam la rdo rje sgrub mchog rtsal du btags shing /
NK128(nyo)001:5338: de gsum gas bshad sgrub kyis sgo nas gdul bya bskyangs shing /
NK128(nyo)001:5339: rang don du man ngag rdzogs pa chen po'i dgongs
NK128(nyo)001:5340: nyams mngon du gyur nas rig 'dzin gyi sa la
NK128(nyo)001:5341: gshegs so // byang chub rnam pa gsum las /
NK128(nyo)001:5342: khyad par du rgya ston blo gros byang chub kyis
NK128(nyo)001:5343: sku tshe'i stod la lho brag pa sna nam zhal
NK128(nyo)001:5344: yon po sogs bzhi la bshad zer ba chos 'byung
NK128(nyo)001:5345: rnying pa rnams la 'dug kyang zhal yon ma yin
NK128(nyo)001:5346: te / rgyal po'i btsun mo sna nam baza'i pha
NK128(nyo)001:5347: ming gi brgyud pa mig yon por yod pas zhal
NK128(nyo)001:5348: yon pa yin zhes gtad rgyar bshad cing /
NK128(nyo)001:5350: shangs kyi stong tshab 'phags pa rgya mtsho /
NK128(nyo)001:5351: sna nam gyi mgar chung tshul khrims bzang po /
NK128(nyo)001:5352: 'u yug pa dbyar gsal ba'i byang chub dang gsum zhang yon po ste bzhir gsungs /
NK128(nyo)001:5353: rgya ston gyi bar du khro bo che khyim phyogs
NK128(nyo)001:5354: kyi tho gar nam mkha' sde la gtsang phung po
NK128(nyo)001:5355: ri bo cher dbang bskur zhing /
NK128(nyo)001:5356: dbang yon du glang bzang po zhig dang nas khal brgya phul zhing /
NK128(nyo)001:5357: gsang mtshan rdo rje dngos grub gter du btags shing rig 'dzin gyi sa la gshegs so //
NK128(nyo)001:5358: rgya ston gyi sku tshe'i smad la nyang smad rgyal chen gyi zhu bsod nams sh+aakya la gsungs shing /
NK128(nyo)001:5359: gsang mtshan rdo rje 'phrin las rtsal du btags shing rig 'dzin gyi sa la gshegs so //
NK128(nyo)001:5360: de ltar rgya ston blo gros byang chub kyi slob
NK128(nyo)001:5361: ma tho gar nam mkha' sde dang zhu ston bsod
NK128(nyo)001:5362: nams sh+aakya gnyis kas zur po che la gnang ba
NK128(nyo)001:5363: yin pas / zur gyi gdung rabs sogs rgyas par gzhan du shes la /
NK128(nyo)001:5364: 'dir rnam thar mdo tsam brjod pa'i dbang du bgyis na /
NK128(nyo)001:5365: gsang sngags kyi bstan pa tha mar zur la babs
NK128(nyo)001:5366: te zur bo che sh+aakya 'byung gnas kyi dbu brnyes
NK128(nyo)001:5367: / zur chung pa shes rab grags kyis srol gtod /
NK128(nyo)001:5368: zur sh+aakya seng ges dar zhing rgyas par mdzad pas na zur mes dben gsum zhes grags la /
NK128(nyo)001:5369: de yang bde gshegs zur po che sh+aakya 'byung gnas kyi 'khrungs yul ni mdo khams yin pas /
NK128(nyo)001:5370: de yang khams kyi yar rdzong zhes sam g.yar mo
NK128(nyo)001:5371: bya ba lung pa ril po rdzong du song ba
NK128(nyo)001:5372: zhig yin la / yab zung +aa tsa ra ya
NK128(nyo)001:5373: zhes bya ba chung ngu la rab tu byung nas
NK128(nyo)001:5374: bsnyen par rdzogs pa'i mtshan shes rab 'byung gnas zhes
NK128(nyo)001:5375: bya ba rgya gar du lo bcu bzhugs te /
NK128(nyo)001:5376: mkhyen pa pan+di ta rnams dang mnyam par gyur pa mtshan nyid sde gsum /
NK128(nyo)001:5377: kri yog sde gsum la sogs pa du ma mkhyen zhing /
NK128(nyo)001:5378: 'khor dang longs spyod spangs te gnas lugs kyi don nyams su bzhes shing bzhugs pa des /
NK128(nyo)001:5379: 'gro ba'i don du rigs rgyud sprul sku 'jog pa'i
NK128(nyo)001:5380: phyir yon bdag mo bde ba lcam zhes bya ba
NK128(nyo)001:5381: las rgyar bsten cing bzhugs pa'i tshe /
NK128(nyo)001:5382: yab kyi mnal lam du nam mkha' nas gser gyi
NK128(nyo)001:5383: 'khor lo rtsibs stong dang ldan pa zhig yum gyi
NK128(nyo)001:5384: phyag tu bab / 'phags pa spyan ras gzigs yum
NK128(nyo)001:5385: la thim pa zhig byung ba dang mnal sad pas
NK128(nyo)001:5386: phyag tu bab / / nyi ma shar zhing 'dzam bu'i gling gi nyi ma bod la shar /
NK128(nyo)001:5387: sprul pa'i sku byon no zhes pa'i sgra grags so //
NK128(nyo)001:5388: yum gyi mnal lam du mi dkar po zhig gi dam rdzas yin zer ba'i ril bu gnyis dang /
NK128(nyo)001:5389: glegs bam zhig sbyin pa rmis nas yab la zhus pas /
NK128(nyo)001:5390: nga la yang mdang rmi lam bzang sprul pa'i sku zhig 'byon pa yin te 'ong /
NK128(nyo)001:5391: bde bar btsas na zhabs tog dang rim gro bya dgos /
NK128(nyo)001:5392: rkyen ma byung bar bya ba gal che bas bzab dgos gsungs so //
NK128(nyo)001:5393: de nas zla dgu ngo bcu nas sku bltams pa'i
NK128(nyo)001:5394: tshe mes chen po rin chen rgya mtsho la bstan
NK128(nyo)001:5395: pas / sangs rgyas kyi bstan pa la phan thogs
NK128(nyo)001:5396: pa zhig yongs bar 'dug gsungs nas mtshan sh+aakya 'byung
NK128(nyo)001:5397: gnas zhes bya bar btags so /
NK128(nyo)001:5398: chung ngu'i dus su yab kyi drung du bris klog mthar phyin par mdzad /
NK128(nyo)001:5399: sgyu 'phrul gyi skor dang gdams ngag phran tshegs mang po zhus /
NK128(nyo)001:5400: sku cher brtas nas bla chen dgongs par rab gsal
NK128(nyo)001:5401: gyi drung du tshigs gsum rim nod kyi bsnyen par
NK128(nyo)001:5402: rdzogs shing / 'dir sprul pa'i skur 'dug pas mtshan spo mi dgos gsungs /
NK128(nyo)001:5403: mes chen po rin chen rgya mtsho'i drung du mtshan
NK128(nyo)001:5404: nyid sde gsum gyi chos la mkhas par sbyangs te
NK128(nyo)001:5405: / gsang sngags phyi rgyud kri ya rnam 'joms ljang gu /
NK128(nyo)001:5406: u pa ya rnam snang sgyu 'phrul dra ba /
NK128(nyo)001:5407: yo ga dpal mchog dang po rnams dang /
NK128(nyo)001:5408: gsang sngags nang gi thabs lam rtsa rlung gi gdams pa yang mang du mkhyen nas /
NK128(nyo)001:5409: 'gro don gar 'phel gzigs pas dbus gtsang du yod par dgongs nas byon te /
NK128(nyo)001:5410: de yang nyid kyi gsungs las /
NK128(nyo)001:5413: gdams ngag skyo grogs su khrid /
NK128(nyo)001:5414: dad pas sna drangs te mdo khams kyi sa cha
NK128(nyo)001:5415: brgal te 'dam phyogs su nye bar sleb ces gsungs
NK128(nyo)001:5416: la / der 'dam du byon nas lam ma rnyed
NK128(nyo)001:5417: pa la sprin gseb nas lha'i bu gnyis kyis legs
NK128(nyo)001:5418: par mchod cing lam bstan nas shis par brjod nyi
NK128(nyo)001:5419: ma dbus phyogs su byon nas yar klung gi na
NK128(nyo)001:5420: mo lung du gsang sngags phyi rgyud la bsgrub pa
NK128(nyo)001:5422: thugs la nga rtsol med theg chen gyi don la blo 'byongs par /
NK128(nyo)001:5424: tshegs chung la bsgrub sla ba tshe 'dir rig 'dzin
NK128(nyo)001:5425: gyi sa non pa'i gsang sngags bla med kyi chos
NK128(nyo)001:5426: zhig btsal la bsgrub bo snyam du dgongs pa'i nub
NK128(nyo)001:5427: mo nags tshal can gyi ri la sgom shig zer
NK128(nyo)001:5428: ba'i lung bstan byung ba la /
NK128(nyo)001:5429: thugs kyi dgongs pa dam pa'i chos 'di dbus su
NK128(nyo)001:5430: babs nas gtsang du dar ba yin pas gtsang po
NK128(nyo)001:5431: 'di dang 'grogs nas 'gro dgos dgongs te yar byon
NK128(nyo)001:5432: pas / gnam ri mo'i ko sa zhes bya ba
NK128(nyo)001:5433: gad pa sna phug 'dra ba'i rtsar phebs pa dang
NK128(nyo)001:5435: 'o gtsang gi phyogs na gsang sngags rnying ma'i chos
NK128(nyo)001:5436: la mkhas shing grub pa brnyes pa gang na su
NK128(nyo)001:5437: yod dris pas / nags tshal sgril gsum bya ba na yod zer ba la /
NK128(nyo)001:5438: sngar mnal lam du nags tshal gyi ri la bsgoms zer ba dran te /
NK128(nyo)001:5439: der byon nas dge gang gi lce sh+aakya mchog la bdud rtsi sman bsgrub la sogs zhus /
NK128(nyo)001:5440: lang gro chos lung gi nyang ye shes 'byung gnas
NK128(nyo)001:5441: la zur gyi pha chos sgyu 'phrul dang sems phyogs
NK128(nyo)001:5442: skor zhus / yul gsar gyi gnyen nag dbang grags
NK128(nyo)001:5443: dang lce sh+aakya rgyal mtshan la gsang dbang dang thabs
NK128(nyo)001:5444: skor zhus / lam skor zhus / gnubs chen sangs
NK128(nyo)001:5445: rgyas ye shes kyi thugs sras bzhi'i gras nyang stod
NK128(nyo)001:5446: kyi 'bre khro chung la par bkab dang lam rim
NK128(nyo)001:5447: skor zhus / lam skor zhus / / ka dag lhun grub skor zhus /
NK128(nyo)001:5448: ldan ma sher tshul la yang dag la sogs pa zhus /
NK128(nyo)001:5449: bsam yas mchims phu'i rog sh+aakya 'byung gnas la yang dag gi skor rnams zhus /
NK128(nyo)001:5450: rgya ston gyi slob ma tho gar nam mkha' lde
NK128(nyo)001:5451: la sgrol gyi se tog gi phur dbang dang rgyud
NK128(nyo)001:5452: bshad zhus / khyad par 'dus pa mdo'i dbang yongs rdzogs gsan zhing /
NK128(nyo)001:5453: mdo lnga 'grel pa thems dang bcas pa mdo phran /
NK128(nyo)001:5454: rdzogs chen man ngag dang bcas pa gsan pa'i yon
NK128(nyo)001:5455: du rta gcig gi sna drangs pa'i nor sna mang
NK128(nyo)001:5456: du phul / gsang mtshan rdo rje bdud 'dul ba rtsal tu btags /
NK128(nyo)001:5457: zhu ston bsod nams sh+aakya la yang mdo yongs rdzogs
NK128(nyo)001:5458: gsan te gsang mtshan rdo rje zhi ba rtsal du
NK128(nyo)001:5459: btags / gzhan yang stong tshab byang chub /
NK128(nyo)001:5460: rgya ston blo gros bka' sdod ye shes snying po rnams la yang mdo lung dbang bsgrub /
NK128(nyo)001:5461: rgyud 'grel 'phrin las dang bcas pa gsan pa yin te /
NK128(nyo)001:5463: zur chen sh+aaka 'byung rdo rje bdud 'dul rtsal //
NK128(nyo)001:5464: tho gar gyis btags zhu yis zhi ba rtsal //
NK128(nyo)001:5465: stong tshab byang chub rgya ston blo gros dang //
NK128(nyo)001:5466: bka' sdod ye shes snying po rnams la ni //
NK128(nyo)001:5467: mdo lung dbang bsgrub rgyud 'grel 'phrin las gsan //
NK128(nyo)001:5469: der ma zad bla ma brgya rtsa tsam brten zhing
NK128(nyo)001:5470: re re la yang 'khor gsum yongs dag gi 'bul
NK128(nyo)001:5471: bas mnyes par mdzad pa yin te /
NK128(nyo)001:5473: khyad par bla ma brgya rtsa mnyes par brten //
NK128(nyo)001:5475: gzhan yang phyis mang mkhar du 'brog mi lo ts+aa
NK128(nyo)001:5476: bas pan+di ta ga ya d+ha ra spyan drangs pa'i
NK128(nyo)001:5477: tshe lam 'bras zhu ba'i gser ma 'khyongs pas /
NK128(nyo)001:5478: zur po che sku bsod rgyas pa'i skabs su yod
NK128(nyo)001:5479: pa la gser gyi phyir du chos 'dod na gser
NK128(nyo)001:5480: khur la shog gsungs par brten gser srang brgya bsnams
NK128(nyo)001:5481: nas byon te / pan chen ga ya ra d+ha
NK128(nyo)001:5482: dang 'brog mi las kye rdo rje'i dbang dang sgrub
NK128(nyo)001:5483: thabs mtsho skyes lugs sogs gsan /
NK128(nyo)001:5484: rgyud 'grel mgur la mkhas par sbyangs pa'i lo rgyus kyang snang ngo //
NK128(nyo)001:5485: de'i tshe lam 'bras kyi chos gsan pas rdzogs pa chen po la rtsal thon te /
NK128(nyo)001:5486: bla ma chen po'i bka' drin gyis /
NK128(nyo)001:5487: a pha'i sems phyogs nor bu rin chen du thal lo //
NK128(nyo)001:5489: bla ma de dag gi nang na ma jo chos
NK128(nyo)001:5490: sgron la sogs pa'i bud med kyi bla ma yang
NK128(nyo)001:5491: bcu drug tsam yod par grags shing /
NK128(nyo)001:5492: mchog tu rtsa ba'i bla ma rnams la spang dag lan bcu gsum tsam mdzad do //
NK128(nyo)001:5493: de ltar bla ma de nyid kyis mkhas pa mang po'i dgongs pa blangs /
NK128(nyo)001:5494: sde snod rgyud sde grub mtha' kun la mkhas par gyur nas /
NK128(nyo)001:5495: rtsa rgyud dang bshad rgyud du bsdebs /
NK128(nyo)001:5497: rgyud dang sgrub thabs su bsdebs /
NK128(nyo)001:5498: sgrub thabs cho ga dbang snyan brgyud gdams ngag phyag bzhes su bsdebs so //
NK128(nyo)001:5499: de ltar thos bsam gyis sgro 'dogs chod nas /
NK128(nyo)001:5500: nags tshal can gyi ri la dpal yang dag gi sgrubs pa mang du mdzad /
NK128(nyo)001:5501: de nas stod smad kun nas slob ma mang du
NK128(nyo)001:5502: 'dus nas mdo sgyu 'phrul la 'chad nyan mdzad pa'i
NK128(nyo)001:5503: dus su / tshe 'di'i g.yeng ba rgyab tu skyur /
NK128(nyo)001:5505: phyi ma'i byang chub da lta mngon du gyur pa
NK128(nyo)001:5506: nam zhig na 'byung snyam du dgongs te sgrub pa
NK128(nyo)001:5507: snying por mdzad pa'i gter len du sprang po rnal
NK128(nyo)001:5508: 'byor pa'i cha lugs shig byung ste /
NK128(nyo)001:5509: de la cung zad cig sbyin pa khos ril por thob nas /
NK128(nyo)001:5510: rtsig pa'i drung zhig tu song nas /
NK128(nyo)001:5511: zur po che 'di snyan pa dang sku bsod che yon tan mnga' bar 'dug na'ang /
NK128(nyo)001:5512: rog sh+aaka 'byung gi rgyun gtor tsam yang mi 'dug
NK128(nyo)001:5513: zer ba nye gnas kyi thos te zhus pas bos
NK128(nyo)001:5514: shog gsungs / 'bod du phyin pas brag phug gcig na ka p+aa lar zan brul za zhig 'dug /
NK128(nyo)001:5515: byon byas pas 'od ma nyan par rog sh+aaka 'byung
NK128(nyo)001:5516: mchims phu na tshe dbang thob nas yod pa yin
NK128(nyo)001:5517: / zur po che la chos len mi thong gyis
NK128(nyo)001:5518: zer rkang pa sa la mi reg pa song ngo
NK128(nyo)001:5520: rang gi slob ma rtse mo bzhi las sgom sgrub
NK128(nyo)001:5521: kyi rtse mo mtsho nya'i bzang sgom shes rab rgyal
NK128(nyo)001:5522: po nyid drel khal dang bcas chos lan du btang
NK128(nyo)001:5523: ba bsam yas su phyin te dris pas /
NK128(nyo)001:5524: gzhan rgyus yod ni mi 'dug rgan mo zhig gis
NK128(nyo)001:5525: mchims phu'i ri 'di la dang po yod pa yin
NK128(nyo)001:5528: skabs re tsa na rnga sgra dang rgyu lu'i sgra ngas kyang thos zer /
NK128(nyo)001:5529: de nas bzang sgom gyis sa cha rtsa mang po
NK128(nyo)001:5530: skye sa zhig tu khal phog dad pa phul phyin
NK128(nyo)001:5531: skyes te zhag bdun gsol ba drag po btab pas
NK128(nyo)001:5532: / sgra chen po zhig byung bas bltas tsa na
NK128(nyo)001:5533: brag phug sgo dang nge ba zhig mthong bas the
NK128(nyo)001:5535: gdong mchi mas gang zhing dad shugs byin rlabs kyi
NK128(nyo)001:5536: rtsal dang ldan pas phug par thal gyis phyiin pas
NK128(nyo)001:5537: / gsang ba'i sgrol ging bco brgyad kyis 'du bar
NK128(nyo)001:5538: 'ong ba 'di sgrol zhing zer brdeg grabs byed pa
NK128(nyo)001:5540: de las can yin pas ma sgrol gsungs /
NK128(nyo)001:5541: der lo rgyus rnams zhus pas /
NK128(nyo)001:5542: nga rog sh+aaka 'byung slob ma zur sh+aaka 'byung /
NK128(nyo)001:5543: mtshams sbyor shes rab rgyal po rnams rten 'brel bzang gsungs te /
NK128(nyo)001:5544: zur po che sngar nas yang dag gsungs pa'i slob ma yin pas dam tshig la dgongs te /
NK128(nyo)001:5545: bzang sgom shes rab rgyal po la sangs rgyas mnyam sbyor gyi dbang bskur zhing /
NK128(nyo)001:5546: yang dag gi bdag don dkyil 'khor drug gzhan don dkyil 'khor drug ste bcu gnyis /
NK128(nyo)001:5547: gzhan yang yang phur sgrags ma sogs dkyil 'khor drug cu rtsa gnyis kyi dbang bskur /
NK128(nyo)001:5548: phyag deb bka' lung gdams pa sgrub rdzas dang bcas pa gnang zhing khyer yongs pas /
NK128(nyo)001:5549: bsam yas brgal ba'i thang la sleb dus /
NK128(nyo)001:5550: drel gyi kha na khye'u dar ber thod can zhig
NK128(nyo)001:5551: 'dug pa gzigs te mchims phur bla ma'i drung du
NK128(nyo)001:5552: log nas rgyu mtshan zhus pas /
NK128(nyo)001:5553: tshang pa dung thod can yin stong grogs byed cing
NK128(nyo)001:5554: 'go bar 'dug pas mchod cig gsungs te tshangs pa'i
NK128(nyo)001:5556: de nas yar byon te bzang sgom shes rab rgyal
NK128(nyo)001:5557: pos chos skor de rnams bla ma la gsang ste
NK128(nyo)001:5558: phul lo // de nas dpon slob kun gyis sgom
NK128(nyo)001:5559: sgrub lo mang du mdzad cing slob ma 'dus pa
NK128(nyo)001:5560: rnams la 'chad nyan mdzad pas 'gro phan che bar
NK128(nyo)001:5561: phul lo // byung yang / 'di yang dge sbyor
NK128(nyo)001:5562: gyi g.yeng bar 'dug pas dben pa zhig tu 'gro
NK128(nyo)001:5563: phul lo // byung yang / dgongs te / bo
NK128(nyo)001:5564: dong mnga' bdag brag la bzhugs te sgom mdzad pas
NK128(nyo)001:5565: grwa slob rnams kyis bla ma 'byon na rang re
NK128(nyo)001:5566: yang 'gro zer te bla ma'i drung du phyin pas
NK128(nyo)001:5567: phul lo // byung yang / dgongs te / / bka' las /
NK128(nyo)001:5568: khyod rnams nga'i rtsar yong don byang chub thob pa la sgom sgrub min pa bya thabs med pas /
NK128(nyo)001:5569: 'jig rten gyi g.yengs ba skyur la sgrub pa la 'bad pa thon cig /
NK128(nyo)001:5570: nga yang sgrub pa kho na byed gsungs te sgrubs pa la bzhugs so //
NK128(nyo)001:5571: de'i tshe mkha' 'gro'i lung gis smad phyogs su /
NK128(nyo)001:5572: byon na 'gro don 'phel bar 'gyur ro zhes gsungs pas /
NK128(nyo)001:5573: dpon slob rnams kyis rta nag gi lung par byon
NK128(nyo)001:5574: te 'ug pa'i tshang yod pa'i brag phug kha shar
NK128(nyo)001:5575: bstan zhig 'dug pa der yang dag lha dgu'i sgrub
NK128(nyo)001:5577: bla mas dpal chen po yang dag lha dgu'i zhal gzigs /
NK128(nyo)001:5578: de nas bzung ste gnas kyi ming la bla ma 'ug bya lung pa zhes su grags /
NK128(nyo)001:5579: der sgrub brgyags dkon par byung ba las /
NK128(nyo)001:5580: skyes bu khyed smad phyogs su byon cig ces pa'i
NK128(nyo)001:5581: lung bstan byung ba ltar 'byon par chas pa'i tshe
NK128(nyo)001:5582: / phrag pa ri'i gzhi bdag ze re ze btsan
NK128(nyo)001:5583: bya ba de mngon sum du 'ong ste bzhugs par
NK128(nyo)001:5584: / zhus pas / bla mas nga la lung bstan yang byung /
NK128(nyo)001:5585: sgrub brgyags kyang zad pas 'gro gsungs pas /
NK128(nyo)001:5586: dpon slob rnams kyi 'tsho ba bdag gis 'bul cis kyang bzhugs par zhu zhes zhus pas /
NK128(nyo)001:5587: 'o na re zhig bsdad kyi gsungs /
NK128(nyo)001:5588: der rta nag gi phyug po chen po zhig la nad drag po byung ba la mo btab pas /
NK128(nyo)001:5589: bla ma 'ug bya lung pa la gtor ma zhus tshogs 'khor thong 'bul ba chen po phul /
NK128(nyo)001:5590: byin rlabs zhus na phan zer /
NK128(nyo)001:5591: nad pas bla ma'i drung du phyin pas zhal mthong ba tsam gyis sngar bas bder song /
NK128(nyo)001:5592: byin rlabs zhus tshogs 'khor byas ma thag tu nad drag go //
NK128(nyo)001:5593: de legs pa nad gdon gyi nyen tshad la byin
NK128(nyo)001:5594: rlabs mdzad pas phan pa'i grags pa yul mi rnams
NK128(nyo)001:5595: dang de 'bul ba dang tshogs gsog mang po byung
NK128(nyo)001:5596: bas sku bsod chen po skyes /
NK128(nyo)001:5597: yon bdag mi shong ba tsam 'dus shing thun mong
NK128(nyo)001:5598: gi dngos grub zas nor gyi yo lang chen po
NK128(nyo)001:5599: byung bas / bla mas dgongs pa /
NK128(nyo)001:5600: thun mong gi bsod nams 'di dge sbyor gyi g.yeng ba byang chub sgrub pa'i bar chad yin /
NK128(nyo)001:5601: ri bo dgu 'dus la sgom du 'gro dgongs te chas pa dang /
NK128(nyo)001:5602: yang gzhi bdag byung ste bla ma lags sgrub rgyags ni phul yod bzhugs par zhu zhus pas /
NK128(nyo)001:5603: khyed kyi 'tsho ba 'di dag po zhig kyang mi 'dug /
NK128(nyo)001:5604: dge sbyor g.yeng bas da lan 'gro gsungs pas /
NK128(nyo)001:5605: gzhi bdag de gdong mchi mas gang bzhin bla ma
NK128(nyo)001:5606: cis kyang mi bzhugs na bdag la thugs rjes dgongs
NK128(nyo)001:5607: te gang bzhugs pa nas gsol ras re gnang bar
NK128(nyo)001:5608: zhu zhus te srog snying phul /
NK128(nyo)001:5609: bla mas kyang dge bsnyen gyi sdom pa phog cing rdo rje mgyogs byed dgra 'dul rtsal du btags /
NK128(nyo)001:5610: bstan pa bsrung bar khas blangs so //
NK128(nyo)001:5611: de nas mar byon pa'i lam du rta nag gi
NK128(nyo)001:5612: g.yon rir gnas pa'i jo mo sna dmar bya ba'i
NK128(nyo)001:5613: gzhi bdag gis kyang srog snying phul nas dam la
NK128(nyo)001:5615: de nas g.yas ru thog tu byon nas /
NK128(nyo)001:5617: nga la ri bo dgu 'dus la sgom zer ba'i
NK128(nyo)001:5618: lung bstan byung ba de brag rgya bo 'di yin
NK128(nyo)001:5619: par 'dug gsungs nas dpon slob thams cad bsgrub pa
NK128(nyo)001:5620: la bzhugs pa'i dus bla ma'i drung du mkha' 'gro
NK128(nyo)001:5621: ma bud med tha mal pa'i cha lugs byas pa
NK128(nyo)001:5622: gsum byung / bla ma khyod kyi gdul bya ni g.yas ru shangs kyi mda'/
NK128(nyo)001:5623: shangs chu'i shar na lung pa dbyibs zla gam kha nub lta /
NK128(nyo)001:5624: de' phu na brag snying 'dra ba /
NK128(nyo)001:5625: mda' na thang ma tram bsgral ba'i pags pa 'dra ba /
NK128(nyo)001:5626: ri'i dbyibs glang po che'i sna 'dra ba /
NK128(nyo)001:5627: brag seng ge'i ya thod lta bu /
NK128(nyo)001:5628: rdza gsum nas chu gsum 'bab bo //
NK128(nyo)001:5629: sku gsum gyi don brnyes par byed pa'i sa zhig yod pas /
NK128(nyo)001:5630: der bsgrubs pas khyod rang skye ba 'di nyid la 'tshang rgya zhing /
NK128(nyo)001:5631: phyis 'gro don rgya cher 'gyur gyis zhes pa'i lung bstan nas mi snang bar song ngo //
NK128(nyo)001:5632: der nam langs pa dang bla mas zur chung pa la /
NK128(nyo)001:5633: nga la lung bstan 'di ltar byung bas sgrub gnas 'tshol du 'gro dgos /
NK128(nyo)001:5634: khyod rang sgrub gnas 'di la gyis gsungs nas mar
NK128(nyo)001:5635: byon te gdong po thang nas gzigs pas lung pa
NK128(nyo)001:5636: mkhyen nas / der phyag phebs te zhang mo yon tan rgyan gyis sbyin bdag byas /
NK128(nyo)001:5637: des phul ba'i phug par bla ma bzhugs /
NK128(nyo)001:5638: zung chung pa sogs sgom chen brgya lhag tsam yod
NK128(nyo)001:5639: pa kun kyang lung pa'i phu mda' thams cad du
NK128(nyo)001:5640: khyab par spyil po dang brag khung sogs pa brten
NK128(nyo)001:5642: 'tsho chas rnams yul mi tsho bdun gyis phul zhing /
NK128(nyo)001:5643: khyad par yon bdag gi rtsa ba sram pa bon grong pas byas /
NK128(nyo)001:5644: bla ma nyid sangs rgyas dngos su 'dzin no //
NK128(nyo)001:5645: der lo mang du sgrub pa mdzad pas zhi ba
NK128(nyo)001:5646: sangs rgyas bzhi bcu rtsa gnyis dang khrag 'thung lnga
NK128(nyo)001:5648: gzhan yang yi dam gyi lha du ma'i zhal gzigs shing /
NK128(nyo)001:5649: khyad par du dpal yang dag gi lha tshogs rnams la mi dang gsung gleng byed pa bzhin mdzad /
NK128(nyo)001:5650: go ri brgyad la sogs pa bran du 'khol /
NK128(nyo)001:5651: gzhan yang mi ma yin rnams las gang bcol nyan
NK128(nyo)001:5652: cing mthun rkyen dang mchod rdzas 'bul ba sogs byung
NK128(nyo)001:5653: ngo // yang dus lan cig zhang mo phug tu
NK128(nyo)001:5654: zur chung pa sogs slob ma rnams la yang dag
NK128(nyo)001:5655: gi dbang bskur mdzad pa'i tshe /
NK128(nyo)001:5658: khyod kyis dpal chen po'i zhal gzigs shing ma mo mkha' 'gro bran du 'khol 'dug pas /
NK128(nyo)001:5659: bdag cag slob ma rnams la yang zhal re ston par zhu zhes zhus pas /
NK128(nyo)001:5661: nga la rig 'dzin bla ma zhig gis he ru
NK128(nyo)001:5662: ka'i sku bzhengs na gdon rnams thul zhing 'gro don
NK128(nyo)001:5663: 'byung ba'i lung bstan yod pas he ru ka'i sku
NK128(nyo)001:5664: bzhengs pa'i dus su zhal bstan gyis gsung zur chung
NK128(nyo)001:5665: pas lung ston pa'i rig 'dzin bla ma de su
NK128(nyo)001:5666: yin zhus pas / bla ma'i zhal nas /
NK128(nyo)001:5667: ngas kyang khyed kyi mtshan ci lags zhus pas /
NK128(nyo)001:5669: nga ni nam mkha'i snying po ste //
NK128(nyo)001:5670: skye 'chi med pa rdo rje'i sku //
NK128(nyo)001:5672: 'gro don mthar rdzogs dbang rnams sbyin //
NK128(nyo)001:5673: skal ldan khyod la smin par shog /
NK128(nyo)001:5674: ces gsungs nas mi snang bar gshegs so //
NK128(nyo)001:5675: de'i dus su nga la bde stong gi nyams khyad par can rgyud la skyes /
NK128(nyo)001:5676: rig 'dzin gyi byin rlabs zhugs pa'i rtags mang po byung gsungs /
NK128(nyo)001:5678: nye gnas don yod rdo rje la /
NK128(nyo)001:5680: khyod kyi bzo bo bos shig /
NK128(nyo)001:5681: nged tshos sa 'dul byed gsungs nas /
NK128(nyo)001:5682: lha khang 'debs sa brag seng ge ya thog gi
NK128(nyo)001:5683: khar bzhugs nas gtor ma bshams te 'phrin las mdzad
NK128(nyo)001:5684: sa bzung gi tshe bla mas dpal chen po'i stang
NK128(nyo)001:5685: stabs mdzad pas / bla ma nyid dpal chen po dngos su mthong ba mang po byung /
NK128(nyo)001:5686: rtsig rmang dang 'gram 'ding ba'i tshe gzhon pa 'gas
NK128(nyo)001:5687: 'gram rdo che ba re blangs te de la sa
NK128(nyo)001:5688: dkar gyi yi ge bris te zur chung pa sku
NK128(nyo)001:5689: lus bongs chung zhing sro ngan pa la zur za
NK128(nyo)001:5690: zhing 'gram rdo 'jog dgos tshul bris pas /
NK128(nyo)001:5692: khyed rang rnams nang du chos ston gsol cig /
NK128(nyo)001:5693: nga yar yong gsungs kyang ma byon /
NK128(nyo)001:5694: gzhan tshos chos ston gsol nas byon pa dang /
NK128(nyo)001:5696: rdzu 'phrul gyi pha bong g.yag shad tsam brgyad la
NK128(nyo)001:5697: zur chung pa'i gyad rdo lags zhes pa'i yi ge
NK128(nyo)001:5698: bris nas phyogs mtshams brgyad du bzhag 'dug pas kun
NK128(nyo)001:5699: yid ches shing / de gong du nag phyogs kyi
NK128(nyo)001:5700: lha 'dre 'gas phrag dog byas te nyin mo brtsigs
NK128(nyo)001:5701: kyang mtshan mo bshig pa la /
NK128(nyo)001:5702: zur chung pas gyad rdo bzhag pa tshun lha 'dres kyang bshig ma nus par grags /
NK128(nyo)001:5703: de nas rtsig pa grub ste thog 'bub pa'i ka ba btsugs pa'i tshe /
NK128(nyo)001:5704: bla mas ka ba bzhi po 'di skyog por 'dug pas zur pas srongs shing gsungs pas /
NK128(nyo)001:5705: zur chung pas ting 'dzin zhig mdzad pas mda' ltar bsrongs so //
NK128(nyo)001:5706: thog phub zin nas dpon slob rnams kyis yang dag
NK128(nyo)001:5707: gi lo sgrub zhig mdzad de sgrub pa thon pa
NK128(nyo)001:5709: nga he ru ka'i sku bzhengs pa'i dus la babs 'dug /
NK128(nyo)001:5710: ngas lha bzo bo bkugs pas khugs yong gin 'dug gsungs pas /
NK128(nyo)001:5711: zhag gnyis nas byung ba dang /
NK128(nyo)001:5712: bla mas ma mkhyen par ltar mdzad de /
NK128(nyo)001:5713: khyed rnams yon tan mkhan gyi rigs yin nam gsungs /
NK128(nyo)001:5714: bdag cag gis lha bzo shes lags /
NK128(nyo)001:5715: bla ma'i drung du chos zhu ru yong bas thugs la 'dogs dgos zhus pas rten 'brel bzang /
NK128(nyo)001:5717: snyigs dus su 'gro don chen po 'byung bas /
NK128(nyo)001:5718: dpal chen po'i sku zhig bzhengs grogs kyis gsungs pa la /
NK128(nyo)001:5721: chos gnang ba bsod nams bsags zer /
NK128(nyo)001:5722: de nas lha bzo ba rnams la yang dag gi dbang bskur zhig gnang /
NK128(nyo)001:5723: dur khrod brgyad kyi sa chu /
NK128(nyo)001:5725: rigs bsrel dang skye bdun gyi sha /
NK128(nyo)001:5726: chos sman sogs dam rdzas khyad par can dang /
NK128(nyo)001:5727: ru shing gi chas rnams bsags te bzhengs pa la /
NK128(nyo)001:5728: sku tshad ji ltar bgyi zhus pas /
NK128(nyo)001:5729: rgyal ba'i sku la tshad bzung ma mchis te //
NK128(nyo)001:5730: mthun 'jug thabs kyis 'gro ba 'dren pa'i dpal //
NK128(nyo)001:5731: gang zag blo dang ji ltar 'tshams par bzhengs //
NK128(nyo)001:5732: 'gro don thog mtha' dpangs dang bstun cig gsungs //
NK128(nyo)001:5733: de nas ru shing brtsigs nas dpal chen yang dag
NK128(nyo)001:5734: 'bras bu'i sku zhal gsum phyag drug pa bzhengs pa
NK128(nyo)001:5735: / bzo bo rnams kyis bltas pas /
NK128(nyo)001:5736: mtshar rngams bzhad pa shin tu legs pa byung yang /
NK128(nyo)001:5737: bla mas zhal gzigs pa ltar ma byung bas da dung skyor cig gsungs /
NK128(nyo)001:5738: lan mang por bshig cing bskyar bas kyang ma byung /
NK128(nyo)001:5739: der bla mas khyed rnams nga la bltas na nga 'dra shes sam gsungs pas /
NK128(nyo)001:5741: sngar slob ma rnams sku bzhengs dus zhal ston par gsungs pa dus la bab ste /
NK128(nyo)001:5742: nye gnas la tshogs 'khor bshams shig gsungs te bla
NK128(nyo)001:5743: mas yang dag gi gzhung bsrangs mchod bstod tshogs 'khor
NK128(nyo)001:5744: rnams mdzad nas / de khyed rang rnams ma yengs par ltos shig gsungs te /
NK128(nyo)001:5745: bla mas dpal chen po'i lta stangs mdzad pas /
NK128(nyo)001:5746: bla ma nyid he ru ka dngos su gyur te
NK128(nyo)001:5747: dbu sprin dang na bun gyi mtshams su lhag ge
NK128(nyo)001:5748: ba / ljags 'dril zhing mche ba gtsigs pa /
NK128(nyo)001:5749: rdo rje'i gshog pas bar snang khebs pa /
NK128(nyo)001:5750: sku mdog mthing nag zhal gcig phyag gnyis pa zhabs
NK128(nyo)001:5751: g.yas 'ug pa lung gi gdong dang g.yon btsang po'i
NK128(nyo)001:5752: pur khang gi ri rtser bzhag pa /
NK128(nyo)001:5753: shin tu che ba dur khrod kyi chas rnams kyis brgyan cing /
NK128(nyo)001:5754: sku la me dpung 'ur 'ur 'bar ba zhig lam me mthong ba dang /
NK128(nyo)001:5755: lha bzo ba rnams zil ma bzod par dran med du brgyal /
NK128(nyo)001:5756: da khyed tshos shes sam gsungs pas /
NK128(nyo)001:5757: da res zhal gcig phyag gnyis pa de mthong ba ma gtogs dran pa gang yang mi gda'/
NK128(nyo)001:5758: da zhal gsum phyag drug pa zhig ston par zhu zhus pas /
NK128(nyo)001:5759: zab kyang zab ste sla yang sla /
NK128(nyo)001:5760: gdul bya'i dbang gis zhal gcig phyag gnyis 'byon /
NK128(nyo)001:5761: zhes sogs gsungs te zhal gcig phyag gnyis pa bzhengs so //
NK128(nyo)001:5762: der bka'i bgro ba mdzad cing bzhengs pas lte ba
NK128(nyo)001:5763: man chad snga ma mthong ba dang 'dra rung tsam
NK128(nyo)001:5764: shes la / de yan chad yang yang skyar dgos byung bas /
NK128(nyo)001:5766: khyed rnams sgrib pa ma dag pa yin /
NK128(nyo)001:5767: nga'i chu mig pha ki bdud rtsi ka p+aa li
NK128(nyo)001:5768: gang gtor ba las byung ba'i sgrub chu yin pas
NK128(nyo)001:5770: lha khang 'di la skor ba bdun gyis la shog /
NK128(nyo)001:5771: der bar du nang la su yang ma 'ong zhig /
NK128(nyo)001:5772: ngas 'dir dpal chen po la gsol ba btab la e yong blta'o gsungs /
NK128(nyo)001:5773: der khong rnams khrus dang skor ba byed ring nang na lab dir ri ri 'dug /
NK128(nyo)001:5774: skor ba tshar nas nang du phyin pas /
NK128(nyo)001:5776: bla ma dgongs pa la bzhugs /
NK128(nyo)001:5777: 'jim pa sbyar ba rnams thams cad zad /
NK128(nyo)001:5778: dpal chen po'i sku stod yan chad rang byon du grub 'dug pas /
NK128(nyo)001:5779: khong rnams kyis bla ma la phyag 'tshal zhing /
NK128(nyo)001:5780: bla ma rang gis 'di ltar mkhyen pa la /
NK128(nyo)001:5781: nged tsho ci byed lta ba 'dug zhus pas /
NK128(nyo)001:5782: nga nyid lta bu'i gang zag la /
NK128(nyo)001:5783: nga nyid lta ba'i rten cig 'byung /
NK128(nyo)001:5785: nad dang gdon gyis gnyen por 'gyur /
NK128(nyo)001:5786: sngar yang he ru ka nyid la brten nas he ru ka nyid 'byung ba yin la /
NK128(nyo)001:5787: da yang he ru ka nyid kyi rten la thim par 'gyur ro //
NK128(nyo)001:5788: zhes ma 'ongs pa na bla ma nyid sku de la thim pa'i lung bstan yang mdzad do //
NK128(nyo)001:5789: 'dir dus phyis tshogs 'du chen po yong bas gsang
NK128(nyo)001:5790: sgrub mi btub pas khro mo brgyad rgyud ltar bzhengs
NK128(nyo)001:5791: shig gsungs nas rgyud lugs ltar bzhengs logs bris ni
NK128(nyo)001:5792: g.yas la sgyu 'phrul zhi ba dang g.yon la khro
NK128(nyo)001:5793: bo'i dkyil 'khor / mdun du mdo yongs rdzogs te dkyil 'khor chen po gsum /
NK128(nyo)001:5794: sgo'i nang logs su dpal mgon legs ldan drag po gshin rje ltar sgrub pa /
NK128(nyo)001:5795: stag zhon mon pa sde brgyad dang bcas pa bris /
NK128(nyo)001:5796: rab gnas ran te chang ma sus byed /
NK128(nyo)001:5798: ja ma dgos sogs bka' bgros pas /
NK128(nyo)001:5800: kha sang nas lha bzo ba dang grwa sgoms las mi rnams yun ring /
NK128(nyo)001:5801: mgron po mang po gso dgos pa la brten nas
NK128(nyo)001:5802: chas ka che ba zhig kyang mi 'dug pas re
NK128(nyo)001:5804: yon bdag rnams la skyin 'phrul 'dra yang dgos pa gda' lags zhus pas /
NK128(nyo)001:5805: zur chen gyis chang la nas khal stong gis 'dang ngam gsungs /
NK128(nyo)001:5806: zur chung pas rab gnas dus la byed sha chang phye gsum mi la skyin 'phrul mi byed /
NK128(nyo)001:5809: sha sram sa bon grong pa'i glang la byed /
NK128(nyo)001:5810: rtsam pa mi ma yin gyi 'bul 'degs bskul bas chog /
NK128(nyo)001:5811: de ltar byas pas ma 'dang ba med gsungs /
NK128(nyo)001:5812: bla ma zur chen gyis nye gnas la khyed rang nas bre drug tshos /
NK128(nyo)001:5813: mi tshor nged rab gnas byed pa'i chang mang po 'tshod kyi yod zer ba gyis gsungs /
NK128(nyo)001:5814: zur chung pas 'og gdong klu bdud kyi sring mo
NK128(nyo)001:5815: de chang mar bkugs pas sbal ba khra mo zhig
NK128(nyo)001:5816: byung ba ting nge 'dzin gyis btul bas /
NK128(nyo)001:5817: bud med dkar mo zhig tu gyur pa la bla mas chang ma gyis gsungs pas /
NK128(nyo)001:5819: nged klu mo 'di grib la sdar /
NK128(nyo)001:5821: bla ma'i zil yang mi bzod pas chang 'go yang
NK128(nyo)001:5822: mi thon pas bdag gi ming po la 'chol pa
NK128(nyo)001:5823: zhu cha rkyen gang dgos 'bul zer nas btang ngo
NK128(nyo)001:5824: // yang bla mas zur chung par khyod 'gugs sam byin gyis brlabs gsungs pas /
NK128(nyo)001:5826: dgongs pa la bzhugs te lcags kyu'i phyag rgya mdzad pas /
NK128(nyo)001:5827: sdig pa rtsig khog tsam zhig byung ba la sngar
NK128(nyo)001:5828: ting nge 'dzin gyis gzir bas rang gzugs bstan pa
NK128(nyo)001:5829: la / bla mas nged kyi rab gnas ma thon par chang ma gyis shig gsungs pas /
NK128(nyo)001:5830: bdag lha 'dre'i rigs 'di bya dga' dang sems 'dzin
NK128(nyo)001:5831: byed dgos pa nga bas mi khom yang bka' mi
NK128(nyo)001:5832: gcog pas gang gsungs sgrub ces klu bdud ming sring
NK128(nyo)001:5833: gis srog snying phul dam tshig mnos /
NK128(nyo)001:5834: ming po la rdo rje bdud 'dul rtsal dang sring mo la dkar mo mdzes ldan mar btags /
NK128(nyo)001:5835: bstan pa bsrung bar dam bcas so //
NK128(nyo)001:5837: rab gnas kyi chang ma byed par gnang yang bas grabs mdzad pa dang /
NK128(nyo)001:5838: nged rnams grib la bsdar bas sa phyogs gtsang mar
NK128(nyo)001:5839: spos chus byug shing sdod pa btsan sar zhu zer
NK128(nyo)001:5841: ngas byin gyis brlabs kyis gsungs te /
NK128(nyo)001:5842: rgya rdzas them bu gsum brtsegs ma spos chus bkrus /
NK128(nyo)001:5843: nas bre drug gi glums blugs te bdud dang klu
NK128(nyo)001:5844: bsten pa'i rdzas mang po dang bcas te klu bdud
NK128(nyo)001:5846: chu blugs sa zhig ma gtogs dar sna lngas dril /
NK128(nyo)001:5848: de'i phyir bla ma'i phod ka rnying pa zhig gi g.yogs /
NK128(nyo)001:5849: thugs dam rdo rje'i mdud pas bcings nas /
NK128(nyo)001:5850: phod ka'i phu dung nas chu blugs shing /
NK128(nyo)001:5851: them bu nas btsag bas 'dzad med byung ngo //
NK128(nyo)001:5853: chang gis ldang bar 'dug phye ji ltar byed zer ba la /
NK128(nyo)001:5854: rtsam pa blugs sa'i phad snod mang po g.yor la shog gsungs /
NK128(nyo)001:5855: phad snod mang po byung ba dang /
NK128(nyo)001:5856: gtor ma zhig bshams gsungs nye gnas la ngas gtor ma bsngo yi /
NK128(nyo)001:5857: khyed rang phad snod rnams kha phye la rtsam pa spar ba re blug la zhog gsungs /
NK128(nyo)001:5858: de ltar byas nas sang nyin bltas pas phad snod thams cad tsam pas khrig ge khengs 'dug go //
NK128(nyo)001:5860: rtsam chang gis yong ba 'dug sha ji ltar byed zhus pas /
NK128(nyo)001:5861: bla ma'i zhal nas rnal 'byor pa zhig song la
NK128(nyo)001:5862: sram sa bon grong pa la glang rnams snang ma
NK128(nyo)001:5864: der rnal 'byor pa des sbyin bdag gi sar phyin te /
NK128(nyo)001:5865: nged rab gnas byed pa'i chang mang po btsos pa'i
NK128(nyo)001:5866: sbang ma nags gseb la pho gtong gi yod pas
NK128(nyo)001:5867: / glang rnams spang ma za ba la thong gsung gi 'dug byas pas /
NK128(nyo)001:5868: glang nyi shu tsam bskur ba ded nas yong /
NK128(nyo)001:5869: bla mas zur chung pa la /
NK128(nyo)001:5870: khyod sgrol lam gso gsungs pas /
NK128(nyo)001:5871: bla mar sgrol bar zhus pas /
NK128(nyo)001:5872: bla ma zur chen dgongs pa la bzhugs te glang rnams la thun re 'phangs /
NK128(nyo)001:5874: glang rnams rang sar 'gyel te khrag ma 'thigs /
NK128(nyo)001:5875: pags pa ma ral sha rnams ma 'gram pa bsgral lo //
NK128(nyo)001:5877: rus pa lhu tshig ma bral bar gyis /
NK128(nyo)001:5878: nang gi don snod la rma med par phyi sha thams cad brnag ma dras nas tshos shig gsungs /
NK128(nyo)001:5879: de ltar sha chang phye sogs thams cad 'byor te rab gnas mdzad cing ston mo cher bshams te /
NK128(nyo)001:5880: rab gnas legs par grub pa dang glang len mi byung ste /
NK128(nyo)001:5881: bla mas zur chung pa la glang gsos la sprod cig gsungs pas /
NK128(nyo)001:5882: zur chung pas glang rnams kyi pags pa'i khar rus pa dang nang rol rnams rang sar bzhag /
NK128(nyo)001:5883: na bzas bkab nas ting nge 'dzin la bzhugs te
NK128(nyo)001:5884: se gol lan gsum gtogs pas glang rnams sngar bas
NK128(nyo)001:5885: bzang ba re byas nas khog ste langs byung ba
NK128(nyo)001:5887: der bla ma yab sras kyis sbyor sgrol bsad gso mdzad pas /
NK128(nyo)001:5888: bu slob yon bdag rnams kyang dad cing mos par gyur /
NK128(nyo)001:5889: bla ma zur chen yang dgyes te /
NK128(nyo)001:5890: dpal chen po'i sku la gzigs te 'gro don nus pa zhig mdzad 'tshal lo gsungs pas /
NK128(nyo)001:5891: sku gzugs kyis hee rmos ci 'tshal zhes gsungs pas /
NK128(nyo)001:5892: dang po sku 'dra'i zhal rngam zhal du yod pa
NK128(nyo)001:5893: la de nas bzhad zhal du song ba yin no
NK128(nyo)001:5894: // yang bla mas nye gnas la chas ka ci
NK128(nyo)001:5895: yod lha khang du nged rang rnams yang dag gi
NK128(nyo)001:5896: sgrub pa zhig byed pa yin gsungs pas /
NK128(nyo)001:5897: lo sgrub mdzad pa'i cha rkyen mi gda' lags zhus /
NK128(nyo)001:5898: zur chung pas chang gis ni ldang bar yod chang ma bsgor bas chog /
NK128(nyo)001:5899: sha lhag dang rtsam pa yang 'dug rnal 'byor pa
NK128(nyo)001:5900: dam tshig ma nyams na 'tsho ba snang srid lha
NK128(nyo)001:5901: 'dres sbyor / da dung gzhi bdag gi 'bul ba
NK128(nyo)001:5902: yong ba yod pas lo sgrub mdzad pa drag zhus
NK128(nyo)001:5903: 'dres sbyor / pas / bla mas 'o na sgrub
NK128(nyo)001:5904: pa byed pa la thams cad 'tshogs shig gsungs pas
NK128(nyo)001:5905: 'dres sbyor / pas / / rnal 'byor pho mo brgya tsam 'tshogs so //
NK128(nyo)001:5906: bla mas nye gnas la khyod kyi chang ka p+aa la re /
NK128(nyo)001:5907: zan bya ngang mo'i sgo nga tsam re /
NK128(nyo)001:5908: sha mo chol tsam re rnams drongs gsungs te lo sgrub mdzad /
NK128(nyo)001:5909: sgrub pa thon pa dang bla mas /
NK128(nyo)001:5910: ngas lung pa 'di yi sa rdo ri brag thams cad khro bo lnga bcu rtsa brgyad dang /
NK128(nyo)001:5911: 'ug pa lung gi sa rdo ri brag thams cad zhi ba'i lha tshogs su mthong /
NK128(nyo)001:5912: khyad par dben ser mo'i lho ri 'di rgyal ba rigs lngar rgyun du lhag ge mthong bas /
NK128(nyo)001:5913: 'ug pa lung du zhi ba'i lha khang bzheng du
NK128(nyo)001:5914: 'gro bas rang re thams cad thegs so gsungs nas
NK128(nyo)001:5915: byon / nye gnas la rdza ma 'di phar khur cig /
NK128(nyo)001:5916: bzo bo las mi grwa sgom kun gyi 'thung rgyu dgos gsungs /
NK128(nyo)001:5917: nye gnas kyis khur bas rjid bya sgro tsam yang mi 'dug /
NK128(nyo)001:5918: chang ma klu bdud ming gnyis na re /
NK128(nyo)001:5919: nged gnyis ko ba la 'gro ba la mi grib
NK128(nyo)001:5920: can dang phrad pas rab kha la 'khrid par zhus
NK128(nyo)001:5921: zer ro // de nas dpon slob rnams grog po'i sum mdor byon /
NK128(nyo)001:5922: bla ma zur chen dgyes te brag rdo rje'i bstan
NK128(nyo)001:5923: pa bya ba'i steng du ru lu'i bro mdzad pas
NK128(nyo)001:5924: / zhabs g.yon long bu man chad 'dam bying ba ltar song ba la /
NK128(nyo)001:5925: zur chung pas nga'i bla ma sangs rgyas kyi ngo
NK128(nyo)001:5926: bo 'dug pas zhabs spyi bor len no zhes zhabs
NK128(nyo)001:5927: rjes la byin rlabs zhus pas dbu skra ral pa'i
NK128(nyo)001:5928: thor tshugs dbu thod yan chad 'jim pa la bcug
NK128(nyo)001:5929: pa ltar rjes lam me byung /
NK128(nyo)001:5930: bzang sgom shes rab rgyal pos 'di la ma 'ongs
NK128(nyo)001:5931: pa na zhabs rjes la byin rlabs zhus dus dbu
NK128(nyo)001:5932: rjes la rdog pas barjisa na sdig pa gsog zer
NK128(nyo)001:5933: phyag sor las gyad stobs po che lnga sprul te
NK128(nyo)001:5934: / bla ma yab sras kyi zhabs dang dbu rjes
NK128(nyo)001:5935: yod pa'i pha bong de zur la spungs te bzhag
NK128(nyo)001:5936: / / ra sa'i zhang 'gos chung dang pan gyi mi nyag 'byung grags na re /
NK128(nyo)001:5937: 'di brten pa nged gnyis la bab zer phyag sor
NK128(nyo)001:5938: gsum gyis kha la pha bong thegs par dka' ba
NK128(nyo)001:5939: re blangs te rtsa ba bltim pa da lta yang
NK128(nyo)001:5940: sgrub khang gi grog mda' na kun gyis mthong sar
NK128(nyo)001:5942: bdag gis brag rgya bod phyin nas phyag phyi zin
NK128(nyo)001:5943: pa sleb yong gsungs te nam mkhar la 'phur nas
NK128(nyo)001:5945: grwa pa gzhan rnams ri ma'i ko ba la byon /
NK128(nyo)001:5946: bla mas nye gnas dang bcas rab la byon te /
NK128(nyo)001:5947: nye gnas kyis chang rdza khur ba btsag nas gsol gyis byon /
NK128(nyo)001:5948: rab khar phebs pa dang nye gnas la khyod rang
NK128(nyo)001:5949: mig tshum gyis la nga'i thu ba la 'jus nas
NK128(nyo)001:5950: shog gsungs pas / nye gnas log rtog skyes te
NK128(nyo)001:5951: nga chu la skyur ba yin nam snyam pa dang
NK128(nyo)001:5952: shog gsungs pas / / bla mas mkhyen te khyod
NK128(nyo)001:5953: pa'i rjes la mi thar ba 'dug pas ko ba
NK128(nyo)001:5954: shog gsungs pas / / bskor la shog / nga
NK128(nyo)001:5955: 'ug pa lung du 'gro gsungs te bla ma nyid
NK128(nyo)001:5956: zhabs chu la mi reg par gshegs so //
NK128(nyo)001:5957: nye gnas mar log ste ko khar phyin pas grwa
NK128(nyo)001:5958: sgom thams cad pha rir thon 'dug pa la ko
NK128(nyo)001:5959: ba thong zhes bos pas re zhig bzhugs shig /
NK128(nyo)001:5960: mgron po gzhan 'dra yod pas bsgugs nas btang ngo zer nas yun ring lus /
NK128(nyo)001:5961: kha skams pas chang btungs te zhim par byung ste /
NK128(nyo)001:5962: rtsis btang bas chang bsings nas lo gcig dang zla ba bzhi song 'dug pas /
NK128(nyo)001:5963: de tsam thub pa'i chang 'ong ba bla mas rdza
NK128(nyo)001:5964: ma'i nang du ci bcug pa yin nam snyams te
NK128(nyo)001:5965: rdza ma'i kha phye nas bltas pas /
NK128(nyo)001:5966: sbrul dkar nag gshog pa can gnya' shing tsam gnyis
NK128(nyo)001:5967: mdud pa shugs te grol nas sram pa sgrub khang
NK128(nyo)001:5969: de'i rjes su sbal lcong sdig sbrul mang po 'ur
NK128(nyo)001:5970: sgra tshig sgra dang bcas te nam mkha' la song
NK128(nyo)001:5971: ma thag sbang ma sngo hrul le seng sa skyur
NK128(nyo)001:5972: seng nge song / de nas chu lhor thon pa dang rdza ma yang chag /
NK128(nyo)001:5973: nye gnas kyi yar phyin pa dang bla ma 'ug pa lung na phebs 'dug pa'i bka' las /
NK128(nyo)001:5975: klu bdud ming sring 'di chu lhor thon na 'ug pa lung dar rgyas che /
NK128(nyo)001:5976: sram pa sgrub khang du dgon pa 'bri gung tsam chags /
NK128(nyo)001:5977: sa dang mi gnyen dar rgyas che ba yod /
NK128(nyo)001:5978: da kho rang ngas sgrub khang gi bka' srung la bskos yod /
NK128(nyo)001:5979: chu byang dang lhor slob dpon ngo bo las slob bu chos mkhas pa yong ba 'dug /
NK128(nyo)001:5980: rdza ma de chu lhor thon pas chu lhor gnas
NK128(nyo)001:5981: gzhi sde dgon mang po chags yong ba 'dug ces
NK128(nyo)001:5983: de nas 'ug pa lung du lha khang bzhengs pa'i
NK128(nyo)001:5984: sa dpyad gzigs pas phun sum tshogs par dgongs te
NK128(nyo)001:5985: / bla ma dpal chen po'i skur bzhengs dus kyi zhabs g.yas bzhag sa der /
NK128(nyo)001:5986: byang chen mchod rten zhig ru gnon du bzhengs /
NK128(nyo)001:5987: slob ma rtse mo bzhi'i steng rtse lkog gcig ste
NK128(nyo)001:5988: lngas kyang sa'i me batsa'i mchod rten bzhengs nas lha
NK128(nyo)001:5989: khang rnams brtsigs / klu dung skyong gnas pa'i chu
NK128(nyo)001:5990: mig la zangs bkab nas rnam snang kun tu zhal
NK128(nyo)001:5991: gyi gtso mdzad pa'i rdor dbyings kyi lha tshogs zhe
NK128(nyo)001:5993: skor khang khyams stod smad glo 'bur dang bcas pa bzhengs /
NK128(nyo)001:5994: der bzo bo rnams kyis shing thams cad gru bzhir
NK128(nyo)001:5995: gzhogs pas gron che zhing phyag rdzas bzan pa'i thabs
NK128(nyo)001:5997: thugs ser sna'i mdud pa grol zhing mkhyen brtse nus
NK128(nyo)001:5998: gsum gyis 'gro ba 'dren pa'i tshul mthong bas 'gyod
NK128(nyo)001:5999: do // 'gyod bshags su lha khang tshar ba'i shing
NK128(nyo)001:6000: lhag las brtsigs pa med kyang ka bas bteg pa'i
NK128(nyo)001:6002: de lta bu'i lha khang na gtso bor gong du smos pa ltar rdor dbyings lha tshogs /
NK128(nyo)001:6003: glo 'bur lhor yum chen dang byang du mar me mdzad gnyis la mchod lha bzhi res bskor ba /
NK128(nyo)001:6004: mgon khang du dpal mgon legs ldan tshangs pa dang brgya sbyin /
NK128(nyo)001:6005: khyams stod la bla ma brgyud rim /
NK128(nyo)001:6007: pad+ma brgya ldan la sogs pa'i dkyil 'khor nye gsum /
NK128(nyo)001:6008: thigs khang na sgrub chen bka' brgyad kyi logs bris /
NK128(nyo)001:6009: khyams smad la sangs rgyas stong sku /
NK128(nyo)001:6010: phyogs bcu'i sangs rgyas rigs gsum mgon po /
NK128(nyo)001:6011: thub chen dang sems dpa' brgyad /
NK128(nyo)001:6015: srid pa 'khor lo la sogs grub bo //
NK128(nyo)001:6016: de'i rab gnas kyi dus su zur che chung gnyis /
NK128(nyo)001:6017: gtso bo rnam snang gi dbu gtsug nas zhugs thugs kar thon /
NK128(nyo)001:6018: thugs ka nas zhugs spyi bor thon pa sogs mdzad pa kun gyis mthong bas mos gus skyes te /
NK128(nyo)001:6019: bzo bo rnams kyis bla ma'i lha khang gi zhabs
NK128(nyo)001:6020: 'degs su bsam yas mchod rten sngon po la dpe
NK128(nyo)001:6021: blangs te bkra shis sgo mang gi mchod rten phul
NK128(nyo)001:6022: / de nas dpon slob kun gyis yang dben ser
NK128(nyo)001:6023: mor yang dag gi lo sgrub mdzad dus mar zad
NK128(nyo)001:6026: mar khu zad gda' lags zhus pas /
NK128(nyo)001:6027: chu mig zhag bdun gyi bar du mar khu byin
NK128(nyo)001:6028: gyis brlabs pas mar khu 'dzad med blangs chog pa
NK128(nyo)001:6029: byung ngo // de rnams kyi bsdus don yang mdo dbang gi dbang byang las /
NK128(nyo)001:6030: thub dang pad+mas lung bstan spyan ras gzigs //
NK128(nyo)001:6031: thugs dam zhal gzigs dam can ci bcol nyan //
NK128(nyo)001:6032: mkha' 'gros lung bstan phyi nang gtsug lag bzhengs //
NK128(nyo)001:6033: grub rtags zhabs rjes spyi dpal dpal chen bzhengs //
NK128(nyo)001:6035: slob ma yang rtse mo bzhi /
NK128(nyo)001:6036: rtse lkog gcig te lngar byed pa dang /
NK128(nyo)001:6037: rtse mo bzhi dang rtse lkog brgyad du byed pa sogs mang yang /
NK128(nyo)001:6038: 'dir spyi dang dbang byang ltar na rtse mo bzhi ni /
NK128(nyo)001:6039: lta dgongs kyi rtse mo zur chung pa shes rab grags /
NK128(nyo)001:6040: mkhyen rgya'i rtse mo la stod ra ba'i zhang 'gos chung ba /
NK128(nyo)001:6041: sgyu 'phrul gyi bshad pa phyogs gcig gi rtse mo bres kyi mi nyag 'byung grags /
NK128(nyo)001:6042: 'phrin las sgom sgrub kyi rtse mo mtsho nya'i bzang sgom shes rab rgyal po dang bzhi'o //
NK128(nyo)001:6043: lha chos kyi steng du mi chos kyi pho so'i
NK128(nyo)001:6044: rtse mo bram gyi rtsegs bla ma bsnan pa'i rtse
NK128(nyo)001:6045: lkog gcig ste lngar byed pa'ang /
NK128(nyo)001:6046: yang na bram gyi rtsags ston rtse lkog brgyad du bsgrangs kyang mi 'gal te /
NK128(nyo)001:6048: zur chung sher grags rdo rje lhun mtsho nya'i bzang sgom shes rab rgyal po ni //
NK128(nyo)001:6049: rdo rje gzi 'bar rtsal te la stod ra sa yi //
NK128(nyo)001:6050: zhang ston 'gos chung rdo rje lhun grub rtsal //
NK128(nyo)001:6051: bres phu'i mi nyag 'byung grags bde ba rtsal //
NK128(nyo)001:6052: bram gyi rtsag ston la sogs rtse lkog brgyad //
NK128(nyo)001:6061: phug ston nam mkha' 'od dang brgyad /
NK128(nyo)001:6068: sbas sgom la sogs sgom chen brgya rtsa ste dpe 'grems sum brgya lhag tsam byung bar grags shing /
NK128(nyo)001:6069: sgom chen brgya rtsa yan thams cad kyang mkha' 'gro dbang phyug dam can bran du 'khol ba /
NK128(nyo)001:6070: chos nyid kyi don rtogs pa nam mkha' la lding ba sogs grub rtags dngos su ston nus pa /
NK128(nyo)001:6071: 'phrin las bzhi la thogs pa med pa sha dag yin par grags so //
NK128(nyo)001:6072: de nas yang dben ser mor 'chad nyan mdzad cing rgyun gtor lhan du gtong ba sogs mdzad /
NK128(nyo)001:6073: thog mar 'phrin las shes pa chung ba'i dus grwa
NK128(nyo)001:6074: pa slob gnyer ba rnams kyis bgro gleng byed skabs
NK128(nyo)001:6075: 'phrin las shes pa rnams la khyed tshos gzhan ci
NK128(nyo)001:6076: shes byas pas / rgyud gtor dus khong tshos 'phrin las byed ma nyan pa la /
NK128(nyo)001:6077: bla mas mtshams pa mdzad de rang sar bden gyi
NK128(nyo)001:6078: zhi dul gyis gsungs pas rtsod pa chos phyogs su
NK128(nyo)001:6079: zhi / rtse mo bzhi la lam nyams su len pa la gal gang che gsungs pas /
NK128(nyo)001:6080: so so'i zhe 'dod sgom nyams tha dad gsungs pa la /
NK128(nyo)001:6081: bla ma zur chen dgyes te gdams pa'i mgur 'di gsungs so //
NK128(nyo)001:6082: khyod slob ma bzhi nga yi snying gtam nyon //
NK128(nyo)001:6083: dam pa'i lha chos byed pa la //
NK128(nyo)001:6084: lam lta sgom spyod pa gsum du gda' //
NK128(nyo)001:6085: lta ba zhes ming du btags pa de //
NK128(nyo)001:6086: lta rgyu zhig byung na lta ba min //
NK128(nyo)001:6087: lta rgyu med pa'i don la blta //
NK128(nyo)001:6088: chos nyid brjod med lam du 'khyer //
NK128(nyo)001:6089: sgom pa zhes ming du btags pa de //
NK128(nyo)001:6090: sgom rgyu byung na sgom pa min //
NK128(nyo)001:6091: sgom du med pa'i don la sgom //
NK128(nyo)001:6092: sems yengs rgyu med pa'i lam du 'khyer //
NK128(nyo)001:6093: spyod pa zhes ming du btags pa ste //
NK128(nyo)001:6094: spyod rgyu byung na spyod pa min //
NK128(nyo)001:6095: spyad rgyu med pa'i don la byed //
NK128(nyo)001:6097: rnal 'byor bdag gi nyams len lags //
NK128(nyo)001:6098: lam 'gro bar 'dod na de nas byon //
NK128(nyo)001:6099: lam gzhan nas phyin na skor thag ring //
NK128(nyo)001:6100: zhes gsungs pas thams cad mos gus skyes so //
NK128(nyo)001:6101: de nas 'ug pa lung du tshogs pa skyongs shing bshad grwa dang sgom grwa chen po mdzad /
NK128(nyo)001:6102: sgro phug tu gsang sngags kyi chos grwa chen po btsugs /
NK128(nyo)001:6103: 'chad nyan sgom sgrub mdzad pa'i dus su /
NK128(nyo)001:6105: sgrub phug gi rgya ri dang thag gi ri gnyis sbubs su bcug pa'i gser 'bum re bzhengs /
NK128(nyo)001:6106: de'i stod gnyis lcags thag gis sbrel ba la dril gdong 'gel lo gsungs pas /
NK128(nyo)001:6108: 'o na nged rang rnams kyis kyang zhal 'debs su lcags thag re /
NK128(nyo)001:6110: dril bu re bsdus nas phul na 'thad dam zhus pas /
NK128(nyo)001:6112: ngas sa chog bya yi gsungs nas sa blangs pa'i cho ga mdzad cing /
NK128(nyo)001:6113: do nub mnal lam btags pas /
NK128(nyo)001:6114: lha ri gdong gi gzhi bdag dang rta nag gi gzhi bdag gnyis mna' bskyal gyi mched yin pas /
NK128(nyo)001:6115: lha ri gdong gser 'bum gyi khongs su mi 'jug
NK128(nyo)001:6116: pa'i zhu ba bya ba la thog mar rta nag
NK128(nyo)001:6117: gi gzhi bdag byung ste rta nag zhon pa'i mi
NK128(nyo)001:6119: gser ra mchin tsam zhig phul nas gser 'bum gnyis po mi 'dzad pa'i zhu ba 'bul zhing /
NK128(nyo)001:6120: zhu rten du lha khang rnams kyi sku'i gser ci
NK128(nyo)001:6121: dgos 'bul bas len mi rnal 'byor pa lnga thong
NK128(nyo)001:6122: las can gsum yong ngo zer gser btang ba'i tshad
NK128(nyo)001:6125: sdig sbrul dang sbal lcong sogs sems can gyi gzugs shig se thon byung ba dang bzhag dgos /
NK128(nyo)001:6126: de gong gang rnyed phul ba lags zer /
NK128(nyo)001:6127: de bzhin du lha ri'i gzhi bdag gis kyang 'bul
NK128(nyo)001:6128: bar zhus te gser len sar bla ma rang gis
NK128(nyo)001:6129: byon pas / ri kha gyes pa'i dbus pha bong
NK128(nyo)001:6130: kha phye ba na gser zangs gang 'dug pa na
NK128(nyo)001:6131: ka p+aa la gang bcus nas byon pas /
NK128(nyo)001:6133: 'brong ri la rnal 'byor pa lnga btang bas rdo
NK128(nyo)001:6134: re bteg pa'i 'og nas kyang gser mang po byung
NK128(nyo)001:6135: / de rjes sems can gyi gzugs 'dra thon byung
NK128(nyo)001:6136: bar rnal 'byor pa gsum gyis da ni 'agro'o byas
NK128(nyo)001:6137: / pas / gnyis kyis chog ma shes par da dung gser blangs pas mdze byung ste shi'o //
NK128(nyo)001:6138: gsum gyis gser khur te bla ma la phul lo //
NK128(nyo)001:6139: mnal lam du phul ba'i gser ra mchin tsam de yang gser kho nar dngos su byung /
NK128(nyo)001:6140: de ltar gser 'bad med du byung bas lha khang
NK128(nyo)001:6141: gi sku thams cad gser gyis byug pa sogs mdzad
NK128(nyo)001:6142: cing / gser lhag ma bre gsum lha khang gi zhig bsos thebs su sbas so //
NK128(nyo)001:6143: mdor na bla ma zur po che de nyid kyi
NK128(nyo)001:6144: slob ma'i tshogs la snga 'gyur gyi 'chad nyan sgom
NK128(nyo)001:6145: sgrub phyogs med du mdzad pas zur lugs zhes yongs
NK128(nyo)001:6147: de'i tshe bla ma zur chen gyis zur chung pa brag rgya bor bzhugs pa gdan drangs te /
NK128(nyo)001:6149: nga'i gdan sa 'di zur chung shes rab grags pas mdzod cig gsungs te gdan sa gtad de /
NK128(nyo)001:6150: slob ma rnams la chos blo dang 'tsham par 'chad pa dang /
NK128(nyo)001:6151: nga'i rjes rnams kyang skyongs shig gsungs pa sogs zhal ta rnams gnang /
NK128(nyo)001:6152: grwa sa rnams la yang zur chung pa 'di dpal
NK128(nyo)001:6153: chen po'i sku gsung thugs kyi dngos grub thob pa
NK128(nyo)001:6154: yin pas / nga bas 'di lhag /'di khyed tsho'i
NK128(nyo)001:6155: bla mar bskos pa yin pas log par ma blta
NK128(nyo)001:6161: ngas ji ltar skyong ba bzhin skyong ba yod pas mos gus phun sum tshogs par gyis shig gsungs /
NK128(nyo)001:6162: gzhan yang yon bdag sogs thams cad la zhal bkod
NK128(nyo)001:6163: zhim par mdzad de zur chung pa gdan sar brkos
NK128(nyo)001:6164: rjes / da nga mi sdod sram pa sgrub khang du 'gro gsungs /
NK128(nyo)001:6165: sgrub khang du byon nas dgongs pa la bzhugs so //
NK128(nyo)001:6166: de ltar bla ma zur chen de sku tshe de
NK128(nyo)001:6167: nyid kyi gdul bya rnams rdzogs nas gzugs sku'i bkod
NK128(nyo)001:6168: pa chos dbyings su bsdu bar bzhed pa'i tshe /
NK128(nyo)001:6169: zhogs pa zhig nye gnas la /
NK128(nyo)001:6170: da nang tsha ba 'phyi gyis gsungs pas /
NK128(nyo)001:6171: nye gnas kyis dge sbyor zhig byed kyis bsdad nyi ma shar byung ba dang /
NK128(nyo)001:6172: da nyi ma yang shar bas tsha ba zhu ran nam bsams te drung du phyin pas /
NK128(nyo)001:6173: bla ma gzims mal nas bzheng gin 'dug par da
NK128(nyo)001:6174: lta nas sku tshags mdzad nas gar gshegs pa yin
NK128(nyo)001:6175: zhus pas / nga bde ba chen po'i zhing du 'gro /
NK128(nyo)001:6176: nga dpal chen po dang dbyer med pas khyod rang
NK128(nyo)001:6177: yi dam lha la gsol ba thob la mos pa
NK128(nyo)001:6179: d+aa ma ru dang rdo rje dril bu phyag tu
NK128(nyo)001:6180: bsnams nas 'khrol gyin sku 'od kyi rang bzhin du
NK128(nyo)001:6181: yal nas yi dam dpal chen po'i sku gzugs kyi
NK128(nyo)001:6182: thugs kar 'od zer kha dog lnga ldan gyi 'phro
NK128(nyo)001:6183: 'du lan gsum du mdzad cing thim par mthong ngo
NK128(nyo)001:6184: // bla ma dpal chen gyi thugs kar thim pa
NK128(nyo)001:6185: dang dus mtshungs par khams pa'i 'bul skyel ba mang
NK128(nyo)001:6187: lam du bla ma dngos dang mjal nas dgon par gshegs par zhu zhus pas ma gnang ste /
NK128(nyo)001:6188: sprul pa'i gzhal yas khang du bla ma nyid rang gi 'bul ba bzhes /
NK128(nyo)001:6189: bsngo smon mdzad de gshegs pa'i shul du khams pa rnams gnyid du song /
NK128(nyo)001:6190: gnyid sad pa dang ci yang mi gda' nas the tshom gyi ngang nas phyin pas /
NK128(nyo)001:6191: lam du bla ma dpal chen po'i thugs kar 'od
NK128(nyo)001:6192: phung gi rang bzhin du thim mo zhes thos so
NK128(nyo)001:6193: // de ltar bla ma zur chen gyi sku dngos
NK128(nyo)001:6194: su thim pa'i dpal chen gyi sku de deng sang
NK128(nyo)001:6195: yang 'gro ba'i don du ma nyams par bzhugs la
NK128(nyo)001:6196: // / de'i rjes su lan cig kyang sku gzugs des gsung byon te /
NK128(nyo)001:6197: rgya ston sh+aakya ye la bsu ba gyis gsungs bsu ba byas pas /
NK128(nyo)001:6198: rgya ston sh+aakya ye shes de yang ba dkar mo zhig la chibs /
NK128(nyo)001:6199: spyang zhwa zhig gsol nas byung ste 'od dkar po
NK128(nyo)001:6200: mtheb chung tsam kha dog lngas brgyan pa zhig tu
NK128(nyo)001:6201: gyur pa la g.yon skor du 'khor nas dpal chen
NK128(nyo)001:6202: por thim pa dkon gnyer ma jo don rgyan gyis
NK128(nyo)001:6203: mthong ngo // mtshan ldan zur mo 'od 'bum bya ba yang dpal chen po'i thugs kar thim mo //
NK128(nyo)001:6204: de ltar bder gshegs zur po che sh+aakya 'byung gnas
NK128(nyo)001:6205: kyis slob ma rnams la 'dus pa chen po'i dbang
NK128(nyo)001:6206: gdams pa lan mang du stsal mod kyang /
NK128(nyo)001:6207: khyad par du lta dgongs kyi rtse mo zur chung shes rab grags la gsungs pa yin te /
NK128(nyo)001:6208: bla ma 'di'i rnam thar mdo tsam brjod na /
NK128(nyo)001:6209: de yang bla ma zur chen de nyid bla chen
NK128(nyo)001:6210: po las bsnyen par rdzogs pa'i gtsang sgom kho nar
NK128(nyo)001:6211: bzhugs pas gdung sras ma spel zhing /
NK128(nyo)001:6212: zur po che'i yab zur a tsar+ya shes rab 'byung gnas la sras bzhi byung ste /
NK128(nyo)001:6213: che ba shes rab bzang po /
NK128(nyo)001:6216: de 'og zur sgom chen dang bzhir yod pa'i /
NK128(nyo)001:6217: zur sgom chen gyi sras zur chung pa yin te /
NK128(nyo)001:6218: de yang yul g.yas ru gtsang gi thag byang ri
NK128(nyo)001:6219: lha ze mo'i mdun rgya 'bar gdong zhes bya bar
NK128(nyo)001:6220: / yab zur sgom chen dang yum ma jo shes
NK128(nyo)001:6221: rab skyid la lhums su zhugs pa'i tshe rmi ltas
NK128(nyo)001:6222: / lnga byung ste / dang po bar snang gi khams la zam pa btsugs pa rmis /
NK128(nyo)001:6223: gnyis pa phrag pa g.yas la nyi ma dang g.yon zla ba shar ba rmis /
NK128(nyo)001:6224: gsum pa nang pa sangs rgyas pa'i ston pa byon zer ba'i sgra dir ri ri sgrog par rmis /
NK128(nyo)001:6225: bzhi pa la bod kyi mun sangs bstan pa'i nyi ma shar zer ba rmis /
NK128(nyo)001:6226: lnga pa la bdud dang mu stegs kyi bstan pa nub /
NK128(nyo)001:6227: nang pa sangs rgyas pa'i bstan pa byon te 'khor
NK128(nyo)001:6228: 'das dbyer med du rtogs te thams cad mnyam pa
NK128(nyo)001:6229: nyid kyi ngang la gnas so zer ba'i sgra byung
NK128(nyo)001:6230: bar snang thams cad sgra 'od kyis gang ba rmis
NK128(nyo)001:6232: nged rang la bu byung na sangs rgyas bstan pa la phan thogs pa zhig yong ba yin gsungs /
NK128(nyo)001:6233: mnal ltas ltar zur chung pa sku 'khrungs /
NK128(nyo)001:6234: dgung lo bdun la bris klog rnams mkhyen /
NK128(nyo)001:6235: dgu la zhi khro'i 'phrin las sogs pha chos kyi cho ga rnams mkhyen /
NK128(nyo)001:6236: dgung lo bcu gcig pa la jo mo zhig blangs te bzhugs pa las /
NK128(nyo)001:6237: chos dang mjal ba'i rkyen ni dgung lo bcu gsum
NK128(nyo)001:6238: lon rtsa na grogs mkhar lung pa na shwa 'od
NK128(nyo)001:6240: gzims mal na phyag dpe gzigs shing yod pa la /
NK128(nyo)001:6241: jo mo rgyud byung ste zhing la shwa log shor ba 'dug go //
NK128(nyo)001:6242: khyod der nyal bas chog pa 'dug gam zer ba la /
NK128(nyo)001:6243: zhabs dor gsar pa zhig yod pa bzhes te rjes
NK128(nyo)001:6244: bcangs kyang ma mdzad par khyem bsnams te chu brgal
NK128(nyo)001:6245: nas bkag pas / jo mo na re /
NK128(nyo)001:6246: kha mig brul brul bar bzos pa'i dor ma rjes
NK128(nyo)001:6247: bcangs kyang mi byed par chus zos su btang zer
NK128(nyo)001:6248: nas 'thabs pas / kho bo mi 'phangs par dor ma 'phangs na de na yod do gsungs /
NK128(nyo)001:6251: yang na dor ma mi barje /
NK128(nyo)001:6252: yang na bskyur nas gtong ba nga la sngan can
NK128(nyo)001:6253: yin zer nas mo rang gi yul du bros so
NK128(nyo)001:6254: // zur chung pa nang du log nas 'khor ba la skyo ba skyes /
NK128(nyo)001:6255: tshe 'di'i snang ba las log ste khyim la gzigs
NK128(nyo)001:6256: pas gdung khung na mo'i zhud lus 'dug pa gzigs
NK128(nyo)001:6257: te / mo da ltos dang zer gsungs btang bas /
NK128(nyo)001:6258: mo'i sems la yar log shog zer ba yin nam snyam nas bsdad pa na zhud gtad de /
NK128(nyo)001:6259: pho nor phor khyer mo nor mo khyer bya ba
NK128(nyo)001:6260: yin pas khyod kyi mo nor 'di lus 'dug go
NK128(nyo)001:6262: mo yang yi chad nas rang yul du log go //
NK128(nyo)001:6263: der zur chung pas kyang pha la gros ma dris /
NK128(nyo)001:6265: grogs kyi ngo ma bltas par spyang slog zhig yod
NK128(nyo)001:6266: pa khyer nas 'ug pa lung du khu bo zur
NK128(nyo)001:6267: po che sh+aakya 'byung gnas kyi drung du byon pa'i
NK128(nyo)001:6268: lam du rta nag gi 'brog pa g.yu dang zangs
NK128(nyo)001:6270: shangs nas khrab dang spyang slog khyer ba zhig rnam
NK128(nyo)001:6271: byung ste 'grogs nas byon te phyag rten rnams phul
NK128(nyo)001:6272: bas / zur chen gyi nye gnas la /
NK128(nyo)001:6273: khong rnams 'khor ba la blo log ma log blta
NK128(nyo)001:6274: bas sbang zan re dang po thug skyug pa 'dra
NK128(nyo)001:6275: ba re drongs shig gsungs nas drangs pas /
NK128(nyo)001:6277: pha ma bu tshe la 'di 'dra za ma myong zer nas ma zos /
NK128(nyo)001:6278: shangs pas skyu chung gsum tsam zos /
NK128(nyo)001:6279: zur chung pas brda thabs su dgongs te kho rang gi de lhag ma med par gsol nas /
NK128(nyo)001:6280: gzhan rnams nas kyang zhal re tsam gsol pas /
NK128(nyo)001:6281: bla ma'i zhal nas spyang slog dang khrab kyi bdag po sdod la /
NK128(nyo)001:6282: g.yu dang zangs bdag po la thong gsungs pas /
NK128(nyo)001:6284: spre'u la mig mi blta ba ya pho la yon mi ster ba'i dpe yin pas /
NK128(nyo)001:6285: phyag rten la mig mi blta ba 'u cag la chos mi slob pa'i rtags yin /
NK128(nyo)001:6286: bla ma gzhan na yang yod zer song /
NK128(nyo)001:6287: der zur chung pa la bla mas rus dang ming sogs dris pas /
NK128(nyo)001:6288: bla ma'i sku tsha yin tshul brjod na 'gran par gyur dogs nas /
NK128(nyo)001:6289: rus zur chung chung zhig lags /
NK128(nyo)001:6290: ming shes rab grags zer zhus pas /
NK128(nyo)001:6291: 'o na ming zung chung shes rab grags bya ba
NK128(nyo)001:6292: thogs gsungs te rjes su bzung nas slob gnyer mang
NK128(nyo)001:6294: sgyu 'phrul ma h+aa yo ga la rgyud sde bco brgyad du phye ba gsan pas /
NK128(nyo)001:6299: 'khor 'das dbyer med rang gi mtshan nyid mngon du gyur /
NK128(nyo)001:6300: rang mdangs su snying rje phyogs med du skyes pa
NK128(nyo)001:6301: sogs thugs dam dgongs nyams du ma mngon du gyur
NK128(nyo)001:6302: pa'i tshe / 'tsho ba chad nas bla mas gtor
NK128(nyo)001:6303: ma btang ba kun blangs nas zan chang du byas
NK128(nyo)001:6304: pa'i tshe / shing gsol bas / mched grogs kun na re /
NK128(nyo)001:6305: kho rang chang btsos shing 'thung ste kha skyur dri chil le byas sdod /
NK128(nyo)001:6306: chang bla ma la yang mi zhu /
NK128(nyo)001:6307: mched grogs la yang mi 'dren par 'dug zer bla ma la zhus pas /
NK128(nyo)001:6309: de ring zur chung pa rang shing thus shig gsungs /
NK128(nyo)001:6310: de'i shul du grwa pa rnams la zur chung pa'i spyil po g.yengs shig gsungs pa ltar g.yengs pas /
NK128(nyo)001:6311: gzhan yo byad gang yang mi 'dug /
NK128(nyo)001:6312: bel po zhig gi 'og na zan chang ka p+aa la gang 'dug pas /
NK128(nyo)001:6313: grwa pa rnams kyang yid ches shing bla mas zur
NK128(nyo)001:6314: chung par 'tsho ba chad na rang re'i thabs la
NK128(nyo)001:6315: shog gsungs pas / nga bla ma'i dkor la 'bags
NK128(nyo)001:6316: re zer mna' bskyal te dka' spyad dpag med mdzad
NK128(nyo)001:6317: shog gsungs pas / cing bzhugs pas / nyin gcig
NK128(nyo)001:6318: bla ma zur chen bse'i ga'u phul dgu 'gro ba
NK128(nyo)001:6319: zhig bsnams nas khyod la skom ster rgyu e yod
NK128(nyo)001:6320: shog gsungs pas / cing bzhugs pas / gsungs par / zan chang zhus pas snod de gsol /
NK128(nyo)001:6321: da dung khyer shog gsungs nas snod do gsol /
NK128(nyo)001:6324: da mi yog par 'dug yog na khyod la bsod nams bod du mi shong ba 'ong ste /
NK128(nyo)001:6325: 'on kyang da dung bsod nams chen po 'ong gsungs
NK128(nyo)001:6326: nas khal gsum gnang nas 'di zad pa dang yo
NK128(nyo)001:6327: byad mi 'thong par yang gsungs pa ltar byung zhing
NK128(nyo)001:6328: / sngon sbyangs dang sprul pa'i sku yin pas nyams rtogs bsam gyis mi khyab pa brnyes /
NK128(nyo)001:6329: lta dgongs kyi rtse mor gyur te slob ma yang bskyangs so //
NK128(nyo)001:6330: de'i tshe zur chung par lung bstan rnam pa gsum byung ste /
NK128(nyo)001:6331: dang po gzhi bdag jo bo grog mkhar rnal 'byor
NK128(nyo)001:6332: pa dung long skya khrol le ba zhig tu byung
NK128(nyo)001:6333: ste / khyed ri bo dgu 'dus kyi rtse mo
NK128(nyo)001:6334: la sgom shig zer ba byung yang 'khrul snang du
NK128(nyo)001:6336: gnyis pa la mkha' 'gro'i lung bstan ma jo smin
NK128(nyo)001:6337: ma dang sma ra se khyug ge bgos smug gyon
NK128(nyo)001:6338: zhing d+aa dril 'khrol ba gar stabs bsgyur ba zhig
NK128(nyo)001:6339: byung nas / ming po khyed ri bo dgu 'dus kyi rtse mo la sgoms shig /
NK128(nyo)001:6340: bdag gzhan gnyis ka'i don grub bo zer mi snang bar song bas /
NK128(nyo)001:6341: lha ze mor byon pas zer mo'i gzhi bdag lha
NK128(nyo)001:6342: lung skyes cig mi dkar rta dkar dar thod can
NK128(nyo)001:6343: du byung ste phyag skor mang po byas te /
NK128(nyo)001:6344: ri bo dgu 'dus kyi rtse la gshegs par zhus kyang ma gnang bar de gar bzhugs pas /
NK128(nyo)001:6345: rgyal gyi zla ba'i tshes bco lnga'i nub mo bar
NK128(nyo)001:6346: snang la lha'i gdugs rgyal mtshan ba dan la sogs
NK128(nyo)001:6347: pas khengs / sa gzhi mi ma yin gyis khengs /
NK128(nyo)001:6348: de rnams kyi nang nas bu mo lo bcu drug
NK128(nyo)001:6349: tsam rus pa'i rgyan drug dang dar gyis brgyan pa
NK128(nyo)001:6350: / g.yas d+aa ma ru dang g.yon gar stabs sgyur
NK128(nyo)001:6351: ba'i mkha' 'gro ma lnga byung nas phyag dang zhabs
NK128(nyo)001:6353: 'o ming po khyod ri bo dgu 'dus la sgom
NK128(nyo)001:6354: shig bdag gzhan gnyis ka'i don 'grub bo zer ba'i
NK128(nyo)001:6356: de na ri bo gang yin snyam pa la /
NK128(nyo)001:6357: mkha' 'gro ma lngas phyag mdzub rnams dus gcig tu brag rgya bo la gtad pas /
NK128(nyo)001:6360: ne'u gsing dgu 'dus pa ni chos theg pa rim dgu dbyings su rdzogs pa'i rtags yin pas /
NK128(nyo)001:6361: der sgom par zhu zhes gsol ba btab bo //
NK128(nyo)001:6362: de ltar lung bstan snga phyi bar gsum du byung ba la brten nas brag rgya bor byon /
NK128(nyo)001:6363: de yang ri bo dgu 'dus kyi rtser song bas
NK128(nyo)001:6364: non dka' bar gyur te brag rgya bo'i gzhi bdag
NK128(nyo)001:6365: phu bo bdud btsan nag po /
NK128(nyo)001:6368: sring mo klu mo sbal mgo khrag mig la sogs pas /
NK128(nyo)001:6369: bla ma'i zil ma theg gdug rtsub shin tu che bar byung ste /
NK128(nyo)001:6370: bla ma sdig pa la shin tu 'jigs pa mdzad yod par rig ste /
NK128(nyo)001:6371: sdig pa nag po'i dmag sa gzhi khengs pa tsam
NK128(nyo)001:6372: drangs te mnyam par bzhag pa'i dus sdig pa de
NK128(nyo)001:6373: rnams kyis sku la 'dzegs par sdig pa'i rwa gnyis
NK128(nyo)001:6374: nas gzung ste / sdig pa mi dge so sor bshags /
NK128(nyo)001:6375: zhes ku re gsungs bzhin sdig pa'i lus po phyed
NK128(nyo)001:6376: mar gshags nas rgyab tu skyar bas sdig pa'i ro
NK128(nyo)001:6377: phung byung / der sdig pa'i dmag dpon gyi rnam
NK128(nyo)001:6378: pa ko mthil tsam zhig byung nas sku rgyab nas
NK128(nyo)001:6379: phung byung / yar 'dzegs / dbu thod nas mar babs te zhal gyi thad du byung ba dang /
NK128(nyo)001:6380: dpal chen po'i stang stabs mdzad de zhal du cham ste gsol bas /
NK128(nyo)001:6383: dgon pa dang nga yon bdag 'di las bzang ba gang na yod pas /
NK128(nyo)001:6384: 'dir sku tshe la gnod pa las mi 'dug pas mi bzhugs par zhu /
NK128(nyo)001:6385: bla ma'i dgongs pa la ma tshug kyang bdag kyang
NK128(nyo)001:6386: bar chad du 'gro ba gda' zhus kyang ma gsan
NK128(nyo)001:6387: par bzhugs pas / yang grog ma'i dmag drangs te /
NK128(nyo)001:6388: grog ma che ba mtheb rdog tsam gyis sa gzhi khengs pa byung ba dang /
NK128(nyo)001:6389: nye gnas la sha ba'i tsong go de khyer shog
NK128(nyo)001:6390: gsungs nas tsong gos brdungs pas nye gnas log ste
NK128(nyo)001:6391: skyes te / bla ma sa phyogs 'di min gzhan du gshegs par zhu /
NK128(nyo)001:6392: sems can brdungs nas sgrib pa che mod zhus pas /
NK128(nyo)001:6393: khyod rang nga la log lta skyes pa'i sdig bshags phyag dang skor ba gyis gsungs nas /
NK128(nyo)001:6394: dar gcig dgongs pa la bzhugs mthar se gol gcig brdabs pas /
NK128(nyo)001:6395: sdig pa dang grog ma'i ro rnams dpal rdo rje
NK128(nyo)001:6396: sems dpa'i sku tshon nger song ste bar snang la
NK128(nyo)001:6398: de nas gzhi bdag thul nas 'khor bcas dngos su
NK128(nyo)001:6399: yongs te phyag dang skor ba byas zhabs spyi bor
NK128(nyo)001:6400: blangs te srog snying phul lo //
NK128(nyo)001:6401: bla mas kyang lce la bdud rtsi bzhag /
NK128(nyo)001:6402: mgo la rdo rje bzhag nas dam la btags /
NK128(nyo)001:6403: gsang mtshan phu bo la rdo rje dgra 'dul rtsal /
NK128(nyo)001:6404: bar pa la rdo rje dbang grub rtsal /
NK128(nyo)001:6405: tha chung la rdo rje drag po rtsal /
NK128(nyo)001:6406: sring mo la klu mo gzi brjid 'od ldan mar btags /
NK128(nyo)001:6407: spyir thub bstan bsrung zhing sgos slob brgyud rnams kyi grogs byed pa khas blangs dam bcas so //
NK128(nyo)001:6408: der dang po yang dag thugs kyi sgrub pa mdzad pas dpal chen po'i zhal gzigs /
NK128(nyo)001:6409: gnas de la rgya bo dge gnas su mtshan gsol zhing /
NK128(nyo)001:6410: gzhi bdag dam la thogs pas dbyar dus kyang sbur pa sogs srog chags mi 'ong zhing /
NK128(nyo)001:6411: de phyogs su sngas bstan nas nyal ba kun la yang byin rlabs zhugs pa byung ngo //
NK128(nyo)001:6412: der bla ma zur chen dang zur chung gnyis kyis
NK128(nyo)001:6413: sram pa sgrub khang gi 'gram bting zhing gyad rdo
NK128(nyo)001:6414: bzhag pa sogs gong du bshad pa ltar la /
NK128(nyo)001:6415: dpal chen po'i sku bzhengs nas yang dag lo sgrub mdzad dus /
NK128(nyo)001:6416: zur chung pas dpal chen po'i gsung gi dngos grub
NK128(nyo)001:6417: thob pa'i rtags ru lu'i sgra 'ol pa gdong nas
NK128(nyo)001:6418: nyan pa dang drung du bsdad par che chung ma
NK128(nyo)001:6420: bla ma zur chen gyis zur chung ba dpal chen
NK128(nyo)001:6421: dngos su gzigs pas grwa pa rnams la ston sgom
NK128(nyo)001:6422: grwa pa khyed rnams zur chung pa'i 'gran zla ma
NK128(nyo)001:6423: yin no // 'di ni don chos sku rnam pa longs skur 'dug pas /
NK128(nyo)001:6424: rtse mo gsum sogs grwa pa rnams kyis khong khur
NK128(nyo)001:6425: cig /'di'i zhabs rjes la yang ma 'gom cig ces
NK128(nyo)001:6426: gsungs te zur chos par bskos so //
NK128(nyo)001:6427: de nas zur chung pa chos 'chad par bskos pas /
NK128(nyo)001:6429: nged rnams rtse mo mched grogs mnyam po la /
NK128(nyo)001:6430: bla mas dpon mo mgo bton zhes cung zad skur ba 'debs pa'ang byung bas /
NK128(nyo)001:6431: bla ma la skur pa btab na las gsog par mkhyen te /
NK128(nyo)001:6432: nam zhig gi tshe e dmar rdo rje spor dpon
NK128(nyo)001:6433: slob thams cad chos 'khor la byon pa'i tshe srang
NK128(nyo)001:6434: kha zhig na khyi mo khyi gu skyes nas smad
NK128(nyo)001:6436: bla ma zur chen gyis phyag reg tsam zhig mdzad nas byon /
NK128(nyo)001:6437: zur chung pas gar song gar 'ded btang ste khyi gu dang khyi mo rnams brdabs te bsad /
NK128(nyo)001:6438: 'bu rnams zhal du gsol bas rtse mo gzhan gyis bla ma la zhus pa /
NK128(nyo)001:6439: zur chung pa zer ba 'di 'dra zhig 'chad nyan du bskos /
NK128(nyo)001:6440: da smyo spyod byas yon bdag gi khyi bsad /
NK128(nyo)001:6441: 'o skol la mos pa ldog par gda' yi zhus pas /
NK128(nyo)001:6443: 'o khyi de rnams ngan song du 'gro ba ngas kyang shes te sgrol ma nus pa yin /
NK128(nyo)001:6444: khong gis bsgral ba ngo mtshar che gsungs /
NK128(nyo)001:6445: der khyi ro rnams mchod pa'i lha mor song /
NK128(nyo)001:6446: zhal du gsol ba'i 'bu rnams phyir pho bas nam mkha' la 'od bun gyis 'phul song ba la /
NK128(nyo)001:6448: da khyed rnams ngo mtshar skyes sam zur chung pa la mos gus kyis phyag phul gsungs par /
NK128(nyo)001:6449: mig 'phrul du gda' zer nas mched grogs rnams nges shes ma skyes par phyag ma phul lo //
NK128(nyo)001:6450: de nas chos 'khor thon nas yar byon shangs chu rgyas dus yin pas /
NK128(nyo)001:6451: bla ma zur chen gyis chu pha rir ka p+aa li rdzu 'phrul gyis skur te /
NK128(nyo)001:6452: 'o 'di sus longs la nga'i bshad grwa 'bogs so gsungs pas /
NK128(nyo)001:6453: rtse mo gzhan gsum na re /
NK128(nyo)001:6454: gdan sa las ma shi ba dga' zer nas sus kyang len mkhan ma byung bas /
NK128(nyo)001:6455: zur chung pas zhabs chu la ma reg par byon nas blangs so //
NK128(nyo)001:6456: de nas khyed rnams rlung 'gran par gyis shig gsungs pas /
NK128(nyo)001:6457: ston sgom gzhan rnams kyis kyang zhabs sa la ma reg tsam byung zhing /
NK128(nyo)001:6458: zur chung pas shing ta la gang tsam 'phags te sram pa sgrub khang du sngon la phebs so //
NK128(nyo)001:6459: de nas khyed rtse mo bzhi dgongs pa 'dren cig gsungs /
NK128(nyo)001:6460: gzhan gsum po yang dgongs pa g.yo 'gul med pa ri bo lta bu byung la /
NK128(nyo)001:6461: zur chung pas ta la gang tsam gyis dgongs pa mtho ba byung skad /
NK128(nyo)001:6462: der rtse mo gzhan gsum zur chung pa la nges shes brnyes so //
NK128(nyo)001:6463: de yang drang don du rtse mo gzhan gsum pos chags sdang ltar snang yang /
NK128(nyo)001:6464: nges don du zur chung pa'i che ba 'don thabs
NK128(nyo)001:6465: kho na las chags sdang rang rgyud pa min par
NK128(nyo)001:6466: shes dgos so // de yang bla ma zur pa
NK128(nyo)001:6467: 'di nyid ni bde gshegs zur po che'i dgongs pa
NK128(nyo)001:6469: mkhyen pa thams cad bum pa gang 'byo'i tshul du mnga' ba /
NK128(nyo)001:6470: blo gros kyi spobs pa mchog tu gyur cing sbyor
NK128(nyo)001:6471: sgrol mtha' phyin pa'i rig 'dzin chen po yin no
NK128(nyo)001:6472: // de nas bla ma zur chen 'ug pa lung du byon /
NK128(nyo)001:6473: zur chung pas thag sgrub khang du byon nas sgrub pa kho na mdzad pa'i dus su /
NK128(nyo)001:6474: dpal chen po yang dag zhal gsum phyag drug pa 'bras bu'i he ru ka zhal gzigs /
NK128(nyo)001:6475: de la legs par gzigs pas bla ma zur chen
NK128(nyo)001:6476: nyid he ru ka'i sku bzhengs pa yin par gzigs
NK128(nyo)001:6477: / der thag sgrub khang du gtsug lag khang bzhengs
NK128(nyo)001:6478: nas he ru ka de lta bu'i sku zhig bzhengs
NK128(nyo)001:6479: / par mdzad pas / lha bzo bas ji bzhin ma byung bas lan gnyis gsum bshig /
NK128(nyo)001:6481: bzo ba rnams kyis rdzong ba ster na bgyis /
NK128(nyo)001:6482: mi ster yang 'gro lha bzo rgyu gzhan na yang yod zer /
NK128(nyo)001:6483: der zur chung pas de ring mchod pa bshams shig /
NK128(nyo)001:6484: ngas bla ma dkon cog la gsol ba btab gyis gsungs /
NK128(nyo)001:6485: der bla ma'i byin rlabs lha bzo ba la zhugs
NK128(nyo)001:6486: te rig pa rang bzhin gyis 'ur te dpal chen
NK128(nyo)001:6487: po gnas yul sgo ma dang bcas pa'i lha tshogs
NK128(nyo)001:6488: bzhengs / gtso bo'i phyag gnyis dang 'gying mi 'dra ba zhal gzigs ltar ro //
NK128(nyo)001:6489: de ltar lha khang grub nas rab gnas kyi tshe
