NK128(nyo)001:6490: dpal chen po'i sku de yang ru lu'i sgra sgrogs
NK128(nyo)001:6491: shing / gnas yul sgo mar bcas pa'i lha 'khor
NK128(nyo)001:6492: rnams kyis kyang ru lu'i gar dbyangs kyis mchod pa
NK128(nyo)001:6494: de nas zur chung pas nyan bshad skyong ba'i dus
NK128(nyo)001:6495: su grwa pa rnam gsum la bshad grwa gtad de
NK128(nyo)001:6496: / khyod tshos nyan bshad kyis bstan pa skyongs shig /
NK128(nyo)001:6497: ngas sgom sgrub la 'gro yi gsungs nas brag rgya bo la gshegs te /
NK128(nyo)001:6498: de yang rdo rje sems dpa'i khang bu bya bar
NK128(nyo)001:6499: gsang ba sgyu 'phrul las byung ba'i phyag rgya bsam
NK128(nyo)001:6500: gtan gyi sgrub pa zhes bya ba rdo rje sems
NK128(nyo)001:6501: dpa'i sgrub thabs la brten nas sgrub pa mdzad pas
NK128(nyo)001:6502: / dpal rdo rje sems dpa'i zhal gzigs te /
NK128(nyo)001:6503: g.yas ru thag gi lung pa thams cad rdo rje sems dpas khengs pa'i gzigs snang byung zhing /
NK128(nyo)001:6504: snang ba zad bar gyi skye mched brnyes cir snang
NK128(nyo)001:6505: ba thams cad rdo rje sems dpa'i rang bzhin du
NK128(nyo)001:6506: bkra lam me gsal ba byung /
NK128(nyo)001:6507: der zur chung pa'i thugs la 'di rnams kyang bzang rtog gi mthus byung ba yin /
NK128(nyo)001:6508: yang dag par gtad so med snyam du dgongs te
NK128(nyo)001:6509: bsam gtan gyi khang bur rdzogs pa chen po rtsol
NK128(nyo)001:6510: bral gyi ngang du mnyam par bzhag pas /
NK128(nyo)001:6511: rdzogs pa chen po rang snang ris med kyi dgongs pa shar te mi rtog pa'i ting nge 'dzin /
NK128(nyo)001:6512: bsam gtan snang ba rnam 'byed kyi ting nge 'dzin
NK128(nyo)001:6513: thob ste sa rdo ri brag thams cad la thogs
NK128(nyo)001:6514: pa med par 'gro ba byung ngo //
NK128(nyo)001:6515: de dus zur chung pa'i mnal lam du chu lho
NK128(nyo)001:6516: nas mtsho chen po zhig byung nas rgya bo'i brag
NK128(nyo)001:6518: zla ba gcig gi khongs su slob ma snod ldan zhig yong bar 'dug gsungs so //
NK128(nyo)001:6519: de'i tshe de lung rtsa brgyad du ma thog byang 'bar bya ba chos gzhi la yongs nas /
NK128(nyo)001:6520: khong mtshan nyid mkhas pa chen po yin pas /
NK128(nyo)001:6521: khong gi gsungs nas nged rang mkhas btsun gyi dgon
NK128(nyo)001:6522: ltag tu sngags pa 'di rnams sdod mi rigs pas
NK128(nyo)001:6523: / khyed grwa pa mkhas pa rnams rgyug la sun phyung la shog gsungs pas /
NK128(nyo)001:6525: bdag gi sun phyung bar bagyi'o zhes khas blangs te brag rgya bor phyin to //
NK128(nyo)001:6526: de'i tshe bla ma stong nyid snying rje zung 'jug
NK128(nyo)001:6527: gi don la rtse gcig tu bzhugs pas phyi nang
NK128(nyo)001:6528: gi rgyu 'grul med par gzigs spyil gyi sgor bya
NK128(nyo)001:6530: btsun chung gis khyed sgom gyin rang yod dam zhus pas /
NK128(nyo)001:6531: dmigs pa gang la gtad 'dug gsungs /
NK128(nyo)001:6532: 'o na mi sgom par yod dam byas pas /
NK128(nyo)001:6533: shes pa gang la yengs 'dug gsungs /
NK128(nyo)001:6534: btsun chung gis mar don shog chos gtam bya'o byas pas /
NK128(nyo)001:6535: chos thams cad brjod med mtha' bral yin gsungs /
NK128(nyo)001:6536: de thul pa phyin slog tu gyon nas byon pas /
NK128(nyo)001:6538: khyod chos log byed rtags thul pa phyir slog byas 'dug zer /
NK128(nyo)001:6540: pags pa dang po nas 'di ltar 'dug pa'i don gyis phyir ma log /
NK128(nyo)001:6541: de ltar na khyed rang rnams kyis gos dang chos
NK128(nyo)001:6542: log gsungs pas btsun chung skyengs te phyir mkhan po'i
NK128(nyo)001:6543: drung du phyin pas sun phyung ngam gsungs /
NK128(nyo)001:6548: nged rang gnangs 'gro gsungs nas mkhan po rang byon /
NK128(nyo)001:6549: der bla ma zur chung pas rten 'brel bsgrigs pas /
NK128(nyo)001:6550: ma thog pa ma tshad nas dbu zhwa phud nas byon pas /
NK128(nyo)001:6551: khar seng mnal lam du byung ba'i mdzo de yin
NK128(nyo)001:6552: par mkhyen nas sla ye rgyu chos kyi bgro gleng
NK128(nyo)001:6553: mdzad pas / rdo'i ka ba zhig yod pa la
NK128(nyo)001:6554: rtsod pa'i thog mar ma thog pas rdo'i ka ba
NK128(nyo)001:6555: 'di rtag par 'dod dam mi rtag par 'dod ces
NK128(nyo)001:6556: mdzad pas / dris pas / bla ma zur chung pas /
NK128(nyo)001:6557: kho bo la gang du yang grub pa mi gda'
NK128(nyo)001:6558: gsungs phyag gi yud yud mdzad rdo'i ka ba dum
NK128(nyo)001:6559: bur chad / yang nam mkha' la sngar bzhin dris pas /
NK128(nyo)001:6560: phyag nam mkha' la phyar te rgyab pas tog tog zer /
NK128(nyo)001:6561: der mkhan po ma thog pa shin tu mos te
NK128(nyo)001:6562: zhabs spyi bor blangs thugs rjes bzung bar zhu zhes
NK128(nyo)001:6563: zhus shing / kho bo ni 'di phyi'i 'dun ma
NK128(nyo)001:6564: legs so gsungs nas bro 'khrabs pas ma thog bro
NK128(nyo)001:6565: zhus shing / ra ba byung / der khong gi grwa pa rnams ni /
NK128(nyo)001:6566: sngags pa de rnams kyis 'o cag gi mkhan po la smyo chu blud nas /
NK128(nyo)001:6567: da ste nged rang rnams 'agro'o zer nas bla ma
NK128(nyo)001:6568: zur chung pa'i sgrub khang du 'ong ste sla ye
NK128(nyo)001:6569: ka gcig ma yod pa de bshus /
NK128(nyo)001:6570: spyir po'i steng nas mar brag g.yag shad tsam mang po la gzu ba bcug ste sgril bas /
NK128(nyo)001:6571: rdo rnams gzims spyil gyi thog tu sleb pa dang
NK128(nyo)001:6572: zur chung pas rdo thams cad stong pa yin gsungs
NK128(nyo)001:6573: nas se gol brdabs pas rdo thams cad rdul du
NK128(nyo)001:6574: bun gyis song ste nus ma thongs par grwa pa
NK128(nyo)001:6576: de nas ma thog par 'khor ba rtsad gcod kyi dbang dang sems sde bco brgyad kyi dbang /
NK128(nyo)001:6577: kun byed sogs rdzogs chen rtsa 'grel rnams gnang ste rjes su bzung ngo //
NK128(nyo)001:6578: de nas yang shab tu phyug po zhig gis /
NK128(nyo)001:6579: khyung po grags bzang dang zur chung pa gnyis chos 'khor la spyan drangs te /
NK128(nyo)001:6580: de'i tshe khyung po de phrag dog can yin pas
NK128(nyo)001:6581: sngags pa zur chung pa 'dra ba bsad na sems
NK128(nyo)001:6583: byang sems kyi bslab bya dang mthun no zer /
NK128(nyo)001:6584: khong ni grwa pa mkhas pa skyo zla gnyis /
NK128(nyo)001:6585: glan yang khyed gnyis te bzhi po la khyed bzhis
NK128(nyo)001:6586: zur chung pa sun phyungs la shog zer btang bas
NK128(nyo)001:6587: / khong bzhis bla ma zur chung la dris shing brtsad pas /
NK128(nyo)001:6588: rtogs pa phul du phyin sgom byung gi shes rab rdol bas spobs pa lan med du gyur nas /
NK128(nyo)001:6589: theg chen gyi chos phyin ci ma log par ston
NK128(nyo)001:6590: pa rig grol spobs par ldan pa'i bshes gnyen 'di
NK128(nyo)001:6592: da lta dngos su phyin na mkhan po mi dgyes pas /
NK128(nyo)001:6593: slar thabs legs kyis slob dpon dang bral nas zur
NK128(nyo)001:6594: chung pa'i drung du gtug pa'i dam bcas te song
NK128(nyo)001:6595: ngo // sang phod khong bzhi byung ba rjes su bzung bas ka ba bzhi byung ba yin te /
NK128(nyo)001:6596: khong bzhi la g.yas ru'i mkha' 'gro'i lha khang du
NK128(nyo)001:6597: 'dus pa mdo'i dbang bskur zhing mnyes pa'i yo byad
NK128(nyo)001:6598: mang du phul / gong bu'i skyo ston sh+aakya ye
NK128(nyo)001:6599: shes sems phyogs rdzogs chen gyi ka ba gsang mtshan
NK128(nyo)001:6601: nag mo ri gseb kyi mda' tig jo sh+aaka 'phrin
NK128(nyo)001:6602: sgrub kyi ka ba gsang mtshan rdo rje dngos grub
NK128(nyo)001:6604: chu bzang gi glan sh+aakya bzang po sgyu 'phrul gyi ka ba gsang mtshan rdo rje myu gu rtsal /
NK128(nyo)001:6605: skyer lung gi yang khyer bla ma mdo'i ka ba
NK128(nyo)001:6606: gsang mtshan thig le 'gyur med rtsal rnams yin par
NK128(nyo)001:6607: grags te / mdo'i dbang byang las kyang gsal bar 'byung ba dang rjes su mthun no //
NK128(nyo)001:6608: ka ba bzhi yang grub pa dang sku che ba'i
NK128(nyo)001:6609: yon tan bsam gyis mi khyab pa dang ldan par
NK128(nyo)001:6611: de ltar bla ma zur chung pas brag rgya bong
NK128(nyo)001:6612: lo nyi shu rtsa bzhi sgrub pa la bzhugs dgongs
NK128(nyo)001:6613: gtad kyang / sku mtshams thon dgos pa'i rkyen bzhi byung bas /
NK128(nyo)001:6614: lo ril po bcu gsum dang ngo bcu bzhir bzhugs
NK128(nyo)001:6615: ring zab mo'i chos nyid mnyam pa'i don rtogs te
NK128(nyo)001:6616: shing ta la bdun tsam 'phags te nam mkhar bzhugs
NK128(nyo)001:6617: pa dang / nyi zer la 'byon bzhud mdzad pa dang /
NK128(nyo)001:6618: rdo rje sems dpa'i skur sprul nus pa sogs kyi yon tan brnyes shing /
NK128(nyo)001:6619: sku mtshams 'grol ba'i rkyen bzhi'i gcig ni gong du
NK128(nyo)001:6620: bshad nyan skyong bar bskos pa'i grwa pa gsum ni
NK128(nyo)001:6623: sum pa dbang tshul gsum yin kyang /
NK128(nyo)001:6625: gsang ba snying por thabs lam ma rgyud cig dgos
NK128(nyo)001:6626: zer nas 'gos khug pa lhas btsas kyi drung du
NK128(nyo)001:6629: sgyu 'phrul gyi dkyil 'khor phyir 'don dus yo ga
NK128(nyo)001:6630: zhig dgos zer nas sum pa dgye 'phar la yo
NK128(nyo)001:6633: sgyu 'phrul 'di la gzhi lam grub mtha' la tshad
NK128(nyo)001:6634: ma zhig dgos zer 'dar chung la tshad ma bslab
NK128(nyo)001:6635: tu song / de ltar go ma chod mi gsum
NK128(nyo)001:6636: gyis bstan pa ma 'khyogs pas bshad grwa skyong dgos
NK128(nyo)001:6638: rkyen gnyis pa ni sgro phug lha khang gi bla
NK128(nyo)001:6639: ma'i phyag rjes skyong ba dang zhes bshad kyang sgro
NK128(nyo)001:6640: phug lha khang bla 'di rang gis bzhengs pas bla
NK128(nyo)001:6641: ma'i phyag rjes zer ba ma dag pa 'dra dpyad
NK128(nyo)001:6642: do // gsum pa ni 'ug pa lung gi gdan
NK128(nyo)001:6643: sa mdzad de bla ma'i drung du dbang thob nas
NK128(nyo)001:6644: man ngag ma thob pa rnams la zab khrid ston
NK128(nyo)001:6645: do // pa dang / bzhi pa ni slob ma
NK128(nyo)001:6646: brgya dang brgyad kyis gtsug lag khang brgya dang brgyad
NK128(nyo)001:6647: bzhengs pa'i rab gnas mdzad dgos pa sogs de bzhi'i
NK128(nyo)001:6649: lha ze mor sku 'chag tu byon rdzi ra zhig
NK128(nyo)001:6650: yod par dro gsol nas bsam gtan cung zhig bsgoms
NK128(nyo)001:6651: te ri zer sku 'chag par mdzad pas nyams dga'
NK128(nyo)001:6652: la 'khrabs snying 'dod mi rtog pa gtad med du
NK128(nyo)001:6653: shar nas bogs thon pa byung /
NK128(nyo)001:6654: de nas rgya bor gshegs pas da ci dro gsol
NK128(nyo)001:6655: gsol ba'i sa der bshos lhag dum zhig lus pa'i
NK128(nyo)001:6656: rjes na tsan dan dkar po gdugs tsam zhig skad
NK128(nyo)001:6658: 'dir rgyal ba zhi ba'i lha khang zhig bzhengs na
NK128(nyo)001:6659: snyigs ma'i dus su 'gro ba la phan zhing nad
NK128(nyo)001:6660: gdon gyi gnyer por 'gyur ba la dgongs te lha
NK128(nyo)001:6661: khang bzhengs pas bzo bo gsum gyis zla ba gsum
NK128(nyo)001:6662: dang zhag bdun la grub ste nyin mo mi'i brtsigs
NK128(nyo)001:6663: pa bas mtshan mo mkha' 'gros brtsigs pa mtho bar
NK128(nyo)001:6664: byung ba mkha' 'gro lha khang du grags /
NK128(nyo)001:6665: zhal slob ma thog byang 'bar gyis lha khang zhig bzhengs bar 'dod nas /
NK128(nyo)001:6666: shing sdong chen po zhing khal gcig gi rgya yod pa /
NK128(nyo)001:6667: sdong po rang bzhin gyis 'khu ba shin tu gnyan pa zhig yod pa la /
NK128(nyo)001:6668: nye gnas la zhags pa zhig gtad nas shing 'di
NK128(nyo)001:6669: la gzhi bdag sbrul dkar nag gnyis yod kyis bzung
NK128(nyo)001:6670: zhig zer nas / ma thog pa rang gis phrag
NK128(nyo)001:6671: pa phud de shing sdong la sta gri rgyab pas
NK128(nyo)001:6672: khrag nu ru ru byung ba'i /
NK128(nyo)001:6673: shing de las kho rang gi lha khang 'byongs shing /
NK128(nyo)001:6674: shing phung ka ba bdun bla ma zur chung par phul /
NK128(nyo)001:6675: spen ma'i ka ba gcig lus nas gtsang po la drangs pas /
NK128(nyo)001:6676: rnga mo 'phrang du zhag lnga chu la bying nas ma thon /
NK128(nyo)001:6677: der grwa pa rnams kyis bla ma zur chung drung
NK128(nyo)001:6678: du 'ongs te ka ba legs po zhig yod kyang
NK128(nyo)001:6679: chu la bying nas ma thon zhus pas /
NK128(nyo)001:6680: 'dir mkha' 'gro lha khang bzhengs na snyigs dus 'gro la phan thogs rgya cher 'dug pa /
NK128(nyo)001:6681: spyir sde brgyad kyi phrag dog byed /
NK128(nyo)001:6682: dgongs rnga mo 'phrang gi gzhi bdag gis phrag dog byed par 'dug pas /
NK128(nyo)001:6683: khyed rang gnyis gtor ma dkar dmar 'di gnyis khyer la dkar gtor 'di brag thog tu spungs /
NK128(nyo)001:6684: dmar gtor 'di mtsho la rgyob la /
NK128(nyo)001:6685: 'o ka ba 'di bla ma zur chung pa'i yin pas /
NK128(nyo)001:6686: khyed rang da lta skyel na skyol cig gyis la phyi mig ma blta bar log shog gsungs /
NK128(nyo)001:6687: khong gnyis kyis de bzhin byas pas shing yang thon
NK128(nyo)001:6688: te gtsug lag khang gi shing sgrig rnams legs par
NK128(nyo)001:6689: grub / dpon slob rnams tsha ba gsol ring bzo
NK128(nyo)001:6690: bos rgya mthongs khel bas sprul pa'i bzo bor grags
NK128(nyo)001:6691: grub / / der rten lha khang grub nas brten pa lha sangs rgyas zhe gnyis kyi sku bzhengs /
NK128(nyo)001:6692: gong gi tsan dan sdong po de'i rtsar tshogs bdag legs ldan gyi sku yang bzhengs shing /
NK128(nyo)001:6693: rab gnas zin pa'i dus bla mas mgon po'i sku
NK128(nyo)001:6694: la phod ka'i mthu ba lan gsum rgyab nas khyod
NK128(nyo)001:6695: sangs rgyas kyi bstan pa e srung gsungs pas /
NK128(nyo)001:6696: dbu gug gug lan gsum byung /
NK128(nyo)001:6697: dkon cog gi dbu 'phang e bstod gsungs pas /
NK128(nyo)001:6698: zhal bzhad khyad par lha rje zur chung pa'i rgyud 'dzin gyi gdong grogs bgyid dam gsungs pas /
NK128(nyo)001:6699: ji ltar bka' bgo ba bzhin du bgyid ces gsung byon no //
NK128(nyo)001:6700: der nye gnas mos gus chen po skyes te de'i rgyu mtshan zhus pas /
NK128(nyo)001:6701: kho bo ni he ru kahdangosa yin pas chos skyong mgon po las la bskul ba yin gsungs /
NK128(nyo)001:6702: de ltar sgro phug mkha' 'gro lha khang bzhengs tshul yang /
NK128(nyo)001:6704: bshos lhag tsan dan sdong por sangs rgyas 'khrungs /
NK128(nyo)001:6705: zhes bsdus don gyi sgo nas gsungs so //
NK128(nyo)001:6706: de nas slar yang brag rgya bor byon te zad
NK128(nyo)001:6707: par gyi ting nge 'dzin la mnga' brnyes pa'i rtags
NK128(nyo)001:6708: su chu sgom pas brag las chu rang babs su
NK128(nyo)001:6709: brdol / rlung bsgoms pas rlung la rang dbang thob ste snga dro 'ug pa lung du snga chos /
NK128(nyo)001:6710: mkha' 'gro lha khang sgro phug tu gung chos /
NK128(nyo)001:6711: brag rgya bor phyi chos la phebs pa mdzad der bshad sgrub kyi grwa chen po bskyangs /
NK128(nyo)001:6712: bu slob mang du 'dus pa'i ka ba bzhi ni gong du bshad pa ltar la /
NK128(nyo)001:6713: gdung ma brgyad ni gnubs ston gapa ma /
NK128(nyo)001:6716: dbus pas mtho rang rtse khram byang dpal /
NK128(nyo)001:6720: sgom chen gnyis ni 'ba' sgom dge ma /
NK128(nyo)001:6722: gzhan yang phyam rtsa bco brgyad /
NK128(nyo)001:6723: phyam phran sum cu so gnyis /
NK128(nyo)001:6726: sta kur mi gnyis la sogs pa byung ste 'chad
NK128(nyo)001:6727: nyan gyi dus dpe 'grims khri phrag lhag tsam byung
NK128(nyo)001:6728: bar grags te bstan pa dar zhing rgyas par mdzad
NK128(nyo)001:6729: do // de ltar bla ma zur chung pa de
NK128(nyo)001:6730: nyid lugs gnyis nas sku bsod brdol ba ltar song
NK128(nyo)001:6731: bas bod kyi sngags pa tshogs tshad kyis phyag mi
NK128(nyo)001:6732: byed pa med cing gral 'gor su yang mi 'gro
NK128(nyo)001:6733: do // ba / dge bshes 'gos khug pa lhas
NK128(nyo)001:6734: btsas zhes bya ba sngags gsar ma'i lo ts+aa ba
NK128(nyo)001:6735: chen po sngon bla ma zur chen gyi drung du
NK128(nyo)001:6736: rta nag pa'i 'brog pa g.yu dang zangs khyer nas
NK128(nyo)001:6737: yongs mkhan de yin pas chos ma gnang ba'i snying
NK128(nyo)001:6738: nad kyis phyis rnying mar 'byams yig mang du btong
NK128(nyo)001:6739: ba po de nyid kun slong phrag dog gi dbang
NK128(nyo)001:6740: do // ba / gis / rang re gsar ma
NK128(nyo)001:6741: ba rnams zur chung ba kho la phyag 'tshal don
NK128(nyo)001:6742: do // ba / gis / yang med / gral
NK128(nyo)001:6743: gsham du sdod don yang med pas nged rang tsho
NK128(nyo)001:6744: khrims gyis shig zer khrims bcas so //
NK128(nyo)001:6745: nam zhig na shangs su ston mo chen po zhig
NK128(nyo)001:6746: byung ba'i tshe dge bshes dang sngags pa thams cad
NK128(nyo)001:6747: tshogs nas / bla ma zur chung pa grwa la
NK128(nyo)001:6748: 'gor bzhugs pa'i spyan sngar dge bshes 'gos rang byon
NK128(nyo)001:6750: ston mo gyes pa'i tshe kho rang gi grwa pa rnams kyis 'gos la /
NK128(nyo)001:6751: zur chung par phyag mi 'tshal khrims bcas nas khyed rang phyag mdzad pa ci lags zhus pas /
NK128(nyo)001:6752: khong gi drung du phyin tsa na bcom ldan 'das
NK128(nyo)001:6753: dpal chen po'am de 'di kha yin par 'dug snyams
NK128(nyo)001:6754: pa las mi'i 'du shes mi skye bar 'dug gsungs
NK128(nyo)001:6755: so // de yang 'di dang dus mtshungs su lo ts+aa ba rin cen bzang po /
NK128(nyo)001:6757: lho brag mar pa lo ts+aa /
NK128(nyo)001:6758: 'gos lo sogs rim par byung bar grags shing /
NK128(nyo)001:6759: skabs 'dir sa skya zhabs drung a mi lags kyis
NK128(nyo)001:6760: mdzad pa'i lam 'bras chos 'byung legs bshad 'dus pa'i
NK128(nyo)001:6762: 'brog ma'i rgya gar du 'byon pa'i rgyu mtshan bslab
NK128(nyo)001:6763: pa gsum la dgra dar tshul gyi lo rgyus 'di
NK128(nyo)001:6764: ltar bkod de / nyang stod du she'u ston pa
NK128(nyo)001:6765: byang 'bar gyis a man si 'dod log lam du
NK128(nyo)001:6766: 'khyer bas tshe 'di la 'tshang rgya ba yin byas
NK128(nyo)001:6767: pas lhag pa tshul khrims la dgra dar /
NK128(nyo)001:6768: nyang smad du zur chung shes rab grags pas rdzogs
NK128(nyo)001:6769: chen byas shes kyi sangs rgyas yid la byed pa
NK128(nyo)001:6770: yin / rnam rtog 'khor ba yin bzlas pas ting nge 'dzin la dgra dar /
NK128(nyo)001:6771: dbu ru byang du dge bshes ston pas bka' gdams bshad nyan ngal ba don med yin /
NK128(nyo)001:6772: so sor thar pa'i sdom pa bsrung zhing thugs rje
NK128(nyo)001:6773: chen po la sogs pa'i yi dam re bsgrubs pas
NK128(nyo)001:6774: dus tshod gcig la yi dam gyis sgro 'dogs thams
NK128(nyo)001:6775: cad chod par 'gyur zhes bya bas lhag pa shes
NK128(nyo)001:6777: zhang mtshal min pas bla ma la lus srog phul
NK128(nyo)001:6778: nas 'khrug pa byas pas 'tshang rgya bzlas pas bslab
NK128(nyo)001:6779: pa gsum ga la dgra dar /
NK128(nyo)001:6781: she'u ston pa'i slob brgyud grags che ba med 'dra zhing /
NK128(nyo)001:6782: zur chung pa rnying ma bka' ma'i phyogs /
NK128(nyo)001:6783: dge bshes ston pa 'brom ston rgyal ba'i 'byung gnas bka' gdams kyi chu 'go /
NK128(nyo)001:6784: zhang mtshal min pa zhes pa thugs kyi zhe 'dod
NK128(nyo)001:6785: zhang tshal pa bla ma zhang rin po cher gsung
NK128(nyo)001:6786: rgyu yin 'dug kyang mtshal min zhes pa yi ge
NK128(nyo)001:6787: nor ba yin nam ha cang 'ju chen po zhig
NK128(nyo)001:6789: zhang mtshal pa ni tshal pa bka' brgyud la zer /
NK128(nyo)001:6790: der mi 'du ba'i mtshal min zhes da lta dol
NK128(nyo)001:6791: mtshal min par grags pa yin tshul sogs rgyal rab
NK128(nyo)001:6794: 'brom ston gyi lhag pa shes rab kyi bslab pa
NK128(nyo)001:6795: la gnod pa la bka' gdams pa gsar rnying tsho
NK128(nyo)001:6796: nas zhu ba 'bul yong ba gzhir bcas shing /
NK128(nyo)001:6797: bla ma zhang gis bslab pa gsum ga la gnod
NK128(nyo)001:6798: pa yang de mtshungs su bka' brgyud pa rnams kyi
NK128(nyo)001:6800: nged snga 'gyur ba rnams kyi zur chung pas lhag
NK128(nyo)001:6801: pa ting nge 'dzin la gnod pa ma bskyal tshul
NK128(nyo)001:6802: mgo thog kha ba sprug pa skabs su bab par
NK128(nyo)001:6803: snang bas / de yang rdzogs chen byas shes kyi sangs rgyas yid la byed pa yin /
NK128(nyo)001:6804: rnam rtog 'khor ba yin zhes pa'i tshig zur chung
NK128(nyo)001:6805: pa'i gsung rab tu 'dug pa rang lugs la ma
NK128(nyo)001:6806: grags kyang / tshig de la skyon chags pa zhig kyang mi 'dug pas bsgrub tu rung ste /
NK128(nyo)001:6807: sangs rgyas yid la byed pa mdo sngags kun gyi lam srol yin pas /
NK128(nyo)001:6808: rang rang gi sgrub bya'i 'bras bu de nyid yid
NK128(nyo)001:6809: la byed cing lam ma bsgrubs na 'bras bu ci
NK128(nyo)001:6810: la 'byung / thos bsam sgom gsum gyi bsam pa de yang yid la byed pa ma yin nam /
NK128(nyo)001:6814: yid la bya ba dang zhes bya ba de yang ji ltar yin /
NK128(nyo)001:6815: yid la byar mi rung na bsam gtan yang gang gis bsgrub par 'gyur /
NK128(nyo)001:6816: tha mal gyi rnam rtog 'khor ba yin pa gzhir bcas te /
NK128(nyo)001:6817: de ltar min na dpal ldan sa skya pa rnams
NK128(nyo)001:6818: dwags po bka' brgyud kyi rnam rtog chos sku la
NK128(nyo)001:6819: yang bka' skyon mdzad mi rigs par snang /
NK128(nyo)001:6820: 'di dag la lung sbyor 'dra du ma 'dug kyang
NK128(nyo)001:6821: brir ma lang bas 'bru gnon des 'thus pa 'dra
NK128(nyo)001:6823: 'brog mi rgya gar du 'byon pa'i rkyen de ltar yin tshul bris nas /
NK128(nyo)001:6824: 'og tu 'brog ma'i rgya gar nas 'khor nas 'chad
NK128(nyo)001:6825: nyan mdzad de slob ma bskrun tshul gyi skabs su
NK128(nyo)001:6826: rgyud tshul gyi slob ma bshad pa'i tshe yang /
NK128(nyo)001:6827: lnga pa ni nya ri zur po che sh+aakya 'byung gnas kyis kyang gzi dang g.yu /
NK128(nyo)001:6828: za 'og gi gdan gang ba zhig phul nas chos zhus pas lo bzhi la /
NK128(nyo)001:6829: rgyud gsum cha lag dang bcas pa mkhyen zhing /
NK128(nyo)001:6830: khyad par du gur la mkhas par gyur nas chos gsungs pas grwa pa'ang brgya lhag re byung zhing /
NK128(nyo)001:6831: nya rir rgyud kyi bshad pa 'dzugs par bzhed pa la khong gi bu chen rtse mo gnyis /
NK128(nyo)001:6835: dral ma sum cu so gnyis /
NK128(nyo)001:6837: bya ba rnams 'dus nas 'bul ba mang po phul
NK128(nyo)001:6838: nas gsang sngags snga 'gyur gyi bstan pa mi bshig
NK128(nyo)001:6839: par zhu zer bas bshad ma nus par de las
NK128(nyo)001:6840: 'phel ba ni cher ma byung la /
NK128(nyo)001:6841: 'on kyang 'brog ma'i slob ma grags che ba zhig yin no //
NK128(nyo)001:6843: 'jig rten kha dper dgos pa rdo rje dang mi
NK128(nyo)001:6844: dgos rdo 'byong zer ba kho na bzhin byung 'dug
NK128(nyo)001:6845: pas / zur chung pa lhag pa ting nge 'dzin gyis bstan dgra yin la /
NK128(nyo)001:6846: de'i bla ma zur po che rgyud la mkhas pa'i
NK128(nyo)001:6847: slob mar mdzad pa ni shin tu mi rigs pa
NK128(nyo)001:6849: zur chung pa zur po che'i sku tsha yin pas
NK128(nyo)001:6850: rnying ma'i lo rgyus 'di rnams la tig tig med
NK128(nyo)001:6851: dgongs 'ol tshod gnags pa'i skyon byung 'dra bas /
NK128(nyo)001:6852: 'brog mi rgya gar du 'byon gdong thog mar sku tsha byung /
NK128(nyo)001:6853: rgya gar du yun ring bzhugs mkhas grub tu gyur nas /
NK128(nyo)001:6854: phyis bod du byon nas gdul bya skyong skabs zur
NK128(nyo)001:6855: chung pa'i khu po zur po che byung ba 'dra
NK128(nyo)001:6856: zhig gis zur khu tshan gnyis snga phyi 'dzol ba'i
NK128(nyo)001:6857: skyon yang snang / bla ma zur po che la
NK128(nyo)001:6858: phyogs ris mi mnga' bas 'brog ma'i slob ma yin
NK128(nyo)001:6859: tshul zur gyi rnam thar du yang gsal la /
NK128(nyo)001:6860: lam 'bras kyi lo rgyus ngo mtshar snang ba sogs
NK128(nyo)001:6861: snga phyi thams cad du 'byung zhing don la gnas
NK128(nyo)001:6863: bla ma chen po'i bka' drin gyis //
NK128(nyo)001:6864: a bo'i sems phyogs nor du thal //
NK128(nyo)001:6865: zhes gsungs pa lam 'bras ba rnams kyi thugs la
NK128(nyo)001:6866: lam 'bras kyi che bar song ba 'dra zhig 'dug
NK128(nyo)001:6867: kyang / snga 'gyur gyi lo rgyus dang tshig don kho rang gi thad du /
NK128(nyo)001:6868: lam 'bras kyi chos kyis rdzogs chen la zab khyad
NK128(nyo)001:6869: thon cing nges shes rnyed pas chos gzhan la 'gram
NK128(nyo)001:6870: chu mi ldang bar rdzogs chen nor bu rin po
NK128(nyo)001:6871: che lta bur song ba yin pas lo rgyus de
NK128(nyo)001:6872: yang lam 'bras kyi zhabs 'degs su 'gro dka' ba
NK128(nyo)001:6873: zhig 'dug / de ltar khu bo zur chen 'brog
NK128(nyo)001:6874: ma'i slob ma yin la sku tsha zur chung pas
NK128(nyo)001:6875: zur chen gyi gdan sa mdzad de 'chad nyan phyis
NK128(nyo)001:6877: 'brog mi rgya gar du 'byon skabs zur chung pas
NK128(nyo)001:6878: lhag pa ting nge 'dzin la dgra byed don mi
NK128(nyo)001:6879: 'dug pas lo rgyus 'di tsho dus mi 'tshungs pa'i
NK128(nyo)001:6880: 'dra min kun 'dus las khungs che bar mi sems
NK128(nyo)001:6881: / zur chung pa'i slob ma'i grangs la snga 'gyur
NK128(nyo)001:6882: dang ma mthun yang thugs rgyus mi mnga' 'dra bas
NK128(nyo)001:6883: / ci zhu zhing / lo rgyus gzhan rnams kyang de 'dra'i mched zla yin dogs 'dug /
NK128(nyo)001:6884: de bzhin du rnying ma'i rgyud khungs rgyal po dzahl chos char babs te /
NK128(nyo)001:6885: gsang bdag gi zhal bstan cing byin gyis brlabs pa de yang mi 'thad tshul bshad pa dang /
NK128(nyo)001:6887: gsang sngags rang nyid len pa ni //
NK128(nyo)001:6888: lus can dmyal ba 'ba' zhig tu //
NK128(nyo)001:6890: slob dpon ku ku ra dza dang ku ku ri ba nor ba sogs du ma 'dug pas /
NK128(nyo)001:6891: gsang ba'i bdag pos rgyal po dzahl zhal bstan cing
NK128(nyo)001:6892: dbang bskur bas bla ma'i go mi chod par bla
NK128(nyo)001:6893: ma'i rnal pa zhig rang nges par dgos na rnal
NK128(nyo)001:6894: 'byor dbang phyug gis bdag med ma'i sprul pa'i dkyil
NK128(nyo)001:6895: 'khor du dbang gsan pa de yang bkag rigs pa
NK128(nyo)001:6896: dang / de ltar min na rgyal po dzahs gsang
NK128(nyo)001:6897: bdag gi zhal mthong zhing nges don gyi bstan pa
NK128(nyo)001:6898: dang theg pa thams cad rdzogs pa'i dbang bskur ba
NK128(nyo)001:6899: dang / yin pas / gsang sngags rang nyid kyis blangs pa'i skyon yang 'jug par mi nus shing /
NK128(nyo)001:6900: klan ka 'di ltar byung gi dogs nas ku ku
NK128(nyo)001:6901: r+aa dza la dri ba mdzad tshul sogs yod pas
NK128(nyo)001:6902: lo rgyus zhib tu ma gzigs pa'i skyon du snang
NK128(nyo)001:6903: / ku ku ri pa dang ku ku r+aa dza
NK128(nyo)001:6904: nor ba ni phyogs 'dir gzigs pa chung ba las
NK128(nyo)001:6905: de tsam de tsam gyi skyon du mi 'gyur pa
NK128(nyo)001:6907: mdzad pa bcu gnyis der yang lo rgyus gsung rabs
NK128(nyo)001:6908: spyi dang mi mthun pa 'ga' re 'dug cing /
NK128(nyo)001:6909: der ma zad stod smad bar gsum du snga phyi mi 'grig pa'i skyon 'ga' zhig dang /
NK128(nyo)001:6910: de bzhin du mgon po chos 'byung du yang rjes
NK128(nyo)001:6911: 'jug rnams dag snang 'gog thabs gzhan zer tshig gi
NK128(nyo)001:6912: 'khar tsam la brten pa'i lo rgyus dgong bro ba
NK128(nyo)001:6913: kha shas 'dug pa zhu lan cung zad 'bul bar
NK128(nyo)001:6914: spro na yang / sa skya ba 'di nyid yab
NK128(nyo)001:6915: sras la kho bos chos nyan cing lam 'bras sogs
NK128(nyo)001:6916: kyi brgyud par bzhugs pas gsungs la dgag sgrub bya
NK128(nyo)001:6917: ba'i yul du ma gyur bas de tsam las ma
NK128(nyo)001:6918: spro na yang / spros shing / babs mkhas pa
NK128(nyo)001:6919: chen po'i bstan bcos kyi rigs rnams legs par brtags
NK128(nyo)001:6920: shing ma mdzad na brgal lan gyi me dpung phyogs
NK128(nyo)001:6922: mos gus kyi ljon shing bsreg pa'i rgyur 'dug pas bag dang ldan par mdzad par rigs so //
NK128(nyo)001:6923: de ltar bla ma zur chung pa de nyid kyis
NK128(nyo)001:6924: 'chad nyan skyong ba'i tshe bu slob rnams kyis rigs
NK128(nyo)001:6925: sras 'jog dgos par gsol ba btab pas /
NK128(nyo)001:6926: gzhan don du 'gyur zhing 'od gsal lha rigs zur
NK128(nyo)001:6927: gyi gdung mi chad par bya ba'i phyir khab tu
NK128(nyo)001:6928: rtsags mo d+har+m+aa b+ho d+hi bzhes pa la jo btsun
NK128(nyo)001:6929: rdo rje 'bar dang jo sras mo sh+aakya lcam gnyis
NK128(nyo)001:6930: 'khrungs shing / jo sras mo mda' mo gtsug tor
NK128(nyo)001:6931: lcam la gsang bdag sgro phug pa 'khrungs pa'i rnam
NK128(nyo)001:6933: de ltar gsang chen rnying ma'i bshad bsgrub dang phrin
NK128(nyo)001:6934: las rnam pa bzhi'i sgo nas snga 'gyur chos kyi
NK128(nyo)001:6935: ring lugs rgya cher spel nas zhing 'di'i gdul bya
NK128(nyo)001:6936: rnams re zhig rdzogs par dgongs te /
NK128(nyo)001:6937: rtag 'dzin can rnams sun dbyung zhing le lo can
NK128(nyo)001:6938: chos la bskul ba'i phyir dgung lo drug cu re
NK128(nyo)001:6939: brgyad la rigs sras sgro phug pa sh+aakya seng ge'i
NK128(nyo)001:6940: don du bsam gtan mig sgron gyi dgongs pa klong
NK128(nyo)001:6941: rdol la mdo rgyud kun gyi bcud 'dus pa /
NK128(nyo)001:6942: zhal gyi gdams pa brgyad cu pa /
NK128(nyo)001:6943: stod 'dus pa mdo phyogs dang mthun pa /
NK128(nyo)001:6945: smad sems phyogs dang mthun pa zhal chems su bris
NK128(nyo)001:6946: nas bzhag ste dgongs pa chos kyi dbyings su thim
NK128(nyo)001:6948: 'di la lo rgyus 'ga' rer drug cu re gcig
NK128(nyo)001:6949: la gshegs par bzhed kyang khungs btsun pa rnams las
NK128(nyo)001:6950: re brgyad pa kho na 'byung ngo //
NK128(nyo)001:6951: de'i tshe brag rgya bor pur bzhu bas nam mkha' la sgra 'od dang /
NK128(nyo)001:6952: bar snang la lha'i gdugs rgyal mtshan sogs kyis rnam pa dang me tog gi char gyis khengs /
NK128(nyo)001:6953: sa gzhir mi ma yin mang pos mchod pa 'bul
NK128(nyo)001:6954: ba dngos su byung zhing gdugs dang ring bsrel grangs
NK128(nyo)001:6955: med pa byon / pur bzhu ba'i brag la dud
NK128(nyo)001:6956: ris kyi bkra shis sgo mang gi mchod rten sgo
NK128(nyo)001:6957: re'i nang na lha sku re bzhugs par gsal bar
NK128(nyo)001:6958: med pa byon / byon zhing / de'i tshe las
NK128(nyo)001:6959: dag pa 'ga' zhig gi ngor mkha' 'gro ma'i tshogs
NK128(nyo)001:6960: kyis bskor te rig 'dzin gyi sa la gshegs par
NK128(nyo)001:6961: med pa byon / byon zhing / mthong ngo //
NK128(nyo)001:6962: de ltar bla ma zur chung pa shes rab grags
NK128(nyo)001:6963: kyis 'dus pa mdo'i dbang ka ba bzhi po la
NK128(nyo)001:6964: med pa byon / byon zhing / mthong ngo //
NK128(nyo)001:6965: gsungs tshul / dbang yon gsang mtshan sogs zur chung
NK128(nyo)001:6966: ba'i rnam thar gyis shugs la bstan pa yin la
NK128(nyo)001:6967: med pa byon / byon zhing / mthong ngo //
NK128(nyo)001:6968: gsungs tshul / / ka ba bzhis lha rje sgro
NK128(nyo)001:6969: phug pa chen po la gsungs pa yin te /
NK128(nyo)001:6970: 'di'i rnam thar cung zad brjod na /
NK128(nyo)001:6972: yab bla ma zur chung shes rab grags /
NK128(nyo)001:6973: yum mda' mo gtsug tor lcam yin te /
NK128(nyo)001:6974: de yang bla ma'i khab bzhes kyi btsun mo jo
NK128(nyo)001:6975: btsun rdo rje 'bar yin yang gtsug tor lcam la
NK128(nyo)001:6976: sprul sku'i las 'brel yod par dgongs te zhal slob
NK128(nyo)001:6977: ka ba bzhi'i nang tshan 'phrin sgrub kyi ka ba
NK128(nyo)001:6978: mda' tig chos sh+aaka la bla ma zur chung pas
NK128(nyo)001:6979: / do nub khyod kyi sring mo 'di nga la sprod cig gsungs pas /
NK128(nyo)001:6980: bka' bzhin bsgrubs te 'bul bar mda' tig rang 'byon
NK128(nyo)001:6981: pa ngo tsha nas brda thabs su dril bu zhig
NK128(nyo)001:6982: gi nang du rdo rje zhig bcug nas sring mo
NK128(nyo)001:6983: la 'di mi gzhan ma brgyud par bla ma zur
NK128(nyo)001:6984: chung pa'i phyag tu phul zhing gsungs pa ltar byas
NK128(nyo)001:6986: lha rje sgro phug pa chen po lhums su zhugs /
NK128(nyo)001:6987: 'on kyang yum de jo mo ngos ma min pas
NK128(nyo)001:6988: grwa pa rnams sdang zhing thams cad kyi gros mthun
NK128(nyo)001:6990: sems phyogs kyi ka ba skyo ston sh+aakya ye shes kyi zhal nas /
NK128(nyo)001:6991: mda' mo gtsug tor lcam 'di'i srin lag las bstan pa'i gtso bo 'khrungs pa rmis /
NK128(nyo)001:6992: sras shig byung na bstan pa la phan srid pas zhog gsungs /
NK128(nyo)001:6993: sgyu 'phrul gyi ka ba chu bar gyi glan sh+aakya
NK128(nyo)001:6994: bzang pos jo mo'i lus la sangs rgyas kyi sku
NK128(nyo)001:6996: 'phrin sgrub kyi ka ba mda' tig jo sh+aaka la
NK128(nyo)001:6997: spyi gtsug nas gser gyis rdo rje thim par rmis
NK128(nyo)001:6998: / bla ma zur chung pa rang la jo mo'i
NK128(nyo)001:6999: lus la phyag rdor gyi sku zhig thim pa sogs
NK128(nyo)001:7000: / byung bas / dpon slob kun bka' bgros te
NK128(nyo)001:7001: yum bde bar bzhag pas zla grangs tshang ba dang
NK128(nyo)001:7002: sku bltams pa'i tshe yab kyi zhal nas nga'i bu
NK128(nyo)001:7003: 'di gsang bdag gis byin gyis brlabs shing bstan pa'i
NK128(nyo)001:7004: gtso bo dang tshul mtshungs pa bstan 'gro la phan
NK128(nyo)001:7005: pa zhig 'ong gsungs te mtshan gsang bdag sh+aakya seng
NK128(nyo)001:7006: / byung bas / ger btags / yum gyi zhal
NK128(nyo)001:7007: nas nga'i bu 'di dge bshes mda' tig gi tsha
NK128(nyo)001:7009: mig rtsa grung ba hor gyi mig 'dra bas mda' tsha hor bar thogs gsungs /
NK128(nyo)001:7010: de ltar gsang bdag sh+aakya seng ge'am mda' tsha hor por grags shing /
NK128(nyo)001:7011: phyis sgro phug bzung bas gsang bdag sgro phug par yang grags so //
NK128(nyo)001:7012: sku bltams nas zla ba brgyad song ba dang yab
NK128(nyo)001:7013: bla ma zur chung dgongs pa chos kyi dbyings su
NK128(nyo)001:7014: gzhol bas / yum dang zhang pos skyongs te mda' phur lo bco lnga bzhugs shing /
NK128(nyo)001:7015: de yang sras kyis 'dri klog ma shes kyi bar
NK128(nyo)001:7016: du yum gyis yab zur chung pa'i phyag dpe la
NK128(nyo)001:7017: la ko lding byas te bzhag /
NK128(nyo)001:7018: la la sgrom bur bcug ste sgo lcags rgyab ste sbas /
NK128(nyo)001:7019: sras kyis dpe cha ngo shes pa dang dpe cha khur cig dang /
NK128(nyo)001:7020: sbrags zhang po mda' tig jo sh+aaka la slob gnyer byed du bcug pas yab chos sgrub 'phrin zhus /
NK128(nyo)001:7021: de nas chu bar du glan sh+aakya bzang po'i drung
NK128(nyo)001:7022: du byon nas gsang ba sgyu 'phrul gyi skor rnams
NK128(nyo)001:7023: legs par gsan / dgung lo bcu dgu pa la
NK128(nyo)001:7024: sgro phug tu che 'don mdzad de mdo sgyu 'phrul
NK128(nyo)001:7025: legs par gsan / gnyis gsungs / de nas sku
NK128(nyo)001:7026: bsod rgyas pa'i dbang gis phyogs gzhan du bzhud pa'i
NK128(nyo)001:7027: skabs ma byung bar mkhas grub kyi bla ma rnams
NK128(nyo)001:7028: tshur spyan drangs shing chos gsan cing thugs gnyer thams
NK128(nyo)001:7030: gtso bo yab kyi slob ma ka ba bzhi po la mdo /
NK128(nyo)001:7032: sems phyogs gsum gyi man ngag 'phrin sgrub phyag bzhes dang bcas pa rdzogs par gsan pa ni /
NK128(nyo)001:7033: sems phyogs kyi ka ba skyo ston la sems phyogs mtha' dag gsan /
NK128(nyo)001:7034: mdo'i ka ba yang la 'dus mdo'i dbang rdzogs par gsan nas /
NK128(nyo)001:7035: sgyu 'phrul gyi ka ba glon la zhi khro sgyu 'phrul gyi skor mtha' dag gsan /
NK128(nyo)001:7036: 'phrin sgrub kyi ka ba zhang po mda' tig la bdud rtsi dang 'phrin sgrub kyi skor gsan /
NK128(nyo)001:7037: bka' tshoms ni bzhi gar gsan /
NK128(nyo)001:7038: khyad par du yang 'dus pa mdo'i dbang bskur man
NK128(nyo)001:7039: ngag dang bcas pa'i brgyud pa'i gtso bo zhang po
NK128(nyo)001:7040: lha rje mda' tig la mda' phur gsan cing /
NK128(nyo)001:7041: glan la li thung gsan pa'i yon bla ma gnyis
NK128(nyo)001:7042: la gsung rab yum rgyas 'bring bsdus gsum gyi sna
NK128(nyo)001:7043: drangs pa'i 'bul ba mang du mdzad cing thugs zin
NK128(nyo)001:7044: par mdzad de / gsang mtshan rdo rje 'jigs med
NK128(nyo)001:7045: rtsal lam dbang phyug rdzogs pa rtsal du grags te
NK128(nyo)001:7046: par mdzad de / / mdo'i dbang byang las /
NK128(nyo)001:7047: gsang bdag sh+aakya seng ge dbang phyug rdzogs pa rtsal zhes gsungs pa'i phyir /
NK128(nyo)001:7048: gzhan yang gdung ma brgyad kyi gras nas ma thog
NK128(nyo)001:7049: pa dang glan nya rtsal ba sogs la yang mang
NK128(nyo)001:7050: du gsan no // de nas nya ri sgro phug
NK128(nyo)001:7051: tu phyag phab nas sgrub pa yun ring du mdzad
NK128(nyo)001:7052: pa'i dus sku'i gzi mdangs kyis thams cad zil gyis
NK128(nyo)001:7053: du gsan no // gnon pa byung / dus der
NK128(nyo)001:7054: rgya gar dam pa sangs rgyas deng ri na bzhugs
NK128(nyo)001:7055: pa dang mjal bar dpon slob lnga byon nas /
NK128(nyo)001:7056: deng ri phebs rgyu'i nyin mo rje dam pa sangs
NK128(nyo)001:7057: rgyas kyis de ring phyag na rdo rje 'byon par
NK128(nyo)001:7058: yod do bsu ba gyis shig gsungs dar gdugs la
NK128(nyo)001:7060: nyi ma sgas su cha tsam na sngags pa dpon slob lnga byung bas /
NK128(nyo)001:7061: grwa pa rnams kyis dam pa la sngags pa lnga
NK128(nyo)001:7062: 'dug pa de yin nam gzhan ni cang mi gda'
NK128(nyo)001:7063: pas / de pa rang yin no gsungs te bsu ba mdzad /
NK128(nyo)001:7064: der gsang bdag sh+aakya seng ges grwa pa zhig la
NK128(nyo)001:7065: khyod rang bla ma yin pa skad kyis la sngon
NK128(nyo)001:7066: du song nas phyag phul zhig gsungs pa la /
NK128(nyo)001:7068: gsang bdag gi mgul na sba ba yod pa la gzigs te /
NK128(nyo)001:7069: phyag na sba ba can gyis drongs /
NK128(nyo)001:7070: dpon slob kyi go gya ma log na legs gsungs /
NK128(nyo)001:7071: de nas gsang bdag dpon slob kyis dam pa la chos gsan pa sogs mdzad cing /
NK128(nyo)001:7072: dam pas kyang sgro phug pa sangs rgyas bstan pa'i spyi dpal chen por lung bstan no //
NK128(nyo)001:7073: yang lan cig sgro phug pas lha bris pa zhig
NK128(nyo)001:7074: la phyag rdor gyi sku 'dri ba'i bris bkod kyi
NK128(nyo)001:7075: tshe / phyag na rdo rje'i skur bstan nas 'di 'dra ba zhig bris gsungs so //
NK128(nyo)001:7076: de ltar rgyu mtshan du ma'i sgo nas lha rje
NK128(nyo)001:7077: sgro phug pa 'di bcom ldan 'das gsang ba'i bdag
NK128(nyo)001:7078: po'i sprul pa yin par kun tu grags la /
NK128(nyo)001:7079: byang phyogs kyi rgyud 'dir gsang sngags kyi bstan pa
NK128(nyo)001:7080: rgyas par bya ba'i gdul bya rnams la bsam gyis
NK128(nyo)001:7081: mi khyab pa'i chos 'khor bskor zhing /
NK128(nyo)001:7082: sgro phug tu chos gsungs pa'i dus chos khri rgyab
NK128(nyo)001:7083: yol med pa zhig tu bzhugs mtha' skor thams cad
NK128(nyo)001:7084: grwa pas 'khor nas yod pa la /
NK128(nyo)001:7085: phyogs thams cad du zhal thal le ba kun tu
NK128(nyo)001:7086: zhal tu byung bas sprul pa'i sku rtsod pa med
NK128(nyo)001:7088: slob ma bskrun tshul yang spyir slob ma gdugs thogs pa stong yod par grags shing /
NK128(nyo)001:7089: bshad nyan gyi dus dpe cha kha phye ba'i shob
NK128(nyo)001:7090: sgras nya ri lung pa'i lug khyu 'grogs pa lta
NK128(nyo)001:7092: khyad par du nag po bzhi /
NK128(nyo)001:7094: mes bzhi sogs byung ba'i nag po bzhi ni /
NK128(nyo)001:7101: gya ston rdo rje mgon po /
NK128(nyo)001:7104: mes bzhi ni gtsang pa byis ston /
NK128(nyo)001:7108: slob ma'i 'dren lugs 'di zur stod lugs yin la /
NK128(nyo)001:7109: smad lugs su mi 'dra ba gzhan zhig yod kyang 'dir ma bris so //
NK128(nyo)001:7110: de ltar mdo sgyu 'phrul gyi phyogs la dbyar chos
NK128(nyo)001:7111: dgun chos kyis dus phyogs rer na mar dpe 'grem
NK128(nyo)001:7113: ston chos dang dpyid chos kyi dus su ma brgya
NK128(nyo)001:7114: tsam re yod pa sogs khyon sdom dpe 'grem khri
NK128(nyo)001:7115: phrag bdun tsam byung bar grags shing /
NK128(nyo)001:7116: de ltar bshad nyan dar bas lha rje sgro phug
NK128(nyo)001:7117: 'di bshad srol zhes yongs su grags shing deng yang
NK128(nyo)001:7118: rgyun ma chad tsam du yod do //
NK128(nyo)001:7119: de ltar zhing 'di'i gdul bya rdzogs par mdzad nas
NK128(nyo)001:7120: zhing khams gzhan du gshegs par bzhed pa'i tshe slob
NK128(nyo)001:7121: ma ston pa bzhi la tshogs kyi 'khor lo rgya
NK128(nyo)001:7122: che bar shoms shig gsungs te /
NK128(nyo)001:7123: tshogs 'khor mdzad nas chos dang man ngag zab mo mang du gnang /
NK128(nyo)001:7124: de nas khyod rnams nga med pa la mya ngan ma byed cig /
NK128(nyo)001:7125: nga lus ma spangs par rig 'dzin gyi sa la
NK128(nyo)001:7126: 'gro yin gsungs nas mgur zhig bzhes te nam mkha'
NK128(nyo)001:7127: la 'phags nas je mtho je mthor gyur te mthar
NK128(nyo)001:7128: mi mngon par gshegs pa dang /
NK128(nyo)001:7129: bu slob rnams sems kyis ma bzod par cho nge chen po bton zhing mtshan nas bos pas /
NK128(nyo)001:7130: slar nam mkha' las babs te byon nas khyed rnams
NK128(nyo)001:7131: kyis nga'i ngag la mi nyan par mya ngan byas
NK128(nyo)001:7133: nga'i chos rgyud dar mi brgyud dar po mi 'ongs
NK128(nyo)001:7134: ba 'dug gsungs te de'i phyi lo dgung lo drug
NK128(nyo)001:7135: cu re gcig pa la mya ngan las 'da' ba'i
NK128(nyo)001:7136: tshul bstan to // pur bzhu ba'i tshe sngags pa
NK128(nyo)001:7137: gzhon nu chas kyis mdzes pa zhig gis rta ngang
NK128(nyo)001:7138: pa bzang po zhig la dung sga rang gug ma
NK128(nyo)001:7139: bstad pa zhig phul bas lha rnams kyis mchod par
NK128(nyo)001:7140: tshul bstan to // grags / gzhan yang klu dang
NK128(nyo)001:7141: gnod sbyin la sogs pas nor bu mang po phul
NK128(nyo)001:7143: de ltar zur mes chen po sh+aakya 'byung gnas /
NK128(nyo)001:7145: zur dbon sh+aakya seng ge gsum gyi rigs la snga
NK128(nyo)001:7146: 'gyur bka' ma'i ring lugs dbu brnyes srol btod dar
NK128(nyo)001:7147: rgyas su mdzad pas zur mes dbon rnam gsum zhes
NK128(nyo)001:7149: 'di gsum gyi rnam thar yang rgyas bsdus sna tshogs
NK128(nyo)001:7150: zur stod smad so so'i lugs srol mang bar 'dug
NK128(nyo)001:7151: kyang / 'di ni 'jam dbyangs rin chen rgyal mtshan
NK128(nyo)001:7152: yab sras kyi bla dpe'i rgyun bzhin bris pas 'khrul
NK128(nyo)001:7154: gzhan rnams kyang grangs nges sna tshogs kyi dbang gis
NK128(nyo)001:7155: gdul bya'i snang ngor 'char tshul du ma grub thob
NK128(nyo)001:7156: kyi rnam par thar pa'i srol yin pas so sor
NK128(nyo)001:7157: bden mod / 'gal 'du ra bltas na ngan 'gro'i
NK128(nyo)001:7158: rgyur 'gyur bas dad pa gsum gyi sgo nas gus
NK128(nyo)001:7160: rnam dag rig 'dzin brgyud pa ma nyams shing //
NK128(nyo)001:7161: smin byed dbang gi chu bo ma nub pa //
NK128(nyo)001:7162: gdams ngag go rim sa rga ma log par //
NK128(nyo)001:7163: skal ldan bsam pa tshim mdzad snga 'gyur chos //
NK128(nyo)001:7164: thog mar gnyags dang bar du gnubs chen brgyud //
NK128(nyo)001:7165: tha ma zur rigs grub pa'i dbang phyug la //
NK128(nyo)001:7166: bka' babs dbang brgyud gdams pa'i srol chen po //
NK128(nyo)001:7167: ljongs 'dir gsang chen bka' mar yongs su grags //
NK128(nyo)001:7168: smin grol lam gyis yongs rdzogs bstan la 'jug /
NK128(nyo)001:7169: nyams su blangs pas mdo sngags zab don rtogs //
NK128(nyo)001:7170: bshad dang sgrub pas rig 'dzin grub pa'i khyus //
NK128(nyo)001:7171: phyogs dus kun tu khyab 'di ngo mtshar rmad //
NK128(nyo)001:7172: ces bya ba 'di bar skabs kyi tshigs su bcad pa'o //
NK128(nyo)001:7173: de yang brgyud tshul dngos la gsang bdag sgro phug
NK128(nyo)001:7174: pa chen pos mgar ston zung de la gsungs pa
NK128(nyo)001:7175: yin kyang / gtad rgya'i lo rgyus rgyas pa 'jam
NK128(nyo)001:7176: dbyangs rin chen rgyal mtshan gyi lugs bzhin bshad na
NK128(nyo)001:7177: yin kyang / / zur chung pa'i slob ma ka
NK128(nyo)001:7178: ba bzhi'i nang tshan skyo ston sh+aakya ye shes kyis
NK128(nyo)001:7179: skyo bye ma lung pa gsang mtshan rdo rje 'bar
NK128(nyo)001:7180: yin kyang / / ba rtsal la / des dam
NK128(nyo)001:7181: pa ya se ras pa gsang mtshan mi nub rgyal
NK128(nyo)001:7182: yin kyang / / ba rtsal la / mtshan rtsal la / de nyid kyi dbang don rgyas bsdus /
NK128(nyo)001:7184: 'dren pa'i las byang che chung la brten pa'i dbang rnams skyo la zhus /
NK128(nyo)001:7185: grub thob sdum bu ba rdo rje lhun grub rtsal
NK128(nyo)001:7186: lam mdo chog la brten pa'i rim gyis pa dang
NK128(nyo)001:7187: / za hor rgyal po pra ha sti'i lugs dang /
NK128(nyo)001:7188: mdo rigs pa'i nyi ma la brten pa'i cig car ba dang zab dbang zhus /
NK128(nyo)001:7189: nyang ri khrod pa'i slob ma mda' ston sdod phu
NK128(nyo)001:7190: ba gsang mtshan rgyal mtshan snying po rtsal la bcos
NK128(nyo)001:7191: ma la brten pa'i mdo dbang dang rna rgyud gser
NK128(nyo)001:7193: ya se chen po dpe dang po glan sh+aakya bzang po dang /
NK128(nyo)001:7194: bar du ma se rdo rje bde chen /
NK128(nyo)001:7195: tha ma dpal ldan gsum la dbang lung khrid gsum
NK128(nyo)001:7196: rdzogs par gnang mod kyang brgyud pa 'di'i lugs la
NK128(nyo)001:7197: 'di gtso bo mi mdzad par glan lugs gtso bo
NK128(nyo)001:7198: mdzad do // yang sgro phug pa chen pos slob
NK128(nyo)001:7199: ma nag po bzhi'i nang tshan zur nag 'khor lo
NK128(nyo)001:7200: gsang mtshan rab gsal 'khor lo rtsal la /
NK128(nyo)001:7201: des a mes shes rab blo gros gsang mtshan thig le dri med rtsal /
NK128(nyo)001:7202: des bla chen ral phu la gsang mtshan drag po rtsal /
NK128(nyo)001:7203: des mes ston mgon po gsang mtshan dbang phyug gzi brjid rtsal /
NK128(nyo)001:7204: des mkhas pa sro chen po /
NK128(nyo)001:7205: des grub thob lhun dpal gsang mtshan 'gyur med rtsal /
NK128(nyo)001:7206: des ban de dbang phyug rgyal mtshan gsang mtshan thugs mchog rtsal /
NK128(nyo)001:7207: des zur byams pa seng ge /
NK128(nyo)001:7208: des rgyal ba g.yung ston pa la brgyud pa dang /
NK128(nyo)001:7209: yang dbang phyug rgyal mtshan pas slob dpon rdo rje 'phel /
NK128(nyo)001:7210: des zur sh+aakya 'byung la brgyud de mdo lugs bla
NK128(nyo)001:7211: ma dga' rab pa las sgyu 'phrul te mdo sgyu
NK128(nyo)001:7212: gnyis ka'i zur sh+aakya 'byung la bzhugs so //
NK128(nyo)001:7213: yang na g.yung gis snye mdo ba la gsan zhes kyang grags /
NK128(nyo)001:7214: brgyud pa 'di lung 'dir mi 'dren yang gtad rgya
NK128(nyo)001:7215: gsang mtshan ma'i dbang chog g.yung gis mdzad pa sogs
NK128(nyo)001:7216: la dpags na 'dren rigs par snang ngo //
NK128(nyo)001:7217: yang lugs gcig tu mdo 'grel lung bstan ltar na
NK128(nyo)001:7218: rtsa ba kun byed la sogs pa'i rgyud phyi ma
NK128(nyo)001:7219: rnams pan chen sh+r+ai seng has bee ro tsa na
NK128(nyo)001:7220: / des spang mi pham sangs rgyas mgon po /
NK128(nyo)001:7222: des sa ze dar ma shes rab dang dbang zer mo dge slong ma bde gnas gnyis la gnang /
NK128(nyo)001:7223: de nas pho brgyud mo brgyud kyi rdzogs chen gnyis
NK128(nyo)001:7224: su gyes pa las mo brgyud ni dge slong ma
NK128(nyo)001:7225: la mar pa khrom rgyal gyis gsan /
NK128(nyo)001:7226: pho brgyud la ya zis nyang ston pra b+ha /
NK128(nyo)001:7228: des mar chung shes rab 'od la gnang ba'o //
NK128(nyo)001:7229: yang brgyud srol gcig la gnubs sras ye shes rgya
NK128(nyo)001:7230: mtshos khu lung pa sna nam tshul khrims byang chub
NK128(nyo)001:7231: la bka' stsal zhing dbang bskur /
NK128(nyo)001:7232: des mar chung shes rab 'od la gtam shul bya
NK128(nyo)001:7233: zo'i dgon par snyigs kyis g.yu dmar bya ba g.yu
NK128(nyo)001:7234: bzang po zhig dang khrab bzang po na bza' bzang
NK128(nyo)001:7235: po rnams phul / gsang mtshan rdo rje bde grub rtsal zhes btags so //
NK128(nyo)001:7236: des shangs 'chums kyi ban grong pa shangs nag mang za bsod nams dar la shangs su dbang bskur /
NK128(nyo)001:7238: yang bla ma zur chung pa la mar pa lho
NK128(nyo)001:7239: brag pas sems phyogs kyi dbang gdengs sgro ba nag
NK128(nyo)001:7240: po'i sgor zhu bar byon pas mar pa tshad nad
NK128(nyo)001:7242: shangs nag gis bso bral mdzad pas bsnyun gdangs te
NK128(nyo)001:7243: de'i drin lan du rdzogs chen brgyud pa tha ma'i
NK128(nyo)001:7245: mdo 'grel lung bstan dang phra mo mang du gnang /
NK128(nyo)001:7246: sgyu 'phrul rdo rje me long la sogs pa bshad rgyud sde bzhi'i man ngag rnams dang /
NK128(nyo)001:7247: zab mo'i dbang gi chos skor rnams gnang skad pas /
NK128(nyo)001:7248: de ltar na zur chung pa /
NK128(nyo)001:7250: shangs nag rnams brgyud dgos par sems /
NK128(nyo)001:7251: shangs nag gis bsang bdag sgro phug pa la gnang ste /
NK128(nyo)001:7252: nya ri rgya ston bya shangs nag dang sgro phug
NK128(nyo)001:7253: pa gnyis ka'i slob ma yin pa zhig gis mtshams
NK128(nyo)001:7254: sbyar te sgro phug tu shangs nag gdan drangs dbang
NK128(nyo)001:7256: g.yu zhig gi sna drangs te zhabs tog mang po bgyis /
NK128(nyo)001:7257: gsang mtshan bde byed gzhon nu rtsal zhes btags so //
NK128(nyo)001:7258: de rnams bar skabs kyi brgyud tshul mi 'dra ba'i tshul lo //
NK128(nyo)001:7260: lha rje sgro phug pa chen pos mgar ston zung de la gnang ba yin te /
NK128(nyo)001:7261: 'di'i rnam thar zhib pa ma rnyed kyang /
NK128(nyo)001:7263: mgar ston zung de mkha' la skor ba mdzad //
NK128(nyo)001:7264: brag la phur btab rdo rje drag po rtsal //
NK128(nyo)001:7266: snyan rgyud zab mo khungs kyi gtad rgyar /
NK128(nyo)001:7267: de yang ye shes kyi mkha' 'gro mas dngos su dbang bskur byin gyis brlabs shing /
NK128(nyo)001:7268: zag med bde ba'i nyams dang ldan pa lags par gda' zhes kyang 'byung zhing /
NK128(nyo)001:7269: mdo dbang dngos grub bskul tshig las /
NK128(nyo)001:7270: 'og gdong lha rje mgar zhes grags //
NK128(nyo)001:7271: ye shes mkha' 'gros byin brlabs pa //
NK128(nyo)001:7272: zag med bde ba'i nyams dang ldan //
NK128(nyo)001:7276: lha rje ni btsan po khri srong gi dus ni /
NK128(nyo)001:7277: mgo nag yongs kyi lha ni btsan po ste //
NK128(nyo)001:7278: des kyang thod du 'khur bas lha rjer thogs //
NK128(nyo)001:7280: yul gnyan pa'i phyir bla chen rnams la lha rje zer ba snga 'gyur du grags /
NK128(nyo)001:7281: mtshan dngos la ston pa zung de gsang mtshan rdo rje drag po rtsal zhes bya la /
NK128(nyo)001:7282: grub pa'i mtshan ma nam mkha' la skor ba mdzad pa dang /
NK128(nyo)001:7284: ye shes kyi mkha' 'gros mngon sum du dbang bskur zhing byin gyis brlabs pa zhig go //
NK128(nyo)001:7285: de yang brgyud srol gcig la bla ma zur chung pas glan sh+aakya bzang po la yang gnang zhing /
NK128(nyo)001:7286: glan de yang lha 'dre thams cad bran du 'khol
NK128(nyo)001:7287: zhing 'phrin las la thogs pa med pa zhig yin
NK128(nyo)001:7288: la / de ltar yin tshul yang dngos grub bskul tshig las /
NK128(nyo)001:7289: g.yas ru chu bar li thung du //
NK128(nyo)001:7290: glan ston sh+aakya bzang po ni //
NK128(nyo)001:7292: 'phrin las spyod la thogs pa med //
NK128(nyo)001:7294: des kyang mgar ston la gnang bas mgar ston gyis
NK128(nyo)001:7295: sgro phug pa dang glan gnyis ka la gsan par
NK128(nyo)001:7296: snang / mgar ston gyis sreg ston rdo rje rgyal mtshan la gnang zhing /
NK128(nyo)001:7297: de yang dgon gnas 'chums kyi 'chad dgon bya ba yin cing /
NK128(nyo)001:7298: sgo gsum gyis bla ma mnyes par mdzad cing gsang mtshan rdo rje 'jigs med rtsal du grags shing /
NK128(nyo)001:7299: dbang bzhi'i chu bo thams cad kyi bka' babs /
NK128(nyo)001:7300: yon tan chen po du ma dang ldan /
NK128(nyo)001:7301: dkyil 'khor gyi khyab bdag mdzad de phyag bzhes thams cad phul du phyin /
NK128(nyo)001:7302: mngon par shes pa'i yon tan ldan pa yin te /
NK128(nyo)001:7305: sregs ston rdo rje rgyal mtshan ni //
NK128(nyo)001:7306: yon tan bsam gyis mi khyab mnga' //
NK128(nyo)001:7307: dbang gi chu bo'i bka' rnams rdzogs //
NK128(nyo)001:7309: sregs ston gyi zur chung pa'i slob ma glan nya tshal ba sh+aakya byang chub la yang gsan te /
NK128(nyo)001:7310: nya tshal ba de yang man ngag rdzogs pa chen
NK128(nyo)001:7311: po la mnga' brnyes pas lta ba dang dgongs pa
NK128(nyo)001:7312: bsam gyis mi khyab pa phul du phyin /
NK128(nyo)001:7313: shes bya thogs med mkhyen gsang sngags kyi bdag po cher por bzhugs te /
NK128(nyo)001:7315: shangs kyi nya tshal khang stod du //
NK128(nyo)001:7316: lha rje sh+aakya byang chub ni //
NK128(nyo)001:7317: rdzogs chen lta ba'i phul du byung //
NK128(nyo)001:7318: shes bya thogs med ma lus mkhyen //
NK128(nyo)001:7320: de ltar na sregs ston gyis nya tshal ba dang mgar ston gnyis ka la gsan pa yin te /
NK128(nyo)001:7321: sregs ston rdo rje rgyal mtshan gyis nya tshal ba
NK128(nyo)001:7322: chen po glan ban rdo rje 'od la gnang ba
NK128(nyo)001:7323: yin te de yang shar ri rgya gar gling chung
NK128(nyo)001:7324: zhes bya ba'i dgon gnas 'dzin zhing /
NK128(nyo)001:7325: g.yu mo ches sna drangs yo byad sna tshogs kyis bla ma mnyes par mdzad /
NK128(nyo)001:7326: gsang mtshan rdo rje drag po rtsal du grags shing sku che ba'i yon tan /
NK128(nyo)001:7327: gsang ba'i bdag po phyag na rdo rje'i zhal gzigs /
NK128(nyo)001:7328: dus gsum mkhyen cing lung du ston /
NK128(nyo)001:7329: rigs pa'i gnas lnga la mkhas shing khyad par mdo
NK128(nyo)001:7330: phyogs la sbyangs pa che ba'i gshis gsang phu ne'u
NK128(nyo)001:7331: thog gi mkhan por zhu ba byung skabs su yang
NK128(nyo)001:7332: gsang sngags kyi 'gro don cher dgongs te khyim pa'i
NK128(nyo)001:7334: mkhas btsun mang pos zhabs la gtugs /
NK128(nyo)001:7335: mthar sham b+ha lar gshegs pa yin te /
NK128(nyo)001:7337: shar ri rgya gar gling chung du //
NK128(nyo)001:7338: mkhas pa glan ban rdo rje 'od //
NK128(nyo)001:7339: gsang bdag gzhal gzigs dus gsum mkhyen //
NK128(nyo)001:7340: sham b+ha lar gshegs gdul bya'ang 'dren //
NK128(nyo)001:7345: sdong po dkon mchog rin chen /
NK128(nyo)001:7346: lha rje lha 'bum rnams la gnang /
NK128(nyo)001:7347: khong rnams kyi yon tan gyis khyad par yang /
NK128(nyo)001:7349: dam chos 'byung gnas shar ri mor //
NK128(nyo)001:7350: glan ston brtson 'grus seng ge ni //
NK128(nyo)001:7351: gdul bya yang dag pa la 'god //
NK128(nyo)001:7353: gung thang dpal gyi dgon pa ru //
NK128(nyo)001:7354: mkhas pa bsod nams rgyal po yis //
NK128(nyo)001:7355: dbang gi 'gro ba du ma smin //
NK128(nyo)001:7356: sprul sku lha rje lha 'bum gyis //
NK128(nyo)001:7357: drag pos gdul bya mang po smin //
NK128(nyo)001:7359: glan brtson 'grus seng ge'i gsang mtshan drag po rtsal /
NK128(nyo)001:7360: glan bsod nams rgyal po'i gsang mtshan rdo rje bde byed rtsal /
NK128(nyo)001:7361: gzhan gnyis kyi gsang mtshan yang rdo rje drag po
NK128(nyo)001:7362: rtsal la sogs de rnams kyi glan dpal ldan chos
NK128(nyo)001:7363: kyi seng ge la gnang ste /
NK128(nyo)001:7364: bla ma de yang ting nge 'dzin gyis dgongs nyams
NK128(nyo)001:7365: bsam gyis mi khyab pa mnga' zhing gtso bor glan
NK128(nyo)001:7366: bsod nams rgyal po mnyes par mdzad de 'dus pa
NK128(nyo)001:7367: chen po'i dbang gsan cing gsang mtshan rdo rje drag
NK128(nyo)001:7369: gtad rgya ni sdong po dkon mchog rin chen dang
NK128(nyo)001:7370: glan bsod rgyal gnyis phar slob tshur slob yin pas
NK128(nyo)001:7371: / glan bsod rgyal gyi sdong po kun rin la
NK128(nyo)001:7372: gsan te dpal ldan chos kyi seng ge la gnang
NK128(nyo)001:7373: / zhing / de yang dngos grub bskul tshig las /
NK128(nyo)001:7374: glan ston chos kyi seng ge ni //
NK128(nyo)001:7375: ting 'dzin dgongs pa'i drod dang ldan //
NK128(nyo)001:7377: glan dpal ldan chos kyi seng ges glan ston sangs rgyas dpal la gnang ba yin te /
NK128(nyo)001:7378: bla ma de yang kho rang gi yab kyis sna drangs pa'i mkhas btsun thams cad la gtugs /
NK128(nyo)001:7379: mdo sngags kyi chos mtha' dag la mkhas shing bla ma glan ston chos seng rab sgrub pa /
NK128(nyo)001:7381: tha ma zang zing gi zhabs tog sogs kyis mnyes
NK128(nyo)001:7382: pas bsgrubs te 'dus pa chen po'i dbang dang gtad
NK128(nyo)001:7383: rgyar bcas pa gsan te gsang mtshan rdo rje bde
NK128(nyo)001:7385: gzhan yang mdo dbang zur lugs /
NK128(nyo)001:7388: zhang lugs thams cad gsan cing mkhyen /
NK128(nyo)001:7389: skye ba snga ma nas kyang rgyud sbyangs pas yi dam gyi lhas dngos su dbang bskur /
NK128(nyo)001:7391: phyogs bcu'i sangs rgyas rnams kyis lung bstan thob cing dgongs pa thugs su chud /
NK128(nyo)001:7392: 'phrin las ji ltar mdzad kyang bar gcod kyis mi
NK128(nyo)001:7393: tshugs shing mkhas btsun gyi yon tan dang ldan pa
NK128(nyo)001:7394: yin te / dngos grub bskul tshig las /
NK128(nyo)001:7395: rdza lung dpal gyi dgon pa ru //
NK128(nyo)001:7396: dbang bzhi rdzogs pa sangs rgyas dpal //
NK128(nyo)001:7398: zhes gsungs pa'i phyir yon tan bsam gyis mi khyab pa dang ldan pa yin no //
NK128(nyo)001:7399: des glan ston bsod nams mgon po la gsang ba yin la /
NK128(nyo)001:7400: bla ma 'di yang glan gyi rigs su 'khrungs te
NK128(nyo)001:7401: rgyud lung man ngag thams cad la mkhas par sbyangs
NK128(nyo)001:7402: / shes bya thams cad phyogs med du mkhyen /
NK128(nyo)001:7403: glan ston sangs rgyas dpal mnyes pa gsum gyis bskur te 'dus pa chen po'i dbang bskur gsan /
NK128(nyo)001:7404: gsang mtshan rdo rje drag po rtsal zhes grags //
NK128(nyo)001:7405: dbang gi chu bo thams cad rdzogs //
NK128(nyo)001:7406: u rgyan pad+ma'i lung bstan bzhin bsam yas pe kar
NK128(nyo)001:7407: gling nas zab chos kyi shog dril bco lnga thon
NK128(nyo)001:7408: / bla ma sman lung dbus pa la gnang /
NK128(nyo)001:7409: gtad rgya'i brgyud pa ni glan ban rdor 'od nas /
NK128(nyo)001:7411: de nas zhang ston kun dga' 'bum la brgyud de gsan /
NK128(nyo)001:7412: 'dus pa chen po'i dbang gi phyag len khrigs kyang mdzad pas bka' drin che zhing /
NK128(nyo)001:7413: gsang sngags rdo rje theg pa'i sgo nas smin grol
NK128(nyo)001:7414: gyis sems can gyi don mdzad pa zhig yin te
NK128(nyo)001:7416: gnas mchog gung thang yang dben du //
NK128(nyo)001:7417: glan ston bsod nams mgon po ni //
NK128(nyo)001:7418: bskyed rdzogs gsum gyi dbang bka' babs //
NK128(nyo)001:7419: dbang gi chu bos smin grol mdzad //
NK128(nyo)001:7421: glan ston bsod nams mgon pos /
NK128(nyo)001:7422: nyang ston dpal ldan rdo rje /
NK128(nyo)001:7423: sgrol chen 'bro ston bsam grub rdo rje /
NK128(nyo)001:7424: gyong khang gzi ston sh+aakya bzang po /
NK128(nyo)001:7425: shang mad'i bla ma grags she ba ste bzhi la gsungs pa yin te /
NK128(nyo)001:7426: dang po nyang ston dpal ldan rdo rje'i rgyud lung gi phyag bzhes mkhas shing /
NK128(nyo)001:7429: rnam 'joms dkar po rnams la grub pa thob pa yin /
NK128(nyo)001:7430: gnyis pa 'bro ston gyi rnam thar 'og tu 'chad la /
NK128(nyo)001:7431: gsum pa shangs gyong khang gi gzi ston sh+aakya bzang
NK128(nyo)001:7432: po ni glan bsod nams mgon po gser sogs yon
NK128(nyo)001:7433: gyis mnyes par mdzad cing dbang bskur zhus pa'i gsang
NK128(nyo)001:7434: mtshan rdo rje drag po rtsal du grags /
NK128(nyo)001:7436: yang dag gi bdag don gzhan don /
NK128(nyo)001:7437: phur sgrub la sogs pa'i lung dbang bka' sgrub thabs
NK128(nyo)001:7438: thams cad rdzogs par mkhyen te thugs kyi sras su
NK128(nyo)001:7439: gyur / thugs sras phyag bzhes 'dzin pa rnams kyi mchog tu gyur /
NK128(nyo)001:7440: yang dag la grub pa thob /
NK128(nyo)001:7441: mgon po stag zhon dang lha mos 'phrin las las ci dgos bsgrub pa yin no //
NK128(nyo)001:7442: bzhi pa shangs mad'i bla grags she ba ni mkhas
NK128(nyo)001:7443: grub mang po'i zhabs la thug cing gshin rje gshed
NK128(nyo)001:7444: kyi a kro nyin khri mtshan khri /
NK128(nyo)001:7445: brgya mchod stong mchod sogs la brtson par mdzad pa zhig yin no //
NK128(nyo)001:7446: glan ston bsod nams mgon po'i thugs sras gnyis pa
NK128(nyo)001:7447: sgrol ma ba 'bro ston bsam 'grub rdo rje ni
NK128(nyo)001:7448: 'dir brgyud pa'i gtso bo yin pas rnam thar mdo
NK128(nyo)001:7449: tsam brjod na / 'khrungs yul ni rta nag rigs 'brog gi rigs /
NK128(nyo)001:7450: yab 'bum 'phel dang yum dpal rgyan gyi sras su shing pho rta la 'khrungs te /
NK128(nyo)001:7451: lhums su zhugs pa dang bltams pa'i tshe ngo mtshar
NK128(nyo)001:7452: ba'i ltas bsam gyis mi khyab pa byung zhing mtshan
NK128(nyo)001:7453: yang chos grags seng ge bsam 'grub 'bum bya bar
NK128(nyo)001:7454: btags so // dgung lo bdun par yab las bris klog rnams legs par sbyangs shing mkhyen /
NK128(nyo)001:7455: brgyad pa la na raka dong sprug la gsung sgrog mang du mdzad pas thugs la zin /
NK128(nyo)001:7456: yab dang bla ma mdo sde 'bum gyis gyi gcung
NK128(nyo)001:7457: po grags pa la sgyu 'phrul tshe dbang chen mo
NK128(nyo)001:7459: dgung lo bcur bar zhi khro'i 'phrin las phyag bzhes dbyangs dang bcas pa mkhyen cing /
NK128(nyo)001:7460: de nas bzung za tshogs dang gtor mar chags myong gsungs /
NK128(nyo)001:7461: dgung lo bcu dgu pa la nyang ston rdo rje
NK128(nyo)001:7462: seng ge'i zhabs la gtugs te zhi khro bka' brgyad
NK128(nyo)001:7465: yang dag ma mo sgang shar rnams kyi bshad bka'
NK128(nyo)001:7466: phyag len dang bcas pa lo gnyis kyi bar du
NK128(nyo)001:7467: legs par sbyangs / bdud rtsi sman sgrub /
NK128(nyo)001:7468: yang dag me gcig sgyu 'phrul tshe sgrub la sogs pa'i sgrub dbang yang rdzogs par gsan /
NK128(nyo)001:7469: dgung lo nyer gcig pa la 'ug pa lung du
NK128(nyo)001:7470: byon te zur chos kyi rje byams pa seng ge'i
NK128(nyo)001:7471: zhabs kyi pad+mora gtugs nas rgyud lung man ngag gi
NK128(nyo)001:7472: chos rnams rdzogs par gsan cing /
NK128(nyo)001:7473: zur chos ni chos rje'i gcung bde byed dpal mgon la yang gsan /
NK128(nyo)001:7474: gzhan yang mda' sh+aakya 'phel sogs mkhas btsun mang po'i zhabs la gtugs /
NK128(nyo)001:7478: phar tshad bsdus pa la sogs rig gnas shes bya thams cad la thogs pa med par mkhyen /
NK128(nyo)001:7479: dgung lo nyer bzhi pa la sgro phug tu zur
NK128(nyo)001:7480: chen byams pa seng ge tshogs pa sum brgya tsam
NK128(nyo)001:7481: gyi dbus su grwa skor dang rnam bzhag bzang po
NK128(nyo)001:7482: mdzad / khyad par du shangs kyi nya tshal du
NK128(nyo)001:7483: bla ma glan chen po mkhas pa bsod nams mgon
NK128(nyo)001:7484: po'i zhabs la gtugs te dbang gos sngon po gan
NK128(nyo)001:7485: gos kyi bor rang gi bu chen sogs 'bul ba
NK128(nyo)001:7486: rgya chen mdzad de 'dus pa chen po'i dkyil 'khor
NK128(nyo)001:7487: du dbang man ngag gtad rgyar bcas pa gsan /
NK128(nyo)001:7488: gsang mtshan rdo rje bde byed chen rtsal du btags /
NK128(nyo)001:7489: bla ma nyid dkyil 'khor gyi gtso bor gzigs shing
NK128(nyo)001:7490: lha tshogs rnams nyid kyi thugs la thim par gzigs
NK128(nyo)001:7491: / mdo'i 'grel bshad rgyas par gsan nas mdo la shin tu mkhas par gyur /
NK128(nyo)001:7492: yang dag la sogs pa'i bka' lung gzhan yang rgya cher gsan te shin tu gus /
NK128(nyo)001:7493: jo nang gi byang sems rgyal ye la sbyor drug gsan nas sgom 'khor yug tu song /
NK128(nyo)001:7494: dgung lo so drug pa la jo gdan tshogs pa'i
NK128(nyo)001:7495: mkhan chen bsod nams grags pa'i drung du yongs rdzogs
NK128(nyo)001:7496: dge bsnyen gyi sdom pa bzhes te mtshan sh+aakya'i dge
NK128(nyo)001:7497: bsnyen rdo rje 'dzin pa bsam grub rdo rjer gsol
NK128(nyo)001:7498: / nyang stod lhan yul ri khrod du mkhas btsun
NK128(nyo)001:7499: bsod nams blo gros la rdzogs chen thig le chos
NK128(nyo)001:7500: skor yongs su rdzogs par gsan te nyams len mthar
NK128(nyo)001:7501: / phyin par mdzad / mus chen rgyal mtshan dpal la do ha'i skor gsan /
NK128(nyo)001:7502: mkhas btsun dkon cog bzang po la rdzogs chen a
NK128(nyo)001:7503: ro'i skor dang ye shes gsang rdzogs phyag chen sogs
NK128(nyo)001:7504: mang du gsan / sgrub pa'i rnam thar yang /
NK128(nyo)001:7505: gtsang gi bye ma seng ger lo bzhi sgrub pa
NK128(nyo)001:7506: mdzad pas yon tan bsam gyis mi khyab pa 'phel
NK128(nyo)001:7507: / rtsa rlung thig le dbang du 'dus pas bde
NK128(nyo)001:7508: stong dbyer med pa'i zab don khyad par can la
NK128(nyo)001:7509: / mnga' brnyes / yig brgya'i bzlas pa zla ba
NK128(nyo)001:7510: drug mdzad pas tho rangs kyi dus su sgrub khang
NK128(nyo)001:7511: thams cad 'od kyi dra bas khyab pa'i dbus na
NK128(nyo)001:7512: dam pa rigs brgya'i dkyil 'khor dong sprug ltar pad+ma
NK128(nyo)001:7513: brgya ldan la bkod pa'i zhal mngon sum du gzigs
NK128(nyo)001:7514: / mnga' brnyes / / de'i dus su thugs la 'di ltar dgongs te /
NK128(nyo)001:7515: don dam ma bcos gnas lugs kyi dbyings 'di la
NK128(nyo)001:7516: ma 'gags pa'i rtsal cir yang 'char ba 'dug dgongs
NK128(nyo)001:7517: pa shar / ri khrod ma lo ma gyon ma'i
NK128(nyo)001:7518: bzlas pa mdzad pas lha mo des kyang zhal bstan
NK128(nyo)001:7519: pa shar / / gzhan yang rnal 'byor gyi dbang
NK128(nyo)001:7520: phyug mi la ras pa dang grub thob lce sgom
NK128(nyo)001:7521: rin po che rnams mnal lam gyi tshul du mjal
NK128(nyo)001:7522: nas bzung sgom 'brel med du skyes pa'i rang mdangs
NK128(nyo)001:7523: pa shar / / snying rje shar / gzhan yang nub bde ba can du byon pa dang /
NK128(nyo)001:7524: sems can thams cad 'khor ba'i btson nas bton pa sogs nyams mang po 'khrungs /
NK128(nyo)001:7525: dgung lo bzhi bcu pa la rta nag tu chos
NK128(nyo)001:7526: dbyings bya ba'i dgon pa btab ste lo gnyis thugs
NK128(nyo)001:7527: dam la bzhugs pas sku tshe 'phos ma thag bde
NK128(nyo)001:7528: ba can du 'khrungs pa'i lung bstan thob /
NK128(nyo)001:7529: de dus gtsug tor 'khor los sgyur ba la thugs
NK128(nyo)001:7530: dam mdzad pas 'khor lo rtsibs bcu'i lte ba rang
NK128(nyo)001:7531: nyid gtsug tor 'khor los sgyur ba dang /
NK128(nyo)001:7532: steng 'og phyogs mtshams kyi khro bo rnams shin tu gsal ba dang /
NK128(nyo)001:7533: 'jam dbyangs smra seng gi zhal gzigs /
NK128(nyo)001:7534: de'i byin rlabs kyi gsung rab kyi tshig don dpyis phyin par rtogs /
NK128(nyo)001:7535: dgon pa chos dbyings kyi gong na pha bong gnyis
NK128(nyo)001:7536: bsgrigs glang po'i gdan 'dra ba zhig 'dug pa mtshan
NK128(nyo)001:7537: lam du pha bong de'i steng du 'od phung chen
NK128(nyo)001:7538: po zhig 'dug pas lung pa thams cad gsal bar
NK128(nyo)001:7539: byas pa lan gnyis gsum tsam byung ba dang mthun
NK128(nyo)001:7540: par khyod kyi sgrub khang brag ya gi'i steng du
NK128(nyo)001:7541: gyis zhes pa'i lung bstan ltar sgrub khang btab ste
NK128(nyo)001:7543: skabs shig las rgyar thabs lam mdzad pas bde stong
NK128(nyo)001:7544: zung 'jug la yun ring du gnas pa byung ba
NK128(nyo)001:7545: nas bzung bde stong gi nyams rgyud la khril le
NK128(nyo)001:7547: yang mkha' 'gro sde lnga dngos su rig mar 'gug nus pa'ang yod par grags /
NK128(nyo)001:7548: de la slob ma mang du 'dus pa'i rnam grangs
NK128(nyo)001:7549: kyang zur gyi bla ma ta'i si tu seng ge
NK128(nyo)001:7550: dpal ba dang / zur sh+aakya 'byung gnas khu dbon lcam sring /
NK128(nyo)001:7551: zur sh+aakya rgyal mtshan dang sh+aakya rdo rje dpal ldan
NK128(nyo)001:7552: sa skya ba'i gdung brgyud bdag po chen po ngag
NK128(nyo)001:7554: dbang rnam sras rgyal mtshan la sogs che btsun du ma dang /
NK128(nyo)001:7555: gzhan yang sngags mtshan nyid kyi bla ma dge bshes
NK128(nyo)001:7556: rtogs ldan mkhas grub du mas zhabs la gtugs shing
NK128(nyo)001:7558: ris med kyi 'gro ba du ma yang thar lam
NK128(nyo)001:7559: la bkod pa yin te bsdus don dngos grub bskul
NK128(nyo)001:7560: tshig las / dben gnas bye ma seng ge ru //
NK128(nyo)001:7561: chos bdag 'bro ston rdo rje ni //
NK128(nyo)001:7562: rgyud lung man ngag kun la mkhas //
NK128(nyo)001:7564: dgung lo nyer bzhi nas gshegs kyi bar tu gsang
NK128(nyo)001:7565: bshad kyang ma chags par gnang ba sogs bstan 'gro'i
NK128(nyo)001:7566: don la gcig tu gzhol pa'i mthar zhing 'di'i gdul
NK128(nyo)001:7567: bya rdzogs nas / rtag 'dzin can rnams chos la
NK128(nyo)001:7568: bskul phyir dgung lo gya gnyis pa shing yos kyi
NK128(nyo)001:7569: lor cung zad snyung ba'i tshul bstan nas /
NK128(nyo)001:7570: slob ma rnams la nub bde ba can du 'gro bas der gsol ba thob cig /
NK128(nyo)001:7571: chos rje byams pa seng ge yang byon byung bas
NK128(nyo)001:7572: mchod pa shoms la kun gyis gsol ba thob cig
NK128(nyo)001:7573: gsungs te / rta zla'i nye bdun gyi nyi dros
NK128(nyo)001:7574: la nam mkha' 'ja' 'od kyis gang ba sogs ngo
NK128(nyo)001:7575: mtshar gyi ltas dang bcas te zhi bar gshegs so
NK128(nyo)001:7576: gsungs te / // dgung zhag bdun nas 'ug pa
NK128(nyo)001:7577: lung nas zur ham rin po che sh+aakya 'byung gnas
NK128(nyo)001:7578: spyan drangs te pur bzhu bas 'ja' 'od dang me
NK128(nyo)001:7579: tog gi char sogs ngo mtshar ba'i ltas kyis khyab
NK128(nyo)001:7580: ste gdung ring bsrel grangs med par byon no //
NK128(nyo)001:7581: sgrol ma bsam grub rdo rjes zur ham thams cad
NK128(nyo)001:7582: mkhyen pa sh+aakya 'byung gnas la gsungs pa yin te
NK128(nyo)001:7583: / 'di'i rnam thar cung zad brjod na /
NK128(nyo)001:7584: yab zur bzang po dpal dang yum yon bdag mo
NK128(nyo)001:7585: a 'dzin gnyis kyi sras su 'khrungs te yab mes
NK128(nyo)001:7586: kyi chos rnams mkhas par sbyangs te dgung lo lnga
NK128(nyo)001:7587: la rtsa brgyud gsang ba snying por bshad pa mdzad
NK128(nyo)001:7588: / dgung lo bdun nas bshad grwa bskyangs /
NK128(nyo)001:7589: bla ma kun spangs pa la dge tshul dang /
NK128(nyo)001:7590: byang sems bsod nams grags par bsnyen par rdzogs pa'i mtshan sh+aakya 'byung gnas su gsol /
NK128(nyo)001:7591: dpal ldan bla ma dam pa zur sh+aakya seng ge /
NK128(nyo)001:7593: sgrol ma 'jam dbyangs bsam grub rdo rje /
NK128(nyo)001:7594: g.yung ston chen po mkhas btsun sangs rgyas sogs bla
NK128(nyo)001:7595: ma mang du brten nas gsang sngags snga 'gyur gtso
NK128(nyo)001:7596: bor gyur pa'i mdo sngags bstan bcos mtha' dag la
NK128(nyo)001:7597: thos bsam rgya cher mdzad nas zur thams cad mkhyen
NK128(nyo)001:7598: pa zhes kun la grags so //
NK128(nyo)001:7599: zur sh+aakya 'byung phyi ma grags pa ni snga ma
NK128(nyo)001:7600: zur chen sh+aakya 'byung dang mi 'dres pa'i ched du
NK128(nyo)001:7601: byas so // khyad par du yang 'dus pa mdo'i
NK128(nyo)001:7602: skor gsan tshul ni glan ston bsod nams mgon po'i
NK128(nyo)001:7603: slob ma bla ma nyang ston dpal ldan rdo rje
NK128(nyo)001:7605: bla ma bzang po ba la byang sems dang ma h+aa a nu sgos su gsan /
NK128(nyo)001:7606: spyir gtad rgya kho na yang lan gsum du gsan
NK128(nyo)001:7607: par bshad pas gtad rgya tshar gcig rgyal ba g.yung
NK128(nyo)001:7608: la yang gsan nam snyam zhing /
NK128(nyo)001:7609: rgyu mtshan g.yung gtad rgya la mkhas shing des mdzad pa'i dbang byang yang yod cing /
NK128(nyo)001:7610: zur ham 'di nyid kyi bla ma yang bzhugs la /
NK128(nyo)001:7611: gtad rgya'i dgos brgyud gcig ma g.yung ston bzhugs tshul gong du smos pas kyang shes par nus /
NK128(nyo)001:7612: sgrol ma ba bsam 'grub rdo rjes shangs gyeng khong
NK128(nyo)001:7613: pa gzi ston sh+aakya bzang po la mdo yongs rdzogs
NK128(nyo)001:7615: gyes khong pas mdo dbang rang ma mdzad pas grags la /
NK128(nyo)001:7616: phyag bzhes kyi brgyud tshul gcig la gyes khong pa nas sgrol chen yin la /
NK128(nyo)001:7617: sgrol chen bsam grub rdo rje zur ham 'dis mdo dbang gsan pa'i bla ma mchog tu nges pas /
NK128(nyo)001:7618: spyir mdo dbang kho na'i don du rgya bod kyi na bza' sman sna thab chas /
NK128(nyo)001:7619: nas khal lnga bcu sogs kyis sna drangs pa'i 'bul
NK128(nyo)001:7620: tshan dang bcas te 'dus pa chen po'i mdo'i dbang
NK128(nyo)001:7621: bskur man ngag rgyab brten gyi lung phyag bzhes sogs
NK128(nyo)001:7623: gtad rgya kho na'i yon du yang gos yug gser
NK128(nyo)001:7624: zho gsum ri ba dang gser zho gang sogs 'bul
NK128(nyo)001:7625: bar mdzad de gsan pa'i lo rgyus kyang snang zhing
NK128(nyo)001:7626: / khyad par mdo dbang tshar gnyis gsan par gsal te /
NK128(nyo)001:7627: dbang gi snyan brgyud zab mo khungs kyi gtad rgya zur ham nyid kyis mdzad pa las /
NK128(nyo)001:7628: de lta bu'i dpal ldan bla ma de nyid kyis
NK128(nyo)001:7629: bdag zur gyi sngags 'chang dge slong rdo rje 'dzin
NK128(nyo)001:7630: pa zur ham sh+aakya 'byung gnas rgyal mtshan dpal bzang
NK128(nyo)001:7631: po la bka' sde zur pa'i gdan sa chen po
NK128(nyo)001:7632: 'ug pa lung gi yang dben du lan gnyis thob
NK128(nyo)001:7633: pa lags / zhes gsungs pa'i phyir dang /
NK128(nyo)001:7634: gzhan yang gtad rgya'i lo rgyus nyid kyis mdzad pa las /
NK128(nyo)001:7635: bla ma bsam grub pa des bdag zur ham sh+aakya
NK128(nyo)001:7636: 'byung gnas dang sring gcig zur mo dge 'dun 'bum
NK128(nyo)001:7637: la gtad rgya dang bcas nas gnang ngo //
NK128(nyo)001:7639: zur ham rin po che lcam sring gsum byung ba'i bsgres pa zur ham nyid /
NK128(nyo)001:7641: lcam dpal ldan 'tsho mo'am zur mo dge 'dun 'bum ste gsum byung bas /
NK128(nyo)001:7642: lcam sring gnyis kyis gsan par gsal lo //
NK128(nyo)001:7643: de ltar 'jam dbyangs bsam grub rdo rje la mdo
NK128(nyo)001:7644: dbang gsan pa'i gsang mtshan rdo rje thod phreng rtsal
NK128(nyo)001:7645: du grags shing / bsdus don ni dngos grub bskul tshig tu //
NK128(nyo)001:7646: bdud rtsi'i chu rgyun yang dben du //
NK128(nyo)001:7648: kun mkhyen 'jig rten gsum gyi mgon //
NK128(nyo)001:7651: rgyud lung man ngag dbang bsgrub kun gyi bdag /
NK128(nyo)001:7652: rgyal tshab bstan 'dzin gdul bya skyong ba'i dpal //
NK128(nyo)001:7653: mang thos kun mkhyen rtogs pa mngon du gyur //
NK128(nyo)001:7654: sh+aakya 'byung gnas rdo rje thod phreng rtsal //
NK128(nyo)001:7656: phyis su mdo dbang zur lugs kyi bstan pa'i bdag po 'di kho na yin la /
NK128(nyo)001:7657: deng sang yang 'di kha'i phyag bzhes kyi rgyun yin
NK128(nyo)001:7658: pas zur ham 'di'i dngos slob gnyal pa bde legs
NK128(nyo)001:7659: pa'i chog khrigs nyid rtsa bar byed pa yin /
NK128(nyo)001:7660: lo rgyus 'di rnams kyi rang bsdus dbang chog gsar
NK128(nyo)001:7661: bsgrigs kyi gtad rgya'i skabs su zur ham nyid kyi
NK128(nyo)001:7662: gsung bzhin bris yod pas kyang rtogs par nus so
NK128(nyo)001:7663: // de ltar zur chen 'di nyid kyi sku che ba'i yon tan du ma mnga' gzhir bcas na'ang /
NK128(nyo)001:7664: bsdu na gzigs snang byung tshul phran bu zur ham nyid kyi gsung las 'di ltar 'byung ste /
NK128(nyo)001:7665: bdag smyon pa'i chol dang rmi nyams la /
NK128(nyo)001:7666: ston pa sh+aakya thub pa ba longs spyod na khri brtsig pa'i zhal ta mdzad kyin gda'/
NK128(nyo)001:7667: badz+ra he ru kahmadze thod bsnams pa 'jigs pa zhig snang /
NK128(nyo)001:7670: pad+ma he ru bkrag mdangs gsal /
NK128(nyo)001:7671: karma he ru sna tshogs par gda'/
NK128(nyo)001:7672: zhi dang rig 'dzin nam mkha' 'gro chos skyong ni
NK128(nyo)001:7673: mi dang mi min nam mkha'i lus can gang du'ang
NK128(nyo)001:7674: rdzu zhing 'phrul ston gyis gda' gsungs so //
NK128(nyo)001:7675: gzhan yang 'dus pa mdo'i lha thems gtad rgya'i 'grel
NK128(nyo)001:7676: pa sogs mang du mdzad de bstan pa'i gsal byed
NK128(nyo)001:7677: chen por gyur / de ltar thams cad mkhyen pa
NK128(nyo)001:7678: sh+aakya 'byung gnas des snga 'gyur bka' ma mdo sgyu
NK128(nyo)001:7679: sems gsum gtso bor gyur pa'i bshad bsgrub kyi bstan
NK128(nyo)001:7680: pa phyogs brgyar spel zhing 'phrin las bzhis gdul bya'i
NK128(nyo)001:7681: re ba bskangs te zhing 'di'i 'phrin las re zhig
NK128(nyo)001:7682: rdzogs nas zhing khams gzhan du 'gro ba'i don la
NK128(nyo)001:7683: dgongs te dgung lo so brgyad pa la sgra 'od
NK128(nyo)001:7684: zer gsum gyi cho 'phrul du ma dang bcas te
NK128(nyo)001:7685: rig 'dzin gyi zhing du gshegs so //
NK128(nyo)001:7686: zur ham thams cad mkhyen pa sh+aaka 'byung phyi ma
NK128(nyo)001:7687: 'dis lang gro sprul sku tshe dbang rgyal po la
NK128(nyo)001:7688: gsungs te / bla ma 'di'i rnam thar zhib par ma 'tshal yang /
NK128(nyo)001:7690: des gdan sa yang dben du sprul sku tshe dbang rgyal po la gnang zhes dang /
NK128(nyo)001:7692: ri sbug dpal gyi dgon pa ru //
NK128(nyo)001:7693: lang gro tshe dbang rgyal po ni //
NK128(nyo)001:7694: mthu stobs dbang phyug sprul pa'i gar //
NK128(nyo)001:7697: lha dang rtogs pa dbyer med 'gro ba'i mgon //
NK128(nyo)001:7698: gdul bya'i smin grol mkha' spyod gnas su gshegs //
NK128(nyo)001:7699: sprul sku tshe dbang rgyal te rdo rje thogs med rtsal //
NK128(nyo)001:7701: zur thams cad mkhyen par mdo dbang gtad rgya dang
NK128(nyo)001:7702: bcas pa gsan cing gsang mtshan rdo rje thogs med
NK128(nyo)001:7703: rtsal te grub pa'i mdzad pa du mas bstan 'gror
NK128(nyo)001:7704: dge legs rgya cher snang bar mdzad pa'i mthar rig
NK128(nyo)001:7706: sprul sku tshe dbang rgyal pos brgyud 'dzin legs par
NK128(nyo)001:7707: dpal bzang la gnang ba yin te rnam thar rgyas
NK128(nyo)001:7709: 'on kyang bsdus don dngos grub bskul tshig las /
NK128(nyo)001:7710: dben gnas chu bar nyi sbug tu //
NK128(nyo)001:7711: brgyud 'dzin legs pa dpal bzang ni //
NK128(nyo)001:7712: rig 'dzin gong ma'i gdung tshob rje //
NK128(nyo)001:7715: bshad bsgrub mthar phyin tshe yi rig 'dzin thob //
NK128(nyo)001:7716: chu bo bzhi rdzogs dbang chen dngos su byon //
NK128(nyo)001:7717: legs pa dpal bzang rdo rje dbang sdud rtsal //
NK128(nyo)001:7719: sprul sku tshe dbang rgyal po las /
NK128(nyo)001:7720: 'dus pa chen po'i dbang gtad rgyar bcas pa gsan cing /
NK128(nyo)001:7721: gsang mtshan rdo rje thogs med rtsal du grags /
NK128(nyo)001:7722: bshad sgrub gnyis ka mthar phyin du sku tshe ring por bzhugs par mngon cing /
NK128(nyo)001:7723: rta mgrin dang gshin rje gshed dmar po sogs pas
NK128(nyo)001:7724: grub pa brnyes pa zhig yin par gsal te mthar
NK128(nyo)001:7725: 'og min tshogs chen gyi dkyil 'khor du rig 'dzin
NK128(nyo)001:7726: gyi gral ring por gshegs so //
NK128(nyo)001:7727: bla ma dam pa chu bar nyi sbug pa lags pa dpal bzang des /
NK128(nyo)001:7728: lha rigs kyi mkhas grub chen po 'jam dbyangs rin
NK128(nyo)001:7729: chen rgyal mtshan dpal bzang por gnang ba yin te
NK128(nyo)001:7730: / bla ma 'di'i rnam thar cung zad bshad na /
NK128(nyo)001:7731: de yang gdung rigs ni mnga' ris pan+di ta chen po'i mgur las /
NK128(nyo)001:7732: skal ldan gyi btsun pa mtsho skyes bdag /
NK128(nyo)001:7733: rigs 'chang gi brgyud pa btsad po rgyal //
NK128(nyo)001:7734: mig dmar gyi sprul pa lha las babs //
NK128(nyo)001:7735: sdang mig gi spyan gsum ldan pa'i rgyud //
NK128(nyo)001:7736: ma sangs kyi dpon du brgyud bltams pa //
NK128(nyo)001:7737: grub thob kyi brgyud pa zam ma chad //
NK128(nyo)001:7738: dpa' mdzangs kyi mes po rigs ma 'chal //
NK128(nyo)001:7739: zhes dang gcung legs ldan zhabs kyi mgur las /
NK128(nyo)001:7740: rigs rgyus ni gung thang gi rje dang mnyam //
NK128(nyo)001:7743: rus gnya' khri btsan po'i brgyud /
NK128(nyo)001:7744: cho 'brang bod yul dkar por bkod pa'i rigs las byung ba /
NK128(nyo)001:7746: jo jo rgod lde gu ger byon //
NK128(nyo)001:7747: khung lung dngul mkhar gyi rgyal sa btab //
NK128(nyo)001:7748: bdud re ti 'gong yag sogs btul /
NK128(nyo)001:7749: khyung lung rdo rje spyan gcig mas gsang yum byas /
NK128(nyo)001:7750: slar glo bor byon g.yu ri sngon po'i rtser dgongs pa mdzad /
NK128(nyo)001:7751: sa dpyad gzigs nas glo bor ma thang stod du rgyal sa bzung /
NK128(nyo)001:7752: rgod lde la sras gsum byung ba'i bar pas bal po dbang du bsdus /
NK128(nyo)001:7753: spu rang du sku mkhar nyi bzung btab cing /
NK128(nyo)001:7754: de nas brgyud pa mang por riim bzhin 'phel tshul du ma yod kyang 'dir ma bris la /
NK128(nyo)001:7755: de ltar rgyal brgyud rnams kyis dkon cog gsum la
NK128(nyo)001:7756: zhabs tog che zhing bstan pa rin po che'i zhabs
NK128(nyo)001:7757: nas bteg tshul mtha' yas par mdzad pa yin pas
NK128(nyo)001:7758: zhib par rig 'dzin rje'i rnam thar sogs las shes
NK128(nyo)001:7759: so // 'dir 'jam dbyangs rin cen rgyal mtshan gyi 'khrungs yul ni mnga' ris glo bo /
NK128(nyo)001:7760: yab gung thang mnga' bdag gi sras chos rgyal nor bu /
NK128(nyo)001:7761: yum g.yur rtse ma ming khrid ces bya yin te /
NK128(nyo)001:7762: yum gyi lhums su 'jug pa'i tshe ngo mtshar gyis ltas mang du byung zhing /
NK128(nyo)001:7763: yum gyi rmi lam du nyi zla phreng ba mang
NK128(nyo)001:7764: po spyi bo nas thim pas lus bde chom chom
NK128(nyo)001:7765: sems khong khro med pa dang /
NK128(nyo)001:7766: rnal 'byor pa rus rgyan can rdor dril thogs pa
NK128(nyo)001:7767: gsum gyis bar snang nas spyi bor bum chus dbang
NK128(nyo)001:7768: bskur zhing rten 'brel snying po dang /
NK128(nyo)001:7770: h+r+aiha hohmh'u phatahcesa rdor dril spyi bor bzhag pas lto
NK128(nyo)001:7771: bar thim pa dang rnal 'byor pa sku mdog smug
NK128(nyo)001:7772: nag cig lus la thim pas snang ba bden med
NK128(nyo)001:7773: du song ba sogs byung zhing sa chen po yang
NK128(nyo)001:7775: de nas yum gyi zhang po grub thob tshul khrims dpal zhes pa'i mnal lam du /
NK128(nyo)001:7776: yum ming khrid kyi khang par dam pa rgya gar dang /
NK128(nyo)001:7779: bi ma la mi t+r+aa dang /
NK128(nyo)001:7781: ma cig lab sgron rnams yin zer ba'i rnal 'byor pa dang /
NK128(nyo)001:7784: pan+di ta mang po zhus song bas /
NK128(nyo)001:7785: de dag ci la byon pa yin /
NK128(nyo)001:7786: nga rang yang mjal du 'gro snyam nas phyin pas /
NK128(nyo)001:7787: khyim na gar pa mang pa rus rgyan 'debs grabs
NK128(nyo)001:7788: byed kyi 'dug nas yus kyis bsnang nas o rgyan
NK128(nyo)001:7790: ma cig lab sgron dang dam pa sangs rgyas sogs ga re dris pas /
NK128(nyo)001:7791: rus rgyan 'debs pa 'di tsho la khyad med yin zer phyag gang la 'tshal ma shes pas /
NK128(nyo)001:7792: thams cad yud tsam la mar me 'bar ba nyi
NK128(nyo)001:7793: shu tsam du song ba'i dbus na dam pa sangs
NK128(nyo)001:7794: rgyas yang yin / u rgyan pad+ma yang yin zer /
NK128(nyo)001:7795: phyag btsal mchi ma phyung bas /
NK128(nyo)001:7796: nga ni mar pa lo ts+aa zhes bya ba yin /
NK128(nyo)001:7798: glo bo ge gar gyi sgrub pa de ma chag
NK128(nyo)001:7799: pa mdzod ang gsungs rkang gling zhig gnang ste yum
NK128(nyo)001:7800: ming khrid la thim song bar rmis pas yum gyi
NK128(nyo)001:7801: drung du byon te rgyu mtshan de dag gsungs shing
NK128(nyo)001:7802: / nga rgad po lo brgya la thug kyang yid bde ba zhig byung ngo gsungs /
NK128(nyo)001:7803: dbyar de yul phyogs su nad med cing lo tog
NK128(nyo)001:7804: dang me tog sngar las rgyas pa che ba mang
NK128(nyo)001:7805: du skyes / ge gar gtsug lag gi srung ma la legs ldan pa'i yum la babs te /
NK128(nyo)001:7807: dkon mchog la mchod pa gyis /
NK128(nyo)001:7809: khang pa'i bar khang na rgya gar gyi grub thob
NK128(nyo)001:7810: he ru kahmanga po bzhugs yod tshogs 'khor mang po
NK128(nyo)001:7811: gyis / tshes bcu la grub thob tshul khrims dpal spyan drongs /
NK128(nyo)001:7814: bdud la mi dga' ba skye ba'i dus yong /
NK128(nyo)001:7816: tshes bcur grub thob spyan drangs /
NK128(nyo)001:7817: bla ma gsang 'dus kyi dbang yum 'khor bcas la gnang ngo //
NK128(nyo)001:7818: grub thob de yang dgung lo brgya dang dgur bzhugs gsar rnying gnyis ka'i grub thob yin nges pa /
NK128(nyo)001:7819: yi dam mang po'i zhal gzigs shing 'gro khar /
NK128(nyo)001:7820: phata phata nga ni rgya gar shing lo pa //
NK128(nyo)001:7821: mkha' spyod gnas nas zhing 'dir mchis //
NK128(nyo)001:7822: brgya dang dgu'i lor bzhugs nas //
