NK128(nyo)001:7823: bshad sgrub tshul bzhin nyan bshad byas //
NK128(nyo)001:7824: nga yi bla ma thams cad kyang //
NK128(nyo)001:7825: 'phags pa'i rnam sprul nyid yin no //
NK128(nyo)001:7826: nga'i slob mar gyur pa rnams //
NK128(nyo)001:7827: dag pa'i zhing du khrid pas na //
NK128(nyo)001:7828: dbu rtse dpal gyi dgon pa 'dir //
NK128(nyo)001:7829: tshul khrims srungs nas bshad sgrub spel //
NK128(nyo)001:7830: bdud bzhi chod cing rigs kyi bu //
NK128(nyo)001:7831: bya bral bsod nams seng ge 'di //
NK128(nyo)001:7832: o rgyan pad+mas byin brlabs pa'i //
NK128(nyo)001:7833: sprul sku phyir mi ldog pa yin //
NK128(nyo)001:7834: sku yi sprul pa du ma yis //
NK128(nyo)001:7836: zab mo bdud gcod rgyas par byed //
NK128(nyo)001:7837: nga ni o rgyan zhing du 'gro //
NK128(nyo)001:7838: gsungs te tshes bcur sgra dang rol mo 'ja' 'od /
NK128(nyo)001:7839: me tog gi char dang bcas te gshegs pa'i gdung la rdor sems /
NK128(nyo)001:7844: ring bsrel mang po dang bcas byon pa zhig yin no //
NK128(nyo)001:7845: de ltar dge mtshan du ma mngon du gyur nas /
NK128(nyo)001:7846: stag lo zla ba drug pa'i tshes bcur sku bltams pa'i tshe ngo mtshar gyi ltas bdun byung /
NK128(nyo)001:7847: de'i tshe grub thob tshul khrims dpal gyi slob ma
NK128(nyo)001:7848: slob dpon tshul khrims 'bar zhes bya ba glo bo
NK128(nyo)001:7849: ge gar gyi gtsug lag khang na yod pa'i mtshan
NK128(nyo)001:7850: lam du / dbu rtse'i dgon pa shar nas rol
NK128(nyo)001:7851: mo mang po'i sgra thos shing gtsug lag khang gi
NK128(nyo)001:7853: nyi ma 'od zer dang bcas te shar nas glo bo ma thang skya lam lam song /
NK128(nyo)001:7854: mi mang po mdung thogs nas nyi ma la rgyag
NK128(nyo)001:7855: gi 'dug pa snyogs ma song ba zhig rmis te
NK128(nyo)001:7856: / mnal sad nas bla ma gsang 'dus kyi thugs
NK128(nyo)001:7857: dam mdzad cing yod pas sgo brdung ba zhig byung
NK128(nyo)001:7858: / / su yin gzigs pas ston pa chos skyong blo gros 'ongs te /
NK128(nyo)001:7859: ming khri la bu zhig skyes 'dug /
NK128(nyo)001:7860: sngags mar zhig dang bsrung mdud khrus chu zhig gnang dgos zer /
NK128(nyo)001:7861: der thos pas sngar grub thob kyi mtshan lam dang /
NK128(nyo)001:7862: kho rang gi mnal lam dran te dgyes drags nas a pha'o /
NK128(nyo)001:7863: a la la bstan pa shar ro //
NK128(nyo)001:7865: gsungs shing gzims mal nas sku rags kyang ma bcings
NK128(nyo)001:7866: par thul pa lhug mor gsol te sgo dbye bar
NK128(nyo)001:7867: byon pas / skas la thul pa zhus te gcer
NK128(nyo)001:7868: bur byung nas sgo phye kha la mar bcug mgo
NK128(nyo)001:7870: de ltar bltams pa'i tshe sa g.yos lan bdun byung
NK128(nyo)001:7871: khang pa yang ma zhig /'brug che la drag pa
NK128(nyo)001:7872: lan bdun ldir / nam mkha' la 'ja' 'khrigs char chen po babs /
NK128(nyo)001:7873: gtsang nyang rdzong pa dang glo bo sman thang pa gnyis 'khrug gi yod pa'i /
NK128(nyo)001:7874: dar mdung slang ba mang po yang shar phyogs su phung phung byung bas /
NK128(nyo)001:7875: slob dpon tshul khrims 'bar gyis kho rang tsho 'khrug na'ang 'khrugs /
NK128(nyo)001:7876: da lan dar phyar ba legs po gsungs /
NK128(nyo)001:7879: rnam rgyal rdzong thos pas yab kyis bu dgra 'dul gnyen 'khyongs kha dro bas /
NK128(nyo)001:7880: rgyal mtshan 'bum du thogs gsungs la /
NK128(nyo)001:7881: mtshan dngos don grub dpal mgon du yang grags so //
NK128(nyo)001:7882: de yang yab dngos gung thang rgyal po'i sras chos
NK128(nyo)001:7883: rgyal nor bu yin pa gdung rigs gcig pa'i yab
NK128(nyo)001:7885: yum gyi bdag mnga' bdag btsan po lde'am /
NK128(nyo)001:7886: dgra dgu che bas btsan dug tu yang grags pa de yin pas /
NK128(nyo)001:7887: phyi 'phyar gyi yab 'dis mdzad de skyong thabs dang yab kyi dod kho na mdzad de /
NK128(nyo)001:7888: de'i lo glo bo ma thang du rab chad bdun la bu skyes /
NK128(nyo)001:7889: gcong nad can bdun gyi nad thon /
NK128(nyo)001:7890: ba bdun la be'u dkar po bdun skyes /
NK128(nyo)001:7891: rgod ma bdun la rta khra bdun skyes /
NK128(nyo)001:7893: lo rgyus legs par phyogs gzhan gyi mi rnams da
NK128(nyo)001:7894: lo skya rgyal bu mang ma thang na 'dug go
NK128(nyo)001:7895: zer ba grags / de ltar 'khrungs tsam nyid nas
NK128(nyo)001:7896: mngal gyi dri ma shas cher spangs pa'i stobs kyis
NK128(nyo)001:7897: 'khrungs 'phral du yul ngo mkhyen pa dang /
NK128(nyo)001:7898: ma yis re'u kham pa zhig gi pags pa 'jam pas blangs so gsungs /
NK128(nyo)001:7899: de nas bskyed pa bsrings te lo gcig tsam song
NK128(nyo)001:7900: ba dang sru mo grongs ba'i phung po bya la
NK128(nyo)001:7901: 'thor ba'i rgod mang po gzigs te /
NK128(nyo)001:7902: kho rang gi jo bo chen po rgyal ba zhes bya ba yang /
NK128(nyo)001:7906: 'u'i sru mo 'das pa'i phung po 'thor ba yin zhus pas /
NK128(nyo)001:7907: shi ba ci la zer gsungs /
NK128(nyo)001:7908: med par 'gro la yin zhus pas /
NK128(nyo)001:7909: bya de rnams gang na yod gsungs /
NK128(nyo)001:7910: yul cha med nas 'ongs pa yin zhus pas /
NK128(nyo)001:7911: khong gis ci la shes gsungs /
NK128(nyo)001:7912: khong la mngon par shes yod pa yin zhus pas /
NK128(nyo)001:7913: mngon shes ci la zer gsungs /
NK128(nyo)001:7916: ma bos pa la 'ong nus pa yin zhus pas /
NK128(nyo)001:7917: 'o na nga rang yang bya rnams dang 'dra bar ya gir 'phur 'gro gsungs /
NK128(nyo)001:7918: grub pa ma thob par 'gro mi nus zhus pas /
NK128(nyo)001:7920: chos zin nas thob zhus pas /
NK128(nyo)001:7923: khyod rang cher song nas shes yong /
NK128(nyo)001:7924: da lta mi shes zhus pas /
NK128(nyo)001:7926: 'o na phyag tshol zer jo jos phyag dang skor ba bslabs so //
NK128(nyo)001:7928: nga nam mkha' la 'gro chos byed /
NK128(nyo)001:7929: grub thob byed kho na gsungs /
NK128(nyo)001:7930: yum gyis thab tu lud pa skyur ba tshig pas /
NK128(nyo)001:7931: a ma gtor nas song zer bshums pas /
NK128(nyo)001:7932: a ma 'di la yod mod ci la bshums zhus pas /
NK128(nyo)001:7933: a ma me la thim med pas song gsungs /
NK128(nyo)001:7934: mchod gnas brtson 'grus bzang po bya bas gdon yin zer cha gsum btang tog gzungs bsgrags pas /
NK128(nyo)001:7935: tog gi stod na pha rol tu phyin pa drug mi rtog nye bar mi rtog /
NK128(nyo)001:7936: rnam par mi rtog bya ba bsgrags pas /
NK128(nyo)001:7937: thugs had de bzhugs nas sbyin pa ci la zer sogs shes rab kyi bar du dris pas /
NK128(nyo)001:7938: mchod gnas kyi sbyin pa ster ba la zer /
NK128(nyo)001:7939: tshul khriims khyim spangs pa la zer /
NK128(nyo)001:7940: bzod pa kha rog sdod pa la zer /
NK128(nyo)001:7941: brtson 'grus myur du bya ba la zer /
NK128(nyo)001:7942: bsan gtan yid la mi byed pa la zer /
NK128(nyo)001:7943: shes rab chos dang 'jig rten go ba yin /
NK128(nyo)001:7944: 'o na chos gang la zer 'jig rten ci la zer /
NK128(nyo)001:7945: mi rtog rnam par mi rtog pa gang yin sogs /
NK128(nyo)001:7946: zhib tu dris nas thugs la 'dzin cing zhal 'don mdzad /
NK128(nyo)001:7947: bsam gtan la rgyun ring por had de bzhugs shing
NK128(nyo)001:7948: rjes shes shin tu bkra la ngar rtsal che bas
NK128(nyo)001:7949: / mi rnams kyis rgod la grung ba 'dug zer ba byung /
NK128(nyo)001:7950: dgung lo lnga tsa nas bdag ni dam pa'i chos
NK128(nyo)001:7951: shig byas la sems can thams cad la phan par
NK128(nyo)001:7952: bya / grol bar bya bde bar bya /
NK128(nyo)001:7953: de'i phyir du mchod rten bzheng dgos gsungs te /
NK128(nyo)001:7954: thog mar byis pa mang po bsags nas pha ma las blangs pa'i zas 'di dag gsol zhig /
NK128(nyo)001:7955: ces gsungs shing sbyin pa phyogs med du gtong /
NK128(nyo)001:7956: tha na shing tog khyer ba re byung yang byis pa drag po rnams la lnga'am gsum /
NK128(nyo)001:7957: chung ba rnams la re gnyis gnyis sbyin pa mdzad /
NK128(nyo)001:7958: de nas byis pa rnams la da ni khyed rnams
NK128(nyo)001:7959: kyis rdo 'jim gyi bya ba 'di bzhin byed par
NK128(nyo)001:7960: zhu / nga mchod rten khyad par can zhig bzheng yin de'i drung du mchod pa byed pa dang /
NK128(nyo)001:7961: chos bshad par bya ba'i chos kyi khri yang byed par zhu /
NK128(nyo)001:7962: zhes gsungs te las la bkol ba sogs rgyun par mdzad /
NK128(nyo)001:7963: nyin gcig nga ri la bsgom gsungs te dbu ri phug mo che zer ba'i phug par byon te /
NK128(nyo)001:7964: mdun na tho chung mang du brtsigs nas lus drang por bsrangs te bsam gtan la bzhugs pas /
NK128(nyo)001:7965: de'i tshe yul de'i drag zhan mang po 'tshogs nas
NK128(nyo)001:7966: skyid zhag gi sha chang ltad mo chen po byed
NK128(nyo)001:7968: yab zhal bkod kyis g.yengs te phyi mor song yang ma dran /
NK128(nyo)001:7969: de nas sras med par mkhyen nas steng 'og phyogs mtshams thams cad du btsal bas kyang ma rnyed /
NK128(nyo)001:7970: chu skor la sogs par dri zhing rgyang ring por pho nya bkye bas /
NK128(nyo)001:7971: lcam sring ma che shos thub pa lcam zhes bya
NK128(nyo)001:7972: ba'i dkon mchog la smre sngags 'don zhing gsol ba
NK128(nyo)001:7973: btab / phyogs kun tu 'bru dkar mo 'thor zhing skyo glu dang bcas te btsal bas /
NK128(nyo)001:7974: glu'i dbyangs kyis bsam gtan sar de khyed rnams gang 'gro gsungs /
NK128(nyo)001:7975: de nas thams cad dga' zhing 'dus te khyim du spyan drangs so //
NK128(nyo)001:7976: yab kyis mang du bkyon cing mi chos kyi bya
NK128(nyo)001:7977: ba bsgrub dgos tshul mang du gsungs pas spyan chab
NK128(nyo)001:7978: 'don zhing chos bya bar zhus so //
NK128(nyo)001:7979: de nas dgung lo bcu gcig la phebs pa'i tshe
NK128(nyo)001:7980: chos rje bsod nams seng ge zhes bya bar nam
NK128(nyo)001:7981: mkha' sgo 'byed kyi byin brlabs zhus /
NK128(nyo)001:7982: slob dpon tshul khrims dpal la gu ru'i gtor dbang /
NK128(nyo)001:7984: rnam 'joms snur lugs kyi rjes gnang sogs gsan de'i
NK128(nyo)001:7985: tshe yul gyi phyugs rnams bsdus te so nam byed
NK128(nyo)001:7987: ri la phyugs skyong ba dang sbrags mdo sdud pa /
NK128(nyo)001:7989: bzang spyod la sogs mdo phran 'ga' zhig dang /
NK128(nyo)001:7990: bla ma'i bstod tshogs mang po thugs la bzung ste zhal 'don mdzad /
NK128(nyo)001:7991: sku zhang slob dpon 'bar ba'i zhabs 'bring mdzad de /
NK128(nyo)001:7992: rnam rgyal 'dzoms la sogs pa thugs gnyer dang /
NK128(nyo)001:7993: n+aa ga rak+sha'i dbang dang gdams pa yang gsan no //
NK128(nyo)001:7994: de nas dgung lo bcu gsum la babs pa'i tshe
NK128(nyo)001:7995: yab kyis grong pa'i bu mo mtshan ldan bdun la
NK128(nyo)001:7996: 'dam kha dang bcas te jo mo bsu ba'i gra
NK128(nyo)001:7997: sgrigs mdzad / nyid ni sngar bzhin ri la phyugs skyong bzhin bzhugs so //
NK128(nyo)001:7998: de'i tshe dbus phyogs nas shes rab pa bya ba
NK128(nyo)001:7999: rtogs pa dang ldan pa sgra tshad kyi slob gnyer
NK128(nyo)001:8000: byang ba zhig gi rmi lam du /
NK128(nyo)001:8001: khyod rang nyi ma nub tu song dang rje mar
NK128(nyo)001:8002: pa dang mjal te byin gyis rlabs par 'gyur ro
NK128(nyo)001:8003: // zhes pa byung ste phyogs su byon pas grub
NK128(nyo)001:8004: chen thang stong rgyal po dang mjal te des kyang
NK128(nyo)001:8005: khyod rang nyi ma nub la song /
NK128(nyo)001:8006: mar pa lo ts+aa ba'i rnam sprul dang phrad do
NK128(nyo)001:8007: gsungs pa rmi lam dang mthun te yar byon skyid
NK128(nyo)001:8008: grong sogs kyi gnas skor byas /
NK128(nyo)001:8009: jo bo'i drung du bdag mar pa dang mjal bar
NK128(nyo)001:8010: mdzad du gsol zhes dmod bor te nyal bas rmi
NK128(nyo)001:8011: lam du thang chen po zhig gi shar ri la
NK128(nyo)001:8012: byis pa rnam dpyod can mig rtsa khra shig go
NK128(nyo)001:8013: zhig na re / nga ni dam pa rgya gar te //
NK128(nyo)001:8014: dam chos sdug bsngal zhi byed shes //
NK128(nyo)001:8015: rang sems stong par rtogs tsam na //
NK128(nyo)001:8016: sdug bsngal zug rngu zhi bar 'gyur //
NK128(nyo)001:8018: yang nga ni rgya gar h+aum ka ra //
NK128(nyo)001:8019: ru lu 'bru brgyad don shes na //
NK128(nyo)001:8020: tshogs brgyad ye shes sku mchog yin //
NK128(nyo)001:8022: yang nga ni dom b+hi he ru ka /
NK128(nyo)001:8023: rigs ngan bu mo bstan shes na //
NK128(nyo)001:8024: dug kyang sman du 'gyur ba yin //
NK128(nyo)001:8026: yang nga ni bee ro tsa na ste //
NK128(nyo)001:8027: snang srid byang chub sems rtogs na //
NK128(nyo)001:8028: rnam snang go 'phang brnyes pa ste //
NK128(nyo)001:8029: chos bdun gyi ni bden pa thob //
NK128(nyo)001:8030: ci yang yid la ma byed cig /
NK128(nyo)001:8034: snang srid thams cad bde chen zhing //
NK128(nyo)001:8035: gzugs snang thams cad rang byung lha //
NK128(nyo)001:8036: lha dang gnyis su ma byed cig /
NK128(nyo)001:8037: zer ba rmis shing 'od gsal du cham cham song bas spro seng nge ba la /
NK128(nyo)001:8038: mnga' ris gung thang nas glo bo'i bar du zhag gsum la sleb ste /
NK128(nyo)001:8039: glo bo smad kyi bar tshigs lam gsum yod pa'i thang bar ma la byon pas /
NK128(nyo)001:8040: snga dro nyi ma shar lhor sa la babs pa dang sras chung 'di dang mjal tshul ni /
NK128(nyo)001:8041: phug rgyab pha bong dmar po'i steng na sngar skyid
NK128(nyo)001:8042: grong du mnal lam la byung ba'i byis pa de
NK128(nyo)001:8043: / mang bo'i dbus na 'ur rdo bzo yin 'dug pas /
NK128(nyo)001:8044: khong thugs nyams 'ur te byis pa'i drung du byon nas khyod su yin dris pas /
NK128(nyo)001:8046: ming med pa zhig yin zer /
NK128(nyo)001:8047: de gang gi lugs yin dris pas /
NK128(nyo)001:8048: ming stong pa med pa zhig la yod yod por btags pa tsam yin mod gsungs /
NK128(nyo)001:8050: nga rang gi bsam pas tsa na 'dug pa zer /
NK128(nyo)001:8051: bsam mkhan su yin dris pas smra mi shes pa 'dug zer /
NK128(nyo)001:8052: ci'i phyir smra mi shes dris pas /
NK128(nyo)001:8053: rtsa ba rang zad dwang sang nge ba la smra
NK128(nyo)001:8054: ru yod dam de ltar byed pa zhig 'dug mod
NK128(nyo)001:8055: zer / 'o na khyod kyi pha su yin dris pas /
NK128(nyo)001:8058: rmi lam de gsal po zhig yod kyang gnyid sad dus mi 'dug pa /
NK128(nyo)001:8059: de ltar de'i pha yang yod pa lta bu la rtsa ba rang rdol /
NK128(nyo)001:8060: phugs su yod ba med pa zhig 'dug go zer /
NK128(nyo)001:8061: 'o na ma yod dam byas pas /
NK128(nyo)001:8062: ma yang pha dang 'dra la khad cig 'dug go zer /
NK128(nyo)001:8063: spun phu nu yod dam dris pas /
NK128(nyo)001:8065: yod pa lta bu zhig la phug pha ma nye tshan gcig kyang med zer /
NK128(nyo)001:8066: 'o na yul 'di la ci zer dris pas /
NK128(nyo)001:8067: yul yod pa rdo chu shing can zer gsungs /
NK128(nyo)001:8072: nged rang gi pha khang la dbu zer /
NK128(nyo)001:8074: ma la ming khrid zer sogs rgya cher gsungs /
NK128(nyo)001:8075: 'o na yul yod na sus byas sus bzos sus btags dris pas /
NK128(nyo)001:8076: ci yang med pa'i gsal seng nge ba zhig yong gi 'dug /
NK128(nyo)001:8078: nga dbus gtsang nas yin ri khrod la 'gro byas pas /
NK128(nyo)001:8079: der phyin nas ci byed zer /
NK128(nyo)001:8080: thugs dam byed pa yin mod byas pas /
NK128(nyo)001:8081: khyod rang gi yul na byed pa med dam zer /
NK128(nyo)001:8083: gnam 'di yang khyed la yod dam zer /
NK128(nyo)001:8088: bya rgyu med pa zhig 'dug pas ci yang ma
NK128(nyo)001:8089: byed par bsam pa lhan ne byas na lus la
NK128(nyo)001:8092: khyed rang yang de kha kho na gyis zer /
NK128(nyo)001:8093: de khyod la sus bstan byas pas /
NK128(nyo)001:8094: ngas nga rang gi sems la bltas te chos gang nas 'ongs /
NK128(nyo)001:8096: chung ma gang nas 'ongs bltas pas sems cham me nyal le zhig yin gda' ste /
NK128(nyo)001:8097: nga'i pha zhig yod pas bag ma bsu zer 'dug /
NK128(nyo)001:8098: nga ni bsu don ci yang med zer /
NK128(nyo)001:8099: de nas rnal 'byor pa des 'o na khyed rang
NK128(nyo)001:8100: nga'i zla la phyin nas khyod rang sems la shar
NK128(nyo)001:8101: ba de dag bsgoms na bla ma bzang po yod
NK128(nyo)001:8102: zer / bla mas ci byed zer /
NK128(nyo)001:8103: sems can la phan byas pas /
NK128(nyo)001:8104: 'o na khyod rang nga'i khyim du song zhig /
NK128(nyo)001:8105: ngas phyugs la nad med par byas te dgong mo sleb yong ngo gsungs /
NK128(nyo)001:8106: de ltar la ba las brtsams pa'i dam pa'i chos dris lan mang du mdzad de /
NK128(nyo)001:8107: khang pa 'di 'dra na pha ma 'di dag yod pas dris la song zhig /
NK128(nyo)001:8108: bza' ba ster zhing skyid pa yong ngo zhes gsungs /
NK128(nyo)001:8109: rnal 'byor pa'i gzims khang du phyin pas /
NK128(nyo)001:8111: gong gi lo rgyus rnams byas pas /
NK128(nyo)001:8113: kho nga'i brgyud pa 'di mi 'dzin pa'i rtags yin
NK128(nyo)001:8114: pas chos la kha mi 'khrigs par 'dir sdod pa'i
NK128(nyo)001:8117: da dbus nas mar pa lo ts+aa'i sprul pa zhig yod zer rmi lam gsal por byung /
NK128(nyo)001:8118: byis pa'i kha nas gtam de rnams thos pas nga
NK128(nyo)001:8119: la ni gtad med kyi nyams dang bde stong gi
NK128(nyo)001:8120: rtogs pa sngar med skyes pa zhig byung /
NK128(nyo)001:8121: nga'i kha la khong mi nyan nam /
NK128(nyo)001:8122: rje btsun mar pa'i sprul pa zhig rang yin nam zer /
NK128(nyo)001:8123: rnal 'byor pa'i sprul pa zhig rang yin nam zer /
NK128(nyo)001:8124: rnal 'byor pa'i rogs gsum po na re /
NK128(nyo)001:8125: nga ni dge sbyor gyi kho thag chod pa'i nges shes rang skyes /
NK128(nyo)001:8126: byis pa de 'dra bas don de lta bu rgyud
NK128(nyo)001:8127: la shar 'dug /'u cag gi chos byas sgom blo
NK128(nyo)001:8128: byas kyang blo thag chod pa med pa'i steng du
NK128(nyo)001:8129: blo sna 'dzings su song ba zhig yang 'dug pa
NK128(nyo)001:8130: de ltar ngo mtshar che zer ro //
NK128(nyo)001:8131: de nas sras dang byis pa rnams kyis kyang phyugs
NK128(nyo)001:8132: bskyangs nas dgong mo gzims khang du byon pa'i tshe
NK128(nyo)001:8133: / sngar bzhin rnal 'byor pa rnams dang gtam gleng bar mdzad pa'i tshe /
NK128(nyo)001:8134: bla ma 'jam dbyangs blo gros dang yab yum sogs
NK128(nyo)001:8135: mang bos 'dus pa'i dbus su rnal 'byor bas smras
NK128(nyo)001:8136: pa / sras 'di sangs rgyas kyi sprul pa gda'
NK128(nyo)001:8137: bas nged dbus gtsang gi phyogs su gnang bar zhu
NK128(nyo)001:8138: pa / / spyir sangs rgyas kyi bstan pa /
NK128(nyo)001:8139: sgos sgrub brgyud la phan pa cher yod nges su 'dug /
NK128(nyo)001:8140: lho brag mar pa'i gdan sa gro bo lung du
NK128(nyo)001:8141: phebs na rigs sad pa'i rtags kyang mang po yong
NK128(nyo)001:8143: sras ci yang mi gsungs par khong rnams ci zer gsan cing 'dug /
NK128(nyo)001:8144: yab kyi zhal nas rgyu mtshan mang du gsungs pa'i mthar 'di nga'i brgyud 'dzin re ba yin /
NK128(nyo)001:8145: zhing khar nor rdzas kyi rtsis byas na bu bcu gsum tsam yang 'khyongs ba tsam yod /
NK128(nyo)001:8146: nged lugs gnyis ka'i sde 'dzin dgos /
NK128(nyo)001:8147: khyed dbus gtsang ba yang sdig sems che ba sogs kyis btong mi phod /
NK128(nyo)001:8148: rnal 'byor pa tsho yang phyogs kyi sgrub gnas tshor bzhugs na mthun rkyen sbyor /
NK128(nyo)001:8149: nged kyi bu 'di yang sems spro ba 'dug gsungs /
NK128(nyo)001:8150: bla ma slob dpon nye drung gzhan rnams kyang de bzhin du gsungs so //
NK128(nyo)001:8151: der sras chung gis tshigs su bcad de gsungs pa /
NK128(nyo)001:8152: kha cig 'chi ba ma dran pas //
NK128(nyo)001:8154: kha cig sde srid 'dzin pa zhu //
NK128(nyo)001:8155: nga ni bla ma ral gcig pa'i //
NK128(nyo)001:8156: drung du skra gcod chos la 'gro //
NK128(nyo)001:8158: de nas zhag shas rnal 'byor pa rnams kyang sdad /
NK128(nyo)001:8159: de dang rjes su mthun par bzhugs rjes yul de'i
NK128(nyo)001:8160: nub phyogs dol pa'i shel gyi ri bo 'brug sgra
NK128(nyo)001:8161: zhes bde mchog gi gnas su rnal 'byor pa rnams
NK128(nyo)001:8162: song ba'i rjes su bros nas byon kyang /
NK128(nyo)001:8163: yab yum rnams kyis gsan te bkug pa'i tshe sras
NK128(nyo)001:8164: kyi kho rang gi chas rnams rnal 'byor pa rnams
NK128(nyo)001:8165: la gtad de 'di skad gsungs so //
NK128(nyo)001:8167: rnal 'byor grub pa rnams kyis dgongs mdzod dang //
NK128(nyo)001:8168: mi rtag pa la rtag par 'dzin lugs sam //
NK128(nyo)001:8169: mi bden pa la bden par 'dzin lugs la //
NK128(nyo)001:8170: da lta nga ni bongs chung shed kyang med //
NK128(nyo)001:8171: dbang med yul gyi lha 'dres 'dzin pa 'dug /
NK128(nyo)001:8172: de nas cher skyes khyod rang phrad pa'i phyir //
NK128(nyo)001:8173: thabs kyis bros nas sgrub la brtson par bya //
NK128(nyo)001:8174: da ni khyed cag lam gyi gegs su song //
NK128(nyo)001:8175: bza' btung 'di dag khyed kyi cha rkyen mdzod //
NK128(nyo)001:8176: ces gsungs nas log byon pa'i lam khang mar du bshums shing dbyar ngos ni de gar bzhugs /
NK128(nyo)001:8177: ston dus cha rkyen zhwa lham zhig nyos te grogs
NK128(nyo)001:8178: dge bshes 'jam dbyangs bzang po sogs gsum bsdebs te
NK128(nyo)001:8179: nang nub tu chos spyod 'dra bslabs /
NK128(nyo)001:8180: nyin mo yab yum gyis ma tshor bar chos kyi
NK128(nyo)001:8181: cha rkyen du me tog mdzad de nas du ma
NK128(nyo)001:8182: zhig rnyed pa la phyed kyis sha khog gcig dang
NK128(nyo)001:8184: grogs gsum gyi nas la chos gos sogs nyos /
NK128(nyo)001:8185: tshes bcu zhig la bla mchod brtson 'grus bzang po'i khang par ston gshoms kyi grabs mdzad /
NK128(nyo)001:8186: sras rang gi dbu rtse nas bla ma slob dpon che bsgros nyer lnga spyan drangs pa la /
NK128(nyo)001:8187: yab kyis ci yin dris pas /
NK128(nyo)001:8188: nga tshes bcu rgya chen po zhig kyang byed /
NK128(nyo)001:8189: smon lam rgya chen po zhig 'debs /
NK128(nyo)001:8190: nged rang gi longs spyod gang yod spong thag tu gtong /
NK128(nyo)001:8191: de nas nga chos byed pa lags so gsungs pas /
NK128(nyo)001:8192: yab brgyal bar gyur pa las mkhan slob rnams kyis slong ste thugs gso ba mdzad par /
NK128(nyo)001:8193: yab kyi zhal nas gdung rus che btsun yin lugs dang bcas mang du gsungs pa'i mthar /
NK128(nyo)001:8194: bu tsha 'di brgyud pa zin lhag gcig yong ngo la /
NK128(nyo)001:8195: bsam pa log pa 'di lta bu dang sdugs so //
NK128(nyo)001:8196: zhes yang yang bshums pas cho ga yang byed ma thub par /
NK128(nyo)001:8197: slob dpon 'bar bya ba na re /
NK128(nyo)001:8198: de ring dus bzang yin pas cho ga yang gtong ba 'thad /
NK128(nyo)001:8201: slar pho lo bco brgyad tsam nas skra bsags pas chog mod /
NK128(nyo)001:8202: gtam dper re zhig byis pa smyo ru chug zer
NK128(nyo)001:8203: ba yin pas ci dga' byed chug gsungs te gros
NK128(nyo)001:8204: bton pas yab kyang thugs gsos /
NK128(nyo)001:8206: dbu skra 'breg par brtsams pas spu gri lnga kha sdugs pas /
NK128(nyo)001:8208: nga'i pho lha ma mnyes pa yin 'os ci yod gsungs /
NK128(nyo)001:8209: der dbu skra cung zad gcig bcad de des rten 'brel 'grig gsungs mtshan sh+aakya 'bum du btags so //
NK128(nyo)001:8210: skyabs gsum 'dzin pa'i sdom pa bla ma 'jam dbyangs blo gros kyis gnang ngo //
NK128(nyo)001:8211: sras dbu skra ril po ma bcad pas de nub
NK128(nyo)001:8212: thugs ma bde bar dbu rtse nas rje btsun chos
NK128(nyo)001:8213: skyong tshul khrims zhes bya ba bzhugs pa'i drung du
NK128(nyo)001:8214: lug sha lag pa gcig dang ras khru bco lnga
NK128(nyo)001:8215: pa zhig phul te sngar gyi lo rgyus rnams zhus
NK128(nyo)001:8216: pas / bla ma des kyang chos byar mi nyan yul dpon chen po yin /
NK128(nyo)001:8217: nga'i tsha mo 'di yang khyod la ster bsam pa yin gsungs pas /
NK128(nyo)001:8219: bla ma dang pha ma yang mi dgyes /
NK128(nyo)001:8220: chos bya bar skra yang mi chod pa 'di sngon las ngan pa ci zhig yod zhus pas /
NK128(nyo)001:8223: khyod sprul pa'i gang zag yin /
NK128(nyo)001:8224: bla ma 'jam dbyangs blo gros pa bzang po yin kyang /
NK128(nyo)001:8225: khyod kyi skra gcod pa la lta dgongs can zhig dgos /
NK128(nyo)001:8226: mdang nga'i rmi lam na thub pa'i gser sku zhig
NK128(nyo)001:8227: gi gtsug tor la spre'u zhig gis spu gris gzhar
NK128(nyo)001:8228: gyi 'dug pas gri kha chag nas mthar glang dmar
NK128(nyo)001:8229: po zhig gis ldags pa rmis /
NK128(nyo)001:8230: ci 'dra yin nam ming ci btags gsungs /
NK128(nyo)001:8231: dge bsnyen sh+aakya 'bum zer lags zhus pas /
NK128(nyo)001:8232: de ni khyed rang gi bla mchod kyi phu bo shi ma thag gi ming yin /
NK128(nyo)001:8234: de ltar na sdom rgyun gzhi thams cad yod par
NK128(nyo)001:8235: smra ba'i lugs dge tshul gyi bar du nga la
NK128(nyo)001:8236: yod khong la kho rang gi pha las thob pa'i
NK128(nyo)001:8237: skyabs gsum 'dzin tsam zhig las med /
NK128(nyo)001:8238: bsrung bya yang ji ltar mdzad kyi yod mi shes /
NK128(nyo)001:8239: 'on kyang bla ma khong yang thugs klong chen po byin rlabs can zhig yin /
NK128(nyo)001:8240: da ste nga la yongs rdzogs dge bsnyen gyi sdom
NK128(nyo)001:8241: pa long gsungs te yongs rdzogs dge bsnyen gnang nas
NK128(nyo)001:8242: mtshan 'jam dbyangs rin cen rgyal mtshan du gsol lo
NK128(nyo)001:8243: // de ltar sras dgung lo bcu gsum gyis ston
NK128(nyo)001:8244: mjug la chos sgor zhugs pas mchog tu dgyes te
NK128(nyo)001:8245: // / rnal rgyal chos sder rab 'byams pa gangs
NK128(nyo)001:8246: can bzang po'i drung du byon nas thugs sbyong mdzad
NK128(nyo)001:8247: // / pas / lo lnga la gzhung phar tshad
NK128(nyo)001:8248: dbu gsum la byas pa'i po ti bcu drug thugs
NK128(nyo)001:8249: // / pas / la chud de / dgung lo
NK128(nyo)001:8250: bco brgyad pa'i thog tu dbu mdzad chos bstan bzang
NK128(nyo)001:8251: // / pas / la chud de / pos thog
NK128(nyo)001:8252: drangs / dge 'dun khri tsho lnga'i dbus su zhag
NK128(nyo)001:8253: bcu gsum gyi bar du grwa skor phul du phyin
NK128(nyo)001:8254: // / pas / la chud de / pos thog
NK128(nyo)001:8255: drangs / par mdzad cing / tshogs pa'i zhabs 'degs
NK128(nyo)001:8256: tshogs gsog kyang bcu gsum bar mdzad do //
NK128(nyo)001:8257: de ltar grwa skor legs shing ston grags dang ldan dus /
NK128(nyo)001:8258: yul gyi dpon a mgon gyi sras sde bdag bkra
NK128(nyo)001:8259: shis mgon pos grwa pa rnams re re bzhin rigs
NK128(nyo)001:8260: rgyus tshe 'brang rnams zhib tu dris dus /
NK128(nyo)001:8262: nga'i yab dang khyed rang gi yab mes rnams gcig
NK128(nyo)001:8263: shul gcig 'dzin gyi mna' gan yod pa yin pas
NK128(nyo)001:8264: / bu la chos bya skabs mi 'ongs /
NK128(nyo)001:8265: lo gcig nas dmag dpon gyi khur byed dgos gsungs pa la /
NK128(nyo)001:8267: nga ni chos rgyal nor bu'i bu yin /
NK128(nyo)001:8268: rigs rus la snying por 'dzin na sngon nas mnga'
NK128(nyo)001:8269: ris skor gsum nged kyi pha mes kyis skyong mod
NK128(nyo)001:8271: nga chos min pa byed re zhes sde pa la zhus pas /
NK128(nyo)001:8272: de 'dra ba'i gtam gyis sa mi chod /
NK128(nyo)001:8273: lugs gnyis phyogs nas byed long yod gsungs /
NK128(nyo)001:8274: chos dus de grol ba dang khams ma bde ri khrod zhig tu 'gro gsungs te /
NK128(nyo)001:8275: g.yog dad pa bzang po dang bcas dbu rtse'i spyil bu zhig tu sku mtshams mdzad /
NK128(nyo)001:8276: sku la dbyi mong pa la sogs thor pa 'byung ba'i rdzas sbyor byas nas /
NK128(nyo)001:8278: bdag khams shin tu ma bde /
NK128(nyo)001:8279: 'tsho byed zhig gnang dgos zhus te 'tsho byed gnang nas bstan pas /
NK128(nyo)001:8280: 'dis bdag gi kha rlangs yin pa 'dug /
NK128(nyo)001:8281: rtsa bde de nad brtag dka' zer sde par zhus
NK128(nyo)001:8282: pas sde pa yang thugs ma bde nas sman dpyad
NK128(nyo)001:8283: rim gro gdon bcos sogs rim can du gnang /
NK128(nyo)001:8284: mo rtsis skag skor sogs byas par /
NK128(nyo)001:8286: de min mi 'tsho ba sogs shar zhing /
NK128(nyo)001:8287: de ga'i rgyu mtshan zhus pas /
NK128(nyo)001:8288: lo gcig gi dgongs pa khrol /
NK128(nyo)001:8289: bdag nad 'dis gtong dogs chung ba 'dug pas gnas skor la phyogs mthar 'gro lugs zhus pas /
NK128(nyo)001:8290: lo gcig khams kyi tsho bzung /
NK128(nyo)001:8292: de bar sku mtshams dam par bcad de /
NK128(nyo)001:8293: rje btsun ma sgrol ma dang o rgyan kho na
NK128(nyo)001:8294: la chos byas chog pa'i gsol ba kho na btab
NK128(nyo)001:8295: pas thugs rje mngon du gyur te /
NK128(nyo)001:8296: lo mtshams grol ba dang sde pas /
NK128(nyo)001:8297: khyed cis kyang mi nyan zhing kha mna' zhig kyang thal song bas mna' zar mi 'jug /
NK128(nyo)001:8298: gnas skor ni dgos pa chung /
NK128(nyo)001:8299: dbus kyi gong dkar du byon la phur ba'i skor rnams mkhas par slobs /
NK128(nyo)001:8300: 'dir bla ma pher nges su bla'i khur ma chungs par mdzod gsungs /
NK128(nyo)001:8301: bla ma dbu rtse pas sde pa la /
NK128(nyo)001:8302: spyir nged dbu rtse pa'i grwa pa rdzong tshad yang 'ug gnyis su rdzogs dgos /
NK128(nyo)001:8303: chos kyang rnying ma bka' gter /
NK128(nyo)001:8304: khyad par mdo sgyu sems gsum /
NK128(nyo)001:8306: ma mgon mgar gsum la sogs chos bka' rgya che
NK128(nyo)001:8307: la dpangs mtho ba'i nyan bshad dgos zhus pa ltar
NK128(nyo)001:8308: / dgung lo nyer gcig pa'i thog tu sde bas rdzong chas spos shel /
NK128(nyo)001:8309: mu men rnams kyi phreng ba gnyis re /
NK128(nyo)001:8310: mu tig gi rtsar pa brgya nyi shu /
NK128(nyo)001:8311: ras sngo mar sgril ma bcu /
NK128(nyo)001:8313: ras yug nyi shu rnams gnang ste /
NK128(nyo)001:8314: 'di la lo sbrel gyi chas mdzod la 'di tshor
NK128(nyo)001:8315: gsang sngags rnying ma'i bshad sgrub yang dag tshug nges
NK128(nyo)001:8316: pa'i slob sbyongs / bka' lung gi rgya chod /
NK128(nyo)001:8317: dpe cha mtha' ma rdugs pa chod pa mdzod byon gsungs nas dbus gtsang la byon te /
NK128(nyo)001:8318: 'ug pa lung du sna gtad nas byon /
NK128(nyo)001:8319: mkhas grub rgyal sras chos rje dang mjal nas chos 'brel gsan tsam las ma byung /
NK128(nyo)001:8320: chu bar nyi sbug tu brgyud 'dzin legs pa dpal
NK128(nyo)001:8321: bzang gi zhabs pad gtsug tu bsnyen nas 'brug lo
NK128(nyo)001:8322: zla ba bcu pa'i tshes brgyad nas hor zla bcu
NK128(nyo)001:8323: gcig pa'i tshes lnga'i bar du 'dus pa mdo'i dkyil
NK128(nyo)001:8324: 'khor chen po drug cu re lnga'i smin byed bka'
NK128(nyo)001:8325: gtad rgyud lung man ngag phyag bzhes dang bcas pa
NK128(nyo)001:8326: gsan / gzhan yang zur ham rgyal ba dpal bzang khu dbon /
NK128(nyo)001:8327: 'ug pa lung pa tshe dpal mgon po /
NK128(nyo)001:8328: gter ston kun skyong gling pa /
NK128(nyo)001:8332: nyi ma 'brug grags thang stong rgyal po sogs dbus
NK128(nyo)001:8333: gtsang gi ljongs su mkhas grub kyi bla ma drug
NK128(nyo)001:8335: de rnams kyi nang nas bla ma drug la phar zhus las med /
NK128(nyo)001:8336: gzhan kun la phar zhu tshur zhu byas gsungs /
NK128(nyo)001:8337: gsan pa'i chos kyang mdo sgyu sems gsum /
NK128(nyo)001:8338: bka' brgyad bka' gter gyis gtsos theg pa rim dgur gtogs pa /
NK128(nyo)001:8342: a ti skor gsum sogs bsam gyis mi khyab par gsan sbyong mdzad de /
NK128(nyo)001:8343: mdor bsdu na rgyud sde bdun cu don gnyis thugs
NK128(nyo)001:8344: la sbyangs shing rgyud sde sum cu so lnga la
NK128(nyo)001:8345: sa gzhung sbol / dbang dang rjes gnang khri tsho gsum la nye ba gsan /
NK128(nyo)001:8346: khrid kha brgya dang go lnga la ngo sprod byas /
NK128(nyo)001:8347: sgrub pa sde dgu'i sngon 'gro dngos gzhi rjes lhag ma brtan skyong yan gyi gar mchams /
NK128(nyo)001:8348: dbyangs bris thig phyag len rnams go yul du ma
NK128(nyo)001:8349: bzhag par thugs su lhon par mdzad pa sogs dbus
NK128(nyo)001:8350: gtsang du lo dgu'i bar bzhugs so //
NK128(nyo)001:8351: lha sar byon nas jo bo sh+aakya mu ne'i drung du bzang spyod 'bum ther zhig zhal 'don mdzad /
NK128(nyo)001:8352: 'dam sog chu kha yan gyi gnas skor dang smon lam mdzad /
NK128(nyo)001:8353: dbus gtsang gi chos grwa thams cad du mdo rgyud
NK128(nyo)001:8354: kyi bshad pa dam bca' rig lung sogs mdzad pas
NK128(nyo)001:8355: mkhas pa'i grags pas khyab ste /
NK128(nyo)001:8356: khams kahthoga nas kyang gdan 'dren byung bar 'byon nam dgongs pa'i tshe /
NK128(nyo)001:8357: glo bo nas sde bdag bkra shis mgon pos zhu yig 'di ltar byung ste /
NK128(nyo)001:8358: khyed kahthoga phyogs su chos 'chad la 'byon 'dod yin na /
NK128(nyo)001:8359: 'dir gsang sngags kyi bstan pa 'dzugs dgos bsam ste
NK128(nyo)001:8360: khyod mi 'byon na 'dir nye 'brel rnams la dka'
NK128(nyo)001:8362: mi theg khur rnams 'gel ba las 'os med /
NK128(nyo)001:8363: lo sbrel gyi chas kyi lo dgu'i chas byas te
NK128(nyo)001:8364: thos bsam sgom gsum mdzad pa rjes su yi rangs
NK128(nyo)001:8365: / da lan chas rkyen du gser srang gang dang ras sngo dmar sgril ma gnyis yod /
NK128(nyo)001:8366: da lo 'dir 'byor pa gal che zhes mi rkang
NK128(nyo)001:8367: tshugs su byung bar sprul sku gter ston kun skyong
NK128(nyo)001:8368: gling par brtag pa zhus par /
NK128(nyo)001:8371: mar pa'i thugs kyi 'od zer las sprul pa yin /
NK128(nyo)001:8372: snying thig bcu gsum gyi lung bstan du thebs /
NK128(nyo)001:8373: nga gter 'don pa'i grogs byas pas lung du zin /
NK128(nyo)001:8375: skye ba sngon ma rab 'byams pa kun dga' nyi ma zhes bya ba pan stod pa yin /
NK128(nyo)001:8376: mkhas rlom gyi gzhan la sun 'byin byas pa'i las
NK128(nyo)001:8377: 'bras kyis chos thams cad la sbyangs sla te gzhan
NK128(nyo)001:8378: rkyen mang / drin gang che sdang /
NK128(nyo)001:8380: da nas shing stag pa skye ba'i gnas su rtse
NK128(nyo)001:8381: gcig tu sgrub la 'bungs na phung por 'od skur
NK128(nyo)001:8382: smin mdo rgyud kyi 'chad brtsam byas na bstan pa'i
NK128(nyo)001:8384: phal cher gzhan rkyen gyis 'jig rten gyi tshul 'dzin dgos /
NK128(nyo)001:8385: de yang bstan pa'i rtsa lag tu 'gyur /
NK128(nyo)001:8386: theg pa chen po'i rnam thar yin /
NK128(nyo)001:8388: dang po la don grub rdo rje /
NK128(nyo)001:8389: de 'og la dbang rgyal rdo rje /
NK128(nyo)001:8390: de 'og la rin chen rdo rje /
NK128(nyo)001:8391: de 'og la snang mdzad rdo rje /
NK128(nyo)001:8392: de 'og tu gnyis la ming mi dgos /
NK128(nyo)001:8393: de 'og la kun bzang rdo rje /
NK128(nyo)001:8394: de 'og tu mgon po legs ldan rdo rjer thogs /
NK128(nyo)001:8395: tshe tshad brgyad cu gya bzhi yin /
NK128(nyo)001:8400: re gcig rnams la bar chad kyi 'phrang re yod
NK128(nyo)001:8401: pas sgrub pa la 'bungs phyis skye ba mi len
NK128(nyo)001:8402: te 'og min du tshom bu gcig tu 'tshogs /
NK128(nyo)001:8403: chos gsang skor 'dis 'gro don cher yong /
NK128(nyo)001:8404: bshad sgrub kyi bstan pa tshugs pa dka'/
NK128(nyo)001:8405: sbyiin bdag la bar chad kyi 'phrang zhig 'dug bsam pa lam lus bya ba yin /
NK128(nyo)001:8406: yar lam thang stong rgyal po dang mjal ba mdzod /
NK128(nyo)001:8408: lo bcu gsum sgrub la nan tan gyi dam bca' mdzod gsungs /
NK128(nyo)001:8409: 'di rnams byin rlabs kyi skal bar bsnams gsungs te pad+ma gu ru'i sku /
NK128(nyo)001:8414: o rgyan rin po che dang mtsho rgyal gyi dbu skra nyag ma bcu gsum re /
NK128(nyo)001:8416: gzhan yang byin rlabs kyi rgyun dpag tu med pa dang /
NK128(nyo)001:8417: zhal bkod phyi nang gsang ba'i tshul du rgyas par gnang la /
NK128(nyo)001:8418: phyag dang bskor ba brgya rtsa byas byon te /
NK128(nyo)001:8419: zur ham rgyal ba dpal bzang sogs bla ma re
NK128(nyo)001:8420: re bzhin la byin rlabs dpe rten dam rdzas rnams
NK128(nyo)001:8421: zhus shing / thams cad kyi bslabs bya rgyas par mdzad /
NK128(nyo)001:8422: gdan 'dren pa dpe cha dang bcas te sngon la bardzangasa /
NK128(nyo)001:8423: rje nyid kyi dpal chen ri bo cher grub chen thang stong rgyal po mjal bar byon /
NK128(nyo)001:8424: de yang grub chen sku mtshams mdzad de lo gcig
NK128(nyo)001:8425: sku gsung thugs dang mjal ba de'i phyi ma sku
NK128(nyo)001:8426: mjal / de'i phyi ma sku gsung gang yang mi mjal ba las /
NK128(nyo)001:8427: sku mjal dus phebs pas nyin par zhal gyi dkyil
NK128(nyo)001:8428: 'khor mjal te gsol ras gnang ba las gsung ngag
NK128(nyo)001:8429: mi mdzad kyang / mtshan gyi gung la gsung byon nas rgyal po mdo bcu /
NK128(nyo)001:8432: thugs rje chen po rigs gsum /
NK128(nyo)001:8434: zang thal la sogs pa'i bka' lung rdzogs par gnang /
NK128(nyo)001:8435: ma 'ongs lung bstan mang du gnang zhing /
NK128(nyo)001:8436: tshe tshad brgya dang bcu gsum yin tshul sogs zhal
NK128(nyo)001:8437: gdams bslab bya du ma zla phyed kyi bar gnang
NK128(nyo)001:8438: nas / 'byon pa'i nyin tshe ril so gsum gnang /
NK128(nyo)001:8439: phu phatahgasunga phyag phyogs mthar bkrug rkyang lan gsum du
NK128(nyo)001:8440: mdzad nye gnas zhig gis khyod sngon bsags las 'phro
NK128(nyo)001:8442: chos dang 'jig rten 'dren pa'i bar chad kyi 'phrang sol skad /
NK128(nyo)001:8443: skra 'dom re tsam du ma sogs par sgrub par gyis /
NK128(nyo)001:8444: de nas so gsum re bzhi pa'i steng du legs par gzobs /
NK128(nyo)001:8446: lam phyogs gang la phyin kyang bar gcod med /
NK128(nyo)001:8447: rang yul la 'gro ba la sems bag tsam ma
NK128(nyo)001:8448: dga' ba'i nad de ngas bsal gyi zer dbyug pa
NK128(nyo)001:8450: des thugs sems kyi gegs phra mo yod pa de bsal song /
NK128(nyo)001:8451: des nas byang 'grims la byon te gegs dang bar gcod med par rang yul glo bor phyag phebs /
NK128(nyo)001:8452: sde bdag gi drung du nyin mtshan med par chos kyi bgro gleng mdzad /
NK128(nyo)001:8453: sde ba sku mched la sgyu 'phrul tshe sgrub /
NK128(nyo)001:8456: srung 'khor ush+ni la sogs pa'i dbang dang gdams pa lkog tu phul /
NK128(nyo)001:8457: phyir bla mchod kyi tshul du bzhugs /
NK128(nyo)001:8458: zla ba lnga'i ring sku ngal brten rjes rnam g.yeng
NK128(nyo)001:8459: spangs te dbu rtse yang dben gyi rtser lo lnga'i
NK128(nyo)001:8460: ring bug sgo 'dag 'byar gyi sgrub pa la rtse
NK128(nyo)001:8461: gcig tu bzhugs / de nas bstan pa'i bya ba lo gsum gyi bar du mdzad de /
NK128(nyo)001:8462: dbu rtse sgyu 'phrul sde brgyad kyi bka' lung man
NK128(nyo)001:8463: ngag sogs 'chad nyan gyi grwa btsugs te bla ma
NK128(nyo)001:8464: gong ma'i mdzad pa dang rnam thar brkyangs /
NK128(nyo)001:8465: de nas 'chad nyan bskos te slar yang sku mtshams la lo lnga bzhugs te /
NK128(nyo)001:8466: de'i bar du snang sems 'dres pa'i rtags bug sgo la zang thal du 'byon pa dang /
NK128(nyo)001:8467: phyag zhabs kyi rjes thogs pa med par 'byon pa dang /
NK128(nyo)001:8468: dgun sgrub khang la 'ja' 'od sna lnga kho re ba dang /
NK128(nyo)001:8469: r+aa hu las dngos su chos nyan pa dang /
NK128(nyo)001:8470: sgrub khang gi steng nas ri rtser skyo sangs la 'phur nas 'byon pa dang /
NK128(nyo)001:8471: dgun grang sgang yang na bza' ras rkyang res dros pa dang /
NK128(nyo)001:8472: sman rag gtor gsum la me tog dang 'bras bu
NK128(nyo)001:8473: smin cing dbyar mi rul dgun mi 'khyags pa dang
NK128(nyo)001:8474: / gshin po'i rnam shes gar gnas /
NK128(nyo)001:8475: gson legs nyes gang yod rnams gsal ler mkhyen pa dang /
NK128(nyo)001:8476: sku zhang dge slong gis sku mtshams phyag phyi byas dus /
NK128(nyo)001:8477: yul mi drag zhan kun gyi byed spyod lab rigs 'di 'dug ces gsungs pa dang /
NK128(nyo)001:8478: sku lus kyang res mngon par 'od lngar phung po
NK128(nyo)001:8479: la sogs bkod pa'i rdzu 'phrul du ma ston cing
NK128(nyo)001:8480: / bya ri dwags kun kyang bug sgo'i 'gag dang sla yer sdod pa kun gyis mthong /
NK128(nyo)001:8481: de dus sde bdag sku mched kyi phyag zhabs kyi sngags btsun kun 'bangs su phul /
NK128(nyo)001:8482: nye 'brel gyi char gtogs grong chen bcu gsum khral med dar rgan du byas /
NK128(nyo)001:8483: rdo rje sgang du 'du khang ka ba brgyad cu gtsang khang dang bcas pa 'debs pa /
NK128(nyo)001:8484: mnga' zhabs kyi rgya dpon gyi bu gsum bar pa rnams bsdus nas chos sgor 'jug /
NK128(nyo)001:8485: gsang sngags rnying ma 'di rgya che se las zab khyad yod snyem ma byung ste /
NK128(nyo)001:8486: bka' mdo rgyud thams cad 'dus shing de dag gi snying po bskyed rdzogs zung 'jug /
NK128(nyo)001:8487: drang nges ldem dgongs kun yod par 'dug pas dar rgyas gang che byed dgos pa 'dug /
NK128(nyo)001:8488: bla ma pas kyang thugs bskyed rgya chen po mdzod
NK128(nyo)001:8489: la bla mchod kyi rgyud du 'gro zhing bstan pa'i
NK128(nyo)001:8490: btsas su 'dug pas lha rigs shing s+aa la lta
NK128(nyo)001:8491: bu chad na mi btubs pas /
NK128(nyo)001:8492: rigs bzang ngan rtogs la rigs sras kyang 'jog pa dgos /
NK128(nyo)001:8493: zhabs 'degs su gang 'gro byed gsungs pa dang /
NK128(nyo)001:8494: kun skyong gling pa'i lung bstan thog tu babs te /
NK128(nyo)001:8496: jo mo mi bzhes pa'i zhu ba nan gyis phul
NK128(nyo)001:8497: nas lo s+n+rel zhig gi sku mtshams la bzhugs pas
NK128(nyo)001:8498: / sde bas kyang yab yar btsan lde dang dmag dpon da ra kha che /
NK128(nyo)001:8499: dpon drung tshe bzang gsum la 'thad bkod du ma dang /
NK128(nyo)001:8500: btsun mo gsum gyis 'dam kha bkur zhing chos rje
NK128(nyo)001:8501: slob dpon pa thugs dgongs rgan tar dog pa ma
NK128(nyo)001:8502: dgos / lugs gnyis ka la rang don gzhan don dgos /
NK128(nyo)001:8503: bka' lung man ngag thams cad kyi brgyud 'dzin rigs
NK128(nyo)001:8504: sras 'jog pa mdo rgyud du mar bshad 'dug pas
NK128(nyo)001:8505: dgongs 'byor yod pa dgos gsung nan cher mdzad pas
NK128(nyo)001:8506: / zhag bcu gsum gyi bar du lha mo sh+ra ma na bsgrubs nas /
NK128(nyo)001:8507: rten 'brel brtags pas rigs bskrun dgos par shar te /
NK128(nyo)001:8508: dgung lo zhe gcig pa'i thog tu 'bro lo ts+aa
NK128(nyo)001:8509: ba'i rigs khrom pa rgyan zhes pa thugs dam brtag
NK128(nyo)001:8510: par chud de khab tu bzhes /
NK128(nyo)001:8511: rigs brgyud 'jog pa'i cho ga mdzad pas kun skyong gling pa'i lung bzhin 'khrul med du byon te /
NK128(nyo)001:8512: sras che ba don grub rdo rje ni gso ba rigs byed phul phyin du gyur /
NK128(nyo)001:8513: gnyis pa dbang rgyal rdo rje ni mnga' ris pan+di
NK128(nyo)001:8514: ta chen po nyid yin te rnam thar cung zad
NK128(nyo)001:8516: de 'og rin chen rdo rje ni lhag bsam dang
NK128(nyo)001:8517: ldan pas skye bo'i gros dpon du gyur cing dam
NK128(nyo)001:8518: chos la yang gdeng dang ldan no //
NK128(nyo)001:8519: de 'og snang mdzad rdo rje ni /
NK128(nyo)001:8520: de bzhin bsnyen par rdzogs shing bshad sgrub la nges pas phyag rdzogs kyi dgongs pa mthar phyin no //
NK128(nyo)001:8521: de 'og gnyis la ming mi dgos zhes lung bstan pa ltar chung ngu nas gshegs so //
NK128(nyo)001:8522: de 'og kun bzang rdo rje ni gnas lugs kho na la brtson pas lam rnyed /
NK128(nyo)001:8523: de 'og mgon po legs ldan rdo rje ni rig
NK128(nyo)001:8524: 'dzin mnga' ris pa chen po ste 'di'i rnam thar
NK128(nyo)001:8526: de ltar kun skyong gling pa'i lung bzhin rigs sras rnams kyang bltams shing /
NK128(nyo)001:8527: dbu rtse dang ma thang lhun grub dpal gyi chos
NK128(nyo)001:8528: sdings dgon pa rnams su bstan 'gro'i don du 'chad
NK128(nyo)001:8529: nyan thos bsam sgom sgrub du mas snga 'gyur gyi
NK128(nyo)001:8530: bstan pa rin po che 'dzin skyong spel gsum 'ba'
NK128(nyo)001:8531: zhig lhur mdzad pa yin te /
NK128(nyo)001:8533: glo bo ma thang chos sdings su //
NK128(nyo)001:8534: 'jam dbyangs rin chen rgyal mtshan ni //
NK128(nyo)001:8535: mkhas grub kun gyi yang rtser son //
NK128(nyo)001:8538: mdo dbang bdud rtsis thugs rgyud dkyus //
NK128(nyo)001:8539: 'jam dpal gshin rje'i gshed zhal gzigs //
NK128(nyo)001:8540: legs ldan mgon pos sras su sprul //
NK128(nyo)001:8541: snying rjes ma rungs dbyings su bsgral //
NK128(nyo)001:8542: 'jam dbyangs rin chen rgyal mtshan de //
NK128(nyo)001:8544: gzhan yang ma 'ongs lung ston yang yang mang po zhig mdzad cing /
NK128(nyo)001:8545: nam zhig gi tshe sde bdag la bka' la pa /
NK128(nyo)001:8546: kho bos lo bzhi bcu rtsa gnyis lon pa yan
NK128(nyo)001:8547: la mnga' ris tha dad kyi mtho dman ring thung
NK128(nyo)001:8549: da ste lo bcu drug tsam na bod 'dir hor la sogs pa'i skad cha mang po zhig yong /
NK128(nyo)001:8550: sa chen po zhig g.yo mi rnams spyod pa yang 'gyur 'gro /
NK128(nyo)001:8551: gsang sngags kyi sgom sgrub 'di dag bor nas sde
NK128(nyo)001:8552: pa'i go khar ngo so su mtho 'tshol ba zhig
NK128(nyo)001:8553: yong / ri brag gi na bun yang chung ngu 'gro /
NK128(nyo)001:8554: sngar yul 'dir sad mi yong yang phyis sgong gshogs su yong /
NK128(nyo)001:8555: de la kho bo'i kha la nyan mkhan yang med /
NK128(nyo)001:8557: rim gro 'di lta bu byed dgos /
NK128(nyo)001:8558: byed lugs 'di lta bu dgos gsungs shing /
NK128(nyo)001:8559: de rnams kyang sde srid la thugs zhen che ba lta bu'i gsung ngar dang bcas nas gsungs shing /
NK128(nyo)001:8560: lan cig tsam du ma zad yang yang du bzlas shing gsungs kyang mi rnams bdud kyis khebs pas /
NK128(nyo)001:8562: dang po ge sar gyi dus byung ba'i lo rgyus tsam yod /
NK128(nyo)001:8563: bshad sgrub btsugs na kho rang gi che khyad thon par shes nas smra ba yin /
NK128(nyo)001:8564: rim gro rnams kyang za ba'i snyad yin zhes sgrog cing /
NK128(nyo)001:8565: de'i dbang gis btang snyoms su lus so //
NK128(nyo)001:8566: de nas dus gsum sgrib pa med par lugs ji
NK128(nyo)001:8567: ltar bstan pa ltar lo bcu drug song ba dang
NK128(nyo)001:8568: mang yul du hor dang por byung ngo //
NK128(nyo)001:8569: de nas glang gi lo sa g.yos ngan pa lo
NK128(nyo)001:8570: gcig la sum cu grangs tsam byung ste mi kun
NK128(nyo)001:8571: gyis bskal pa 'jig par ngos bzung ngo //
NK128(nyo)001:8572: de'i dus su skye bo phal cher yang chos mi
NK128(nyo)001:8573: dran zhing sgo phyugs thams cad bsad de za zhing
NK128(nyo)001:8574: chang bag med du 'thung ba sogs spyod lam yang
NK128(nyo)001:8575: ngan pa gyur pas sngon ji ltar lung bstan pa
NK128(nyo)001:8577: de'i tshe skye bo rnams shes rgyud 'gyur bas nyan par dka' yang /
NK128(nyo)001:8578: dam 'di snying rje chen pos ma bzod par de'i lo yang 'di skad ces gsungs so //
NK128(nyo)001:8579: da lo sa phyogs 'dis gtso byas 'ga' zhig brlag nges pa'i sa g.yos so //
NK128(nyo)001:8580: thog ser drag po yong ngo ri gzar po la ma 'gro /
NK128(nyo)001:8581: khang sa mthon por ma sdod gsungs te /
NK128(nyo)001:8582: sa g.yos chen por yong ba'i gong zla ba gsum nas sde bdag sogs la zhal bkod mdzad /
NK128(nyo)001:8583: rje nyid rang yang khang pa zhol gcig dang /
NK128(nyo)001:8584: gur gcig gsar du bcos pa der bzhugs te drung du yang mi thams cad la /
NK128(nyo)001:8585: kho re tsho snang ba chen po 'gyur ba yod de /
NK128(nyo)001:8586: dkon cog la skyabs 'gro dge las dang rim 'gror 'bad kyis gsungs /
NK128(nyo)001:8588: kho bo la nyan mkhan yod na dngos grub thams cad ster ba yin te /
NK128(nyo)001:8589: bu dang slob ma mi nyan gsungs /
NK128(nyo)001:8591: de nas glang lo zla ba lnga pa'i tshes lnga'i
NK128(nyo)001:8592: tho rangs rje rin po che nyid rang gis bka'
NK128(nyo)001:8594: de ring dgon pa steng 'og thams cad phyi rol tu thon cig /
NK128(nyo)001:8595: su ma nyan pa la rkyen chen po yong bas go bar gyis shig /
NK128(nyo)001:8597: nyi ma rtse shar la bzhugs gdan yang kho rang
NK128(nyo)001:8598: gis bsnams te zhing khar byon nas cung zhig lon
NK128(nyo)001:8599: tsam la bzod par dka' ba gnam sa kha log
NK128(nyo)001:8600: pa lta bu'i sa g.yo chen po thengs lnga byung
NK128(nyo)001:8601: ste mi mang po kha phung la song /
NK128(nyo)001:8602: dgon gnas dang rgyal sa mang pos brdal du song /
NK128(nyo)001:8603: gzims khang yang 'jig pa la nye ba'i tshe gsungs chen pos 'di skad gsungs so //
NK128(nyo)001:8604: dus gsum gyi bla ma yi dam lha tshogs dpa' bo mkha' 'gro chos skyong srung ma /
NK128(nyo)001:8605: nga bla ma dam pa rnams kyi bka' lung tshad
NK128(nyo)001:8606: ma ltar tshad ldan yang yin kho bo'i chos rgyud
NK128(nyo)001:8607: 'di yang dri ma med pa'i khung thub pa yin
NK128(nyo)001:8608: na / spyir sems can rnams la sdug bsngal drag po ma btang /
NK128(nyo)001:8609: sgos bdag la bltos pa'i sde ba yab yum sras dang bcas pa /
NK128(nyo)001:8611: bdag gi dgon pa rten gsum dang bcas pa la bar chad ma btang bar srungs shig /
NK128(nyo)001:8612: de ltar mi bden kho bo'i bla ma dang /
NK128(nyo)001:8613: de'i lung bstan thams cad dang kho bo'i chos rgyud
NK128(nyo)001:8614: 'di rnam par dag pa min na ci mi rung
NK128(nyo)001:8617: gzims khang pad+ma ltar kha gyes pa yang kha 'grig nas yul khams thams cad thal bar brlag kyang /
NK128(nyo)001:8618: gzims khang dang lha khang dgon pa'i grwa khang sogs
NK128(nyo)001:8619: thams cad kyi thog rtsa phan tshun 'phrom ba tsam
NK128(nyo)001:8621: slar yang kha gas pa zhig yod pa yang khrig gis 'grig par gyur /
NK128(nyo)001:8622: bltos bcas kyi sde pa yon bdag grwa slob dang
NK128(nyo)001:8623: bcas pa yang bar chad med par bden pa'i tshig
NK128(nyo)001:8624: mngon sum du gyur pa byung ba 'di ni ngo
NK128(nyo)001:8625: mtshar gzhan las khyad par che'o //
NK128(nyo)001:8626: gzhan yang drung 'od zer bya ba'i gnas brtan gcig
NK128(nyo)001:8627: dang btsun ma tshul khrims dpal mo bya ba zhig
NK128(nyo)001:8628: rang gi nas thog la bsod snyoms la phyin pas
NK128(nyo)001:8629: gtsang le brag 'phrang du sa g.yos dang thug /
NK128(nyo)001:8630: brag 'phrang mig rgyang gang gi sar mdun du mi drug /
NK128(nyo)001:8631: rgyab tu mi lnga bzong bung bzhi mdzo gcig rnams brag ral bas lhungs te shi /
NK128(nyo)001:8632: khong gnyis 'jam dbyangs rin cen rgyal mtshan mkhyen zhes
NK128(nyo)001:8633: rtse gcig tu gsol ba btab pas nyams nyes gang
NK128(nyo)001:8634: yang med par thon pa yin zhes mnga' ris pan
NK128(nyo)001:8635: chen rin po che'i gsung las byung ngo //
NK128(nyo)001:8636: de ltar mkhyen brtse nus gsum gyi mnga' bdag mkhas
NK128(nyo)001:8637: pa dang grub pa'i dbang phyug nges pa don gyi
NK128(nyo)001:8638: 'jam dbyangs rin chen rgyal mtshan dpal bzang po de
NK128(nyo)001:8639: nyid kun skyong gling pas tshe tshad brgyad cu gya
NK128(nyo)001:8641: rje thang stong rgyal pos brgya dang bcu gsum du lung bstan pa las /
NK128(nyo)001:8642: don du dgung lo brgya dang bcu gsum bzhugs nges pa'i rgyu mtshan /
NK128(nyo)001:8643: rigs sras legs ldan rjer yab rang gi tshe pha bu mnyam zhes dang /
NK128(nyo)001:8644: nga tshe tshad brgyad cu gya bzhi'am brgya dang bcu gsum nas kun tu bzang po'i klong du 'gro /
NK128(nyo)001:8646: rig 'dzin rjes brgya dang bcu gsum du bzhugs pas
NK128(nyo)001:8647: yab sras gnyis ka de ltar nges pa'i gtan tshigs
NK128(nyo)001:8648: grub pa yin pas zhing 'dir bshad sgrub dang sku
NK128(nyo)001:8649: tshe mthar phyin nas dgung lo brgya dang bcu gsum
NK128(nyo)001:8650: gyi steng du dpa' bo dang d+aa ki'i tshogs kyis
NK128(nyo)001:8651: mdun bsus te 'og min tshogs chen 'dus pa'i dkyil
NK128(nyo)001:8652: 'khor gyi khyab bdag tu gshegs te zhing khams rgya
NK128(nyo)001:8653: mtshor sprul pa sna tshogs kyis 'gro ba 'dul ba
NK128(nyo)001:8655: lha rigs 'od gsal gdung las sprul pa'i gar //
NK128(nyo)001:8656: mkhas grub rgya mtsho'i 'khor los sgyur ba'i tshul //
NK128(nyo)001:8657: snga 'gyur bstan pa'i rtsa lag gcig pu ba //
NK128(nyo)001:8658: 'jam dbyangs chos kyi rgyal por der phyag 'tshal //
NK128(nyo)001:8659: dang po yongs 'dzin mang bsten thos bsam mdzad //
NK128(nyo)001:8660: bar du bshad sgrub bstan pa'i nyi 'od gdal //
NK128(nyo)001:8661: tha ma mkha' spyod dkyil 'khor gtso bo'i tshul //
NK128(nyo)001:8662: sna tshogs sprul pa'i gar mdzad he ru ka /
NK128(nyo)001:8663: ljongs 'dir grub pa'i slob dpon ches mang yang //
NK128(nyo)001:8664: mkhas grub tshad ma'i yul gyur khyod kho na //
NK128(nyo)001:8665: rlabs chen mdzad pas bstan 'gro'i don bsgrub par //
NK128(nyo)001:8666: mi g.yel mgon khyod lta bur bdag 'gyur shog /
NK128(nyo)001:8668: de ltar bka' drin mnyam pa med pa'i rje btsun
NK128(nyo)001:8669: des rigs sras pan chen mched la stsal ba yin
NK128(nyo)001:8670: kyang / brgyud pa'i gtso bo rig 'dzin rje la brgyud dgos shing /
NK128(nyo)001:8671: 'on kyang gcen mnga' ris pan chen nyid gcung legs
NK128(nyo)001:8672: ldan zhabs kyii yongs 'dzin gyi gtso bor yang bzhugs
NK128(nyo)001:8673: shing / bstan pa yongs rdzogs la bka' drin shin tu che bas /
NK128(nyo)001:8674: 'dir brgyud tshul dngos la mi dgos kyang dad pa'i
NK128(nyo)001:8675: rjes su 'brang ste rnam par thar pa cung zad
NK128(nyo)001:8676: cig gleng ba bya ba la /
NK128(nyo)001:8677: 'khrungs yul ni glo bo ma thang gi lhun grub chos sdings dang /
NK128(nyo)001:8678: yab ni rje btsun 'jam dbyangs rin chen rgyal mtshan dang /
NK128(nyo)001:8679: yum 'bro lcam khrom pa rgyan yin la /
NK128(nyo)001:8680: rigs rgyus sogs ni gong du smos pas 'dir brjod ma dgos /
NK128(nyo)001:8681: de yang lhums su zhugs pa'i tshe yab kyis lhar bskyed cing dbang bskur ba sogs mdzad de /
NK128(nyo)001:8682: pan chen nyid kyi zhal gsungs ma rnam thar tshigs bcad las /
NK128(nyo)001:8683: grub thob kyi rgyal po rdo rje 'chang //
NK128(nyo)001:8684: mnga' ris kyi sngags 'chang mkhyen rtogs can //
NK128(nyo)001:8685: de nyid kyi brgyud pa bdun ldan gyi //
NK128(nyo)001:8686: dang po yi rjes su skyes pa'i dus //
NK128(nyo)001:8687: ya mtshan gyi rtags bcu kun la grags //
NK128(nyo)001:8688: bde skyid kyi longs spyod lo bdun skyongs //
NK128(nyo)001:8689: lo brgyad kyi sngon du ma yi rum //
NK128(nyo)001:8690: de nyid du bzhugs pa'i srid pa la //
NK128(nyo)001:8691: lha sku ru bskyod nas dbang drag ni //
NK128(nyo)001:8692: dbang bskur dang byin rlabs tshul bzhin thob //
NK128(nyo)001:8694: me mo lug lo la sku bltams pa'i tshe lung
NK128(nyo)001:8695: bstan dang mtshan 'dogs mdzad tshul yang de nyid las
NK128(nyo)001:8696: / skal bzang gi skyes bu grub thob kyi //
NK128(nyo)001:8697: rig 'dzin rgyal po sras brgyad kyi //
NK128(nyo)001:8698: pad+ma yi rigs kyi rtags 'chang ba //
NK128(nyo)001:8699: the tshom dang bral lo ming 'di bzung //
NK128(nyo)001:8700: pad+ma yi rigs las dbang chen rgyal //
NK128(nyo)001:8701: rdo rje sems dpa' kun tu bzang //
NK128(nyo)001:8702: grags pa yi rgyal mtshan phyogs brgyar 'dzin //
NK128(nyo)001:8703: de ma brjed bu yi yid la bzung //
NK128(nyo)001:8704: ma khyod kyang 'bro ston lo ts+aa ba //
NK128(nyo)001:8705: mtshungs bral gyi bshes gnyen brgyud par ldan //
NK128(nyo)001:8706: mkha' 'gro yi rtags dang ldan pa de //
NK128(nyo)001:8707: don de nyid la rnam thar mdzod cig gsungs //
NK128(nyo)001:8709: dgung lo brgyad pa la dge bsnyen du bsgrubs shing thugs bskyed dbang bskur mang du gsan /
NK128(nyo)001:8710: yab dkyil 'khor gyi gtso bor gzigs pa sogs yin te /
NK128(nyo)001:8712: lo brgyad kyi dus su dge bsnyen gnang //
NK128(nyo)001:8713: sems bskyed kyi sdom pas rgyud sbyangs nas //
NK128(nyo)001:8714: rgyud kun gyi rgyal po mtshan brjod dang //
NK128(nyo)001:8715: sgyu 'phrul gyi rgyal po rdo rje sems //
NK128(nyo)001:8716: zhi khro yi dkyil 'khor chen por bcug /
NK128(nyo)001:8717: khrag 'thung gi rgyal po yang dag thugs //
NK128(nyo)001:8718: drug dang brgyad kyi bdag nyid can //
NK128(nyo)001:8719: de bzhin du lnga bcu rtsa brgyad pa //
NK128(nyo)001:8720: nyi shu yi bdag nyid 'khor ldan pa //
NK128(nyo)001:8721: bco brgyad me dgu rnams su bcug /
NK128(nyo)001:8722: rgyud lung dang man ngag ci yang nos //
NK128(nyo)001:8723: dkyil 'khor gyi bdag po pha jo mthong //
NK128(nyo)001:8724: mos gus kyi bsam pa zhe nas tshims //
NK128(nyo)001:8726: lo dgu yi steng du sems ngo sprad //
NK128(nyo)001:8727: chos bdag med kyi pho go lan cig mthong //
NK128(nyo)001:8728: gzhung sgyu 'phrul dang sems phyogs snying thig nyan //
NK128(nyo)001:8730: lo bcu yi dus su 'chi ba dran //
NK128(nyo)001:8731: cir snang kun bden pa med pa la //
NK128(nyo)001:8732: dngos 'dzin du zhen pa thams cad la //
NK128(nyo)001:8733: tshad med kyi snying rje chu ltar brdol //
NK128(nyo)001:8735: dgung lo bcu gcig la rgyud sder thos bsam dang /
NK128(nyo)001:8736: bcu gnyis pa bshad pa mdzad pa'i tshul yang de nyid las /
NK128(nyo)001:8737: bcu gcig gi lo la rgyud sde ma //
NK128(nyo)001:8738: bshad sbyar gyi gtan la legs phab nas //
NK128(nyo)001:8739: sgyu 'phrul rtsa rgyud gsang snying la //
NK128(nyo)001:8740: rgya gar gyi slob dpon sgeg pa yi //
NK128(nyo)001:8741: bshad 'grel dang rgya gzhung mang po dang //
NK128(nyo)001:8742: g.yung ston gyi t+aik+ka la sogs pa //
NK128(nyo)001:8743: phal cher zhig zla ba bdun la bzung //
NK128(nyo)001:8744: khyad par can dgongs pa 'dus pa'i mdo //
NK128(nyo)001:8745: phal cher zhig blo la byang bar byas //
NK128(nyo)001:8747: bcu gnyis kyi dus su yum phyogs kyi //
NK128(nyo)001:8748: mkhas tshogs 'dus pa'i dbus nyid du //
NK128(nyo)001:8749: jo bo dang nu bo bdag dang gsum //
NK128(nyo)001:8750: khri steng du bzhag nas dar gdugs phub //
NK128(nyo)001:8751: gzhung bskyur dang bcas te bshad gsar byas //
NK128(nyo)001:8753: de skabs ngo mtshar gyi ltas byung ba yang /
NK128(nyo)001:8754: de dus su dgun gyi cho 'phrul la //
NK128(nyo)001:8755: me tog gi char pa zhag bdun babs //
NK128(nyo)001:8757: de nas bsnyen sgrub kyi thog mar mdzad tshul yang /
NK128(nyo)001:8759: de mtshams nas lhun grub chos sdings su //
NK128(nyo)001:8760: gcen po dang lhan cig sgrub pa byas //
NK128(nyo)001:8761: bla ma yi sgrub pa gsang 'dus dang //
NK128(nyo)001:8762: bde gshegs zhi khro sgyu 'phrul dang //
NK128(nyo)001:8763: rta mchog dpal dang dbang drag rtsal //
NK128(nyo)001:8764: bsnyen sgrub kyis gtan la phab pa'i tshe //
NK128(nyo)001:8766: gzigs snang gi thog mar yab rje mar pa lo
NK128(nyo)001:8767: ts+aa'i rnam sprul yin pas de'i rgyu mtshan gyi dud
NK128(nyo)001:8768: sol lha mo'i zhal gzigs te /
NK128(nyo)001:8770: mthongs kha na dpal ldan dud sol ma //
NK128(nyo)001:8771: gsal ba ru yang yang bdag gis mthong //
NK128(nyo)001:8772: lta ba dang bsres shing mchod bstod byas //
NK128(nyo)001:8777: shwa bud kho lan gcig song ba las //
NK128(nyo)001:8778: yul phyogs kyi zhing khal sum brgya bshal //
NK128(nyo)001:8779: gnyis pa la kho bo sa der rtol //
NK128(nyo)001:8780: phur pa zhig gdengs pas khyim gyis 'khyil //
NK128(nyo)001:8781: sdig mdzub cig bstan pas thog so bdun //
NK128(nyo)001:8782: gyen phyogs su log ste 'khyil nas song //
NK128(nyo)001:8783: gsum pa zhig byung ba rdo nag la //
NK128(nyo)001:8784: sngags 'phreng zhig bzlas nas 'phangs pa las //
NK128(nyo)001:8785: nub phyogs su rtol nas thengs bdun bzlog /
NK128(nyo)001:8787: bcu gsum gyi lo la 'od gsal bskyangs //
NK128(nyo)001:8788: bla ma yi dam bstod tshogs brtsams //
NK128(nyo)001:8790: gzhan yang rme brtsegs kyi zhal gzigs tshul yang /
NK128(nyo)001:8791: rme brtsigs kyi sgom bzlas byas pa'i tshe //
NK128(nyo)001:8792: nam mkha' 'di sngo sangs ting thug bral //
NK128(nyo)001:8793: mkha' 'gro yi dbang mo sol ba'i mdog /
NK128(nyo)001:8794: dag byed bum pa shel ltar dngas //
NK128(nyo)001:8795: mthong tsam nas sku las me 'od 'bar //
NK128(nyo)001:8796: me sgra ni gar khang dzar khang gi //
NK128(nyo)001:8797: sngags sgra ru khrol khrol lhan ne mthong //
NK128(nyo)001:8798: lha sku la sems zin nyi phyed tsam //
NK128(nyo)001:8799: rtog med kyi ngang du lhan ne ba //
NK128(nyo)001:8801: dgung lo bcu bzhi par gsang sngags kyi phyag lan mtha' dag legs par sbyangs shing /
NK128(nyo)001:8802: thugs dam dka' spyad mdzad tshul yang /
NK128(nyo)001:8804: bcu bzhi yi thog tu lon tsam na //
NK128(nyo)001:8805: bka' brgyad dang ma gshiin rta mgrin sogs //
NK128(nyo)001:8806: sgrub khrigs kyi lag len mang du bslabs //
NK128(nyo)001:8807: sgrub thabs kyi rgyal po bla ma'i lam //
NK128(nyo)001:8808: gsang 'dus sogs sngags kyi grangs la skyon //
NK128(nyo)001:8809: bdud gcod kyi ro snyoms lo 'ga' byas //
NK128(nyo)001:8810: bye ma dang chu rdol me tog sogs //
NK128(nyo)001:8811: dka' spyod dang bcud len lo bdun tsam //
NK128(nyo)001:8813: bco lnga yi lo la mi dbang gi //
NK128(nyo)001:8814: sku rim dang sgrub mchod gtso bor byas //
NK128(nyo)001:8815: sman raka dang bdud rtsi mtsho bzhin khol //
NK128(nyo)001:8816: gtor bzlog gi dus su sa steng du //
NK128(nyo)001:8817: khru re tsam ma reg bar snang la //
NK128(nyo)001:8818: khro rgyal dpung tshogs dang bcas pa //
NK128(nyo)001:8819: bdud dmag gi phyogs su gtor rgyogs 'phangs //
NK128(nyo)001:8820: nyin mtshan du thub pa'i bstan pa bsam //
NK128(nyo)001:8821: sha khrag gi yo lang ring du spangs //
NK128(nyo)001:8822: rang 'khor la yig drug nyams len bslabs //
NK128(nyo)001:8823: bsnyung gnas dang gso sbyong mang du byas //
NK128(nyo)001:8824: rigs drug gi 'dren pa spyan ras gzigs //
NK128(nyo)001:8825: zhal mthong gi snang ba thengs bdun thob //
NK128(nyo)001:8826: them spang gi dam bca' lo gsum dang //
NK128(nyo)001:8827: ngag bcad kyi dam bca' lo gsum byas //
NK128(nyo)001:8828: mnyam med kyi mkhas grub du ma la //
NK128(nyo)001:8829: phyag 'tshal dang chos zhus nyams su blangs //
NK128(nyo)001:8830: lo gcig tu bla ma gsang 'dus kyi //
NK128(nyo)001:8831: gdams ngag la gcig zhus gcig sgom byas //
NK128(nyo)001:8832: zhes sogs mang du gsungs pa'i don gtso che ba re re tsam bsdus te bris pa yin la /
NK128(nyo)001:8833: gzhan yang dam pa mang du bsten nas chos gsan tshul yang /
NK128(nyo)001:8834: tshigs bcad de'i 'phros las mang bar yod cing /
NK128(nyo)001:8835: 'dus pa mdo'i dbang gsan tshul yang /
NK128(nyo)001:8837: mdo rgyud kyi lung las bshad sbyar dang //
NK128(nyo)001:8838: dkyil 'khor gyi cho ga dbang dang bcas //
NK128(nyo)001:8839: theg dgu yi rgyal po mdo dbang dang //
NK128(nyo)001:8840: 'phrin las kyi rgyud rgyal phur pa nyan //
NK128(nyo)001:8841: blo sems kyang bde ba'i tshad du byung //
NK128(nyo)001:8842: pha jo yang sangs rgyas rdo rje 'chang //
NK128(nyo)001:8843: khrag 'thung gi rgyal po kho thag chod //
NK128(nyo)001:8845: khyad par can sgrub pa bka' brgyad kyi //
NK128(nyo)001:8846: them yig la yang yang nan chags byas //
NK128(nyo)001:8847: bcu drug gi lo la dgra bcom pa //
NK128(nyo)001:8848: mkhas btsun gyi rgyal po chos bstan bzang /
NK128(nyo)001:8849: mtshungs bral gyi bla ma yiin no zer /
NK128(nyo)001:8850: de nyid kyi drung du 'jol gyin phyin //
NK128(nyo)001:8851: chos grwa yi rgyal po brag dkar gyi //
NK128(nyo)001:8852: bar gling du mjal bas dran med brgyal //
NK128(nyo)001:8853: zhes sogs bla ma bsten tshul dang /
NK128(nyo)001:8854: gzhan yang sngon du shwa bud bzlog pa nas grub rtags du ma bstan mod /
NK128(nyo)001:8855: dgung lo bcu drug pa 'di'i thog tu grub rtags
NK128(nyo)001:8856: khyad par can bzhag pa'i tshul yang de nyid las
NK128(nyo)001:8857: / brag dmar gyi mtsho la ro snyams byas //
NK128(nyo)001:8858: smun nags kyi chu la rngog pas barjisa //
NK128(nyo)001:8859: lha lung gi brag la bya ltar lding //
NK128(nyo)001:8860: ba gam can brag la byi ltar 'dzul //
NK128(nyo)001:8861: mgo bo can brag gi logs la rgyugs //
NK128(nyo)001:8862: grogs sher seng dang sher dpal rgyal bzang gsum //
NK128(nyo)001:8863: byang rgyal dang bla ma rin seng pa //
NK128(nyo)001:8864: skyes pho mo 'ga' grub thob grub thob zer //
NK128(nyo)001:8865: der grub thob kyi go ba nga mi len //
NK128(nyo)001:8866: chos nyams blangs kyi nyams snang thos tsam yin //
NK128(nyo)001:8867: don 'pho 'gyur bral ba ma rtogs na //
NK128(nyo)001:8868: lus sgyu ba'i cho 'phrul bya byis ston //
NK128(nyo)001:8870: deng sang rang gzhan gyi bshes gnyen 'ga' zhig mnga' ris pan chen mkhas btsun tsam yin zer yang /
NK128(nyo)001:8872: brag la bya ltar 'phur ba dang /
NK128(nyo)001:8873: ri brag la thogs pa med pa byi ltar 'dzul ba /
NK128(nyo)001:8874: g.yang sar rgyug pa sogs grub rtags kyi ngo mtshar
NK128(nyo)001:8875: 'di las che ba rang grub par khas len pa
NK128(nyo)001:8877: gzhan yang khyad par can gyi dam bcas mang du mdzad de /
NK128(nyo)001:8879: bcu bdun gyi lo la zhe dam byas //
NK128(nyo)001:8880: dge 'dun la mthong phyag 'tshal ba dang //
NK128(nyo)001:8881: pha yul du zhag bdun mi mang bar //
NK128(nyo)001:8882: dben gnas dang ri khrod 'grims pa dang //
NK128(nyo)001:8883: rgyal sa yi sgo la lan gsum du //
NK128(nyo)001:8884: 'grim 'grul gyi bya ba spang ba dang //
NK128(nyo)001:8885: tshong khe dang gral 'go mi 'dzin zhing /
NK128(nyo)001:8886: ro chog dang dbu gtso mi byed par //
NK128(nyo)001:8887: bsod snyoms kyi zas la brten byas nas //
NK128(nyo)001:8888: sgrub pa dang thos bsam dam bca' byas //
NK128(nyo)001:8889: yul phyogs kyi ri brag chu klung dang //
NK128(nyo)001:8890: dur khrod dang khang stong bya skyibs su //
NK128(nyo)001:8891: bka' gdams kyi gdams pa lhu ru blangs //
NK128(nyo)001:8892: spyod yul gyi man ngag snying la bzhag /
NK128(nyo)001:8893: sgo gcig pa'i brtul zhugs tshul bzhin bzung //
NK128(nyo)001:8894: rdzogs chen gyi nyams len phu thag bcad //
NK128(nyo)001:8897: bco brgyad kyi lo la dgra bcom pa //
NK128(nyo)001:8898: mkhas btsun gyi rgyal po chos bstan bzang //
NK128(nyo)001:8899: rnam rgyal dang seng ge brag sogs su //
NK128(nyo)001:8900: yang yang du bsnyen nas dam chos zhus //
NK128(nyo)001:8901: 'dul ba dang mdo sde'i gdams pa 'ga' //
NK128(nyo)001:8902: snying gtam du bka' gdams lag len bslabs //
NK128(nyo)001:8903: n+aa ro pa'i gdams pa mkha' spyod ma //
NK128(nyo)001:8904: snyan rgyud dang zhal gdams tshang bar zhus //
NK128(nyo)001:8905: bskyed rdzogs kyi snying po dmar khrid bskyangs //
NK128(nyo)001:8907: skyid grong gi 'phags pa wa ti mjal //
NK128(nyo)001:8908: jo bo yi gsung byon zer ba yi //
NK128(nyo)001:8909: grags pa yis phyogs der khyab na yang //
NK128(nyo)001:8910: lam rtags la zhen pa rmi lam ltar //
NK128(nyo)001:8912: de'i dus su sngon rgya bod kyi mkhas grub du
NK128(nyo)001:8913: mar 'khrungs tshul rnams thugs la shin tu gsal bar
NK128(nyo)001:8914: byung yang / 'dir yul phyogs rjes su dran tshul tsam zhig gsungs te /
NK128(nyo)001:8915: yul rgya gar bal po spu rang dang //
NK128(nyo)001:8916: kha che dang dol po dbus gtsang dang //
NK128(nyo)001:8917: khyad par du la stod sh+r+ai dang //
NK128(nyo)001:8918: ya mtshan can chu dbang yid la shar //
NK128(nyo)001:8919: de bzhin du dpal ldan sa skya dang //
NK128(nyo)001:8920: bo dong dang shab stod shab rmad dang //
NK128(nyo)001:8921: snar thang dang lho brag zab lung dang //
NK128(nyo)001:8922: yar klungs dang bsam yas 'phan yul dang //
NK128(nyo)001:8923: 'chad ka dang gsang phud mkha' reg dang //
NK128(nyo)001:8924: rgya ma dang yol phu grwa dol dang //
NK128(nyo)001:8925: rdog gzhung gi snang ba lam lam shar //
NK128(nyo)001:8926: pha ma dang spun zla bya byed dang //
NK128(nyo)001:8927: dam chos dang yi dam lham me dran //
NK128(nyo)001:8928: zhes gsungs pa yang ngo mtshar bsam gyis mi khyab pa'i gnas yin par rtogs so //
NK128(nyo)001:8930: bcu dgu yi lo la pha yul gyi //
NK128(nyo)001:8931: 'gro ba la yig drug chos 'khor bskor //
NK128(nyo)001:8932: me tog gi char pa bcu gsum babs //
NK128(nyo)001:8933: 'ja' 'od kyi gur khar rgyun du byung //
NK128(nyo)001:8935: nyi shu'i lo la byams chos sde lnga dang //
NK128(nyo)001:8936: phar phyin tshad ma dbu ma rtsa sher dang //
NK128(nyo)001:8937: bzhi brgya pa dang bslabs btus spyod 'jug dang //
NK128(nyo)001:8938: dngos brgya don bdun cu sogs phal cher gyi //
NK128(nyo)001:8939: gzhung rnams khong bcug 'ga' zhig dgra bcom pa //
NK128(nyo)001:8940: chos bstan bzang po slob dpon nam mkha' la //
NK128(nyo)001:8941: legs par nyan cing gzhung lugs brgya phrag gcig /
NK128(nyo)001:8942: bltas shing khong du chud par byas nas kyang //
NK128(nyo)001:8944: 'di gcig pu yang mdzad pa 'gangs che bar sems so //
NK128(nyo)001:8946: nyi shu gcig nas 'jam dbyangs chos skyong dang //
NK128(nyo)001:8947: mkhas pa'i dbang po sdom brtson tshul khrims dpal //
NK128(nyo)001:8948: dri med dam pa rin chen seng ge sogs //
NK128(nyo)001:8949: mkhas grub kun la dkon pa'i sems kyis bsten //
NK128(nyo)001:8951: 'jam dbyangs chos kyi rgyal po'i zhabs bsten nas //
NK128(nyo)001:8952: gshin rje gshed dmar spros med la sogs pa'i //
NK128(nyo)001:8953: dbang dang gdams pa rgyud dang sgrub thabs 'ga' //
NK128(nyo)001:8954: brtse ba'i thugs rjes thos shing po ta lar //
NK128(nyo)001:8955: dgu zlas gnyis su sgrub pas zhag bdun na //
NK128(nyo)001:8956: 'jam dbyangs dapa'o gshin rje gshed dmar de //
NK128(nyo)001:8957: gsal bar mthong ba mi chos bla ma med //
NK128(nyo)001:8958: kha dog dmar po mthong tsam nyid na yang //
NK128(nyo)001:8959: gu ru drag po rta mgrin mkha' spyod ma //
NK128(nyo)001:8960: gshin rje gshed dmar nyid du lham me ba //
NK128(nyo)001:8962: nyi shu gnyis kyi lo la pha jo yi //
NK128(nyo)001:8963: gdams pa kun gyi zhun thar legs par dpyad //
NK128(nyo)001:8964: bka' brgyad bsgrub dus dgun dus bdud rtsi khol //
NK128(nyo)001:8965: me mar chung ngus zhag gsum bar du thub //
NK128(nyo)001:8966: 'khyags pa'i dngos po zhu zhing rlangs pa thon //
NK128(nyo)001:8967: rnga dang rol mo kun la me 'od 'bar //
NK128(nyo)001:8969: de'i tshe yab rje dam pa nyid la gzigs snang
NK128(nyo)001:8970: dang mthun par lung bstan tshul yang de nyid las
NK128(nyo)001:8971: / de'i tshe pha jo rdo rje 'chang chen des //
NK128(nyo)001:8972: 'dus pa'i dbus su bka' stsal 'di skad gsungs //
NK128(nyo)001:8973: bu khyod tshe la bar chad ma byung na //
NK128(nyo)001:8974: 'jig rten 'di ni chos kyi 'khor lo sgyur //
NK128(nyo)001:8975: mdang gsum dkyil 'khor mtha' la kun bskor nas //
NK128(nyo)001:8976: bla ma zur chen rdog ston chen po dang //
NK128(nyo)001:8977: rje btsun grags pa 'phags pa rin po che //
NK128(nyo)001:8978: nam mkha'i snying po bsod nams bla ma dang //
NK128(nyo)001:8979: 'gro mgon myang dang ras chung rdor grags dang //
NK128(nyo)001:8980: rgyal sras dbang chen glo bo yab sras dang //
NK128(nyo)001:8981: chag lo chos dpal khro phu lo ts+aa dang //
NK128(nyo)001:8982: nag tsho lo ts+aa kun mkhyen mus srad pa //
NK128(nyo)001:8983: mkhas grub bsod bzang grub chen dmar zhabs dang //
NK128(nyo)001:8984: dam pa sangs rgyas bee ro bi ma la //
NK128(nyo)001:8985: o rgyan yab yum rgyal po khri srong dang //
NK128(nyo)001:8986: ma cig lab sgron zhang lo ras chen pa //
NK128(nyo)001:8987: khams pa sga lo rgya gar pan chen la //
NK128(nyo)001:8988: gcig la gcig blta 'dzum zhing bzhad pa la //
NK128(nyo)001:8989: kun kyang nga ni pad+ma dbang rgyal yin //
NK128(nyo)001:8990: smra zhing thams cad khyod la thim nas song //
NK128(nyo)001:8991: snyan brgyud thob pa khyod la dam chos kun //
NK128(nyo)001:8992: rang byan tshud bar 'dug go a bo ye //
NK128(nyo)001:8993: kha la nyon cig bshad sgrub brgyud pa bzung //
NK128(nyo)001:8994: khyed kyi mi brgyud sum cu rtsa bzhi'am //
NK128(nyo)001:8995: slob brgyud sum cu rtsa gnyis tshul bzung nas //
NK128(nyo)001:8996: phyogs mthar bstan pa'i rgyun lam yong bas na //
NK128(nyo)001:8997: sman gtor rak+ta rdul mtshon tshags gyis la //
NK128(nyo)001:8998: sangs rgyas bstan pa 'dzin skyong dbang bskur ro //
NK128(nyo)001:8999: de skad ces sogs lo rgyus mang po gsungs //
NK128(nyo)001:9000: zhes pa'i rnam thar 'di kho na yang blo'i rwa ba las 'das pa'i ngo mtshar gyi gnas so //
NK128(nyo)001:9001: 'di man chad mdor bsdus pa'i phyir rnam thar tshigs bcad kyi don lhug par bshad pa ni /
NK128(nyo)001:9002: dgung lo nyer gsum pa la 'jam dbyangs glo lo
NK128(nyo)001:9003: ts+aa bar gsung ngag rin po che lam 'bras bu
NK128(nyo)001:9004: dang bcas pa tshogs bshad dang slob bshad gnyis gsan
NK128(nyo)001:9005: tshul dang / de'i tshe yang bla ma nyid dgyes mdzad rdo rje dngos su gzigs /
NK128(nyo)001:9006: dgung lo nyer bzhi pa la yang lam 'bras tshar gcig gsan pa /
NK128(nyo)001:9007: nyer lnga pa la bsam grub gling du glo bo mkhan chen bsod nams lhun grub kyi mkhan po /
NK128(nyo)001:9008: 'khor lo sdom pa dkon mchog chos skyabs kyi slob
NK128(nyo)001:9009: dpon rab 'byams kun dag'i mtshan can gyis gsang ston
NK128(nyo)001:9010: / rab 'byams rgyal mtshan skyabs kyis grib tshod pa /
NK128(nyo)001:9011: rab 'byams bsod nams dpal bas grogs dan /
NK128(nyo)001:9014: mkhas dbang tshul khrims bzang po sogs dad pa'i dge slong nyi shu rtsa lnga'i dbus su /
NK128(nyo)001:9015: bu ston rin po che'i las chog gzhir bzhag la /
NK128(nyo)001:9016: nam bsod pa dang 'phags pa rin po che'i las
NK128(nyo)001:9017: chog sogs las bshad sbyar dang bcas te nyi byed
NK128(nyo)001:9018: la dge bsnyen / phyi ma red dge tshul /
NK128(nyo)001:9019: de'i phyi ma dge slong gi dngos por gyur te
NK128(nyo)001:9020: tshul gsum yongs su rdzogs pa'i tshul khrims rnam par
NK128(nyo)001:9021: dag pas thugs rgyud yongs su gtams pa'i mtshan dge
NK128(nyo)001:9022: slong pad+ma dbang rgyal grags pa rgyal mtshan dpal bzang
NK128(nyo)001:9023: po bstan pa'i rgyal mtshan du gsol lo //
NK128(nyo)001:9024: de nas mkhan slob de rnams las chos kyang mang du gsan /
NK128(nyo)001:9025: nyer drug pa la shel gyi ri bo 'brug sgra sogs kyi dben pa brten cing /
NK128(nyo)001:9026: chos gos gsum dang glegs bam /
NK128(nyo)001:9028: lhung bzed las gzhan pa'i yo byad spangs shing sgo
NK128(nyo)001:9029: gcig pa'i brtul zhugs bzung ste mnga' ris kyi gnas
NK128(nyo)001:9030: rten rnams mjal zhing dag snang dang lung bstan 'ga'
NK128(nyo)001:9031: yang thob cing / dad ldan rnams la dam pa'i chos kyang ci rigs su stsal /
NK128(nyo)001:9032: slar yang glo bor phebs te /
NK128(nyo)001:9033: yab rje dam pa nyid las rgyud lung man ngag rgya cher gsan zhing /
NK128(nyo)001:9034: glo bo mkhan chen la dgra gdong 'jigs byed /
NK128(nyo)001:9037: nyer bdun pa la mkhas btsun nam mkha'i mtshan can dang pad+ma 'bum sogs la chos gsan cing /
NK128(nyo)001:9038: po ta lar zla ba drug tu sku mtshams mdzad cing nyams khrid bskyangs /
NK128(nyo)001:9040: gu ge pan chen rnam rgyal dpal bzang dang /
NK128(nyo)001:9041: 'jam dbyangs blo gros dpal mgon rnams la sgra tshad
NK128(nyo)001:9042: brtag gnyis kyi bshad pa dbang gdams ngag sogs mang
NK128(nyo)001:9043: du gsan / spu rong dang te se kho char sogs gnas rten rnams mjal /
NK128(nyo)001:9044: slar yang glo bor byon te /
NK128(nyo)001:9045: drang po gter ston sh+aakya bzang po dang mjal zhing
NK128(nyo)001:9046: byang gter sgrub skor gsum sogs dbang chos mang du
NK128(nyo)001:9047: gsan / sgo le kha'i phug par byang gter spyan ras gzigs kyi bsnyen pa mdzad pas /
NK128(nyo)001:9048: mgon po gur gyi sku'i rnam 'gyur mi 'dra ba gsum gzigs /
NK128(nyo)001:9049: nyer brgyad bzhes dus glo bo mkhan chen las chos mang du gsan cing /
NK128(nyo)001:9050: dgung lo nyer dgu pa 'jam dbyangs kun bsam pa'i drung du bde mchog skor sogs mang du gsan /
NK128(nyo)001:9051: 'di lo dam pa mang por chos kyi bka' drin mang du gsan /
NK128(nyo)001:9052: gnas skor dang bde kye gsang gsum /
NK128(nyo)001:9054: yang dag rnams la bsnyen sgrub du ma mdzad /
NK128(nyo)001:9055: dgung lo sum cu par 'jam dbyangs blo gros dpal
NK128(nyo)001:9056: mgon la rdo rje gur sogs chos mang du gsan
NK128(nyo)001:9057: / dgung lo so gcig par glo bo mkhan chen las gsan bsam mang du mdzad /
NK128(nyo)001:9058: so gnyis par glo bo mkhan chen gyi zhabs 'bring du spu rong sogs la byon /
NK128(nyo)001:9059: de nas mkhan chen pa'i gsung bzhin slar yang skyid grong du byon nas jo bo mjal zhing /
NK128(nyo)001:9060: grub chen dkar po zhes lo brgya dang so drug
NK128(nyo)001:9061: lon pa'i drung du gsang 'dus ye shes zhabs lugs
NK128(nyo)001:9062: / bka' brgyad sogs gsar rnying mang du gsan /
NK128(nyo)001:9063: slar yang glo bo mkhan chen la lam 'bras kyi zhor chos gsan /
NK128(nyo)001:9064: sngags 'chang sh+aakya bzang por rta mgrin nyang lugs skor gsan /
NK128(nyo)001:9065: phyir 'khor nas glo bo'i rma bya shug rung gi
NK128(nyo)001:9066: phug par bde mchog lhan skyes dang mgon po zhal
NK128(nyo)001:9068: zhal bram gzugs dngos su byon nas gtor ma gsol zhing sgrub thabs kyi gnad gsungs /
NK128(nyo)001:9069: thag gcod gling zhes bya bar shing sdong gog po'i
NK128(nyo)001:9070: nang du thugs rje chen po'i sgrub pa mdzad pas
NK128(nyo)001:9071: / yang snying 'dus par sangs rgyas stong gis skor ba zhal gzigs /
NK128(nyo)001:9072: dgung lo so gsum par slar yang lam 'bras gzhung bshad dang bcas pa /
NK128(nyo)001:9073: bde mchog lo nag dril gsum /
NK128(nyo)001:9074: dus 'khor 'grel chen sogs mang du gsan /
NK128(nyo)001:9075: so bzhi par ku thang phyogs su byon /
NK128(nyo)001:9076: slar yang skyid grong gi 'phags pa mjal /
NK128(nyo)001:9077: sngags 'chang sh+aakya bzang por nyang gi gter skor mang du gsan /
NK128(nyo)001:9078: so lnga par ku thang rtsum gyi rtsig pa rkang
NK128(nyo)001:9079: thil phug tu rab 'byams chos rje las chos mang
NK128(nyo)001:9080: du gsan zhing gzhan yang dam pa du mar zab
NK128(nyo)001:9081: chos nos / gsang bdag gnyis pa rje sangs rgyas
NK128(nyo)001:9082: skyabs la phyag rdor che ba brgyad bskor gsan phyir
NK128(nyo)001:9083: gangs la sogs la dka' ba mang du spyad de
NK128(nyo)001:9084: byon nas phyag rdor skor gsan dus re rer yang
NK128(nyo)001:9085: ngo mtshar gyi ltas mang du byung zhing /
NK128(nyo)001:9086: khyad par u tsa ya drag sngags kyi che ba'i dbang gi dus /
NK128(nyo)001:9087: bla ma gsang bdag tu gyur pa'i zhal nas ha ha dang hi hi h'u h'u gsung zhing /
NK128(nyo)001:9088: phyag gi rdo rje las me dpung thul thul chad
NK128(nyo)001:9089: cing nam mkha' la khyung gi dmag dpung 'khrigs pa
NK128(nyo)001:9090: sogs byung zhing / chos bsgugs mang du dgos pa byung yang tshang bar gsan cing /
NK128(nyo)001:9092: mnga' gsol du ma mdzad de phyir byon nas /
NK128(nyo)001:9093: gang phebs su chos kyi 'phrin las rgya cher bskyangs /
NK128(nyo)001:9094: rab 'byams dkon cog bsam 'grub pa'i drung du ras
NK128(nyo)001:9095: chung snyan rgyud kyi dbang khrid gdams pa rdzogs par
NK128(nyo)001:9096: gsan cing / gzhan yang phyag chen /
NK128(nyo)001:9099: yang dgon pa'i ri chos sogs mang du gsan /
NK128(nyo)001:9100: dgung lo so lnga pa slar yang skyid grong phyogs
NK128(nyo)001:9101: su byon nas sngags 'chang sh+aakya bzang por nyang gi
NK128(nyo)001:9103: khros nag sogs chos lhag ma rnams rdzogs par gsan
NK128(nyo)001:9104: te bal bor byon so drug bal yul shing kun
NK128(nyo)001:9108: yam bu rgya gar gyi grub chen sha ba ri pa dang mjal /
NK128(nyo)001:9109: bal yul yang le shod du zhag bdun bzhugs /
NK128(nyo)001:9110: o rgyan chen po la sgrub sde brgyad kyi lhas bskor ba'i zhal gzigs /
NK128(nyo)001:9111: bal po'i bla ma dz+ny+aa na sh+r+ai yab sras las mi g.yo /
NK128(nyo)001:9117: rim bzhin bla ma dang gnas rten mjal zhing nyan
NK128(nyo)001:9118: bshad kyis dus 'da' ba nas glo bor byon te
NK128(nyo)001:9119: ngor chen lha mchog bzang por yang lam 'bras tshar
NK128(nyo)001:9120: gcig dang zab chos mang du gsan /
NK128(nyo)001:9121: dgung lo so bdun pa la glo bo smad dge lung du thugs dam mdzad /
NK128(nyo)001:9122: slob dpon a b+h+ya ka ra'i skye bar mkha' 'gros lung bstan te /
NK128(nyo)001:9123: lo chen dkon cog chos skyabs las rdo rje 'phreng
NK128(nyo)001:9124: ba'i dbang rdzogs par gsan dus thog mar bla ma
NK128(nyo)001:9125: des dbang mi gnang ba'i rtsis mdzad pa'i tshe mtshan
NK128(nyo)001:9126: lam du bde mchog sku gsung thugs dkyil yongs su
NK128(nyo)001:9127: rdzogs pa'i dkyil 'khor gyi gtso bo pan chen pad+ma
NK128(nyo)001:9129: de yang zhal bzhi phyag bcu gnyis pa'i rnam par gyur pa zhig 'dug par /
NK128(nyo)001:9130: mkha' 'gro ma'i cha byad cig gis bsrungs nas nang
NK128(nyo)001:9131: du ma btang ba'i ltas byung bas thugs 'gyod cing
NK128(nyo)001:9132: dbang bskur yongs rdzogs dang lam 'bras dmar ma sogs
NK128(nyo)001:9133: gnang zhing shel gyi sum mdor bde mchog bong zhal
NK128(nyo)001:9134: can gyi ljags bsnyen mdzad pas /
NK128(nyo)001:9135: thun gcig la gnam sa thams cad khrag 'thung sum cu so bdun du gzigs /
NK128(nyo)001:9136: so brgyad pa la gsar rnying gi chos 'khor rgya cher bskor /
NK128(nyo)001:9137: so dgu pa la yang gsan bsam mang du mdzad /
NK128(nyo)001:9138: bzhi bcu pa'i dgung mor rdo rje 'phreng ba'i dkyil
NK128(nyo)001:9139: 'khor thams cad la bsnyen par rdzogs par mdzad pas
NK128(nyo)001:9140: / deng sang gi phreng ba mkhan po rnams kyi
NK128(nyo)001:9141: tshod na 'di gcig pu yang ngo mtshar che ba
NK128(nyo)001:9142: / 'dra / zhe gcig pa la yang glo bo
NK128(nyo)001:9143: mkhan chen pa'i phyag phyir byon te zab chos du
NK128(nyo)001:9144: / 'dra / ma gsan cing / gsar rnying ris
NK128(nyo)001:9145: su ma bcad pa'i dbang khrid gdams pas gdul bya
NK128(nyo)001:9146: / 'dra / ma gsan cing / mang po bskyangs
NK128(nyo)001:9147: / yab rje 'jam dbyangs chen po'i bka'i bsdu ba
NK128(nyo)001:9148: / 'dra / ma gsan cing / mang po bskyangs
NK128(nyo)001:9149: / rnams mdzad / de nas glo bo mkhan chen
NK128(nyo)001:9150: pa'i bkas bskul nas dbus gtsang gi phyogs su gsar
NK128(nyo)001:9151: rnying ris su ma chad pa'i chos rgyun nyams pa
NK128(nyo)001:9152: rnams gso ba'i phyir 'byon par bzhed de /
NK128(nyo)001:9153: yab rje 'jam dbyangs rin cen rgyal mtshan la gnang ba zhus /
NK128(nyo)001:9154: de bzhin du glo bo'i sde bdag sogs kun la khrol cha zhu bar mdzad dus /
NK128(nyo)001:9155: yab rje dam pa nyid kyis kyang khyod 'di phyogs
NK128(nyo)001:9156: su sdad na dgos pa'i khyad par 'ga' zhig 'dug
NK128(nyo)001:9157: mod kyang yang yang 'gro stabs bcag pas da res
NK128(nyo)001:9158: ci bde bar mdzod cig ces bslab bya /
NK128(nyo)001:9161: phyi phyag mdzad de dbus gtsang gi phyogs su rgyal
NK128(nyo)001:9162: ba'i bstan pa riin po che gso ba'i thugs bskyed
NK128(nyo)001:9163: rnam par dag pa dang bcas te byon no //
NK128(nyo)001:9164: 'di yan chad du mnga' ris glo bo skyid grong
NK128(nyo)001:9165: sogs kyi mkhas btsun rnams la dam pa'i chos gsan
NK128(nyo)001:9166: bsam mdzad cing / gtso bor 'jam dbyangs zhal gnyis
NK128(nyo)001:9167: zhes yab rje 'jam dbyangs rin cen rgyal mtshan dang
NK128(nyo)001:9168: glo bo mkhan chen bsod nams lhun grub legs pa'i
NK128(nyo)001:9169: 'byung gnas nyid kyi zhabs phyir bcar bzhugs mdzad de
NK128(nyo)001:9170: gsan pas mdzad pa yin no //
NK128(nyo)001:9171: de nas rim bzhin byon te zang zang lha brag
NK128(nyo)001:9172: dang ri bo bkra bzang du byon smon lam dang
NK128(nyo)001:9173: gnas gzigs mdzad / byang ngam ring gi sa'i cha
NK128(nyo)001:9174: dgon pa bde grol du thugs sras nam mkha' rgyal
NK128(nyo)001:9175: gnas gzigs mdzad / mtshan dang / drang po sngags 'chang sh+aakya bzang po gnyis bzhugs pa dang mjal /
NK128(nyo)001:9176: gcung legs ldan rje yang der zang thal gsan pa'i skabs yin pas /
NK128(nyo)001:9177: dgung lo zhe gnyis par sku mched lhan du dbus
NK128(nyo)001:9178: la phebs te gtsang pa phug tu sngags 'chang rgya
NK128(nyo)001:9179: hor rdo rje dang mjal te 'od gsal gsang skor
