NK128(nyo)001:9180: dang sgyu 'phrul tshe dbang sogs gsan /
NK128(nyo)001:9181: rin spungs nas rong chung brgyud 'di bar gtsang du
NK128(nyo)001:9182: lo gcig bzhugs nas zhe gsum par chos 'khor lha
NK128(nyo)001:9183: sar phebs te / lha sa ra mo che /
NK128(nyo)001:9184: pho brang dmar lcang sogs la phyag skor dang smon
NK128(nyo)001:9185: lam mdzad de rngog chos dang zhi byed kyi chos
NK128(nyo)001:9186: la thugs 'dun gtad de smon lam mdzad pas /
NK128(nyo)001:9187: rdze btsun ma sgrol ma'i lung bstan dang /
NK128(nyo)001:9188: khyad par dpal lha sa bar skor gsum gyi ring
NK128(nyo)001:9189: dngos su byon te gsung gleng mang du mdzad cing
NK128(nyo)001:9190: lung bstan pa / khyed dri med lta ba'i don rtogs kyang /
NK128(nyo)001:9191: ring 'gro drug gi don bsam pa /
NK128(nyo)001:9192: lus da lan tsam las len mi 'tshal /
NK128(nyo)001:9193: chos sdug bsngal gyi phung po zhi byed de /
NK128(nyo)001:9194: dus myur du khyed kyis longs par nges /
NK128(nyo)001:9195: rje na ro dang me tra'i gdams ngag la /
NK128(nyo)001:9196: dus da lta rngog ston gzhung ba mkhas /
NK128(nyo)001:9197: gnad bsre 'pho de re zhig tsam nas longs /
NK128(nyo)001:9198: dus da lan gung thang phyogs su song /
NK128(nyo)001:9199: don smra rgyu bral ba'i blo thag chod ces gsungs
NK128(nyo)001:9200: pa ltar gung thang du byon nas phyag skor mdzad
NK128(nyo)001:9201: / de nas slar yang zhi byed dang rngog chos
NK128(nyo)001:9202: kyi khungs lung bstan bskyar ma byung ba'i don bzhin
NK128(nyo)001:9203: sku mched gnyis kas klur brgyad 'u shang rngo mjal
NK128(nyo)001:9204: / zhing / kam pa la'i rtse nas gzhung la phyag mchod mdzad /
NK128(nyo)001:9205: lum pa grur byon pas gzhung mda' nya mo kyur
NK128(nyo)001:9206: ru dud sol mas bsu ba'i tshul du zhal bstan
NK128(nyo)001:9207: / gzhung spre'u zhing dang khyad par thar pa gling
NK128(nyo)001:9208: du rngog rin po che bsod nams bstan 'dzin la
NK128(nyo)001:9209: rngog dkyil rnams legs par gsan zhing thugs thag chod
NK128(nyo)001:9210: / / grwa thang du zha lu lo chen chos skyong bzang po la gshed dmar skor sogs gsan /
NK128(nyo)001:9211: chos 'khor bsam yas su phyag phebs te gnas rten rnams mjal sngon gyi bag chags du ma sad /
NK128(nyo)001:9212: bar khang du bka' brgyad bde gshegs 'dus pa'i /
NK128(nyo)001:9213: dkyil 'khor sogs mang du bzhengs nas sgrub mchod dang smon lam mdzad /
NK128(nyo)001:9214: lho brag g+hu ru ba sogs la dam chos mang du gsungs /
NK128(nyo)001:9215: kahthoga pa chos rje bsod nams rgyal mtshan sogs bshes gnyen mang po chos skyes 'bul res mdzad /
NK128(nyo)001:9216: de nas 'phreng phu o rgyan chos rdzong du byon nas /
NK128(nyo)001:9217: kong chen rin po che nam mkha' dpal ldan rgya
NK128(nyo)001:9218: mtsho la bla ma dgongs 'dus sogs gsan cing thugs
NK128(nyo)001:9219: yid 'dres / yang rdzogs dang mchims phur byon thugs dam mdzad pas rtsa gsum mang po'i zhal gzigs /
NK128(nyo)001:9220: slar yang gtsang phyogs su phyir thegs bzhed kyang gu
NK128(nyo)001:9221: ru chos dbang gi gdung rabs brgyad pa sprul sku
NK128(nyo)001:9222: chos kyi dbang po'i bka' bzhin lho brag tu dgung
NK128(nyo)001:9223: lo zhe bzhi bar byon nas zhe lnga'i bar du
NK128(nyo)001:9224: bzhugs shing / lho brag mkhar chu /
NK128(nyo)001:9225: bsam grub bde ba chen po'i gtsug lag khang /
NK128(nyo)001:9226: lha bro dang smra bo lcog /
NK128(nyo)001:9227: gro bo lung la sogs par phebs /
NK128(nyo)001:9228: myang rin po cher u rgyan dngos kyi lung bstan te /
NK128(nyo)001:9229: mnga' ris pan chen rin po che chos brgyud kyi
NK128(nyo)001:9230: nyams pa gso bar gsungs pa'i don mngon du gyur
NK128(nyo)001:9231: te myang gi gdung sgang zur sogs la rang lugs
NK128(nyo)001:9232: kyi nyan bshad sna tshogs mdzad /
NK128(nyo)001:9233: sprul sku chos kyi dbang por yang chos mang du gsan cing phul /
NK128(nyo)001:9236: khong gi sku dgra la zhag gsum nas rtags ston pa sogs zhabs tog mang du bsgrubs /
NK128(nyo)001:9237: lho brag tu sdig can zhig la gnas spor mdzad
NK128(nyo)001:9238: de 'ja' 'od kyi bar snang bkang ba sogs snga
NK128(nyo)001:9240: lho brag zhal stod dang btsan gro sogs su bka'
NK128(nyo)001:9241: brgyad sgrub chen mdzad de sman sgrub dang skye bdun
NK128(nyo)001:9243: khyad par bka' brgyad bde gshegs 'dus pa tshar nyer
NK128(nyo)001:9244: lnga gsan pa'i phyi ma khungs btsun zhing thugs thag
NK128(nyo)001:9245: chod pa dgon dkar du grub chen bde gshegs 'dus
NK128(nyo)001:9248: gsang rdzogs dong sprugs sogs mang du gsan nas 'di
NK128(nyo)001:9249: la basngagasa brjod shin tu che ba rnam thar dang
NK128(nyo)001:9251: grub chen 'di yang ri brag la thogs pa med par bya ltar lding /
NK128(nyo)001:9252: mthar zhing du byon skabs ngo mtshar gyi ltas du ma bstan pa zhig yin pas /
NK128(nyo)001:9253: pan chen rin po ches mdzad pa'i bka' brgyad bde
NK128(nyo)001:9254: gshegs 'dus pa'i 'chad thabs mun sel nyi zla'i 'khor
NK128(nyo)001:9255: lor gsal / lho brag phyogs su rnying ma bka'
NK128(nyo)001:9256: gter gyi 'chad nyan mang du mdzad nas phyir gri
NK128(nyo)001:9257: gu brgyud bsam yas su phebs te /
NK128(nyo)001:9258: zhe drug par bsam yas bar khang du mkha' 'gro snying thig /
NK128(nyo)001:9259: gsang 'dus rim lnga sogs bsam yas su chos rgyal lha'i gdung rnams la gsungs /
NK128(nyo)001:9260: de'i tshe gcung legs ldan rjes lho brag srin mo
NK128(nyo)001:9261: sbar rjes can gyi kha byang rnyed pa dang bstun
NK128(nyo)001:9262: nas / bsam yas dbu rtse'i steng khang rnam snang
NK128(nyo)001:9263: gsang sgrom nas zab chos rig 'dzin yongs 'dus sogs
NK128(nyo)001:9265: snga phyi zab gter lnga spyan drangs bar grags /
NK128(nyo)001:9266: de nas re zhig gtsang du byon te yar res snye mor dgongs 'dus sgrub chen btsugs /
NK128(nyo)001:9267: phung po ri bo cher bde 'dus kyi 'chad nyan mdzad /
NK128(nyo)001:9268: ngor e wam chos ldan dang thub bstan gser mdog can sogs su byon nas /
NK128(nyo)001:9269: de rnams su dge tshul slong gi las kyi cho ga mang du mdzad /
NK128(nyo)001:9270: nyang stod zhwa lu sogs la phebs te gnas skor dang 'gro phan 'chad nyan rgya cher mdzad nas /
NK128(nyo)001:9271: zhe bdun par rong chen brgyud dbus su slar phebs
NK128(nyo)001:9272: te dpal chen chu bo ri nas snying phur byon
NK128(nyo)001:9273: / de nas sgrags phu ri zangs mdog tu byang
NK128(nyo)001:9274: gter sgrub skor gsum dang bka' brgyad rang shar zang
NK128(nyo)001:9275: thal yang phur sogs 'chad nyan rgya cher mdzad /
NK128(nyo)001:9276: de nas gzhung du byon nas rngog chos kyi lhag ma rnams dang bsre 'pho sogs gsan cing /
NK128(nyo)001:9277: bde mchog dang bir wa ba /
NK128(nyo)001:9278: bdag med lha mo bco lnga /
NK128(nyo)001:9279: gur lcam dral sogs kyi dag snang dpag med shar /
NK128(nyo)001:9280: de nas phyir byon te lum pa gru ba rgyud
NK128(nyo)001:9281: rdo rje brag gi dgon pa btab ma zin kyang
NK128(nyo)001:9282: de skabs dang da lta dgon pa yod par grong
NK128(nyo)001:9283: khyim zhol 'dra yod tshod nas der bzhugs shing sku
NK128(nyo)001:9285: brag phug pa'i rten 'brel sogs las phyogs der gsang
NK128(nyo)001:9286: sngags kyi bstan pa dang rjes 'jug 'byung ba'i brda
NK128(nyo)001:9289: brag rdo rje ru nub gcig ngal gsol //
NK128(nyo)001:9290: lo skor gcig tshe srog 'khyol ba'i brda //
NK128(nyo)001:9291: sa de nyid nas slar yang shar la phyin //
NK128(nyo)001:9292: brag phug pa'i dbal kha thur du zug /
NK128(nyo)001:9293: brda de kun yang snang stong zung 'jug gi //
NK128(nyo)001:9294: lam bskyed rdzogs kyi bstan pa zin pa'i brda //
NK128(nyo)001:9295: slar de nas kyang rjes 'jug rnam pa brgyad //
NK128(nyo)001:9296: mi bdag nyid la rjes su phyir 'brang ba //
NK128(nyo)001:9297: phyogs mtshams brgyad nas brgyud 'dzin yong ba'i brda //
NK128(nyo)001:9299: thub bstan rdo rje brag tu pan chen sku mched
NK128(nyo)001:9300: byang ba yab sras nas rim brgyud snga 'gyur gyi
NK128(nyo)001:9301: bstan pa dang khyad par rje btsun nyid kyi rjes
NK128(nyo)001:9302: 'jug rgyud 'dzin 'byung ba'i lung bstan rdo rje'i gsung
NK128(nyo)001:9303: du go / de nas phal cher bsam yas bu
NK128(nyo)001:9304: tshal gyi lcog tu bzhugs shing phyogs bral gdul bya'i
NK128(nyo)001:9306: rgyal ba'i bstan pa rin po che mtha' dag gso zhing /
NK128(nyo)001:9307: snga 'gyur bka' gter dam pa'i chos kyi 'phrin las
NK128(nyo)001:9308: bskyangs pas dgung lo zhe bdun yan zhal gsungs kho
NK128(nyo)001:9309: na ltar gung sgrigs pa yin /
NK128(nyo)001:9310: 'di man chad lo rtsis sogs zhib par ma gyur kyang /
NK128(nyo)001:9311: rig 'dzin rje'i rnam thar dang pan chen rang gi
NK128(nyo)001:9312: gsang ba'i rnam thar sogs las dpyad de cung 'dri
NK128(nyo)001:9313: na / byams pa gling du lo chen bsod nams rnam rgyal la sangs rgyas mnyam sbyor gsan cing /
NK128(nyo)001:9314: mkha' 'gro' snying thig gi dbang khrid rnams phul te thugs yid gcig 'dres su gyur pa rnams dang /
NK128(nyo)001:9315: rje btsun bsod nams rgyal mchog las byams gling pa'i
NK128(nyo)001:9316: chos skor gzhan rnams gsan pa sogs ni gsung las
NK128(nyo)001:9317: / mnga' ris stod kyi ma thang pa //
NK128(nyo)001:9318: pad+ma dbang rgyal rdo rje yis //
NK128(nyo)001:9319: chos phyir lus srog thed la bor //
NK128(nyo)001:9320: rgya gar yul gyi sa mtshams nas //
NK128(nyo)001:9321: dwags kong bar gyi sa ru phyin //
NK128(nyo)001:9322: dam chos khungs ldan thams cad btsal //
NK128(nyo)001:9323: bka' dang bstan bcos du ma nyan //
NK128(nyo)001:9324: khyad par g.yo ru grwa nang gi //
NK128(nyo)001:9325: byams pa gling du rje dang mjal //
NK128(nyo)001:9326: spyi bshad dkyil 'khor nam mkha' gang //
NK128(nyo)001:9327: u rgyan yab yum gsang 'dus gshed dmar sogs //
NK128(nyo)001:9328: gang snang lha yi 'khor lor gyur pa kun //
NK128(nyo)001:9329: gnas lugs lta ba nyid dang bsdebs te byas //
NK128(nyo)001:9331: bstan pa yongs rdzogs kyi bshes gnyen chen po yin tshul yang /
NK128(nyo)001:9333: chos rdzogs chen gyi ri rgyal rtse mor phyin //
NK128(nyo)001:9334: gnad grub chen gyi bka' brgyad gling bzhir gdal //
NK128(nyo)001:9335: lam 'bras bu yi nyi zla mkha' la 'char //
NK128(nyo)001:9336: dus 'khor lo'i dbyings su rtsal snang rdzogs //
NK128(nyo)001:9337: chos phyag chen gyi 'dod yon ro brgya myong //
NK128(nyo)001:9338: lam chos drug gi zlos gar ci yang rtse //
NK128(nyo)001:9339: rdzong dbu ma'i khang par skyid nyal byas //
NK128(nyo)001:9340: bka' mdo sde'i dkor nor ci yang bsags //
NK128(nyo)001:9341: lung 'dul ba'i skye tshal kun nas mdzes //
NK128(nyo)001:9342: g.yog bsre 'pho'i bang phyin thabs re mkhas //
NK128(nyo)001:9343: rgyu blo sbyong gi sa rgya mang du bcad //
NK128(nyo)001:9344: dgra jag gi steng du gcod yul bskyangs //
NK128(nyo)001:9345: bdud zhi byed kyi sman pa mkhas pas zin //
NK128(nyo)001:9346: gnas rigs gsum kha lo 'khor lo sdom //
NK128(nyo)001:9347: sangs rgyas kyi sa ru gsang ba 'dus //
NK128(nyo)001:9348: rig 'dzin gyi gral du dgyes rdor nga //
NK128(nyo)001:9349: bdud bzhi yi dgra la nag cing rngams //
NK128(nyo)001:9350: gdong drug gi nga ro phyogs brgyar sgrog /
NK128(nyo)001:9351: srid zhi yi dgra bo 'jigs par byed //
NK128(nyo)001:9352: nga bdag gi rtsa ba gshed dmar po //
NK128(nyo)001:9353: sgyu ma yi chos la chen po rol //
NK128(nyo)001:9354: sangs rgyas kyi sa ru mnyam sbyor ba //
NK128(nyo)001:9355: dpal chen mchog gi rdo rje sems //
NK128(nyo)001:9357: rnam rtog dra ba chos skur sdom //
NK128(nyo)001:9358: rang byung gi ye shes kun tu bzang //
NK128(nyo)001:9360: blo gros la nang byan rnyed nas gda' //
NK128(nyo)001:9361: snang ba sems su rtogs nas gda' //
NK128(nyo)001:9362: sems nyid kyang gsal stong rdo rje dbyings //
NK128(nyo)001:9363: mi nga rang dang dkon cog gcig tu 'dres //
NK128(nyo)001:9364: don 'di nyid kyang rang byung rang gi rtsal //
NK128(nyo)001:9365: rang grol gyi ngang nas khrol lo lo //
NK128(nyo)001:9366: rang gsal gyi rnam thar kun tu shar //
NK128(nyo)001:9367: thams cad kyang de don bsam shes na //
NK128(nyo)001:9368: rang nyid dang dbyer med rdo rje 'gyur //
NK128(nyo)001:9370: de ltar mnga' ris pan chen mkhyen rab dbang bskur
NK128(nyo)001:9371: de nyid skabs 'ga' yang 'on phyogs su byon nas
NK128(nyo)001:9372: gdul bya bskyangs / khyad par sngags 'dul che sogs zhus /
NK128(nyo)001:9373: de nas grwa phyir rgya ston gyi //
NK128(nyo)001:9374: dgon gnas lcags ri zhes byar phyin //
NK128(nyo)001:9375: bya spyod rgyud kyi rnam bshad zhus //
NK128(nyo)001:9377: gzhan yang nyan thos rnam pa bdun /
NK128(nyo)001:9378: bde mchog chos skyong sde lnga la sogs kyi zhal mang po gzigs /
NK128(nyo)001:9379: bsam yas mchims phur rgyal ba mchog dbyangs kyi phug par sku 'tshams mdzad dus /
NK128(nyo)001:9380: chos rgyal khri srong dang gu ru chos dbang gi sprul par lung bstan thob /
NK128(nyo)001:9381: bka' brgyad 'dus pa'i bdag nyid du dbugs dbyung zhing
NK128(nyo)001:9382: dam can rnams bran du 'khol ba'i lung bstan gzugs
NK128(nyo)001:9383: med pa'i sgra las 'di ltar byung ste /
NK128(nyo)001:9384: bde ba can na rang byung ba //
NK128(nyo)001:9385: po ta la ru mngon par snang //
NK128(nyo)001:9387: khyod na khri srong lde'u btsan //
NK128(nyo)001:9388: bde gshegs thams cad gcig yin te //
NK128(nyo)001:9389: ting 'dzin kun kyang de bzhin no //
NK128(nyo)001:9390: gcig dang tha dad med pa yi //
NK128(nyo)001:9391: sprul pa thams cad bsdus pa ni //
NK128(nyo)001:9393: rdo rje'i brag lhar mnyam sbyor ba //
NK128(nyo)001:9394: ded dpon sum cu phyi bzhin 'brang //
NK128(nyo)001:9396: gzhan yang bla ma rig 'dzin gyi khrom tshogs 'dus te 'di skad gsungs so //
NK128(nyo)001:9400: khyod kyi srog pa rtsa nyid las //
NK128(nyo)001:9401: che mchog yon tan gter rnams 'byung //
NK128(nyo)001:9402: snying la yang dag thugs gter 'byung //
NK128(nyo)001:9403: sha la 'jam dpal sku yi gter //
NK128(nyo)001:9404: lce dang khrag la pad+ma gsung //
NK128(nyo)001:9405: rgyu ma nang khrol nyid la ni //
NK128(nyo)001:9406: rbod gtong ma mo'i gter chen 'byung //
NK128(nyo)001:9407: klad pa la ni rdo rje dbyings //
NK128(nyo)001:9408: rus pa rtsig khyim rkang rnams las //
NK128(nyo)001:9410: rkang dang khu ba mig dang tshil //
NK128(nyo)001:9411: bla med don rdzogs rnal 'byor gsum //
NK128(nyo)001:9412: chos rnams snying po gter gyi mdzod //
NK128(nyo)001:9413: khyod nyid yin par mngon brjod bya //
NK128(nyo)001:9415: yi dam zhal gzigs tshul yang bka' las /
NK128(nyo)001:9416: che mchog rdor dbyings rdo rje thod pa dang //
NK128(nyo)001:9417: dus 'khor bde mchog 'khor chen gdan bzhi dang //
NK128(nyo)001:9418: bka' brgyad dkyil 'khor dgu yi gzhal yas khang //
NK128(nyo)001:9419: rgyud sde kun gyi 'di bar cung zad chad snyams
NK128(nyo)001:9420: &a&a&a&a&ariga 'dzin rje dang sku mched lhan cig par 'on
NK128(nyo)001:9421: smon ldan du gzims khang btab nas rgyun ring bar
NK128(nyo)001:9422: bzhugs / gcung legs ldan rjes thugs 'khos mdzad de
NK128(nyo)001:9423: bstan 'gro'i bde thabs su gzigs nas bsam yas su
NK128(nyo)001:9424: rje 'bri gung pa rin chen phun tshogs spyan drangs
NK128(nyo)001:9425: bzhugs / te / mnga' ris pan+di ta chen po mched gnyis dang /
NK128(nyo)001:9426: chos rgyal 'bri gung pa rin chen phun tshogs te
NK128(nyo)001:9427: bla ma dam pa gsum gyis rab gnas mnga' gsol
NK128(nyo)001:9428: sogs rten 'brel mang du mdzad pas /
NK128(nyo)001:9429: bod khams su lo bcu gsum gyi bar bde skyid 'byung ba'i rten 'brel 'grig /
NK128(nyo)001:9430: zla gcig ring zhabs tog tshang ma rig 'dzin rjes mdzad pa yin /
NK128(nyo)001:9431: de nas gcung legs ldan rje lho 'bras mo gshongs kyi gnas sgo 'byed pa sogs la phebs /
NK128(nyo)001:9432: pan chen rin po ches 'on bsam gnyis su bzhugs nas bstan 'gro'i don rgya cher mdzad do //
NK128(nyo)001:9433: mdor na bla ma dam pa 'di nyid ni bod
NK128(nyo)001:9434: yul du grags pa'i mdo sngags gsar rnying gi gzhung
NK128(nyo)001:9435: lugs yongs su grags pa phal cher dang /
NK128(nyo)001:9436: rig pa'i gnas mtha' dag la mkhas shing nges par
NK128(nyo)001:9437: don gyi pan+di ta chen po tshad med pa'i mkhyen
NK128(nyo)001:9438: rab can 'chad rtsod rtsom gsum gyi gter chen por
NK128(nyo)001:9439: gyur pas sdom gsum rnam nges sogs kyi gsung rab
NK128(nyo)001:9440: kyang mang du mdzad pa'i tshig don thams cad zab
NK128(nyo)001:9441: cing barlingasa / so sor thar pa'i tshul khrims rnam par dag pa /
NK128(nyo)001:9442: sdor dkar gdan gcig gi brtul zhugs bzung nas chos
NK128(nyo)001:9443: gos rnam pa gsum sogs dge slong gi mkho ba'i
NK128(nyo)001:9444: yo byad dang / sku gsung thugs rten dbang rdzas
NK128(nyo)001:9445: dang dkyil 'khor sgrub pa'i yo byad 'ga' zhig las
NK128(nyo)001:9446: bdag tu mi 'dzin pa bka' gdams kyi dge ba'i
NK128(nyo)001:9447: bshes gnyen shin tu gtsang ba'i mthar thug pa rnams
NK128(nyo)001:9448: kyi dpe zlar 'os shing btsun pa /
NK128(nyo)001:9449: byang chub sems kyi sdom pas thugs rgyud yongs su
NK128(nyo)001:9450: gtams te sems can kho na'i don las skad cig
NK128(nyo)001:9451: kyang mi g.yel ba'i brtse ba chen po /
NK128(nyo)001:9452: gsang sngags rdo rje theg pa'i sdom pa dang dam
NK128(nyo)001:9453: tshig rnams ji ltar rgyud las bshad pa ltar tshul
NK128(nyo)001:9454: bzhin du bsrung bas nyes ltung gi dri ma thams
NK128(nyo)001:9456: dkyil 'khor rgya mtsho'i khyab bdag rdo rje 'chang chen po /
NK128(nyo)001:9457: gsar rnying gi rim gnyis zab mo rnams thun bzhir brtson pas nyams su bzhes shing /
NK128(nyo)001:9458: gtso bo 'od gsal rdzogs pa chen po'i dgongs pa
NK128(nyo)001:9459: 'khor yug tu gdal bas 'khor 'das rig pa'i klong
NK128(nyo)001:9460: du rang sar grol ba'i grub pa mthar phyin pa'i
NK128(nyo)001:9461: rtags tshad du ma mngon sum du ston nus pa
NK128(nyo)001:9462: / de'i dbang gis 'phrin las rnam pa bzhi la thogs pa med par nus pa'i bdag nyid can /
NK128(nyo)001:9463: gu ru pad+mas zab mo'i gter kha rnams las gsal bar lung gis bstan cing /
NK128(nyo)001:9464: khyad par rang gter rig 'dzin yongs 'dus dang gu ru drag po sogs las /
NK128(nyo)001:9465: u rgyan chen po rig 'dzin brgyad sogs dang dgongs pa gnyis su med par lung bstan cing /
NK128(nyo)001:9466: &&&&tha na zhal chab dang gsang chab myong zhing mtshan
NK128(nyo)001:9467: lan gcig thos pa rnams kyang 'khor ba mtha' can
NK128(nyo)001:9468: du 'gyur bar gsungs pa'i 'brel tshad don ldan gyi
NK128(nyo)001:9470: mdor na dam pa 'di'i rnam par thar pa ni
NK128(nyo)001:9471: bdag sogs tshur mthong gi blo can gyis brjod pa'i
NK128(nyo)001:9473: 'dir dad pa'i sa bon tsam du mdo tsam zhig bris pa yin la /
NK128(nyo)001:9474: rgyas par rnam thar rin chen 'phreng ba dang gsang ba'i rnam thar rin po che'i rna rgyan dang /
NK128(nyo)001:9475: gsan yig dang bka' 'bum sogs las shes par bya'o //
NK128(nyo)001:9476: de ltar re zhig zhing 'di'i gdul bya rdzogs par mkhyen nas /
NK128(nyo)001:9477: nye gnas rin rdor ba sogs sku 'khor rnams la zhal gdams dang /
NK128(nyo)001:9478: khyad par pan chen rin po che rang gi nye
NK128(nyo)001:9479: bar gnas pa'i 'khor sum ldan rdo rje 'dzin pa'i
NK128(nyo)001:9480: lcog grwa chung ngu yang dag pa'i bsam gtan pa
NK128(nyo)001:9481: / bstan pa yongs rdzogs kyi sde nyung zad cig yod pa de la gnas skabs su dgongs shing /
NK128(nyo)001:9482: ma 'ongs pa na dgos pa rgya chen po gzigs te /
NK128(nyo)001:9483: lcog sgar bsgrigs kyi bka' yig rdo rje 'bar ba'i gzi byin zhes pa zhal /
NK128(nyo)001:9484: gdams su bzhag pa deng sang yang e wam lcog
NK128(nyo)001:9485: sgar ba'i bca' yig gi rtsa ba yang de yin
NK128(nyo)001:9486: no // de nas mdzad pa tha ma ni 'on
NK128(nyo)001:9487: smon ldan gyi bla brang du stag lo zla ba
NK128(nyo)001:9488: brgyad pa'i tshes gnyis la 'ja' 'od rol mo'i sgra
NK128(nyo)001:9489: dang bcas te zab mo chos kyi dbyings su mnyam
NK128(nyo)001:9491: sku gdung rin po che mchod de sbyangs shing ngo mtshar gyis kun tu khyab bo //
NK128(nyo)001:9492: gdung yid bzhin gyi nor bu zhugs la phul ba'i
NK128(nyo)001:9493: gyang logs la bkra shis sgo mang gi mchod rten
NK128(nyo)001:9494: byis pa deng sang yang smon ldan bla brang na
NK128(nyo)001:9495: yod do // de ltar dgongs rdzogs kyi bya ba rnams grub rjes nye gnas sangs rgyas snying pos /
NK128(nyo)001:9496: gcung legs ldan zhabs lho 'bras gshongs kyi phyogs su bzhugs pa spyan drangs te /
NK128(nyo)001:9497: 'on du phebs nas phyi rten du rje btsun dam
NK128(nyo)001:9498: pa mkhyen rab dbang phyug nyid kyi gzims mal sku
NK128(nyo)001:9499: 'dra / u rgyan rin po che'i sku dang /
NK128(nyo)001:9500: thugs rten mchod rten rnams sman 'dam las bzhengs /
NK128(nyo)001:9501: 'di skabs pan chen mched gnyis ka mkhas btsun grub
NK128(nyo)001:9502: pa'i sa la gangs can gyi ljongs 'dir 'gran pa'i
NK128(nyo)001:9503: zla thams cad dang bral ba zhig yin na'ang /
NK128(nyo)001:9504: 'jig rten zang zing gi thad nas deng sang gi
NK128(nyo)001:9505: bla chen lta bu rta zhon ber gyon gyi chos
NK128(nyo)001:9506: brgyad la bskyed 'phel gtong mkhan ma yin par /
NK128(nyo)001:9507: mched gnyis ka bya bral kun tu rgyur song bas
NK128(nyo)001:9508: bla ma zhing la gshegs pa'i sku chas hab thob
NK128(nyo)001:9509: la mi 'cham par 'khrug long byed mi dgos shing
NK128(nyo)001:9510: / khyad par pan chen rin po che 'dod chung
NK128(nyo)001:9511: chog shes kho na la gtso bor 'don pas zang
NK128(nyo)001:9512: zing gi yo byad ma mchis la /
NK128(nyo)001:9513: phyag dpe dbang rdzas rnams kyang gcung legs ldan rje
NK128(nyo)001:9514: rang gis bdag gis ma mdzad par zhal slob so
NK128(nyo)001:9516: rig 'dzin rjes 'di ltar bka' stsal te /
NK128(nyo)001:9517: rin po che'i dgongs pa rdzogs byed du sa skya
NK128(nyo)001:9518: ba'i dpe cha lha rten rin rdor bas bzung la
NK128(nyo)001:9519: 'chad nyan gyis / bka' gdams dang mtshan nyid skor dpon po shes rgyal bas gyis /
NK128(nyo)001:9520: bka' rgyud skor sangs rgyas snying pos gyis /
NK128(nyo)001:9521: rnying ma bka' gter skor re zhig ngas bzung /
NK128(nyo)001:9522: lo shas nas dbon po mjam dbyangs pas e yong /
NK128(nyo)001:9523: rten ba zheng rnams 'o skol bya btang yin pas chen po byed rgyu med /
NK128(nyo)001:9524: phran bu gros mthun byed chog /
NK128(nyo)001:9525: dgon pa'i gdan sa dpon po gnyis gang 'thad du byed chog /
NK128(nyo)001:9526: rin po che bshad sgrub rang la dgyes pas /
NK128(nyo)001:9527: de nyid la 'o skol tsho ma lhod pa gyis /
NK128(nyo)001:9528: des rten rnams yig rigs tha dad dang spyir gyis
NK128(nyo)001:9529: dgos pa byung dus bde spyod dus kyang byas chog
NK128(nyo)001:9530: / lo gsum nas sprul pa zhig 'byin no skad na /
NK128(nyo)001:9531: de dus kho rang la tha dad nas 'phrod pa
NK128(nyo)001:9532: zhig spyi mthun du gyis gsungs pa ltar byas shing
NK128(nyo)001:9533: / lo gsum nas byon pa'i sprul pa'i sku chos
NK128(nyo)001:9534: kyi rgyal po bkra shis stobs rgyal nyid yin pas
NK128(nyo)001:9535: rgyas par gzhan du gsal lo //
NK128(nyo)001:9536: rgya chen chos kun mkhyen pa'i pan+di ta //
NK128(nyo)001:9537: pad+ma'i rgyal tshab rig 'dzin dbang gi rgyal //
NK128(nyo)001:9538: mkhyen rab dbang phyug rje btsun 'jam pa'i dbyangs //
NK128(nyo)001:9539: grags pa'i rgyal mtshan 'dzin der snying nas 'dud //
NK128(nyo)001:9540: sdom gsum rnam dag thub bstan yongs rdzogs kyi //
NK128(nyo)001:9541: bshes gnyen bstan pa'i sgron ma 'gro ba'i mgon //
NK128(nyo)001:9542: rgya bod gsar rnying mkhas grub ma lus pa'i //
NK128(nyo)001:9543: thugs rje gcig tu 'dus pa lung gis grub //
NK128(nyo)001:9544: de phyir skyabs kun 'dus pa'i bdag nyid la //
NK128(nyo)001:9545: rnam kun mi phyed dad pas gsol 'debs na //
NK128(nyo)001:9546: tshe rabs kun tu dam pa khyod nyid kyi //
NK128(nyo)001:9547: sku gsung thugs kyi gsang bas dgyes 'dzin thog /
NK128(nyo)001:9549: de nas brgyud tshul dngos bshad par bya ste /
NK128(nyo)001:9550: grub pa'i dbang phyug yab rje 'jam dbyangs rin chen rgyal mtshan gyis /
NK128(nyo)001:9551: rig 'dzin mnga' ris pa chen po legs ldan bdud
NK128(nyo)001:9552: 'joms rdo rje nyid la 'dus pa chen po mdo'i
NK128(nyo)001:9553: dbang lan gnyis su stsal ba 'di brgyud pa'i gtso
NK128(nyo)001:9555: gcung legs ldan zhabs kyi rnam par thar ba cung zad gleng bar bya ste /
NK128(nyo)001:9556: de yang rigs rus 'khrungs yul yab yum sogs ni
NK128(nyo)001:9557: mnga' ris pan+di ta chen po'i rnam thar brjod ma
NK128(nyo)001:9559: sku mched du song bas smos ma dgos la /
NK128(nyo)001:9560: de yang yab rje dam pa dgung lo re gcig
NK128(nyo)001:9561: pa'i dgung keg thog tu shin tu bsnyung bar byung
NK128(nyo)001:9562: ba'i tshe ma gza' rdor gsum gyis mi'i rnam par
NK128(nyo)001:9563: bstan nas bsnyung g.yog byed pa dang /
NK128(nyo)001:9564: khyad par rdo rje sems dpa' mdun gyi nam mkhar byon nas lung bstan pa /
NK128(nyo)001:9565: da ste zhag dgu nas cha yis drag 'gro /
NK128(nyo)001:9566: rdo rje sems dpa' lo gcig gam zla ba gsum du sgom sgrub gyis /
NK128(nyo)001:9568: rigs shig 'byung ste sngon gyi bag chags sad pa 'byung /
NK128(nyo)001:9569: sangs rgyas bstan pa'i bya ba byed par 'gyur zhes lung bstan pa ltar bsnyun las grol 'phral /
NK128(nyo)001:9570: bka' ma rdo rje sems dpa' phyag rgya rkyang gcig gi sgrub pa lo gcig dang /
NK128(nyo)001:9571: rdo rje phur ba'i bsnyen sgrub zla ba gsum grol
NK128(nyo)001:9572: ba'i dus rdo rje phur pa'i ting nge 'dzin la
NK128(nyo)001:9573: gnas bzhin pas legs ldan zhabs yum gyi mngal du
NK128(nyo)001:9574: bskrun par mdzad / de'i tshe yum la yang mnal lam du dung 'bud pa /
NK128(nyo)001:9579: nam mkha' 'od lnga'i gur nang du phyin pa /
NK128(nyo)001:9580: 'dus pa mang po la chos ston pa /
NK128(nyo)001:9582: rdo rje dang dril bu 'dzin pa /
NK128(nyo)001:9583: bum bcud 'thung zhing gzhan la sbyin pa /
NK128(nyo)001:9584: dbu rgyan gyon nas glegs bam sgrog pa /
NK128(nyo)001:9585: phreng ba'i rigs du ma mgul la dkris pa /
NK128(nyo)001:9586: bud med rgan gzhon mang po'i tshogs gral du longs spyod pa /
NK128(nyo)001:9587: shel gyi ri chen po la 'dzegs shing mang du bsgrub pa rnams byung zhing /
NK128(nyo)001:9588: lhums su h'u kho na 'dren pa yum gyis gsan te /
NK128(nyo)001:9590: lhums nas h'u h+r+aih'i sgra sgrogs shing //
NK128(nyo)001:9591: zhes gsungs pa'i don thog tu bab par sems /
NK128(nyo)001:9592: yum yang sku lus gnad drang por srangs na ting
NK128(nyo)001:9593: nge 'dzin gyi nyams du ma 'byung zhing sku lus
NK128(nyo)001:9594: yo na mi bde ba byung /
NK128(nyo)001:9595: de nas sprel lo sprel zla'i tshes bcu rgyal phur
NK128(nyo)001:9596: 'dzom pa'i nyi ma dros chen la sku bltams shing
NK128(nyo)001:9597: / de'i nyin yab yum sras 'khor bcas pas tshes bcu'i mchod pa rgyas par mdzad cing /
NK128(nyo)001:9598: tshes bcu'i gtor dbang jo lags pan chen gyis mdzad pa /
NK128(nyo)001:9599: sku tshe 'di'i yongs 'dzin la snga ba pan chen rin po che nyid yin no //
NK128(nyo)001:9600: de nas dgung lo bdun pa la yum gyis 'bri
NK128(nyo)001:9601: klog rnams bslabs shing khyod lhums su yod dus rmi
NK128(nyo)001:9603: u rgyan gyi byin rlabs zhugs pa yod pas 'jig rten gyi bya ba ma byed par /
NK128(nyo)001:9604: ri khrod 'grims la tshe dang bshad sgrubs snyoms pa
NK128(nyo)001:9605: e yong ltos gsungs yang yang bslab bya mdzad pas
NK128(nyo)001:9606: / klog dang chos spyod sems kyi gnas tshul ngo sprod kun la ma drin che'o gsungs /
NK128(nyo)001:9607: dgung lo brgyad pa la yab kyi dbu skra bregs /
NK128(nyo)001:9608: kun skyong gling ba'i lung bzhin mtshan legs ldan rdo
NK128(nyo)001:9609: rje grags mod kyang chos ming nyi zla grags bzang
NK128(nyo)001:9610: du btags / las byang le brgyad /
NK128(nyo)001:9611: zhi khro ma mgon mgar gsum /
NK128(nyo)001:9617: sgyu ma'i dpe brgyad rnams yab kyi gsung nas ngag bslabs mdzad de mkhyen pas /
NK128(nyo)001:9618: yab kyis shes ra ba che bar 'dug gsung byams
NK128(nyo)001:9619: par mdzad pas lo gcig gnyis tsam gyi bar sku
NK128(nyo)001:9620: shin tu 'tshub ba'i tshul gyis byis pa'i rnam thar
NK128(nyo)001:9621: bskyangs drags pas / mi kun gyis 'di gcung po legs ldan ma nor bar 'dug zer ba byung /
NK128(nyo)001:9622: de'i tshe sru mo skyong nge zhes pa nyid la
NK128(nyo)001:9623: shin tu byams par yod pa zhig sha dug gis
NK128(nyo)001:9624: grongs pas / thugs la sdug bsngal bzod par dka'
NK128(nyo)001:9625: ba zhig byung ste nga la yang sru mo lta
NK128(nyo)001:9626: bu'i shi ba yong thag chod nga'i spyod pa gya
NK128(nyo)001:9627: ma de 'dis grul gang yang na mi btub par
NK128(nyo)001:9628: grongs pas / 'dug / skye 'chi la rang dbang
NK128(nyo)001:9629: thob pa zhig byed dgongs pa kho nas bza' btung
NK128(nyo)001:9630: mi dran pa zhag mang du byung bas /
NK128(nyo)001:9632: khyad zas za gos gyon yang na klog thon /
NK128(nyo)001:9633: mi nus na rtsed mo la song /
NK128(nyo)001:9634: byung na bslab sbyangs gyis gsungs kun gzims nas bzhugs pas /
NK128(nyo)001:9635: 'di la ci byung ngam kha seng tsho dang mi 'dra ba zhig 'dug /
NK128(nyo)001:9636: jo jos khrid la yab kyi drung du gtor dbang
NK128(nyo)001:9637: zhus shog 'chi 'dod pa ni min nam gsungs pas
NK128(nyo)001:9638: / yum la tshigs su bcad de 'di skad zhus so //
NK128(nyo)001:9639: dal 'byor sbyin pa'i drin cen a ma kye //
NK128(nyo)001:9640: bdag la zur bu'i nad dag ma mchis te //
NK128(nyo)001:9641: sru mo gshegs thos yid chad snying ma dga' //
NK128(nyo)001:9642: ma bu gnyis la'ang de 'dra yong snyam nas //
NK128(nyo)001:9643: a ma bsams pas sru mo dran nas song //
NK128(nyo)001:9644: da ni rtse gcig byang chub sgrub byed pas //
NK128(nyo)001:9645: mi med lung stong zhig tu 'gro ba lags //
NK128(nyo)001:9646: de ru pha ma nye 'brel su yang med //
NK128(nyo)001:9647: gu yang rtsed mo byed kyang sdug bsngal med //
NK128(nyo)001:9648: sdug bsngal med na bde ba dam par 'dug /
NK128(nyo)001:9650: yum gyis spyan cher gzigs te spyan chab khyil tsam mdzad nas /
NK128(nyo)001:9651: rtsom pa dag byas 'di la chos smyo zhig yong 'dod par 'dug /
NK128(nyo)001:9652: yab kyi sku mtshams nang du skyol gsungs spom chen na yab sku mtshams la bzhugs pa'i sar skyal /
NK128(nyo)001:9654: 'dir 'tshub po ma byed par nang dgongs blo 'dzin gyis /
NK128(nyo)001:9655: nyin mo brgyad stong pa sgrogs gsungs kyang /
NK128(nyo)001:9656: bka' ma theg pa'i thun cha tsam las nyin mtshan
NK128(nyo)001:9657: med par sru mo thugs la lam me des rkyen
NK128(nyo)001:9658: byas mi rtag pa kho na dran zhing /
NK128(nyo)001:9659: de'i dpes yab yum sras bcas sems can kun la yang de ltar yong /
NK128(nyo)001:9660: nga 'dir sdod ring ma de shi na ci tsugs
NK128(nyo)001:9661: byed dgongs shing mtshan lam du yang skyo shas kho
NK128(nyo)001:9662: na byung zhing yum grongs dogs rgya dkar nas rtag
NK128(nyo)001:9663: par gzigs pas / 'di mi tshug par 'dug a
NK128(nyo)001:9664: ma'i rtsar song gsungs te mar byon nas yum gyi
NK128(nyo)001:9665: par gzigs pas / rtsar bzhugs shing / skabs re sku rtser la dum tsam g.yengs kyang /
NK128(nyo)001:9666: rtag par nges 'byung skyo shas dang /
NK128(nyo)001:9667: dpe don du ma'i sgo nas mi rtag pa dran te yum la /
NK128(nyo)001:9668: a ma lags nga'i lus ngag yid gsum 'di ci 'dra na zhus pas /
NK128(nyo)001:9670: bu lus ngag yid gsum dang mi 'dra ba'i dum
NK128(nyo)001:9671: bu mi 'dug snang srid thams cad dpe 'dug pa
NK128(nyo)001:9674: srid pa 'gro drug gi sder chags pa don dam par rgyu rkyen las 'das kyang /
NK128(nyo)001:9675: rten 'brel 'char sgo 'gag med du shar ba yin par 'dug gsungs /
NK128(nyo)001:9676: de dag gi don rgyas par gsungs dang zhus pas /
NK128(nyo)001:9677: don rgyas par ngas mi shes yab la zhus gsungs te /
NK128(nyo)001:9678: yang yab kyi drung du yum gyis khrid de /
NK128(nyo)001:9679: bu chung 'di nga la cal col du ma lab cing 'dri ba 'dug /
NK128(nyo)001:9680: chos kyi ngo sprod go shas che bas /
NK128(nyo)001:9681: bka' lung 'dra gnang ba zhu lags zhus pas /
NK128(nyo)001:9682: yab kyi byis pa col lab la gtan tshigs med gsungs /
NK128(nyo)001:9683: de nas sku mtshams de grol 'phral du chos 'dod
NK128(nyo)001:9684: 'gas gsol ba btab pa la brten nas rig 'dzin
NK128(nyo)001:9685: legs ldan rje dgung lo brgyad pa la glo bo
NK128(nyo)001:9686: ma thang lhun grub chos sdings dpal gyi dgon par
NK128(nyo)001:9687: yab barje dam pa grub pa'i 'khor los sgyur ba
NK128(nyo)001:9688: chen po nyid gyis yos lo zla ba dang po'i
NK128(nyo)001:9689: tshes brgyad nas gnyis pa'i tshes lnga'i bar du sngags
NK128(nyo)001:9690: btsun gyi 'dus pa brgya nyi shu tsam la mdo
NK128(nyo)001:9691: dbang dkyil 'khor drug cu re lnga'i dbang lung khrid
NK128(nyo)001:9692: rnams rgyas par gnang ba gsan cing /
NK128(nyo)001:9693: de nas rim par sgyur 'phrul dkyil 'khor bcu gcig /
NK128(nyo)001:9695: gnas lung dkyil 'khor drug cha lags dang bcas pa /
NK128(nyo)001:9696: sems klong sde gsum cha lag phra mo yan chad /
NK128(nyo)001:9697: bka' brgyad gsang ba yongs rdzogs chos tshan brgya nyi shu /
NK128(nyo)001:9702: dzam lha dbu dgu pa gnubs rang gi gter ma /
NK128(nyo)001:9703: gzhan yang dbang khrid lung man ngag ngo sprod phyag
NK128(nyo)001:9704: len sngags sdebs rlung 'khor 'cham gar dbyangs sogs lo
NK128(nyo)001:9705: gsum gyi bar du bar ma chad par gnang ba
NK128(nyo)001:9706: rnams gsan / sgrub chen dkon cog mgon po la dmar khrid tshom bu lugs /
NK128(nyo)001:9710: grub rgyal lugs kyi tshe sgrub sogs mang du pan chen rin po che'i phyag phyir gsan /
NK128(nyo)001:9711: de nas yab sku grib la brten nas dum tsam zhig bsnyel dus /
NK128(nyo)001:9712: sras sku mched thams cad la so so'i bzhed mthun gyi phyag rdzas gnang sbyin mdzad de /
NK128(nyo)001:9713: nga'i lag g.yon de bzhin gyi gyis /
NK128(nyo)001:9714: don grub kyis kun bzang 'di mgo thon /
NK128(nyo)001:9715: dbang rgyas gyis legs ldan 'di skyongs /
NK128(nyo)001:9716: rin rdor ni logs su phyogs grub pa der 'dug
NK128(nyo)001:9717: ces sogs sku mched so sor lugs kyi bslab bya
NK128(nyo)001:9718: dang / nga da lo kun skyong rin po che'i lung bstan skeg thog tu sleb 'dug pas /
NK128(nyo)001:9719: gal srid ma 'tsho na bstan pa spyi bye brag /
NK128(nyo)001:9720: khyad par rnying ma so zur gnubs gsum /
NK128(nyo)001:9721: gter chos nyang chos dbang rnams su bstan pa'i rtsa
NK128(nyo)001:9722: lag thams cad 'dus 'dug pas bka' gzhung ma nub
NK128(nyo)001:9723: pa gyis / gter chos 'di rnams snyigs ma'i sems
NK128(nyo)001:9724: can la dgongs pa'i zab par 'dug pas mis ma
NK128(nyo)001:9726: rnying ma'i sgyu 'phrul zhi khro lus dang 'dra /
NK128(nyo)001:9727: bka' brgyad bka' gter yan lag nying lag dang 'dra /
NK128(nyo)001:9728: bla ma zhi drag rnams dbang po lnga dang 'dra /
NK128(nyo)001:9729: rdzogs chen sems klong don lnga snod drug dang 'dra /
NK128(nyo)001:9731: man ngag phran bu las kha tshar rnams nying lag
NK128(nyo)001:9732: phran por dang 'dra bas srol shes dgos pa yin
NK128(nyo)001:9733: / bsnyen sgrub yan lag bzhi sgal tshigs dang 'dra bas ma nyams shig /
NK128(nyo)001:9734: spyi chos rnams gzhung tshugs dgos /
NK128(nyo)001:9735: bshad chos tshogs bshad rnams spyir shod /
NK128(nyo)001:9736: slob bshad rnams brgyud 'dzin rnams la ston /
NK128(nyo)001:9737: sbas bshad rnams snod ldan re re tsam brgyud ma chad tsam gyis /
NK128(nyo)001:9738: gab bshad rnams spyi sgos su gces /
NK128(nyo)001:9739: dkrugs bshad rnams lag len du 'khyer shes dgos /
NK128(nyo)001:9740: gsang ba'i bshad pa rnams snyan brgyud du bsdebs nas ngo sprod thebs pa gal che ba yin /
NK128(nyo)001:9743: yo ga gsum rnams kyang dril na rdzogs chen du thams cad 'du /
NK128(nyo)001:9744: mar bskyang na drang ldem du thams cad yod /
NK128(nyo)001:9745: nyams len bla rdzogs thugs gsum yongs rdzogs dang bzhir 'dus /
NK128(nyo)001:9746: mchog thun las che chung mgon po dregs pa nor
NK128(nyo)001:9747: lhar 'du ba yin pas sngar nas mang du song
NK128(nyo)001:9751: dpe don rtags gsum gyis snang srid 'khor 'das gtan la 'bebs pa yin pas /
NK128(nyo)001:9752: rtsa ba so thar byang sems sngags gsum gyi sdom
NK128(nyo)001:9753: pa dam tshig las dus nam du yang ma g.yos
NK128(nyo)001:9754: pa khag che / bla mar pha ngan slob mar
NK128(nyo)001:9755: bu ngan mched grogs spun ngan sogs kyi dper ma
NK128(nyo)001:9756: pa khag che / song ba gyis / dam tshig
NK128(nyo)001:9757: mi bsrung na mi pha phad yin kyang chos pha
NK128(nyo)001:9759: nga lo mtshams shig byed bu spun slob mas mtha' brgyan pa rnams /
NK128(nyo)001:9760: de ltar dgos so gsungs te sku mtshams su bzhugs /
NK128(nyo)001:9761: de nas yab kyi gsung ltar jo lags pan chen rin po che'i phyag phyir byon te /
NK128(nyo)001:9762: bka' chos gnang tshad gsan thugs dam la brtson par mdzad /
NK128(nyo)001:9763: drag dmar lha lung phug tu rdo rje drag po rtsal gyi dbang lung khrid bcas /
NK128(nyo)001:9764: chos spyod lam rim ma ti lugs /
NK128(nyo)001:9771: skyer sgang lugs kyi rigs gtad dkar dmar blo sbyong gi rigs mang po /
NK128(nyo)001:9773: mdo dran pa nyer bzhag /'dzangs blun /
NK128(nyo)001:9777: dkon cog brtseegs pa sogs mdo mang po ti bcu bzhi /
NK128(nyo)001:9778: bla ma gsang 'dus kyi dbang khrid lung skor /
NK128(nyo)001:9779: bla ma nor bu skor lnga /
NK128(nyo)001:9780: rdor sems snying thig sogs gsan pas thugs dam la bogs thon /
NK128(nyo)001:9781: sgo le khar gsang sngags lam rim gyi bshad la gnang bas kyang thugs bskyed thon /
NK128(nyo)001:9782: de nas rdo rje drag po rtsal sngon po'i bsnyen
NK128(nyo)001:9783: sgrub zla ba gsum mdzad pa'i sngon 'gro yig brgya
NK128(nyo)001:9784: khri tsho gcig song ba'i nub /
NK128(nyo)001:9785: rdo rje drag po rtsal dkar po mi tshang gcig
NK128(nyo)001:9786: mdun gyi gyang logs la gsal ler gzigs pa 'di
NK128(nyo)001:9787: dag snang gi thog ma yin /
NK128(nyo)001:9790: rnam dag chos dbyings pho brang la /
NK128(nyo)001:9791: zhes sogs kyi gsol 'debs tshigs bcad mdzad nas lha
NK128(nyo)001:9792: dang bdag bsres te mnyam par gzhag pas zhag bdun
NK128(nyo)001:9793: du bza' btung gi spros pa med par rtog med
NK128(nyo)001:9794: kyi ting 'dzin la gnas pa byung /
NK128(nyo)001:9795: dngos gzhi'i dus su thugs nyams la lus med nam mkha' yin snyam pa sogs du ma byung /
NK128(nyo)001:9796: de nas nyin pha wong gi dur khrod du nor
NK128(nyo)001:9797: bu skor lnga'i bsnyen sgrub zla ba bzhir gnang bas
NK128(nyo)001:9798: phyi sgrub dus su snying rje phyogs med du shar
NK128(nyo)001:9799: / nang sgrub dus su snang srid dag snang du shar /
NK128(nyo)001:9800: gsang sgrub dus su mdun gyi nam mkhar bla ma
NK128(nyo)001:9801: thod phreng rtsal mkha' 'gro bzhis bskor ba'i zhal gzigs
NK128(nyo)001:9802: shing / gsal nyams de zhag gsum gyis bar byung bas /
NK128(nyo)001:9803: na mo dngas pa'i mkha' la pad sdong 'od lha'i dbus //
NK128(nyo)001:9804: zhes sogs kyis gsol ba btab pas /
NK128(nyo)001:9805: 'od lngar spung nge zhu nas sgrub rten la thim pa byung /
NK128(nyo)001:9806: yang gsang sgrub pa'i gnas su u rgyan nga rang yin dgongs pa'i thugs nyams cher 'ur ba dang /
NK128(nyo)001:9807: mtshan lam du sgrub khang gi ri la sogs dpe
NK128(nyo)001:9808: chas gang zhig rus rgyan dang bcas gar byed pa'i
NK128(nyo)001:9809: rang nas nam mkha' u rgyan phyi sgrub kyi sku
NK128(nyo)001:9810: la dpa' bo mkha' 'gro mang bos bskor ba 'od
NK128(nyo)001:9811: lnga'i gur nas gar stabs bsgyur zhing /
NK128(nyo)001:9812: bu ltos shig ltos shig yar la ltos /
NK128(nyo)001:9813: lus med lus te lus kyi mchog /
NK128(nyo)001:9814: ces lan gsum gsungs te nam mkha' thim pa dang
NK128(nyo)001:9815: glegs bam gyi dbus su rdo rje skyil krung du
NK128(nyo)001:9816: bzhugs pa byung / de nas bogs 'don la ri
NK128(nyo)001:9817: khrod du phebs bzhed cing dgon par chas ka blangs
NK128(nyo)001:9818: na tshor dogs a ce thugs rje la chas blangs
NK128(nyo)001:9819: byas pas sran ma tshom pa zhig phul ba ka
NK128(nyo)001:9820: li gang bsnams te zla gcig bar zhag re la
NK128(nyo)001:9821: sran rdog sum cu pa re dang /
NK128(nyo)001:9822: chu ka p+aa li re ma gtogs gzhan bza' btung
NK128(nyo)001:9823: gang yang med par ri khrod kun tu byon nas
NK128(nyo)001:9824: brtul zhugs kyi spyod pa mang du mdzad skabs /
NK128(nyo)001:9825: jo lag pan chen gyis 'bod mi gnang bar brten /
NK128(nyo)001:9826: ma dgon du byon pas dge sbyor 'phel lam /
NK128(nyo)001:9827: zla ba du song khar song nas ri khrod la phyin nam /
NK128(nyo)001:9828: sngon la gzhes len cig byed /
NK128(nyo)001:9829: de nas nyams rtogs shig phul gsungs te tshogs rdzas ka to ra gang gnang ba /
NK128(nyo)001:9830: las byang nor bu pad phreng tshar gcig gi thog nas tshogs 'khor rnams bzhes pas /
NK128(nyo)001:9832: bu rten 'brel bzang na ning thugs sgrub kyi dus
NK128(nyo)001:9833: dgong gtor zhig sbyin pa gtor chu de pho song
NK128(nyo)001:9834: bas da res 'tsho ba dkon pa de'i rten 'brel
NK128(nyo)001:9835: yin / da lan sgrub chas cha tsam 'byung ba 'dug /
NK128(nyo)001:9836: da dge sbyor la nyams myong ji ltar byung gsungs pa la /
NK128(nyo)001:9837: mgur dbyangs kyi thog ma 'di ltar phul ba /
NK128(nyo)001:9838: rje dus gsum sangs rgyas ngo bo nyid /
NK128(nyo)001:9839: u rgyan brgyud par bcas la 'dud /
NK128(nyo)001:9840: dang po dal 'byor gyi lus thob 'di /
NK128(nyo)001:9841: bcud dang ldan pas sa gzhi 'dra //
NK128(nyo)001:9843: mi smyon bdag gi nyams 'bul lags //
NK128(nyo)001:9844: yin thog khel na dbugs dbyung dang //
NK128(nyo)001:9845: log 'khrul mchis na gegs sel zhu //
NK128(nyo)001:9846: grag stong mchod sprin rje la 'bul //
NK128(nyo)001:9847: dmigs med dge rtsa 'gro don bsngo //
NK128(nyo)001:9848: zhes pa'i bar mgur du phul bas /
NK128(nyo)001:9850: de rnams sngags lugs kyi rim skyes pa'i nyams go yul du ma lus par byung 'dug /
NK128(nyo)001:9851: da dung deng sang dgon pa gong du sdod la dge sbyor skyongs /
NK128(nyo)001:9852: skabs su blo sbyongs kyang rgyud sde 'dra la gyis /
NK128(nyo)001:9853: dbang phyug rgyal mtshan gyis mtshams kyi grogs kyang mdzod /
NK128(nyo)001:9854: nga brag dmar la zhag shas 'gro gsungs /
NK128(nyo)001:9855: de nas dbang phyug rgyal mtshan la mdze byung ba'i
NK128(nyo)001:9856: dmigs skyor dang sbrags sku mtshams dam du mdzad de
NK128(nyo)001:9857: bla ma zhi drag gi bsnyen sgrub la gtso bor
NK128(nyo)001:9858: mdzad / zla ba lnga tsam nas dpon slob gnyis
NK128(nyo)001:9859: sku chas rnams zad de skyel mi yang ma byung
NK128(nyo)001:9860: mdzad / bas / a ne sbyin bzang la nyung ma brel bco lnga blangs te /
NK128(nyo)001:9861: cong zhi brdungs nyung ma btsos pa dang bsres te
NK128(nyo)001:9862: nyin re la dpon slob gnyis kas bzhes can re
NK128(nyo)001:9863: gsol zhing / de la brten nas zla gcig song ba dang kho rtsam pa bskyal 'dug kyang /
NK128(nyo)001:9864: rje 'dis dka' thub kho na la brten nas thog
NK128(nyo)001:9865: mar me tog ril bu du ma tsam re gsol
NK128(nyo)001:9866: / de nas nyi ma re la nyung sreg rdog
NK128(nyo)001:9867: po re tsam gsol zhing bzhugs pas zla ba brgyad
NK128(nyo)001:9868: nas grogs po'i mdze yang sos /
NK128(nyo)001:9869: de nas sku mtshams grol te pan chen rin po cher nyang lugs brag dmar skor /
NK128(nyo)001:9873: de'i tshe yab rje dam pa'i lo mtshams kyang grol nas zhabs drung du phyin pas /
NK128(nyo)001:9874: spyan hur re gzigs te phyag gis bzung nas /
NK128(nyo)001:9875: byis pa 'di byas chog pa'i bslab sbyangs mi byed par /
NK128(nyo)001:9876: smyon pa dbang rgyal dang 'di gnyis res ri la 'gro /
NK128(nyo)001:9880: nged kyi mi brgyud nas bud pa gnyis 'dug gsungs te /
NK128(nyo)001:9883: zhal 'gram la lan gsum du phyag 'bebs dang bka' bkyon mang du gnang bas /
NK128(nyo)001:9884: yab la cher gyis gzigs pas /
NK128(nyo)001:9885: yab rje dam pa nyid dpal chen po badz+ra he
NK128(nyo)001:9886: ru ka zhal gcig phyag gnyis rdo rje thog khrag
NK128(nyo)001:9887: 'dzin pa dur khrod kyi chas ldan rdo rje'i gshog
NK128(nyo)001:9888: pa gdengs pa zhig tu sngo lam me gzigs /
NK128(nyo)001:9889: sku lus kyi zug rnams bde bar shar /
NK128(nyo)001:9890: da dung bka' bkyon phyag 'bebs de las lhag pa
NK128(nyo)001:9891: byung na dngos grub tu 'byung bar 'dug pa la
NK128(nyo)001:9892: dgongs te phyag 'tshal te phyir phebs pas /
NK128(nyo)001:9894: kha sing nas mtshams mi byed par ci byed 'di byed med pa byed 'dug zer /
NK128(nyo)001:9895: de 'dra ma byed par yang na 'di gang sdod la slob gnyer gyis /
NK128(nyo)001:9896: yang na pan chen gyi phyag phyir song yon tan mthil phyin pa slobs shig gsungs /
NK128(nyo)001:9897: de nas yab zhabs skor mdzad pa'i gyang logs la 'di ltar bris te /
NK128(nyo)001:9899: drin can gyi pha ma bka' drin can //
NK128(nyo)001:9900: dal 'byor bskrun pa'i thabs mkhas po //
NK128(nyo)001:9901: bka' lung dang man ngag gnang ba'i rje //
NK128(nyo)001:9902: mi shes la bslabs pa'i thugs rje can //
NK128(nyo)001:9903: kho bo gtad med kyi smyon pa ngas //
NK128(nyo)001:9904: nyin mtshan gnyis su bsams tsa na //
NK128(nyo)001:9905: zhes sogs mang bar tshigs su bcad pa'i mthar /
NK128(nyo)001:9906: dus da res 'khrul tshad 'don pa'i phyir //
NK128(nyo)001:9907: gang shar gyi spyod pa skyong ba la //
NK128(nyo)001:9908: thugs dgongs par 'gal ba mthol zhing bshags //
NK128(nyo)001:9909: zhes sogs gyang la sbyar te pan chen rin po che'i sku drung du byon nas /
NK128(nyo)001:9910: thugs rje chen po yang snying 'dus pa 'khor ba
NK128(nyo)001:9911: dong sprugs rnams kyi bka' lung bshad pa dang bcas
NK128(nyo)001:9912: pa gsan / de nas pan chen rin po che rgyal sar byon te /
NK128(nyo)001:9913: sngags 'chang sh+aakya bzang po dang mjal te phyir byon nas gcung legs ldan zhabs la /
NK128(nyo)001:9914: da res phyin pa la don byung /
NK128(nyo)001:9915: 'khrungs yul drang po ba mtshan sh+aakya bzang po zer ba dang mjal /
NK128(nyo)001:9917: thugs rje chen po dang rig 'dzin gdung sgrub skor bsnams 'dug pa gzigs pas /
NK128(nyo)001:9920: thugs la rtogs med kyi bde nyams dpag med 'khrungs te bdag mjal bar phyin e chog zhus pas /
NK128(nyo)001:9921: khyod rang shog bu thul nas dpe bris /
NK128(nyo)001:9922: bris tshar ba dang dbang lung zhu ba dang bsgrags te 'gro gsungs /
NK128(nyo)001:9923: de nas zhag bcu gcig song ba dang sku mched lhan du byon nas mjal /
NK128(nyo)001:9924: sku gzigs pa tsam gyis bde stong gi nyams su song /
NK128(nyo)001:9929: rta mgrin nyang lugs lcags ral can /
NK128(nyo)001:9930: kho rang gi rnam thar lung bstan mchod rten dmar po'i gter ma /
NK128(nyo)001:9932: rje drang po bal yul du mchod rten bya rung
NK128(nyo)001:9933: kha shor gyi zhig gso la byon pa'i zhabs phyir
NK128(nyo)001:9934: 'byon bzhed kyang ma nus par phyir byon /
NK128(nyo)001:9935: pan chen po ta lar sku mtshams mdzad /
NK128(nyo)001:9936: yab rje 'jam dbyangs chen po gnyen sa brgya rtsa 'grim pa'i zhabs phyir byon nas /
NK128(nyo)001:9941: +aar+ya de wa'i tshigs bcad che chung sogs gcod skor mang du gsan /
NK128(nyo)001:9942: bya bral bsod nams seng ge'i ri chos dgos pa
NK128(nyo)001:9943: kun 'byung la gzhung khrid mdzad de zla ba gsum
NK128(nyo)001:9944: gyi bar yab dang lhan du gnyan sa brgya rtsa
NK128(nyo)001:9949: lam mdo sogs kun tu byon pas bsnyems thag chod cing bog /
NK128(nyo)001:9950: thon dgu na yab las slar yang 'od gsal gsang skor rnams tshang bar gsan /
NK128(nyo)001:9951: de'i tshe yab kyis spyan 'bru tshugs su gzigs te /
NK128(nyo)001:9952: gyang logs la yi ge dag ma nyung ba zhig bris 'dug ste /
NK128(nyo)001:9953: bya rgan gyi spu 'thog ran bya ba lags /
NK128(nyo)001:9954: lag mgo zan nas dpung pa la bab pa yin pas /
NK128(nyo)001:9955: chen po gsum gyi sgro 'dogs da res chod dgos pas gang byung ma byed par bsgoms la /
NK128(nyo)001:9956: dpe don rtags gsum dang mi 'gal ba'i dri ba 'bul rgyu yod pa mdzod cig gsungs pas /
NK128(nyo)001:9957: bka' lung de rang don kho na yin snyam bsgoms
NK128(nyo)001:9958: pas nyams rtogs bsam gyis mi khyab pa 'khrungs te
NK128(nyo)001:9959: / rgyu mtshan zhib par yab kyi drung du zhus pas /
NK128(nyo)001:9960: chos la go ba chags tsam yin da rung 'bung la bsgoms /
NK128(nyo)001:9961: dam tshig dang sdom pa ma nyams na dpa' bo mkha' 'gros byin gyis brlabs pa yin gsungs /
NK128(nyo)001:9962: lar mi smyon la chos 'go zer ba bden par 'dug gsungs /
NK128(nyo)001:9963: de nas grol ston gyi tshogs gral du rtogs pa'i mgur phul /
NK128(nyo)001:9964: dpon slob rnams glo bo sde bdag gi sku rim du 'byon pa'i 'cham spyongs mdzad pas /
NK128(nyo)001:9965: zhag bcu gsum la dam can spyi 'cham rnams mkhyen /
NK128(nyo)001:9966: dpon slob rnams la bsnyen bkur zhig byung ba'i tshogs gradula mnal dum tsam byung skabs /
NK128(nyo)001:9967: sngar nas yang yang yong ba'i bud med smug mo de byung nas /
NK128(nyo)001:9968: bu kho de gsang sngags zab mo'i nye lam la
NK128(nyo)001:9969: brten nas tshe gcig 'tshang rgya ba'i phyir zab mo'i
NK128(nyo)001:9971: rdo rje lus kyi gar stabs kyis /
NK128(nyo)001:9972: dpa' bo mkha' 'gro ma dgyes na /
NK128(nyo)001:9973: 'gro ba dga' ba'i lus rtsed kyis /
NK128(nyo)001:9974: dal 'byor stong zad ma byed par /
NK128(nyo)001:9975: deng sang cho 'phrul chen po la /
NK128(nyo)001:9976: thugs rje chen po sgrubs shig ang /
NK128(nyo)001:9978: dpa' bo mkha' 'gro ma mnyes tshar /
NK128(nyo)001:9979: da nas 'cham mi byed dgongs te dgon par byon
NK128(nyo)001:9980: nas gzims khang 'og ma'i steng du thugs rje chen
NK128(nyo)001:9981: po 'gro ba kun grol gyi bsnyen pa ngag mtshams
NK128(nyo)001:9982: la zhugs / tshes bco lnga'i nub mo mtshan thog thag gi dge sbyor mdzad pas /
NK128(nyo)001:9983: tho rangs drin can drang po sprul sku chen po'i
NK128(nyo)001:9984: sku mtho tshad tsam 'od zer 'phro ba zhig mdun
NK128(nyo)001:9985: gyi nam mkha' 'od lnga'i klong na bzhugs te zhal
NK128(nyo)001:9986: gdams 'ga' gsungs te yal khar thugs rje chen po'i
NK128(nyo)001:9987: rnam par lam gyur te song ba byung bas mgur
NK128(nyo)001:9988: bzhes shing / kha skong sbyin sreg kyang grub nas
NK128(nyo)001:9989: sku mtshams grol te pan chen drung du byon nas
NK128(nyo)001:9990: bzhes shing / chos gsan / drung yig lha mchog
NK128(nyo)001:9991: seng ger phyag bris legs pa zhig slob dgongs nyin
NK128(nyo)001:9992: cig phyag byas gnang bar rtsams pa la /
NK128(nyo)001:9993: nga de ring shi na yi ges ci byed dgongs
NK128(nyo)001:9994: te de'i tshab tu yig brgya brgya re 'dren pa'i
NK128(nyo)001:9996: ri sgang zhig tu yig brgya 'dren zhing bzhugs pas /
NK128(nyo)001:9997: d+aa ma ru'i sgra zhig byung ste gzigs pas /
NK128(nyo)001:9998: phrag pa can gyi nam mkha' la a ma lab sgron la steng na dam pa sangs rgyas /
NK128(nyo)001:9999: mdun du bsod nams bla ma /
NK128(nyo)001:10001: g.yon du thod pa don grub /
NK128(nyo)001:10002: rgyab na 'jam dbyangs bla ma rnams mi tshad tsam
NK128(nyo)001:10003: 'od phung de 'dug pa gzigs dbyings rig bsres te
NK128(nyo)001:10004: phatahgasuma rgyab pas / gtso 'khor thams cad 'od du
NK128(nyo)001:10005: zhu nas thim pa'i nyams shar bas nyin zhag gcig
NK128(nyo)001:10007: de nas po ta lar pan chen rin po che
NK128(nyo)001:10008: dang lhan du bzhugs te dbang lung bsam gyis mi
NK128(nyo)001:10009: khyab pa gsan / glo bo mkhan chen la jo bo'i chos 'byung brgya rtsa /
NK128(nyo)001:10014: mkhan chen bsod nams lhun grub de nyid las dge tshul du sgrub par mdzad /
NK128(nyo)001:10015: mkhan chen dkon cog chos skyabs la bde mchog nag po lugs kyi skor gsan /
NK128(nyo)001:10016: pan chen rin po che pu rong du gu ge
NK128(nyo)001:10017: pan chen la sgra'i dogs gcod dang chos gsan par
NK128(nyo)001:10018: phebs shul zla ba drug gi ring ri khrod du
NK128(nyo)001:10020: dgun zla gsum gyi ring yum dang lhan du sgo
NK128(nyo)001:10021: le khar bla ma rig 'dzin gdung sgrub kyi phyi
NK128(nyo)001:10022: nang gsang ba'i bsnyen pa mdzad dus dag snang dang
NK128(nyo)001:10023: lung bstan dpag med byung zhing /
NK128(nyo)001:10024: khyad par khye'u zhig gis sbas yul dang zab gter gyi kha byang sogs yod tshul /
NK128(nyo)001:10025: skye ba gsum brgyud nas 'chi med kyi sku thob tshul /
NK128(nyo)001:10026: 'gro don 'byung tshul sogs rgyas par gsungs pa'i mthar
NK128(nyo)001:10027: u rgyan chen po zhal gyis bzhes te sku la
NK128(nyo)001:10028: thim pa sogs ngo mtshar mang du byung /
NK128(nyo)001:10029: de nas skyid grong phyogs su gnas gzigs la phebs /
NK128(nyo)001:10030: mnga' ris rdzong dkar du jo lags pan chen rin
NK128(nyo)001:10031: po che dang sngags 'chang sh+aakya bzang po gnyis bzhugs
NK128(nyo)001:10032: pa dang mjal / jo bo'i drung du phyag skor smon lam mdzad /
NK128(nyo)001:10033: byams sprin sogs gnas rnams zhib par mjal /
NK128(nyo)001:10034: ri bo dpal 'bar du phebs bzhed kyang grogs stobs kyis ma thub /
NK128(nyo)001:10036: rdo rje rdzong grib ma rdzong rnams mjal du thugs nyams 'ur /
NK128(nyo)001:10037: slar rdzong dkar du phebs nas rje drang po ba la bde mchog dkar po /
NK128(nyo)001:10040: rme brtsegs sogs tshe brtan rgyal mtshan pa'i gter kha /
NK128(nyo)001:10041: byang gter bka' brgyad thor bu sogs gsan nas glo bor phebs /
NK128(nyo)001:10042: pan chen rin po che'i gcod rgyal thang lugs nyams khrid du gnang zhing /
NK128(nyo)001:10043: gnyan khrod brgya rtsa mdzad pas tshar lhongs thams cad 'grig /
NK128(nyo)001:10044: pan chen gyi phyag phyir rin po che nam mkha' shes rab la ni gu'i skor rnams gsan /
NK128(nyo)001:10045: pan chen nyid la chos dbang lugs kyi n+aa ga
NK128(nyo)001:10046: rak+sha'i skor gsan te nub cig thugs dam mdzad pas
NK128(nyo)001:10047: sku la dam tshig gi phyag rgya dang thugs la
NK128(nyo)001:10048: ye shes kyi phyag rgyas thebs /
NK128(nyo)001:10049: byang gter sgrub skor gsum dang ma ni bka' 'bum sogs mang du gsan /
NK128(nyo)001:10050: dbyar smad hor gnyen chen po byung bas sne shang
NK128(nyo)001:10051: phyogs su phebs pas lam du 'brum nad byung yang
NK128(nyo)001:10052: gcod dmigs kho nas sman dpyad rim groo kun gyi
NK128(nyo)001:10053: go chod de snyun las grol /
NK128(nyo)001:10054: rin po che nam mkha' shes rab la mkha' 'gro snying thig gsan /
NK128(nyo)001:10055: pan chen gyi glo bo mkhan chen drung du lo
NK128(nyo)001:10056: shas sdod gsungs pa'i bka' ma chog par phebs kyang
NK128(nyo)001:10058: ri khrod zhig la phebs bzhed de yum la zhus
NK128(nyo)001:10059: pas re zhig sdod la yab kyi drung du sgro
NK128(nyo)001:10060: 'dogs 'dra chod gsung ste re zhig bzhugs pa'i bar
NK128(nyo)001:10061: la pan chen rin po ches bla ma bcu gcig
NK128(nyo)001:10062: tsam gyis gtsos mi nyer lnga la chos dbang gi
NK128(nyo)001:10063: bla ma gsang 'dus thams cad thems can thems med
NK128(nyo)001:10070: sman bla sogs gnang ba'i zhor chos gsan /
NK128(nyo)001:10071: bstan pa spyi rim du 'dus pa bcu gsum gyi mdo brgyad /
NK128(nyo)001:10074: bzlog mnan brgya rtsa rnams zla ba gsum gyi bar du mdzad /
NK128(nyo)001:10075: hor gyi kha gnon rig 'dzin brgyad kyi rdo lha bzhengs ba sogs mdzad /
NK128(nyo)001:10076: slar yang yab rje dam pa la 'dus pa mdo dbang yongs su rdzogs pa tshar gcig gsan cing /
NK128(nyo)001:10082: mdo mgon ljang sngon drag po sogs bka' lung gi lhag ma rnams dang /
NK128(nyo)001:10083: mdo rgyud bskyed rdzogs dbang khrid zhal gdams /
NK128(nyo)001:10084: bsnyen brgyud phra mo rnams kyang dgyes bzhin du gnang ste /
NK128(nyo)001:10086: chos lhag rnams ma lus par song ngo //
NK128(nyo)001:10087: mi res babs pa'i dus yong bas //
NK128(nyo)001:10088: chos mdun yang ma lhod par 'dug pas bshad sgrub la 'bungs /
NK128(nyo)001:10090: rigs brgyud 'dzin dgos pa'i bslab bya sogs rgyas par
NK128(nyo)001:10091: gnang ba'i mthar khab bzhes dgos tshul dang jo mo'i
NK128(nyo)001:10092: 'dam kha sogs lung dang 'brel ba'i bslab ston gnang
NK128(nyo)001:10093: yang khab bzhes mdzad pa'i zhal len ma phul zhing
NK128(nyo)001:10094: / chos thams cad kyi gnad gar 'dus /
NK128(nyo)001:10105: gdul bya gar phyogs su yong /
NK128(nyo)001:10110: skye ba dur mjal zhus pas /
NK128(nyo)001:10113: chos thams cad kyi gnad lta bar 'dus /
NK128(nyo)001:10117: nyams su ting nge 'dzin gyis blang /
NK128(nyo)001:10119: gnad byang chub kyi sems che /
NK128(nyo)001:10122: 'gro don lam rim ma nor bar gyis /
NK128(nyo)001:10125: gdul bya'i yul nges pa med /
NK128(nyo)001:10126: slob ma sngags btsun stong phrag tsam la 'brel pa 'jog /
NK128(nyo)001:10127: smin grol lam sna zin nges brgya las mi 'byung /
NK128(nyo)001:10128: phra mo rigs 'dus khri phrag gsum la dkar po'i las 'brel 'jog /
NK128(nyo)001:10129: drag po mngon spyod kyi 'brel pa yang mang du 'byung /
NK128(nyo)001:10130: zhing khams skye ba 'ga' nas las rab grub pa'i zhing du byon /
NK128(nyo)001:10131: nga tshe tshad brgyad cu gya bzhi'am brgya dang bcu gsum nas kun tu bzang po'i klong du 'gro /
NK128(nyo)001:10133: de dang rim gyis mjal bar gda' yi gsungs /
NK128(nyo)001:10134: de nas hor skad che bar byung bas rten mchod
NK128(nyo)001:10135: rnams dang yab rje nyid kyang bsgres pa sogs nas
NK128(nyo)001:10136: sne shar phyogs su gnas 'phos na zhus pas /
NK128(nyo)001:10137: nga ma shi bar du las sla gsungs /
NK128(nyo)001:10138: yang pan chen rin po che'i phyag phyir byon te
NK128(nyo)001:10139: glo bo mkhan chen las 'jigs byed ro langs brgyad
NK128(nyo)001:10140: skor sogs gsan / zur cho nas rin po che
NK128(nyo)001:10141: mgon po dpal bzang rta mgrin yang gsang skor yang
NK128(nyo)001:10142: skor sogs gsan / gsan / dgun dpyid gnyis kyang
NK128(nyo)001:10143: pan chen rin po cher zab chos du ma gsan
NK128(nyo)001:10144: skor sogs gsan / gsan / / de nas pan
NK128(nyo)001:10145: chen rin po che dang sbrags gung thang phyogs su
NK128(nyo)001:10146: byon pa la jag pa byung bar /
NK128(nyo)001:10147: pan chen rin po ches dkon cog gsum la phyag
NK128(nyo)001:10148: 'tshal lo gsungs nas phyag mdzad pas jag dpon de
NK128(nyo)001:10149: phor langs kyis shi la thug pas bshags pa phul
NK128(nyo)001:10150: / skyid grong gi dgon pa dkar ye rje drang
NK128(nyo)001:10151: po ba la nyang gi mkha' 'gro chen mo'i skor
NK128(nyo)001:10152: / dang / byang gter bka' brgyad phur ba thugs sgrub sogs gsan /
NK128(nyo)001:10153: ku thang rtsus su rin po che sangs rgyas skyabs
NK128(nyo)001:10154: pa la phyag rdor che ba brgyad skor gsan cing
NK128(nyo)001:10155: / gzhan yang rab 'byams pa dkon cog bsam grub la ras chung snyan brgyud sogs gsan /
NK128(nyo)001:10156: gcung legs ldan rje dpon slob gnyis kyis bal por byon /
NK128(nyo)001:10157: gcen pan chen dpon slob skyid grong du bzhugs kyang phyis thugs 'gyur te bal por byon /
NK128(nyo)001:10158: sku mched lhan du gnas rten rnams zhib mjal mdzad /
NK128(nyo)001:10159: grub chen sha ba ri +aa tsar ya sngo sangs
NK128(nyo)001:10160: dar khra'i gos gyon zhing rus pa'i rgyan drug gsol
NK128(nyo)001:10161: ba / d+aa ma ru dang kha t+w+aam thogs pa zhig dang mjal /
NK128(nyo)001:10162: phag mo dur khrod du gson bsreg mdzad pa'i sar
NK128(nyo)001:10163: pan chen nags rin yang grub thob kyi chas de
NK128(nyo)001:10165: dz+h+aa na sh+r+ai dang gu na sh+r+ai yab sras la rdor dbyings /
NK128(nyo)001:10167: bde mchog lhan skyes dkar sngo /
NK128(nyo)001:10171: gri gug sgrol ma bla med rnams gsan /
NK128(nyo)001:10172: rig 'dzin rgod ldem can gyi skye ba dngos bal por yong ba lung bstan pa de dang mjal /
NK128(nyo)001:10173: yang le shod rgod ldem rje'i gter skal 'dug pa gzigs te byin rlabs zhus shing smon lam mdzad /
NK128(nyo)001:10174: a su ra dang rgya'i gong kha dkar cung tshun
NK128(nyo)001:10175: du phebs te yul ltas gnas gzigs byin rlabs dag
NK128(nyo)001:10176: snang spro dga' dpag med byung /
NK128(nyo)001:10177: gar phebs kyi sar pan chen rin po cher chos
NK128(nyo)001:10178: zhu mang du byung ba thams cad legs par gsan
NK128(nyo)001:10180: ri bo dpal 'bar du rje sh+aakya bzang po'i zhabs
NK128(nyo)001:10181: phyir byon te dpon slob gnyis kas lo mtshams la
NK128(nyo)001:10182: bzhugs / thugs dam 'phel zhing dag snang mang po shar /
NK128(nyo)001:10183: lo mtshams grol bstun glo bor phebs pas yum zhing du phebs 'dug par brten /
NK128(nyo)001:10184: glo bo mkhan chen grwa slob dang bcas par mang ja bsngo rten dang /
NK128(nyo)001:10185: khyad par yab rje dam pa dbus bzhugs kyi dbu
NK128(nyo)001:10186: re'i grwa btsun lnga brgya la nyin 'degs kyi zhabs
NK128(nyo)001:10187: tog dang / yul pa bying la nas 'gyed sogs nyid rang gi phyag rdzas steng nas sgrub rjes /
NK128(nyo)001:10188: lo gcig sku drin bsab phyir yab kyi zhabs phyi
NK128(nyo)001:10189: 'bad pa drag pos mdzad de ston sdud tshu na
NK128(nyo)001:10190: dag thon mdzad / nyid rang gi sku skal steng
NK128(nyo)001:10191: nas yum gyis don du bsod snyoms pa stong phrag
NK128(nyo)001:10192: tsam la snen bkur dang bsngo rten mdzad /
NK128(nyo)001:10193: de lhag nas khal bcu gsum bsgrub brgyags su bsnams
NK128(nyo)001:10194: te stang skya zhes pa'i phugs pa sus kyang ma
NK128(nyo)001:10195: tshor bar lo mtshams mdzad de /
NK128(nyo)001:10196: zhi ba rdo rje sems dpa'i snying thig gi thog
NK128(nyo)001:10197: drangs khro bo sgrub pa sde dgu'i bsnyen pa mdzad
NK128(nyo)001:10198: / grub rtags kyang gtor ma 'od du zhu ba /
NK128(nyo)001:10199: chang rdza nyes pa slar log pa /
NK128(nyo)001:10200: sman gtor rak+ta mchod rdzas rnams mi 'khyags ma rul ba dang /
NK128(nyo)001:10201: zhi khro dam pa rigs brgya'i zhal mngon sum du gzigs pa'i tshe /
NK128(nyo)001:10202: snod bcud rnam par dag pa'i 'od klong du /
NK128(nyo)001:10203: zhes sogs kyi bstod pa mdzad /
NK128(nyo)001:10204: lo mtshams grol nas pan chen rin po che'i zhabs
NK128(nyo)001:10205: phyir dol po gshongs su stong chen mkhan po'i drung
NK128(nyo)001:10206: du rdo rje phreng ba gsan par byon /
NK128(nyo)001:10209: n+aa ro mkha' spyod sogs kyang zhor la gsan /
NK128(nyo)001:10210: de nas sngar bzhin pan chen gar phebs su byon te dbang chos mang du gsan /
NK128(nyo)001:10211: nyid rang gi gsang sngags lam rim ma bu cha
NK128(nyo)001:10212: lag rnams bsgrig par mdzad cing gsung chos kyi thog
NK128(nyo)001:10213: mar gsang sngags lam rim gsungs /
NK128(nyo)001:10214: 'ga' zhig la mi la'i rnam mgur gyi lung mdzad /
NK128(nyo)001:10215: sbyong dkyil bcu gnyis yum don du ras bris su bzhengs /
NK128(nyo)001:10216: glo bor yab rje 'jam dbyangs chen po'i drung du 'bum po ti bcu drug /
NK128(nyo)001:10218: rgya tog gser gsum sogs po ti bco lnga tsam gyi lung gsan /
NK128(nyo)001:10219: rje drang po ba'i spyan 'dren byung ba ltar skyid
NK128(nyo)001:10220: grong dkar yer byang gter phug pa spu gri'i skor
NK128(nyo)001:10221: dang rgyud bcu bdun sogs gsar snying gi chos mang
NK128(nyo)001:10222: du gsan / sngags nag gsang sngags rdo rje la sang gling tshe sgrub skor gsan /
NK128(nyo)001:10223: sngags 'chang sh+aakya bzang po'i zhabs phyir bcar mar bzhugs
NK128(nyo)001:10224: nas mchod dpon gyi las 'dzin mdzad de gar phebs
NK128(nyo)001:10225: sar byon nas rim bzhin ngam ring bde grol du
NK128(nyo)001:10226: thugs sras rin po che nam mkha' rgyal mtshan dang
NK128(nyo)001:10227: mjal zhing / der bzhugs 'dod kyang rje drang po
NK128(nyo)001:10228: ba'i bka' ma grol bar brten re zhig glo bor
NK128(nyo)001:10229: mjal zhing / phebs / de nas dgun byang ngam
NK128(nyo)001:10230: ring bde grol du thugs sras rin po cher rje
NK128(nyo)001:10231: drang po ba zang thal gsan pa'i phyag phyir byon
NK128(nyo)001:10233: der nyin mo bka' chos gsan /
NK128(nyo)001:10235: snga dgong bskang gso mdzad pa sogs zla ba drug gi bar du mdzad /
NK128(nyo)001:10236: de nas zang thal gyi spros bcas bum dbang skabs dam bcas 'di ltar mdzad de /
NK128(nyo)001:10237: bdag deng nas lo gsum gyi bar du zhabs phyir 'brangs te sdod /
NK128(nyo)001:10238: de bar du ri bo bkra bzang pa'i lugs kyi
NK128(nyo)001:10239: gter chos sho lo ka gcig kyang ma lus pa'i
NK128(nyo)001:10240: dbang lung / phyag len dmar khrid gnad gsang brtse bas skyong 'tshal /
NK128(nyo)001:10241: de nas ri bo dpal 'bar du lo bcu sgom pa lags /
NK128(nyo)001:10242: tshe 'di la snang bzhi'i lam rtags rdzogs par byed
NK128(nyo)001:10243: pas thugs rje can gyis bskyong du gsol zhus te
NK128(nyo)001:10244: / bem gdan zhig ma gtogs thams cad bla ma'i drung du phul lo //
NK128(nyo)001:10245: bla mas kyang shin tu legs /
NK128(nyo)001:10246: shes rab dang go 'dun drag po 'dug pas mi res babs dus yong lags po gsungs /
NK128(nyo)001:10247: de nas gsung chos dngos gzhi grub nas rin po
NK128(nyo)001:10248: che drang po ba stong chen du zla phyed bar
NK128(nyo)001:10249: bzhugs pa'i zhabs phyir byon nas chos phran 'ga' gsan
NK128(nyo)001:10250: / dgon pa shar du drang po bas kun bzang thugs gter tshar gcig gsungs pa gsan /
NK128(nyo)001:10251: de nas bde grol du phyin byon pa'i tshe /
NK128(nyo)001:10252: mnga' ris glo bo nas jo lags pan chen rin
NK128(nyo)001:10253: po che glo bo mkhan chen pa'i bka' bskul te
NK128(nyo)001:10254: dbus gtsang gi phyogs su gsar rnying gi chos bka'
NK128(nyo)001:10255: chad pa rnams gso bar phebs pa dang sku mched
NK128(nyo)001:10257: phyag phyir phebs dgos tshul rje drang po bas gsungs par /
NK128(nyo)001:10258: snga sor gyi dam bca' yod tshul zhus pas /
NK128(nyo)001:10259: ma 'ongs pa na dgos pa rgya chen po yod /
NK128(nyo)001:10260: da lam phyag phyir song thos pa rgya chen po dgos pa yin gsungs /
NK128(nyo)001:10261: rin po che thugs sras pas kyang dam bca' nged
NK128(nyo)001:10262: rang gi drung du phul bas skyon med gsungs te
NK128(nyo)001:10263: / bla ma gsum gyi bka' sgrub ste 'byon mar chas pa'i tshe thugs skyo ba'i mgur /
NK128(nyo)001:10264: pha dus gsum bla ma zhal gnyis kyi /
NK128(nyo)001:10265: zhes sogs gsungs te bsam grub rtser phebs /
NK128(nyo)001:10266: brag dmar chos sde'i drung nas la u rgyan rnam thar gyi lung dang zlum po bzhi dbang gnang /
NK128(nyo)001:10267: de nas pan chen gar phebs su byon pas rin
NK128(nyo)001:10268: po che rgya hor rdo rje sogs la chos gsan
NK128(nyo)001:10269: pa sogs gtsang du lo gcig tsam bzhugs te dbus
NK128(nyo)001:10270: la phebs / lha sa dang gung thang 'u shang rdo sogs brgyud /
NK128(nyo)001:10271: gzhung du phebs te rngog gong 'og rnams su rngog dkyil gsan /
NK128(nyo)001:10272: 'phreng bu u rgyan chos rdzong du rin po che
NK128(nyo)001:10273: rgya hor rdo rje'i gsung shog gis mtshams sbyar te
NK128(nyo)001:10274: / kong chen rin po cher dgongs 'dus la sogs sangs rgyas gling pa'i gter kha yongs rdzogs /
NK128(nyo)001:10275: zhang khrom gyi gter skor lcags sdig skor dang /
NK128(nyo)001:10276: gzhan yang khra mo brag pa'i gza' bdud skor dang /
NK128(nyo)001:10277: nyang chos dbang skor sogs mang du gsan cing /
NK128(nyo)001:10278: zla ba gsum bzhugs ring lha lung chos rje gser
NK128(nyo)001:10279: khang pas nas 'bo gsum phul ba'i 'tsho chas tsam
NK128(nyo)001:10280: la brten nas sku mched gnyis kas dka' spyad mdzad
NK128(nyo)001:10281: / rig 'dzin rjes nyin re bzhin bla ma gnyis
NK128(nyo)001:10282: kyi zhabs tog tu dgongs te chu thag ring ba
NK128(nyo)001:10283: nas chab bsu bum pa bcu tsam re chag med
NK128(nyo)001:10284: / len par mdzad / gzhung du byon skabs chu
NK128(nyo)001:10285: nad kyi snyun gzhi byung ba yang sgrib pa sbyangs
NK128(nyo)001:10286: te dag tshul gyi sku dngas /
NK128(nyo)001:10288: nga la snga bu mang du yod de phyir bu khyed gnyis yin pas /
NK128(nyo)001:10289: dpe rnams bris lung bstan thob pa'i mi yin /
NK128(nyo)001:10290: byung na da res tsa rir song ngas zang thal gyis po ti zhig kyang sbyin gyis gsungs /
NK128(nyo)001:10291: de dus tsa rir ma phebs pas rten 'brel 'ga' zhig 'phyugs pa yin gsungs /
NK128(nyo)001:10292: de nas yang rdzong gi la thog tshun kong che rin po ches skyel ma mdzad de /
NK128(nyo)001:10293: kho de khyod gnyis da dung dang phrad yong bsam 'dug ste /
NK128(nyo)001:10294: nga zla ba gsum nas mngon dag'i zhing du 'gro /
NK128(nyo)001:10295: mngon par rdzogs pa'i rtags ma 'jog /
NK128(nyo)001:10296: de nas sprul pas 'gro don byed pa yin /
NK128(nyo)001:10297: bla ma rgan pa 'di khri srong lde btsan gyi
NK128(nyo)001:10298: yon tan gyi sprul pa mnga' bdag gi skye ba
NK128(nyo)001:10299: yin / 'gro don lho phyogs su lo lnga yong mnga' bdag gi bstan pa gso /
NK128(nyo)001:10300: khyed rdo rje bdud 'joms kyi gsung gi sprul pa yin /
NK128(nyo)001:10301: de'i bstan pa dbus mtha' kun tu gso /
NK128(nyo)001:10303: bla ma dgongs 'dus kyi bstan pa 'di shar nas lhor dar /
NK128(nyo)001:10305: nub nas byang du dar zer ba yin /
NK128(nyo)001:10306: pha bu da res las lus rten 'dir mi mjal /
NK128(nyo)001:10307: dag pa'i zhing du mjal bas bstan pa'i rgyal mtshan
NK128(nyo)001:10308: tshugs par gyis shig gsungs te zhal gdams bslab bya
NK128(nyo)001:10309: ngo sprod / byin rten sogs mang du gnang /
NK128(nyo)001:10310: thugs yid 'phreng bzhin du yang rdzong du phebs te gnas rten rnams mjal /
NK128(nyo)001:10311: bsam yas su phebs te rin po che gu ru
NK128(nyo)001:10312: ba dad u rgyan bzang po sogs dang mjal zhing
NK128(nyo)001:10313: bar khang du pan chen rin po che'i bka' brgyad
NK128(nyo)001:10314: sgrub chen sogs gnang ba'i las kyi rdo rjee slob
NK128(nyo)001:10315: dpon mdzad / lho brag tu gu ru pa dang
NK128(nyo)001:10316: sku mched gnyis kas lhan cig phebs pa'i lam yar
NK128(nyo)001:10317: dpon mdzad / klungs brgyud de / rig 'dzin rjes shel brag gi gnas rten rnams mjal /
NK128(nyo)001:10318: lho brag tu gdul bya skyong dgos phal cher pan chen rin po ches gnang zhing /
NK128(nyo)001:10319: srin mo sbar rjes can nas legs ldan rjes zab gter kyi kha byang rnyed /
NK128(nyo)001:10320: pan chen rin po ches kyang bsam 'grub bde ba
NK128(nyo)001:10321: chen po'i gtsug lag khang nas bka' brgyad skor gyi
NK128(nyo)001:10323: slar sku mched gnyis kas dbus su phebs te bsam
NK128(nyo)001:10324: yas steng khang rnam snang gsang sgrom nas zab chos
NK128(nyo)001:10326: ngam ring bde grol phebs pa nas bzung 'di yan phal cher sku mched lhan du phebs shing /
NK128(nyo)001:10327: de nas skabs 'gar lhan du bzhugs shing phal cher
NK128(nyo)001:10328: zab chos kyi 'gro don dang gdul bya so sor
NK128(nyo)001:10329: bskyang pa yin pas rgyas par rnam thar chen mo
NK128(nyo)001:10331: mdo tsam 'bri na legs ldan rjes stod lung btsad po brag tu byon pa dang /
NK128(nyo)001:10332: de nas rmor du pan chen rin po che phebs pa dang mjal zhing gdan sa thel du byon /
NK128(nyo)001:10333: 'bri gung ti sgror 'bri gung pa chos rgyal rin chen phun tshogs dang mjal te /
NK128(nyo)001:10334: thog mar bla ma dgongs 'dus kyi bka' lung phul zhing /
NK128(nyo)001:10335: gzhan yang byang gter dang bka' brgyad bde gshegs 'dus pa /
NK128(nyo)001:10336: rig 'dzin yongs 'dus sogs snga phyi zab chos mang du phul /
NK128(nyo)001:10337: tshur yang dgongs pa yang zab sogs 'ga' zhig kyang
NK128(nyo)001:10338: gsan pas dpon slob dam tshig sel med yin pa
NK128(nyo)001:10339: 'bri gung pa'i rnam thar du gsal /
NK128(nyo)001:10340: 'brong sum mdor rje 'bri gung pas mnga' gsol mdzad
NK128(nyo)001:10341: de rnga sar 'khor lo ris sogs gdan gyi bye
NK128(nyo)001:10342: brag / ber rin chen spungs pa sogs na bza'/
NK128(nyo)001:10343: 'bras shel bkra shis 'khyil sogs dngos spyad /
NK128(nyo)001:10344: dam kha rin chen 'bar ba rgyab yig dang bcas pa /
NK128(nyo)001:10345: chibs rlung sems kyis gtso pa'i rta drel lnga sga 'khor bcas pa /
NK128(nyo)001:10348: khro zangs sogs gnang sbyin rgyas par mdzad cing /
NK128(nyo)001:10349: 'on phu 'bri sgang mchod thebs su 'bul ba sogs
NK128(nyo)001:10350: mdzad pas 'dir phan chod bya bral kho na yin
NK128(nyo)001:10351: kyang 'di nas bzung bla tshugs 'dzin par mdzad de
NK128(nyo)001:10352: dpon slob thugs yid gcig 'dres nas skyel thung dang
NK128(nyo)001:10354: rgya ma rgyud de bsam yas su byon /
NK128(nyo)001:10355: 'di skabs kyang dag snang lung bstan dpag med byung /
NK128(nyo)001:10356: de nas bsam yas sa phug tu sku mtshams la bzhugs ring yang dag snang mang du byung zhing /
NK128(nyo)001:10357: gter srung rnams kyi lung bzhin brag dmar mgrin bzang
NK128(nyo)001:10358: nas shog dril gnyis gter nas bzhes shing thog ser
NK128(nyo)001:10359: sogs 'tshub lhong yang che bar byung /
NK128(nyo)001:10360: dus 'khrug zhi phyir thugs rje byams pa'i man ngag zhag dgur sgrub pa gnang /
NK128(nyo)001:10361: rtse thang nas pan chen rin po che'i gsung shog gi lan phul zhing /
NK128(nyo)001:10362: pha gcig mkhyen rab dbang phyug la /
NK128(nyo)001:10363: bstan pa'i bdag po mi zer ram /
NK128(nyo)001:10365: de nas 'on phyogs su byon te bka' brgyad drag
NK128(nyo)001:10366: po rang byung rang shar gyi sgrub chen sman sgrub
NK128(nyo)001:10367: dang sbrags pa zhig mdzad pas sman zhag gsum la
NK128(nyo)001:10368: langs shing phyi nang gi rtags ngo mtshar can mang
NK128(nyo)001:10369: du byung zhing / gzigs snang du sgrub pa'i dkyil
NK128(nyo)001:10370: 'khor 'od du 'khyil ba'i dbus su che mchog smug
NK128(nyo)001:10371: mthing zhal gcig phyag gnyis pa'i rigs bdag rdo rje
NK128(nyo)001:10372: sems dpa' dkar por yod pa'i 'khor du sgrub sde
NK128(nyo)001:10373: du byung zhing / brgyad dang / sman gyi ga'u'i
NK128(nyo)001:10374: dbus su bdud rtsi 'khyil ba ljang ser zhal gcig
NK128(nyo)001:10376: rta mgrin zhal lnga phyag bcu pa sgo ma bzhis bskor ba sogs gzigs /
NK128(nyo)001:10377: 'di skabs rnam thar chen mor bsnyen dbang la mi
NK128(nyo)001:10378: nyer lnga ma'i dbang cha lnga byung gsung ba la
NK128(nyo)001:10379: dpags na pan chen sku mched gnyis sgrub chen dus
NK128(nyo)001:10380: kyang dbang mi nyer lngar bcad de mdzad pa ma
NK128(nyo)001:10381: gtogs rnying ma ba spyi ltar khro chos mdzad kyi
NK128(nyo)001:10383: de nas sgrub sngas kyi phud rnams pan chen rin
NK128(nyo)001:10384: po cher 'bul bar mdzad pas bka' shog ya mtshan
NK128(nyo)001:10385: can phebs / de dus dag snang du pan chen
NK128(nyo)001:10386: rin po che dang 'bri gung rin chen phun tshogs
NK128(nyo)001:10387: sogs skye brgyud du mar 'brel tshul gyi lung bstan
NK128(nyo)001:10388: can phebs / gsal ba dang / bsam yas bar khang na zab gter yod tshul byung /
NK128(nyo)001:10389: de nas bsam yas su pan chen rin po che
NK128(nyo)001:10390: gdan bzhugs 'bul bar phebs phyag bzhi pa'i rgyud lung
NK128(nyo)001:10391: rnams pan chen rin po cher 'bul ba gnang /
NK128(nyo)001:10392: bar khang gi sgoo gsum steng bee ro'i bzhugs khang
NK128(nyo)001:10393: nang nas bstan pa'i rim gro dang gtsug lag khang
NK128(nyo)001:10394: gso thabs kyi shog dril la tshas can zhig gi
NK128(nyo)001:10396: bsam yas su zhabs skor sogs zla gcig tsam bzhugs rjes 'on 'bri sgang du phebs /
NK128(nyo)001:10397: gzigs snang mang du byung zhing rtogs pa'i mgur du ma bzhes /
NK128(nyo)001:10398: khyad par nub cig rnga yab gling du byon nas
NK128(nyo)001:10399: gtso bo u rgyan chen po zhal gsum phyag drug
NK128(nyo)001:10400: zhabs bgrad pa / g.yas dkar g.yon dmar dbus sngo
NK128(nyo)001:10401: skya khro 'dzum dpal chas kyis brgyan pa dbu gtsug
NK128(nyo)001:10402: na rta mgo gsum yod pa /
NK128(nyo)001:10403: phyag dang po gnyis rdo rje dang thod khrag /
NK128(nyo)001:10404: bar ba gnyis ral gri dang sdigs mdzub /
NK128(nyo)001:10405: tha ma gnyis nyi zla bar snang du brdeb pa /
NK128(nyo)001:10406: yum zhal gsum phyag drug g.yas dkar g.yon sngo da mar ba'i rtse phag zhal gsum ngur ba /
NK128(nyo)001:10407: g.yas gsum gri gug kha t+w+aam lcags kyu /
NK128(nyo)001:10408: g.yon gsum thod khrag ral gri zhags pa 'dzin pa la /
NK128(nyo)001:10409: mtshan brgyad zhal gsum phyag drug pas bskor ba'i sprul
NK128(nyo)001:10410: pa'i dkyil 'khor du dbang bzhi ngo sprod dang bcas
NK128(nyo)001:10411: pa rgyas par gsan cing phyis gnas gsar ba 'jam
NK128(nyo)001:10412: dbyangs mkhyen brtse'i dbang phyug la yang u rgyan chen
NK128(nyo)001:10413: po sku mdog smug nag tsam ma gtogs 'di kho
NK128(nyo)001:10414: na bzhin gyi zhal bstan pa rig 'dzin rjer rgyu
NK128(nyo)001:10415: mtshan zhus pas 'di ltar yin gsungs shing /
NK128(nyo)001:10416: sgrub thabs kyang mdzad de 'jam dbyangs mkhyen brtser gnang
NK128(nyo)001:10417: ba bla ma gnyis ka'i rnam thar cha mthun par
NK128(nyo)001:10418: byung ba yid ches kyi gnas so //
NK128(nyo)001:10419: de nas skabs 'di dang snga phyir gzigs snang mang zhing gsol 'debs zhal gdams /
NK128(nyo)001:10420: gsung mgur sogs kyang mang bar yod /
NK128(nyo)001:10421: de nas 'on phu 'bri sgang gi phu bkra shis
NK128(nyo)001:10422: chos sbug ces pa'i ri khrod du zhal sleb drung
NK128(nyo)001:10423: ras chung pa kun dga' 'od zer bya bas chos
NK128(nyo)001:10424: gzhi bteg nas / yang gsang bla na med pa
NK128(nyo)001:10425: rdzogs pa chen po kun bzang dgongs pa zang thal
NK128(nyo)001:10426: nyams khrid du gnang zhing gegs med du grol ba'i
NK128(nyo)001:10427: gzhi bteg nas / tshogs gral du / 'dir 'dus kyi rdo rje spun tshogs rnams //
NK128(nyo)001:10428: ma yengs rang rig ngang nas gson //
NK128(nyo)001:10429: 'og min chos dbyings pho brang na //
NK128(nyo)001:10430: lhun grub kun bzang zhi khro'i tshogs //
NK128(nyo)001:10431: nyams su rang rig ye shes dga' //
NK128(nyo)001:10432: blo ru lhun grub kyi khyab gdal bde //
NK128(nyo)001:10433: de zag bcas kyi nyams dga' blo bde min //
NK128(nyo)001:10434: don ma bcos sku gsum gyi bzhugs tshul lags //
NK128(nyo)001:10436: de nas 'on mda' sgang dkar du thugs rje chen
NK128(nyo)001:10437: po 'gro 'dul dkyil 'khor du skye bdun sgrub chen
NK128(nyo)001:10438: mdzad dus kyang gzigs snang bsam las 'das pa byung
NK128(nyo)001:10439: / slar yang 'on phur byon te char 'bebs mdzad /
NK128(nyo)001:10440: de skabs yan chad 'on phu stag tshang gu ru'i gnas chen yin par grags shing /
NK128(nyo)001:10441: sprul sku u rgyan gling pas zab gter spyan drangs
NK128(nyo)001:10442: pa tsam las sus kyang 'gro 'ong med par gzigs
NK128(nyo)001:10443: snang gi brdas bskul nas stag tshang gi gnas sgo
NK128(nyo)001:10444: phye ste sngar sus kyang longs ma spyod pa'i phug
NK128(nyo)001:10445: pa rnying ba sgo rdo chen gsum gyis bkag pa
NK128(nyo)001:10446: bsal nas nang du phebs pas /
NK128(nyo)001:10447: gu ru chen po'i bzhugs khri sogs rnyed cing /
NK128(nyo)001:10448: re zhig bzhugs sar lhongs dang cho 'phrul du ma
NK128(nyo)001:10449: byung ba'i mthar gnas kyi lo rgyus sogs rgyas par
NK128(nyo)001:10450: mtshan lam du gnas srung gis bstan pa ltar rnyed
NK128(nyo)001:10451: / gzigs snang sogs du ma byung zhing mkha' 'gro'i lung bstan du /
NK128(nyo)001:10452: u rgyan mkhan po seng ge sgras //
NK128(nyo)001:10453: dregs pa dbang bsdus zil gyis mnan //
NK128(nyo)001:10454: mal dro gzi can la sogs pa'i //
NK128(nyo)001:10455: klu dang sa bdag dam la btags //
NK128(nyo)001:10456: zhabs rjes khri dang lnga brgya yod //
NK128(nyo)001:10457: rang byon lha sku brgya phrag gcig /
NK128(nyo)001:10459: deng sang yang zhabs rjes shin tu mang ba dang /
NK128(nyo)001:10460: rig 'dzin rje rang gi zhabs rjes gsal ba dang /
NK128(nyo)001:10461: lha sku yig 'bru sogs shin tu mang ba mjal rgyu yod /
NK128(nyo)001:10462: de ltar stag tshang nas gu ru drag po dbu dgu'i skor rgyud dang bcas pa /
NK128(nyo)001:10463: rta mgrin srog 'phrog dregs pa zil gnon gyi skor sogs zab gter mang du bzhes shing /
NK128(nyo)001:10464: 'on phu mda' rnams su re zhig bzhugs pa'i tshe
NK128(nyo)001:10465: 'bri gung nas chos mang du gsan bzhed kyi spyan
NK128(nyo)001:10466: 'dren byung bar zhal bzhes phul zhing /
NK128(nyo)001:10467: thog mar bsam yas su tshur phebs dgos tshul gyi zhu ba mdzad de /
NK128(nyo)001:10468: de'i phyir du 'on gzhung la sdum bu mdzad de
NK128(nyo)001:10469: grabs yul gnang nas bsam yas su pan chen rin
NK128(nyo)001:10470: po cher rgyu mtshan phul bas /
NK128(nyo)001:10471: khyod chos brgyad ches 'bri gung pa tsam mgron por 'bod pa'i stobs cha lags ci yod gsung /
NK128(nyo)001:10472: cung zad bkyon pa la tshigs bcad kyi ku re phul zhing /
NK128(nyo)001:10473: rje 'bri gung pa yang phebs te sku mched gnyis
NK128(nyo)001:10474: dang bcas te bsam yas su bstan pa gso thabs
NK128(nyo)001:10476: bsam yas phu 'ja' stod dgon par sku mtshams dam par mdzad /
NK128(nyo)001:10477: gzigs snang mang du byung zhing /
NK128(nyo)001:10478: gnas gu yangs 'ja' stod brag steng na //
NK128(nyo)001:10479: mi gu yangs mnga' ris lha btsun dang //
NK128(nyo)001:10480: chos gu yangs lo 'das rjen pa skyong //
NK128(nyo)001:10481: zhes sogs nyams mgur mang du gsungs /
NK128(nyo)001:10482: der gsol chas kyang bkren par byung nas phal cher zwa'i dka' thub kho na mdzad par gsal te /
NK128(nyo)001:10484: zwa thug sngon mo'i tshogs mchod 'di dang gcig /
NK128(nyo)001:10485: tshogs snod 'khyags pa'i lo bde 'di dang gnyis //
NK128(nyo)001:10486: mthun rkyen spen ma'i skyo ra 'di dang gsum //
NK128(nyo)001:10488: sku mtshams de grol nas tshar gsum khug pa dang bir srung sogs 'ga' zhig gnang /
NK128(nyo)001:10489: slar yang pan chen rin po che'i bka' bzhin 'on smon ldan du byon nas chos mang du gsungs /
NK128(nyo)001:10490: slar bsam yas su phebs pas zas grib la brten
NK128(nyo)001:10491: pa'i shin tu snyung ba zhig gi mthar re zhig
NK128(nyo)001:10492: zhal dbugs kyang chad pa'i tshe /
NK128(nyo)001:10493: u rgyan chen po rigs lnga mtshan brgyad dang bcas
NK128(nyo)001:10494: pa byon te sku tshe'i lung bstan zhing tshe dbang
NK128(nyo)001:10495: bskur bas slar sku khams dngas bar gyur /
NK128(nyo)001:10496: de nas rje 'bri gung pa snye mor phebs te
NK128(nyo)001:10497: gdan 'dren byung ba bzhin phebs te rnying ma rgyud
NK128(nyo)001:10498: 'bum sogs chos mang du phul nas /
NK128(nyo)001:10499: gzhu'i phu dang mtshur phu dang stod lung du phebs
NK128(nyo)001:10500: pas sbas lung 'bras gshongs su phebs dgos pa'i lung
NK128(nyo)001:10501: bstan byung / stod lung 'phar tshang brag nas rdzogs chen snying po bsdus pa dang /
NK128(nyo)001:10502: phyag chen sems kyi me long gi zab gter bzhes /
NK128(nyo)001:10503: stag lung brag tu zang thal tshar gcig dang /
NK128(nyo)001:10505: de nas chu bo ri lcags zam rtse'i dgon bdag
NK128(nyo)001:10506: mdzad cing zang thal gyi khrid ka btsugs pas gzigs
NK128(nyo)001:10507: snang lung bstan dpag med byung /
