NK128(nyo)001:10508: mtsho rgyal phug nas bla ma sku gsum ma'i skor
NK128(nyo)001:10509: dang gnas bdag skyin mthing ma'i sgrub skor sogs zab
NK128(nyo)001:10510: ga ter bzhes te nyams bzhes mdzad pas dag snang
NK128(nyo)001:10512: na mo zhen med kyi nyams shar gtad so med /
NK128(nyo)001:10513: rgyal ba'i bzhugs gnas tshe chu phug /
NK128(nyo)001:10514: dus gsum gyi sangs rgyas u rgyan la //
NK128(nyo)001:10515: dpa' bo dang mkha' 'gros yongs bskor nas //
NK128(nyo)001:10516: bdag rgyud la byin gyis rlob pa'i tshe //
NK128(nyo)001:10517: gzung 'dzin gyi rtog pa dbyings su dag /
NK128(nyo)001:10518: dri med kyi shes pa rjen par bud //
NK128(nyo)001:10519: rang rig la rgyal po chos kyi sku'i //
NK128(nyo)001:10520: pho sgo de ring rang gis mthong //
NK128(nyo)001:10521: bka' drin la che'o rig pa'i sku //
NK128(nyo)001:10522: mngon sum gyi ye shes mchod par bzhes //
NK128(nyo)001:10523: snang bzhi la mthar phyin dngos grub zhu //
NK128(nyo)001:10525: de nas 'on smon ldan du pan chen rin po che mjal /
NK128(nyo)001:10526: lha sar jo bo rin po cher brtag dril phul
NK128(nyo)001:10527: zhing babs te sbas yul phyogs su lo skor gcig
NK128(nyo)001:10528: 'bad pa'i dam bca' dang bcas te 'bras ga shogs
NK128(nyo)001:10529: phyogs su byon te rgyal rtser phebs /
NK128(nyo)001:10530: mnga' ris sa 'dra dang mjal te /
NK128(nyo)001:10531: rje drang po ba gshegs pa'i gtam gsan nas gsol 'debs mdzad /
NK128(nyo)001:10532: 'bri mtshams mdo khra gcen lugs sogs brgyud de /
NK128(nyo)001:10533: rim bzhin byon nas re zhig la stod byang phyogs
NK128(nyo)001:10534: su phebs pas thugs sras nam mkha' rgyal mtshan gshegs
NK128(nyo)001:10535: pa'i gtam gsan pas gsol 'debs mdzad pas sku dngos
NK128(nyo)001:10536: su bstan te lung bstan dang ngo sprod zhal gdams
NK128(nyo)001:10537: gsan / de nas bde grol du gdung mchod phul zhing gdung sras mjal /
NK128(nyo)001:10538: bkra bzang du phebs te rnam mjoms lha khang du dag snang shar zhag shas bzhugs /
NK128(nyo)001:10539: bka' brgyad rang shar gyi cha lag zhig gter nas bzhes /
NK128(nyo)001:10540: 'di phyi'i zhabs drung bdag por gnang ba gsan yig tu yod /
NK128(nyo)001:10541: rig 'dzin rgod ldem can gyi sdon gnas gsal bar dran te gter gnas spo ba dang /
NK128(nyo)001:10542: gter kha gso dgos sogs mdzad /
NK128(nyo)001:10543: sa skya mjal nas gnam kha 'ur byon te dpal
NK128(nyo)001:10544: mgon zhal gyi dag snang gzigs shing bskang bstod mdzad
NK128(nyo)001:10545: / de nas slar yang gnas chen phyogs su phebs
NK128(nyo)001:10546: te gcen lung gi phur gnas tshad ma byung ba
NK128(nyo)001:10547: la bden pa brdar bas ser ba bol nub tsam
NK128(nyo)001:10548: / babs / brag 'og cig tu thugs nyams shar ba'i mgur 'di ltar gsungs pa /
NK128(nyo)001:10549: skye yul mnga' ris glo bo yin kyang //
NK128(nyo)001:10550: rgyal khams phyogs med kun tu 'khyams pa //
NK128(nyo)001:10551: yul med bdag ni blo re bde bas //
NK128(nyo)001:10552: da ni pha yul dgos pa mi gda' //
NK128(nyo)001:10553: rigs ni gung thang rgyal brgyud yin kyang //
NK128(nyo)001:10554: rgyal srid dor nas bya btang byas pas //
NK128(nyo)001:10555: lha btsun bdag ni lo re bde bas //
NK128(nyo)001:10556: da ni rgyal srid dgos pa mi gda' //
NK128(nyo)001:10557: zhes sogs nges par 'byung ba'i mgur gsungs /
NK128(nyo)001:10558: de nas mdo khra sogs la phebs te bzhugs /
NK128(nyo)001:10559: nag sdengs chu skor rma bya lung sogs brgyud gzigs snang dang bstun bzhin byon /
NK128(nyo)001:10560: lho nags kyi dug ri'i rtser lcog phub la brten pa'i sku mtshams bdun gcig mdzad /
NK128(nyo)001:10561: mgon po phyag drug pa'i sgrub skor gyi zab gter
NK128(nyo)001:10562: 'di'i chos bdag mjam dbyangs mkhyen brtse yin kyang gnang
NK128(nyo)001:10563: ma thub / der rdo lha'i mchod khang bzhengs /
NK128(nyo)001:10564: re zhig gnas sgo phyi nang rnams su bzhugs /
NK128(nyo)001:10565: dag snang dang lung bstan dpag med byung /
NK128(nyo)001:10566: dbang khrid gdams pa mang du gnang /
NK128(nyo)001:10567: de'i tshe dbus su pan chen rin po che zhing
NK128(nyo)001:10568: khams 'phos pa'i rkyen gyis re zhig tshur phebs dgos
NK128(nyo)001:10573: lha sa sogs su phebs te gdul bya bskyangs /
NK128(nyo)001:10574: 'bri gung du phebs te nyid kyi gter gsar phyag
NK128(nyo)001:10575: rdzogs skor dang rten 'brel chos bdun sogs phul zhing
NK128(nyo)001:10577: spro lung du bzhugs pa'i tshe nyer lnga zhig la
NK128(nyo)001:10578: chos dbang rat+na sogs kyi rnam thar mthun pa'i rnga
NK128(nyo)001:10579: yab gling gi dag snang rgyas shing ngo mtshar ba
NK128(nyo)001:10580: byung / slar yang 'bras gshongs phyogs su phebs te
NK128(nyo)001:10581: spa gro stag tshang nas rin po che kah thog
NK128(nyo)001:10582: pa rnam grol bzang po drang lung chos sdings su
NK128(nyo)001:10584: mnga' ris gung thang nas gdan 'dren byung yang phebs mi thub pa'i rgyu mtshan phul /
NK128(nyo)001:10585: byang sgo ba ri stag tshang sogs rim bzhin phebs /
NK128(nyo)001:10586: mtsho khra'i mdor phebs tshe lho bod kyi lha 'dre
NK128(nyo)001:10587: 'khrugs pa'i kha rlangs su nyin zhag gnyis kyi bar
NK128(nyo)001:10588: kha ba cher byung ba la /
NK128(nyo)001:10589: u rgyan chen por smre sngags kyi mgur gsol 'debs su mdzad pas nyi ma dro bar gyur /
NK128(nyo)001:10590: de nas gnas bdag lha ri gangs sman gyi dngos
NK128(nyo)001:10591: nyams du mar lung bstan pa bzhin gnas nang du
NK128(nyo)001:10592: gegs med phebs / lha ri rin chen snying po'i
NK128(nyo)001:10593: mgul nas 'chi med bdud rtsi 'khyil ba'i skor gyi
NK128(nyo)001:10594: zab gter bzhes pa sogs rnam thar chen mor gsal
NK128(nyo)001:10595: gegs med phebs / zhing / gnas chen 'di'i phyogs su lan mang du byon zhing /
NK128(nyo)001:10596: dbyar dgun thog re tsam yang /
NK128(nyo)001:10597: mang du bzhugs pa sogs zhib cha rnam thar chen mor gsal /
NK128(nyo)001:10598: mdor na snga phyir zab gter yang mang du bzhes shing gsang mtshan rdo rje gro lod rtsal dang /
NK128(nyo)001:10600: pad+ma nag po sogs yongs su grags /
NK128(nyo)001:10601: de ltar sbas yul 'bras mo gshongs kyi gnas sgo legs par phye zhing u rgyan 'ja' 'od phug /
NK128(nyo)001:10603: lha ri rin chen snying po sogs kyi gnas rnams
NK128(nyo)001:10604: gtan la phab ste slar yang dbus phyogs su byon
NK128(nyo)001:10607: snye mo lcam mkhyen rtse ma las rgyar bzhes te
NK128(nyo)001:10608: rigs sras grub chen thang stong rgyal po'i rnam sprul
NK128(nyo)001:10609: rgyal sras pad+ma chos rgyal bskrun te bka' gter bstan
NK128(nyo)001:10611: gzhan yang zur dbang phyug rdo rje /
NK128(nyo)001:10612: bya pa khri dpon sogs che dgus zhabs nas bteg /
NK128(nyo)001:10613: gtsang du gnas gsar ba 'jam dbyangs mkhyen brtse'i dbang phyug khu dbon dang lan du mar mjal zhing /
NK128(nyo)001:10614: rje 'di la mchog tu gus pa'i tshul khong rang
NK128(nyo)001:10615: gi rnam thar dang gsung mgur sogs las gsal zhing
NK128(nyo)001:10616: / khyad par nyug rgyal khang du 'dus pa chen
NK128(nyo)001:10617: po mdo'i dbang bskur yongs rdzogs gnang zhing lung zin
NK128(nyo)001:10618: gyi slob ma chos bdag gi gtso bo yin pas
NK128(nyo)001:10619: slob rgyun rnams dang dam tshig sel med kyi rgyun
NK128(nyo)001:10620: / bzang / spyir dam pa 'dis yongs 'dzin gyi
NK128(nyo)001:10621: bla ma mang du bsten pa dang las ldan gyi
NK128(nyo)001:10622: slob bu mang du byung tshul sogs kyang /
NK128(nyo)001:10624: pha yis dbu gtsos bla ma nga lnga bsten //
NK128(nyo)001:10625: mdo rgyud man ngag bka' lung dpag med zhus //
NK128(nyo)001:10626: da lta bu slob tha dad kun tu 'phrod //
NK128(nyo)001:10627: snang ba 'dir bde da ni sgrub la 'bad //
NK128(nyo)001:10628: rang las lhag pa'i bla ma rnam pa bdun //
NK128(nyo)001:10629: rtse gcig sgrub brtson grub chen rnam pa bcu //
NK128(nyo)001:10630: rigs rus gcig pa'i dbon po rnam pa lnga //
NK128(nyo)001:10631: mkhyen rtogs ldan pa'i bshes gnyen rnam bcu dang //
NK128(nyo)001:10632: dad gus ldan pa'i bud med chos 'chad lnga //
NK128(nyo)001:10633: dad brtson ldan pa'i 'brel thogs dpag yas rnams //
NK128(nyo)001:10634: zhes gsungs pas rtogs nus la /
NK128(nyo)001:10635: spyir dus kun snang srid dag pa rab 'byams su
NK128(nyo)001:10636: shar bas bla ma yi dam dpa' bo mkha' 'gro
NK128(nyo)001:10637: chos srung du ma'i zhal gzigs shing /
NK128(nyo)001:10638: gsar rnying gi yi dam thams cad la yang sprul
NK128(nyo)001:10639: pa'i dkyil 'khor du dbang gsan cing zhal ma gzigs
NK128(nyo)001:10640: pa med / khyad par u rgyan chen po'i zhal nyer lnga gzigs te /
NK128(nyo)001:10642: pad+ma'i zab gter lon pa yin //
NK128(nyo)001:10643: u rgyan rje dang nyer lnga mjal //
NK128(nyo)001:10644: gdams pa'i ngo sprod thob pa yin //
NK128(nyo)001:10646: gzhan yang bsam yas steng khang rnam snang thugs ka
NK128(nyo)001:10647: nas zab chos 'khor ba dbyings sgrol gyi skor spyan
NK128(nyo)001:10648: drangs te 'bri gung thel gyi gser khang chos rje'i
NK128(nyo)001:10649: steng khang du shog ser phab cing chos bka' zhal
NK128(nyo)001:10650: phye bas bum pa'i kha rgyan las me tog 'khrungs
NK128(nyo)001:10651: pa sogs ngo mtshar dpag med byung ba dang /
NK128(nyo)001:10652: chu bo rir byang gter mgon po bstan srung yongs
NK128(nyo)001:10653: rdzogs kyi ljags bsnyen mdzad pas gsar rnying gi chos
NK128(nyo)001:10654: skyong rnams kyi zhal cig car du bstan pa dang
NK128(nyo)001:10655: / chu bo rir bde dgyes gsang 'jigs ma h+aa
NK128(nyo)001:10656: ma ya sogs gsar ma'i rgyud sde'i lha lus dkyil
NK128(nyo)001:10657: gyi tshul du gzigs te rang nyid yi dam so
NK128(nyo)001:10659: dam can rnams bran du 'khol bas 'phrin las la
NK128(nyo)001:10660: thogs pa med cing rtag par zhal ston pa dang
NK128(nyo)001:10661: / bsam yas su gnod sbyin chen po ar la gtad de slar dam bzhag mdzad pa dang /
NK128(nyo)001:10662: rtag par bshad sgrub 'chad nyan kho nas dus 'da'
NK128(nyo)001:10663: bar mdzad tshul sogs rgyas par rnam thar chen mo
NK128(nyo)001:10664: dang mgur 'bum gsan yig sogs las shes dgos pas
NK128(nyo)001:10665: 'dir mdo tsam smos pa yin la /
NK128(nyo)001:10666: de nas dgung lo brgya phrag tsam du nye ba
NK128(nyo)001:10667: na sngon pan chen rin po che'i sprul sku 'byon
NK128(nyo)001:10668: par bka' stsal pa de nyid g.yas su byang pa'i
NK128(nyo)001:10669: rigs su 'khrungs shing chos bka' btsal ba'i dus la
NK128(nyo)001:10670: bab par gzigs te chu bo ri nas la stod
NK128(nyo)001:10672: byang nas chos rgyal bkra shis stobs rgyal yang sngon
NK128(nyo)001:10673: gnas rjes dran gyi tshul du bag chags sad de
NK128(nyo)001:10674: dam pa 'di nyid spyan 'dren par btang ba rten
NK128(nyo)001:10675: 'brel shugs kyis 'grigs te byang ngam ring gi phyogs
NK128(nyo)001:10676: su phebs te zhal mjal zhing /
NK128(nyo)001:10677: snga 'gyur bka' gter gyi gdams ngag phal che ba
NK128(nyo)001:10678: bum pa gang byo'i tshul du mdzad de chos kyi
NK128(nyo)001:10679: bdag por bskos / ma 'ongs lung bstan yang mang du gnang /
NK128(nyo)001:10680: chos rgyal byang pas gsang ri zhes par snga 'gyur
NK128(nyo)001:10681: rdo rje theg pa'i chos grwa cher btsugs pa'i mkhan
NK128(nyo)001:10682: po mdzad cing gang 'dul gdul bya'i re ba bkang
NK128(nyo)001:10683: nas dgung lo brgya dang bcu gsum du phebs pa'i
NK128(nyo)001:10684: tshe re zhig zhing 'di'i gdul bya rdzogs par mkhyen
NK128(nyo)001:10685: nas / gsang sngags theg mchog gling gi lha gnas
NK128(nyo)001:10686: dga' ba'i tshal du rdzogs chen zang thal gyi bar
NK128(nyo)001:10687: do lnga'i snyan brgyud gsung ba'i tshe mya ngan las
NK128(nyo)001:10689: chos rgyal chen pos rab tu mya ngan las mi mda' bar bzhugs pa dang /
NK128(nyo)001:10690: gal te zhing khams 'pho srid na /
NK128(nyo)001:10691: sprul sku myur du 'byon dgos par gsol ba btab pas /
NK128(nyo)001:10692: nga da res bsdad pas yong ba med /
NK128(nyo)001:10693: khyod nga la de tsam du gtsigs che na khyod rang gi bur yong ngo //
NK128(nyo)001:10694: zhes lung bstan te glang lo'i ston nyer gsum la zhi bar gshegs /
NK128(nyo)001:10695: 'di la 'ga' zhig gi las sbyor brtsams pa'i mthu
NK128(nyo)001:10696: rtags su dril rgya cher sgrog par byed mod kyang
NK128(nyo)001:10697: / mi lo brgya dang bcu gsum tsam du bshad
NK128(nyo)001:10698: sgrub kyi bya ba mthar phyin nas gshegs pa rang
NK128(nyo)001:10699: mthu rtags su mi 'gro ba 'dra ste /
NK128(nyo)001:10700: mdzad pa 'phror lus te rkyen drag pos gshegs pa tsho mthu rtags su sgrog pa zhu /
NK128(nyo)001:10701: bstan 'dzin gyi skyes bu rnams mthus bkrongs par bsgrags
NK128(nyo)001:10702: na rang nyid rgyu 'bras mi shes pa'i rgyur 'gyur
NK128(nyo)001:10703: ro // de'i tshe byang du yang dus 'gyur byung
NK128(nyo)001:10704: bar brten sku gdung yid bzhin gyi nor bu rim
NK128(nyo)001:10705: bzhin dbus phyogs chu bo rir spyan drangs te zhugs
NK128(nyo)001:10706: ro // la phul zhing / gdung khang gi za
NK128(nyo)001:10707: ma tog byin rlabs kyi gzi byin 'bar ba deng
NK128(nyo)001:10708: sang yang chu bo ri lcags zam rtser mchod pa'i
NK128(nyo)001:10709: gnas su ma nyams par bzhugs so //
NK128(nyo)001:10710: lha ris grub pa'i 'khor los sgyur ba'i rgyal //
NK128(nyo)001:10711: theg mchog bstan pa'i shing rta rig 'dzin mchog /
NK128(nyo)001:10712: legs ldan bdud 'joms rdo rje dpal bzang po'i //
NK128(nyo)001:10713: ngo mtshar mdzad pa'i tshul la snying nas dad //
NK128(nyo)001:10714: khyod sngon bzang skyong lha yi bur 'khrungs shing //
NK128(nyo)001:10715: u rgyan drung na rdo rje bdud 'joms rje //
NK128(nyo)001:10716: snyigs dus bstan pa'i sgron me gro lod rtsal //
NK128(nyo)001:10717: bsam bzhin srid par skye sprul sna tshogs ston //
NK128(nyo)001:10718: zab pa gter dang rnam dag bka' ma'i rgyun //
NK128(nyo)001:10719: dam chos bdud rtsi dpal la mnga' 'byor zhing //
NK128(nyo)001:10720: rang gter chos kyi bgo skal nyer blangs te //
NK128(nyo)001:10721: dus babs 'gro ba'i don mdzad ngo mtshar gnas //
NK128(nyo)001:10723: bla ma dam pa des skyi ston tshe ring dbang po rjes su bzung ba yin te /
NK128(nyo)001:10724: dam pa 'di'i rnam thar rgyas par ma rnyed kyang mdo tsam bri ba'i dbang du byas na /
NK128(nyo)001:10725: de yang gdung ni phur pa jo mo lugs las
NK128(nyo)001:10726: grub pa brnyes pa lang lab byang chub rdo rje
NK128(nyo)001:10727: zhes bya ba / rwa lo rdo rje grags sogs
NK128(nyo)001:10728: kyang mthu stobs dang nus pas pham par mdzad pa
NK128(nyo)001:10729: bcom ldan 'das rdo rje gzhon nu nyid dang dgongs
NK128(nyo)001:10730: pa dbyer med pa de la slob ma'i mchog bzhi
NK128(nyo)001:10732: mdo rgu'i skyi nag gyang 'gyel zhes bya ba /
NK128(nyo)001:10733: yum mi rnams kyis nor phyugs khang zhing thams cad
NK128(nyo)001:10734: phrogs pa la brten lang lab la phur pa zhus
NK128(nyo)001:10735: pas dbang rgyud man ngag bstan te rjes su bzung
NK128(nyo)001:10736: nas / zla ba dgu bsnyen gyis /
NK128(nyo)001:10737: de nas bse lcags shes gsum la zla ba gnyis sgrubs shig don 'grub bo //
NK128(nyo)001:10738: zhes lung bstan pa ltar sgrub pas drod tshad brnyes nas phyin byon pas /
NK128(nyo)001:10739: gyang zhig gi drung na mi mang po nyi ma
NK128(nyo)001:10740: 'de zhing 'dug pa la thams cad dgrar ma gyur
NK128(nyo)001:10742: gong khug nas phur pa phyungs te gyang la btab
NK128(nyo)001:10743: pas gyang 'gyel ba'i thibs 'og tu mi kun shi
NK128(nyo)001:10744: bas skyi nag gyang 'gyel du grags shing /
NK128(nyo)001:10748: gyang 'gyel ni mthu stobs kyi dpa' mtshan du grags /
NK128(nyo)001:10749: mkhyen rab che bas rgyud 'grel man ngag thams cad bdag por gyur /
NK128(nyo)001:10750: grub pa'i dbang phyug de'i rigs las byung bas na
NK128(nyo)001:10751: skyi ston dang mtshan dngos rigs sngags 'chang ba tshe
NK128(nyo)001:10752: ring dbang por grags pa de nyid /
NK128(nyo)001:10753: gzhon nu nas mkhas grub kyi dam pa du ma bsten cing /
NK128(nyo)001:10754: dam pa'i chos spyi dang bye brag snga 'gyur bka'
NK128(nyo)001:10755: gter gyi zab chos du mas thugs kyi bum bzang
NK128(nyo)001:10757: khyad par gtsang nyug gi rgyal khang du gnas gsar
NK128(nyo)001:10758: pa thams cad mkhyen pa mkhyen brtse'i dbang phyug gis
NK128(nyo)001:10759: / rig 'dzin mnga' ris pa chen po legs ldan
NK128(nyo)001:10760: bdud 'joms rdo rje spyan drangs te 'dus pa chen
NK128(nyo)001:10761: po mdo'i dbang yongs su rdzogs pa /
NK128(nyo)001:10762: rgyab rten mdo dgongs 'dus kyi lung dang bcas pa
NK128(nyo)001:10763: gsan pa'i tshe sngags 'chang tshe ring dbang po nyid
NK128(nyo)001:10764: kyang rig 'dzin rjes brtse ba chen pos rjes bzung
NK128(nyo)001:10765: ste phyis bstan pa'i gsal byed chen por 'gyur ba
NK128(nyo)001:10766: mngon par mkhyen pas gzigs te dbang rgyud man ngag
NK128(nyo)001:10767: thams cad gab sbas med par gnang zhing /
NK128(nyo)001:10768: gsang mtshan rol pa'i rdo rje zhes grags so //
NK128(nyo)001:10769: rang don du rtogs pa mngon du 'gyur bar bya
NK128(nyo)001:10770: ba'i phyir grub pa'i gnas chen du mar yo ga
NK128(nyo)001:10771: gsum gyi rnal 'byor la brtson par mdzad pas grub
NK128(nyo)001:10772: mtshan du ma mngon du gyur zhing /
NK128(nyo)001:10773: gzhan don gdul bya'i slob ma du ma smin grol gyi lam la 'god par mdzad /
NK128(nyo)001:10774: de'i tshe gnas gsar ba grub pa'i dpa' bo rdo rje dbang phyug rab brtan nyid kyi bka' las /
NK128(nyo)001:10775: rig 'dzin mnga' ris pa chen po nyid las brgyud
NK128(nyo)001:10776: pa'i 'dus pa mdo'i dbang 'di nyid rig sngags 'chang
NK128(nyo)001:10777: ba khyod kyis spel bar gyis shig ces dgongs pas
NK128(nyo)001:10778: byin gyis brlab pa'i mthu la brten gtsang sde srid
NK128(nyo)001:10779: nas kyang mkho dgu'i rnyed pa stob pa dang /
NK128(nyo)001:10780: slob ma'i tshogs bsdu bar bka' gnang ste pho brang
NK128(nyo)001:10781: chen po bsam grub rtse spel dkar zhes bya bar
NK128(nyo)001:10782: snga 'gyur bka' ma'i chos kyi bdag po zur 'ug
NK128(nyo)001:10783: bya lung pa'i zhal ngo zur bstan 'dzin rdo rjes
NK128(nyo)001:10784: gtsos 'dus pa rnams la bstan pa yongs rdzogs kyi
NK128(nyo)001:10785: smin grol gyi 'jug ngogs chen po 'dus pa mdo'i
NK128(nyo)001:10786: dbang gtad rgyar bcas pa rgyas par mdzad pa yin
NK128(nyo)001:10787: te / de dag gi bsdus don rig 'dzin brgyud
NK128(nyo)001:10788: pa'i dbang byang khyab bdag sman lung pa chen pos
NK128(nyo)001:10789: te / mdzad pa las / 'jam dbyangs mkhyen brtse'i bka' drin las //
NK128(nyo)001:10790: legs ldan bdud 'joms rdo rje mjal //
NK128(nyo)001:10791: mdo dbang smin grol gdams rdzogs nas //
NK128(nyo)001:10792: rgyab rten mdo lung dgongs 'dus gsan //
NK128(nyo)001:10793: dbang phyug rab brtan rgyal ba yi //
NK128(nyo)001:10794: dgongs pas byin rlabs med dbang rgyun //
NK128(nyo)001:10795: khyed kyis spel zhes gnang ba thob //
NK128(nyo)001:10796: pho brang bsam rtse'i spel dkar du //
NK128(nyo)001:10797: mdo dbang gtad rgyar bcas pa mdzad //
NK128(nyo)001:10798: skyi ston tshe ring dbang por grags //
NK128(nyo)001:10799: gsang mtshan rol pa'i rdo rje ste //
NK128(nyo)001:10800: da lta rig 'dzin gnas na bzhugs zhes dang //
NK128(nyo)001:10802: brag dmar chos lung don pa ru //
NK128(nyo)001:10803: skyi ston tshe ring dbang po ni //
NK128(nyo)001:10804: bka' gter chos kyi rgyal srid 'dzin //
NK128(nyo)001:10805: zhes gsungs pa don la gnas pas /
NK128(nyo)001:10806: mkhyen brtse nus gsum gyi mnga' bdag tu gyur nas /
NK128(nyo)001:10807: ngam ring mkhan chen klu sgrub chos kyi rgyal mtshan /
NK128(nyo)001:10808: bla chen bres pa sogs gzhan phan nus pa'i slob tshogs mang du bskrun pa'i mthar /
NK128(nyo)001:10809: zhing 'di'i gdul bya rdzogs te 'og min tshogs chen
NK128(nyo)001:10810: gyi dkyil 'khor du rig 'dzin grub pa'i sar gshegs
NK128(nyo)001:10811: so // bla ma dam pa des bla chen bres
NK128(nyo)001:10812: gshongs pa chos rgyal rdo rje rjes su bzung ba
NK128(nyo)001:10813: so // yin te / 'di'i rnam thar mdo tsam brjod na /
NK128(nyo)001:10814: 'khrungs yul ni g.yas ru gtsang gi sa'i cha bres gshongs zhes bya ba yin la /
NK128(nyo)001:10815: gdung ni gnyag gi rigs las mang ra 'bum smyon
NK128(nyo)001:10816: zhes bya ba zur pak+shi sh+aaka 'od dang dus mtshungs
NK128(nyo)001:10817: shing / zur pas brag rdo rje tshe brten nas
NK128(nyo)001:10818: u rgyan gyi tshe chu mu men gyi bum pa
NK128(nyo)001:10819: gang yod pa 'don par bskul ba ltar mang ra
NK128(nyo)001:10820: 'bum smyon gyis bton nas phul zhing /
NK128(nyo)001:10821: tshe chu des hor se chen rgyal po'i tshe bsrings pa'i lo rgyus kyang snang /
NK128(nyo)001:10822: de ltar bu'i 'bum smyon gyi rgyud las byung ba yab rig 'dzin pad+ma bdud 'dul dang /
NK128(nyo)001:10823: yum rnam rgyal sgron ma'i sras su chu pho stag
NK128(nyo)001:10824: lo ston zla 'bring po'i tshes lnga gza' pa sangs
NK128(nyo)001:10825: dang skar ma nam gru la 'khrungs shing mtshan 'jam
NK128(nyo)001:10826: dbyangs chos rgyal rdo rje btags /
NK128(nyo)001:10827: bcu gcig par bris klog sogs sbyangs /
NK128(nyo)001:10828: bco lnga par yab las pha chos sgyu 'phrul zhi khro'i dbang dang gsar snying gi lung /
NK128(nyo)001:10829: 'jam dbyangs bla ma'i rtsa gsum dril sgrub /
NK128(nyo)001:10830: na rag dong sprug drag dmar nyang lugs 'char ka /
NK128(nyo)001:10831: smyung gnas dpal mo lugs sogs gsan /
NK128(nyo)001:10832: yab mes kyi grub mtha' skyong ba'i phyir snga 'gyur
NK128(nyo)001:10833: bka' ma'i bstan pa'i 'byung khungs zur 'ug bya lung
NK128(nyo)001:10834: du yab yum gyi bkas bskul nas thugs gnyer la
NK128(nyo)001:10835: byon nas sgyu 'phrul dang legs ldan skor sogs gsan
NK128(nyo)001:10836: cing / thugs gnyer dang phyag bzhes rnams mtha' chod par sbyangs /
NK128(nyo)001:10837: zur mo chos ldan bzang mo 'od gsal gsang skor dang sgyu 'phrul skor sogs gsan /
NK128(nyo)001:10838: mnga' ris 'od gsal mchog ldan zhes pa'i grub pa'i dbang phyug gi snyan pas thugs phrogs te /
NK128(nyo)001:10839: gtsang rong chu tshan lha rgang zhes bya bar byon
NK128(nyo)001:10840: nas bla ma yang tig gi nyams khrid steng nas
NK128(nyo)001:10841: ka dag gi thugs ngo sprad cing /
NK128(nyo)001:10842: lhun grub kyi nyams snang gtan la phab /
NK128(nyo)001:10843: de bzhin du zab mo yang tig /
NK128(nyo)001:10844: mkha' 'gro yang tig /'gro mgon dung mtsho ras pa'i
NK128(nyo)001:10845: yang tig nag po gser gyi 'bru gcig gi mun
NK128(nyo)001:10846: khrid sogs zab lam rdzogs pa chen po'i gdams pa
NK128(nyo)001:10847: dang / nyang gi bka' brgyad bde gshegs 'dus pa'i dbang lung /
NK128(nyo)001:10848: pad gling tshe khrid rdo 'phreng sogs gter kha mang po'i chos skor dang ma cig gi gcod skor /
NK128(nyo)001:10849: 'bri gung lugs kyi dz+aa b+hir rlung khrid sogs du ma gsan /
NK128(nyo)001:10850: rab tu byung bar bzhed nas gtsug phud 'bul bar zhus pas /
NK128(nyo)001:10851: ngas khyod kyi skra bcad pas mi yong dbang rtags
NK128(nyo)001:10852: ral pa 'jog dgos zhes gsungs par brten bla ma'i
NK128(nyo)001:10853: bkas dbu skra bzhar ma thub par ral pa'i thor
NK128(nyo)001:10854: tshugs dang ldan yang tshangs spyod gtsang ma yin tshul
NK128(nyo)001:10855: 'og tu gsal / chos rgyal dpal mo zhes par
NK128(nyo)001:10856: u rgyan gling pa'i thang yig dang mtsho rgyal rnam
NK128(nyo)001:10857: thar dri med kun dag'i gter ma /
NK128(nyo)001:10858: 'bri gung dgongs pa yang zab kyi rtsa gsum gtor dbang dang lugs sogs gsan /
NK128(nyo)001:10859: dam pa sangs rgyas kyi rnam sprul rdzogs chen pa
NK128(nyo)001:10860: nam mkha' 'brug sgra bzang po la rgyud bcu bdun
NK128(nyo)001:10861: khros nag gi rgyud dang bcas pa /
NK128(nyo)001:10862: mkhas grub klong chen pa'i mdzod bdun ngal bso skor gsum /
NK128(nyo)001:10863: snying tig yab bzhi sogs gsan /
NK128(nyo)001:10864: bi la'i rnam sprul kong smyon rig 'dzin kun bzang
NK128(nyo)001:10865: rnam rgyal la karma gling pa'i thos grol gyi dbang
NK128(nyo)001:10866: lung khrid bcas / rat+na'i klong gsal sogs mang du gsan /
NK128(nyo)001:10867: glang bu chos rje chos skyong dbang phyug la bde mchog mkha' 'gro rgya mtsho'i skor 'ga' zhig gsan /
NK128(nyo)001:10868: dpal ldan sa skya pa'i gdung las sgar chen mthu stobs dbang phyug /
NK128(nyo)001:10869: khri chen a mi lags kun dga' bsod nams /
NK128(nyo)001:10870: rtse gdong khri chen kun dga' bsod nams lhun grub /
NK128(nyo)001:10871: rje zhwa dmar drug pa gar dbang chos kyi dbang phyug /
NK128(nyo)001:10872: gong ra lo chen gzhan phan rdo rje sogs las zab chos du ma gsan /
NK128(nyo)001:10873: 'dus pa mdo dbang gsan tshul ni /
NK128(nyo)001:10874: gong ra lo ts+aa bar tshar gcig gsan pa dang /
NK128(nyo)001:10875: byang ba rdzogs chen pa nam mkha' 'brug sgras gtsang
NK128(nyo)001:10876: bu theg mchog gling pa rnams la mdo dbang gnang
NK128(nyo)001:10877: dus kyang tshar gcig gsan cing /
NK128(nyo)001:10878: rdzogs chen pa de nyid gsang 'grel mun sel thugs la tshud pa sogs sku yon che zhing /
NK128(nyo)001:10879: zang zang lha brag tu sgrub pa mthar phyin pas nyams rtogs kyi mnga' bdag tu gyur mod kyang /
NK128(nyo)001:10880: mdo dbang gi sgyu 'phrul goms 'dris cher yod na ma gtogs 'chad dka' bas dbab /
NK128(nyo)001:10884: brtan sogs kyi sdom tshig rnams ma khrol ba dang /
NK128(nyo)001:10885: phyag rgya'i 'ching tshul sogs la mi mkhas pas /
NK128(nyo)001:10886: rje 'di 'ug pa lung du sgyu 'phrul la sbyangs
NK128(nyo)001:10887: pa song ba'i shas kyis skyon things tshul khyab bdag
NK128(nyo)001:10888: sman lung ba'i gsung las thos /
NK128(nyo)001:10889: khyad par rig 'dzin rje las brgyud pa'i mdo dbang 'di nyid /
NK128(nyo)001:10890: skyi ston tshe rig dbang pos pho brang bsam grub rtse'i spel dkar du gnang skabs gsan cing /
NK128(nyo)001:10891: phyag len dka' ba'i gnad 'ga' zhig kyang zin bris
NK128(nyo)001:10892: su 'debs pa sogs mdzad pas de ltar na 'dus
NK128(nyo)001:10893: pa chen po'i dbang lan gsum du gsan par 'khrul
NK128(nyo)001:10894: pa med / gzhan yang mnga' bdag phun tshogs rig
NK128(nyo)001:10895: 'dzin las byang gter thugs sgrub skor 'ga' zhig dang
NK128(nyo)001:10896: pa med / / gser mdog can mkhan po sh+aakya
NK128(nyo)001:10897: bstan 'dzin las gsar ma 'ga' zhig gsan khyab bdag
NK128(nyo)001:10898: sman lung pa chen po bloo gros mchog gi rdo
NK128(nyo)001:10899: rje las bka' snyan brgyud rdo zam sogs kyang gsan
NK128(nyo)001:10900: pa med / / no // de ltar dam pa
NK128(nyo)001:10901: du ma las zab chos rnams legs par gsan nas
NK128(nyo)001:10902: thos don nyams su bzhes tshul yang /
NK128(nyo)001:10903: lho 'bras mo ljongs su byon te sgrub pa mdzad pas nyams rtogs bzang po 'khrungs pas mtshon /
NK128(nyo)001:10904: dus skabs thams cad du dben gnas 'ba' zhig tu sgrub pa mdzad cing /
NK128(nyo)001:10905: de dag kyang skabs 'gar 'tsho chas dang /
NK128(nyo)001:10906: skabs 'gar dka' thub bcud len la brten pa sogs
NK128(nyo)001:10907: sgo du ma nas sgrub pa lhun len gyii brtul
NK128(nyo)001:10909: thag gi brag rgya bo dang bee ro'i sgrub phug /
NK128(nyo)001:10911: nyug gi rdo rje sgrom bu sogs su gcig pur sgrub pa kho na mdzad /
NK128(nyo)001:10912: khyad par dgon spug ces bya ba'i ri khrod du
NK128(nyo)001:10913: a lce bgres mo zhig gis zhabs 'bring mdzad nas
NK128(nyo)001:10914: lo dgu'i bar du ri mi 'bab kyi sgrub pa
NK128(nyo)001:10916: sgrub 'bras 'khor 'das kyi chos thams cad ka dag
NK128(nyo)001:10917: chen po'i ngang du grol bas tshogs drug gi snang
NK128(nyo)001:10918: ba gang shar rang grol rtsis gdab med pa 'khor
NK128(nyo)001:10919: yug 'od gsal chen por 'byams su klas pa'i rang
NK128(nyo)001:10920: mdangs 'gag med lhun grub kyi rig rtsal snang srid
NK128(nyo)001:10921: dag pa rab 'byams su 'char ba'i gshis las rang
NK128(nyo)001:10922: gzhan gyi bde sdug legs nyes /
NK128(nyo)001:10923: gzhan gyi dngos po 'bul ba sogs ji ltar yong mngon par mkhyen pa dang /
NK128(nyo)001:10924: nyung gi rdo rje sgrom bur mkha' 'gro'i skad gsan
NK128(nyo)001:10925: pa dang rta mgrin la ljags bsnyen mdzad pas rta
NK128(nyo)001:10926: skad kha yar gsan cing rta mgrin gyi sprul par
NK128(nyo)001:10927: yang grags te / bka' thang gnubs sgrigs mar /
NK128(nyo)001:10929: gtsang shangs dben dmar phyogs su 'byung //
NK128(nyo)001:10930: rta mgrin byin rlabs skyes bu yin //
NK128(nyo)001:10931: phrad tshad ngan song 'khor lo chod //
NK128(nyo)001:10933: rig 'dzin srog sgrub las kyang rta mgrin gyi sprul par lung du bstan no zhes grags skad /
NK128(nyo)001:10934: skabs shig mngon dgar phebs dus tshon lnga'i 'ja' ris
NK128(nyo)001:10935: kyi rgyab yol lta bur skor ba phyugs rdzis mthong
NK128(nyo)001:10936: ba dang / zab phur rdo rje sems dpa'i sku
NK128(nyo)001:10937: gsal por gzigs pa sogs rtogs pa'i yon tan du
NK128(nyo)001:10938: ma mngon du gyur pa yin /
NK128(nyo)001:10939: khyad par rtsa rlung la dbang 'byor bas khams dwangs
NK128(nyo)001:10940: ma yungs 'bru tsam yang ma nyams pa yin ces
NK128(nyo)001:10941: khyab bdag sman lung par gsungs pas /
NK128(nyo)001:10942: dam pa des kyang dbang byang du /
NK128(nyo)001:10943: char yar spyi bo'i gtsugs tu bcings /
NK128(nyo)001:10945: bcas ldan dge slong la lhag ma dang po dang
NK128(nyo)001:10946: byang sems gyi kun rdzob byang chub sems kyi rgyu
NK128(nyo)001:10947: dang / sngags sdom la rtsa lhung lnga pa sogs
NK128(nyo)001:10948: sdom gsum mtha' dag gi rtsa bar gyur ba yin
NK128(nyo)001:10949: pas ngo mtshar ba'i mdzad pa 'di gcig pu yang
NK128(nyo)001:10950: bla na med pa'i rnam thar du go //
NK128(nyo)001:10951: gzhan don gdul bya bskyangs tshul yang /
NK128(nyo)001:10952: sgrub pa snying por mdzad pa'i thun mtshams su /
NK128(nyo)001:10953: lo ltar gyi myong grol gyi gdams pa stsal ba'i
NK128(nyo)001:10954: slob ma yang khyab bdag sman lung pa chen po
NK128(nyo)001:10956: zur yang 'ug gi gdung brgyud gdan sa 'og rtse gdong zhabs drung khri rgyan rnam gnyis /
NK128(nyo)001:10957: 'od gsal mchog gi sprul sku sgrol ma sbug pa sku mched /
NK128(nyo)001:10958: kong po rdzogs chen sprul sku sogs rigs rus skye
NK128(nyo)001:10959: ba mkhas btsun grub pas che ba'i dam pa rnams
NK128(nyo)001:10960: dang / mchog dman gyi gdul bya bgrang bar yas
NK128(nyo)001:10961: pa la smin grol gyi bka' drin du ma stsal
NK128(nyo)001:10962: dang / / 'bul nod byung ba rnams kyang dbus
NK128(nyo)001:10963: gtsang du mang 'gyed bsngo rten sogs tshogs gsog kho
NK128(nyo)001:10965: char 'bebs sad srung sogs kyang gzhan gyis bskul bar
NK128(nyo)001:10966: ma ltos pa'i thugs bskyed kyis kun nas blangs te
NK128(nyo)001:10967: mdzad / nad gdon gyis nyen sar byin rlabs mdzad
NK128(nyo)001:10968: pas phan pa rgya cher 'byung bas mtshon 'gro ba
NK128(nyo)001:10969: la phan bde mchog tu stsal /
NK128(nyo)001:10970: khyad par 'od mchog sprul sku dang sgrol ma sbug
NK128(nyo)001:10971: sku mched sogs la snga phyir mdo dbang 'dra gnang
NK128(nyo)001:10972: skad kyang nges gsal dang rnam thar zin bris su
NK128(nyo)001:10974: 'on kyang rig 'dzin rje las brgyud pa'i mdo dbang
NK128(nyo)001:10975: chen mo dbang lung gdam ngag yongs su rdzogs pa
NK128(nyo)001:10976: ni khyab bdag sman lung pa chen por bstsal ba
NK128(nyo)001:10977: yin te / gnas gsar ba rdo rje 'chang mgon po'i mtshan can gyi bkas bskul ba'i rkyen las /
NK128(nyo)001:10978: shangs bar du khyab bdag khra tshang pa kho nar chig rgyud du stsal ba yin la /
NK128(nyo)001:10979: 'di skabs rig 'dzin rje nas brgyud pa'i mdo dbang
NK128(nyo)001:10980: mched kyis spel nas gzan phyogs kyi brgyud par phyogs
NK128(nyo)001:10981: snga 'gyur te sngar nas mdo dbang gsan pa'i brgyud
NK128(nyo)001:10982: pa gzhan dag gi thugs 'phog byung na dam tshig
NK128(nyo)001:10983: la nyams chag tu gyur dogs phyi 'char du rje
NK128(nyo)001:10984: bla ma khra tshang par yang ti nag po gnang
NK128(nyo)001:10985: khul gyis sku mtshams khog tu gnang ba yin zhes
NK128(nyo)001:10986: thos la / 'di dus gsang dam drags pas rkyen
NK128(nyo)001:10987: byas deng sang yang gzhan phyogs 'ga' zhig khyab bdag
NK128(nyo)001:10988: sman lung pa chen por slob dpon /
NK128(nyo)001:10989: bres rin po ches mdo dbang ma gnang bas dran
NK128(nyo)001:10990: rgya kho na yin zhes lkog shub tu gleng zhing
NK128(nyo)001:10991: / kho bo'i gam du yang 'di las brtsams te
NK128(nyo)001:10992: bla ma mchog la bsting tshig gi skur 'debs phyogs
NK128(nyo)001:10993: la zur bstan du byed pa mang mod kyang snga
NK128(nyo)001:10994: phyir gnas gsar ba mjam dbyangs mkhyen brtse khu dbon
NK128(nyo)001:10995: gsum dang rgyal dbang thams cad mkhyen pa chen po'i
NK128(nyo)001:10996: bka' drin la brten nas rig 'dzin rje nas brgyud
NK128(nyo)001:10997: pa'i mdo dbang 'di ma chad tsam byung ba yin
NK128(nyo)001:10998: / pas / phyogs gtam 'di lta bu'i sgro skur
NK128(nyo)001:10999: bgyis na chos spong dang dam pa de dag kun
NK128(nyo)001:11000: la ngag gi sgrib pa du ma gsog pa'i rgyu
NK128(nyo)001:11001: 'gyur bas las ngan gyi 'gro ba 'di dag snying
NK128(nyo)001:11002: / pas / rje'i gnas so // de ltar bla
NK128(nyo)001:11003: chen bres gshongs pa de nyid ni sdom gsum gyi
NK128(nyo)001:11004: bcas pa phra mo las kyang mi 'da' ba'i tshul
NK128(nyo)001:11005: khrims dang sdom pa dam tshig rnam par dag /
NK128(nyo)001:11006: ma h+aa yo ga'i rnal 'byor gyis brtan g.yo'i dngos po dag par 'char /
NK128(nyo)001:11007: a nu yo ga'i man ngag gi phung khams zab
NK128(nyo)001:11008: mo lus kyi dkyil 'khor du mkhyen cing rtsa rlung
NK128(nyo)001:11009: la dbang thob / rdzogs chen a ti yo ga
NK128(nyo)001:11010: khregs chod dang thod rgal gyi don la gdeng rnyed
NK128(nyo)001:11011: la dbang thob / / tshe 'di'i bya ba thams
NK128(nyo)001:11012: cad sgyu mar mkhyen pas 'du 'dzi'i yo langs la
NK128(nyo)001:11013: mi spyod par 'dod chung chog shes su mdzad pa
NK128(nyo)001:11014: la dbang thob / / yin no // mnga' ris
NK128(nyo)001:11015: 'od gsal mchog de yongs 'dzin gyi gtso bo yin
NK128(nyo)001:11016: pa'i rten 'brel las 'od mchog sprul sku 'od gsal
NK128(nyo)001:11017: klong yangs la thugs tshig che zhing /
NK128(nyo)001:11018: gong ma'i rgyun dang dag snang gi byang gter thugs
NK128(nyo)001:11019: rje chen po dang thugs sgrub legs ldan rje'i gter
NK128(nyo)001:11020: gsar 'khor ba dbyings sgrol gyi skor rnams gsan cing
NK128(nyo)001:11021: gdan sar mnga' gsol ba'i rten 'byung yang mdzad ces
NK128(nyo)001:11022: thos la / de ltar zhal slob rnams la 'dod
NK128(nyo)001:11023: chos du ma dang khyad par snga 'gyur bka' ma
NK128(nyo)001:11024: mdo sgyu sems gsum gyi bstan pa rgya cher spel
NK128(nyo)001:11026: bla ma'i dbang byang gi bskul tshig khyab bdag khra tshang ba'i gsung las /
NK128(nyo)001:11027: dam pa du ma'i zhabs pad bsnyen //
NK128(nyo)001:11028: rtsa rlung dgongs pa mngon du gyur //
NK128(nyo)001:11029: char yang spyi bo'i gtsug tu bcings //
NK128(nyo)001:11030: tshangs par spyod pa'i rnal 'byor pa //
NK128(nyo)001:11031: chos kyi rgyal po rdo rje'i mtshan //
NK128(nyo)001:11032: bzhugs ni rig 'dzin gnas na bzhugs //
NK128(nyo)001:11035: gtsang stod bres kyi ri khrod du //
NK128(nyo)001:11036: bla chen chos rgyal rdo rje dpal //
NK128(nyo)001:11037: mdo sgyu'i smin grol srog shing 'dzin //
NK128(nyo)001:11038: zhes gsungs pa don la gnas so //
NK128(nyo)001:11039: mdor na dgung lo bdun cu don bdun gyi bar
NK128(nyo)001:11040: du bshad sgrub kyi sgo nas zhing 'di'i gdul bya
NK128(nyo)001:11041: skyongs rjes sbrul lo cho 'phrul chen po'i tshes bcu'i
NK128(nyo)001:11042: nyin sgra 'od sogs ngo mtshar ba'i ltas du ma
NK128(nyo)001:11043: dang bcas te gdod ma'i sa la gshegs so //
NK128(nyo)001:11044: der bu slob rnams gyis bla ma dkyil 'khor gyi
NK128(nyo)001:11045: gtso bo dang gnyis su med pa mchod sprin du
NK128(nyo)001:11046: mas mchod cing bur sbyangs te /
NK128(nyo)001:11047: de yang ngo mtshar gyi cho 'phrul du ma mngon par snang bar gyur ces grags so //
NK128(nyo)001:11048: bla chen bres gshongs pa chos rgyal rdo rje de
NK128(nyo)001:11049: nyid kyis kho bo'i bla ma khyab bdag sman lung
NK128(nyo)001:11050: pa chen por gnang ba yin te /
NK128(nyo)001:11051: yongs 'dzin 'di nyid kyi rnam par thar pa rgyal
NK128(nyo)001:11052: dbang mchog gis mdzad pa'i rtogs brjod nyung ngu rnam
NK128(nyo)001:11053: gsal du zhib par yod cing /
NK128(nyo)001:11054: bsdus pa kho bos brtsams pa'i dad pa'i 'jug ngogs zhes pa sa bon tsam zhig kyang yod mod /
NK128(nyo)001:11055: 'dir yang cung zad btus te bri bar rigs song /
NK128(nyo)001:11056: de yang bla ma dam pa de nyid kyi gdung
NK128(nyo)001:11057: rus ni nyang mchog ldan mgon po'i gsung las nyang
NK128(nyo)001:11058: ston chen pos bstan pa'i dbu brnyes nas mnyam med
NK128(nyo)001:11059: dben ston bstan pa'i srol chen btod /
NK128(nyo)001:11060: mkhas chen sman lung pa yi dbu bzung nas //
NK128(nyo)001:11061: nyang ban sku mched ring 'dir dar zhing rgyas //
NK128(nyo)001:11063: sangs rgyas nyang ston brtson 'grus seng ge sogs mkhas
NK128(nyo)001:11064: grub mu tig gi 'phreng ba ltar rim bzhin byon
NK128(nyo)001:11065: pa'i mthar yul g.yon ru yar mo lung gi sa'i
NK128(nyo)001:11066: cha / pho brang chen po yum bu gla sgang
NK128(nyo)001:11067: gi 'dabs grub pa'i bsti gnas khra tshang bla brang
NK128(nyo)001:11068: du yab nyang ston karma gzi brjid dang karma mthu
NK128(nyo)001:11069: cha / stobs mched gnyis / yum sde ba mkhar
NK128(nyo)001:11070: ldan ma'i sras mo mkha' 'gro'i mtshan rtags can gyi
NK128(nyo)001:11071: sras su lug gi lo nyi ma me bzhi'i 'grub
NK128(nyo)001:11072: sbyor gyi nyi shar la sku bltams /
NK128(nyo)001:11073: de yang yum gyi lhums su zhugs pa'i tshe chos
NK128(nyo)001:11074: dbang gdung rabs dgu pa karma gu rus byin gyis
NK128(nyo)001:11075: brlabs shing skyes chen 'byung bar lung bstan /
NK128(nyo)001:11076: 'khrungs nas kyang rje de nyid kyis tshe dbang rtsal /
NK128(nyo)001:11077: dgung lo bzhir phebs tshe yab karma mthu stobs yum dang bcas te sman lung du bzhugs shing /
NK128(nyo)001:11078: yab kyi mtshan sh+aakya skyabs sbyin du gsol /
NK128(nyo)001:11079: dgung lo bdun pa'i steng rdo rje 'chang dbang phyug
NK128(nyo)001:11080: rab brtan la dge bsnyen du sgrub par mdzad nas
NK128(nyo)001:11081: byang gter tshe dbang lcags sdong ma gsan /
NK128(nyo)001:11082: dgung lo bcu bzhi pa'i tshe yar stod karma lha
NK128(nyo)001:11083: khang du chos dbang rin po che'i gdung rabs bcu
NK128(nyo)001:11084: pa rgyal sras gar dbang karma dbang 'byor gyi zhabs
NK128(nyo)001:11085: drung du phebs te chos dbang gi zab gter snying
NK128(nyo)001:11086: po gsang 'dus bla ma'i sgrub thabs kyi dbang khrid
NK128(nyo)001:11089: rdzogs pa chen po sangs rgyas mnyam sbyor gyi nyams khrid dang dbang lung /
NK128(nyo)001:11091: bka' brgyad gsang ba yongs rdzogs kyi sgrub chen sman sgrub dang /
NK128(nyo)001:11092: 'brel ba'i dbang lung sogs gsan cing /
NK128(nyo)001:11093: khyad par rdo rje slob dpon nus pa'i dbang gi tshe khrir bkod de /
NK128(nyo)001:11094: bla ma nyid kyi dbu zhwa dang sku ber sgron /
NK128(nyo)001:11095: rdo rje dril bu phyag tu gtad /
NK128(nyo)001:11096: khyed chos kyi bdag po yin no zhes gzengs bstod par mdzad pas /
NK128(nyo)001:11097: de skabs rje karma dbang 'byor la e gnyal lho
NK128(nyo)001:11098: brag dbus gtsang gi phyogs nas slob ma mang bar
NK128(nyo)001:11099: yod pa rnams kyi khrod nas rje 'di la gtso
NK128(nyo)001:11100: bor mdzad pa ni ma 'ongs pa'i dgongs pa rgya
NK128(nyo)001:11101: chen po mngon par mkhyen par snang /
NK128(nyo)001:11102: gzhan yang thugs sgrub dregs pa tshar gcod /
NK128(nyo)001:11103: rdzogs chen tshe dbang sogs dang /
NK128(nyo)001:11104: nyang rin po che'i zab gter bka' brgyad bde gshegs 'dus pa'i skor /
NK128(nyo)001:11105: rta mgrin drag po lha gsum sogs dang /
NK128(nyo)001:11106: rdzogs chen snying thig gi rgyud bcu bdun sogs zab chos dpag med gsan cing /
NK128(nyo)001:11107: dbu la phyag gi byugs te chos bum gang byor byed gsungs pa'i zhal bzhes dang /
NK128(nyo)001:11108: zhar byung phyag len dang dka' gnas thams cad kyang yang yang bkrol zhing gnang ste /
NK128(nyo)001:11109: karma dbang 'byor la gtugs pa yin zhes ngom chog
NK128(nyo)001:11110: pa mdzod ces ku re dang bcas te gsungs pas
NK128(nyo)001:11111: / ji ltar gsung ba ltar phyag tu khel zhing /
NK128(nyo)001:11112: bla ma 'di la gdung rigs mkhas grub thams cad
NK128(nyo)001:11113: 'dzom pa 'gran zla dang bral ba'i yin ces mchog
NK128(nyo)001:11114: tu gus par mdzad pa zhig 'dug go //
NK128(nyo)001:11115: gzhan yang chos dbang rin po che'i sras chung gi
NK128(nyo)001:11116: gdung rabs 'dzin pa brag sna ba chos dbang bstan
NK128(nyo)001:11117: 'dzin la nyang gter tshe sgrub mtsho skyes rdo rje
NK128(nyo)001:11122: chos dbang gi phur pa spu gri /
NK128(nyo)001:11123: jo mo'i nyams len skor dgu sogs du ma /
NK128(nyo)001:11124: bka' ma snyan brgyud rdor zam /
NK128(nyo)001:11125: gzhan yang gter kha sna tshogs kyi dbang chos mang du gsan /
NK128(nyo)001:11126: brag sna chos rje u rgyun bstan 'dzin la yang rgyud bcu bdun sogs gsan /
NK128(nyo)001:11127: bla ma nam mkha' chos dbang la bka' brgyad bka'
NK128(nyo)001:11128: ma rdzogs 'phrang skor rin chen gling pa'i chig chod
NK128(nyo)001:11129: kun grol / nyang gi bla ma dmar khrid /
NK128(nyo)001:11132: mgon po g.yul zlog sogs dang gnas brtan ldang ma
NK128(nyo)001:11133: lhun rgyal gyi zab gter snying thig thams cad kyi
NK128(nyo)001:11134: rtsa ba zab pa pod bzhi skor /
NK128(nyo)001:11135: chos dbang gi rdzogs chen spyi ti'i rgyud skor nyer lnga sogs mang du gsan /
NK128(nyo)001:11136: tshar lugs kyi sngags grwa bkra shis sder re zhig sgrigs 'grim mdzad de /
NK128(nyo)001:11137: gnas gsar ba chen po rdo rje 'chang dbang phyug
NK128(nyo)001:11138: rab brtan gyi zhabs pad brten nas bka' brgyad yongs
NK128(nyo)001:11139: rdzogs kyi lha khrid gnad du thebs pa dang /
NK128(nyo)001:11140: zab gnad mang po lhug par gsan pas thugs bskyed
NK128(nyo)001:11141: dang thugs dam la bogs shin tu che ba thon
NK128(nyo)001:11142: / 'brum nag shin tu mched pa zhig gi skabs rgyu mtshan zhus pas /
NK128(nyo)001:11143: o lo rang dreed mi dgos zhes mgul srung gnang
NK128(nyo)001:11144: ba'i byin rlabs las sku tshe'i ring la dbus gtsang
NK128(nyo)001:11145: du 'brum nad bdun brgyad tsam byung bar 'dzem cha
NK128(nyo)001:11146: ma thub kyang nad kyis ma btab pa dam pa
NK128(nyo)001:11147: de nyid kyi byin rlabs kho na yin gsungs ba
NK128(nyo)001:11148: thos / skabs shig rtse dong bsam gtan gling gi zhal 'dzin mdzad dgos byung bar brten /
NK128(nyo)001:11149: khyab bdag rdo rje 'chang mgon po bsod nams mchog
NK128(nyo)001:11150: ldan gyi zhabs drung du kye rdo rje man ngag
NK128(nyo)001:11152: gur lha brgya dang zhal bsnyen dus kyi rjes gnang gsan /
NK128(nyo)001:11153: gzhan yang n+aa ro mkha' spyod /
NK128(nyo)001:11154: 'jigs byed r+aa lugs bcu gsum ma /
NK128(nyo)001:11159: phur pa spu gri dang dpyal lugs /
NK128(nyo)001:11162: chos dbang gi yang gsang drag po rta skad can /
NK128(nyo)001:11164: byang gter thugs rje chen po 'gro ba kun grol /
NK128(nyo)001:11165: tshe sgrub bu ston gong khu nga ma /
NK128(nyo)001:11166: tshe brtan rgyal mtshan gyi drag po spyan mang /
NK128(nyo)001:11167: 'char ka sgrom bu ma sogs gter ma'i skor mang ba /
NK128(nyo)001:11168: brgyad stong pa'i sogs kyis mtshon gsar rnying gi zab chos mang ba gsan /
NK128(nyo)001:11169: rje 'bri gung pa rin chen phun tshogs kyi gter
NK128(nyo)001:11170: ma dbyug gu ma spun gsum gyi dbang lung gsan
NK128(nyo)001:11171: pa nas bzung longs spyod kyang rgya cher 'phel /
NK128(nyo)001:11172: rje 'di mkhas btsun grub par yongs su grags pa yin pas mchog tu gus par 'dzin cing /
NK128(nyo)001:11173: phyis su dam pa 'di'i gsungs 'phros tsam byung yang spyan chab 'byin par mthong ngo //
NK128(nyo)001:11174: zhwa dmar drug pa dpal ldan gar dbang chos kyi
NK128(nyo)001:11175: dbang phyug gi bzhugs sgar du phebs shing brtse ba
NK128(nyo)001:11177: bar ma rab byung nas bsnyen rdzogs kyi bar mdzad
NK128(nyo)001:11178: cing rab byung gi mtshan karma blo gros mchog gi
NK128(nyo)001:11180: phyis gang ra lo chen gyi mdo dbang gi skabs
NK128(nyo)001:11181: blo mchog rig pa'i rdo rjer bsgyur ba yin zhes
NK128(nyo)001:11182: sku dngos kyi gsung las thos /
NK128(nyo)001:11183: sgar du rje 'di dang lo chen bstan pa gnyis sku btsun par grags /
NK128(nyo)001:11184: mkhan po thams cad mkhyen pa chos kyi dbang phyug
NK128(nyo)001:11185: gi zhabs drung du bcom ldan 'das dus kyi 'khor
NK128(nyo)001:11196: sman bla sogs kyi rjes gnang /
NK128(nyo)001:11197: phyag chen chos drug gi nyams khrid sogs karma kam tshang lugs kyi dbang khrid rjes gnang du ma /
NK128(nyo)001:11198: gzhan yang klu sgrub lugs kyi sems bskyed /
NK128(nyo)001:11203: 'dul ba'i skor sogs mang du gsan /
NK128(nyo)001:11204: rgyun par sgar du dpe mtshams lta bu mdzad de bsdus rgyud /
NK128(nyo)001:11208: sum rtags dang snyan ngag me long ma'i gzhung sogs rtsa ba mang po thugs la bzung /
NK128(nyo)001:11209: de dag gi ti ka dang 'grel pa mang po gzigs pa'i gsan sbyong kho na lhur mdzad /
NK128(nyo)001:11210: sgar chen shangs su phebs skabs sdeb lha phu bas
NK128(nyo)001:11211: rje zhwa dmar ba yang zab rdo rje gro lod
NK128(nyo)001:11212: dbang zhus par dbang rdzas su mgur phur g.yar bar
NK128(nyo)001:11213: sde ba chos rgyal phreng ba gnang bar gsol ba
NK128(nyo)001:11214: btab pas gnang / zab phu gdan sa sogs la
NK128(nyo)001:11215: mkha' 'gro snying thig gi ljags lung gnang ba zhor
NK128(nyo)001:11216: btab pas gnang / la gsan / karma pa chos
NK128(nyo)001:11217: dbyings rdo rjer thugs rje chen po'i sgom lung lan
NK128(nyo)001:11218: btab pas gnang / la gsan / du ma gsan
NK128(nyo)001:11219: / bla ma drung yig par chos spyod sogs 'ga'
NK128(nyo)001:11220: btab pas gnang / la gsan / du ma gsan
NK128(nyo)001:11221: / zhig gsan / gtsang du karma pa yab sras
NK128(nyo)001:11222: zhal rgyas kyi tshes bcu rgyas par gnang skabs rje
NK128(nyo)001:11223: 'dis tshogs las kyi 'cham dpon mdzad pas /
NK128(nyo)001:11224: shin tu dgyes pa'i gtang rag tu chibs chas legs pa zhig gnang /
NK128(nyo)001:11225: de rjes khyab bdag karma dbang 'byor la gsan bsam
NK128(nyo)001:11226: gyi 'phros rnams gnang bzhed kyis sgar nas dgongs pa
NK128(nyo)001:11228: phebs kar rje zhwa dmar ba'i bka' las /
NK128(nyo)001:11229: nyid rang gar lugs phyogs gtogs byed ba bzhin ma byed /
NK128(nyo)001:11230: kar bstan 'di rang gang 'dra byed mi shes /
NK128(nyo)001:11231: khyod rang gi mnyam med chen po nas bzung sman
NK128(nyo)001:11232: lung pa mi bskyod rdo rje sogs rnying ma'i skyes
NK128(nyo)001:11233: chen yang rab cig byung 'dug pas /
NK128(nyo)001:11234: spyir rnying ma yang dgos pha chos rang la nyams
NK128(nyo)001:11235: len mdzod gsung pa sogs mngon par mkhyen pa'i bslab
NK128(nyo)001:11236: ston zhib rgyas gnang ste rang gnas sman lung du
NK128(nyo)001:11238: yab yum grwa rigs dang bcas pas jo mo len
NK128(nyo)001:11239: pa'i sta gon mdzad pas ma bzhed par gtsang rog
NK128(nyo)001:11240: gang rang lo chen gzhan phan rdo rje'i drung du
NK128(nyo)001:11241: phebs te sgra k+aa la pa'i mtshams sbyor ming le
NK128(nyo)001:11242: kun bshad kri ta rnams kyis ris /
NK128(nyo)001:11243: snyan ngag me long le'u gsum pa yan gyi rtsom rgyugs /
NK128(nyo)001:11244: sdeb sbyor rin chen 'byung gnas sogs la sbyangs pa mdzad /
NK128(nyo)001:11245: byang gter thugs sgrub drag po rtsal /
NK128(nyo)001:11246: mnga' ris pan chen sku mched nas brgyud pa'i bka' brgyad bde 'dus /
NK128(nyo)001:11247: khra mo brag gi bla ma spyi 'dus /
NK128(nyo)001:11250: gsang skor snyan brgyud shangs lugs /
NK128(nyo)001:11251: bee ro'i 'dra 'bag sogs bka' gter gyi chos mang du gsan cing /
NK128(nyo)001:11252: khyad par 'gro mgon dung mtsho ras pa'i yang tig
NK128(nyo)001:11253: nag po gser gyi 'bru gcig gi mun khrid rtags
NK128(nyo)001:11254: thon par mdzad / sna nam skye sprul byang pa
NK128(nyo)001:11255: rig 'dzin ngag gi dbang por mnyam sbyor gyi khrid
NK128(nyo)001:11256: thon par mdzad / chen brgyad dang / yang snying 'dus pa'i lung thor bu /
NK128(nyo)001:11257: mtsho rgyal gtsug gi rgyan cig /
NK128(nyo)001:11258: sems bskyed bstan pa'i snying po sogs chos dbang skor kha shas dang /
NK128(nyo)001:11259: yab chos rgyal dbang pa 'i sde'i gsung kha shas dang byang gling phyag rdor gsang sgrub skor /
NK128(nyo)001:11260: gnyen lo'i gter ma mgon po zhal dar khra can /
NK128(nyo)001:11261: tshe dpag med 'chi med dpal ster sogs gsan /
NK128(nyo)001:11262: rdo rje brag tu sku mtshams shig gi skabs mtshams
NK128(nyo)001:11263: 'og tu bzhugs te bla dpe rnams la gzigs mo
NK128(nyo)001:11264: dang / sman lung du yang spyan 'dren gnang skabs rig 'dzin ngag gi dbang pos /
NK128(nyo)001:11265: nyang chos dbang gi gter chos brgyud khungs btsun pas
NK128(nyo)001:11266: chos gsan bzhed kyi rong pa sku mdun brgyud de
NK128(nyo)001:11267: phebs sgo gnang yang 'bul ma thub par lus /
NK128(nyo)001:11268: rta nag sgrol ma phug pa'i zhabs drung sku 'bring
NK128(nyo)001:11269: ba la tshe bdag gi dbang nges don bde 'jug
NK128(nyo)001:11270: dang sgron drug gi lung sogs gsan /
NK128(nyo)001:11271: gter ston 'ja' tshon snying por rang gter dkon mchog spyi 'dus skor gsan /
NK128(nyo)001:11272: snga sor gong rar mdo dbang kah thog lugs shig gsan grub kyang /
NK128(nyo)001:11273: khyab bdag bka' 'gyur ba chen po'i bkas bskul te
NK128(nyo)001:11274: bla chen bres gshongs pa chos rgyal rdo rjer zur
NK128(nyo)001:11275: lugs rig 'dzin rje yab sras brgyud par bzhugs pa'i
NK128(nyo)001:11276: 'dus pa mdo'i dbang yongs su rdzogs pa /
NK128(nyo)001:11277: 'jam dbyangs bla ma'i rtsa gsum dril sgrub dang /
NK128(nyo)001:11278: 'char ka gnubs dang gnam skas ma'i lugs sogs mang du gsan /
NK128(nyo)001:11279: yab mched las zhal ngo nang btud kyi khro rol lung dang phyag bzhes /
NK128(nyo)001:11280: 'char ka'i mdos dang 'khor lo'i zhib cha sogs gsan /
NK128(nyo)001:11281: sprul sku gsung sprul rin po che tshul khrims rdo
NK128(nyo)001:11282: rjer rnying ma brgyud 'bum dang pad gling pa'i bla
NK128(nyo)001:11283: ma nor bu rgya mtsho sogs gsan /
NK128(nyo)001:11284: yar 'brog pa bkra shis lhun grub la rnying rgyud po ti bcu lhag tsam /
NK128(nyo)001:11286: pad gling drag dmar sogs 'ga' zhig gsan /
NK128(nyo)001:11287: gter ston sangs rgyas gling pa'i gdung brgyud kong po
NK128(nyo)001:11288: snyi phu ba karma rig 'dzin dbang por sangs rgyas
NK128(nyo)001:11289: gling pa'i phur pa rnam sras /
NK128(nyo)001:11290: nyang gi gdung rabs 'ag'i rnam thar /
NK128(nyo)001:11291: bde 'dus kyi lung dang khro rol gyi phyag len mtha' chod sogs gsan /
NK128(nyo)001:11295: g.ya' bzang bla ma karma shes rab la nyi ma mdung gang ma sogs gsan /
NK128(nyo)001:11296: kha rag sprul skur zhi byed skor gsan /
NK128(nyo)001:11297: bre bon lung pa tshul khrims rgyal mtshan la pad gling nor bu rgya mtsho sogs gsan /
NK128(nyo)001:11298: rdo rje 'chang bka' 'gyur ba chen po mgon po
NK128(nyo)001:11299: bsod nams mchog ldan gyi rgyal ba'i bka' 'gyur rin
NK128(nyo)001:11300: po che'i lung la thugs rtsol chen po mdzad de
NK128(nyo)001:11301: / rje 'di nyid la chos 'tshol bar bkas bskul ba'i rgyu dang /
NK128(nyo)001:11302: lho brag nyi lder bka' 'gyur tshugs pas rkyen byas
NK128(nyo)001:11303: dpon slob gnyis chibs dang bcas lho brag phyogs su
NK128(nyo)001:11304: phebs pas lam nor te seng ge rdzong dang nye
NK128(nyo)001:11305: ba'i lung pa kha dog la gting zab pa zhig
NK128(nyo)001:11306: tu byon nas skad cha dri yul yang ma rnyed
NK128(nyo)001:11307: par / nye gnas kyi chibs pa khrid rje nyid
NK128(nyo)001:11308: kyi rta 'phongs skyor te dka' ba spyad mthar grong
NK128(nyo)001:11309: gcig ma zhig tu phebs nas dri ba mdzad pas
NK128(nyo)001:11310: par / / lam 'dir rta thar ba ngo mtshar
NK128(nyo)001:11311: che do nub gar yang mi sleb pas 'dir bzhugs
NK128(nyo)001:11312: zer ba ltar mdzad cing sang nyin grong pa des
NK128(nyo)001:11313: bstan pa'i lam la byon nas lung stong zhig tu
NK128(nyo)001:11315: lho phyogs nas bya rog gcig 'phur zhing skad sna tshogs bsgrags te drung du byung bas /
NK128(nyo)001:11316: thugs skyo shas dang chos skyong la gdung shugs drag
NK128(nyo)001:11317: po 'khrungs te gsol zan las gtor ma'i dbyibs bzos
NK128(nyo)001:11319: bya rog gi zos te 'phur ba'i bshul du byon pas /
NK128(nyo)001:11320: mda' rgyang gang las mi ring bar 'phur sdod byed
NK128(nyo)001:11321: pa'i rjes ma 'khrul bar mdzad pas lho stod kyi
NK128(nyo)001:11322: grong sna zin par byon pas bya rog de mgon
NK128(nyo)001:11324: der nyi sde dgon du sdom brtson tshogs gnyis dpal
NK128(nyo)001:11325: grub kyi bka' 'gyur ljags lung gnang ba'i skabs nas
NK128(nyo)001:11326: shes phyogs rdzogs nas mdo mang cha pa'i steng du
NK128(nyo)001:11328: mdo mang sogs tshar ba rnams kyang gsos te po ti lnga bcur nye ba'i lung gsan pas /
NK128(nyo)001:11329: ston pa bde bar gshegs pa dang /
NK128(nyo)001:11330: bstan pa bde bar gshegs pa'i bka' thog mtha' bar gsum du dge ba dang /
NK128(nyo)001:11331: bdag rkyen dge ba'i bshes gnyen yongs 'dzin bka' 'gyur
NK128(nyo)001:11332: ba chen po dang chos ston pa po sogs la
NK128(nyo)001:11333: thugs dad dbyar mtsho ltar 'phel zhing /
NK128(nyo)001:11334: tshigs su bcad pa gcig tsam yang thos par dka' ba'i 'du shes rgyun chags su byung /
NK128(nyo)001:11335: slar yang rje bka' 'gyur ba chen po'i bskul ma
NK128(nyo)001:11336: gnang ba ltar gsol chas kyi mthu rkyen rgyal dbang
NK128(nyo)001:11337: mchog gis bkas do bo ljongs nas gnang ba dang
NK128(nyo)001:11338: bstun rdi tsha sprul sku 'jig rten dbang phyug la
NK128(nyo)001:11340: phyis su rgyal dbang thams cad mkhyen pa chen po'i
NK128(nyo)001:11341: bka' stsal dang rjes su mthun par dge slong grub
NK128(nyo)001:11342: pa rdo rje la 'dul ba dang /
NK128(nyo)001:11343: gong dkar chos sde'i 'chad nyan pa rab 'byams chos
NK128(nyo)001:11344: rje rin cen rgya mtshor gsar ma brgyud 'bum yang
NK128(nyo)001:11345: gsan pas / rgyal ba'i bka' 'gyur ro cog gi lung tshar bar gsan /
NK128(nyo)001:11346: rje 'bring gung pa chos kyi grags pa dgongs pa
NK128(nyo)001:11347: yang zab kyi nyams len dmigs khrid kyi chos 'brel
NK128(nyo)001:11348: dang / zur chen rdo rje 'chang chos dbyings rang
NK128(nyo)001:11349: grol la bla ma'i rnal 'byor gyi chos 'brel gsan
NK128(nyo)001:11350: yongs 'dzin sprul thub bstan dpal bzang la gter mgon
NK128(nyo)001:11351: nyang lugs dang brag dmar phur zhabs can sogs gsan
NK128(nyo)001:11352: pas mtshon snga phyir gsar rnying gi yongs 'dzin du
NK128(nyo)001:11353: ma las dam pa'i chos kyi bka' drin mtha' yas
NK128(nyo)001:11354: dang / par gsan / de dag gi don nyams su bzhes tshul yang /
NK128(nyo)001:11355: khra tshang du sku mtshams mdzad de rdzogs chen sangs
NK128(nyo)001:11356: rgyas mnyam sbyor sogs la nyams bzhes gtso bor mdzad
NK128(nyo)001:11357: pas / ka dag lhun grub kyi lam khregs chod thod rgal mngon du gyur pa'i rang mdangs su /
NK128(nyo)001:11358: gtso bor bla ma'i thugs sgrub gsang ba 'dus pa'i
NK128(nyo)001:11359: bsnyen sgrub las sbyor dus grangs mtshan ma mthar phyin
NK128(nyo)001:11360: du mdzad pas / rang rig don gyi u rgyan
NK128(nyo)001:11361: rdo rje 'chang dang zhal mjal bas bdag gi bla
NK128(nyo)001:11362: ma 'di yan chod kyi slob rgyud du bla ma
NK128(nyo)001:11363: gsang ba 'dus pa'i thugs dam la brten pa'i gu
NK128(nyo)001:11364: ru pad+ma'i zhal ma gzigs pa med ces gsungs /
NK128(nyo)001:11365: gzhan yang sgrub chen bka' brgyad gsang ba yongs rdzogs
NK128(nyo)001:11366: yo ga gsum gyi dkyil 'khor la brten pa'i nyams
NK128(nyo)001:11367: bzhes bsnyen sgrub thams cad rdzogs par mdzad /
NK128(nyo)001:11368: gzhan yang yon bu dang khra tshang gnyis su drag dmar bde gshegs 'dus pa dang /
NK128(nyo)001:11369: thugs sgrub dreg pa tshar gcod kyi ljags bsnyen /
NK128(nyo)001:11370: yar klung shel brag tu nyang gi khros nag la
NK128(nyo)001:11371: ljags bsnyen mdzad cing 'di la thugs gtsigs kyang nan
NK128(nyo)001:11372: tan che / gzhan yang bsam gtan gling dang sman lung sogs su yang rdzogs chen tshe sgrub /
NK128(nyo)001:11375: legs ldan ma ning sogs la bsnyen sgrub mthar phyin
NK128(nyo)001:11376: pas rtsa gsum de dag gi rang zhal mngon du
NK128(nyo)001:11377: gyur mod kyang / grub rtags ji ltar byung dri ba zhus pa'i tshe /
NK128(nyo)001:11378: sgrub pa'i snying po 'di la dril nus na /
NK128(nyo)001:11379: spyod pa bslab gsum mdzes pa'i grub rtags shig /
NK128(nyo)001:11380: rang gzhan kun gyi snang ngor ston nus shing /
NK128(nyo)001:11381: de las gzhan pa'i grub rtags med kyang bzod /
NK128(nyo)001:11382: ces gsungs pa'i lung 'dren par mdzad pa yin /
NK128(nyo)001:11383: de ltar mkhas btsun grub pa'i bdag nyid nges pa
NK128(nyo)001:11384: don gyi rdo rje 'chang chen po 'di nyid sngon
NK128(nyo)001:11385: gyi smon lam gyi mthu las /
NK128(nyo)001:11386: khyab bdag bka' 'gyur ba chen po'i thugs rje dang mtshams sbyor gyi rten 'brel bzang po'i mthu las /
NK128(nyo)001:11387: khams gsum 'gro ba'i bla ma srid pa gsum na
NK128(nyo)001:11388: 'gran zla thams cad dang bral ba yongs rdzogs bstan
NK128(nyo)001:11389: pa'i nyi ma chen po kun mkhyen rgyal ba'i dbang
NK128(nyo)001:11390: po thams cad mkhyen pa bdag gi mkhan po don
NK128(nyo)001:11391: gyi slad du mtshan nas smos pa ngag dbang blo
NK128(nyo)001:11392: bzang rgya mtsho thub bstan lang tsho'i sde'am /
NK128(nyo)001:11393: mtshan gzhan rgyal dbang pad+mas snga 'gyur chos kyi bdag
NK128(nyo)001:11394: por dbang bskur ba'i tshe rdo rje thogs med rtsal
NK128(nyo)001:11396: spyir snyigs ma'i dus kyi 'gro ba dus kyi chad pas nyam thag pa rnams dbugs 'byung ba dang /
NK128(nyo)001:11397: phyogs dang ris su ma bcad pa'i rgyal ba'i bstan
NK128(nyo)001:11398: pa mtha' dag gi gud pa gso ba'i phyir phyogs
NK128(nyo)001:11399: dus kyi rgyal ba thams cad gcig tu 'dus pa'i
NK128(nyo)001:11400: ngo bo nyid du gyur pas bstan 'gro'i sgron me
NK128(nyo)001:11401: dam par kun la gsal zhing /
NK128(nyo)001:11402: khyad par snga 'gyur rdo rje theg pa bka' gter
NK128(nyo)001:11403: gyi bstan pa rin po che dus dbang las rim
NK128(nyo)001:11405: rang phyogs kyi grub pa'i mtha' zhugs pa rnams kyang
NK128(nyo)001:11406: bshad sgrub don du mi gnyer bas grong chog dang
NK128(nyo)001:11408: gzhan 'phrul bdag po snying la zhugs pa'i mkhas rlom
NK128(nyo)001:11409: 'gas kyang chags sdang bstan pa'i gad bdar du sgrog
NK128(nyo)001:11410: cing / rig pa dang bstan pa'i gtan tshigs 'gal
NK128(nyo)001:11411: 'brel gyi sgro gtags du ma'i tshig yi ger bkod
NK128(nyo)001:11412: cing spel ba'i cal sgrog gis /
NK128(nyo)001:11413: sems can blo chung 'ga' zhig kyang log lta'i mun
NK128(nyo)001:11414: pas sgrib ste chos khyur mi chud par nye bar
NK128(nyo)001:11415: gyur pa la / rgyal mchog rigs brgya'i bdag po
NK128(nyo)001:11416: 'di nyid kyis rmad du byung ba'i thugs bskyed dang
NK128(nyo)001:11417: smon lam bzang po'i dus babs la brten nas /
NK128(nyo)001:11418: rigs rus sprul pa'i khyad par gyi che ba'i snga
NK128(nyo)001:11419: 'gyur gyi bstan 'dzin rnams la lugs gnyis sogs byams
NK128(nyo)001:11420: pa dang brtse ba'i sgo du ma nas phan par
NK128(nyo)001:11421: mdzad cing / thos bsam sgom pa'i tshul yang dag pa'i sa la sbyor ba dang /
NK128(nyo)001:11422: bka' gter gyi chos rgyun nyag phra ba chad par
NK128(nyo)001:11423: nye ba mtha' dag kyang legs par gso zhing spel
NK128(nyo)001:11424: / bstan pa bshad sgrub kyi sgo nas 'dzin dgos shing /
NK128(nyo)001:11425: de yang bshes gnyen 'dus pa'i sde la rag dgos
NK128(nyo)001:11426: pa'i phyir bla ma dam pa 'di nyid kyi nyer
NK128(nyo)001:11427: bar gnas pa'i sde nges gsang rdo rje gling /
NK128(nyo)001:11432: bdud dpung zil gnon gling la sogs pa khrims ldan gyi sde bo che du ma btsugs shing /
NK128(nyo)001:11433: de dag kyang zang zing gis mi 'brel ba'i phyir mchod pa'i rkyen sbyor bar mdzad /
NK128(nyo)001:11434: snga 'gyur gyi sde rigs rnying pa rnams kyang dar rgyas su 'gro ba'i thugs rje chen pos bskyangs /
NK128(nyo)001:11435: so zur gnubs rigs sprul ba'i gter ston rnams kyi
NK128(nyo)001:11436: brgyud 'dzin gyi ming tsam 'dzin pa rnams kyang sbyin
NK128(nyo)001:11437: pa rnam pa bzhis skyong zhig phan par 'doms pa
NK128(nyo)001:11438: sogs u rgyan rdo rje 'chang pad+ma 'byung gnas brgyud
NK128(nyo)001:11439: par bcas pa'i ring lugs snga 'gyur kho na'i dus
NK128(nyo)001:11440: la 'gran bzod par bla nas blar 'degs pa'i thugs
NK128(nyo)001:11441: rje rmad du byung ba'i skabs su gyur pas /
NK128(nyo)001:11442: bdag gi bla ma dam pa 'di nyid kyang rigs rus kyis mtho ba /
NK128(nyo)001:11443: gsan rgya che la phyag bzhes mkhas pa /
NK128(nyo)001:11445: lung rtogs kyi yon tan du ma'i bdag nyid du gzigs nas yongs 'dzin du bzhes te /
NK128(nyo)001:11446: bka' ma mdo sgyu sems gsum zhes yongs su grags pa las /
NK128(nyo)001:11447: 'dus pa chen po'i mdo'i dbang cha lag dang bcas pa /
NK128(nyo)001:11448: sgyu 'phrul zhi khro tshe gsum rgyud bshad lung man ngag /
NK128(nyo)001:11449: sems phyogs rdzogs pa chen po bka' gter /
NK128(nyo)001:11450: khyad par nyang chos dbang gi zab gter las byung
NK128(nyo)001:11451: ba rnams kyis thog drangs rnying ma bka' gter gyi
NK128(nyo)001:11452: gdams pa rgya mtsho bsam gyis mi khyab pa dang
NK128(nyo)001:11453: / gzhan yang rgyal ba'i bka' 'gyur rin po ches
NK128(nyo)001:11454: thogs drangs gsar rnying gi lung man ngag mtha' dag
NK128(nyo)001:11455: / legs par gsan / bla ma dam pa 'dis
NK128(nyo)001:11456: kyang rgyal dbang mchog las bsnyen pa rdzogs pa bskyar
NK128(nyo)001:11458: gsar rnying gi zab pa dang rgya che ba'i dam pa'i chos bka' drin mang du gsan /
NK128(nyo)001:11459: 'dren pa mchog gi rigs bdag tu gyur pa'i bdag
NK128(nyo)001:11460: rkyen la brten nas yongs 'dzin yang mang du brten
NK128(nyo)001:11461: par mdzad de / chos rgyal gter bdag gling pa las nyid kyii zab gter skor sogs 'ga' zhig /
NK128(nyo)001:11462: stag lung zhabs drung ngag dbang bkra shis dpal grub
NK128(nyo)001:11463: las rig 'dzin rje'i gter gsar 'khor ba dbyings sgrol
NK128(nyo)001:11464: sogs / dpal ri sprul sku rin po che ngag
NK128(nyo)001:11465: dbang pad+ma 'phrin las la dgongs pa yang zab dang
NK128(nyo)001:11466: 'phreng po gter ston gyi skor sogs du ma /
NK128(nyo)001:11467: zhwa lu mkhan chen bsod nams mchog grub la rtsa gsum dril sgrub /
NK128(nyo)001:11468: bla ma dam pa mngon dga' rab 'byams par bde
NK128(nyo)001:11469: mchog bde chen ral gcig skor rig 'dzin rje nas
NK128(nyo)001:11470: brgyud pa dang rgyud 'bum sogs mang ba /
NK128(nyo)001:11471: gling stod mkhan chen sems dpa' chen po dkon chog
NK128(nyo)001:11472: dpal 'byor la 'od dpag med kyi nyal sgom dang
NK128(nyo)001:11473: chos rgyal byang pa'i gsung dur khrod bdag po'i skor
NK128(nyo)001:11474: / nyang gi gdung tha ma smra bo lcog pa
NK128(nyo)001:11475: mnga' bdag bstan 'dzin chos dbang las drag dmar bde
NK128(nyo)001:11476: 'dus kyi snang srid lha 'dre'i srog dbang dang lung
NK128(nyo)001:11477: / thor bu / se ston legs grub tshe ring
NK128(nyo)001:11478: las sgyu 'phrul skor dang gshin rje gdong drug sogs
NK128(nyo)001:11479: / thor bu / / bkra bzang rig 'dzin se
NK128(nyo)001:11480: ston thugs mchog 'od 'bar las byang gter dang chu
NK128(nyo)001:11482: zur rigs ngag dbang phun tshogs las byang gter dang tshe bstan rgyal mtshan /
NK128(nyo)001:11483: rin cen gling pa sogs bka' gter gyi chos skor mang ba /
NK128(nyo)001:11484: bla ma dkon cog lhun grub la 'bri gung brgyud pa'i drags sngags 'ga' zhig /
NK128(nyo)001:11485: rat+na'i gdung e chos rje spel lcog par rat+na'i gter skor /
NK128(nyo)001:11486: rje bka' 'gyur ba chen po'i mchod dpon 'jam dbyangs
NK128(nyo)001:11487: rgyal mtshan las jo bo lugs kyi dzam dkar sogs
NK128(nyo)001:11488: / gzhan yang gsar rnying gi dbang lung man ngag rgyun dkon pa bzhugs nges pa'i dge slong /
NK128(nyo)001:11489: sgom chen bya bral ba ku s+aa li du ma las zab chos ci rigs gsan te /
NK128(nyo)001:11490: khyab bdag rgyal dbang mchog gi dgongs pa'i dkyil 'khor gang bar mdzad /
NK128(nyo)001:11491: gzhan yang gdan sa thel bsam gdengs mgon khang shin
NK128(nyo)001:11492: tu gnyan pa'i zhig gsos skabs sa skya'i zhal gyi
NK128(nyo)001:11493: gter sgrom sus kyang ma rnyed par dam pa 'dis
NK128(nyo)001:11494: gtor bsngosa mdzad pas bya rog gis mchu btsugs te
NK128(nyo)001:11495: bstan pa dang / gong dkar chos sder bzhugs skabs mi ma yin gyi mchod pa'i ltas dang /
NK128(nyo)001:11496: pho brang chen po po ta lar phebs lam ljongs su sgrol dkar gyi zhal gzigs pa dang /
NK128(nyo)001:11497: rgyal dbang mchog gi sku rim bsgrub tshul li byin ha ras lung bstan pa dang /
NK128(nyo)001:11498: gong ra'i mchod g.yog gis sku srog la rgol bar
NK128(nyo)001:11499: brtsams pa'i tshe chos skyong gis dngos su bsgral ba
NK128(nyo)001:11500: dang bcas pa'i ngo mtshar du ma 'dug pa rnam
NK128(nyo)001:11502: gzhan don gnang ba'i slob ma 'phel tshul yang /
NK128(nyo)001:11504: khyab bdag rdo rje 'chang mgon po bsod nams mchog ldan /
NK128(nyo)001:11505: gong ra lo chen gzhan phan rdo rje /
NK128(nyo)001:11506: gter ston rig 'dzin chen po 'gyur med rdo rje /
NK128(nyo)001:11508: dpal ri sprul sku rin po che /
NK128(nyo)001:11510: zhwa lu mkhan chen bsod nams mchog grub sogs bla mar gyur pa 'ga' zhig dang /
NK128(nyo)001:11511: slob ma'i rigs lha gzigs phag mo grub pa yab
NK128(nyo)001:11512: sras sgrol ma sbug pa'i gdung brgyud 'od mchog sprul
NK128(nyo)001:11513: pa'i sku / chos dbang gdung brgyud nyang stod kha mo nas /
NK128(nyo)001:11514: de srid sna dkar rtse pa khri dpon zil gnon dbang rgyal rdo rje /
NK128(nyo)001:11515: sprul sku karma nor bu sogs che btsun mkhas grub du ma dang /
NK128(nyo)001:11516: bdag sogs thub bstan e wam lcog rgar ba'i 'dus
NK128(nyo)001:11517: tshogs sogs 'dus pa'i sde mang por yang dbang chos
NK128(nyo)001:11518: stsal / rgyal dbang mchog gi ti sh+r+air bkur ba'i sman yon gyis /
NK128(nyo)001:11519: gtsang rong gong ra dang ri lung sbug /
NK128(nyo)001:11520: chu bo ri tshe chu sgrub sde sogs dgon gnas
NK128(nyo)001:11521: mchod thebs mang po gsar du chod cing 'dus pa'i
NK128(nyo)001:11522: de tshugs pa'i kun dga' ra ba dri'i gtsang khang
NK128(nyo)001:11523: / sku gsung thugs rten bzhengs pa sogs bya ba las kyi 'khor lo yang du ma mdzad /
NK128(nyo)001:11524: gtso bor phyi ltar so so thar pa'i bslab bya
NK128(nyo)001:11525: lhag pa tshul khrims kyi bslab bya la thugs rgyud
NK128(nyo)001:11527: sdom pa gsum ka'i nyams len lhag pa shes rab kyi bslab pa dang /
NK128(nyo)001:11528: lhag pa ting nge 'dzin gyi bslab pa dang yang
NK128(nyo)001:11529: dag par ldan bskyed rdzogs kyi bzlas sgom chu bo'i
NK128(nyo)001:11531: 'khor yug 'od gsal chen po la bzla /
NK128(nyo)001:11532: 'phrin las rnam bzhi'i sgo nas bstan 'gro'i don bsgrub
NK128(nyo)001:11533: pa'i gtso bo rgyal dbang mchog gi sku'i rim gro
NK128(nyo)001:11534: nas nye bar bzung mchog dman kun gyi re bskong
NK128(nyo)001:11535: bar mdzad / bshad sgrub 'chad nyan kho nas dus
NK128(nyo)001:11536: 'da' bas rje 'di'i slob rgyun bzang la mang bas
NK128(nyo)001:11537: bar mdzad / kun tu khyab / zhabs drung du
NK128(nyo)001:11538: bsdad na nyin re la yang blo bskyed dang go
NK128(nyo)001:11539: ba bsam gyis mi khyab pa sgo du ma nas
NK128(nyo)001:11540: 'byung ba sogs gdul bya bkri ba'i thabs la mkhas
NK128(nyo)001:11541: bar mdzad / kun tu khyab / / mdo sngags
NK128(nyo)001:11542: gsar rnying gi dbang lung man ngag gang gnang yang
NK128(nyo)001:11543: 'di kho na las mkhas so snyam pa 'byung /
NK128(nyo)001:11544: legs bshad rtsom pa'i tshul yang /
NK128(nyo)001:11548: bka' brgyud yongs rdzogs kyi sgrub khog rnam bshad 'phrin las rab rgyas gu ru'i dgongs rgyan /
NK128(nyo)001:11549: las bzhi'i sbyin sreg ma 'dres yongs rdzogs sogs rang
NK128(nyo)001:11550: lugs la shin tu mkho che ba du ma dang
NK128(nyo)001:11551: / gur mgon gyi rjes gnang sogs gzhan lugs 'ga' zhig /
NK128(nyo)001:11552: sum rtags kyi 'grel bshad zung 'jug yid kyi shing rta /
NK128(nyo)001:11553: snyan ngag dka' 'grel dbyangs can bzhad pa'i rol mtsho sogs du ma /
NK128(nyo)001:11554: rtsod yig gi skor yang gsung snyan rin po che'i dris lan kun bzang dgongs rgyan /
NK128(nyo)001:11555: nang so 'jam dbyangs pa'i rtsod lan byis pa rgan po'i rlung sman sogs dang /
NK128(nyo)001:11556: gzhan yang chab shog gi rigs sogs du ma yod pa rnam thar dang bka' 'bum du gsal /
NK128(nyo)001:11557: de ltar dngos kyi zhing 'dir bstan 'gro'i don mtha'
NK128(nyo)001:11558: yas pa mdzad zin nas zhing khams gzhan du 'gro
NK128(nyo)001:11559: don rgya che ba la dgongs te lcags phag zla
NK128(nyo)001:11560: ba lnga pa nas sku khams cung zhig snyung tshul
NK128(nyo)001:11561: bstan par sku rim sgo du ma nas bsgrubs shing
NK128(nyo)001:11562: / nges gsang rdo rje gling pa spyi tshogs kyis
NK128(nyo)001:11563: gdan bzhugs phul ba'i gsol 'debs tshigs bcad dgos zhus
NK128(nyo)001:11564: / par / pad 'byung rgyal ba rgya mtsho'i byin rlabs las /
NK128(nyo)001:11565: blo gros mchog gi dgongs pa mi 'gyur zhing //
NK128(nyo)001:11566: gsol 'debs slob bu'i sgo gsum byin gyis rlobs //
NK128(nyo)001:11567: dbyer med ka dag chen por yongs grol shog /
NK128(nyo)001:11569: tshes bco lnga'i nyin nam mkha' sum phrugs kyi dgongs
NK128(nyo)001:11570: pa'i lta gdengs dang bcas te rong ri lung sbug
NK128(nyo)001:11571: tu 'od gsal chos sku chen po mngon du mdzad
NK128(nyo)001:11572: de dgongs pa chos kyi dbyings su thim pa'i tshul
NK128(nyo)001:11573: bstan no // de'i tshe nam mkha' 'ja' sprin gyis
NK128(nyo)001:11574: gtibs pa sogs ngo mtshar ba'i ltas dag kyang rnam
NK128(nyo)001:11576: snga sor zhing du ma phebs dus kyang rgan po
NK128(nyo)001:11577: lnga ba'i lam du gyur na grwa phrug mis bdag
NK128(nyo)001:11578: byed la khad lta bu 'di rnams khyod kyis skyong
NK128(nyo)001:11579: dgos so zhes bka' shog dang dngos kyi gsung du
NK128(nyo)001:11580: mar stsal ba'i smon lam kyi stobs las /
NK128(nyo)001:11581: thugs dam dgongs pa'i gsal 'debs su bdag la 'gro
NK128(nyo)001:11582: dgos tshul rgyal dbang mchog gi bka' shog spyi bor
NK128(nyo)001:11583: lhungs ma thag / dbyar dus kyi chu 'phrang bgrod
NK128(nyo)001:11584: par dka' ba du ma brgal te rtsal mchog dang
NK128(nyo)001:11585: dbyer ma mchis pa'i gdan sa ri lung sbug tu
NK128(nyo)001:11586: sku gdung rin po cher mgo bos gtugs pa'i smon
NK128(nyo)001:11587: lam dang phyag mchod du ma phul /
NK128(nyo)001:11588: nges gsang ba'i gdung chog pa rnams dang sbrags bla
NK128(nyo)001:11589: ma gsang 'dus dang bka' brgyad yongs rdzogs dong sprug
NK128(nyo)001:11590: dang bcas pa'i cho ga 'ga' zhig btang /
NK128(nyo)001:11591: thugs rje chen po 'khor ba dbyings sgrol la brten pa'i thugs dam gsal 'debs dang /
NK128(nyo)001:11592: bla ma gsang ba 'dus pa'i dkyil 'khor sgrub mchod
NK128(nyo)001:11593: la brten nas sku gdung rin po che dbang zhing
NK128(nyo)001:11594: / bla ma dkyil 'khor gyi gtso bor bltas te
NK128(nyo)001:11595: mchod 'bul gsol 'debs dbang bzhi blangs dang rten 'gang
NK128(nyo)001:11596: che ba zhig slong 'dod kyang shul na mchis pa'i
NK128(nyo)001:11597: grwa slob rnams ru sprod kyi mgo tshugs 'dug pas
NK128(nyo)001:11598: lam ma nus par rgyun bzhes kyi tsan dan bzhes
NK128(nyo)001:11599: zhal tsam zhig dad pa'i rten du bzung /
NK128(nyo)001:11600: bla ma de nyid kyi rdo rje'i gsung rnams yid
NK128(nyo)001:11601: la bzhag ste grwa rigs rnams la tshogs gtam phul
NK128(nyo)001:11603: phyis kho rang dpon slob dus zing cher langs dus
NK128(nyo)001:11604: kyang dbus gtsang gnyis kar bang phyin ched kyis basngagasa
NK128(nyo)001:11606: phyogs mthong zhig ma gtogs gsan mkhan ma byung bas
NK128(nyo)001:11607: bla ma dam pa yid la dran pa'i gsos su
NK128(nyo)001:11608: gyur te mos gus kyi mchi ma khog par 'phrul
NK128(nyo)001:11609: zhing bsdad / de ltar bla ma dam pa de
NK128(nyo)001:11610: nyid zhing du phebs nas sku gdung zhugs 'bul mdzad
NK128(nyo)001:11611: srol yab mes kyi rgyun la med pas /
NK128(nyo)001:11612: 'gro 'dren rgyal dbang mchog gi thugs rje las gser
NK128(nyo)001:11613: dngul las grub pa'i byang chen mchod rten bzhengs pa'i
NK128(nyo)001:11614: nang du sku gdung ril po gcig tu gyur te
NK128(nyo)001:11615: bstan 'gro'i bsod nams kyi zhing du bzhugs so //
NK128(nyo)001:11616: nyang rigs gdung las u rgyan rdo rje 'chang //
NK128(nyo)001:11617: mkhas grub ngur smrig 'dzin pa'i rdzu bag gis //
NK128(nyo)001:11618: bdag sogs 'gro ba'i 'dren par rab byon pa //
NK128(nyo)001:11619: blo mchog rig pa'i rdo rjer lan brgyar 'dud //
NK128(nyo)001:11620: sras bcas rgyal ba'i mkhyen brtse nus pa kun //
NK128(nyo)001:11621: gcig bsdus dkyil 'khor rgya mtsho'i khyab bdag mchog /
NK128(nyo)001:11622: rab mthong blo gros mchog gi rdo rje yi //
NK128(nyo)001:11623: zhal dkyil bdag gi yid la yang yang dran //
NK128(nyo)001:11624: mgon po khyod kyi drin gyis legs bskyangs te //
NK128(nyo)001:11625: nan tan rjes su gdams pa'i snga gyur chos //
NK128(nyo)001:11626: bka' gter thos bsam sgom dang nyan bshad la //
NK128(nyo)001:11627: brtson 'dis khyod dgongs rab rdzogs rjes 'dzin shog /
NK128(nyo)001:11628: ces pa gsol 'debs kyi dbyangs su bsnyad do //
NK128(nyo)001:11629: de ltar bla ma dam pa de nyid kyis bdag rjes su bzung ba yin la /
NK128(nyo)001:11630: kho bo'i rtogs pa ni bris kyang ngal ba tsam du zad mod /
NK128(nyo)001:11631: 'on kyang phyis chos rgyun 'dzin pa rnams kyis brgyud pa ngos zin pa'i phyir phyogs tsam 'dri na /
NK128(nyo)001:11632: skye yul g.yon ru'i cha mon mkhar rnam sras gling
NK128(nyo)001:11633: du bya nag gi rigs las pha karma phun tshogs
NK128(nyo)001:11634: dbang po dang / 'brug smon kun legs kyi rigs
NK128(nyo)001:11635: las ma rig 'dzin bu khrid dbang mo gnyis kyi
NK128(nyo)001:11636: bur lcags sbrul hor zla gsum pa'i tshes brgyad rgyal
NK128(nyo)001:11637: phur gyi 'grub sbyor yod pa'i nyi shar la skyes
NK128(nyo)001:11638: dbang po dang / shing / rig 'dzin yol mo ba chen po bzhugs pa dang 'grig ste /
NK128(nyo)001:11639: karma tshe dbang phun tshogs su ming btags shing byin gyis brlabs /
NK128(nyo)001:11640: tshe dbang sogs stsal legs ldan zhabs kyi yang srid
NK128(nyo)001:11641: byang ba rig 'dzin ngag gi dbang po'i skye bar
NK128(nyo)001:11642: sgro btags kyi rang lo drug par thub bstan rdo
NK128(nyo)001:11644: 'gro ba'i bla ma thams cad mkhyen pa chen po
NK128(nyo)001:11645: chog bsgrigs grub nas blo bzang rgya mtsho'i sder skra
NK128(nyo)001:11646: phud phul zhing blo bzang pad+ma 'phrin las theg mchog
NK128(nyo)001:11647: dbang gi rgyal po yongs 'dus sde zhes pa'i ming
NK128(nyo)001:11648: dang / phyis mdo dbang tshar lnga tsam bskur zhing
NK128(nyo)001:11649: chog bsgrigs grub nas kun tu bzang po'i rgyal tshab
NK128(nyo)001:11650: kyi rten 'brel du kun bzang pad+ma phrin las zhes
NK128(nyo)001:11651: dang / bsgyur ba gnang / dge bsnyen gyi sdom pa /
NK128(nyo)001:11652: gsol 'debs le'u bdun ma sogs kyi ljags lung stsal
NK128(nyo)001:11653: te rjes su bzung rigs kun bdag po zur chen
NK128(nyo)001:11654: rdo rje 'chang chos dbyings rang grol gyis smin grol
NK128(nyo)001:11655: gdams pa rgya mtsho rim bzhin gnang /
NK128(nyo)001:11656: rang lo bcu gnyis par kun mkhyen rgyal ba'i dbang
NK128(nyo)001:11657: po shar phyogs rgya nag gi yul du gong ma
NK128(nyo)001:11658: chen po'i mchod yul du spyan drangs pa'i skabs gong
NK128(nyo)001:11659: dkar rdo rje gdan gyi chos grags rdo rje 'chang
NK128(nyo)001:11660: bka' 'gyur ba chen po mgon po bsod nams mchog
NK128(nyo)001:11661: ldan las bka' 'gyur rin po che'i lung rdzogs par
NK128(nyo)001:11662: nyan cing / dge bsnyen dang bar ma rab byung
NK128(nyo)001:11663: nas dge tshul gyi bar du bsgrubs pa'i ming pad+ma
NK128(nyo)001:11665: gzhan yang dpal sa skya pa khri chen kun dga' bsod nams lha sar phebs pa dang mjal zhing /
NK128(nyo)001:11666: gur lha gsum ma'i rjes gnang dang gsol btab la
NK128(nyo)001:11667: ma ltos par kun dga' pad+ma dbang rgyal zhes 'dogs
NK128(nyo)001:11668: par mdzad / phyis sras ngag dbang bsod nams dbang
NK128(nyo)001:11669: phyug yab sras la bdag med lha mo bco lnga
NK128(nyo)001:11670: par mdzad / sogs nos / rgyal ba 'bri gung
NK128(nyo)001:11671: pa chos kyi grags par 'char ka yang zlog sogs
NK128(nyo)001:11672: par mdzad / sogs nos / nos / phyis 'bri
NK128(nyo)001:11673: gung sprul sku ngag dbang chos grags bzang por yang
NK128(nyo)001:11675: gzhan yang dgyes mdzad rdo rje 'chang dkon cog dpal 'byor /
NK128(nyo)001:11677: sgom smyon phyag rdor nor bu /
NK128(nyo)001:11678: kong bo snyi phu ba karma rig 'dzin dbang po /
NK128(nyo)001:11679: gter ston rig 'dzin chen po 'gyur med rdo rje /
NK128(nyo)001:11680: thugs sras sprul sku bstan 'dzin 'gyur med rdo rje /
NK128(nyo)001:11683: brag dkar ba byams pa rin chen chos 'phel /
NK128(nyo)001:11684: rab 'byams chos rje rin chen rgya mtsho /
NK128(nyo)001:11685: grub mchog dge slong ye shes phun tshogs sogs bshes
NK128(nyo)001:11686: gnyen mang po gus pa gsum gyis bsten nas gsar
NK128(nyo)001:11687: rnying gi dam chos mang du nos /
NK128(nyo)001:11688: rang lo bcu drug par kung thang du khyab bdag
NK128(nyo)001:11689: zur chen rdo rje 'chang las rdzogs chen gyi ngo
NK128(nyo)001:11692: bcu dgu par ma'i mngal lo rtsis pa'i nyes med phun tshogs yong rtsis kyi /
NK128(nyo)001:11693: mkhan po thams cad mkhyen pa don gyi slad du
NK128(nyo)001:11694: mtshan nas smos na ngag dbang blo bzang rgya mtsho'i
NK128(nyo)001:11695: zhabs drung du bsnyen par rdzogs shing dge tshul phan
NK128(nyo)001:11696: chad bskyar mi dgos gsungs te bsnyen rdzogs kho na
NK128(nyo)001:11697: gnang / slar yang rang lo so brgyad par rnam
NK128(nyo)001:11698: par dag pa'i sdom rgyun las mkhan po de nyid
NK128(nyo)001:11699: kyi drung du tshul gsum rim can du nos /
NK128(nyo)001:11700: yongs 'dzin rdo rje 'chang 'di nyid la snga phyir
NK128(nyo)001:11701: chos kyi bka' drin gzhal du med par thob cing
NK128(nyo)001:11702: / tshe rabs kyi bla ma nges par thob pas
NK128(nyo)001:11703: yongs 'dzin rnams kyi nang nas mchog tu gyur pa'o
NK128(nyo)001:11704: / // de yang rang lo bcu drug par sgrags yang rdzong du mtshams shig la yod skabs /
NK128(nyo)001:11705: rdo rje 'chang mgon po'i mtshan can gyi bka' shog
NK128(nyo)001:11706: cig phebs par mdo dbang dkyil 'khor drug cu re
NK128(nyo)001:11707: lnga'i smin byed nos pa nyid rang la 'bul rgyu
NK128(nyo)001:11710: kho bo rang la stsol ba'i dgongs gtad khyab bdag
NK128(nyo)001:11711: sman lung pa chen por khu lung gzhes kar gsan
NK128(nyo)001:11713: khoo bo sngon las kyi bla gzugs 'dzin dgos pa'i
NK128(nyo)001:11714: rnam g.yeng kho na'i dbang gis zhu ma thub par
NK128(nyo)001:11715: / bla ma rdo rje 'chang de nyid mkha' spyod
NK128(nyo)001:11716: du grub mtha' snyogs te gshegs khar yang zhabs 'bring
NK128(nyo)001:11717: pa byams pa lags la rdo rje brag tu mdo
NK128(nyo)001:11718: dbang 'bul ma thub pa 'di sems kyi lhag mar
NK128(nyo)001:11719: / byung / zhes gsungs pa thos pas yid mchog tu skyo bar gyur pa zhig byung /
NK128(nyo)001:11720: 'on kyang rgyal dbang thams cad mkhyen pa chen po'i
NK128(nyo)001:11721: tshad med pa'i thugs rje'i mthu las mdo dbang thob
NK128(nyo)001:11722: pa yin te / 'bras spungs su phyin dus shig
NK128(nyo)001:11723: khyab bdag sman lung pa chen po rgyal po rgyal
NK128(nyo)001:11724: dbang mchog gi zhabs drung du phebs 'dug pa thog
NK128(nyo)001:11725: mar mjal yang dad mi dad dang chos zhu ba'i
NK128(nyo)001:11726: snang ba sogs gang yang ma byung rung /
NK128(nyo)001:11727: pho brang chen po po ta lar phebs 'dug pa'i
NK128(nyo)001:11728: tshe nged kyang zhabs drung du 'byor ba dang 'grig
NK128(nyo)001:11729: pa'i rgyal dbang mchog gi bka' las mdo dbang zhus
NK128(nyo)001:11730: pa 'gab tshul gyi bslab ston bzhin snyan gsan phab
NK128(nyo)001:11732: slar dus tshes nges pa can du bsgrigs nas rang
NK128(nyo)001:11733: lo nyer bzhi bar rigs brgya'i khyab bdag sman lung
NK128(nyo)001:11734: pa de nyid rang gnas thub bstan rdo rje brag
NK128(nyo)001:11736: phebs nyin rang sgo 'byed phyag rdor gyi dbang gnang zhing /
NK128(nyo)001:11737: de nas rim par rtsal ba'i tshogs chen 'dus pa'i
NK128(nyo)001:11738: sa gzung gi tshe bla ma dam pa nyid kyis
NK128(nyo)001:11739: gsang phod dang thang zhu sogs chas su zhugs nas
NK128(nyo)001:11740: rdo rje dril bu dang yungs kar rgyang zhags bsnams
NK128(nyo)001:11741: te bgegs bskrad pa'i mthar rdo rje'i 'gros mdzad skabs
NK128(nyo)001:11742: rkang mthil gnyis su sna tshogs rdo rje 'bar ba
NK128(nyo)001:11743: re res mtshan par gyur h'u h'u zhes gsungs shing
NK128(nyo)001:11744: khro bo'i stang stabs dang sdang mig tu gzigs pa
NK128(nyo)001:11745: tsam gyis zil chen po bzod par mi nus pa
NK128(nyo)001:11747: bla ma dam pa de nyid bcom ldan 'das zhe
NK128(nyo)001:11748: sdang rdo rje dngos yin snyams pa lta bu'i dad
NK128(nyo)001:11749: gus skyes te 'ur shogs byed nas lha dngos su
NK128(nyo)001:11750: mthong ba yin byas kyang chog pa tsam du yod
NK128(nyo)001:11751: / de nas bzung ste mos pa je 'phel du song /
NK128(nyo)001:11752: ci mdzad thams cad legs shing gang ltar mdzad kyang
NK128(nyo)001:11753: ye shes kyi rol pa las mi 'da' bar nges
NK128(nyo)001:11755: tshogs chen gyi rig 'dzin bla ma'i dbang gi skabs
NK128(nyo)001:11756: brgyud pa dngos la mi bzhugs kyang ngo mtshar brgyud
NK128(nyo)001:11757: par 'jam dbyangs mkhyen brtse khu dbon gnyis brjod par
NK128(nyo)001:11758: mdzad / rje nyid rang la bka' drin che ba'i dbang gis /
NK128(nyo)001:11759: kun 'dus rtsa ba'i rtsa ma mchog /
NK128(nyo)001:11761: sgo gsum zhabs tog ma 'grub kyang //
NK128(nyo)001:11762: byin brlabs mtshan ma yang yang mthong //
NK128(nyo)001:11763: nges shes mos gus gting nas skyes //
NK128(nyo)001:11764: bzhugs ni bdag gi spyi bor bzhugs //
NK128(nyo)001:11765: gsang mtshan karma dbang drag rtsal //
