NK128(nyo)001:11766: zhes kyang yig chung du btab nas dbang gnang skabs
NK128(nyo)001:11767: gsung ba'i tshe spyan chab kyis brnangs te bzhugs pa
NK128(nyo)001:11768: mthong bas rang yang mchi ma mang po shor zhing
NK128(nyo)001:11769: ji tsam bsran yang mi bzod pa lta bur gyur
NK128(nyo)001:11770: / de ltar 'dus pa chen po'i dbang yongs su
NK128(nyo)001:11771: rdzogs par mdo mgon gyi bka' gtad bar rgyas par
NK128(nyo)001:11772: / gnang zhing / gsang ming rdo rje bdud 'joms rtsal du 'dogs par mdzad /
NK128(nyo)001:11773: gtad rgya'i tshe bka' las shing nya gro d+ha zhes
NK128(nyo)001:11774: bya ba sa bon shin tu phra ba zhig btab
NK128(nyo)001:11775: pas 'bras bu ljon pa'i shing chen po yal gas
NK128(nyo)001:11776: phyogs kun tu khyab pa zhig tu 'gyur ba'i dpe
NK128(nyo)001:11777: bzhin / rgad po'i mdo dbang gi sa bon chung
NK128(nyo)001:11778: ngu 'di khyod kyi rgya cher spel zhing rgyas par
NK128(nyo)001:11779: bgyid dgos zhes gsungs pa yid la bcags par gyur
NK128(nyo)001:11780: te chos 'di'i phyogs su thos bsam sgom pa dang
NK128(nyo)001:11781: 'chad nyan rgya cher bgyid pa'i dam bca' phul bas
NK128(nyo)001:11782: bzhin / / bla ma mchog kyang dgyes par gyur /
NK128(nyo)001:11783: rang lo nyer lnga bar gtan gyi skyabs gnas rgyal
NK128(nyo)001:11784: dbang rdo rje 'chang chen pos chog sgrigs shig bri
NK128(nyo)001:11785: dgos tshul gyi bka' stsal phebs pa ltar bri bar
NK128(nyo)001:11786: brtsams / 'on kyang thos bsam ma rdzogs pas dgos pa mang zhing bri bde bar ma gyur pas /
NK128(nyo)001:11787: rang lo nyer drug par slar yang khyab bdag sman
NK128(nyo)001:11788: lung pa chen po rang gnas su spyan drangs te
NK128(nyo)001:11789: sgyu 'phrul zhi khro'i dkyil 'khor du smin byed kyi
NK128(nyo)001:11790: dbang dang mdo dbang gi phyag bzhes phra zhib sa
NK128(nyo)001:11791: chog gi stang stabs tshun chad legs par zhus /
NK128(nyo)001:11792: snga sor dbang gi dus yig rnying gi lung rnams 'ga' zhig lus pa yang tshang bar zhus te /
NK128(nyo)001:11793: de'i tshe dka' gnad kyi zhib cha dang /
NK128(nyo)001:11794: kahthoga lugs kyi glegs bam sogs lag tu 'jog pa gnang zhing /
NK128(nyo)001:11795: rgan po lnga par ma gyur gong du chog sgrigs
NK128(nyo)001:11796: bris tshar ba zhig gyis zhes nan gyis bka' stsal
NK128(nyo)001:11797: pa ltar bri bar byas kyang rnam g.yeng sna tshogs
NK128(nyo)001:11798: kyi dbang las btang snyoms su lus pa'i tshe /
NK128(nyo)001:11799: dad 'dus 'ga' zhig la mdo dbang byed dgos byung
NK128(nyo)001:11800: bas khyab bdag bla ma gtsang na bzhugs par tsaka
NK128(nyo)001:11801: li g.yar po zhu ba sogs bya ma rta ched
NK128(nyo)001:11802: btang ba'i tshe / nyer mkho'i phyag dpe mang po
NK128(nyo)001:11803: dang tsaka li bcas bka' shog rin po che 'di
NK128(nyo)001:11804: btang ba'i tshe / ltar phebs te / der snying
NK128(nyo)001:11805: phu sku skye sogs dad 'dus rnams la theg pa
NK128(nyo)001:11806: yongs kyi dbang rgyun bka' drin bskyangs rtsis de bzhin
NK128(nyo)001:11807: la thal mo snying gar zum ste rjes su yi
NK128(nyo)001:11808: btang ba'i tshe / ltar phebs te / rangs 'bul
NK128(nyo)001:11809: / mdor na nga rang la gang yod rnams bstan
NK128(nyo)001:11810: pa'i bdag po la mi 'bul na ci byed lta
NK128(nyo)001:11811: btang ba'i tshe / ltar phebs te / rangs 'bul
NK128(nyo)001:11812: / bur 'dug / sngar dbang lung phul ba rnams
NK128(nyo)001:11813: lta ci smos dpe rgyun phul ba rnams kyi yang
NK128(nyo)001:11814: legs bshad bsdu ba gnang 'os rnams kyang bsdu ba
NK128(nyo)001:11815: bka' gnang du gsol snyam du bla ma yi dam
NK128(nyo)001:11816: bka' srung rnams la gsol ba btab nas rjes su
NK128(nyo)001:11817: gnang ba phul ba yin no //
NK128(nyo)001:11818: zhes pa'i bka' shog kyang phebs /
NK128(nyo)001:11819: de nas kyang re zhig nas chog khrigs tshar yod
NK128(nyo)001:11820: dam dgongs pa'i rting bskul du bka' shog 'di ltar
NK128(nyo)001:11821: byung ste / mdo dbang chog khrigs gsar du bzhad
NK128(nyo)001:11822: pa de lag 'thong byung tshe zhu mi btang bas
NK128(nyo)001:11823: myur du grub pa dgos zhes phebs /
NK128(nyo)001:11824: sprel lo rang gnas su spyan drangs te bka' brgyad
NK128(nyo)001:11825: gsang ba yongs rdzogs kyi sman sgrub chen mo dang
NK128(nyo)001:11826: 'brel bar smin byed kyi dbang rgyas pa dang lung
NK128(nyo)001:11828: nyang gi bde gshegs 'dus pa'i dbang bskur chen mo /
NK128(nyo)001:11829: mkha' 'gro gsang ba ye shes kyi dbang /
NK128(nyo)001:11830: chos dbang gi phur pa spu gri /
NK128(nyo)001:11831: nyang gi khros nag sogs du ma zhus /
NK128(nyo)001:11832: ma ning srog dbang snga mo nas yongs rdzogs dkyil
NK128(nyo)001:11833: 'khor dang 'brel ba'i dbang gi dus cis kyang yod
NK128(nyo)001:11834: phebs kyang 'ga' zhig gis bar du bcad de thob
NK128(nyo)001:11836: khyad par gsang rdzogs kyi sman sgrub dbang dang 'brel
NK128(nyo)001:11837: ba'i phyag len zin bris shig bris pa spyan sngar
NK128(nyo)001:11838: bstan pas legs so'i me tog bzang po ci yang
NK128(nyo)001:11839: gtor ba gnang / de nas skabs shig chu bo
NK128(nyo)001:11840: ri nas gzhan don du gshegs par dgongs shing bdag
NK128(nyo)001:11841: la brtse ba'i bka' shog kyang 'di ltar phebs te
NK128(nyo)001:11842: gtor ba gnang / / deng sang ni pak+shu 'dis de phyogs su mi thar ba 'dug /
NK128(nyo)001:11843: de nas ni gtsang du sleb 'gro ba 'dra /
NK128(nyo)001:11844: gang ltar bar srid kyi sngon du lan cig mjal bar smon zhes sogs gnang byung bar yang brten /
NK128(nyo)001:11845: nged chu bo rir gnas 'brel zhig la phyin skabs
NK128(nyo)001:11846: rje bla ma yang bzhugs pa dang 'grigs pas ser
NK128(nyo)001:11847: sbreng sogs kyi thugs g.yeng rgya cher gnang 'dug cing
NK128(nyo)001:11848: / phan tshun dgyes bzhin par mjal yang nged mtshams
NK128(nyo)001:11849: kyi stabs nas snyan rgyud zhag ma'i zhal shes kyi
NK128(nyo)001:11850: lung dang bka' bsgo tsam ma gtogs chos gzhan zhu
NK128(nyo)001:11851: / ma thub / de rjes nged kyi u rgyan phug tu mtshams bcad /
NK128(nyo)001:11852: rje bla ma yar klungs phyogs su phebs /
NK128(nyo)001:11853: nged sdod ring de gar phyir phebs byung bas nged
NK128(nyo)001:11854: kyis kyang mtshams par zhig tu mjal bar phyin pas
NK128(nyo)001:11855: dgyes pa chen pos brtse bas bzung zhing /
NK128(nyo)001:11856: 'di phyir dge ba'i bslab ston mang du gnang /
NK128(nyo)001:11857: nged dpon slob tshe 'dir mjal ba'i rting ma de yin /
NK128(nyo)001:11858: de nas nged kyis sngar bzhin u rgyan phug tu mtshams la bsdad /
NK128(nyo)001:11859: bla ma dam pas re zhig bzhugs te gtsang la
NK128(nyo)001:11860: phebs song ba'i chibs kha bsgyur khar mtshams nang nas
NK128(nyo)001:11861: phebs lam la thugs cag dang skyabs 'jug gnang dgos
NK128(nyo)001:11862: tshul gyi zhu yig cig phul ba'i lan tshigs su
NK128(nyo)001:11863: bcad pa zhig gnang byung bar /
NK128(nyo)001:11864: rgad bu sang nyin snga char 'gro ba la //
NK128(nyo)001:11865: u rgyan thugs rjes gang bskos ma gtogs pa //
NK128(nyo)001:11866: ca gas khyad 'gyur yong ba dka' mod kyang //
NK128(nyo)001:11867: skyabs mgon mchog des lho nub srin yul nas //
NK128(nyo)001:11868: bskyed de bka' 'bangs rgad po'i dgon gog 'di //
NK128(nyo)001:11869: blos ma thongs pa'i gzhis srungs tsho'i 'dzin du //
NK128(nyo)001:11870: mngon sum bzhugs pa'i thugs rje'i spyan rgyang gis //
NK128(nyo)001:11871: nges par skyabs la sol nyi ma mchis snyan //
NK128(nyo)001:11872: sems nyid khyod thugs g.yo med dang bsres nas //
NK128(nyo)001:11873: sgyu lus gog pos re zhig gtsang skor te //
NK128(nyo)001:11874: nag zla'i mjug dang sa ga'i mtshams nyid du //
NK128(nyo)001:11875: nges par shog ces gong gi bka' bcings pa //
NK128(nyo)001:11876: ji bzhin 'od rgya shar ri'i phrag pa nas //
NK128(nyo)001:11877: slar yang 'char bzhin khyod zhal mjal ba dang //
NK128(nyo)001:11878: khyod gsung bdud rtsi 'thung bar smon no kye //
NK128(nyo)001:11879: zhes bya ba'i gsung gi tha ma stsal te snga bar gtsang du thegs pa'i tshe /
NK128(nyo)001:11880: tshe chu sgrub sde'i 'og gi 'phred lam nas nged
NK128(nyo)001:11881: o rgyan phug tu yod par zhal bsgyur te phyag
NK128(nyo)001:11882: zhabs phul la bkab nas yang yang gzigs shing phebs
NK128(nyo)001:11883: song zhes thos pas sems la 'phreng bar gyur /
NK128(nyo)001:11884: de ltar tshigs su bcad pa de yang drang don
NK128(nyo)001:11885: du slar zla ba gsum pa dang bzhi pa'i mtshams
NK128(nyo)001:11886: su po ta lar phebs skabs mjal zhes par 'dug
NK128(nyo)001:11887: kyang / nges don du bdag la brtse bas byin
NK128(nyo)001:11888: gyis brlabs pa'i brdar thugs yid bsre ba'i g.yar dam
NK128(nyo)001:11889: kyang / dang / slar shar phyogs nas sku'i rnam
NK128(nyo)001:11890: sprul 'byung bar dbang lung sogs gyis shig pa'i brda
NK128(nyo)001:11891: kyang / dang / chos su go / de ltar
NK128(nyo)001:11892: bla ma mchog de'i dgongs pa rdzogs thabs dang rgyal
NK128(nyo)001:11893: dbang mchog gi bka' gnang gcig tu byas te spyi
NK128(nyo)001:11894: bor blangs nas 'bad pa chen pos mdo dbang chog
NK128(nyo)001:11895: khrigs gsar du bris pa yin la /
NK128(nyo)001:11896: de yang 'jam dbyangs sa pan gyi rigs gter du /
NK128(nyo)001:11897: gangs ri'i khrod 'dir mkhas pa'i rgyu skar bye ba brgyas /
NK128(nyo)001:11898: dpal ldan grags pa'i gsung rab pad+mo rab phye mod /
NK128(nyo)001:11899: gang blo'i nyi 'od snang bas ma khyab de srid du /
NK128(nyo)001:11900: gzhung lugs dgongs don ge sar snying po gsal ma nus /
NK128(nyo)001:11901: zhes pa ltar bla ma dam pa rnams kyi thugs
NK128(nyo)001:11902: rje dang khyad par 'khor lo'i mgon po sman lung
NK128(nyo)001:11903: pa chen pos lan du mar dbang khrid man ngag
NK128(nyo)001:11904: phyag bzhes mdzub tshugs su gnang zhing ut+pala lta bu'i
NK128(nyo)001:11905: dpe rgyun dkon pa dag kyang mang bar gnang /
NK128(nyo)001:11906: dgongs pas byin gyis brlabs pa sogs kyi mthu las /
NK128(nyo)001:11910: so lugs sogs kyi yig rnying gzhan gyis gsal bar
NK128(nyo)001:11911: ma nus pa'i dka' gnad mtha' dag legs par bkrol
NK128(nyo)001:11912: ba'i chog khrigs dkyil 'khor rgya mtsho'i 'jug ngogs kyi
NK128(nyo)001:11913: rtsom pa mthar phyin pa yang bla ma'i byin rlabs
NK128(nyo)001:11914: bdud rtsi'i zil mngar gyis blo gros kyi bum bzang
NK128(nyo)001:11915: yongs su gtams pa las byung ba yin la /
NK128(nyo)001:11916: de ltar rang lo zhe gcig pa phan la mdo
NK128(nyo)001:11917: dbang tshar lnga song ba sogs bla ma mchog gi
NK128(nyo)001:11918: dgongs pa chos kyi dbyings su rdzogs pa'i rgyur 'gyur
NK128(nyo)001:11919: ram snyam / de las gzhan pa'i kho bo la
NK128(nyo)001:11920: dang por thos bsam dang bar du nyams len mthar
NK128(nyo)001:11921: mar gzhan phan sogs byas tshul gyi rnam thar brir
NK128(nyo)001:11922: rung ba ci yang ma mchis shing /
NK128(nyo)001:11923: za nyal 'chag b+hu su ku'i spyod pas dus 'da'
NK128(nyo)001:11924: bzhin gnas pa 'di kun gyi spyod yul du gyur
NK128(nyo)001:11926: dam pa'i yon tan mtha' yas rin cen tshogs //
NK128(nyo)001:11927: sde legs tshig gi srad bu la brgyus te //
NK128(nyo)001:11928: blo gsal bstan 'dzin tshogs kyi mgul rgyan du //
NK128(nyo)001:11929: ngo mtshar dad pa'i phreng ba 'di na spel //
NK128(nyo)001:11930: brgyud pa gsum ldan rig 'dzin bla ma mchog /
NK128(nyo)001:11931: rgya bod pan grub mu tig phreng ba ltar //
NK128(nyo)001:11932: rim byon rnam par thar pa bgrang yas pa //
NK128(nyo)001:11933: legs bsdus tshig nyung don rgyas tshul gyis bkod //
NK128(nyo)001:11934: 'on te grub pa'i slob dpon re res kyang //
NK128(nyo)001:11935: mdzad phrin mtha' yas gtam gyis sbyor ba rnams //
NK128(nyo)001:11936: ngo mtshar mdzad pa'i pha mtha' mi mngon phyir //
NK128(nyo)001:11937: mtha' dag yi ger 'dri ba su yis nus //
NK128(nyo)001:11938: ha cang rgyas min shin tu bsdus min par //
NK128(nyo)001:11939: rgyas la btus shing bsdus las rgya cher spel //
NK128(nyo)001:11940: grangs nges gdul bya'i snang ba mi 'gal bar //
NK128(nyo)001:11941: gcig tu byas 'di rnam dpyod blo yis bskrun //
NK128(nyo)001:11942: snga 'gyur theg pa mchog gi lam bzang la //
NK128(nyo)001:11943: rten nas rig 'dzin grub pa'i sar gshegs pa //
NK128(nyo)001:11944: khyab bdag rdo rje sems dngos bla ma'i tshogs //
NK128(nyo)001:11945: rtogs pa brjod 'di'i bsod nams bla na med //
NK128(nyo)001:11946: de phyir dus gsum dge tshogs ci yod dang //
NK128(nyo)001:11947: lhan cig 'di brtsams ngal ba'i legs byas kun //
NK128(nyo)001:11948: gcig bsdus mthu yis 'gro kun thamsacada mkhyen //
NK128(nyo)001:11949: kun tu bzang po'i go 'phang thob phyir bsngo //
NK128(nyo)001:11950: phyogs bral rgyal ba'i bstan pa kun tu dar //
NK128(nyo)001:11951: der 'dzin dge ba'i bshes rnams sku tshe brtan //
NK128(nyo)001:11952: 'gro rnams rdzogs ldan dpal gyi bde skyid rgyas //
NK128(nyo)001:11953: phan bde'i dpal la rtag tu spyod gyur cig /
NK128(nyo)001:11954: bdag kyang tshe 'di'i mdun thabs kho na'i ched //
NK128(nyo)001:11955: bzang rdzu'i 'bad pa lhur len bla gzugs kyis //
NK128(nyo)001:11956: rnam g.yeng 'du 'dzi'i khol por mi 'gyur bar //
NK128(nyo)001:11957: dam chos sgrub la bar chod med par shog /
NK128(nyo)001:11958: o rgyan pad+ma rgyal bas nyer bstan pa'i //
NK128(nyo)001:11959: sgrub ri'i mgul nas smin grol lam stegs kyis //
NK128(nyo)001:11960: mtshams sbyar tshe 'adi'isnanga ba nub ma thag /
NK128(nyo)001:11961: mkha' spyod rnga yab dpal rir bder 'gro shog /
NK128(nyo)001:11962: dkar nag bzang ngan 'brel par gyur pa kun //
NK128(nyo)001:11963: rgyal kun ngo bo rig 'dzin pad+ma'i drung //
NK128(nyo)001:11964: grub pa'i gral ring phyir mi ldog pa'i sar //
NK128(nyo)001:11965: nye bkod ma lus 'gro ba'i don 'grub shog /
NK128(nyo)001:11966: sa gsum skye dgu'i legs byas khang bzang rtser //
NK128(nyo)001:11967: thub bstan mdo sngags bstan pa'i rgyal mtshan mchog //
NK128(nyo)001:11968: snga 'gyur yid bzhin dbang gi tog mdzes pa //
NK128(nyo)001:11969: srid mthar mi g.yo dge legs bkra shis shog //
NK128(nyo)001:11970: de ltar 'dus pa mdo dbang gi bla ma brgyud
NK128(nyo)001:11971: pa'i rnam thar ngo mtshar dad pa'i phreng ba zhes
NK128(nyo)001:11973: mdo dkyil dbang gi chog khrigs dkyil 'khor rgya mtsho'i 'jug ngogs kyi rgyab chos su dmigs te /
NK128(nyo)001:11974: thub bstan e wam lcog gi chos smra ba'i dge
NK128(nyo)001:11975: slong bya bral ba pad+ma 'phrin las kyis rang lo
NK128(nyo)001:11976: zhe gcig pa lcags mo bya'i lo dbyar zla ra
NK128(nyo)001:11977: ba s+n+ron gyi zla bas 'go brtsams /
NK128(nyo)001:11978: dbyar 'bring chu stod kyis nya ba'i dbang phyogs bzang
NK128(nyo)001:11979: po dang po'i tshes la yongs su tshang bar 'og
NK128(nyo)001:11980: min bla ma'i gdan sa thub bstan rdo rje brag
NK128(nyo)001:11981: gi yang dben 'chi med pho brang du legs par
NK128(nyo)001:11982: sbyar ba'i yi ge pa ni dge slong sman mchog
NK128(nyo)001:11983: gis bgyis pa phyogs dus kun tu dge zhing bkra
